NK077(tsu)001:1: // mu k+ti ka m+aa la n+aa ma m+aa y+aa pa
NK077(tsu)001:2: tha kra ma n+aam t+ai ka bi ha ra ti
NK077(tsu)001:3: sma //// sgyu 'phrul lam gyi rim pa'i 'grel pa mu tig phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4: na mo rat+na gu ru ye /
NK077(tsu)001:5: ka dag kun bzang gdod nas ye sangs rgyas //
NK077(tsu)001:6: 'khor 'das mnyam nyid gnyis med klong du gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:7: dang po'i sangs rgyas dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK077(tsu)001:8: gsang bdag chen po khyed la mi phyed 'dud //
NK077(tsu)001:9: rgyal sras dbang phyug gsang ba'i bdag po'i sku //
NK077(tsu)001:10: sangs rgyas stong gi bstan pa 'dzin byed cing //
NK077(tsu)001:11: gdul dka' 'dul mdzad phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK077(tsu)001:12: gsang bdag gnyis pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:13: thub pa'i lung bstan o rgyan mkha' 'gro'i gtso //
NK077(tsu)001:14: gsang sngags rgyud sde zab mo'i rgyud 'chang ba //
NK077(tsu)001:15: rin chen mang gi rnam 'phrul thams cad mkhyen //
NK077(tsu)001:16: ku ku ra tsa'i zhabs la rgyal ba'i zhal slob ma 'ongs lung bstan pa //
NK077(tsu)001:17: chos kyi rgyal po nges don rgya mtsho'i bdag /tshe gcig sangs rgyas sa la gshegs mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:18: in tra pu tri'i zhabs la gsung rabs rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i pha rol phyin //
NK077(tsu)001:19: don bcud gsang sngags zab mo'i gnas lugs rtogs //
NK077(tsu)001:20: 'dod yon spang med rnam dag lam du khyer //
NK077(tsu)001:21: sh+aakya pu tri'i zhabs gsung rabs rgya mtsho'i gzhung don khung du chud //
NK077(tsu)001:22: ka dag gnas lugs rang byung 'gyur med rtogs //
NK077(tsu)001:23: sa brgyad non mdzad stobs kyis pha rol phyin //
NK077(tsu)001:24: sa brgyad sems dpa'i zhabs la theg chen rnal 'byor gsang sngags zab mo'i bdag /
NK077(tsu)001:25: bla med rdo rje theg pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK077(tsu)001:26: tshe gcig tshe 'dir rin chen mchog thob pa //
NK077(tsu)001:27: rdo rje yon tan gzungs la yang dag thugs kyi sgor zhugs dngos grub brnyes //
NK077(tsu)001:28: mi 'gyur bde stong dbyer med rdo rje 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:29: zab lam bstan pa'i mnga' bdag chos kyi rje //
NK077(tsu)001:30: grub chen h'u ka ra la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:31: gsang sngags phyi nang chos la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK077(tsu)001:32: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs rnams zhal gzigs nas //
NK077(tsu)001:33: sna tshogs thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:34: pra chen hasti'i zhabs 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyis thugs rjes rjes bzung nas //
NK077(tsu)001:35: phyi nang theg pa'i chos rnams thugs la rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:36: ngo mtshar gzhung dang gdams pa du ma'i gter //
NK077(tsu)001:37: sangs rgyas gsang ba de la 'od dpag med kyi rnam 'phrul 'chi med sku //
NK077(tsu)001:38: d+ha na ko sha'i mtsho gling pad+ma skyes //
NK077(tsu)001:39: sangs rgyas bstan pa rgyas mdzad chos gter bdag /o
NK077(tsu)001:40: rgyan pad+ma'i zhabs pan chen du ma 'tshogs pa'i dbus
NK077(tsu)001:41: na mdzes // rigs pa'i gnas lnga ma lus thugs la rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:42: rgya gar mkhas pa'i mchog gyur b+hi ma la //
NK077(tsu)001:43: dri med bshes gnyen de la lung rigs gsung gi dbang phyug mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:44: pha rol smra ba'i log rtog tshar gcod cing //
NK077(tsu)001:45: zab rgyas chos kyi rgya mtsho bsgyur mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:46: lo tsa rin chen mchog la thub dbang bstan pa rgyu 'bras theg pa la //
NK077(tsu)001:47: ci bzhin ma nor mngon gsum rtogs gyur nas //
NK077(tsu)001:48: zag med dgongs pa mchog la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK077(tsu)001:49: kye re mchog skyong de la rnam dag theg pa'i lung chos thugs la rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:50: gsang sngags zab mo'i bsgrub rgyud bstan pa 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:51: zag med zug 'jug mngon sum snyogs pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:52: rgyal ba'i yon tan zhabs la thub dbang bstan pa'i dpal la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK077(tsu)001:53: mi 'gyur ye shes go 'phang mchog thob nas //
NK077(tsu)001:54: lung chen theg mchog lam la 'god mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:55: ye shes rin chen zhabs la mkhyen rab stong nyid rgya mtsho chen po la //
NK077(tsu)001:56: 'gags med snying rje'i rlabs chen kun tu g.yo //
NK077(tsu)001:57: gsang sngags zab don rin chen 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK077(tsu)001:58: yon tan rgya mtsho'i zhabs la de nyid sku yi sras gyur gsang sngags 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:59: rab 'byams bstan pa'i srog shing mdzod gsum bdag /tshad med thugs rje'i bslab bya gting nas rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:60: ye shes rgya mtsho'i zhabs la gsang sngags zab mo'i gnas lugs khong du chud //
NK077(tsu)001:61: yang phur sman gsum rgyud lung man ngag bcas //
NK077(tsu)001:62: mkhas grub gnyis kyis rgyal rgyud 'dzin mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:63: blo gros byang chub de la sgyu 'phrul theg pa'i chos la dbang thob nas //
NK077(tsu)001:64: nyon mongs ye shes chen po'i lam du khyer //
NK077(tsu)001:65: gsang sngags mnga' brnyes bstan 'dzin chos kyi rje //
NK077(tsu)001:66: sh+aakya 'byung gnas de la bskal mang sngon nas sbyangs pa zhib pa'i mthus //
NK077(tsu)001:67: theg chen gsang sngags zab mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK077(tsu)001:68: bdag gzhan mchog gi sa la sbyor mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:69: zur chung shes rab grags la gnas kyi khyad 'phags ke lung zhes bya ste //
NK077(tsu)001:70: mdo bzhi dem lnga la sogs gsang sngags chos //
NK077(tsu)001:71: ma lus thugs su chud nas bsgrub pa mdzad //
NK077(tsu)001:72: yang khyed bla ma'i zhabs la gzhung lugs rab 'byams don la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK077(tsu)001:73: gdul bya mtha' dag theg pa'i lam la 'dzud //
NK077(tsu)001:74: sangs rgyas bstan pa rgya cher spel mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:75: sh+aakya seng ge de la theg pa mtha' dag khung chud rdzogs chen don //
NK077(tsu)001:76: ci bzhin rtogs pas gzung 'dzin rang sar grol //
NK077(tsu)001:77: bdag gzhan don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'i dpal //
NK077(tsu)001:78: rdzogs chen pa zhes de la rgya gar yul du byang chub sems sbyangs nas //
NK077(tsu)001:79: gangs chen khrod 'dir gsang sngags bstan pa skyongs //
NK077(tsu)001:80: bde ba can der rgyal sras byang chub sems //
NK077(tsu)001:81: sa bcu'i dbang phyug dam pa de la 'dud //
NK077(tsu)001:82: lung rigs man ngag kun la mkhas gyur nas //
NK077(tsu)001:83: mdo rgyud dgongs pa thugs la nyi ma shar //
NK077(tsu)001:84: bskyed rdzogs gnyis med bdag gzhan rgyud sbyang pa //
NK077(tsu)001:85: chos rje gtsang ston zhabs la chos nyid rnam dag byams pa'i ri bo la //
NK077(tsu)001:86: snying rje'i 'bras ldan dpag bsam 'bum gyis brgyan //
NK077(tsu)001:87: mtshan mchog don ldan 'gro mgon chos kyi rje //
NK077(tsu)001:88: byams pa chen po'i zhabs la snang stong gnyis med chos kyi nam mkha' la //
NK077(tsu)001:89: gnas lugs 'gyur med rang byung rdo rje'i sku //
NK077(tsu)001:90: lung bstan mchog thob rtsa sde spyan sngar zhes //
NK077(tsu)001:91: nam mkha' rdo rje'i zhabs la rgyud sde'i srog shing gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:92: thos pa bsam b+hee ba'i bya ba mthar phyin nas //
NK077(tsu)001:93: 'chad rtsod brtsams pa'i don la ma rmongs pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:94: thugs rje ye shes zhabs ldem dgongs brgyad dang mtha' drug tshul bzhi dang //
NK077(tsu)001:95: rton pa bzhi dang gzhung gis 'bod lan gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:96: gsang sngags zab mo'i rgyud gzhung gtan la dbab //
NK077(tsu)001:97: ston pa dbang 'byor zhabs la dam chos bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po bskyil //
NK077(tsu)001:98: lung rigs dri med pad mo'i kha phye nas //
NK077(tsu)001:99: blo gsal rkang drug ldan la dga' ston 'gyed //
NK077(tsu)001:100: rje btsun dpal 'bar zhabs la kun mkhyen zabs yangs bstan pa'i mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK077(tsu)001:101: sdom gsum rnam dag nyes ltung dri mas dben //
NK077(tsu)001:102: mtshungs med chos rje gdul bya'i mgon gyur pa //
NK077(tsu)001:103: ston pa mgon rgyal zhabs la dri med tshul khrims rnam dag rgyal ba'i mtshan //
NK077(tsu)001:104: theg mchog zab don ma lus thugs su chud //
NK077(tsu)001:105: mkhyen rab 'jam pa'i dbyangs dang gnyis med pa //
NK077(tsu)001:106: tshul khrims rgyal mtshan zhabs la mkhas pa rgya mtsho 'tshogs pa'i dbus na mdzes //
NK077(tsu)001:107: sna tshogs theg pa'i gzhung lugs bshad rtsal che //
NK077(tsu)001:108: rang 'dod med cing gzhan phan kho na'i sems //
NK077(tsu)001:109: d+harma klag k+sha'i zhabs la mdo sngags rgya mtsho'i dbus su 'khrugs pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:110: gsung rabs pad mo'i mnga' bdag chos kyi rje //
NK077(tsu)001:111: don bcu sbrang rtsi lta bu'i bcud ldan pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:112: drin chen dz+ny+aa na ke du la gsol ba 'debs //
NK077(tsu)001:113: de ltar bka' rgyud dri med gser phreng la //
NK077(tsu)001:114: phyag 'tshal gsol btab bden pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:115: rang rgyud smin cing gzhan rgyud grol ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:116: brtsam la bar chad med cing mthar phyin shog /
NK077(tsu)001:117: des sgyu 'phrul mnga' brnyes pa'i rgya bod kyi grub
NK077(tsu)001:118: chen rnams la mchod par brjod pa'i ngag thog mar
NK077(tsu)001:119: song ngo // de la dgos ched ci yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:120: brtsam pa la bar chad mi 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:121: chos 'di'i lugs kyi brgyud pa'i rnam bzhag la mkhas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:122: thos chung log rtog can 'ga' zhig gis /
NK077(tsu)001:123: rnying ma rgya gar la ma 'gyur zin yin zer ba'i don la /
NK077(tsu)001:124: chos sku kun bzang nas bzung ste rgya gar gyi grub chen rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:125: bod kyi lo tsa ba rma rin chen mchog nas bzungs ste /
NK077(tsu)001:126: rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar 'dir sgro bskur med par bkod pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:127: da bshad par dam bca' ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:128: dus gsum sangs rgyas bgrod pa'i lam gzhung de //
NK077(tsu)001:129: gsang sngags zab don thabs grol gnyis yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:130: de dag mtshon par byed pa'i brjod byed ni //
NK077(tsu)001:131: kun mkhyen rgyal ba mi bskyod rgyal po des //
NK077(tsu)001:132: sgyu 'phrul dra ba stong phrag brgya pa gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:133: de dag dgongs don ku ku ru tsa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:134: in tra pu tris man ngag rnam bkod mdzad //
NK077(tsu)001:135: de rjes pan chen sangs rgyas gsang ba yis //
NK077(tsu)001:136: sgyu 'phrul lam rim rgyas pa yi ger bkod //
NK077(tsu)001:137: 'di la 'grel bshad du ma snang na yang //
NK077(tsu)001:138: la la dka' tshom 'grel gyis don ma chus //
NK077(tsu)001:139: la la 'bru 'grel rgyas par snang na yang //
NK077(tsu)001:140: lam gyi gnad 'gags chod tshul dag lugs dang //
NK077(tsu)001:141: gzhung gi 'bod lan rnam dbye'i stong thun dkon //
NK077(tsu)001:142: la la gzhung mchan ka ta snang na yang //
NK077(tsu)001:143: bris nor dbang gis gzhung don gsal ma nus //
NK077(tsu)001:144: la la rgyab chos phyogs su 'grel pa yang //
NK077(tsu)001:145: lung 'dren brgal len rgyas par snang na yang //
NK077(tsu)001:146: gzhung don 'di nyid gtan la dbab ma nus //
NK077(tsu)001:147: de phyir 'grel bshad rtogs sla 'di byas so //
NK077(tsu)001:148: 'di la rang bzo ma yin mkhas pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:149: gzhung 'grel yig chung lhan thabs du ma dang //
NK077(tsu)001:150: bla ma'i man ngag ngo sprad gsang thig la //
NK077(tsu)001:151: rang gis rnam dpyod shes rab legs sbyang nas //
NK077(tsu)001:152: khams 'grel dri med mu tig phreng ba byas //
NK077(tsu)001:153: bshes gnyen rnams kyi mdzes pa'i rgyan du thogs //
NK077(tsu)001:154: gdul bya gsang sngags rigs can yid tshims mdzod //
NK077(tsu)001:155: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i mkhyen rab rgya mtsho las //
NK077(tsu)001:156: bstan bcos rnam dag pad mo'i tshal 'di 'khrungs //
NK077(tsu)001:157: tha snyad kha dog tsam la ma chags par //
NK077(tsu)001:158: don bcud sbrang rtsi ci bzhin len par mdzod //
NK077(tsu)001:159: 'phrag dog rlung 'tshubs dag gis ma g.yos par //
NK077(tsu)001:160: gzu bor gnas shing rnam dpyad ldan pas nyon //
NK077(tsu)001:161: rgya gar gyi mkhas grub chen po slob dpon sangs
NK077(tsu)001:162: rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i sgyu 'phrul lam rim 'di
NK077(tsu)001:164: 'chad nyan ci ltar bya ba'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:165: gang 'chad par bya ba dam chos kyi rnam bzhag /
NK077(tsu)001:166: 'chad nyan mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan dang gsum mo //
NK077(tsu)001:168: 'chad pa po slob dpon gyis mtshan nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:169: nyan pa po slob ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:173: de ltar bshad pa'i phan yon no //
NK077(tsu)001:174: dang po mtshan nyid la gnyis ste /
NK077(tsu)001:176: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyi chos kun mnyam pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:177: kyi don gnas lugs rtogs shing khong du chud pa
NK077(tsu)001:178: / brgyud pa'i zam ma chad pa /
NK077(tsu)001:179: dbang bzhi'i chu bo ma nub pa /
NK077(tsu)001:180: byin rlabs nyams rtogs kyi mdangs ma yal ba /
NK077(tsu)001:181: snyan brgyud gdams ngag gi gnad ma 'chug pa /
NK077(tsu)001:182: gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhung dkyil chog /phrin las rnam bzhi mtha' dag la mkhas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:183: slob ma rjes su 'dzin pa'i gnyer dang ldan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:184: mdzod gsum 'dzin pa'i bla ma gcig dgos ste /
NK077(tsu)001:185: 'di nyid kyi le'u bdun pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:186: ston pa mdzod gsum chu bo rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:187: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK077(tsu)001:190: bla ma lnga bcu pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:191: brtan zhing dul la blo gros ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:192: bzod ldan rang la g.yo sgyu med //
NK077(tsu)001:193: sngags dang rgyud kyi sbyor ba shes //
NK077(tsu)001:194: snying brtser ldan shing bstan bcos mkhas //
NK077(tsu)001:195: de nyid bcu ni yongs su shes //
NK077(tsu)001:196: dkyil 'khor bris pa'i las la mkhas //
NK077(tsu)001:199: bla med snying po smin pa'i skyen //
NK077(tsu)001:200: blo gros chen pos dri ba'i yul //
NK077(tsu)001:201: lam ston sa mkhan bshes gnyen mgon //
NK077(tsu)001:202: mun sel sgron ma rin po che //
NK077(tsu)001:203: mthong mig dbang po yid rnams kyi //
NK077(tsu)001:204: chu bo rab med sgrol ba'i gru //
NK077(tsu)001:205: 'jigs pa'i rdzong chen brtan pa'i mkhar //
NK077(tsu)001:206: 'khor ba'i gcong 'byin sman pa'i mchog /mtsho gling rin chen len byed pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:207: ded dpon dam pa bla ma la //
NK077(tsu)001:208: slob tu nges par shes par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:210: gzhan yang chos bshad mkhan la yang tha na yon tan 'di gsum 'dzom dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:214: sbyor ba'i bzod pa gsum mo //
NK077(tsu)001:216: bshad bya la mkhas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:217: shes bya'i sde snod tha dag la mkhas pa la sogs yod kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:218: 'on kyang rang gi rgyud gzhung khas gang blangs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:219: khung du chud pa gcig nam yang dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:220: des gdul bya'i the tshom gcod nus so //
NK077(tsu)001:221: gnyis pa 'chad byed la mkhas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:224: ji ltar bshad kyang 'thad pa gsum gyi ngag 'brel zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:227: gnyis ka'i rna bar snyan cing yid chag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:228: gsum pa kun spyod la mkhas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:229: tshul chos ma yin par rang gi sgo gsum chos
NK077(tsu)001:230: dang mthun par mkhas shing gdul bya dang ba 'dren
NK077(tsu)001:231: shing dad pa'i gnas su gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:232: gzhan gyi kun spyod la mkhas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:233: gdul bya dbang po rno rtul dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos bstan pa la mkhas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:234: gnyis pa mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:235: rang bzo dang bcos mas bka' rgyud dri ma med par bslad par byed pa'i slob dpon ni /
NK077(tsu)001:236: bdag gzhan kun la gnod pas mi brten spang bar gsungs te /
NK077(tsu)001:238: log par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK077(tsu)001:239: log lta'i spyi brdol gtum khro che //
NK077(tsu)001:240: sdig spyod don dang mi ldan yang //
NK077(tsu)001:241: bdag 'di nges pa kho na zhes //
NK077(tsu)001:242: bab bcol bka' rgyud bslu byed bslad //
NK077(tsu)001:243: de yang ci lta bu zhe na //
NK077(tsu)001:244: chos skyongs ba yi rnal 'byor pa //
NK077(tsu)001:245: pra ma ta zhes bya ba zhig /don dang lam la ma mthong bar //
NK077(tsu)001:246: bdag ni lam mkhan kho na zhes //
NK077(tsu)001:247: kun la rgya cher grags pa las //
NK077(tsu)001:248: rgyal ba'i bka' rkus 'gro gang rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:249: bslu bar gyur pa'i smin pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:250: ngan 'gror bying gyur gnas de rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:251: thar nas log pa'i 'jig rten pa //
NK077(tsu)001:252: bdag 'dzin spyod pa'i lam du ltung //
NK077(tsu)001:253: de 'dra'i tshul byung der ma spyod //
NK077(tsu)001:256: slob dpon tshad mar ma gyur sprel 'dra'i lung /
NK077(tsu)001:257: brten kyang lam nor rtog pas zin ta re //
NK077(tsu)001:259: gnyis pa chos bshad tshul la mang du yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:262: sbyor ba la bkod pa bshams pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:263: khri dang gdugs la sogs pa'i cha byad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:264: dkon mchog la gsol ba btab cing 'jam dbyangs bstod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:265: bdud sde tshar bcad cing 'khor la byams pa b+hee ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:266: dngos gzhi la phar phyin drug ldan gyi sgo nas bshad dgos pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:267: chos dngos su bshad pa sbyin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:268: de la rang 'dod dang tshul 'chos med pa tshul khrims /
NK077(tsu)001:269: 'khor gyi dri ba'i lan 'debs shing skyo dub med pa ni bzod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:270: le lo med cing chos bshad pa la spro ba brtson 'grus so //
NK077(tsu)001:271: rnam g.yeng med cing chos la rtse gcig tu gnas pa bsam gtan /
NK077(tsu)001:272: chos de'i tshig don ma lus pa shan 'byed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:273: brda' sprod nus pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:274: khyad par gsang sngags bshad tshul la /
NK077(tsu)001:275: nyes pa'i skyon brgyad dang bral zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:279: gol sgrib bzhi bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu rnams kyis sgo nas bshad dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:280: de rnams kyis don mdo tsam zhig bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:287: ci bzhin pa ma yin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:289: yi ge'i don gyi tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:294: mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:297: gang zag gi bsam pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:309: don de'ang drang don la mi brton /
NK077(tsu)001:311: nges don de yang rnam shes la mi brton ye shes la brton pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:312: nyes pa'i skyon brgyad la sogs pa'i don rgyas pa gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:313: rjes dge ba'i rtsa ba byang chub tu bsngo bas zin par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:314: gsum pa gsang sngags kyi don rtogs nas gzhan la bshad pa'i phan yon ni /
NK077(tsu)001:316: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK077(tsu)001:317: yon tan spyi gtsug nyid du 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:318: de yang ci lta bu zhe na //
NK077(tsu)001:319: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK077(tsu)001:320: drang srong rnal 'byor ka ya nas //
NK077(tsu)001:321: drang srong srungs rnams mang ste la //
NK077(tsu)001:322: theg chen gsang ba'i basngagasa pa brjod //
NK077(tsu)001:323: de rnams nges par bkod pa las //
NK077(tsu)001:324: mang pos rig can 'dzin pa thob //
NK077(tsu)001:325: gang der basngagasa pa brjod byed pa //
NK077(tsu)001:326: gsang bdag chen po rgyal por 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:327: des na theg chen gsang ba 'di //
NK077(tsu)001:328: kun la basngagasa pa brjod par gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:329: des ni nga yi dgongs pa thob //
NK077(tsu)001:331: gnyis pa nyan pa po slob ma'i mtshan nyid la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:332: slob ma de'i mtshan nyid des chos nyan pa'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:336: klong gsal nyi ma'i rgyud las /
NK077(tsu)001:337: dad ldan snying rje gtong phod che //
NK077(tsu)001:338: rgyud dul sdig 'dzem dbang po rno //
NK077(tsu)001:339: gsang thub nyams len brtul zhugs spyod //
NK077(tsu)001:340: skyo shas sdug sran snying rus che //
NK077(tsu)001:341: de ni gsang sngags gsang ba'i snod //
NK077(tsu)001:342: ces snod ldan la sbyin par gtong pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:343: gnyis pa mtshan nyid ngan pa'i snod ngan la gsang sngags mi bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:345: yang dag don gyi lta ba gsang ba 'di //
NK077(tsu)001:346: gang zag phyin ci log dang lta ba dman //
NK077(tsu)001:347: thos pa chung la blo rtul shes rab med //
NK077(tsu)001:348: nor 'phang kha ral la sogs snod med la //
NK077(tsu)001:349: 'di bstan gnyis ka bsreg phyir rab tu gsang //
NK077(tsu)001:351: gnyis pa slob ma des chos nyan pa'i tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:352: nyan pa'i skyon spangs ste ma yengs par nyan dgos ste /
NK077(tsu)001:354: nga rgyal dang ni ma dad dang //
NK077(tsu)001:355: don du gnyer ba med nyid dang //
NK077(tsu)001:356: phyi rol rnam g.yengs yid bsdus dang //
NK077(tsu)001:357: skyo bas nyan pa'i dri ma yin //
NK077(tsu)001:360: chos dang chos smra ba la gus pa bskyed dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:361: sngong po bkod pa'i mdo las bdag nyid la nad pa'i 'du shes /
NK077(tsu)001:362: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sman pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:363: chos la sman gyi 'du shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:364: nan tan rjes su bsgrub pa la nad 'tsho ba'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:366: gsum pa de ltar nyan pa'i phan yon ni byams pa seng ge sgras zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK077(tsu)001:367: bstan bcos bstan pa'i dus bstan phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:369: thos pa'ang byang chub thob gyur na //
NK077(tsu)001:370: nyan phyir lhags pa smos ci dgos //
NK077(tsu)001:372: khyad par du sngags kyi gzhung don la thos bsam byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:373: sku lnga'i sangs rgyas thob pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:375: dper na kyi ling sgrogs bskrol ltar //
NK077(tsu)001:376: rnam grol thos bsam sgo mo yis //
NK077(tsu)001:377: shes rgyud kun grol thogs med 'gro //
NK077(tsu)001:379: gnyis pa gang 'chad nyan byed pa dam chos kyi rnam bzhag la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:380: gang zag 'jug ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:381: dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:382: don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i phyir bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:383: bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs gsum du gnas pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:384: dang po spyir chos ngos bzung ba la yang mang du yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:387: 'das chos la theg chung dang theg chen gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:388: theg chen la mtshan nyid gsang sngags gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:389: gsang sngags la phyi pa dang nang pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:390: nang pa la ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:391: 'dir ma h+aa yo ga /de la bde bar gshegs pa'i zhal nas gsung pa'i rgyud /
NK077(tsu)001:392: de la brten pa'i man ngag gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:393: dang po rgyud sde la tan sde chen po bco brgyad kyi dbye ba ni logs su shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:394: 'o na bka' dang rgyud la khyad ci yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:395: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i zhal nas gsung pa thams cad rgyud yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:396: ston pa sprul pa'i sku'i gsung pa thams cad bka' yin /
NK077(tsu)001:397: yang dal gyi bya ba'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa thams cad rgyud yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:398: de mi ston pa thams cad la bka' zhes so //
NK077(tsu)001:399: yang gzhi dang lam gyi nyes pa zad pa'i zhal nas gsung pa thams cad rgyud yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:401: lam gyi ltos pa ma zad pa rnams kyi gsung pa thams cad la bka' zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:402: des ni bka' dang rgyud kyi dbye ba zhor la bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:403: gnyis pa 'di ni de la brten pa'i man ngag yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:406: rgyud kyi don ma nor rtogs pa'i man ngag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:410: gnyis pa bslabs cing nyams su blangs ba'i man ngag la /
NK077(tsu)001:411: lam gyi gtso bo'i man ngag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:413: 'dir sgyu 'phrul lam gyi rim pa 'di nyid lam gyi gtso bo'i man ngag go //
NK077(tsu)001:414: gnyis pa lam gyi cha rkyen la /
NK077(tsu)001:417: sgeg rdor gyis bdun du dbye /
NK077(tsu)001:418: sangs rgyas gsang bas bcur dbyes kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:419: 'di rnams bcur dbye ru rung la /
NK077(tsu)001:421: de yang man ngag de rnams kyi rnam grangs phra mo drug cu rtsa bzhi ngos bzung na /
NK077(tsu)001:422: dar rje dpal gyi grags pas mdzad pa'i zhi khro gal phreng /
NK077(tsu)001:424: nyang po klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i mtshan nyid sgron ma /
NK077(tsu)001:425: b+hi ma la mi tras mdzad pa'i shes rab spyan 'byed /
NK077(tsu)001:426: lta ba'i man ngag sgron ma /
NK077(tsu)001:430: thabs shes rab kyi sgron ma /
NK077(tsu)001:431: lta ba rin chen sgron ma ste lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:432: lnga po de rdzogs chen yin /
NK077(tsu)001:433: yum bzhi'i lung tshigs sbyin sregs rtsa ba nas mdo gdan brtsig du yod kyis lung mdo rims /
NK077(tsu)001:434: man ngag kyi mdo sgyu 'phrul gyis me long /
NK077(tsu)001:435: rig pa'i me tog /gsang thig 'jam thig gcig char /
NK077(tsu)001:442: zhi ba rlung gi bsam gtan /
NK077(tsu)001:444: khro bo man ngag sgron ma /
NK077(tsu)001:445: khro bo rtogs pa'i lha rgyud rgyas bsdus gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:446: de rnams b+hi ma las mdzad do //
NK077(tsu)001:447: sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i thig ga sin thar ta /
NK077(tsu)001:448: dbang gi gal po che ba /
NK077(tsu)001:453: zhi ba rdo rje las rim /
NK077(tsu)001:454: khro bo rdo rje las rim /
NK077(tsu)001:455: dra chung rin chen 'od kyi snang ba tshags bar dgu /
NK077(tsu)001:456: zhi ba phyag rgya bsam gtan /
NK077(tsu)001:457: khro bo snang ba dam pa rgyan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:458: khro bo phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK077(tsu)001:460: lam rim che chung rnams khro bo phyag rgya gcig pa sde ba gnyis pa /
NK077(tsu)001:461: ku ku r+aa tsa'i rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK077(tsu)001:463: dpal he ru ka pad ma gar gyi dbang phyug /rin chen nyi ma /
NK077(tsu)001:464: rta mchog rol pa gsang ba'i don rnam par bkod
NK077(tsu)001:465: pa dang drug /sgyu 'phrul tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i sgrub
NK077(tsu)001:466: thabs / dbang dang dal gyi las rim rin chen 'phreng ba /
NK077(tsu)001:467: ro lang rdo rjes mdzad pa'i zas tshogs rdor lung /
NK077(tsu)001:469: dam tshig gsal bkra phra rgyas gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:470: rim drug /khog gzhung gsal ba'i sgron ma /
NK077(tsu)001:471: b+hi ma las mdzad kyang zer /
NK077(tsu)001:472: slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa'i gzhal yas khang gi gsal byed mun sel sgron ma /
NK077(tsu)001:473: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis mdzad pa'i sku gdung las 'phreng /
NK077(tsu)001:474: b+hi ma las mdzad kyang zer /
NK077(tsu)001:475: rgyal ba bzang po dpal bas mdzad pa'i zhi ba 'od kyi phyag rgya /
NK077(tsu)001:476: dz+ny+aa na dza yas mdzad pa'i me long lta bu'i bsgrub thabs /
NK077(tsu)001:477: dzi na mi tras mdzad pa'i zhi rtsa rgyud don gsal byed /
NK077(tsu)001:478: in tra pu tris mdzad pa'i man ngag rnam bkod /
NK077(tsu)001:479: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes zhi chung rtsa ba /
NK077(tsu)001:480: ro bsreg rtsa ba bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i rgyud la rten pa /
NK077(tsu)001:481: zhi ba phyag rgya gcig pa'i bsam gtan /
NK077(tsu)001:482: gegs sel brgya pa'i man ngag /skye bsod nams bzang po'i lam rim khog don /
NK077(tsu)001:483: rdzogs chen gyi man ngag la /
NK077(tsu)001:484: bzhad pa'i rdo rjes la shan lta ba'i sgron ma /
NK077(tsu)001:485: ska ba dpal brtsegs kyis lta ba shan 'byed /
NK077(tsu)001:486: klu sgrub kyis g.yu thang rnams so //
NK077(tsu)001:487: de rnams ni rgya bod kyi mkhas grub rnams kyis
NK077(tsu)001:488: mdzad pa'i man ngag bod du dar ba rnams kyi
NK077(tsu)001:489: rnam grangs zhor la bkod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:490: gnyis pa don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:492: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyi bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:493: 'dir spyi don gsum gyis ston te /
NK077(tsu)001:494: seng+ge'i 'gros kyis spyi don gyi khog dbub /
NK077(tsu)001:495: stag mo 'gros kyis gzhung don gyi sa bcad /
NK077(tsu)001:496: ru sbal 'gros kyis tshigs don gyi 'bru gnyer ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:497: dang po spyir bka' thams cad phun sum tshogs pa lngas 'chad /
NK077(tsu)001:498: bstan bcos thams cad rtsis 'gor lngas 'chad /
NK077(tsu)001:499: bye brag tu klu sgrub yab sras kyis sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyi sgo nas 'chad /
NK077(tsu)001:502: brgal len mtshams sbyor lnga'i sgo nas 'chad /
NK077(tsu)001:504: 'chad pa po'i ngag dag /nyan pa po'i snod dag
NK077(tsu)001:505: /thun mong du bstan bcos kyi brjod bya dag pa
NK077(tsu)001:506: ste / dag pa gsum la brten nas 'chad /
NK077(tsu)001:507: rdo rje gdan pas mdzad pa po slob dpon gyi che ba /
NK077(tsu)001:508: des mdzad pa bstan bcos kyi che ba /
NK077(tsu)001:509: de gnyis dang ldan pa'i bstan bcos che ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:510: che ba gsum gyi sgo nas 'chad lugs 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:511: 'bri ka ma la sh+ri la'i bzhed yin kyang zer /
NK077(tsu)001:512: che ba gsum dang ldan pa'i sgo nas 'chad pa la sogs pa'i lugs mang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:513: 'di nyid rgyud la brten pa'i man ngag yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:516: thos chung gsar bu yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:517: man ngag spyi don brtsis 'go klad nas gzhom //
NK077(tsu)001:519: khung btsun cing yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:520: slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:521: bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:522: rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gar gtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:523: bstan pa la mtshan nges shing don gyi mdo tsam gcig rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:524: mtshan ci la btags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:525: brtsams pa la don yod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:526: dgos ched gang gis don du mdzad pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:527: shes shing khung du chud par bya ba'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:528: dbu zhabs su don dus bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK077(tsu)001:530: spyir bstan bcos brtsams pa'i tshad la /
NK077(tsu)001:531: rab chos nyid bden pa'i don mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:532: 'bring yi dam lha yi zhal mthong zhing lung bstan thob pa /
NK077(tsu)001:533: tha ma bka'i dgongs don 'grel zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:534: theg pa'i shan 'byed cing la bzla ba /
NK077(tsu)001:535: tshig don la mkhas shing bye brag phyed pa gcig gis brtsams dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:537: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rab //
NK077(tsu)001:538: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro yis //
NK077(tsu)001:539: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK077(tsu)001:540: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK077(tsu)001:541: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK077(tsu)001:543: gzhung 'di nyid kyi brtsam pa po slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:544: brtsam tshad gsum dang ldan pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:546: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /kun rdzob du'ang dbyer med pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:547: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:549: sngon nas sbyangs pa yun ring la dar drag pa'i stobs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:550: chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:557: dbyangs can ma la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:558: khyad par gzhung 'di nyid kyi rgyud kyi ston pa /
NK077(tsu)001:559: rdo rje sems dpa' rnams kyi zhal 'du 'bral med par gzigs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:560: de'ang rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i brjod bya shan 'byed cing la zlos pa /
NK077(tsu)001:561: tshig don la nor 'khrul dang lhag chad mi mnga' zhing bye brag phyed pas /
NK077(tsu)001:562: brtsam tshad rab 'bring gsum ka dang ldan pa'i slob dpon des mdzad /
NK077(tsu)001:563: yang na tha ma rigs pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas pa gcig dgos zhes bya ba yang snang bas /
NK077(tsu)001:564: slob dpon 'di nyid rgya gar chu bzhi'i pan tri ta rnams kyi bla phud du gyur cing /
NK077(tsu)001:565: 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas pa lus lhag med du gshegs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:566: ri bo rtse lngar 'phags pa 'jam dpal dang lhan gcig du bzhugs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:567: de yang rnam thar mdo tsam gcig bkod na /
NK077(tsu)001:568: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba 'di thog mar gsan pa rgya chung shing /
NK077(tsu)001:569: dad pa shin tu che ba /
NK077(tsu)001:570: sgom bsgrub la mos pa gcig yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:571: 'jam dpal a ra pa tsa na bya ba'i bsgrub thabs gcig bslab nas /
NK077(tsu)001:572: bsgrub pa'i rten 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi thang sku
NK077(tsu)001:573: gcig /ba dmar ser gyi 'o ma bum pa gang
NK077(tsu)001:574: / me tog ud pa la gcig bsnams nas /
NK077(tsu)001:575: a su ra'i brag phug tu bsgrub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:579: me tog mdangs dang ldan par gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:580: de yang me tog 'jam dpal gyi bris sku la phul /
NK077(tsu)001:581: 'o ma de gsol nas dngos grub thob pa yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:582: slob dpon gsan pa rgya chung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:583: dngos grub len ma len ma mkhyen te /
NK077(tsu)001:584: ci tsug byed snyam pa'i dar gcig bsdad bar du /
NK077(tsu)001:585: gnod sbyin mo gcig yin zer nas /
NK077(tsu)001:587: 'gram pa la thal lcags rgyab nas ru rgyal bar gyur skad /
NK077(tsu)001:591: me tog mdangs yal nas 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:592: dngos grub len ma mkhyen par shes nas /
NK077(tsu)001:593: 'o ma bo ba'i shul du thig gcig lce steng du bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:594: bdag thos pa chung ba 'di yang bdud kyi las su rig par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:595: dper na nga dang nga lta bu'i gsung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:596: za hor gyi yul du gsan pa la byon te /
NK077(tsu)001:597: za hor gyi rgyal po pra b+ha hasti la /
NK077(tsu)001:598: dang po 'dus pa gsang ba'i rgyud /
NK077(tsu)001:599: tan tra pang tra has gsan /
NK077(tsu)001:600: de la sogs pa phyi rgyud tha dag gsan nas /
NK077(tsu)001:601: mkhas pa chen por gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:602: man ngag a ba da ra /
NK077(tsu)001:603: bsam gtan phyi ma'i rgya cher 'grel la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:604: slob dpon gyis brtsam pa'i chos kyang mang du bzhugs skad do //
NK077(tsu)001:605: de nas nang pa'i rgyud kyang mang du bslabs shing
NK077(tsu)001:606: mkhyen nas sgom bsgrub mdzad par thugs la dgongs pa
NK077(tsu)001:607: la / 'chad par byed pa'i slob dpon du gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:608: sgom sgrub byar ma byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:609: da ltar thos pa che na yang bdud kyi las su rig par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:612: bod yul ra'i dgon phug zhes bya bar /
NK077(tsu)001:613: gangs ti se tse la sgom bsgrub mdzad du byon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:614: thugs dam gyi lha rdo rje sems dpa' la mdzad
NK077(tsu)001:615: nas bsgrub pa mdzad pas yi dam gyi lha'i zhal
NK077(tsu)001:616: mngon du gzigs nas snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting
NK077(tsu)001:617: nge 'dzin thob nas bzhugs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:618: bod kyi brtsad po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis gsan nas /
NK077(tsu)001:622: tsangs the len ne len tra dang gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:623: gser phye bre gsum bardzangasa nas spyan 'dren du btangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:626: glang su ga to go cha /
NK077(tsu)001:629: slob dpon dba' khri shes dang lnga yin par bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:630: de nas slob dpon gyi spyan sngar mchis nas /
NK077(tsu)001:631: gser phye bre do phul te /
NK077(tsu)001:632: bod du gshegs par zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:633: ngas bod srin po gdong dmar 'dul ba'i dus la bab ma bab /
NK077(tsu)001:634: yi dam lha la dri gsungs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:635: nub mor tshogs kyi mchod pa rgya chen po phul te /
NK077(tsu)001:636: dris pas lan ma gnang skad /
NK077(tsu)001:637: de yang 'dul ba'i du la ma bab par 'dug zer /
NK077(tsu)001:638: lugs gcig la slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:639: sngon brag phug dgra 'dul lha zhal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:640: pan tri ta rnams nyams bsdur dus /
NK077(tsu)001:641: bod srin po gdong dmar gang gis gdul bya yin min brtag pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:642: rgyal po khri srong gi dus slob dpon pad mas 'dul bas /
NK077(tsu)001:645: bod du byon du ma gnang /
NK077(tsu)001:646: 'on kyang nga'i chos kyis phan thog te 'ong bas /
NK077(tsu)001:647: dbang bskur chos bshad gsung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:648: gangs ti tse shel gyi mchod rten du byin gyis brlabs nus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:649: mtsho ma pham g.yu'i man+dala du rlobs nus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:650: dpag tshad dang rgyang grags thig sna dor bas lha'i
NK077(tsu)001:651: dal du sprul nus pa des de bzhin du bzhugs
NK077(tsu)001:652: pas / mdun gyi nam mkha' la thig sna dor bas /
NK077(tsu)001:653: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs wal gyis gsal bar byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:654: dbang nga la nod dam lha la nod gsungs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:655: khong gis slob dpon gyi thugs rigs pa lha'i dal du shar ba ma shes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:656: ru ngan pa lha bzang bar byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:657: dbang lha la zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:658: lha rnams de nyid du mi snang bar gyur skad /
NK077(tsu)001:660: dbang nga la nod byas na lha la dbang nod du 'ong ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:661: nga ngan lha bzang bar byas pas lha rnams mi snang bar gyur ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:662: 'on kyang dbang bskur gyi gsung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:664: lo tsa ba rnams la chos bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:665: de'i dus su rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga'i bsgrub thabs mang du mdzad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:666: khyad par du rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul dra
NK077(tsu)001:667: ba'i man ngag mtshan nyid gsum du bsdus pa'i lam
NK077(tsu)001:668: chung mdzad / des kyang bde blag tu ma rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:669: lam rim chen po le'u dgu pa 'di nyid mdzad nas bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:670: lugs gcig la gangs ti tser ser /
NK077(tsu)001:671: phyi rgyud min pa ma gsung gsang sngags nang pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:672: man ngag lam rim la sogs rgya gar du mdzad
NK077(tsu)001:673: zer / gsang sngags 'tshol mi lnga yang /
NK077(tsu)001:675: rang gi slob ma sgeg rdor la sogs pa lnga yin par 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:676: gzhan yang brtsad dpe'i skyes lan du /
NK077(tsu)001:677: man ngag a ba da ra brtsams nas bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:679: dka' blas byas pa'i don du /
NK077(tsu)001:680: byang chub pa'i sin tar ta dang /
NK077(tsu)001:681: bsam gtan phyi ma'i rgya chen 'grel brtsams so //
NK077(tsu)001:682: snang ba dam pa rgyan brtsams nas bskur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:683: de yang ru nyid g.yengs ba che bar dgongs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:684: slar rgya gar du gshegs te /
NK077(tsu)001:685: brgya byin bshal brang gi yang thog tu bzhugs te /
NK077(tsu)001:686: mi dang mi ma yin pa'i 'khor la theg pa chen po'i chos lo brgyar bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:687: de nas lo brgyar 'khor rnams kyi dbus na chos mi gsung bar tsog gi bzhugs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:688: gnyis brgya lon nas 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas nas rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs te /
NK077(tsu)001:689: 'jig rten pa rnams kyis ston pa gnyis pa zhes mtshan btags so //
NK077(tsu)001:690: rnam thar rgyas pa ni logs su shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:691: gnyis pa bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:692: rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gar gtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:694: stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud dag las //
NK077(tsu)001:696: thugs sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud nas btus shing /
NK077(tsu)001:697: phyogs ma h+aa yo gar gtogs so //
NK077(tsu)001:698: gsum pa mtshan ci la btags pa ni spyir mtshan gyi 'dogs lugs la lnga las /
NK077(tsu)001:701: don rang gi ngo bo la 'dogs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:702: mtshan don rgyas bshad ni gzhung 'grel du shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:703: bzhi pa dgos ched gang gi don du mdzad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:705: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma dang //
NK077(tsu)001:706: de rjes ma 'ongs skal ldan sogs //
NK077(tsu)001:708: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba rang gis 'khor dam pa'i rigs can sngags 'tshol mi lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:709: ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag chos kyi mig can /
NK077(tsu)001:710: las dang skal ba ldan pa rnams kyi don du mdzad do //
NK077(tsu)001:711: lnga pa dbu zhabs su don dus bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:714: zhabs don gsum du shes par bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:717: bcud la gzhi lam 'bras gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:718: gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:719: lam rang gnas rtogs shing goms par byed pa /
NK077(tsu)001:720: 'bras bu rang gnas sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:721: de'ang lam la rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK077(tsu)001:722: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:723: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med kyi rig 'dzin no //
NK077(tsu)001:726: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:727: 'o na de rnams le'u gang gis ston na /
NK077(tsu)001:728: gzhi ye shes rang gnas le'u dang pos ston la /
NK077(tsu)001:729: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba le'u gnyis pas /
NK077(tsu)001:731: stong pa chen po'i rnam 'byor le'u gsum pas /
NK077(tsu)001:732: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor le'u bzhi pas /
NK077(tsu)001:733: phyag rgya gcig pa'i le'u lnga pas /
NK077(tsu)001:734: phyag rgya spros pa le'u drug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:735: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa le'u bdun pas rig 'dzin bzhi le'u brgyad pas ston la /
NK077(tsu)001:736: 'bras bu mthar thugs dgu pas ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:737: des spyi don gyis khog dbub pa de song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:738: gzhung don gyi sa bcad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:739: tshig don gyi 'bru gnyer ba gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:740: bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs dang 'brel ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:741: des khog dbub bsdus pa tsam gcig brjod pa yin gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:742: rgyas par sgyu 'phrul ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud sde /
NK077(tsu)001:744: pan tri ta tshad ma rnams kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:745: de la brten nas man ngag brtsams tshul /
NK077(tsu)001:746: chos 'di rnams la brgyud tshul gsum gyis brgyud lugs /
NK077(tsu)001:747: de rnams 'chad par byed pa'i thabs la man ngag
NK077(tsu)001:748: gnad nas 'dzin nas bshad lugs rnam pa mang po
NK077(tsu)001:749: yod pa de / yi ge mang gis dogs pa'i phyir 'dir ma bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:750: bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs la /
NK077(tsu)001:751: spyi don rnam pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:752: man ngag brtsams pa la 'jug pa'i yan lag klad kyi don dang /
NK077(tsu)001:753: chos kun khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:755: mjug gi don dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo zhing smon lam gdabs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:757: bgrang bar chad bsal zhing tshogs rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir phyag bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:759: phyag 'tshal ba'i yul rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK077(tsu)001:761: spyi don rnam pa bzhi yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:767: don rdo rje sems pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:768: rtags rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:769: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK077(tsu)001:770: bden gsum dbyer med 'ching grol thams cad dang bral ba de nyid gnyis pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:771: gdul bya'i snang ngo la ye shes sgyu ma'i sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis spras pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:772: rdo rje sems dpa' mthar lam pa'i snang ngo la shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:775: lang ka'i bdag po de kho na nyid ci bzhin pa de ni /
NK077(tsu)001:776: thams cad nas thams cad du gnyen po med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:783: dngos po med pas ngo bo nyid du bcom pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:784: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:785: 'di ni lung gi tshig kho nas don go bar zad do //
NK077(tsu)001:787: skye 'jig gi mtha' dang bral ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:789: mtshan nyid mtha' rnams kun bral bas //
NK077(tsu)001:790: cir yang bzung du med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:793: rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dang dbyer mi phyed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:796: dpal zhes pa rgya gar sang tri ta'i skad du sh+r+ai'i skad du drangs na /
NK077(tsu)001:798: legs pa'i yon tan thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa gcig la dpal zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:803: 'jig rten gyi bde legs phun sum tshogs pa la dpal 'byor zer ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:804: theg pa 'og ma'i rang sa'i 'bras bu la dpal zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:806: rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang /
NK077(tsu)001:809: dgra bcom nas stug po bkod pa man chad /
NK077(tsu)001:810: chos nyid kyi don phyogs re phyogs 'ga' tsam rtogs pa bdag gi dpal te chos sku yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:811: des gdul bya'i don phyogs re phyogs g+ha tsam byed pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:812: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal ste gzugs sku rnam gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:813: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i dpal ni /
NK077(tsu)001:814: gong gi thun mong de las khyad par du gyur pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:817: nga ni spyi dpal bla na med //
NK077(tsu)001:818: skyon bral thabs kyi rgyal por 'dod //
NK077(tsu)001:822: dang po rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal ni /
NK077(tsu)001:823: 'khor 'das snang srid kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:824: ngo bo mnyam pa nyid ro gcig pa'i don sems
NK077(tsu)001:825: can thams cad la stor bral med par gnas shing
NK077(tsu)001:826: / sku lnga lhun grub gyis sangs rgyas rang chas
NK077(tsu)001:827: su yod pa ni gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub
NK077(tsu)001:829: gnyis pa rig pa rang snang ba'i dpal ni /
NK077(tsu)001:830: de lta bu'i rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas lugs de rtogs shing mthar phyin pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:831: bdag don gyi legs pa phun sum tshogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:832: rtogs pa bdag gi dpal de chos sku'o //
NK077(tsu)001:833: gsum pa thugs rje chen po zhar byung gi dpal ni /
NK077(tsu)001:834: de ltar rang don chos sku thob pa'i zhar la thugs rje'i mdzad pas gdul bya'i don /
NK077(tsu)001:835: gang la gang 'tshams su mdzad pa de ni /
NK077(tsu)001:836: gdul bya gzhan gyi don du /
NK077(tsu)001:837: legs pa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa 'byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:838: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:840: de rnams ni dpal zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK077(tsu)001:843: sngon 'byung rdo rje sems dpa' dgongs pa la ldan pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:844: rjes 'jug la dpal gsum gyi don de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:845: rig pa rang snang la ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:846: tshul ji ltar du ldan na /
NK077(tsu)001:847: ngo bo nyid kyi ldan pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:850: mar dang snum ldan pa lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:851: rdo rje sems pa'i nges tshig ni /
NK077(tsu)001:852: don rdo rje chos lnga yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:853: de la dang po phrin las gzhan 'joms ba'i rdo rje ni /
NK077(tsu)001:854: rdo rje lta bu'i zhes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:855: dper na rdzas rdo rje pha lam gyi phar gzi
NK077(tsu)001:856: mchong la sogs pa'i dmigs 'bug cing 'joms par byed
NK077(tsu)001:857: / tshur la gcig kyang mi tshugs ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:858: don rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs snang stong gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:859: med pa'i ye shes sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK077(tsu)001:860: shes kyi dngos po dang dngos med la sogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:861: gnyis 'dzin gyi lta ngan thams cad 'joms pas na
NK077(tsu)001:862: / phrin las gzhan 'joms pa'i rdo rje zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:864: 'joms shing cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:865: rang byung chen po lha yi lha //
NK077(tsu)001:866: de nyid rtogs pa'i rigs pa la //
NK077(tsu)001:867: badz+ra zhes ni gdags par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:869: gnyis pa ngo bo 'dus ma byas pa'i rdo rje ni /
NK077(tsu)001:870: ye shes 'dus ma byas zhes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:871: sgrib g.yog thams cad dang bral ba'i ye shes kyi
NK077(tsu)001:872: gnas lugs de nyid dang po rgyu las ma byung
NK077(tsu)001:873: bar du rkyen gyi ma bskyed tha ma dngos po
NK077(tsu)001:874: ma grub pas 'dus ma byas zhes zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:876: rgyu rkyen bral ba'i skad cig mas //
NK077(tsu)001:877: rang snang nyid du byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:879: gsum pa yon tan rtsal ba med pa'i rdo rje ni /
NK077(tsu)001:880: ma brtsal lnga rdzogs zhes pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:881: dper na chu la gsher lhun gyis grub pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:882: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de rtogs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:883: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga
NK077(tsu)001:884: gzhan nas brtsal ma dgos par rang la rdzogs pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:886: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK077(tsu)001:887: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:888: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:889: de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK077(tsu)001:891: bzhi pa mtshan nyid skye 'jig dang bral ba'i rdo rje ni /
NK077(tsu)001:892: rkyen bral mi shigs zhes pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:893: dper na 'byung chen gtos kyi nam mkha' 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:894: rgyu rkyen las ma byung bas 'pho 'gyur med pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:896: rgyu las ma byung rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:898: skye 'jig dang bral bas mi shig ces zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:900: rdo rje zhes ni bya ba las /
NK077(tsu)001:901: snying po'i rang bzhin de la ni //
NK077(tsu)001:902: skye 'jig med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK077(tsu)001:903: rdo rje zhes ni brjod pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:905: lnga pa rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje ni /
NK077(tsu)001:908: don dam skye med spros pa dang bral ba'i dbyings de nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:909: kun rdzob rig pa sgyu ma cir yang ma 'gags
NK077(tsu)001:910: pa'i ye shes gnyis ye nas 'du 'bral med par
NK077(tsu)001:911: chu dang gsher ba bzhin du dbyer med du gnas
NK077(tsu)001:912: pa'o // de yang sgyu 'phrul me long las /
NK077(tsu)001:913: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:914: rang rig byang chub sems nyid de //
NK077(tsu)001:915: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:916: rdo rje zhes ni brjod pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:919: de ltar rdo rje'i chos lnga'i sgra don bshad pa
NK077(tsu)001:920: des rdo rje'i bshad pa de grub pa yin no
NK077(tsu)001:921: // gsum pa sems kyi don bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:922: nyid gnyis med ngang gsal mi g.yo mi sems sems che zhes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:923: gong du bshad pa'i don de nyid gnyis su med pa'i rig pa rang snang bas kyang sems /
NK077(tsu)001:924: byed pa po med par ngang gi rang gsal ba'i phyir sems /
NK077(tsu)001:925: gzhan du mi g.yo ba'i phyir sems /
NK077(tsu)001:926: de ka sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin pas na chen po zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:927: 'di'i don zhib tu ngo sprad na /
NK077(tsu)001:928: sems zhes pa la don bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:929: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:930: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid la chos sku'i sems 'di la gnyis med ces zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:931: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:932: mtshan ma'i sgrib g.yogs med pa sprul sku'i sems 'di la ngang gsal zhes zer /
NK077(tsu)001:933: dbyer med byang chub kyi sems phyag rgya gcig pa'i dgongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:934: yod med rtag chad gang gi phyogs su ma lhung ba /
NK077(tsu)001:935: longs sku'i dgongs pa 'di la mi g.yo ba'i sems zer /
NK077(tsu)001:936: spros bral dang bral ba byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK077(tsu)001:940: yul yul can cir yang mi sems pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:941: mi sems pa'i sems zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:942: sems la dbye na 'gro drug 'khrul snang gi sems dang /
NK077(tsu)001:943: mu stegs rtag chad log pa'i sems dang /
NK077(tsu)001:944: theg pa 'og ma phyogs 'dzin gyi sems dang /
NK077(tsu)001:945: de rnams thams cad phyogs re ba'i sems la /
NK077(tsu)001:946: 'di nyid gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:947: ma skyes ma 'gags dbyer med spyod yul dang bral
NK077(tsu)001:948: ba don dam lhag pa'i chos sku chen po de
NK077(tsu)001:949: nyid khung du chud pa la sems chen po zhes
NK077(tsu)001:951: dpa' zhes bya ba'i don bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:952: phrin las kyi bdud bzhi bcom pas na dapa'o zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:955: dug lnga rang ga mar spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:956: nyon mongs lnga nyid ma spangs ye shes lngar gyur pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:957: nyon mongs pa'i 'dud bcoms pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:958: phrin las dang sbyar na zhi ba phung po'i bdud
NK077(tsu)001:959: ni phung po lnga la rang rgyud du bzung zhing
NK077(tsu)001:960: sdug bsngal gyi rten du gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:961: phung po lnga nyid ma spangs rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:962: phung po'i bdud bcom pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:963: phrin las dang sbyar na rgyas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:965: skye shi rang rgyud du bzung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:966: sems nyid skye shi med pa'i don mngon du gyur pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:967: 'chi bdag gi bdud bcoms te phrin las dang sbyar na dbang /
NK077(tsu)001:969: re dogs bzang ngan gyi 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:970: lha rtogs gnyis su med pa'i don mngon du gyur pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:971: lha'i bu'i bdud bcom pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:972: phrin las dang sbyar na drag po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:973: rdo rje sems dpa'i mdzad pa phrin las gyi bdud bzhi bcom pas dpa' ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:975: dper na 'jig rten na dgra'i dpung 'joms pa'i skyes bu la dpa' bo zer ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:976: rang nyid na sangs rgyas gsang ba lha'i zhes pa
NK077(tsu)001:977: theg pa thun mong gi lha ni 'jam dbyangs yin
NK077(tsu)001:978: la / khyad par gyi lha ni gsang sngags ma
NK077(tsu)001:979: h+aa yo ga'i lugs la rdo rje sems dpa'i ston
NK077(tsu)001:981: skabs 'dir tha snyad pa 'ga' zhig gis /
NK077(tsu)001:984: rnam par dag pa'i lha dang /
NK077(tsu)001:985: don gyi lha la sogs pa'i dbye ba 'ga' zhig byed 'dug ste spang bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:986: de lta bu'i don rtags gnyis dang ldan pa'i lha
NK077(tsu)001:987: de la phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul gnyis med mos zhes
NK077(tsu)001:988: pa 'di ni / lta ba rtogs pa'i phyag yin par mngon pas /
NK077(tsu)001:989: de yang rdo rje sems dpa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:990: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dgongs pa gnyis shar nub kyi
NK077(tsu)001:991: nam mkha' lta bur dbyer med gcig tu 'dres pa
NK077(tsu)001:992: ni / lta ba rtogs pa'i phyag go //
NK077(tsu)001:1003: gzhan yang dgos ched la dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1010: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par 'chad spro na /
NK077(tsu)001:1011: gzhung lugs gzhan bshad srol ltar gyis la /
NK077(tsu)001:1012: khyad par du gzhung 'di nyid don dang sbyar nas 'chad pa gal che /
NK077(tsu)001:1013: 'dir yi ge mang gi dogs pa'i phyir ma bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:1014: gnyis pa khung btsun zhing yid ches par bya ba'i lo rgyus la gsum bgrang /
NK077(tsu)001:1015: spyir gsang bdag gis dam pa'i rigs can lnga la gsang sngags gsung pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1017: 'dir gsang bdag gi dam pa'i rigs can lnga la gsang sngags gsung pa'i lo rgyus gsung yang /
NK077(tsu)001:1018: chos rgyud dri ma med pa 'di dang po ji ltar byung ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1019: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag gsum //
NK077(tsu)001:1020: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK077(tsu)001:1021: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1023: rgyal ba dgongs par brgyud pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1024: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos /
NK077(tsu)001:1025: rgyal tshab rigs lnga la brgyud /
NK077(tsu)001:1026: rigs lngas rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa' la sogs pa lhan gcig pa'i 'khor la brgyud pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1027: rig 'dzin rigs par brgyud pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1028: mi ma yin pa la brgyud pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1029: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis la brgyud pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1030: dang po ni thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1031: lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:1034: spyan ras gzigs kyi bsgrub pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1035: phyag rdor gyi spyod pa bstan zer yang /
NK077(tsu)001:1036: gsang sngags kyi lta spyod bsgrub pa gsum ka'i don /
NK077(tsu)001:1037: 'jam dpal gzhon nu mdzes pa'i sku dang ldan pa des /
NK077(tsu)001:1038: lha rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun chos bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:1040: lha grags ldan mchog skyong la bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:1042: des skye dgu'i bdag po tshangs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:1043: des tshangs pa kun grol des tshangs pa gtsug phud 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:1045: des lha'i rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la /
NK077(tsu)001:1046: de ltar gyur pas lha rnams kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:1047: byang chub sems dpa'i rig 'dzin cing //
NK077(tsu)001:1048: rgyal ba rnams kyi gdung 'tshob par gyur to //
NK077(tsu)001:1049: spyan ras gzigs bdud rtsi sman gyi sku dang ldan pa nges /
NK077(tsu)001:1050: klu dug can rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par /
NK077(tsu)001:1051: klu rgyal g+h+ri na nag po la bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:1052: des klu mo kha 'dul ma la /
NK077(tsu)001:1053: des klu yid 'ong dga' ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:1055: des klu tshom bu 'bum sde la /
NK077(tsu)001:1056: de ltar klu rnams kyang gong ma bzhin tu gyur to //
NK077(tsu)001:1057: phyag na rdo rje 'jigs tshul ldan pa'i sku dang ldan pa des /
NK077(tsu)001:1058: gnod sbyin rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa mthun par /
NK077(tsu)001:1059: gnod sbyin grags ldan mchog skyongs la bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:1060: des gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la /
NK077(tsu)001:1061: des gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong la /
NK077(tsu)001:1062: des gnod sbyin tshom bu 'bum sde la /
NK077(tsu)001:1063: de ltar gnod sbyin rnams kyang gong ltar gyur to //
NK077(tsu)001:1064: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la gsang bdag gis chos bshad tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1065: 'di nyid yin la thub pa'i dbang pos mya ngan
NK077(tsu)001:1066: las 'das khar ji ltar lung bstan pa 'di ltar
NK077(tsu)001:1067: te / mdo'i zhe gsum pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:1068: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK077(tsu)001:1069: lo ni brgya dang bcu gnyis na //
NK077(tsu)001:1070: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:1071: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK077(tsu)001:1072: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK077(tsu)001:1073: mi la skal ldan rigs can te //
NK077(tsu)001:1074: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK077(tsu)001:1075: sngon du ltas rnams snang bar 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:1076: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rtser //
NK077(tsu)001:1077: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK077(tsu)001:1078: lang+ka yi bdag po la sogs pa //
NK077(tsu)001:1079: lag na rdo rje gnang bar 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:1081: thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:1082: brgyad kyi dus su dam pa'i rigs can lnga ri
NK077(tsu)001:1083: ma la ya'i rtser lhags nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1084: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la gdung tshig mi 'dra ba
NK077(tsu)001:1085: nyi shu rtsa gsum gyi sgo nas gsol ba btab
NK077(tsu)001:1086: pas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi gsan nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1087: lcang lo can du 'dus nas gsang bdag la bka' bgro mdzad /
NK077(tsu)001:1088: gsang bdag gis zhal gyis bzhes pa'i rjes thog nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1089: ston pa gsang ba'i bdag po ri ma la yar
NK077(tsu)001:1090: dam pa'i rigs can lnga'i spyan sngar mngon sum du
NK077(tsu)001:1091: gshegs nas chos gsung pa 'di ltar ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1092: de yang chos gsung yul dam pa'i rigs can lnga ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1093: lha'i rig pa 'dzin pa lha grags ldan mchog skyongs te blo gros mtha' yas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1094: klu las klu rgyal 'jog po ste blo gros 'dus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1095: gnod sbyin las gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong ste blo gros dad sel /
NK077(tsu)001:1096: srin po las srin po lang+ka mgrin bcu ste blo gros thabs ldan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1097: mi las mi dge bsnyen li tsa byi dri ma
NK077(tsu)001:1098: med par grags pa ste blo gros rab zhi zhes
NK077(tsu)001:1099: bya ba dam pa'i rigs can lnga 'di nyid gsang
NK077(tsu)001:1100: sngags rtogs pa'i las 'phro dang skal bar ldan pa
NK077(tsu)001:1102: lung a nu yo ga'i chos mdo snga ma bdun phyi ma bdun rnams gsung pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1103: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par spro na /
NK077(tsu)001:1104: spyi bcing 'grel pa nang la gzigs mdzod /
NK077(tsu)001:1105: tha snyad pa 'ga' zhig gi gong gsang ba'i bdag po mngon gshegs kyi skabs la /
NK077(tsu)001:1106: gsang bdag gis bye ba bzhi thub pa'i 'bru ga
NK077(tsu)001:1107: nyer rnams byed 'dug ste don chung bas ma bkod
NK077(tsu)001:1108: / khyad par du rgyal po dza la gsang sngags bab cing 'grub pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1110: za hor gyi yul a par ta mu nya'i rgyal
NK077(tsu)001:1111: po u ta dz+nya na zhes bya ba'i bu rgyal
NK077(tsu)001:1113: d+ha he da le zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:1114: in tra pu tri zhes kyang bya ba /
NK077(tsu)001:1115: 'di sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rang gis zhal slob yin par snang /
NK077(tsu)001:1116: 'di nyid theg chen rten gyi gang zag gsang sngags
NK077(tsu)001:1117: kyi rigs can de la gsang bdag gis dam pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1118: rigs can lnga la lung a nu yo ga'i chos
NK077(tsu)001:1119: gsung pa dang dus mnyam du tri shang a su
NK077(tsu)001:1121: gsang sngags phyi rgyud la sgrub pa byed zhing yod la rmi ltas bdun shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1122: de'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:1123: ri ma la ya de'i shar lho na /
NK077(tsu)001:1124: tri shang a su ra'i brag phug zhes bya ba na /
NK077(tsu)001:1125: phug rin po che zur brgyad du yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1126: sgo rin chen zla gam du dod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1127: ngos la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo byung ba /
NK077(tsu)001:1128: log la brag seng+ge dkar mo khyi tshugs su yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1129: mkhar yang thog sum rim dang bcas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1130: steng bya ka len ta kas tshang bcas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1131: chos thams cad thig le nyag gcig tu sgrogs nas yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1132: rtsa ba na bdud rtsi'i chu mig rang rdol yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1133: mdun na me tog gi snam bu yod pa shing yal ga phyogs bzhir gyes pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1134: dus bzhi'i dgra las skyobs pa ltar yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1135: shing de'i me tog dang 'bras bu sman du gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:1136: zos na nad sna tshogs sos pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1137: de lta bu'i nyams dga' ba'i gnas khang der /
NK077(tsu)001:1138: las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams bgrod du thar la /
NK077(tsu)001:1139: las dang skal bar mi ldan pa rnams kyis ni bgrod du mi thar ba'i gnas khang de nang /
NK077(tsu)001:1141: gsang sngags phyi rgyud la bsgrub pa mdzad cing bzhugs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:1142: rmi ltas bdun zhag re la rmis yang skad /
NK077(tsu)001:1143: zhag gcig la rmis yang skad /
NK077(tsu)001:1144: de la rmi ltas dang po ni phyag na rdo rje mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon te /
NK077(tsu)001:1145: sku'i gnas nas 'od zer 'phros te gdul bya thams cad kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs /
NK077(tsu)001:1146: gsung gi gnas nas bstan pa dang theg pa'i sgra bsgrags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1147: gdul bya thams cad go bar mdzad /
NK077(tsu)001:1148: thugs kyi gnas nas rdo rje 'od 'bar ba byung nas rgyal po'i thugs kar thim /
NK077(tsu)001:1149: spyi'i gtsug nas nyi ma byung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1150: rgyal po'i gtsug tu thim pa rmis so //
NK077(tsu)001:1151: de yang dgongs 'dus kyi 'grel pa lung bstan rdo rje las /
NK077(tsu)001:1152: sku gsung thugs kyi rtags thim pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1154: rmi ltas de ni bag chags kyi sgrib pa thams cad byang ba'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1156: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi nyi ma zla ba la bcibs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1157: phyag na gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:1158: pa bsnams nas sems can thams cad la chos kyi
NK077(tsu)001:1160: de yang chos kyi bgro ba mdzad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1162: rmis ltas de ni chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1164: nas mkha' la sprin gser gyi kha dog can chags /
NK077(tsu)001:1166: cho 'phrul gyi 'brug dam pa chos kyi sgra 'ur ti ri ri sgrogs pa rmis te /
NK077(tsu)001:1168: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1170: de ni thugs rjes 'gro la chos kyi char chen po 'bebs pa'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1172: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas bdud rtsi chu rgyun bab ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1173: sa phyogs thams cad chags chags gdab /
NK077(tsu)001:1174: gdul bya thams cad kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1175: kun kyang rdo rje rnal 'byor ma zhes gsang sngags kyi sgra ti ri ri grags pa rmis so //
NK077(tsu)001:1177: bdud rtsi'i char du bab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1179: ltas de ni 'gro ba kun gyi gsang sngags kyi don rtogs pa'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1181: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas rin po che'i sgrom gyi
NK077(tsu)001:1182: nang rin po che mthing gi shog gu la gser
NK077(tsu)001:1183: gyi rgya rang nan du bris pa'i po ti dang
NK077(tsu)001:1184: / glegs bam skar mda' sa la bab tsam lhung gis rmis so //
NK077(tsu)001:1186: rin chen char du bab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1188: ltas de steng du glegs bam bab pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:1189: chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ba'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1191: po ti glegs bam de rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:1192: rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:1194: la las ni bskor ba byed /
NK077(tsu)001:1195: la las ni bstod pa byed pa'i sgra sgrogs pa rmis so //
NK077(tsu)001:1197: pu tsa rgya chen byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1199: ltas de ni gsang sngags kyi che ba ston pa'i snga ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1201: nam mkha'i mthong na gzugs su ma grub pa'i lung ston pa'i sgra /
NK077(tsu)001:1202: las dang skal bar dang ldan cing //
NK077(tsu)001:1203: bsod nams chen po dra ma khyod //
NK077(tsu)001:1204: sprul pa ji ltar lung bstan zhing //
NK077(tsu)001:1205: rgyal ba 'byung bar lung bstan pas //
NK077(tsu)001:1206: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /skal ldan khyod la sgrogs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1207: ltas de ni gsang ba dam pa rgya cher sgrogs pa'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1209: der rgyal po rnal sad de /
NK077(tsu)001:1210: mkhar gyi yang thog tu sku chags su byon pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1211: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje'i sku /
NK077(tsu)001:1212: rgyu rin po che smug po las grub pa khru gang pa gcig bzhugs cing gda' skad /
NK077(tsu)001:1215: zhabs spyi bo'i gtsug tu blang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1216: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad mchog sku /
NK077(tsu)001:1217: 'dren pa mchog gi dpal lags gang //
NK077(tsu)001:1218: mos pa'i yid kyi lha mchog khyod //
NK077(tsu)001:1219: sngon tshe gong nas bsgrub pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:1220: las kyi 'brel pa'i lha mchog khyod //
NK077(tsu)001:1221: bskal pa brgyar yang mi gtong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:1223: yi dam gyi lhar bzung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1224: zla ba bdun du bsgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1225: po ti dang glegs bam de rnams mngon sum du bab cing /
NK077(tsu)001:1226: de'i byin brlabs snang ba dpe char shar ba yin skad /
NK077(tsu)001:1227: rgyal po rang gi las dang smon lam rnam par /
NK077(tsu)001:1229: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje phrin las gnyis 'brel pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1230: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje bstan pa phun sum tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:1231: pa de nyid / re zhig po ti glegs bam
NK077(tsu)001:1232: gyi tshogs su snang ba la rgyal po rang gis
NK077(tsu)001:1233: mngon sum du brtags pa'i po ti rnams kyi nang
NK077(tsu)001:1234: pa de nyid / nas / rdo rje sems dpa'
NK077(tsu)001:1235: zhal mthong gi le'u dang thugs kyi bsgrub pa'i le'u
NK077(tsu)001:1237: thugs kyi bsgrub pa de nyid kyi sgo nas rdo
NK077(tsu)001:1238: rje sems dpa' de nyid zla ba bdun bsgrub nas
NK077(tsu)001:1239: rdo rje sems dpa' dngos su grub nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1240: mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon te zhal bstan nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1241: rigs kyi bu dngos grub ci 'dod gsung pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:1242: glegs bam 'di dag gi don rtogs par 'tshal /
NK077(tsu)001:1244: rigs kyi bu phung po sbyangs shig /ma 'ongs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1245: dus na gsang bdag gis lung bstan par 'gyur ro
NK077(tsu)001:1246: // zhes gsungs nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK077(tsu)001:1247: yang zla ba bdun du gsang ba'i bdag po bsgrubs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1248: gsang ba'i bdag po dngos su byon la /
NK077(tsu)001:1249: rdo rje sems dpa'i lung bstan pa'i smon pa'i lha phyag na rdo rje dang de ru mjal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1250: rdo rje lan gsum nam mkha' la bsor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1251: gsang sngags mnyam pa nyid kyi don spang blangs med pa brtul zhugs kyi dbang bskur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1252: bka' lung bstan pa'i dngos grub de nas thob bo //
NK077(tsu)001:1253: de lta bu'i gsang sngags mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas
NK077(tsu)001:1254: lugs rtogs shing khong du chud pas don dam bcud
NK077(tsu)001:1255: kyi de nas rgyas zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1256: de'i dus su po ti glegs bam rnams ma 'dres
NK077(tsu)001:1257: par rtogs shing bdag gzhan gnyis kyi don lhun gyis
NK077(tsu)001:1258: grub pas na 'dod pa'i bsam pa de ru 'grub
NK077(tsu)001:1259: ces zer ro // yang lugs gcig la /
NK077(tsu)001:1260: de rgyal pos po ti glegs bam de rnams la brtag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1262: gdul bya gzu lum can dang ras gcod can dgag pa'i phyir du /
NK077(tsu)001:1263: ma rtogs pa ltar du snang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1264: 'jig rten khams na mkhyen pa su che byas /
NK077(tsu)001:1265: za hor yul na rgyal po u pa ra dza zhes bya ba /
NK077(tsu)001:1268: khong nyid kyis kyang rgyal po'i thugs kyi rtogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:1269: ma chod kyi dogs nas byon du ma bzhed skad
NK077(tsu)001:1270: / po ti dang glegs bam rnams rta dang glang
NK077(tsu)001:1271: po che la khol la thog cig /ngas brtag go
NK077(tsu)001:1272: / gsungs nas / po ti dang glegs bam rnams stag sgro gzig sgro'i nang du bcug nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1273: a ka ru dang du ru ka la sogs pa'i spos sna tshogs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1274: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i pu tsa sna tshogs dang bcas te spyan drangs te /
NK077(tsu)001:1275: khong gis brtags pas tshig gcig kyang brda' ma mjal skad /
NK077(tsu)001:1276: sngon gyi mtshan rtags dang sbyar na /
NK077(tsu)001:1277: rgyal po nyid kyis rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1278: gsungs nas tshur spyan drangs skad /
NK077(tsu)001:1279: yang rgyal po nyid kyis brtags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1281: ma rtogs pa ltar snang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1282: yang 'jig rten gyi khams na mkhyen pa su che /
NK077(tsu)001:1284: sangs rgyas rin chen mang gis sprul pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1285: dge slong ku ku r+aa dza mkhyen pa rgya che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1287: spyan drangs su btang bas rgyal po'i thugs kyi rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:1288: pa ma chod kyi dogs nas byon du ma gnang
NK077(tsu)001:1289: bar / po ti dang glegs bam stag sgro dang gzig sgro'i nang du bcug nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1290: a ka ru dang du ru ka la sogs pa'i spos sna tshogs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1291: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i bye brag sna tshogs dang bcas pa spyan drangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1292: dge slong ku ku r+aa dza nyid kyis brtags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1293: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud bya ba /
NK077(tsu)001:1295: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs sgrub kyi le'uma /
NK077(tsu)001:1296: rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:1297: zla ba bdun du bsgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1298: rdo rje sems dpa' ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo la byon te /
NK077(tsu)001:1299: rigs kyi bu si ti ci 'dod /
NK077(tsu)001:1301: bstan pa dang theg pa tha dag rtogs pa'i dngos grub zhu /
NK077(tsu)001:1303: phyag na rdo rjes lung bstan par 'gyur gyi gsung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1305: phyag na rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1306: rdo rje lan gsum bsor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1307: spangs len brtul zhugs spyod pa'i dbang //
NK077(tsu)001:1308: dge bas bkur nas sdig pa med //
NK077(tsu)001:1310: rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i mtshan nyid theg pa spangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1311: rtsol ba med par gsang sngags kyi theg pa nyams su len pa khyod la /
NK077(tsu)001:1313: bstan pa thams cad rdzogs par dbang bskur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1314: tshig gi bstan pa de dag dge slong li tsa byi dri ma med pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:1315: zhus gcig par lung bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1316: ku ku ra dzas gsang ba'i bdag po'i bka' bzhin du bsgrub cing /
NK077(tsu)001:1317: rgyud sde de rnams la tan tra chen po sde
NK077(tsu)001:1318: bco brgyad du phyes nas skal ldan rgyal po dza
NK077(tsu)001:1319: la gsungs so // rim par tshogs bsgrub cing 'grub pa'i lo rgyus so //
NK077(tsu)001:1321: rgyal po dzas glegs bam gyi don rtogs shing grub
NK077(tsu)001:1322: pa thob pa'i rjes de nas dzam bu gling gi
NK077(tsu)001:1323: yul dbus rgya gar rdo rje gdan steng gi shar
NK077(tsu)001:1325: byang shar gyi phyogs mtshams su ri ma la yod pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:1326: za hor gyi yul na yin /
NK077(tsu)001:1328: a su ra gsang ba'i brag phug yod kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:1329: pho brang dam pa de'i dbyibs rin po che zur brgyad du yod /
NK077(tsu)001:1330: sgo rang byung zla gam du yod de'i nang du
NK077(tsu)001:1331: ngo mtshar gyi ri mo bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:1332: dang / nyi zlas mtshan pa yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:1333: de'ang rang bzhin gyi bzang ba /
NK077(tsu)001:1334: grub pa thob pa rnams kyi byin gyis rlabs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1335: de sa thams cad kyi zhabs kyis bcag pa'i gnas
NK077(tsu)001:1336: mchog dam pa'i khang bu ru bsgrub pa po'i gang
NK077(tsu)001:1337: zag ji lta bu zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:1338: ku ku ra dza yis dpon byas pa'i tshom bu 'bum /
NK077(tsu)001:1339: in tra pu ti yis dpon byas pa'i tshom bu khri dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1340: sing+ha u pa r+aa dza yis dpon byas pa'i tshom bu stong dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1341: sras mo go mas dpon byas pa'i tshom bu brgya /
NK077(tsu)001:1342: sa la sogs zhes pa sogs khung na sh+aa kya su tri /
NK077(tsu)001:1344: sangs rgyas gsang ba yan chad bsdus so //
NK077(tsu)001:1345: 'di rnams kyi thog mar sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dbang
NK077(tsu)001:1346: phyi nang gsang gsum thob nas thos bsam gyis lta
NK077(tsu)001:1347: ba rtogs shing / tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi mthar phyin nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1348: sbyor lam zhi khro'i tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gcig gsum lnga pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1349: dkyil 'khor rgyas bsdus 'bring gsum de rnams tshogs lam
NK077(tsu)001:1350: du sbyangs pa gang song ba gcig 'dir mngon du
NK077(tsu)001:1351: bsgrub ste / gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:1352: bzhi thob nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:1353: 'chang gi bar mngon du gshegs so //
NK077(tsu)001:1354: brtsam pa mi 'gyur ba bya ba'i phyir bshad par dam bca' ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1356: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas gsang ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:1357: bdag pos dam pa'i rigs can lnga la chos bshad
NK077(tsu)001:1358: pa dang / rgyal po dza la brgyud pas dang por khungs btsun /
NK077(tsu)001:1359: de nas ku ku ra dza la sogs pa'i tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:1360: bsgrub pas gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK077(tsu)001:1361: thob pas / bar du grogs bzang /
NK077(tsu)001:1362: 'di nyid kyi don nyams su blang na 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las bsgrol bas /
NK077(tsu)001:1363: tha mar skyabs che ba la sogs pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK077(tsu)001:1364: gsum dang yon tan mtha' yas pa de lta bu
NK077(tsu)001:1365: 'dug pa'i phyir / bdag lta bu la spangs rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:1366: mthar phyir pa med kyang sangs rgyas gsang ba'i mtshan
NK077(tsu)001:1367: thob pa ngas bstan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1368: zhes khengs bskyung ba'i tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:1369: gang gis don du bstan na /
NK077(tsu)001:1370: dam pa'i rigs can zhes bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1371: dam pa yang dag pa gsang sngags kyi rigs can slob dpon nyid dang lhan gcig pa'i 'khor /
NK077(tsu)001:1372: rgya gar na sgeg pa'i rdo rje la sogs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1373: bod na bran ka mur ti /
NK077(tsu)001:1374: sbas many+dzu sh+r+ai la sogs pa ra ma ste ya
NK077(tsu)001:1375: rab rnams dang de dang rjes su mthun pa'i ma
NK077(tsu)001:1376: 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa skal ba dang ldan pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1377: don bya ba'i phyir bstan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1378: gang nas btus te bstan na /
NK077(tsu)001:1379: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i le'u
NK077(tsu)001:1380: stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud dag las bsdus te bstan
NK077(tsu)001:1381: pa'o // gang bsdus te bstan na /
NK077(tsu)001:1382: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi gshegs shul /
NK077(tsu)001:1383: da lta dang ma 'ongs pa rnams kyi lam /
NK077(tsu)001:1384: lam de yang theg pa 'og ma'i lam las khyad
NK077(tsu)001:1385: par gsum gyis 'phags pas na mchog ces bya ste
NK077(tsu)001:1386: / khyad par gsum gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:1391: bskal pa grangs med gsum du bsgrub mi dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:1392: tshe gcig gis 'bras bu thob pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:1394: nyon mongs pa spangs ma dgos par /
NK077(tsu)001:1396: de nyid lam du khyer bas chog go //
NK077(tsu)001:1398: 'og ma'i lam 'di'i lam stegs su sngon tu song bas rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1399: gshegs pa'i gting mtha' ma lus par khong du chud cing /
NK077(tsu)001:1400: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pas rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1402: lam gyi nang nas nye lam bde rdzogs shing //
NK077(tsu)001:1403: thabs kyi nang na ma nor dam pa'i mchog /ces sogs /
NK077(tsu)001:1404: 'di zhes pa nye bar mtshon pa'i tshig yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:1405: gsang sngags kyi snying po gzhi lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i chos 'di bstan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1406: tshul ji ltar du bstan na /
NK077(tsu)001:1408: rgyud sde dag na 'thor ba phyogs gcig tu bsdus la /
NK077(tsu)001:1409: 'khrugs pa go rim du bsdeb cing /
NK077(tsu)001:1410: mang ba nyung du bsdus nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1411: zab mo'i don rnams rgyas par bkrol te bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1412: dus gang gi tshe bstan na /
NK077(tsu)001:1413: dus snyigs ma lnga la nye ba'i shes pa rgyud drang po'i dus kyi tshe na bstan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1414: de la snyigs ma lnga gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:1420: de la dus kyi snyigs ma ni rtsod ldan no //
NK077(tsu)001:1421: sems can gyi snyigs ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1424: tshe lo brgya pa man chad /
NK077(tsu)001:1426: mi dge bcu la longs spyod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1427: nyon mongs pa'i snyigs ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1429: dgos ched ci'i phyir bstan na /
NK077(tsu)001:1430: de lta bu sems can 'dul bar dka' ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:1431: nyon mongs pa spangs thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1434: bsgyur thabs kyis 'dul ba'i dus min te /
NK077(tsu)001:1435: gsang sngags bla med kyi 'dul ba'i dus la bab pa'i phyir bstan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1436: spyir bshad par dam bca' ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:1437: dam bca' brtsam tshul dang 'brel pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1440: mdor bstan dang las sogs rnams shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1441: gzhung gi don la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1442: brgyud pa'i man ngag med na rang nyams kyi mi rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1445: man ngag mi nyams par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:1446: snod brtag cing sbyin mi sbyin gyi dmigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1447: snod ldan la sbyin pa'i man ngag rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1450: brgyud pa'i man ngag med na rang nyams kyi mi rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1452: spyan bzang zhes pa long ba la bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1454: u lu tra sha ka zer /
NK077(tsu)001:1458: 'o na long ba'i sgra bshad pa na /
NK077(tsu)001:1459: zha ba dang 'du shes chung ba gnyis ci la bshad zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:1460: de ni de'i mtshan nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:1461: de la 'gro ba'i nus mthu med pa'i dmigs bu ste long khrid dam /
NK077(tsu)001:1462: lam mkhan dang 'dra ba de dang bral ba'i dbang
NK077(tsu)001:1463: gis 'gro nyams med de lam stor bas lam la
NK077(tsu)001:1464: bsgrod cing rang gi 'dod pa'i gnas su phyin par
NK077(tsu)001:1465: mi nus pa'i dpe de bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:1466: tshig phyir blo 'drang ba'i blo rtsing po rgyud ma
NK077(tsu)001:1467: sbyangs shing ma dul ba'i dmu rgod de lta bu'i
NK077(tsu)001:1468: rang bzo'i rang nyams kyis gsang ba'i snying po'i don
NK077(tsu)001:1469: rtogs shing 'bras bu mthar phyin par mi 'gyur te
NK077(tsu)001:1470: / dper na bul shing zhes bya ste thang shing
NK077(tsu)001:1471: smug po la gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu me tog
NK077(tsu)001:1472: dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu shing thog gnyis ka
NK077(tsu)001:1475: gnas skabs kyis 'bras bu dang mthar thug gis 'bras bu gnyis ka 'byung bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1476: 'di rnams la bshad tshul 'bru yi 'dug sa bsgyur
NK077(tsu)001:1477: don gyi go rim bsdebs nas bshad par 'dug ste
NK077(tsu)001:1478: / rgyud yin na bshad lugs de mi phyed pa'i thabs med /
NK077(tsu)001:1479: man ngag bstan bcos 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:1480: tshig 'khrugs kyang don ma 'khrugs par yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1481: dkrugs nas ma bsdebs kyang 'gal ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:1482: des na brgyud pa'i man ngag dang ldan pa'i bla ma bsten dgos pa de la gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:1484: bla ma bkur ba'i thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1486: des na brgyud pa'i man ngag dang bla ma nyams ldan ma bsten na /
NK077(tsu)001:1487: don gsang ba'i snying po sems kyi gnas lugs mi rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:1488: gnas skabs mthar thug gi 'bras bu mi thob pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1489: skyon yod pa de bas na bla ma rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:1490: slob dpon dam pa de rgyud lung rnams kyi nang
NK077(tsu)001:1491: nas bshad pa bzhin du bkur dgos pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1494: bla ma sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK077(tsu)001:1495: zhes bla ma sangs rgyas dang mnyam par bltas te bkur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1496: bla ma lnga bcu pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:1497: bla ma dang ni rdo rje 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:1498: tha dad par ni mi blta'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1500: bla dang sangs rgyas tha dad med par bltas te bkur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1502: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas bas //
NK077(tsu)001:1503: bla ma gnyan par shes par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:1505: bla ma sangs rgyas gnyan pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1506: lhag par bltas te bkur ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1507: 'di rnams la bla ma sangs rgyas dang mnyam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1508: bla ma sangs rgyas dang tha dad med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1509: bla ma sangs rgyas bas lhag pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1514: zhib tu bshad rgyu yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:1515: yi ge mang dogs pa'i phyir ma bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:1516: slob dpon gyis slob bu'i snod brtag par bya'i phyir spyo ba byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:1518: zhe gcod pa'i tshig rtsub ci smras pa thams cad kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:1520: de yang tshul ji ltar bsam nas bzod par bya snyam na /
NK077(tsu)001:1521: 'jig rten tshe 'di'i sdug bsngal gyis mthong ba'i gdung ba ci byung yang khur du mi lta'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1522: ci'i phyir khur du mi blta na /
NK077(tsu)001:1523: brtag spyo zhe gcod la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal de
NK077(tsu)001:1524: dag kun tshe phyi ma'i gtan tshigs te yun gyi
NK077(tsu)001:1526: khur ba'i yon tan la gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:1528: bla ma khur ba'i yon tan gdams ngag gnang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1530: sgo gsum gyis dka' ba'i bla ma bsten cing khur na bla ma rdo rje rgyal po des /
NK077(tsu)001:1531: nga la chos zab mo 'di lta bu yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:1532: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs pas /
