NK077(tsu)001:1533: man ngag sbyin pa zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK077(tsu)001:1534: gdams ngag nyams kyis gnang ba thob par gyur te
NK077(tsu)001:1535: gnang ba thob pas de'i tshe rgyud chen gsang ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:1536: snying po'i le'u dgu pa'i gzhung 'di nas bshad pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1537: yon / rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK077(tsu)001:1538: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyigs //
NK077(tsu)001:1540: ces gsung pa bzhin phul nas zhus na bla ma
NK077(tsu)001:1541: de'i thugs kyi snying khu man ngag zab mo rnams
NK077(tsu)001:1542: slob bu de la ster bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1543: gdams ngag gnang ba'i yon tan sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1545: man ngag thob pa'i gang zag de yis dper na
NK077(tsu)001:1546: bzhon pa ni rta dang glang po che yin la
NK077(tsu)001:1547: bzang ba ni chos gsum dang ldan pa yin te
NK077(tsu)001:1548: gang zhe na / mgyogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1551: de gsum dang ldan pa'i bzhon pa bzang po de
NK077(tsu)001:1552: zhon nas 'gro ba'i mi de rang gi gang 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:1553: pa'i gnas su myur du phyin par byed pa bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:1554: du / don gsang ba'i man ngag rdzu 'phrul rta dang 'dra ba /
NK077(tsu)001:1555: stobs glang po che dang 'dra ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1558: tshe gcig gis 'bras bu thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1560: nyon mongs pa lam du byed pas bde ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1561: gol ba'i dbang du mi 'gro bas brtan pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1562: de lta bu'i man ngag la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1563: bzhon pa bzang po zhon nas 'gro ba'i gang zag bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:1564: 'bras bu'i gnas su phyin par byed pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1565: de yang lam gyi bgrod tshul ci lta bu'i 'bras bu'i gnas su phyin par byed zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:1566: 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa ltar rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba mthong /
NK077(tsu)001:1567: gsum pa nas bdun pa'i bar /
NK077(tsu)001:1568: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1569: sbyor lam bar chad med par tshom bu tshogs bsgrubs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1570: le'u brgyad pa ltar 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan
NK077(tsu)001:1571: nyid rig 'dzin bzhi bgrod nas le'u dgu pa ltar
NK077(tsu)001:1572: mthar thug gi 'bras bu thams cad mkhyen pa ye
NK077(tsu)001:1573: shes chen po'i gnas su phyin par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1574: bzhi bsgrod nas zer ba 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:1577: lam rim pa ltar bgrod nas 'jug pa yin nam min /
NK077(tsu)001:1579: rnam smin thob nas tshe dbang bgrod dgos par thal /
NK077(tsu)001:1580: min na bzhi bgrod nas zer ba'i gzhung 'di dang 'gal /
NK077(tsu)001:1582: spyir lam sa tha dad kyi dbang du bzhi bgrod /
NK077(tsu)001:1586: tshe dbang du bgrod thabs med /
NK077(tsu)001:1587: de gnyis gang rung gcig thob nas gong ma la sbyor ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:1588: gnyis pa snod brtag pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:1592: snod bcud 'dzom nas zab mo'i gnas lugs rtogs cing /
NK077(tsu)001:1593: mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob pa'i yon tan yod
NK077(tsu)001:1594: pa de bas bla ma rdo rje slob dpon slob
NK077(tsu)001:1595: bu yal bar mi gtong ba'i gnyer dang ldan bas
NK077(tsu)001:1597: slob bu snod dang ldan mi ldan rgyang nas brtag pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1600: dad pa che chung gi lo rgyus rnams zhib par dris te brtag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1602: lus ngag gi bya spyod brtson 'grus drag zhan /
NK077(tsu)001:1603: dam pa'i chos kyi snod du rung mi rung zhib par brtag par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1605: rngam glog ltar byis pa gtsang ma'i sems la pra phab nas brtags pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1606: mkha' 'gro ma la gtor ma byin pa yis gsang
NK077(tsu)001:1607: sngags ston du rung mi rung gi ltas rmi lam
NK077(tsu)001:1608: du ston gcig ces brtag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1609: sngar bzhin spyo ba sna tshogs byas pa'i sgo nas brtag par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1610: de ltar brtag thabs lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1611: gzhan yang thabs sna tshogs kyi sgo nas slob bu
NK077(tsu)001:1612: de snod du rung mi rung ci nas kyang brtag
NK077(tsu)001:1614: snod ldan la man ngag kyi thugs sbyin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1616: de ltar slob bu'i snod brtag pas bzang ba'i mtshan nyid dang ldan na phyir mi ldog pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1619: dang po nas gsang sngags kyi don la mi bskrag pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1620: rang bzhin gyis rigs nges pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1621: dkyil 'khor la zhugs nas dbang zhu zhing dam tshig gi bslab bya la nan tan byed pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1622: bslab bya la rigs nges pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1623: lta ba rtogs pa ni rigs mthong ba'i rigs nges pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1624: de ltar gsang sngags kyi theg pa 'di las gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:1625: du blo mi ldog cing brtan par bya ba'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:1626: dbang bskur dam dbog par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1627: snod de rtas shing rgyud min pa yi sang tri
NK077(tsu)001:1628: ta'i skad du shi sha bod skad du slob bu
NK077(tsu)001:1629: ste / snod dang ldan pa gang yin de'i lag tu man ngag zab mo rnams gtad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1630: snod ngan la mi sbyin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1633: snod ngan la mi sbyin zhing 'tsham par don bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1635: gong ltar snod brtag pas ngan pa'i mtshan nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:1636: skyon rtags mthong ba'i mngon sum du shes pas slob
NK077(tsu)001:1637: dpon gyis snod dang mi ldan pa'i gang zag la
NK077(tsu)001:1638: man ngag zab mo mi sbyin par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1639: de yang snod dang mi ldan pa'i mtshan nyid ci lta bu zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:1640: chos nyams su blang mi bsam par tshe 'di'i zas
NK077(tsu)001:1641: nor la sogs pa bsgrub pa'i 'dod pa phra mo'i
NK077(tsu)001:1642: rgyur chos byed pa dang 'jig rten gyi rnyed pa
NK077(tsu)001:1643: dang bkur sti la sogs pa'i khe dang 'jig rten
NK077(tsu)001:1644: gyi chos brgyad grags pa che 'dod pa'i rgyu ru
NK077(tsu)001:1645: chos byed cing chos par barloma pa ni snod dang
NK077(tsu)001:1646: mi ldan pa'o // snod ngan pa'i skyon bzhi ni
NK077(tsu)001:1647: man ngag gi bcud chen po rjed nges par mi
NK077(tsu)001:1648: go ba bar 'dzag pa ni snod zhabs rdol lta
NK077(tsu)001:1649: mi ldan pa'o // bu'i skyon dang / rang gis
NK077(tsu)001:1650: shes mi khom par gzhan la ston pas gsang mi
NK077(tsu)001:1651: thub pa ni dbo ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1652: snod gzhog ral lta bu'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1653: man ngag zab mo bstan kyang mi go ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1654: mi chags pa ste snod kha sbub lta bu'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1655: thub mtha' mi gcig pa'i gzhung gzhan dang 'dres nas rang gis chos la the tshom za ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1656: ma rung par byed pa ste snod dug can lta bu'i skyon dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1657: gzhan yang snod ngan gyi mtshan nyid la 'jig rten
NK077(tsu)001:1658: gyi longs spyod zang zing gi dngos po zas nor
NK077(tsu)001:1662: mi 'dod pa de bla ma la 'bul zhing gtong /
NK077(tsu)001:1663: dmar ba'i bzang po dbus ste zhes par drang po 'dod pa de rang gis 'ching ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1665: gang zag g.yo can ngo dga' che la ltag pa
NK077(tsu)001:1666: sprod pa dang lkog tu bskur pas 'debs pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:1667: / bla ma'i lkog na spyod pa rang dgar byed cing spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1668: kha snying so sor byed pa ngag la rigs nges te bzang po zlo /
NK077(tsu)001:1669: bsam pa la mi nges ste ngan pa sems pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1670: bud med yin yang sems 'dod chags gis dbang du song ste 'dod pa des /
NK077(tsu)001:1671: gnyen po dang ngo tsha med par rang khar shor ba'i phyal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1672: 'di bud med zer yang pho mo thun mong gi skyon yin par 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:1673: mun pa'i khrod dang mi med pa'i lkog tu gang
NK077(tsu)001:1674: 'phrad par 'dod chags spyod pa la snyegs pa ste
NK077(tsu)001:1675: / de lta bu'i gang zag pho mo gang yin
NK077(tsu)001:1676: yang tan tra ste rgyud sde rnams nas snod ldan
NK077(tsu)001:1677: / du ma basngagasa / yin pa la yun bskal
NK077(tsu)001:1678: par lus dang grib ma bzhin du 'khor bar 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:1679: / du ma basngagasa / yang / thugs kyi bde
NK077(tsu)001:1680: ba de sems kyi gnas lugs dus gsum sangs rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:1681: kyi dgongs pa zab mo de spro bar mi bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:1682: / du ma basngagasa / yang / // 'o na thugs rje ye med dam /
NK077(tsu)001:1683: gdams ngag mi sbyin nam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:1684: kho rang dang blo 'tsham par lha'i sku sgom thabs tsam bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:1685: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig gcan gzan gyi 'phrang dang 'dra ba sbyin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:1691: skyo shas zhen log /byams snying rje /
NK077(tsu)001:1692: gsang sngags 'di'i lam stegs kyi chos rnams bshad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1696: 'tshams par don byas pa de lta bu min na
NK077(tsu)001:1697: yang dper na be'u rgyag bardzuda gnyis ske sbrel nas
NK077(tsu)001:1698: ri la btang na rdzud pa de g.yang du lhung
NK077(tsu)001:1699: ba'i zhor la rgyag pa de yang g.yang du skyur
NK077(tsu)001:1700: bar 'gyur ba bzhin du dpon slob gnyis ka ngan
NK077(tsu)001:1702: slob dpon de zas nor 'dod pa'i khengs sems kyis
NK077(tsu)001:1703: blo phrog ste bsnyen bkur la bltas shing mi chos
NK077(tsu)001:1704: kyi lcam phyar che bar gyur te gdams ngag 'chol
NK077(tsu)001:1705: par btang bas snod kyi skyon ma rtogs par snod
NK077(tsu)001:1706: ngan la zab mo'i chos spros ste bshad na bsil
NK077(tsu)001:1707: ba'i tshal la sogs pa dur khrod kyi gleng brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:1708: kyi las kyi ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma rnams
NK077(tsu)001:1709: dur khrod kyi ro la bya dang gcan gzan 'dus
NK077(tsu)001:1711: nyams pa can de la mkha' 'gro ma legs nyes kyi ltangs 'dzin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:1712: dam tshig gi rjes gcod pa rnams kyis tshe 'di
NK077(tsu)001:1713: la de'i sha za nas srog la 'bebs shing phyi
NK077(tsu)001:1714: mar ngan song du ltung bar 'gyur ba'i skyon chen
NK077(tsu)001:1716: snod kyi skyon yon brtag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1717: snod dang mi ldan pa la zab mo'i chos mi sbyin pa ni shin tu gal che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1718: de la dur khrod chen po'i gnas ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1719: bdud rtsi bam brgyad nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:1720: rgya gar yul na bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod
NK077(tsu)001:1721: sing ga la'i yul na sku la rdzogs pa'i dur
NK077(tsu)001:1722: khrod / kha che yul na he chen bdal ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:1723: dur khrod ma la ya na gsang chen rol pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1724: khrod / dur khrod / bal po'i yul na lhun grub brtsegs pa'i dur khrod /
NK077(tsu)001:1725: o rgyan yul na pad ma brtsegs pa'i dur khrod /
NK077(tsu)001:1726: za hor yul na lang ka brtsegs pa'i dur khrod /
NK077(tsu)001:1727: li'i yul na 'jig rten brtsegs pa'i dur khrod dang brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:1728: dur khrod chen po'i gnas de rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:1729: mkha' 'gro ma srin mo king thod ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1739: zhes rgyas par spro na gong du sbyar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1740: snod ldan la sbyin pa'i man ngag la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:1744: gong du snod kyi skyon yon shes shing de ltar
NK077(tsu)001:1745: brtag pa'i don snod ldan bzang po las 'phro skal
NK077(tsu)001:1746: ldan gyi don bya ba'i phyir du lus rnam par
NK077(tsu)001:1747: bzhag pa'i mdor bstan du bshad par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1749: brjod bya don gyi rnam grangs phye na bcu gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:1750: brjod byed tshig gi gzhung tshad le'u dgu /
NK077(tsu)001:1753: lam la mtshan nyid gsum dang lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1754: de dag gi tshig don ni 'di lta ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1757: 'bras bu gsum ston par byed pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:1759: ma bcos ma bslad par rang bzhin rang byung gi
NK077(tsu)001:1760: ye shes lam dang 'bras bu thams cad kyi dngos
NK077(tsu)001:1761: po bden gsum dbyer med du ye nas rang la
NK077(tsu)001:1762: gnas pa ni gzhi'i don ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1763: de ston par byed pa'i le'u dang po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1764: gnyis pa lam la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1765: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1766: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1767: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:1768: dang po rgyud shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1769: der mthong zhes pas gzhi'i don de nyid shes rab spyan gyis phyin ci ma log par /
NK077(tsu)001:1770: bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba ci bzhin pa rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1771: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid de /
NK077(tsu)001:1772: le'u gnyis pas rgyas par bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:1773: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:1774: der 'jug ces pa gcig char ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1777: bden gsum dbyer med du goms par byed pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1778: le'u gsum pa'i khog stod nas ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:1779: gnyis pa rim gyis 'jug pa tshogs sbyor gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:1782: de la dang po stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1783: le'u gsum pa'i stod ma gtogs pa'i gzhung hril pos ston /
NK077(tsu)001:1784: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor ni le'u bzhi pas ston /
NK077(tsu)001:1785: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor ni le'u lnga pas ston /
NK077(tsu)001:1786: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor ni le'u drug pas ston /
NK077(tsu)001:1787: sbyor lam la bar chad med pa bsgrubs zhes pas zag med kyis mthong lam la sbyor ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:1788: lam gzhan gyi bar ma chod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1789: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pas na bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1790: de ni le'u bdun pas rgyas par ston to //
NK077(tsu)001:1791: de lnga ni rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:1792: gsum pa 'bras bu'i mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:1796: dang po mthong lam la gnyis yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:1797: blo chung rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1798: blo che ba tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:1799: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:1800: mthar lam lhun grub pa'i rig 'dzin dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:1801: 'di bzhi ni gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med kyi rig 'dzin bzhi yin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1802: rgyas pa le'u brgyad pas ston /
NK077(tsu)001:1804: lam des gzhi ci lta ba bzhin mngon du byas
NK077(tsu)001:1805: pa ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu ste le'u dgu
NK077(tsu)001:1810: brjod bya don la bcu gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:1811: brjod byed tshigs la le'u dgu yod pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:1812: rgyas bshad kyi skabs la de rim pa ltar brjod par bya ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:1813: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1814: gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1815: lam rang gnas rtogs shing goms par bya ba'i thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1816: 'bras bu rang gnas mngon du byed pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1822: gong du gzhi lam 'bras gsum bshad pa de la /
NK077(tsu)001:1823: dang po gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:1824: rgyas par spros nas bshad pa'i gzhi gnas lugs de
NK077(tsu)001:1825: nyid skal ldan de yis shes par bya ba ni
NK077(tsu)001:1826: 'di lta ste / gzhung rgyas pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:1827: rang bzhin ye shes rang gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1828: de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1829: 'khrul yang lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med de rang la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1832: gzhi chos kun rang snang la 'khor 'das gnyis su med par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1834: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di chos can /
NK077(tsu)001:1835: de sa'i ngo bo nyid de yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:1836: dam bca' gtan tshigs 'khor ba sems nyid rang snang yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:1837: sems nyid rang snang yin pa 'di bsgrub pa la bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1840: gcig la du mar snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1841: shes pa gsum gyi rjes su 'jug pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1842: gzhan yang snang ba sems yin pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK077(tsu)001:1844: shes pa'i mtshan nyid gsal zhing rig pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:1845: gsal rig dang mi ldan pa'i shes pa mi srid pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1846: shes bya'i chos thams cad sems su grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1848: tshogs drug gi chos thams cad sems las tha dad du bden pa med de /
NK077(tsu)001:1849: lhan gcig du gsal ba nyams su myong ba yod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:1850: dper na 'dod chags kyi rtog pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:1852: shes bya'i chos thams cad sems yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:1853: chu gcig la rigs drug gi mthong snang bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:1855: snang ba thams cad sems yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:1856: shes pa gsum gyi rjes su 'jug pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1857: gzhan yang snang ba sems yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1860: nang sems thog tu btsal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1862: sems nyid dngos po med cing 'dus ma byas yin lugs /
NK077(tsu)001:1863: zhib tu ngo sprad rgyu yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:1864: snyan brgyud zhal gyi gdams pa khrid ces bya ba la shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:1867: phyi nang gi chos thams cad sems yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1868: sems dngos po med cing 'dus ma byas pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:1869: gtan tshigs de'i phyir na rin po che'i gling du
NK077(tsu)001:1870: phyin na sa rdo brtsal bas mi rnyed pa bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:1871: du / de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid te /
NK077(tsu)001:1873: rnam grangs bsam yas su snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1874: 'o na mya ngan las 'das pa'i mthar lhung ngo
NK077(tsu)001:1875: zhe na 'khor ba'i rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu mi
NK077(tsu)001:1877: de la ltos pa'i 'bras bu mya ngan 'das pa phyogs gcig tu yod pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:1878: 'khor 'das dbyer med 'khor 'das gnyis kyis mtha' las grol ba'i spyi gzhi chen mo yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:1879: ma rtogs sems can gyi 'khrul gzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1880: ma dag kun gzhi yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:1881: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1882: rtogs pa sangs rgyas kyi grol gzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:1883: stong nyid rtogs pa'i shes rab zer yang /
NK077(tsu)001:1884: bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba khong du chud dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:1885: 'khor 'das tha dad la skyon brjod pa la gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:1887: 'khor 'das rang bzhin tha dad pa'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1890: de ltar mya ngan las 'das pa'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1891: 'khor ba'i rgyud dang rang rgyud pa tha dad du
NK077(tsu)001:1892: grub pa med pas gnas lugs byang chub kyi sems
NK077(tsu)001:1893: mchog lhag pa'i chos sku chen po dag gi ngo
NK077(tsu)001:1894: bo de la 'khor 'das so so'i rang bzhin tha
NK077(tsu)001:1895: dad rang rgyud du nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:1897: 'khor ba de la yang dag pa'i lam gyis mya
NK077(tsu)001:1898: ngan las 'das par bsgyur zhing bcos su med de
NK077(tsu)001:1900: ngo bo tha dad pa'i skyon dpe dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1902: 'das pa yang dag par sangs rgyas de bzhin gshegs pa dang 'khor ba'i log rtog gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:1903: ngo bo nyid kyi tha dad du gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1904: zhe na 'khor ba de la mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam gyis bcos shing bsgyur du med de /
NK077(tsu)001:1905: dper na rin chen 'ching bu la phyag dang mchod pa byas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:1906: nor bu rin po che lta bu'i yon tan mi
NK077(tsu)001:1907: 'byung ba bzhin tha dad na 'khor ba la 'das
NK077(tsu)001:1909: de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1911: 'khor 'das tha dad la skyon yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1912: de bas dbyer med yin pa de lta'ang 'khrul ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:1913: tshul 'og nas 'byung ba 'di bzhin du 'khrul pas
NK077(tsu)001:1914: so // 'khrul tshul 'di la sa nang tshan du bcad na /
NK077(tsu)001:1924: rgyu lhan gcig skyes pa'i ma rig pa ngo ma shes /
NK077(tsu)001:1925: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas log par rtog
NK077(tsu)001:1926: pa sna tshogs kyi zhags pa dang 'dra bas 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:1927: ba'i rgyu byas / las gsum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1928: nyon mongs pa lnga dang brgyad kyi rkyen gyis 'khor ba 'byung ba'i rkyen byas /
NK077(tsu)001:1929: 'khor tshul rten 'brel bcu gnyis tshul du srid pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:1930: 'khor lo'i gnas su yang nas yang du bskyar nas
NK077(tsu)001:1931: / lus can rnams dngos su 'khor la /
NK077(tsu)001:1932: lus med rnams bag chags gis tshul du 'khor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:1933: 'bras bu ni rten phyi snod kyi 'jig rten gnas tha dad du snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1934: nang bcud kyi sems can ni lus dang longs spyod la sogs 'dod pa tha dad pa'i don no //
NK077(tsu)001:1935: de yang bde ba 'dod pa'i zhen pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1936: sdug bsngal gyis dogs pa'i lus sems shin tu gdung
NK077(tsu)001:1937: ba'i nyams thag cing thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen
NK077(tsu)001:1939: dus ni 'khor brtsom pa'i dus thog ma med pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1943: rang bzhin ye shes rang gnas nyid las nyams pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:1944: gong gi rtsam med bzhi dus kun tu nyams /
NK077(tsu)001:1946: 'khor ba brtsam pa'i dus thog ma med pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1948: dag pa'i don las nyams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1949: zhes pa'i 'bru gnon pa yang 'dug go //
NK077(tsu)001:1950: 'khrul yang lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med de rang la gnas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:1952: dpe dang sbyar te mdor bstan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1954: 'khrul par shar ba'i dus de lta'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:1955: dper na rgyal po'i phru gu 'bangs su 'khyam /
NK077(tsu)001:1956: zhes pa skabs 'dir 'bangs kyi stong thun rgyas par bshad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:1957: ngo sprad gal che ste 'dir yi ge mang dogs pa'i phyir ma bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:1958: don de bzhin du 'khrul kyang chos nyid kyi rigs las gzhan du 'gyur ba med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1959: shul dang don 'bras bu rang las gzhan min pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:1960: dper na lha 'khrul dag'i longs spyod rang la 'khrul
NK077(tsu)001:1961: nas rang gis longs spyod pa'i tshul lta bu ste
NK077(tsu)001:1962: 'bras bu gzhan las min te rang la gnas pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:1963: // spyir gzhi lam 'bras gsum gcig gam tha dad /
NK077(tsu)001:1965: gcig la gsum du dbye ba don med la /
NK077(tsu)001:1966: mi gcig na gtan la dbab mi btub zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:1967: ngo bo gcig yin te byed las kyi sgo nas gsum du dbye dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:1969: rtogs pa'i cha nas lam brtan pa thob pa'i cha nas 'bras bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:1970: lam dang 'bras bu gzhan med de rang la gnas
NK077(tsu)001:1971: pa de'ang kun rdzob don dam dbyer med kyi rnam
NK077(tsu)001:1972: pa gsum gnas pa'i tshul du lus rnam par bzhag
NK077(tsu)001:1974: don rgyas pa la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:1975: kun rdzob tu lam 'bras bu gzhan med rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1980: kun rdzob tu gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:1982: sems nyid rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad yi ge
NK077(tsu)001:1983: dpa' bo 'bru lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gnas
NK077(tsu)001:1984: pa de / me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:1988: h+aa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:1989: yang na gzugs la sogs pa phung po lnga sku lnga yin /
NK077(tsu)001:1990: lus skur gnas te mtshon pa /
NK077(tsu)001:1991: ngag gsung du gnas te mtshon pa +aah yid thugs su gnas te mtshon pa h'u /
NK077(tsu)001:1992: so so'i don dgos 'dod 'char bas yon tan te /
NK077(tsu)001:1994: bya ba byed pa phrin las te /
NK077(tsu)001:1996: de lta bu'i yi ge sku dang ye shes rang chas su ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:1997: gnas pa'i cha nas gzhi yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:1999: mngon du gyur pa'i cha nas 'bras bu yin pas thabs chen po zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:2001: rgyud drug las kyi 'gro ba kun la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2002: de yang lus can rnams la dngos su gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:2003: lus med rnams la bag chags kyi tshul du gnas so //
NK077(tsu)001:2004: tshul ji ltar du gnas na rang bzhin ngang gis gnas pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2005: gnas lugs dmar mchan ltar shes par mdzad do //
NK077(tsu)001:2006: 'di ni kun rdzob tu gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2007: re zhig sku dang ye shes nyid ma rtogs pa'i lus can rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:2008: yi ge'i gzugs su gnas pa kho na la dgongs so //
NK077(tsu)001:2009: dper na shes rig gzung 'dzin rang kha ma 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:2010: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la ngo sprad pa lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2012: rgyud don rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2013: lam gyi ngo bo rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2014: cha rkyen rang la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2015: rgyud don rang gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2018: spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab
NK077(tsu)001:2019: sum bcu rtsa gnyis gdugs phub pa'i tshul du gnas
NK077(tsu)001:2020: / mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo na rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:2021: 'dab bcu drug /bum pa d+r+wa bar bcug pa'i tshul
NK077(tsu)001:2022: / du gnas / snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:2023: pad ma 'dab brgyad gyes pa ltar gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:2024: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:2025: gru gu btings pa ltar gnas so //
NK077(tsu)001:2027: 'khor lo de dag gi g.yas na rtsa ro ma /
NK077(tsu)001:2029: dbus na kun d+har ma gsum gyi 'khor lo bzhi la /
NK077(tsu)001:2030: kun d+har ma srog shing gis tshul dang gnyis pa rlung non gyis tshul du gnas so //
NK077(tsu)001:2031: rtsa gsum 'khor lo bzhi 'di rnams las /
NK077(tsu)001:2032: gdugs dang gdung 'gyog gi tshul du 'dod pa dang nya rgya brkyangs pa lta dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2033: spos rgya btab pa lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2034: dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dzing pa lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2035: thang shing skyes pa lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2038: de rnams kyi brtsegs lugs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2039: yi ge'i gnas tshul la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2040: mkhas pa rnams kyi bzhed gzhung mi 'dra du ma
NK077(tsu)001:2041: snang ngo gdul bya blo rigs bsam gyis mi khyab
NK077(tsu)001:2042: pa'i don la / 'dul byed ston pas 'dul thabs mtha' yas pa gsungs pa yang /
NK077(tsu)001:2043: gang la gang 'dul de la der ston yin pa ltar 'di yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2044: nam yang 'gal bar mi sems so //
NK077(tsu)001:2045: gong gi 'khor lo bzhi'i gnas na ka li la
NK077(tsu)001:2046: sogs pa'i sgra yig dang dbyangs yig bcu drug la
NK077(tsu)001:2047: sogs pa dang ldan par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2048: tshul ci ltar gnas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2054: yum ni gsang ba'i mkha' la ldan par gnas pa 'di ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2055: thabs lam 'og sgo'i ston 'khor phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2056: thabs lam steng sgo'i ston 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2057: srog mi shig pa'i thig le snying po rlung gi sgrom bu gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:2058: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo'i steng na yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:2059: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas bshad dmar mchan ltar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:2060: de ltar gleng gzhi gnyis po de yi tan tra te rgyud kyi don bde gsal mi rtog pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2061: lam sa rnams kyi ngo la mngon sum du 'byin par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2062: de ltar gong du bshad pa bzhin gnas pa'i cha nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2065: blangs ba'i cha nas gleng bslangs /
NK077(tsu)001:2066: nyams su blang ba'i cha nas rgyud don no //
NK077(tsu)001:2069: gleng gzhi gnyis kyi skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:2071: zhor la bshad dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2072: rgyud don gyi ngo bo thabs shes yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:2073: thabs sgra yig ka li rang la gnas lugs /
NK077(tsu)001:2074: shes rab dbyings yig a li rang la gnas lugs yin par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2076: rang la gnas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:2078: grol lam rang rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2080: tan tra de yis don ston par byed pas rgyud don grol lam rang la gnas lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2081: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo gsang ba'i rlung gi
NK077(tsu)001:2082: sgrom gyi gnas de na mdun chos nyid kyi rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:2083: thig le mi rtog par gnas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2084: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2085: g.yas ye shes kyi rtsa thig le 'gags med du gnas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2086: kun snang gis ting nge 'dzin ni snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2087: g.yon yon tan gyi thig le bzhi lha'i sku yab yum du gnas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2088: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2089: rgyab na las nyid kyis dkyil 'khor te dbang po
NK077(tsu)001:2090: rang rgyud kyi rtsa'i thig le lha du mar char
NK077(tsu)001:2091: du gnas pa / phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor rang la gnas tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:2092: de ltar rnal 'byor lam gyi rim pa rnams rang bzhin gyis gnas te /
NK077(tsu)001:2093: de ltar yin pa'i don rtogs shing goms pa mngon du 'char ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2094: thabs lam rang la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2096: de yang thabs lam rang la gnas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2097: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags rang la gnas pa nyid la bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2098: 'o na des 'khor ba 'grub par byed pa'i rgyu yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2099: lam du ji ltar 'gyur zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2101: chags pas khams 'grub gcig shos kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:2102: zhes pas chags pa rang khams khams gsum 'khor ba 'grub par byed pa'i rgyu yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:2103: gcig shos te chags pa thabs kyis zin na rang
NK077(tsu)001:2104: bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes 'grub par byed
NK077(tsu)001:2107: phrin las rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2109: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo la gnas pa'i phrin las bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2115: rtsa de rnams kyi 'od kyi kha dog ni bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2129: drag po rnams rim pa ltar sbyar bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2130: 'khor lo bzhi la phrin las bzhi gnas tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2131: gnas bzhi'i 'byung ba'ang zhes pa'i gnas snying kha /
NK077(tsu)001:2134: sgrom mdo bzhi na yod pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:2139: phrin las bzhi'i ngo bo yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2143: rlung drag po'i phrin las yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:2144: phrin las bzhi 'og sgo la gnas tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2145: yum gyi gsang ba'i mkha' la yang phrin las bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:2146: rang bzhin gyi ye nas lngan par gnas pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:2147: te / de yang phyi khyams gru gsum drag po /
NK077(tsu)001:2148: bar khyams gru bzhi rgyas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2150: dbyings phyug gi sna rtser sna tshogs mdud pa zlum po zhi ba'i las so //
NK077(tsu)001:2153: chos nyid kyi rtsa'i thig le de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ste bsnyen pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2154: ye shes kyi rtsa'i thig le kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2156: yon tan gyi rtsa'i thig le phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ste bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2157: rang rgyud kyi rtsa'i thig le /
NK077(tsu)001:2158: spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ste bsgrub pa chen po /
NK077(tsu)001:2159: de ltar bsnyen sgrub bzhi yang rang bzhin gyis ye nas rang la ldan par gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2160: de la bsnyen pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2161: rtsa gnas thig les gang ba smin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2162: de la rang bzhin gyi bde ba 'byung ba nye bsnyen /
NK077(tsu)001:2163: de ltar ngos zin nas nyams su blang bsgrub pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2164: bde ba rgyas te mngon sum du myong ba ni bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2165: de ltar nyams su len pa ni bsnyen rgyud zhal gyi gdams pa las shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:2168: rtsa ba'i rtsa bzhi de la phye na /
NK077(tsu)001:2170: yon tan gyi rtsa la gsum gsum ste drug /ye
NK077(tsu)001:2171: shes dang rang rgyud kyi rtsa la ma phye bas
NK077(tsu)001:2172: gnyis te / yan lag brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:2173: shi ra na rtsa la ma d+ha la dkyil 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:2174: te srog mi shig pa'i thig le bam gi dbyibs
NK077(tsu)001:2176: rtsa brgyad po 'khor du gnas pa'i phyir dkyil 'khor rang la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2179: de yang sum mdor ram las me /
NK077(tsu)001:2182: g.yas kyi rtsa ro ma ni dgang gzar /
NK077(tsu)001:2183: g.yon gyi rkyang ma ni blugs gzar //
NK077(tsu)001:2184: dbus kyi kun d+har ni me lha //
NK077(tsu)001:2185: ye shes snying po ni bsreg lha //
NK077(tsu)001:2186: nyon mongs pa la sogs rnam par rtog pa'i tshogs ni bsreg rdzas ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2187: de ltar sbyin bsreg yang rang bzhin gyi ye nas rang la lngan par gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2190: gnas pa rtsa dang brten pa thig le la /
NK077(tsu)001:2191: phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2192: nang nus pa'i dbang lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2193: gsang ba zab mo dbang gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2194: dbang chog bco brgyad po rnams rang bzhin ye nas rang la ldan par gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2195: dbang bco brgyad po 'di rnams kyi gnas tshul rgyas par dmar ma chan ltar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:2198: gsang ba'i mchod pa rang la gnas tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2199: thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i snyoms 'jug gi
NK077(tsu)001:2200: dus su gsang ba'i lha mo bcu gnyis shar ba
NK077(tsu)001:2201: yin te / sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:2202: dgugs dang 'dzin pa de bzhin te //
NK077(tsu)001:2204: sdom dang mi gtong dbang bskur te //
NK077(tsu)001:2205: bde ba'i sgra snyan phyogs bcur sgrogs //
NK077(tsu)001:2206: shin tu sgegs pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK077(tsu)001:2209: gzugs mdzes spyod pas phyogs bcur g.yos //
NK077(tsu)001:2210: kun tu tshim byed bro bsrung thims //
NK077(tsu)001:2213: bdud rtsi bsil dro 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK077(tsu)001:2215: gsang mchod kyi skabs 'dir gsang ba'i lha mo bcu gnyis don bshad dgos pa gzhan du shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:2216: de rnams dngos su snang ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2218: med na mi 'byung ba'i tshul gyis rang la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2226: 'dod yon gyi mchod pa rang la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2227: gsum pa dam rdzas kyi mchod pa rang la ldan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2228: lte ba'i rtsa na sha chen /
NK077(tsu)001:2229: lang ka'i rtsa na dri chen /
NK077(tsu)001:2230: a ba d+hu ti na byang sems /
NK077(tsu)001:2233: de dag ni dam rdzas kyi mchod pa yin te rang la gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2236: gong du bstan pa de dag rang la gnas shing
NK077(tsu)001:2237: de las mi 'da' bas lus ngag yid gsum las
NK077(tsu)001:2238: / rang bzhin ye nas lhag par gnas pa'i phyir sa ma ya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2240: spyod pa rang la gnas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2242: rang bzhin gyi sgo nas lus ngag yid gsum gyi 'du byed kyi spyod pa ni gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2243: phyi ltar na lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod pa dngos su spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2244: nang ltar na rtsa'i kha dog dbyibs su yod pa ni lus /
NK077(tsu)001:2245: rtsa'i nang na thig le yi ge'i dbyibs su yod
NK077(tsu)001:2246: pa ni ngag /de la gnas pa'i tshul gyi rtag
NK077(tsu)001:2247: pa bde ba'i rang bzhin du yod pa ni yid
NK077(tsu)001:2248: do // gsang ba'i lugs ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:2249: gsang ba'i yul pad ma lus /
NK077(tsu)001:2250: gsang ba'i dbang po rdo rje ngag /gsang ba'i rnam shes yid do //
NK077(tsu)001:2251: yang na phyi lus kyi spyod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2253: gsang ba yid kyi spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2254: de ltar phyi nang gsang gsum lus ngag yid gsum gyi 'du byed kyi spyod pa thams cad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2256: spyod pa nyid du rang bzhin ngang gi ye nas rang la ldan par gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2257: 'bras bu rang la gnas pa gnyis bgrang /
NK077(tsu)001:2258: rtog tshogs lha'i dal du las dang ngo bo 'bras bu rang la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2260: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su 'dus ma
NK077(tsu)001:2261: byas cing dbyer med pas rdo rje phung po lnga
NK077(tsu)001:2262: / 'byung ba lnga'i yan lag dbang po rnam shes
NK077(tsu)001:2263: yul dus la sogs pa rtog pa'i tshogs thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:2264: / kun / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yab lnga dang
NK077(tsu)001:2265: yum lngar grags pa'i sogs gi sgras rtog pa bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:2266: bcu rtsa gnyis rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rang
NK077(tsu)001:2268: des na phyi nang gi dngos po kun ni chags zhes pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2269: phyi yul rnams yum du sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2270: nang phung po lnga yab du sangs rgyas pa'i tshul gyi 'bras bur gnas pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2271: de la b+hee pa'i byed las dang rang gi ngo
NK077(tsu)001:2272: bo rtog tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor du gzhi gdod ma
NK077(tsu)001:2273: nas sangs rgyas pas 'bras bur rang la gnas nas
NK077(tsu)001:2274: yod do // dpe dang sbyar te rtog tshogs rgyal ba'i sku ru sangs rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2277: don gyi go rim bsdebs nas bshad dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:2278: gong gi rgyu rkyen rten 'brel 'dus nas snang la rang bzhin med pa sgyu ma'i dpes mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2279: phung po lnga dang khams bco brgyad skye mched bcu
NK077(tsu)001:2280: gnyis rnams rgyu rkyen gyis rang rgyud du grub pa
NK077(tsu)001:2281: med pa ni / log rtog sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2282: snang ba gzung du med pa chu zla'i dpe mtshon
NK077(tsu)001:2283: nas phyag rgya bzhi rdzogs lha'i dkyil 'khor so sor
NK077(tsu)001:2284: phyag rgya ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gsal
NK077(tsu)001:2285: la rtog pa med pa ni phyag rgya sgyu ma'o
NK077(tsu)001:2286: // 'gro 'ong med la cir yang snang ba sprul
NK077(tsu)001:2287: pa lta bu'i dpes mtshon pa bzhin de ltar lha'i
NK077(tsu)001:2288: sku phyag rgya de dag kyang gdul bya'i ngo la
NK077(tsu)001:2289: sems kyi ngo bo cir yang shar bas sna tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:2290: su 'gyur zhing gang du bsam pa ltar snang bas
NK077(tsu)001:2291: cir yang 'grub pa ni rig pa sgyu ma'i /
NK077(tsu)001:2292: yang na gong gi de rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:2294: yang dag /thabs sgyu ma zhes kyang brjod do //
NK077(tsu)001:2295: rtogs ldan pa'i dgongs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:2299: sprul pa bzhin du snang la rang bzhin med pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2300: de nyid gzhi rdzogs phyag rgyar ma 'dres gsal /
NK077(tsu)001:2301: de nyid ci ltar bsam pa bzhin sgom zhing nyams su blangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2302: ji ltar bsam pa bzhin du 'byung ba la //
NK077(tsu)001:2305: kun rdzob kyi gnas tshul 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:2306: mu stegs pa ltar rtag lta mi red pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK077(tsu)001:2307: gsang sngags bla med kyi dgongs pa khyad par can yin pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK077(tsu)001:2309: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du phye ba 'di nyid la dgongs gzhi dgos ched yod lugs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2312: cha rkyen rnams kyi lam skor 'di rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:2313: gzhi rang la gnas pa'i rgyu mtshan zhib tu bshad rgyu yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:2314: yi ge mang gi dogs pa'i phyir ma 'grel lo //
NK077(tsu)001:2315: 'di rnams la 'bru gnon kho nas mi chog go //
NK077(tsu)001:2316: don khung du chud dgos pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:2317: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa bzhi la /
NK077(tsu)001:2318: bsnyen sgrub bzhir ngo sprad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2319: phrin las bzhir ngo sprad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2320: ting nge 'dzin bzhir ngo sprad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2321: ston 'khor phun sum tshogs par ngo sprad pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:2322: ma 'dres par khung du chud cing shan 'byed pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2324: 'di 'di la dgongs zer ba gcig dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:2325: spyir mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi yon tan tshur bsdu na /
NK077(tsu)001:2326: sku gsung thugs phrin las lnga yin /
NK077(tsu)001:2327: de sems can gyi dus su rang gnas ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2328: lus ngag yid gsum gyi bya byed /
NK077(tsu)001:2329: dgos 'dod 'byung ba gnyis dang lnga yin /
NK077(tsu)001:2330: 'di lnga ma gtogs pa'i snang ngo la /
NK077(tsu)001:2331: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga yin byas na the tshom za /
NK077(tsu)001:2332: rtogs pa'i snang ngo la 'di bcu chos mthun cing /
NK077(tsu)001:2333: 'di la logs nas lam dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams thob byar med pa thag chod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2334: gong gi kun rdzob kyi gnas tshul rnams kyang 'di dang 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2335: kun rdzob kyi gnas tshul 'di gsang sngags kyi khyad chos yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:2336: don gyi gnas tshul ni theg pa thun mong pa phal cher dag gis 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:2337: don dam du lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med par rang la gnas pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:2339: don dam du gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2341: don dam la chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su dag par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2343: gnas tshul gsum las dang po kun rdzob bstan nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2344: 'dir bar ma don dam pa'i bden pa la lam dang 'bras bu'i chos rnams rang la gnas te /
NK077(tsu)001:2346: gtan tshigs ci'i phyir na chos kun gang yang rigs
NK077(tsu)001:2347: rgyud tha dad dngos po phyogs gcig tu rtag par
NK077(tsu)001:2349: 'o na 'khor 'das gnyis snang la sogs pa zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2350: chos kun sems nyid rang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:2351: de bzhin du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad /
NK077(tsu)001:2352: kun kyang gong gi lam de dang 'bras bu de gnyis dbyer med pa dang mtshungs te /
NK077(tsu)001:2355: de zhes pa snyegs pa'i tshigs yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2356: gang gi gang yang rigs rgyud rtag min pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2357: zhes pa de dang sems phyir de gnyis la /
NK077(tsu)001:2358: 'bru gnon pa yang 'thad 'dug /de yang spyir 'khor ba'i chos su snang ba /
NK077(tsu)001:2359: gzugs kyi sgo nas dbyibs dang kha dog gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2360: pho mo ma ning gi mtshan ma gsum yod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2361: mtshan ma med pa sgong nga lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2362: bye brag tu khams gsum gyi gnas mtho dman de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2363: nang tshan ris mi 'dra ba 'dod khams la bzhi cu rtsa gcig pa sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2364: sde tshan so so'i cha nas rang rgyud pa dngos
NK077(tsu)001:2365: por grub pa yod pa min te don dam rig
NK077(tsu)001:2366: pa spros bral gyi ngang la yul med du yongs
NK077(tsu)001:2367: su rdzogs pa'o // rtogs ldan pa'i bzhed la /
NK077(tsu)001:2368: gzugs gnyis mtshan gsum yod dang med /
NK077(tsu)001:2369: 'di khams gsum la 'bru gnon pa yang 'dug go //
NK077(tsu)001:2371: dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pa dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2372: gong du bshad pa'i don dam pa ma 'dres yongs
NK077(tsu)001:2373: rdzogs de nyid gnyis 'dzin gyi yul dang bral bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:2374: du 'khor ba'i chos ma spangs par de nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:2375: ngor / dkor bdun ldan pa'i tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2376: bsgrub bya'i don gyi snying po'i mchog tu gyur pa
NK077(tsu)001:2377: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK077(tsu)001:2378: lnga ni 'bras bu'i don dam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2379: don dam rtogs pa'i 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:2380: chos kyi dbyings phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:2381: yi rig pa'i ye shes ni rig pa'i don dam
NK077(tsu)001:2382: pa'o // chos nyid mu mtha' dang bral ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2384: de ltar sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:2385: dbyings ye shes gnyis te dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2388: dbyings don dam gsum yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:2389: lhag pa'i don dam pa'i bden pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:2390: dper na dpag bsam gyi shing dang rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:2391: bdun ni gsum po de kun snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2392: 'o na ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub bya ba'i don gang yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2394: bskyed bya bskyed byed kyi rgyu 'bras dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2395: rnam par bzhag 'jog gi rgyu 'bras dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2396: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu 'bras so //
NK077(tsu)001:2398: rgyu la 'bras bu'i ngo bo ma grub la /
NK077(tsu)001:2399: rkyen dang 'phrad na de bskyed pa'i nus pa tsam gcig gnas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2400: dper na sa bon dang myu gu'am /
NK077(tsu)001:2401: me dang du ba lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2403: gtan tshigs blo yul du gyur pa la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2404: bsgrub bya blo yul du ma gyur pa gcig bsgrub pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2405: dper na shing leb gnyis rtse sprad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2406: gnyis ka mi 'gyel ba lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2407: gsum pa ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu 'bras ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2408: rgyu'i dus na 'bras bu ngo bo nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:2410: cha bram nyid chu yin pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:2411: don dam lhag pa'i chos skur gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2413: 'jig rten gyi brtan pa snod dang g.yo ba bcud
NK077(tsu)001:2414: la sogs pa 'khor 'das kyi chos kun snang ba
NK077(tsu)001:2415: nyid na rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba
NK077(tsu)001:2416: ngo bo la dngos por grub pa med de /
NK077(tsu)001:2417: de nyid rnam pa mchog ldan gyi chos sku chen po yin /
NK077(tsu)001:2418: rang de yang rang bzhin nam ngang gis de ltar du gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2419: don dam du gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:2420: chos kun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bshad pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:2421: sems kyi gnas lugs kyis ngo bo'i yon tan yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:2422: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs de nyid la 'bras bu'i che
NK077(tsu)001:2423: yon gzhi nas rdzogs pa dkor bdun ngo bo nyid
NK077(tsu)001:2425: rgyu sems can la ngo bo nyid kyis rgyur gnas lugs /
NK077(tsu)001:2426: gnas dus de'i dri ma med pa don dam lhag
NK077(tsu)001:2427: pa'i chos sku chen por ngo sprod par shes par
NK077(tsu)001:2428: bya'o // 'bras bu rang la gnas pa'i gtan tshigs dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2430: gong du bshad pa'i rang bzhin gnas pa'i don lhag
NK077(tsu)001:2431: pa'i chos sku chen po de las gzhan pa'i 'bras
NK077(tsu)001:2432: bu bzang po gcig gud na thob bya rdul tsam
NK077(tsu)001:2433: yang med de / de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2434: chos kun kyang 'bru'i ngo bor smin zin yin pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:2435: de la gzhan du lam bgrod pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:2436: lam rang la gnas pa'i gtan tshigs dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2438: de ltar don dam de nyid lam gyi yang ngo bo yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2439: dang po de la 'jug cing rtogs par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:2440: bar du gnas shing goms par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:2441: tha ma 'bras bu mngon du 'byin bas phye ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:2442: yang na 'jug gnas 'byin pas phye ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:2444: dang po gzhi la 'jug /bar du lam la gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:2445: tha ma 'bras bu 'byin pa'i bshad pa yang 'dug
NK077(tsu)001:2446: /don dam gnyis med kun gyi dngos por bstan pa
NK077(tsu)001:2448: rang byung gi ye shes ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2450: don dam de nyid chos kun gyi 'byung gnas yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2451: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi
NK077(tsu)001:2452: chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:2453: la sems nyid rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pa rang
NK077(tsu)001:2454: byung chen po khyab bya khyab byed med par kun
NK077(tsu)001:2455: tu khyab / khyab bya khyab byed med pa'i rang
NK077(tsu)001:2456: byung gi ye shes de nyid dngos po mtshan ma
NK077(tsu)001:2457: med par phyogs med kun tu rang snang bas kun
NK077(tsu)001:2458: gyi phyag rgya ste gzhi rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:2459: tu khyab / / lam lta ba'i phyag rgya /
NK077(tsu)001:2460: lhag pa 'bras bu'i phyag rgya dang gsum po kun gyi rgyu yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:2461: chos kun de lta bu'i ngang du gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2462: de'i ming gi rnam grangs kyi kun gyi dngos gzhir bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2464: don dam bcos bslad med las de bzhin nyid mthar thug pa med pas dbyings /
NK077(tsu)001:2465: bsgrib g.yog med par rang gsal bas ye shes te /
NK077(tsu)001:2466: de nyid shes rab stong nyid kho na ma yin
NK077(tsu)001:2467: zhing 'gags pa med par sku dang ye shes su
NK077(tsu)001:2468: 'dod pa'i thabs kyi phyag rgya ste sna tshogs su
NK077(tsu)001:2469: snang bas 'khor 'das kun gyi ngo bo nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:2470: rgyu'o // de yang rkyen bzhi la sogs pa ming
NK077(tsu)001:2471: grangs med pa'i snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:2472: rgyu'o // nyid dang / don dam la 'khor 'das
NK077(tsu)001:2473: kyi chos kun lhag ma med par gnas pa yongs
NK077(tsu)001:2474: su rdzogs pa zhes kyang brjod do //
NK077(tsu)001:2475: dbyer med rang la gnas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:2476: dbyer med la gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa la gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2477: lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med de rang la gnas par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2480: gzhi 'khor 'das dbyer med la ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2482: bden pa gnyis pa'i don gong du song nas gsum pa dbyer med kyi don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2483: don dam stong bar 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2484: kun rdzob snang bar 'dod pa'i dngos por zhen pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:2485: mya ngan las 'das pa dang 'khor ba'i chos kun
NK077(tsu)001:2486: gnyis su med pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2487: gtan tshigs ci'i phyir na ye nas mya ngan las
NK077(tsu)001:2488: 'das pa'i rigs 'khor ba'i rgyu ci snang yang rtag
NK077(tsu)001:2489: pa min pas / bye brag so so'i gzugs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2494: chos la sogs pa 'khor 'das kyi bye brag tha snyad ming du btags pa kun /
NK077(tsu)001:2495: dper na 'ja' tshon sna lnga ma 'dres par snang
NK077(tsu)001:2496: yang nam mkha' stong pa'i ngang du gcig pa ltar
NK077(tsu)001:2497: / kun rdzob rig pa sgyu ma la 'khor 'das
NK077(tsu)001:2498: kyi chos thams cad ma 'dres par gsal yang don
NK077(tsu)001:2499: dam spros bral la nam mkha' lta bur gcig cing
NK077(tsu)001:2501: bden pa dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2503: 'ja' ltar mkha' ltar ma 'dres gsal ba'i don de
NK077(tsu)001:2504: nyid rang byung gi ye shes 'dus ma byas nyid
NK077(tsu)001:2505: 'dus byas ltar snang la 'dus byas su snang ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:2506: dus nyid na'ang / ngo bo rang byung ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:2507: su dbyer mi phyed pa'i don gyis na rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:2508: dus nyid na'ang / nyid zhes bya'o // rang bzhin dbyer med dgos ched dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2510: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med gyi don de rgyal
NK077(tsu)001:2511: ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK077(tsu)001:2513: 'gro ba sems can gyi shes pa sgrin pas ma
NK077(tsu)001:2514: bcos par rang bzhin ni ngang gis bden pa dbyer
NK077(tsu)001:2515: med pa ste'ang gi sgras sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa
NK077(tsu)001:2517: snang ba dang stong pa dbyer med kyi tha snyad
NK077(tsu)001:2518: med kyang de ltar rtogs pa min pa'i tha dad
NK077(tsu)001:2519: du 'dzin pa'i 'khrul snang la snang stong gnyis kyi
NK077(tsu)001:2520: zhen pa yod pas de grol ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:2521: de'i don gyi dbyer med du bstan pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:2522: gnyis can gnyis med byed pa de rang gnyis zhes
NK077(tsu)001:2523: pas ngo bo gnyis can de gnyis med la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:2525: gnyis 'dzin gyi zhen pa grol ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:2526: bden pa dbyer med ces smos pa'i brjod pa tsam
NK077(tsu)001:2527: ma gtogs pa don gyi ngo bo la tha snyad
NK077(tsu)001:2528: gi tshig dang snang stong gnyis par de dbyer med
NK077(tsu)001:2529: bya ba tsam rang du yang /
NK077(tsu)001:2530: blos bsam zhing ngag gis tshig tu brjod pa'i yul
NK077(tsu)001:2531: las kyang 'das te smra bsam brjod du med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:2532: don yin no // yul sems dbyer med rang byung ye shes su bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2534: 'o na shes par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2535: shes par byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis su snang ba 'di ci yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2536: yul dang shes par snang ba de yang ma bcos
NK077(tsu)001:2537: pas rang byung gi ye shes nyid rang snang bar
NK077(tsu)001:2538: zad do // rgyu 'bras phyi nang dbyer med du bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2540: rgyu 'bras gnyis kyi ltar snang yang ngo bo la
NK077(tsu)001:2541: rgyu 'bras gnyis pa med de rang byung ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:2543: phyi snod nang bcud gnyis su gsal ba'ang de sems nyid kyi ngang du dbyer med gcig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2544: lam dang 'bras bu gzhan na med de rang la gnas par bstan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2546: de ltar chos kun ye shes rang la gnas pas
NK077(tsu)001:2547: de lta bu bden gsum dbyer med kyi gnas tshul
NK077(tsu)001:2548: ji lta ba bzhin yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2549: de nyid yang lam dang 'bras bu kun gyi dngos gzhi yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2551: skabs 'dir gzhi lam 'bras gsum po ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:2552: 'bras bu thob par byed pa'i thabs theg pa 'og ma pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2555: bsgyur ba las khyad par du 'phags pas na chen
NK077(tsu)001:2556: po ma h+aa yo ga'i lam gyis nyams su blangs
NK077(tsu)001:2557: pas / 'bras bu mngon sum du snang bar byed pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2559: rang la med pa gcig gzhi nas byung ba ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2560: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub sangs rgyas de nyid rang la 'byung bar zad do //
NK077(tsu)001:2561: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lugs kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:2562: gzhi de nyid gtan la dbab pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2563: lam de nyid nyams su blangs 'bras bu de nyid mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2567: kun rdzob dbyer med kyi ye shes rnams rang la
NK077(tsu)001:2568: lhun grub tu gnas pa de dag gis gsal bar
NK077(tsu)001:2569: ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams gcod
NK077(tsu)001:2570: cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u
NK077(tsu)001:2571: zhes bya ste las bgrang dang po'i don du gada'o
NK077(tsu)001:2572: ////spyi don gnyis pa gtan la phab pa lam gyi
NK077(tsu)001:2573: skabs 'dir khog don la bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2578: mtshan nyid gsum gyi khog don no //
NK077(tsu)001:2580: tshogs lam gyi rim pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2588: le'u gnyis pa rang gnas mthong ba'i le'u ston to //
NK077(tsu)001:2590: le'u gsum pa nas drug pa'i bar /
NK077(tsu)001:2592: da de dag la ci'i phyir tshogs lam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2593: le'u lnga pa der bsod nams ye shes kyi tshogs rgya chen po sogs pa'i phyir tshogs lam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:2594: de yang 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2595: spyod yul kun tu tshad dpag med //
NK077(tsu)001:2596: kun nas nyon mongs spyod pa yang grol //
NK077(tsu)001:2597: thun mong lam gnyis de bzhin pas //
NK077(tsu)001:2598: rnam smin gnyis med tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:2600: tha mal spyod las lhag par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:2601: spyod pa rgyun gyis tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:2604: longs spyod med las thams cad spyod //
NK077(tsu)001:2607: rgyu spyod bsod nams tshogs chen ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:2608: de ming ma chags ye shes che //
NK077(tsu)001:2611: lha yi sku ni gsal sgom na //
NK077(tsu)001:2612: zhes sogs tshigs rkang bzhis bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:2614: spyod bzhin ma chags ye shes yin //
NK077(tsu)001:2615: bde ba'i mchog nyid bsod nams tshogs //
NK077(tsu)001:2616: zhes tshogs gnyis po de lam gong ma bzhi la med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2617: 'di ni gtso bo la btags pa ste tshogs gnyis ma rdzogs par zab mo'i don mi thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2618: tshogs kho na sogs pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:2619: de skad ces bya lam bzhi po la tshogs gnyis shin tu rgya che bar yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:2620: tshogs lam la ming mi 'dogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2621: shugs la rdzogs pa yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2622: chos nyid la sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2626: gtso che bas ming de ltar btags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2627: yang na tshogs bsags pa'i g+ho zug bsam yang na sbyor lam gyi rgyu yin pas tshogs lam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:2629: bar chad med pas tshogs bsgrub le'u bdun pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2631: bar chad med par sbyor ba yi //
NK077(tsu)001:2632: bsgrub pa dus kyi tshogs bshad bya //
NK077(tsu)001:2633: bar chad med pa'i lam bsgrub pa'ang //
NK077(tsu)001:2635: mthong lam la sbyor bas so //
NK077(tsu)001:2636: mthong lam ni le'u brgyad pa'i ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:2637: de'ang kho rang gi skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:2638: zag kun zag pa'i rigs chen 'di zhes tshig rkang bzhis bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2639: chos kun mi mthong chos nyid kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:2642: snga ma mthong ba'i lam nyid du //
NK077(tsu)001:2643: rang gi shes rab gsum goms pas //
NK077(tsu)001:2646: sa yis cha yis phye ba yi //
NK077(tsu)001:2647: nus pa thob dang ma thob kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:2648: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK077(tsu)001:2650: de yang zag med kyi chos nyid rang mtshan mthong ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:2652: phyag rgya chen po ste le'u brgyad pa'i dkyil gyis ston te /
NK077(tsu)001:2653: yang de nyid kyi skabs las zag pa med pa sgom pa'i lam /
NK077(tsu)001:2654: mig g.yo rnal 'byor nyid du yang brjod /
NK077(tsu)001:2656: de yang mthong lam pa'i lam la sgom pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:2659: brgyad pa'i gsham gyis ston te /
NK077(tsu)001:2660: de yang de nyid kyis skabs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2661: tha ma'i ming grangs mthar phyin lam /
NK077(tsu)001:2662: zhes pa tshig rkang bzhi pas gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:2664: de las lam gzhan gyis skye byed du byar med pa'i phyir gzhan yang mdo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2665: in tra b+ho d+his lam lnga bshad pa dang du ma yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2666: kha gcig lam lnga sa gcod pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:2667: mtshan nyid pa'i lugs yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2672: tshe rnam phyag rgya lhun grub rig 'dzin bzhi lam du byed zer ba dag yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2673: 'di rnams ni stod lung gi skabs la gsal bar bstan pa bzhin yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:2674: de rnams dang lam lnga ngo bo gcig yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:2675: gnyis pa zag bcas dang zag med kyi khog don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2676: tshogs bsgrub man chad zag bcas /
NK077(tsu)001:2677: tshe rnam yan chad zag med yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:2679: tshogs bsgrub man chad la lus khams skye gnas kyis zag pa gsum ka yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2680: de yang lus kyi zag pa yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2681: bsgrub pa pos 'tsho ba'i yo byad kha zas la longs spyod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2682: dri chen dri chu la sogs pa 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2683: khams kyi zag pa yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2684: sman dang sman par bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2686: mthong lam ma thob kyi bar du /
NK077(tsu)001:2687: skye gnas kyi zag pa yang yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2688: de phyir dbang bsgyur phyi ma'i dus /
NK077(tsu)001:2689: nyid du sbyor ba'ang smos ci dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:2690: de sogs tshig rkang drug gi gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:2691: gal te sum cu phrag drug nas tshe dbang thob pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:2693: skye gnas kyi zag pa yod dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2694: thob pa'i dus su rang la med la ma thob pa'i dus na yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2695: thob la ci yang ma rag pa'i dus na'ang bar chad 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2696: 'byung na skye gnas su 'gro dgos pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:2697: rnam smin zag med yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2698: zag pa'i gtso bo skye gnas kyi zag pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:2699: rnam smin la de med de /
NK077(tsu)001:2700: lus dang bral ma thag phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2701: tshe dbang la zag pa gsum ka med de /
NK077(tsu)001:2702: zag gsum zag pa 'di la med /
NK077(tsu)001:2704: de ming mi ldog zag med dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2705: dbang bskur dbang bsgyur rigs kyi mtshan la brjod /
NK077(tsu)001:2707: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin yan chad la lta ci smos te //
NK077(tsu)001:2708: gsum pa zag ldog dang bcas /
NK077(tsu)001:2709: ma bcas su sa bcad na /
NK077(tsu)001:2710: zag ldog dang bcas pa'i lam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2711: zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa'i lam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2712: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam dang gsum mo //
NK077(tsu)001:2714: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi'i skabs su na /
NK077(tsu)001:2715: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum yod la /
NK077(tsu)001:2716: dam tshig nyams pa la sogs pa byung na ngan song du ldog la yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:2718: de phyir lam bzhir ldog zag yod //
NK077(tsu)001:2723: zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa'i lam ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2724: sbyor lam bar chad med par tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2725: de yang zag pa yod pa ni sngar bstan to //
NK077(tsu)001:2728: mtshams med pa lnga spyad kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:2729: ngan song du ldog pa med pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2730: der las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa rags pa sbyangs pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:2732: 'gro drug dus gnas de dag snang //
NK077(tsu)001:2733: zhes sogs tshig rkang bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2734: bsod nams ye shes dpung tshogs kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:2735: zhes sogs tshigs rkang gsum gyis gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:2736: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2737: lam mchog rdzogs pa'i tshe yan chod gsungs te /
NK077(tsu)001:2738: rnam smin yan chad zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:2739: bzhi pa mtshan nyid gsum du sa bcad na /
NK077(tsu)001:2744: de dag mtshan nyid bsdu ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2745: shes 'jug man chad mthun par bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2748: gzhi lam rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2749: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid sgom pa nyams su blang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2750: mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid zag med kyi
NK077(tsu)001:2751: lam bgrod tshul gtan la bab pa dang gsum mo
NK077(tsu)001:2753: lam spyir mtshan nyid gsum brtsi ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2754: bye brag tshogs sbyor la brtsi ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2757: dang po'i lam mchog bshad par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:2758: zhes lta ba la mtshan nyid dang por bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2761: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bshad //
NK077(tsu)001:2763: rnal 'byor bzhi sbyor lam dang lnga ru bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2766: mthar phyin 'bras bu mtshan nyid bshad //
NK077(tsu)001:2769: mtshan nyid tha ma'i tha ma ni //
NK077(tsu)001:2772: 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid rig 'dzin bzhi yin la de'i yang tha ma ni sangs rgyas zhes gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2773: mtshan nyid gsum lung las gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:2774: gnyis pa bye brag tu tshogs sbyor gnyis la mtshan nyid gsum du sa bcad na /
NK077(tsu)001:2775: tshogs lam la rgyu shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2778: gsum pa nas drug pa'i bar du /
NK077(tsu)001:2781: spyod lam ste zag bcas kyi lam mthar phyin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2784: skabs kyis rgyu mtshan 'bras gsum ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:2786: de la re zhig mtshan nyid gsum du sa bcad na gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2787: spyi don gnyis pa lam rang gnas shing goms par byed pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:2788: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2789: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2790: gnas skabs kyis 'bras bu zag med kyis rig 'dzin bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2791: de la dang po le'u gnyis pa lta ba bstan pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:2792: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang le'u'i gzhung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2794: de la dang po phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2795: de yang le'u dang por bshad pa bzhin gzhi ye
NK077(tsu)001:2796: shes rang la gnas pa bden gsum gyi don lhun
NK077(tsu)001:2797: grub du gnas pa'i ngang la phyag 'tshal ba ni
NK077(tsu)001:2798: lta ba rtogs pa'i phyag go //
NK077(tsu)001:2799: nas zhes pa 'brel mtshams sbyar ba'i tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:2800: lta ba rtogs pa 'di nyid lam thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro bas dang po'i lam zhes bya /
NK077(tsu)001:2801: de la lta ba dang po'i lam du 'gro ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2802: lam la mos pa'i lam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2803: ci bzhin pa'i lam gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:2804: lta ba ma rtogs pa'i gong du sgom pa thams cad /
NK077(tsu)001:2806: rtogs nas sgom pa thams cad ci bzhin pa'i lam zhes bya /
NK077(tsu)001:2807: 'dir ci bzhin pa'i lam gyi sngon du lta ba 'gro dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:2809: dman la rgya gsum goms brtan dang //
NK077(tsu)001:2810: brten nas rtog dpyod klung zhugs mthong //
NK077(tsu)001:2811: sgom pa lam du bstan par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:2812: rims par skyes la the tshom med //
NK077(tsu)001:2814: lta ba'i sngon du sgom 'gro bar gsungs pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:2815: de la spyir lam la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:2818: de la lta ba'i sngon du sgom pa 'gro ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2819: drang don gyi lam yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:2822: blo dman pa khrid par bya ba'i phyir gsungs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2823: de bas na 'dir nges pa'i don du /
NK077(tsu)001:2824: lam thams cad kyi sngon du lta ba 'gro dgos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2825: lta ba dang po'i lam du bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:2826: yang na gang zag lam du 'jug tshul la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:2827: mkhas pa pan tri ta'i dpyad sgom dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2828: ku su lu pa'i 'jog sgom gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:2830: mgon po byams pa'i zhal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2831: rig pa'i gnas lnga dag la mkhas par ma sbyangs na //
NK077(tsu)001:2832: 'phags mchog gis kyang thams cad mkhyen pa rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:2833: de bas gzhan dag rjes su bzung zhing tshar bcad dang //
NK077(tsu)001:2834: bdag nyid kun shes bya phyir de'i de la brtson //
NK077(tsu)001:2836: dang por rig pa'i gnas lnga la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2837: shes bya phyogs med la sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2838: thos bsam gnyis kyis lta ba gtan la dbab /
NK077(tsu)001:2839: de nas sgom dgos par bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:2841: goms pa bas kyang rtogs pa gces //
NK077(tsu)001:2842: rtogs pa gting du ma gyur na //
NK077(tsu)001:2843: sgom pa mtshan ma'i ngang du sgom //
NK077(tsu)001:2844: rtsol ba nyon mongs zhen pa rtsol //
NK077(tsu)001:2846: gnyis pa sngon la sems 'dzin byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2847: thog mar gnas pa skye gnas pa de'i dri ma phyed /
NK077(tsu)001:2848: snyoms 'jug dgu skor gyi 'phrang la grol nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2849: sems kyi rang bzhin sgrib g.yog thams cad dang bral
NK077(tsu)001:2850: ba lhag mthong gi don mngon gsum du rtogs pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:2852: dmigs pa dag la brten nas su //
NK077(tsu)001:2853: mi dmigs pa dag rab tu skye //
NK077(tsu)001:2855: zhi gnas sgom bas lhag mthong skye //
NK077(tsu)001:2857: 'di nyid ni gtso cher pan tri ta'i bslab lugs kyis dbang btsan du mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2859: lam 'di gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2867: ma 'dres par sangs kyis phyung pa la bshad zer ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:2868: 'dir lta ba'i dgos ched la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2869: don bcu bzhi po rnams ma 'dres par ston pas bshad ces bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2875: gang zag lam pa lta ba rtogs pa'i skal ba
NK077(tsu)001:2876: dang ldan pa gang dag gzhi ye shes rang la
NK077(tsu)001:2877: gnas pa'i don de mthong bar 'dod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:2878: dgos ched la sogs pa don bcu bzhi'i sgo nas ston dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:2879: thog mar lta ba rtogs pa'i dgos ched bstan pa dang gcig /dus bstan pa dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:2882: rkyen dang lnga thabs dang drug /rnam grangs dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:2886: drod dang bcu gcig /rtags dang bcu gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:2888: ma rtogs pa'i skyon bstan pa dang bcu bzhi pos
NK077(tsu)001:2889: mdor bstan 'di dag /yan lag rgyas par bshad cing
NK077(tsu)001:2890: spros pa'i rtsa bar lus rnam bzhag gi sgo nas
NK077(tsu)001:2892: de la dang po lta ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2896: lta ba dang mi mthun pa'i phyogs sel ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:2898: lta ba rtogs cing mthun pa'i phyogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2899: dus gsum kyang sngon la snod brten gyi gang zag bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:2900: dus nye ba rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2901: dus ring ba sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2902: de gnyis kyi go ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2903: sngar theg pa chung ngu ma sbyang /
NK077(tsu)001:2904: theg chen gyi chos go nus rtogs nus kyi blo dang ldan pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:2905: dus nye ba rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:2906: sngar theg pa chung ngu la sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2907: theg chen go nus rtogs nus kyi blo dang ldan pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:2908: dus ring ba sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa zer /
NK077(tsu)001:2910: rims dang gcig char gnyis gnyis su phye ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2912: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2913: sngar theg pa gang la yang ma sbyangs par /
NK077(tsu)001:2914: ma h+aa yo ga la 'jug nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2915: gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa ni rgyu 'bras kyi
NK077(tsu)001:2916: theg pa chen po gang rung gcig la sbyangs nas
NK077(tsu)001:2917: / ma h+aa yo ga la 'jug nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2918: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2919: phal pa'i sems brgyad nas bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2920: yo ga man chad kyi theg pa la rim gyis sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2921: ma h+aa yo ga la 'jug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2922: rim gyis pa'i gcig char ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:2923: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi la sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:2924: phyi rgyud sde gsum dor nas ma h+aa yo gar 'jug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2926: sems skye ba'i rgyu rkyen bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2927: lta ba rtogs pa'i rgyu rkyen gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:2928: dang po sems skye ba'i rgyu rkyen bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:2930: mtshungs par ldan pa'i rgyu dang //
NK077(tsu)001:2931: lhan gcig skyes pa'i rgyu gnyis las //
NK077(tsu)001:2933: bde gshegs snying pos mtshungs par ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:2935: bde gshegs snying po rang chas su yod pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2938: rgyu rkyen lnga po tshogs nas 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2941: rang bzhin rgyu'i bsnyung bar gnas //
NK077(tsu)001:2944: de bdag ces gsungs pas bla ma de bdag po'i rkyen no //
NK077(tsu)001:2947: theg pa chen po'i sgo de dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK077(tsu)001:2948: skad gcig 'phel ba de ma thag ces pa /
NK077(tsu)001:2950: phyi ma phyi mas go phye ba de yang /
NK077(tsu)001:2951: de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK077(tsu)001:2952: de ltar rgyu rkyen lnga po 'tshogs pa de la
NK077(tsu)001:2953: brten nas bla mas theg pa gong ma'i yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:2954: brjod / 'og ma la skyon brjod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:2955: gong ma la dga' brod kyis dngas /
NK077(tsu)001:2958: lta ba rtogs pa'i skyon la gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:2962: rang bzhin bdun dang mtshungs par ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:2963: gcig shos rgyu ru nges pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:2965: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan de mtshungs rgyu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2966: phyi ma ni gang dag gnyan bsam shes rab che /
NK077(tsu)001:2967: nyan cing thos 'dzin bsam pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:2968: bsam pa'i tshe na rtogs dpyod pa //
NK077(tsu)001:2969: gnyis po 'di dag shes pa'i rgyu //
NK077(tsu)001:2972: bsam pa gnyis po de dag lhan gcig byed pa'i rgyur 'dod //
NK077(tsu)001:2979: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu gcig ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2982: mkhan po lung dang man ngag bcas //
NK077(tsu)001:2983: lhan gcig byed pa'i rkyen du 'dod //
NK077(tsu)001:2985: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon lung man ngag dang bcas pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:2988: 'dir ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK077(tsu)001:2990: sems kyi skabs dang mthun no //
NK077(tsu)001:2991: lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i thabs la /
NK077(tsu)001:2992: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste /
NK077(tsu)001:2993: don gyis dmigs bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2994: gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad de don gyi dmigs ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2995: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste don gyi dmigs ngos bzung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:2996: 'di rnams kyi ston thun rgyas pa 'og rtogs thabs rang la 'chad //
NK077(tsu)001:2997: lta ba'i ngo bo dang rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:2998: gtan tshigs kyi ngos nas lta ba'i rnam grangs su bzhag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:2999: rgyud don gyi ngos nas lta ba'i rnam grangs su
NK077(tsu)001:3000: bzhag pa dang lam rim gyi ngos nas lta ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:3001: rnam grangs su bzhag pa dang lta ba rang gi
NK077(tsu)001:3002: ngo bo'i ngos nas lta ba'i rnam grangs su bzhag
NK077(tsu)001:3003: pa dang bzhi'o // dang po ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3004: gtan tshigs gar yod pa na grub mtha' re yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3005: rnam grangs kyang de'i rjes su 'agro'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3007: rgyud don yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po bcu la /
NK077(tsu)001:3011: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba yan chad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3012: mthar phyin pa'i lam man chad la /
NK077(tsu)001:3015: rnam shes tshogs brgyad rang lta ba'i ngo bo yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3016: lta ba'i rnam grangs brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:3018: bdag don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3020: de yang lta ba rtogs pa don du gnyer ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3021: lta ba rtogs pa khong du chud pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3023: lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i thabs la /
NK077(tsu)001:3024: thos bsam gyi spyod pa rnams yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3025: bdag don gyi spyod pa gtso che /
NK077(tsu)001:3027: lta ba rtogs zin pa'i spyod pa rnams yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3028: gzhan don gyi spyod pa gtso che //
NK077(tsu)001:3029: yon tan la rtogs pa'i yon tan mthar mi gtong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3030: rtogs pa'i yon tan gang spyad kyang tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3031: rtogs pa'i yon tan don gsum rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3032: rtogs pa'i yon tan 'khor bar mi gtong zhing bde bar bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3037: stobs kyis rtogs pa'i klung ldan pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:3042: thos bsam gyi lta ba mthar phyin pa'i tshad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3043: lta ba'i ngo bo gcig kyang bogs su 'gro ba bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3045: rgya mtsho dwangs ba'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK077(tsu)001:3046: zhes sogs tshigs drug gis bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:3048: 'on kyang sa dang sa yi rim //
NK077(tsu)001:3050: dper na mig gi rnam par shes pa'i spyod yul la /
NK077(tsu)001:3051: rdzas kyi rnam pa gsal ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:3053: rang mtshan ci lta ba bzhin mi gsal /
NK077(tsu)001:3054: nye na je gsal du 'gro ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:3055: rdzas kyi ngo bo mi 'gyur la blta mkhan gyi ngo la je gsal du 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:3056: lta ba'i ngo bo la 'gyur ba med kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:3057: lta ba stobs 'phel ba'i rims pa yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3058: bye brag gong nas gong du bogs dbyung du yod par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3059: lta ba ma rtogs pa'i skyon ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3060: blo ngan gyis ma rtogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:3061: le lo byas pa'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3062: don ma rtogs par tshigs gi mnyam pa sangs mi rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3063: lta ba med na lam kun zag cing 'ching bas skyon bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3064: de ltar spyi don bcu bzhir gnas pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:3065: bsdu na rnam pa gsum du bsdus te /
NK077(tsu)001:3066: lta ba rgyud la gnas par byed pa'i rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:3067: lta ba rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3069: de la lta ba'i rgyu la /
NK077(tsu)001:3075: spyod pa dang drug po de /
NK077(tsu)001:3076: lta ba rgyud la gnas par byed pa'i rgyur sdud do //
NK077(tsu)001:3079: lta ba'i ngo bor sdud do //
NK077(tsu)001:3085: lnga po de lta ba'i dgos ched du sdud do //
NK077(tsu)001:3087: dang po rgyu la drug du bstan kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:3089: de ya nga lta ba ma skyes pa skyes par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3090: skyes pa brtan par byed pa'i rgyu gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:3091: de la dus kyang lta ba ma skyes pa skyes par byed pa'i rgyu ru 'gro ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3093: dus re zhig smon pa'i sems kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3094: nyan pa la brtson 'grus kyi sbyor ba de yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3095: lta ba ma skyes pa skyes par byed pa'i rgyu ru 'agro'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3096: snod kyang rang bzhin gyi rgyus snod du rung ngam /
NK077(tsu)001:3097: sbyang pas snod du rung yang blo'i mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3098: lta ba go nus rtogs nus su byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:3099: lta ba ma skyes pa skyes pa'i rgyu ru 'agro'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3100: snod kyi yon tan dang ldan pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:3101: skyes pa brtan par byed pa'i rgyu ru 'agro'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3104: spyod pa gsum ni go sla'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3106: ngo bo la gsum yod kyang gcig tu 'dus te /
NK077(tsu)001:3107: ngo bo la dbye ba byas pas rnam grangs byung /
NK077(tsu)001:3108: rnam grangs bshad pas ngo bo byung /
NK077(tsu)001:3110: lta ba'i ngo bo mthar phyin pa la tshad zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3111: dgos ched la lnga yod kyang gnyis su 'dus te /
NK077(tsu)001:3116: drod gsum po de don gnyer gyi dgos ched /
NK077(tsu)001:3117: ma rtogs pa'i skyon bstan pa de gzhan sel gyi dgos ched do //
NK077(tsu)001:3118: rgyas pa la don bcu bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3120: rtogs pa'i dgos ched la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3122: gzhan sel lta ba med na lam mi rnyed pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3123: lta ba dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3125: chos nyid rgya chad phyogs lhung thams cad dang bral
NK077(tsu)001:3126: ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i don ma rtogs shing
NK077(tsu)001:3127: ma mthong bas / phyogs 'dzin gyi sgom pa bsam
NK077(tsu)001:3128: du med pa'i ting nge 'dzin dkyil 'khor du 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:3130: chos nyid don mi shes pas blun po /
NK077(tsu)001:3131: yang dag pa'i gnas lugs la bsgrib pas mun pa
NK077(tsu)001:3132: don gyi the tshom ma chod pas ma nges pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:3133: sprul pa'i blo can de la shes rab kyi mig
NK077(tsu)001:3134: med pas / long ba'i grong cher chen por 'gro ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3136: don gnyer des na thos bsam gyis lta ba rtogs dgos par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3138: lta ba ma rtogs na sgom kyang lam mi rnyed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3141: ma rig pa ling tog dang 'dra bas shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:3142: kyi ming ldong ba ste long bas de la rdo
NK077(tsu)001:3143: rje slob dpon thur ma mkhan dang 'dra ba de
NK077(tsu)001:3144: zang zing sri zhus mnyes par byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:3145: dbang thob pa la sogs pa sngon du byas nas
NK077(tsu)001:3146: gzod ma h+aa'i gzhung thos te shes rab kyi spyan
NK077(tsu)001:3147: dbye ste shes bya rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor lta
NK077(tsu)001:3148: bas don mthong bar bya dgos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3149: des na lam gyi thog mar lta ba rtogs par bya dgos pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3150: don gnyer ba'i dgos ched ces bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3151: gnyis pa snod du gsum pa dus thun mong du bstan pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:3156: de ltar rtogs shing mthong bar byed pa de yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3157: rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa la nye zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3158: sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa la ring zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3160: sngar theg pa chen po la ma sbyang par /
NK077(tsu)001:3161: theg pa chen po'i chos go nus rtogs nus su
NK077(tsu)001:3162: 'dug pa gcig rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa
NK077(tsu)001:3163: yin la / sngar theg pa thun mong la sbyangs nas 'di nyid kyi snod du gyur pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3164: sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3165: gtan gyi gang zag la de gnyis yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:3166: de gnyis la yang rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3167: rim gyis pa'i gcig char ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3168: gcig pa'i gcig char ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3169: gcig char ba'i rims pa dang bzhi cha yis phye
NK077(tsu)001:3170: bas rnal 'byor chen por 'jug cing rtogs par byed
NK077(tsu)001:3172: sngar phal pa'i sems brgyad nas bzungs te yo ga
NK077(tsu)001:3173: man chad kyi theg pa la sbyangs pas sngon du
NK077(tsu)001:3174: song nas / de nas ma h+aa yo ga la 'jug nus pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3175: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3176: rim gyis pa'i gcig char ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3177: des 'byung gi theg pa bzhi la sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3178: sngags phyi rgyud sde gsum dor nas ma h+aa yo ga la 'jug nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3179: gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3180: sngar theg chen gang rung gcig la sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3181: ma h+aa yo ga la 'jug nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3182: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3183: sngar theg pa gang la yang ma sbyangs par ma h+aa yo gar 'jug nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3185: dus ring ba sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3186: dus nye ba rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3191: dus ring ba la bskal pa sprul sku'i zhing gi khams rdul snyed tsam du /
NK077(tsu)001:3192: nges 'byung gi theg pa la sogs pa la shin
NK077(tsu)001:3193: tu sbyangs pa la rab tu gnas shing shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:3194: kyi mig dang ldan pa gcig /ma h+aa 'dir 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:3195: cing rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3196: dus ring ba'ang rim gyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3198: de yang shin tu sbyangs pa 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:3203: dar drag pa dang bzhi'i sgo nas 'chad dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:3205: theg pa sna tshogs la sbyong pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3206: yun ring ba ni zhing gi rdul snyed do //
NK077(tsu)001:3208: res sbyangs res ma sbyangs pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3209: bar ma chad par sbyangs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3210: de yang le lo snyoms las kyi dbang gis ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3211: brtson 'grus yun ring la dar drag par sbyangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3212: shin tu sbyangs kyi sgra 'dug go //
NK077(tsu)001:3214: lung gis yid ches pa'i mdor bstan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3215: de'i don man ngag gi ngo sprod rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3218: sbyangs pa'i rim gyis pa'i lung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3220: snga ma rim gyis pa de'ang tan tra gsang snying gi gzhung nyid las /
NK077(tsu)001:3221: sa rnams kyi khyad par dang rim pa bkod pa de yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3222: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam stegs yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3223: sbyangs pa'i gcig char ba'i lung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:3228: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa bzhi'i tshul ji ltar du na /
NK077(tsu)001:3229: lha mi'i theg pas ngan song las /
NK077(tsu)001:3230: nyan rang 'khor ba las byang sems mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung la /
NK077(tsu)001:3231: sngags phyi rgyud sde gsum bor te ma h+aa'i theg
NK077(tsu)001:3232: pa gcig gi 'bras bu gnas de yang nges 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:3234: lam stegs sngon du rdzogs par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3235: de nas ma h+aa rang la sbyar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:3236: de dag gis don man ngag gis ngo sprod rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3237: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3238: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3241: sems skye ba'i gzhi'i skyes pa bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3243: lung nas bshad pa de'i phyir rigs ma nges te /
