NK077(tsu)001:3244: so so skye bo'i sa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3245: 'khor ba spyi btsan la mtha' med gtan du 'khyam dgos pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:3246: 'dir rigs sad cing 'khor ba mtha' yod yin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:3248: de nas so so skye bo mun pa'i shes pa dang ldan pa de nyid nas //
NK077(tsu)001:3249: sems skye ba spyi'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3251: bde gshegs snying po rang bzhin gyi gnas pa'i rgyu de yis /
NK077(tsu)001:3252: 'khor ba la skyo ba bag tsam skyes te /
NK077(tsu)001:3253: de yang rang bzhin gnas pa'i rigs med na /
NK077(tsu)001:3254: 'khor ba la skyo ba skyes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3255: mya ngan las 'das pa la brod pa bskyed pa mi 'ong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:3256: 'khor ba'i chos la skyo ba skye zhing tshul khrims
NK077(tsu)001:3257: sna re srungs ba ni smyung bar gnas pa ste
NK077(tsu)001:3259: de yang 'jig rten phal pa'i sems brgyad skyes te mthar gnas pa de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK077(tsu)001:3260: gong ma nges 'byung gi theg pa la 'jug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3261: de yang phal pa'i sems brgyad ni dad pa'i sems
NK077(tsu)001:3262: la gcig /sbyin pa'i sems la drug /tshul khrims kyis
NK077(tsu)001:3263: sems la gcig dang brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:3264: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par dmar mchan bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3265: bder gshegs snying por rang bzhin gyis gnas pas mtshungs pa dang ldan pa'i rgyu yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3266: de yang lhan skyes ma rig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3267: lhan skyes ye shes gnyis dus mtshungs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3272: mtshungs rgyu 'di ltar du rtogs so //
NK077(tsu)001:3275: snying po rang bzhin gyi gnas lugs 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:3276: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la 'dra ba'i mtshungs pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3278: de'i steng na bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyer 'gro
NK077(tsu)001:3279: ba'i mgon po la lam gong 'og gi skyon yon
NK077(tsu)001:3282: lam gong ma'i yon tan mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3283: skyon yon de yis 'og ma'i skyon gyi lung thos na skyo zhing rmongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3284: gong ma'i yon tan gyi lung thos na brod cing dwangs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3285: mtshungs rgyu gong du song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3286: gnyis pa lhan gcig byed pa'i rgyu ru gsung pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:3287: lhan gcig byed pa'i rgyu 'di'i skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:3288: lha mi'i theg pa nas bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3289: gsang sngags man chad skyon yon gyi bye brag rgyas par shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:3290: bshes gnyen mgon po de bdag po'i rkyen gsang sngags
NK077(tsu)001:3291: kyi theg pa la sogs pa lha mi'i theg pa
NK077(tsu)001:3292: yan chad dmigs pa'i rkyen yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3294: rang bzhin rgyu'i smyung bar gnas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3298: lha mi theg pa la 'jug pa'i rgyu so so skye bo mun pa'i shes pa can de la /
NK077(tsu)001:3299: phal pa'i sems brgyad skye lugs 'byung /
NK077(tsu)001:3302: phal pa'i sems brgyad mthar phyin nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3303: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi la /
NK077(tsu)001:3304: rgyu rkyen drug gi sgo nas 'jug dgos pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3305: snying po rang bzhin mtshungs pa nas bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3306: skad gcig 'phel ba de ma thag gi bar la /
NK077(tsu)001:3307: rgyu rkyen drug ngos bzung dgos par rtogs /
NK077(tsu)001:3308: phal pa'i sems brgyad smyungs bar gnas pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:3309: lha mi'i theg pa'i rgyu rkyen du 'gro yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3310: theg pa gsum po la sbyar du ma btub pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:3311: 'o na rgyu'i rkyen gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:3312: gang du bshad pa'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3313: yon tan mthong ba'i gang zag slob bu de gong
NK077(tsu)001:3314: ma gong ma'i don gyi snod du gyur pas rgyu'i
NK077(tsu)001:3316: skad cig snga mas go phye nas phyi mar 'phel ba ni de ma thag pa'i rkyen dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3317: rgyu rkyen 'dzom nas lam stegs kyi theg pa la rim gyis skyes tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3319: de ltar rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3320: drug las dper na rtsa la me chung ngu la
NK077(tsu)001:3321: chen por mched pa bzhin du sems cher 'phel zhing
NK077(tsu)001:3323: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi yod pa'i thog mar
NK077(tsu)001:3324: lha mi'i theg pa la sems skye bas dang por
NK077(tsu)001:3325: zhog zhes bya'o // de nas nyan rang byang sems
NK077(tsu)001:3326: la sogs pa nas rim gyis bgrod par byas te
NK077(tsu)001:3327: zhog zhes bya'o // / rgyu'i theg pa snga ma
NK077(tsu)001:3328: nas rgyu rkyen gyi theg pa gong mar 'phar ba
NK077(tsu)001:3329: zhog zhes bya'o // / yin te / yo ga
NK077(tsu)001:3330: nas ma h+aa la sems skye zhing 'jug tshul bstan
NK077(tsu)001:3331: zhog zhes bya'o // / yin te / pa'o // drang /
NK077(tsu)001:3332: rnal 'byor yo ga'i rgyud kyi don la gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:3333: la ma h+aa yo ga 'di nyid kyi ston pa
NK077(tsu)001:3334: bshes gnyen 'gro ba'i mgon po la lung gnyis thos
NK077(tsu)001:3335: pas / de ni gong du bstan pa ci lta
NK077(tsu)001:3336: ba bzhin du rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhis theg pa
NK077(tsu)001:3337: mchog gi don ma h+aa la g.yo ba'i sems 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:3338: pas / bar 'gyur te / g.yo ba byang chub kyi sems zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3339: g.yo ba'i sems kyis gzhi de go phyes nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3340: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i don ci nas kyang
NK077(tsu)001:3341: khung du chud na ci ma rung snyams pa'i smon
NK077(tsu)001:3343: smon pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK077(tsu)001:3344: las dang bya bas lhag pas na lhag pa mtshon cing 'dra bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:3345: gzugs can gyis dkyil 'khor du rdo rje las rim nas 'byung ba bzhin 'jug pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3347: 'jug pa la thog mar bla med mchog gi theg
NK077(tsu)001:3348: pa ma h+aa yo ga'i rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK077(tsu)001:3349: gi dam tshig kyang skabs de ru byin nas rigs
NK077(tsu)001:3350: nges par 'gyur ba la phan pa'i dbang bcu dang
NK077(tsu)001:3352: bdag don byed nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3355: gnyis kyis byin rlabs tsam slob bu'i rgyud la bzhag par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3356: de nas shes rab kyis rang gi spyan mchog 'byed
NK077(tsu)001:3357: pa'i thabs thos bsam la brtson pa'i rgyu yis rang
NK077(tsu)001:3358: bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor mthong bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3359: thos bsam dang po len par byed pa ni gnas pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK077(tsu)001:3360: rim gyis pa'i gcig char ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3362: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa la gzhan pa'i gang
NK077(tsu)001:3363: zag kha gcig sngar phan chad thun mong gi theg
NK077(tsu)001:3365: kri yog sde gsum bor te dus kyi mtha'i tshe
NK077(tsu)001:3366: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga la sbyor bas rim
NK077(tsu)001:3367: gyis pa'i gcig char bas 'di ni dus mtha'i gcig
NK077(tsu)001:3368: char zer ro // gzhan yang gcig char gyi dbye ba drug yod pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:3369: rgyas par spro na dmar mchan ltar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:3371: ci lta bu yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:3372: tshe da snga phan chad bskal pa'i grangs zhing gi
NK077(tsu)001:3373: rdul snyed tsam du lam stegs kyi theg pa sbyangs
NK077(tsu)001:3374: pa sngon du song bas thun mong gi theg pa
NK077(tsu)001:3375: la yun gong du bshad pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3376: de sbyangs de snyed sbyangs pa'i mtha' ru thun mong
NK077(tsu)001:3377: ma yin pa'i theg pa la phyi nang gnyis yod
NK077(tsu)001:3378: pa la phyi rgyud sde gsum dor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3379: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i don la zhugs pa de yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3380: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du /
NK077(tsu)001:3381: sngar sbyangs nas 'di tshe ma h+aa la 'jug pa'ang nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi la sbyangs bas /
NK077(tsu)001:3382: rim gyis sngar sbyangs la tshe 'di nyid la ma
NK077(tsu)001:3383: h+aa yo ga la 'jug nus pa ni gcig char
NK077(tsu)001:3385: rims gyis pa'i gcig char ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3386: dus nye ba'i rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3387: dbang po rnon po'i rgyu mtshan gyis mtshan nyid bdun ldan mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3388: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3389: dang po blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3390: sbyangs pa las gzhan pa'i las rang bzhin gyi dbang
NK077(tsu)001:3391: po rnon po dag rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen
NK077(tsu)001:3392: po gnyis rkyen dang gang 'phrad gcig la 'jug pa
NK077(tsu)001:3393: yin te / sngar theg pa che chung gang la
NK077(tsu)001:3394: yang ma sbyangs par theg pa chen po la 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:3396: de'i rgyu mtshan grub pa gsum phyir gyi rnon po bsgrub dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:3397: grub pa gsum la rtogs ldan pa'i bzhed la /
NK077(tsu)001:3398: rang bzhin ngo bo nyid kyis grub pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3399: bde gshegs snying po ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo la bya /
NK077(tsu)001:3401: theg pa chen po'i rigs can blo'i mtshan nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:3403: byin gyis rlabs gyis grub pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3404: de dang tshul mthun par sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK077(tsu)001:3405: sems dpa' thams cad kyis byin gyi rlabs pa'i nus
NK077(tsu)001:3407: 'di la gshis chos nyid yin pa'i don gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3408: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan 'byung rung /
NK077(tsu)001:3409: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan nges shes bya'i gting mtha' chod nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3412: 'di ltar du 'dod pa yang 'dug /chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3413: chos can rang gis ngo bos grub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3414: chos tsam rang gis sam mtshan nyid kyis grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3416: chos dbyings spros pa dang bral ba /
NK077(tsu)001:3417: sems kyi chos nyid rtsal cir yang sna tshogs 'gags med rang bzhin gyis 'char ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3418: rno rtul la sogs pa yang rang bzhin gyis 'char bas /
NK077(tsu)001:3419: ngo bo nyid kyis rgyur grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3421: kun rdzob rig pa'i ye shes nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:3422: cir yang ma g+hag char ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3423: gang zag sbyangs pa mnyam po la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3424: 'ga' zhig sngags kyi gtam gcig char du thos pa la mi skrag /
NK077(tsu)001:3426: thogs pa med par go ba 'dug pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:3427: blo rang gis ngo bos grub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:3429: phyi rol gyi chos can gang la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3432: lcags la rno rtul gyi ngar che chung la sogs pa yod pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:3433: nang rig pa la rno rtul yod par mngon no //
NK077(tsu)001:3434: de la blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan gyi blo 'phang mtho ba nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3435: mi 'gyur ba brtan pa'i ro bo lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3436: shes bya kun la myur ba glog lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3437: shes bya gting mtha' chod nus pas rno ba ral gri lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3438: thams cad shes pa rgya che ba sa gzhi lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3440: bral bar go bas yangs pa bar snang lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3441: ming 'dogs thams cad dang bral bar go bas rgya mtsho lta bu dang bdun yod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3442: de lta bu'i rgyu blo dang ldan pa'i gang zag
NK077(tsu)001:3443: de nyid kyang gzhan rkyen theg chen ston pa'i dge
NK077(tsu)001:3444: ba'i bshes gnyen dang snod de rims pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3445: phye bas rgyu'i theg pa chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3446: 'bras bu'i theg pa chen po rnams la ma nges
NK077(tsu)001:3447: par 'jug pa'i gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:3448: / gcig char ba'i gcig char ba ma h+aa'i ston pa dang 'phrad nas 'di nyid du 'jug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3449: de la dbang po rno rtul gnyis po 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:3450: rgyu 'bras kyi gzhung kun nas bshad kyang phal cher sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon ma gtogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3451: rang bzhin dbang rnon khas len la /
NK077(tsu)001:3456: rang bzhin gyis rno ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3457: ci'i phyir na tha mal gyi shes rgyud 'di la shin tu rnon po dag yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:3458: dper na ma brdungs pa'i gnam lcags thog rgod shin tu rno ba dang 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3459: rnon po 'di med na theg pa chen po'i chos 'ong mi srid do //
NK077(tsu)001:3461: sems can dang po'i las can la //
NK077(tsu)001:3462: gcig char ba ni bstan par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:3463: de nas sbyangs pa'i phro can la //
NK077(tsu)001:3464: rim gyis pa ni bstan par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:3466: mdo dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:3467: sems can rnams kyi shes pa'i rgyud la rno rtul rang bzhin gyis med pa ni ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3470: zhing khams de na 'khod pa'i semasasa can de dag ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3471: sems kyis rang bzhin sna tshogs pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3472: blo shin tu zab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3481: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3483: shes bya la rno rtul gnyis ka las grol ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3485: rno rtul gnyis ka las ma grol ba'i /
NK077(tsu)001:3487: rang bzhin blo chung ba'i rtul po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3488: blo rang bzhin gyis rno ba'i rnon po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3489: rno rtul gnyis ka yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3491: gzhi rang byung gi ston pa 'khrul ma myong ba'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3493: 'khor ba mtha' med kyi sems can /
NK077(tsu)001:3495: theg chung la sbyangs nas theg chen la rtogs nus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3499: rtogs grol dus mnyam pa yang srid do //
NK077(tsu)001:3501: blo'i rigs ma nges shing nges med du bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3504: gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa theg pa gang mos nas 'jug pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3505: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba gdod ma nyid nas ma h+aa la 'jug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3506: dang po rgyu rkyen spyi'i 'brel pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3507: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po gang rung ma nges pa'i rnon po de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3508: ma h+aa yo ga 'di nyid du nges par 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:3509: pa'i shin tu rnon po de'ang 'brel pa bzhi dang
NK077(tsu)001:3511: rang gi sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyi rgyud dam /
NK077(tsu)001:3512: mtshan bya don gyi bstan pa'i dngos gazhi'ang yin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3513: de ltar yang dag don gyi bshes gnyen rnams dang gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo te /
NK077(tsu)001:3514: ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:3515: de yang blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan gyi gzhi stong nyid rang byung gi ye shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3516: yang dag pa rang rig dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi thugs dgongs /
NK077(tsu)001:3517: de gnyis chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:3521: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis gzhi la ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3523: 'dir da res theg chen go nus rtogs nus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3524: rang sems bstan pa'i dngos gzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:3525: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan dgongs pa nye bar len nus pa'i shes rab de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3526: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po ston par byed pa'i bshes gnyen rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3527: ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yod /
NK077(tsu)001:3528: dper na gser 'dod pa la gser bstan pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:3529: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan theg chen go nus rtogs nus pa de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3530: theg chen rtogs shing khung du chud pa'i bshes gnyen de gnyis kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:3531: shes rab kyi cha la khyad med pas ngo bo
NK077(tsu)001:3532: bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yin par rtogs so
NK077(tsu)001:3533: // rang sems bstan pa'i dngos gazhi'am /
NK077(tsu)001:3534: chos nyid kyi don de dang ldan pa ni shes bya /
NK077(tsu)001:3535: rang bzhin gyi dbang po rnon po ni shes byed
NK077(tsu)001:3536: te de gnyis shes bya shes byed kyi 'brel pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:3537: // yang na blo'i mtshan nyid bdun dang ldan pa de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3538: theg chen gyi chos gnyis shes bya shes byed kyis 'brel pa yod /
NK077(tsu)001:3539: rang bzhin bdun ldan gyi snod yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:3540: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po rnams ni bcud du 'gro bas /
NK077(tsu)001:3541: des na rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po'i lung rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3542: gang zag de snod bcud kyi 'brel pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3543: bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'gro ba'i mgon po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3544: gang zag dbang po rnon po de gnyis ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3545: gang zag de la thugs rje skye bar bya ba'i las 'phro yod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3546: bla ma de la thugs rje skye bar byed pa'i thabs yod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3547: de gnyis las dang thugs rjes 'brel pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3549: gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3551: gdod ma nas theg pa chen po /
NK077(tsu)001:3554: de ltar 'brel pa bzhi yod pa de'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3555: theg chung las khyad par du gyur pa mchog gi
NK077(tsu)001:3556: lung theg chen dbu ma nas yo ga'i bar dang
NK077(tsu)001:3557: / de ston par byed pa'i rdo rje slob dpon
NK077(tsu)001:3558: rnams dang dngos su mjal bar byed pa'i phyir ro
NK077(tsu)001:3559: / // thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa mchog
NK077(tsu)001:3560: gi bstan pa'i lung chen 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo
NK077(tsu)001:3562: brgyud nas 'brel pa byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:3563: de ltar rgyu rkyen drug dang ldan pa ma nges
NK077(tsu)001:3564: par 'jug pa ni gong du bstan pa bzhin rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:3565: gnyis rkyen bzhi ste drug dang ldan pas rigs ma
NK077(tsu)001:3567: rgyu 'bras kyi theg chen gang rung gcig tu 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:3568: pa'i rten gyi gang zag de ni rang gi shes
NK077(tsu)001:3569: rab kyi dbang po rno rtul gyi rim pa bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:3570: du / rang rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gang la mos mi mos kyi bye brag gam /
NK077(tsu)001:3571: bshes gnyen gang 'phrad kyi rkyen gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3572: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa chen po'am /
NK077(tsu)001:3573: bya ba'i rgyud kyi theg pa kri ya'am /
NK077(tsu)001:3574: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud yo ga'i theg pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3575: de dag gang rung gcig gis shes par 'jug cing sbyor bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3576: des ma h+aa la sems skye zhing 'jug tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:3578: theg pa chen po gang rung gcig la zhugs pa
NK077(tsu)001:3579: de nas gong du bstan pa de bzhin du rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:3580: rkyen drug gi sgo nas gsang sngags ma h+aa yo
NK077(tsu)001:3581: ga'i sgo 'dir 'jug pa'ang sngon du sbyangs pa'i dbang
NK077(tsu)001:3582: po rnon pa'i rim gyis pa'i skabs su bstan pa
NK077(tsu)001:3583: bzhin tu / rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po
NK077(tsu)001:3584: gang rung nas rgyu rkyen drug gis g.yo ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:3586: 'jug pa'i sems kyis gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga la sbyor ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3587: de ltar gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i don de
NK077(tsu)001:3588: la thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab gsum gyis gnas
NK077(tsu)001:3589: pa'i ma h+aa yo ga'i don mthar phyin par byed
NK077(tsu)001:3590: pa ni thog ma sbyongs pa'i dbang po rnon po
NK077(tsu)001:3592: rang bzhin gyis dbang po rnon po gcig char ba
NK077(tsu)001:3593: la ltos pa'i ring ba'i dus nyid yin par 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:3594: do // gcig char ba'i gcig char ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3597: ma h+aa la sems skye ba'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3599: rigs ma nges so so skye bo'i sa nas 'brel
NK077(tsu)001:3600: pa bzhi dang ldan zhing rgyu rkyen drug dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:3601: pa'i rnal 'byor mchog ma h+aa la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3603: sngar theg pa gang la ma sbyor zhing so so'i
NK077(tsu)001:3604: skye bo nas blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan de dang
NK077(tsu)001:3605: / ma h+aa yo ga'i ston pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3606: ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3607: ma h+aa yo ga'i chos de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3608: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan de gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3609: shes bya shes byed kyis 'brel pa'i snod dang bcud kyis 'brel pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3610: bya byed thugs rje'i 'brel pa yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:3612: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu bde gshegs snying po rang chas su gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3613: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu 'khor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3615: ma h+aa'i yon tan thos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3616: 'og ma la skyo zhing gong ma la 'jug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3617: rgyu'i rkyen rang bzhin rgyu'i smyung bar gnas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3618: 'khor ba la blo log pa'am ma h+aa yo ga de /
NK077(tsu)001:3619: go nus rtogs nus pa de rgyu'i rkyen no //
NK077(tsu)001:3620: bdag po'i rkyen mchog 'di nyid kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen /
NK077(tsu)001:3621: dmigs pa'i rkyen gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3622: de ma thag pa'i rkyen snga ma snga mas /
NK077(tsu)001:3623: phyi ma phyi ma go 'byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3624: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga rang la sbyor lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3625: dper na mun pa la nyi ma'i 'od zer byung ba'i tshul lam /
NK077(tsu)001:3626: rtsa la me mched pa ltar ma h+aa yo ga la sems skye ba de'ang g.yo ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3629: sngon rim gyis pa bzhin yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:3630: snod ldan 'jug pa'i khyad par ro //
NK077(tsu)001:3631: snod kyi mtshan nyid dang bdun dang ldan pa'i gang zag de'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:3632: tan tra ni rgyud de gsang ba'i snying po'i gzhung gis le'u gsum pa de nyid nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3633: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:3634: ces gsungs pa bzhin 'dir yang ngang chu bo'i gzhung ltar ring ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3635: zhes kyang yid mi 'khrugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3636: tshul shes pa ste glang po che gsar ba'i spyod pa lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3637: rang bzhin bzang ba ste gser btso ma lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3639: blo ri bo lta bur mi 'gyur bar brtan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3640: byams snying rje che ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3641: lus dang longs spyod la 'phang pa med par chos phyir gtong nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3642: de lta bu'i snod yon tan dang ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3643: thos bsam sgom gsum gyis shes rab gsum la bslab
NK077(tsu)001:3644: pa la rang bzhin lhun grub gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:3645: chen po ru / 'jug pa gzhi'i yan lag bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:3646: yin te gzhung thos pa'i 'jug pa dmigs phye ba
NK077(tsu)001:3647: chen po ru / dang 'dra / don rtogs pa'i 'jug pa dkyil 'khor mthong ba dang 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:3648: goms par byed pa'i 'jug pa dal du chud pa dang 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:3649: 'bras bu thob pa'i mngon du gyur ba'i 'jug pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3651: de ltar 'jug pa'i man ngag bzhi'i nang na mchog
NK077(tsu)001:3652: /dang po thos pa ched du gnyer bar byed dgos
NK077(tsu)001:3653: pa'o // de yang thos pa gal che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3654: thos pa la brten nas dwangs dwangs ba la brten nas mos /
NK077(tsu)001:3655: mos pa la brten nas bsgrub pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3656: bsgrub pa la brten nas legs pa'i mchog skye ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3659: snod dang ldan pa'i gang zag de thos pa'i shes
NK077(tsu)001:3660: rab kyis lta ba tshol ba'i tshe sbyangs pa'i snod
NK077(tsu)001:3661: du gyur pa la rgyu gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3662: rkyen bzhis rim gyis sbyangs nas ma h+aa'i don la
NK077(tsu)001:3663: mi skrag cing bzod pa thob pa dang ldan pa
NK077(tsu)001:3664: 'di ni / gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:3665: 'bras kyi theg pa chen po gnyis la blo sngon
NK077(tsu)001:3666: du sbyangs nas ma h+aa yo ga la mi skrag
NK077(tsu)001:3668: rang bzhin ngang gis bzod thob ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3669: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba gdod ma nas ma
NK077(tsu)001:3670: h+aa la 'jug cing mi skrag pas bzod pa thob
NK077(tsu)001:3671: pa'o // pas zhes pas de gnyis gang gis kyang
NK077(tsu)001:3672: ma h+aa yo ga'i gzhung de khung du chud par
NK077(tsu)001:3673: bya ba la re ba dang smon pa'i sems kyis
NK077(tsu)001:3674: pa'o // nyan pa dang / sgom pa la brtson 'grus byed cing sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3676: lnga pa rkyen thun mong du bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3680: blo'i rang bzhin bdun dang mtshungs par ldan pa de lhan gcig byed pa'i rgyu la dgar bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:3681: gcig shos te mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ru nges pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3682: blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan de dag ma h+aa'i bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba 'di gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3683: snod bcud mtshungs pa'i phyir mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3684: blo'i rang bzhin bdun ldan gyi rgyu de med na /
NK077(tsu)001:3685: 'bras bu lta ba rtogs su mi rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:3686: lhan gcig byed pa'i rkyen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3688: rgyud lung man ngag gis don bkrol bar byed pa'i mkhan po de bla ma dam pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3689: rgyal ba'i lung dang bla ma gong ma'i man ngag
NK077(tsu)001:3690: dang bcas pa de ni lta ba rtogs pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:3691: lhan gcig tu byed pa'i rgyu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3692: de dag rgyu'i rkyen du 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:3696: gang dag thos pa'i shes rab kyis ming ngam /
NK077(tsu)001:3699: bsam pa'i shes rab kyis tshigs don gnyis ka la dmigs nas dpyod cing thos bsam byed pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:3700: dang por thos pa bya ba'i gnas bla ma la
NK077(tsu)001:3701: gzhung chos nyan cing rna bas thos pa'i tshig blo
NK077(tsu)001:3703: 'dzin pa'i tshig don la bsam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3704: brtsams pa'i shes rab kyi tshe na don che long gi rnam pa'i rtog pa ste rtsings pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3705: don la zhib du dpyod pa ste thos bsam gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:3706: po 'di dag gis lta ba rtogs shing shes par
NK077(tsu)001:3707: byed pa'i rgyu'o // 'ga' zhig gis rtogs dpyod gnyis po shes pa'i rgyu yin par 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:3708: rtogs dpyod gnyis ni bsam pa'i khongs su gtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3709: thos pa ma byas pa la rtogs dpyod btang rgyu med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3711: lta ba rtogs pa'i rgyu thos bsam gnyis yin par shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:3712: 'o na rgyu rkyen 'di rnams la zlos skyon byung zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:3716: don zlos 'ga' zhig gis skyon mi che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3717: phar phyin la stong nyid bco brgyad bshad pa yang yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:3720: phar phyin gyi 'gres rkang brgya rtsa lta bu yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3721: de yang dgos ched mi bldab /
NK077(tsu)001:3722: dgos ched ngo bo la zlos skyon byung na /
NK077(tsu)001:3725: drug pa lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3729: de ltar dus snod 'brel pa rgyu rkyen dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:3730: pa'i shes rab kyi spyan lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe
NK077(tsu)001:3731: lta ba rtogs byed kyi thabs gsum kyi ston te
NK077(tsu)001:3733: dang po gtan tshigs 'og nas ston par byed pa
NK077(tsu)001:3734: rnams kyis gzhal bya gzhig cing rmal bar bya ste
NK077(tsu)001:3736: gnyis pa gol sgrib kyis gdar sha bshad cing rtogs par bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3737: don nor pa'i shes rab ste 'jig rten pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3738: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa yo ga man
NK077(tsu)001:3739: chad kyi gol ba dmigs kyi bzung zhing bsal nas
NK077(tsu)001:3741: 'ga' zhig nor ba gzhan sel la bzhag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3742: shes rab don gnyer la bzhag pa yang 'dug /gsum
NK077(tsu)001:3743: ma nor bar don dmigs nas grub mtha' blang ba
NK077(tsu)001:3744: ni / gnas lugs don ma nor ba'i ma h+aa
NK077(tsu)001:3745: yo ga 'di nyid kyi grub mtha' dmigs kyis phye
NK077(tsu)001:3746: ni / nas / dang du blangs zhing gtan la dbab par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3748: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3749: gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad de don gyi dmigs bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3750: don ma nor bar dmigs nas grub mtha' blang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3755: gzhal bya gzhal gzhi dang gzhal byed gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3756: gtan la dbab pa grub pa'i don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3758: de ltar lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs la gsum yod
NK077(tsu)001:3759: pa'i snga ma gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:3760: gzhi ru mdo tsam du bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:3761: de la gzhal bya'i ngo bo //
NK077(tsu)001:3763: rnam grangs rnam par phye ba dang bzhi yod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:3765: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab bya'i yul du gyur pa gcig gzhal bya'i ngo bo /
NK077(tsu)001:3766: nges tshig ni gtan la dbab bya'i yul du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3771: gtan tshigs gtan la dbab mi btub pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3774: sngon byung gis gzhal bya de kho na nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:3775: rjes 'jug zhen snang gi gzhal gzhi gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:3780: gtan tshigs kyi ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3781: grub mtha' gtan la dbab pa'i nus pa dang ldan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3783: gtan la 'beb par byed pa las mi 'da' /
NK077(tsu)001:3785: don gtan la phebs par byed pa la dgos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3786: dbye ba la sngon byung dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs rjes 'jug tshul lnga'i gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:3787: de gnyis mtshon par byed pa la tshig gis gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:3788: de la dpyad du yod pa'i go ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3789: dpyod du med pa'i go ba gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3790: dpyad du yod pa'i go ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:3791: tshig don mi mthun pa'i go ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3794: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3795: sgra mthun don dpag gis gtan tshigs gnyis tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs la /
NK077(tsu)001:3796: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:3797: bden pa dbyer med kyis gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:3798: dag pa gsum mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:3804: gcig du bral la sogs pa rnams yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3805: gsum pa gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab pa'i grub
NK077(tsu)001:3806: mtha' rang gi ngo bo la yang bzhi yod de
NK077(tsu)001:3808: shes rab kyi dbang po yul med rang gsal du byung ba lta ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3813: sgrib g.yogs thams cad dang bral bar rtogs shing khung du chud pa lta ba'i nges tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:3815: lta ba ma rtogs na skyon yod /
NK077(tsu)001:3816: rtogs na yon tan yod pas lta ba dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:3818: rgyud kyi lta grangs dgu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3819: lam gyis lta grangs dgu la sogs pa rnams yin par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3822: gtan tshigs dang des gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3825: sngon byung gi gzhal bya de kho na nyid mjal byed dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3827: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ston pa chos
NK077(tsu)001:3828: kyi sku la sogs pa sku lngas 'dul ba'i 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:3829: / ye shes rgya mtsho la sogs pa lnga po rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:3830: skye med don gyi gsung la sogs pa gsung lnga
NK077(tsu)001:3831: po bstan pas gzhal bya de kho na nyid sems
NK077(tsu)001:3832: kyi gnas lugs ci bzhin pa dngos su gtan la
NK077(tsu)001:3833: phabs shing mjal bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3834: de ni sngon byung gis gzhal bya de kho na
NK077(tsu)001:3835: nyid sems kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin pa la gzhal
NK077(tsu)001:3836: ba'o // 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3837: dang po ston pa sku lnga bshad pa la rang ngo gzhan ngo gnyis su shes dgos la /
NK077(tsu)001:3839: sems nyid skye 'gag gnas gsum gyi mtha' dang bral zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:3840: spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad nye bar zhi ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3841: de nyid gdul bya'i ngo la chos sku kun bzang rdo rje 'chang lta bu la shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3842: nyid longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3843: ma 'gag pa 'khor ba la longs spyod /
NK077(tsu)001:3844: ma dmigs pa 'das pa la longs spyod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3845: 'khor 'das gnyis med ro gcig pa'i don rtogs shing mthar phyin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3846: de nyid gdul bya'i ngo la rgyal ba rigs lnga lta bu /
NK077(tsu)001:3847: kha sbyor yan lag bdun ldan gyi longs sku ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3849: thun mong gi longs sku ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3850: rnam par snang mdzad yab rkyang lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3852: skye med kyi ngang las snang ba sna tshogs su shar zhing gnyis su med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3855: sprul sku sh+aakya seng ge lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3857: sku gsum dbyer med dgongs pa zang thal ba snang stong gnyis su med pa'i don la bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3858: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyi gtso cher zhe sdang la
NK077(tsu)001:3859: sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa dug lnga ma spangs par
NK077(tsu)001:3860: chos nyid kyi klong du shar ba rdo rje'i skur
NK077(tsu)001:3861: gsung ste / zhe sdang rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3862: badz+ra he ru ka'i thugs dam bskangs /
NK077(tsu)001:3863: la sogs rnams kyis shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3864: gdul bya'i ngo la badz+ra he ru ka la sogs pa rigs lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:3865: khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor du shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3866: nyid mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3867: shes bya'i chos nyi ma'i dkyil na mun pa ka nas dag pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:3868: ye shes lnga'i 'khor yug ma gtogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3869: nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i chos bas la ba ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3871: gdul bya'i ngo la sa snying la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3872: byang chub sems dpa' nye ba'i sras brgyad lta bu'i gzugs su shar nas snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3873: dam pa bde bar gshegs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3874: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa rnams sku lngar nges bzung ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3875: kun bzang yab yum ni chos kyi sku'o rigs lnga yab yum rnams ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3876: thub pa rnams ni sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3877: sems dpa' rnams ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3878: khro bo yab yum rnams ni rdo rje'i sku'o gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:3880: chos sku'i 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3881: ye shes lnga'i rang gzugs rgyal ba rigs lnga'i skur snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3883: longs sku'i 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3887: sar smin pa bzhi yod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:3888: sa bcu pa rnam par smin pa yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3889: ma h+aa'i phyag rgya cher po'i rig 'dzin rnams shas che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3890: rdo rje'i sku'i 'khor dbyer med rdo rje'i tshogs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3891: snang stong gnyis med kyi don rtogs shing mthar phyin pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:3892: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang la sogs pa spangs pa med par /
NK077(tsu)001:3893: chos nyid du shar ba mthar phyin pa'i lam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3894: 'di lhun grub rig 'dzin pa shas che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3895: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku yi 'khor /
NK077(tsu)001:3897: spangs rtog mthar phyin pa'i sangs rgyas rgyal ba rgya mtsho ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3898: theg pa 'og ma'i sangs rgyas yo ga man chad rnams shas che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3899: sprul sku'i 'khor mos pa rgya mtsho ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3900: tshogs sbyor gnyis la gnas pa'i lam pa rnams kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:3901: don dam mtshan nyid pa 'phags pa'i mnyam bzhag gi
NK077(tsu)001:3902: ye shes khong du ma chud cing tshogs sbyor gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:3903: kyi mnyam bzhag de chos sku yin par mos pas
NK077(tsu)001:3904: / mos pa spyod pa'i sa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3905: gtso cher tshogs sbyor gnyis kyi lam sa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:3906: yar ded na tshe dbang rig 'dzin sprul sku mtshan nyid pa'i 'khor du 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:3907: mar ded na 'gro drug yang 'khor yin par 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:3909: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung nam mkha' lta
NK077(tsu)001:3910: bu des ye shes rgya mtsho'i 'khor la brda sprad
NK077(tsu)001:3911: lugs ni / dper na nam mkha' dwangs pa la zla ba shar ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:3912: chu dwangs pa la thogs pa med par zla ba'i gzugs brnyan snang ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:3913: chos sku kun bzang gi dgongs pa skye med don gyi gsung nam mkha' lta bu de /
NK077(tsu)001:3914: 'khor longs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga la dgongs pa shar ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3915: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa gtso che la /
NK077(tsu)001:3916: 'dir ston 'khor gyi dgongs pa la khyad med /
NK077(tsu)001:3917: gdul bya'i ngo la ston 'khor gyi tshul du snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3918: 'di man chad la sku bzhi po'i ston 'khor la khyad yod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3919: 'khor la yang dri ma yod par 'dod /
NK077(tsu)001:3920: 'ga' zhig gis longs sprul gnyis kyi 'khor dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3921: rdo rje'i sku'i 'khor lhun grub rig 'dzin gsum la yod /
NK077(tsu)001:3922: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3923: theg pa 'og ma'i sangs rgyas rnams la dri ma med par 'dod pa snang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3924: 'di ni gsang sngags bla med kyi dgongs pa ji bzhin pa ma lon cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3925: 'og ma dang shan phye ma thub pa'i rtags yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:3926: 'di rnams la khyad yod lugs zhib tu ngo sprad rgyu yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3927: le'u dgu pa 'bras bu skabs su 'chad /
NK077(tsu)001:3928: longs spyod pa'i sku'i dgongs pa brda'i gsung ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3929: dper na byad la dri ma yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:3930: me long la bltas na me long gi brjod pa med kyang dri ma ngos zin pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:3931: shes sgrib gab skungs mchom pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:3932: bder gshegs sku la bltas pas rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3933: tshul ji ltar du rtogs na /
NK077(tsu)001:3934: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la mdun rgyab med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3935: mnyam par mi bzhag pa mi mnga' ba la sogs pa'i sgo nas shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:3937: sprul pa'i sku'i brjod pa tshig gis gsung ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3938: gdul bya las dag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3939: ma dag pa mos pa spyod la dngos su bshad pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3941: rgyal po ma skyes dgra la /
NK077(tsu)001:3942: sprul sku thub pa chen pos /
NK077(tsu)001:3943: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK077(tsu)001:3944: bzhag par bya ba yang cung zad med /
NK077(tsu)001:3945: yang dag nyid la yang dag lta /
NK077(tsu)001:3946: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK077(tsu)001:3948: brjod pa tsam du rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:3949: tshig de la brtags dpyad ma dgos par sems kyi
NK077(tsu)001:3950: gnas lugs de kho na nyid gtan la 'bebs shing
NK077(tsu)001:3952: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung brag cha lta bu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3953: dper na brag cha'i sgra la 'dzin pa med de stong pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:3954: dngos po phyi nang gi chos thams cad dbyer med ro gcig tu rtogs shing mjal pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3955: mngon par byang chub pa'i gsung nyi ma'i snying po lta bu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3956: dper na nyi ma la mun pa ka nas dag pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:3957: shes bya'i chos thams cad ye shes lnga'i 'khor yug ma gtogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3958: nyon mongs pa rtsa ba nas chod par rtogs shing brda' mjal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3959: rjes 'jug gzhan snang gis gzhal gzhi bstan pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:3961: gzhal bya gnas lugs gzhan snang dang bcas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:3963: gzhal byed de yang gtan tshigs rnams kyis yongs su brtag cing dpyad par bya ba'i gzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3964: dbang po lnga'i yul du mngon sum du snang ba kun chos can /
NK077(tsu)001:3965: yul rnams rang rgyud du yod pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:3966: zhes dam bca' gtan tshigs rang byung gi ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:3967: kyi kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid phyi nang
NK077(tsu)001:3968: gis dngos po sna tshogs par snang ba de'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:3969: 'khor ba dang / 'das pa'i dngos po phyogs rer
NK077(tsu)001:3970: zhen pa'i snang ba la brtag cing gzhal bar bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:3971: 'khor ba dang / // de ji ltar mjal ba'i dmigs bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3973: gzhal bya'i yul ngo bo ni 'jig rten gyi khams 'di na shes bya la /
NK077(tsu)001:3974: srid tshad ci yod pa'i ming tha dad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3975: mtshan mar yul du 'dzin pa la sogs pa'i de ma yin pa la der 'dzin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:3976: log rtog so so'i rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:3977: ji ltar gnas pa dpyad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3978: gzhal bya 'di rnams la 'khor ba la gzhal lam /
NK077(tsu)001:3979: 'das pa la gzhal ba la sogs pa'i bshad pa mang po 'dug ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3980: 'di nyid kyi dgongs gzhi rtogs ma nus pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:3981: rjes 'jug gis gzhal bya gzhal pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:3982: dper na mda' 'phen pa la 'ben mthong dgos pa
NK077(tsu)001:3983: bzhin du shes bya'i gnas lugs lta ba gtan la
NK077(tsu)001:3984: phabs pa la 'khrul snang 'di nyid brtag cing gzhal
NK077(tsu)001:3986: dag pa kun gzhi'i gnas lugs ma rtogs cing /
NK077(tsu)001:3987: ma dag kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid ngo bo sna tshogs su shar yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3991: ming mtshan ma sna tshogs su shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:3992: de lta bu shar tshad mang po shar yang /
NK077(tsu)001:3993: yin tshad gcig tu chod pa'i thabs byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:3994: 'og nas skad cig la kun rdzogs phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:3996: gzhal gyis mi lang pa'i dgos pa bsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:3998: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi dngos po gnyis la zhen pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:3999: dngos po dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams thams
NK077(tsu)001:4000: cad la shar tshad mang po shar yang /
NK077(tsu)001:4001: yin tshad gcig gis 'gros yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4002: da ltar gyi skad cig ma gcig la kun rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:4003: pa'i phyir rtsa ba gcig bcad na yan lag khri
NK077(tsu)001:4004: 'bum skam / mdud pa gcig grol na /
NK077(tsu)001:4005: de thag brgya chad pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4006: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams rig pa skad cig mar 'dus la /
NK077(tsu)001:4007: rig pa skad cig kyang chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4008: de dngos po'i gnas lugs kun gzhi rang snang du
NK077(tsu)001:4009: mthong ba yang dag pa'i don phyin ci ma log
NK077(tsu)001:4010: pa rig pa rang snang ba yin pa bzhin du
NK077(tsu)001:4011: / 'khor 'das gnyis kyi bsdus pa'i chos kun kyang de ltar du shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:4013: gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid shes na /
NK077(tsu)001:4014: chos thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa nyid shes par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:4017: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad da lta'i skad cig ma gcig la rdzogs lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4018: dper na tshar non lta bu gcig la 'das pa yal ga lo 'dabs can dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4019: ma 'ong pa zhig nas thal bar song ba gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4020: da lta'i tshar non rang la grub gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:4021: gzhal bya'i nges tshig med pa'i dgos pa bsal ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4023: the tshom gyi dogs pa gzugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4025: de ltar na kun brtags kyi shes pa bsam byung
NK077(tsu)001:4026: gi shes rab yin la bar mar 'gyur zhes pa
NK077(tsu)001:4027: ni / thos bsam sgom gsum yod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:4028: gzhal bya 'di bar ma bsam byung gis shes rab kyi yul zhen pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4029: zhen yul 'di nyid yul la gzhal lam /
NK077(tsu)001:4033: dper na lus med na grib ma mi 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:4034: gzhal bya'i yul med pas gzhal du mi btub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:4035: sems rang nyid la rang nyid gzhal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:4037: rang la rang gis gzhal du mi btub ste /
NK077(tsu)001:4038: dper na 'dzub mos 'dzub mo la reg ma btub pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4042: gzhal bya kun brtags kyi zhen pa de dag pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:4043: gnyen po sgom byung gi shes rab min pa'i kun
NK077(tsu)001:4044: brtags kyi zhen pa dag pa min zhing gzhal bya
NK077(tsu)001:4045: gtan tshigs grub mtha' gsum la /
NK077(tsu)001:4046: 'dir bar ma bsam byung gi gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab pa'i yul yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4047: gzhal bar bya ba'i nges tshig 'grub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:4052: don de nyid rtogs par byed pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:4055: tshig gi gtan tshigs mdo tsam gcig brjod pas gsung
NK077(tsu)001:4056: lngas mtshon pa'i don rgyas par 'byung ba'i gazhi'am khungs
NK077(tsu)001:4057: so // 'di rnams kyi don ni sngon byung ston pa sku lngas /
NK077(tsu)001:4058: 'khor lnga la gsung dngos su brda' sprad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4063: sngon byung gtan tshigs kyis 'dir skabs la dgos ched ci yod zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:4066: shes bya'i gting mtha' ma lus pa rtogs shing khong du chud pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4067: rjes 'jug gis kyang de ltar gtan la dbab cing rtogs dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4068: lta ba 'di yang khung btsun zhing yid ches pa'i dgos ched yod /
NK077(tsu)001:4069: tshig dang yi ge ris la ma brten par sngon
NK077(tsu)001:4070: byung ston pa sku lnga dang tshul mthun par rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:4071: pa ni / tshul gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4073: snang srid phyi nang gi chos thams cad kyis ston pa byas nas rtogs pa shar lugs yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4074: tshig dang yi ge ris la brten nas brtag dpyad byas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4079: dngos lnga rgyal ba dgongs rgyud /
NK077(tsu)001:4081: tshig lnga gang zag snyan rgyud zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:4085: tshig lnga tshig yin zer 'dug ste /
NK077(tsu)001:4087: 'di rnams la shan phye zhing skabs phye dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:4089: sku bzhi pos tshig tu brjod pa min kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:4090: sprul sku'i gsung ni tshig yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4091: tshig de brjod tsam gyis brtag dpyad ma dgos par rtog pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4092: ma skyes dgra'i gtam rgyud lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4093: 'di nyid kyis le'u dgu pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:4095: gsung lngas brda' sprad lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4096: brjod dang brjod 'dra'i phyir nges pa //
NK077(tsu)001:4097: yi ge med par mjal ba bzhi //
NK077(tsu)001:4098: yi ge drug bcu drug gsum brgyas //
NK077(tsu)001:4100: tshul lnga'i skabs la'ang de dang 'dra ste /
NK077(tsu)001:4101: sku bzhi po tshig min kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:4102: sprul sku dang mthun pa'i tshul gyi skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:4103: so so'i skad du brda sprad ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:4110: zer ba tsam gyis tshig la brten nas brtag dpyad
NK077(tsu)001:4111: ma dgos par rtogs pa shar ba yang yod do
NK077(tsu)001:4115: bzhi rjes mi dpyod gcig rjes dpyod /
NK077(tsu)001:4117: dpyad du med pa'i go ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4119: dpyad du med pa'i go ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4120: tshig dang yi ge ris tsam la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4121: brtag dpyad ma byas par rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4123: de brjod byed kyis de nyid mthong //
NK077(tsu)001:4124: de bas gser blta gser bzhin du //
NK077(tsu)001:4126: 'o na dngos lnga'i sprul sku'i tshig de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4127: tshul lnga'i sprul sku dang tshul mthun pa'i tshig de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4128: tshig gis skabs la dpyad du med pa'i go ba 'di gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:4129: khyad mi snang zhe na khyad yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:4130: dngos lnga'i ston pa sangs rgyas rang yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:4132: rtogs pa'i rtogs grol thar pa dus mnyam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:4135: ston pa dang tshul mthun pa bla ma rtogs ldan gcig yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:4138: sems ji bzhin pa rtogs kyang rjes shes ma zad //
NK077(tsu)001:4140: dpyad du med pa'i go ba yang /
NK077(tsu)001:4141: dpyad ma dgos par go yang /
NK077(tsu)001:4142: gong ma la ltos na rtogs pa ci bzhin pa min no //
NK077(tsu)001:4143: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par gzhung khog pa 'grel dus gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:4144: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:4145: sngon byung dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4146: de dang tshul mthun par go tshul gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4147: dngos dang tshul gyi gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:4148: tshig gis gtan tshigs la dbab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4150: mdor bstan gyi skabs na gtan tshigs gsum yod pa
NK077(tsu)001:4151: de la gtan tshigs dngos sku lnga yi 'khor lnga
NK077(tsu)001:4152: la / dngos su de kho na nyid brda' sprad
NK077(tsu)001:4153: cing de'i rjes su phyi rabs kyi blo dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:4154: pa rnams 'jug cing bstan pa 'byung ba'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:4155: dper na gser yin nam min bsreg /lha yod med bcad /
NK077(tsu)001:4156: ra yod med brdar nas brtag pa'i gser du 'dug
NK077(tsu)001:4157: pa ma nor bar gtan la phab pa bzhin du
NK077(tsu)001:4158: gtan tshigs rjes 'jug rnams kyi dngos lngas legs par
NK077(tsu)001:4159: brtag ste gtan la dbab par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4164: de ltar dngos lnga'i rjes su tshul lnga yis 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:4165: ba de dang mya ngan las 'das pa de gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:4166: la / 'khor ba de dang 'das pa de'i rang bzhin ji ltar yin pa brtag par bya ba'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:4167: rgyas par bshad pa de la drug /
NK077(tsu)001:4169: ngo bo nyid kyi gsung gis tshul rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4171: tshul gyis gtan tshigs skabs 'dir don bzhi la go dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:4176: chos nyid kyi don rtogs su rung ba dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:4177: pa'i rnal 'byor pa blo mchog tu gyur pa rnams
NK077(tsu)001:4179: phyi nang gi dngos po sna tshogs su snang ba
NK077(tsu)001:4180: 'di nyid sems nyid kyi dkyil 'khor rig pa rang
NK077(tsu)001:4181: snang ba gsang sngags kyi dgongs pa yin pa ni
NK077(tsu)001:4183: de ltar gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de ni sgro
NK077(tsu)001:4184: skur du bral bas nges pa don gyi lung yin
NK077(tsu)001:4185: pa'i phyir / dngos po mthong thos thams cad kyis chos tshur la ston pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4186: chos ston pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:4187: de yang tshig tu brjod pa med par brjod pa
NK077(tsu)001:4188: dang 'dra bar yul med rang gsal du brda' sprad
NK077(tsu)001:4189: pas go zhing rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4191: de rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyis bshad pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4192: ma 'ongs pa'i gdul bya'i don du gtan tshigs nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:4193: chos sku'i gsung gi tshul skye med don gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4195: yang na sngar gyi de yang yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:4196: 'di yang yin pas yang zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4197: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang 'dra bar shes rab kyis mig dang ldan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4199: rtogs pa rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba med pa'i don mngon sum du /
NK077(tsu)001:4200: ched du ma brtsal bar rang bzhin ngang gi mngon sum du snang bar byed pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4202: snang bar byed pa de'ang tshig tu brjod pa med
NK077(tsu)001:4203: kyang de nyid skye med rang snang du rtogs shing
NK077(tsu)001:4204: brjod pa dang 'dra bar brda sprad pa ni rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:4205: tshul lo // longs sku'i gsung gi tshul dgongs pa brda'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4207: blo dang ldan pa gang dag 'khor gyi tshul /
NK077(tsu)001:4208: phyi rang bzhin brda' gzugs kyis chos ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4209: nang rnal 'byor gyis brda'i chos bstan pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:4211: phyi gzugs kyi chos ston lugs gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4212: mthong thos la sogs rang bzhin brda' zhes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4217: kha dog la nag po 'gyur ba med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:4218: dkar po dri ma med par rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4219: dbyibs la zlum po spros pa dang bral ba la sogs pa rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4220: gzhan yang rna bas sgra thos pa la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:4221: gzugs snang gis chos thams cad kyis rkyen byas nas
NK077(tsu)001:4223: 'o na ngo bo nyid kyi tshul dang 'di gnyis 'dres so zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4224: ngo bo nyid kyi skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:4225: dngos po sna tshogs chos thams cad brtags dpyad ma dgos par /
NK077(tsu)001:4226: chos sku'i ngo bo lhag gis shar ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4227: 'dir dkar po dri ma med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:4228: nag po 'gyur ba med pa'i brda la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4229: rtogs dgos par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4230: rnal 'byor nang gis brda'i mtshan pa rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4231: dpa' bo brda' dang zhes pa /
NK077(tsu)001:4233: bsam gtan gyi chos drug bca' zhing mnyam par bzhag pas don rtogs nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4235: dgongs pa la mnyam par bzhag pa'i brda' yis don rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4236: rang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi 'char lugs dmigs pa la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4237: mi dmigs pa skye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4238: zhi gnas la brten nas lhag mthong skye ba rnams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4240: tshig tu ma brjod kyang brjod pa dang 'dra bar
NK077(tsu)001:4241: don dang brda' sprad cing rtogs par byed pa ni
NK077(tsu)001:4243: 'di rnams la rang bzhin gyi brda' la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4244: dbang yul rnam shes lam du khyer ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4246: lta stangs lam du khyer ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4247: dgongs pa'i brda' la brten te /
NK077(tsu)001:4248: dper nam mkha' don rig pa don lam du khyer ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4249: ting nge 'dzin gyi brda' la brten te /
NK077(tsu)001:4250: nyams lnga lam du khyer ba'i gnad yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4251: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i gsung gi tshul rigs pa byin rlabs kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4253: chos ston tshul dper na sa 'og na gser yod pa'i rlangs pa nam mkha' la 'char ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4254: me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad kyis me thon pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:4255: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun kyang rang byung gi ye shes rig pa rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4256: rang bzhin ngang gis rig pa drod 'byung zhing ched
NK077(tsu)001:4257: du ma brtsal bar rang bzhin ngang gis rtogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:4259: tshig tu ma brjod kyang brjod pa dang 'dra bar
NK077(tsu)001:4260: ye shes rang gsal du blo la snang zhing rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:4262: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung gis tshul grags stong dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4264: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun kyang snang stong grags stong
NK077(tsu)001:4265: dbyer med brag cha'i sgra bzhin yin pa'i phyir chos
NK077(tsu)001:4266: ston tshul / grags stong dbyer med de rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:4267: sku'i gsung dang tshul mthun par sgra thos pa tsam
NK077(tsu)001:4268: nyid kyis grags stong dbyer med de nyid du tshig
NK077(tsu)001:4269: don so sor ma brtag par don mjal zhing go
NK077(tsu)001:4270: ston tshul / bar byed pa'o // sprul pa'i sku'i gsung gis tshul bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4272: don dper blangs na chos ston tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4273: sngon byung du ston pa sprul pa'i sku'i brjod pa tshig gis gsung dbyangs /
NK077(tsu)001:4274: yan lag sum brgya drug bcu dang ldan pa shin
NK077(tsu)001:4275: tu snyan pa'i dpe 'jig rten gyis myes po tshangs
NK077(tsu)001:4276: pa'i skad dam ngag lta bu'i /
NK077(tsu)001:4278: klu la klu'i skad la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:4279: 'gro ba so so'i skad du chos bstan nas go brda' sprad pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:4280: rjes 'jug tu rang gis bla ma dam pas ngag
NK077(tsu)001:4281: snyan pa'i sgo nas rang rang gis skad rigs dang
NK077(tsu)001:4282: sbyar nas dam pa'i chos blo dang mtshams tshad du
NK077(tsu)001:4283: ston pa'o // sngon byung de ltar bstan pas mos
NK077(tsu)001:4284: pa spyod pa'i sa la gnas pa rnams grol bar
NK077(tsu)001:4286: rjes 'jug de dang tshul mthun par /
NK077(tsu)001:4287: rang gis bla mas chos zab mo tshig tu brjod
NK077(tsu)001:4288: pa yis slob bu la chos nyid kyi don brda'
NK077(tsu)001:4289: sprod cing skal ldan rnams rgyud yongs su grol bar
NK077(tsu)001:4290: byed pa'o // tshul lnga 'di nyid gang zag dbang
NK077(tsu)001:4291: po rab la snang srid 'dis ston pa byas nas
NK077(tsu)001:4292: byed pa'o // / chos nyid kyi don rtogs pa byung /
NK077(tsu)001:4294: chos nyid ma bcos ma slad par ston pa'i tshig ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4295: ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:4296: skye med brjod med du ston pa'i tshig thams cad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4298: rig pa rang gsal lam ye shes lngar ston pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:4299: tshig thams cad mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i tshig
NK077(tsu)001:4300: go // dbyer med ston pa'i tshig thams cad /
NK077(tsu)001:4302: brda dang ldem dgongs ston pa'i tshig thams cad /
NK077(tsu)001:4304: bkri drang ston pa'i tshig thams cad /
NK077(tsu)001:4306: thabs lam ston pa'i tshig thams cad gsang ba'i sku'i tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:4307: de ni longs sku'i tshig tu bsdus pas tshig lnga zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4308: tshig gis gtan tshigs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:4310: tshig gis mtshon pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4312: rten gyi gang zag las dang po'i shes rgyud la shes rab kyi dbang po rno rtul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4313: rigs kyis mos pa bye brag mi mthun pa blo
NK077(tsu)001:4314: rigs tha dad yod pa'i phyir thabs lam grol lam
NK077(tsu)001:4315: gang mos kyis sgo nas grol ba yod mod kyang
NK077(tsu)001:4318: gang zag shes rab che zhing blo rno ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4319: tshul lnga'i gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas grol ba yod mod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:4320: shes rab chung zhing blo rtul ba 'ga' zhig gis /
NK077(tsu)001:4321: tshig gis gtan tshigs la mos pa'i gang zag rnams
NK077(tsu)001:4322: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab kyi mnyam pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:4323: la sbyor zhing rtogs pa'i thabs yod kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4324: thos bsam sgom gsum de la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:4325: dmigs pa yul gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4326: sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i khyad par gnyis su phye dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:4331: ming don gnyis ka la dmigs /
NK077(tsu)001:4332: sgom pas don 'ba' zhig la dmigs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4340: spangs bya mi mthun pa'i phyogs rtsa ba nas dag par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4342: thos pa'i shes rab kyis gzhung gi tshig thos /
NK077(tsu)001:4343: bsam pa'i shes rab kyis tshig de'i don rtogs /
NK077(tsu)001:4344: sgom pa'i shes rab kyis don la mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4345: 'bras bu gzhan nas 'ong ba ma yin par rang
NK077(tsu)001:4346: gi rig pa las byung bas rang byung zhes bya
NK077(tsu)001:4347: / rang dang sangs rgyas dbyer med du rtogs sam /
NK077(tsu)001:4348: rgyal ba'i dal kun 'grub par byed pas kun ngam zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4349: mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon sum du 'grub par byed pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4350: don dam chos nyid cir yang mi dmigs pa'i ngang yin la bab kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:4351: blo rtul po gtan tshigs la brten nas don la
NK077(tsu)001:4352: dmigs pa'i cho 'phrul brjod pa tshig gi sgo dang
NK077(tsu)001:4353: / tshig de yang yi ge yis mtshon cing rtogs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4354: dngos dang tshul gyi rjes su tshig gis mtshon par gdams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4356: sku lnga la gsung lnga dngos su thos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4357: dngos lnga de yang tshul mthun par go bas tshul lnga byung yang /
NK077(tsu)001:4358: de gnyis kyi rjes su tshig gis mtshon par bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4360: tshig gis gtan tshigs gtan la 'bebs tshul gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4361: spyir rgyal ba sku bdun gyis gsung mtshon pa'i tshig gis gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4362: bye brag tu sprul sku'i tshig gis blo dang sbyar te gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4367: ngo bo nyid rang snang du ston pa ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i gsung gi tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4368: skye med rang snang du ston pa chos sku'i tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4369: ldem dgongs kyi brda'i chos nyid mtshon pa longs sku'i tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4370: gang zag lam la bkri zhing drangs ba'i thabs su rgyud tshig tu ston pa sprul sku'i tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4371: 'dod pa rang rkyen du ston pa gsang ba'i sku'i tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4372: chos thams cad dbyer med du ston pa rdo rje'i sku'i tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4373: chos nyid rang rig mngon gsal du ston pa mngon
NK077(tsu)001:4374: par byang chub pa'i sku'i tshig gis don mtshon pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:4376: rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas kyi snod sgo bzhir gzigs nas chos bstan pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4378: mtha' med pa yi grogs gang dag /
NK077(tsu)001:4379: 'di dag snod bzhi kho nar gzigs //
NK077(tsu)001:4380: zhen chags can dang log sred can //
NK077(tsu)001:4381: blo gros can dang rigs rgyud can //
NK077(tsu)001:4382: 'dod khrid thabs su nges par sbyor //
NK077(tsu)001:4384: log sred can gyi gdul bya la ston pa sprul pa'i skus bkri drang brgyud pa'i tshul du bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:4385: zhen chags can gyi gdul bya la /
NK077(tsu)001:4387: 'dod pa rang rkyen gyi tshul du bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:4388: rigs rgyud can gyi gdul bya la /
NK077(tsu)001:4389: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus /
NK077(tsu)001:4390: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshul du bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:4391: blo gros can gyi gdul bya la /
NK077(tsu)001:4393: don dam nges pa'i tshig tu bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:4394: mdor na gdul bya thams cad blo sgo bzhi re
NK077(tsu)001:4395: gzigs nas rang rang blo dang 'tshams par chos ston
NK077(tsu)001:4396: to // de ltar bstan pa'i mdo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4398: blo phyogs lhung can gyi gang zag rnams kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4403: ngos lung rnams kyi dgongs pa len ma shes par
NK077(tsu)001:4404: rang gi blo dang gang mthun gyi lung rnams la
NK077(tsu)001:4405: / nges pa'i don ston pa'i lung du 'du shes nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4406: phyogs lhung gi blos mthar 'dzin gyi grub mtha' sna tshogs bzung mod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:4408: mtha' bzhi rnam grol gcig pu las med par rig par bya'o gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:4409: rgyas par bshad pa la bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:4411: ngo bo nyid kyi gsung mtshon pa rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyis tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4413: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gsang sngags kyi don ngo bo nyid rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4414: ngo bo de la mtha' ngan pa dang dbus bzang po zhes bya ba med /
NK077(tsu)001:4415: chos nyid de bzhin nyid dbyer med pa'i ngang du
NK077(tsu)001:4416: ye nas gnas pa la rang byung gi ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:4417: lngar rtogs par 'dod pa'i don bya ba'i phyir phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:4418: bzhi dbus dang lngas mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4419: ye shes lnga ru gnas par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4420: de bzhin du kha dog lnga la sogs kun la
NK077(tsu)001:4421: de ltar ye shes lngar 'byor par gyis shig ces
NK077(tsu)001:4422: pa gdams pa'o // 'o na ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4424: gnyis ka sems nyid rang snang du 'dug pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4426: sems nyid rang snang tsam du 'dra yang tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4427: chos nyid rang snang rtogs pa'i cha nas bzhag /tshig ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4428: gzhung na chos thams cad ma bcos pa'i chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:4429: rang snang du ston pa'i cha nas bzhag pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:4430: no // chos sku'i gsung mtshon pa skye med don gyi tshig tu bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4432: yi ge dang tshig dang sgra'i tha snyad spang pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4433: tshig tu brjod du med pa'i skye med kyi ngang
NK077(tsu)001:4434: du gnas pa ni chos sku'i gsung nyid rang bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:4435: skye ba med pa yis dngos su 'khor 'das kyi
NK077(tsu)001:4436: chos rnams thams cad ye nas rang bzhin gyi rnam
NK077(tsu)001:4437: par dag pa'i chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:4438: thugs stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su gyur zin
NK077(tsu)001:4439: pas na brjod pa'i sgra dang mtshon pa'i tshig la
NK077(tsu)001:4440: don ji lta ba bzhin gnas pa min /
NK077(tsu)001:4441: gnas pa min pa de dag chos sku'i gsung brjod med spros bral mtshon pa'i tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:4442: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i gsung mtshon pa rig pa byin rlabs kyi tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4444: mya ngan las 'das pa dang ma 'das pa 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:4445: ba'i chos kyi bsdus pa dus gsum gyi chos rnams
NK077(tsu)001:4446: thams cad kun / yang dag pa'i shes pas rab
NK077(tsu)001:4447: tu brtag na rang bzhin phyogs gcig gang yang grub
NK077(tsu)001:4450: snang ba'i dus nyid na mu mtha' med pa chos kyi dbyings yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4451: de ltar rig cing rtogs pa'i shes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4452: kun la dbang ye shes des bsgyur zhing rig pa
NK077(tsu)001:4453: la rang dbang thob pas rang dbang can zhes bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:4454: // ye shes kyi tshig gsal ba'i dpe 'khor 'das
NK077(tsu)001:4455: kyi chos thams cad tshig gis sgra yis mtshon nas
NK077(tsu)001:4456: don gsal ba byed pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:4457: ye shes su gsal bar gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4458: de ltar ye shes su gnas pa 'di ni rang
NK077(tsu)001:4459: byung gi ye shes rig pa'i gsung yin pas na
NK077(tsu)001:4460: gsung gi che ba'i mchog yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4461: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung mtshon pa grags stong dbyer med kyi tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4463: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams bsam gyis mi khyab ste
NK077(tsu)001:4464: snang ba sna tshogs sems su gcig pa'i phyir mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:4465: dang dbus gnyis su med pa'i 'gro 'ong med par
NK077(tsu)001:4466: 'khor 'das kun la chos nyid du khyab la /
NK077(tsu)001:4467: 'o na khyab bya khyab byed yod dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4468: khyab bya dang khyab byed gnyis su med dbyer med
NK077(tsu)001:4469: rdo rje'i sku 'byung ba dang skye 'gro la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:4470: pa'i sgra skad sna tshogs bsgrags pa yang dngos por
NK077(tsu)001:4471: grub pa med pa las dngos po'i sgra skad sna
NK077(tsu)001:4472: tshogs byung ste / dpe ji ltar zhe na pi
NK077(tsu)001:4473: wam de nyid skyes bu'i lag tu thogs nas bsgyur
NK077(tsu)001:4474: tshogs byung ste / na / sgra skad kyi rnam
NK077(tsu)001:4475: pa ni mi mthun pa'i bye brag sna tshogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:4477: sgra de gzhu rgyud las byung ngam /
NK077(tsu)001:4479: 'di las byung ba'i dngos po med de /
NK077(tsu)001:4480: dpe de bzhin du sgra rnams grags pa'i dus na
NK077(tsu)001:4481: ngo bo stong pa gnyis med de bzhin nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:4482: ston pa'o // mdor na gzhung na grags pa'i snang
NK077(tsu)001:4483: stong dbyer med gar ston pa thams cad rdo rje'i
NK077(tsu)001:4485: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i gsung mtshon pa ldems dgongs man ngag gi tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4487: 'di ni don dper blang ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4488: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:4489: rnams la sprul sku'i tshig tu gsung pa de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:4490: du longs sku brda'i gsung mchog tshig tu mi smra
NK077(tsu)001:4491: ste / 'o na des chos ji ltar du ston zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4492: sku'i brda'i chos rnams 'khor gyi blo la mjal bar ston pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4493: dper na me long nang du gzugs brnyan shar bas
NK077(tsu)001:4494: byad kyi dri ma ngos zin pa bzhin du ston
NK077(tsu)001:4495: pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la bltas pas ston
NK077(tsu)001:4496: pa'i yon tan ma bsgrib par snang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4497: byang chub sems dpa' rang gi rgyud la sgrib pa gang yod ngos zin to //
NK077(tsu)001:4498: longs sku 'dis 'khor la brda' sprad lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4499: de pa ni ye shes sgyu ma'i sgra yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4500: gcig dang du ma las grol la /
NK077(tsu)001:4501: byang chub sems dpa' smon lam gyi lus gcig dang du ma las ma grol /
NK077(tsu)001:4502: de pa kha sbyor gyi bde ba la gnas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:4503: 'dzin pa med pa las grol la /
NK077(tsu)001:4504: rang nyid kha sbyor gyi bde ba la gnas nas
NK077(tsu)001:4505: 'ching bar 'dug /de pa la mnyam rjes med pa
NK077(tsu)001:4506: la / rang nyid la mnyam rjes yod /
NK077(tsu)001:4507: de pa'i sku la mdun rgyab med pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:4508: rang nyid la mdun rgyab yod pa la sogs pas shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:4509: 'o na tshig 'di dngos kyi skabs su byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:4510: tshig tu bstan pa 'gal lo zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4512: dngos kyi skabs na longs sku nyid kyis byang chub sems dpa' rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:4513: de ltar brda' dngos su sprad pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:4515: ston tshul de gzhung du bkod pa'i cha nas tshig yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4516: sprul pa'i sku'i tshig mtshon pa bkri /
NK077(tsu)001:4517: drang brgyud pa'i tshig tu bstan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:4519: 'khor 'das kyi bsdus pa'i chos rnams ma lus pa thams cad kun sprul sku des /
NK077(tsu)001:4520: mos pa bskyed pa'i gdul bya la btags pa'i ming
NK077(tsu)001:4521: dang brjod pa'i tshig tu btags nas bkri drang rgyud
NK077(tsu)001:4522: pa'i tshig tu ston pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4523: de ltar ston nas 'khor 'das kyi rnam grangs ji
NK077(tsu)001:4524: snyed mang po'i don dang tshig brjod kyang grags stong
NK077(tsu)001:4525: dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung las spros pa med /
NK077(tsu)001:4526: spros pa med pa de nyid ming dang tshig sna
NK077(tsu)001:4527: tshogs par snang nas 'gro ba kun la go brda'
NK077(tsu)001:4528: mjal bar byed pa'i ye shes kyi gsung yin pa
NK077(tsu)001:4530: ye shes kyi gsung de ni sgra dang ming tshigs kun las 'das pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4531: sgras smras kyang nyes pa med pa'i dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4532: sgra thams cad kyis mtha'i skyon gyi ma gos pas
NK077(tsu)001:4533: pad+ma 'dam na gnas kyang 'dam gyis dri ma med
NK077(tsu)001:4534: pa bzhin du / sprul sku'i gsung tshig tu brjod pa'i dus de nyid na'ang chags pa med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4536: tshig gsum la khyad ci yod /
NK077(tsu)001:4537: gsum ka tshig tu 'dug zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4538: 'di rnams kyi don gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4539: gsang ba'i sku'i gsung mtshon pa bde chen thabs kyi tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4541: yab yum gyi dbang po rnam gnyis bsrub pa yis /
NK077(tsu)001:4542: yab yum gyi mkha' la nyi ma thig le dmar po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4543: zla ba dkar po gnyis dus gcig tu bde bar shar /
NK077(tsu)001:4544: dper na mi 'jigs pa seng ges ri dwags gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:4545: rnams zil gyis non pa'i tshul du stong nyid rang
NK077(tsu)001:4546: byung gi ye shes kyis chags rtog zil gyis mnan
NK077(tsu)001:4547: cing lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes mthong bar byed
NK077(tsu)001:4548: pa'o // rgyu mtshan de'i phyir thig le'i dngos po
NK077(tsu)001:4549: lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye shes la gtan tshigs su
NK077(tsu)001:4550: pa'o // 'jog pa ni / rtog pa zil gyis non pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4551: don mthong bar byed ba'i las la sbyor ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4553: de ltar dngos la lnga byung /
NK077(tsu)001:4554: tshul la drug /tshig la bdun byung ba /
NK077(tsu)001:4555: ci lta bu yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4556: spyir shes bya rgyas bsdus kyi dbang du bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:4558: chos sku'i khongs su bsdu gsang ba'i sku longs sku'i khungs su bsdu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4559: bye brag tu don gyi rnam grangs ngos bzung nas bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:4560: tshul lnga'i skabs na ngo bo nyid kyi sku byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4561: skad cig snga ma 'khrul rtog 'khor ba'i chos 'di dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4562: chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes gnyis dbyer med gcig tu rtogs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:4563: 'khor 'das dbyer med ngo bo nyid kyi sku gtan
NK077(tsu)001:4564: la phab dgos pas ngo bo nyid kyi sku byung
NK077(tsu)001:4565: ngo // dngos lnga'i skabs la ngo bo nyid kyi sku mi 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4566: 'khrul rtog rang kha ma med pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:4567: 'o na sprul sku'i 'khor tshogs sbyor gnyis la yod zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4568: de dus don rtogs pa'i dus su dngos po la brtag nas rtogs pa ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4569: sprul sku'i tshig la brtan nas rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4571: gsang ba'i sku 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4572: sku lnga'i skabs la dbang po rab la /
NK077(tsu)001:4573: lta ba gcig char du rtogs pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4574: thabs la brten mi dgos la /
NK077(tsu)001:4575: 'dir lta ba gcig char du rtogs ma nus pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4576: tshig dang yi ge ris su brten dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:4577: gang zag chags pa can la thabs lam shes rab can la grol lam bshad dgos byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:4578: gsang ba'i sku byung ba'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK077(tsu)001:4579: bye brag tu sprul sku'i tshig gis blo dang sbyar te gtan la dbab pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:4582: mjug bsdus te gdams pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4583: dang po mdor bstan ni de ltar phye na bdun yod med kyang bsdu na gnyis yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:4585: sku bzhi'i rjes su mi dpyod sprul sku'i gsung gcig po'i rjes su dpyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4586: de yang dpyod du yod med rnam pa gnyis kyi tshul gyis don rtogs shing dpyod par byed pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:4587: shes rab kyis dbang po che chung dang mthun par sbyar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4589: dngos lnga tshul tshig kun gyi zhabs sdud yin par 'dod /
NK077(tsu)001:4590: bzhi rjes mi dpyod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4591: sku bzhi'i rjes su mi dpyod de /
NK077(tsu)001:4593: sku bzhi'i rjes su'ang mi dpyod de /
NK077(tsu)001:4595: sku bzhi'i rjes su mi dpyod /
NK077(tsu)001:4597: sku bzhi'i dpyad du med pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:4598: gcig rjes dpyod ces pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4600: dngos tshul tshig gsum la dpyod dgos zer 'dug ste /
NK077(tsu)001:4603: 'dir bshad pa bzhin tshig gis 'jug sdud la 'thad
NK077(tsu)001:4604: rgyas pa la gnyis dpyad du med pa'i go ba
NK077(tsu)001:4605: dang / dpyad pas go ba'i gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4608: dpyad du med pas go ba'i rgyu mtshan la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4610: gzhal bya chos kun snying po byang chub yin pas dpyad du med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4612: de la snga mas dpyad du med pa'i go bar
NK077(tsu)001:4613: byed pa'ang 'gro drug sems can gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK077(tsu)001:4614: rnams ma lus thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:4615: ye gdod ma nas byang chub kyi snying por gnas pa de'i phyir dpyad par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4616: dpyod par byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis med do //
NK077(tsu)001:4618: shes bya'i chos thams cad mi srid na mi srid /
NK077(tsu)001:4619: srid na srid tshad thams cad chos sku /
NK077(tsu)001:4621: snang na snang tshad thams cad chos sku /
NK077(tsu)001:4622: dper na rin po che'i gling du phyin na /
NK077(tsu)001:4623: sa rdo snang mi snang gi dpyad pa mi zhugs pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:4624: snang grags kyi chos thams cad chos sku'i rba klong
NK077(tsu)001:4625: yin pa'i don la brtag dpyad kyis tha snyad med
NK077(tsu)001:4626: pa'o // dpyad du med pas 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan khung dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4628: yang dag pa chos kyi sku'i don ji lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:4629: bzhin tshig dang yi ges kyang mi mtshon te mtshon
NK077(tsu)001:4632: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis kyang sku bzhi'i dgongs pa chos nyid de 'di kho na'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4633: zhes rnyed par dka' bas bstan par dka' zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4635: chos nyid shes bya ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4636: de ni rnam par shes mi nus //
NK077(tsu)001:4638: chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i dgongs pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:4639: thos bsam sgom gsum gyis yul ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4640: sangs rgyas shes gsum yul ma yin //
NK077(tsu)001:4642: rgyal ba sku bzhi'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4643: 'khor sras po rnams la sku bzhi'i dgongs pas tshig tu cang mi gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:4644: tshig tu ma gsung pa nyid kyang don mjal zhing rtogs pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:4646: 'di'i skabs na ston pas tshig tu 'chad pa dang 'khor gyis nyan pa gnyis ka med do //
NK077(tsu)001:4647: yang na rgyal ba'i sras pos cang ma gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:4650: byang chub sems dpa' yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:4652: dge bsnyen li tsa byi dri ma med par grags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4654: khang pa stong pa gcig gi nang du /
NK077(tsu)001:4656: stan med du gzim nas na ba'i tshul bcos te bzhugs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4657: de yang khang pa stong pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4658: khams gsum 'khor ba'i khang mo che'i brda' yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4659: sngas med stan med du gzim pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4660: 'gro drug gi sems can dus gsum gyis barda'o ba'i brda' yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4661: bcom ldan 'das kyis mkhyen bzhin du //
NK077(tsu)001:4662: dge bsnyen li tsa byi dri ma med par grags pa na shin 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4663: dri 'gro nus pa su yod dam byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4664: a cang 'gro zer ba'i khas lan mi ma byung /
NK077(tsu)001:4665: der kun dga' bo bcom ldan 'das kyis nye gnas yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4667: kun dga' bo sngar yang sun bton pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4670: sngon bcom ldan 'das bsnyung tshul bstan pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:4672: grong na mar dang 'o ma 'tshol du song ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:4674: dge bsnyen li tsa byi dang 'phrad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4676: bcom ldan 'das bsnyung bas 'o ma 'tshol du 'gro byas pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:4677: bcom ldan 'das nyon mongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4679: na ba rang gang na yod /
NK077(tsu)001:4680: gal te na ba yod nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4681: khyod kyi de kas phan na /
NK077(tsu)001:4682: sangs ma rgyas pa yin mod /
NK077(tsu)001:4683: gcol ma chung bar yar log byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:4684: kun dga' bo sun bton no //
NK077(tsu)001:4685: sngar sun bton pa des bred nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4687: 'phags pa 'jam dpal la 'gro nus sam byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4688: 'phags pa 'jam dpal mkhyen rab kyi bdag por gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4689: de la bdag gis 'agro'o gsungs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4691: de 'khor rnams de na re kun dga' bo khyod zas 'dod nas 'ong sam /
NK077(tsu)001:4693: kun dga' bo ye nas bred pa de bas kyang bred bcug te /
NK077(tsu)001:4695: khang pa stong pa 'dir ci bgyid byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4696: dge bsnyen li tsa byi'i zhal nas kun dga' bo /
NK077(tsu)001:4697: khyod kyi khang pa gcig pu 'di stong par mthong ngam /
NK077(tsu)001:4698: ngas ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad stong par mthong na gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:4700: chos nyid zab mo'i don la bsnyung rgyu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4702: chos nyid snying po byang chub zhes bya ba'i don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4704: dge bsnyen li tsa byi dri ma med par grags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4705: ngo bo mtshon brjod 'das pa la dgongs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4709: 'o na chos nyid byang chub snying po'i don smra brjod thams cad dang bral ba byung /
NK077(tsu)001:4711: cang ma gsungs pa nyid kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4712: slar don rgya che bar bshad ces byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:4713: don de la tshig du bshad pa nyan pa gnyis ka grub pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:4714: de bzhin skal ldan gzhan gyis kyang go bar nus pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4715: rtog dpyod gtan la mi pheb pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4717: don yang dag pa yin min gyi dpyod pa zhugs
NK077(tsu)001:4718: na rang las gzhan du rtog pa'i gzhi de ltar
NK077(tsu)001:4719: rtogs pa zhugs na yul du dmigs pa'i rten yul
NK077(tsu)001:4720: du dmigs pa zhugs na bdag tu 'dzin pa 'ong
NK077(tsu)001:4721: gzung bdag tu 'dzin pa zin phyir grol bar mi
NK077(tsu)001:4722: 'gyur ro // 'o na gang du bsam pa'i tshe na rtog dpyod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:4723: gnyis po 'di dag shes pa'i rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:4724: ces pa rtog dpyod gnyis lta ba rtogs pa'i rgyur bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4725: 'dir rtog dpyod gnyis skyon du bshad pa 'gal lo zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4726: gong du bshad pa'i don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4728: lta ba gcig char du rtogs ma nus /
NK077(tsu)001:4729: thog mar gzhung la thos pa byas /
NK077(tsu)001:4730: thos pa'i tshig la brtag dpyad byas /
NK077(tsu)001:4731: brtag dpyad byas pas go ba skye /
NK077(tsu)001:4732: go mkhan rang thog tu bzhag pas gnas pa skye gnas pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4733: lhag mthong lta ba'i rtogs pa shar /
NK077(tsu)001:4735: dang po thos bsam byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:4736: gnyis po 'di dag shes pa'i rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:4738: 'dir don ngo bo rtogs pa'i skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:4739: chos nyid blo 'das yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:4740: rtog dpyod kyis blo yul du gzhal bas gar 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:4742: gsang sngags yid yul gang gis rnyed //
NK077(tsu)001:4744: des na rtog dpyod dmigs 'dzin med par de nyid
NK077(tsu)001:4745: kyis de nyid mtshon pa dpe dang sbyar ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:4747: de ltar dpyad du med pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:4748: dpyad na gzung 'dzin la mi grol bas de bsad
NK077(tsu)001:4749: ser na gang gi gser lta bar 'dod pa la
NK077(tsu)001:4750: / kha dog ser po gcig yod byas na ra gan dang nor /
NK077(tsu)001:4753: rin thang byas na g.yu lta bu dang nor te /
NK077(tsu)001:4754: phyogs re tsam las ma rtogs shing gser gtan la mi phebs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4755: des na gser lta bar 'dod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:4756: gser kho rang lag mthil tu bzhag na /
NK077(tsu)001:4757: brtag dpyad ma dgos par gser la nges shes skyes
NK077(tsu)001:4758: pa bzhin du chos nyid rig pa bdag nyid chen
NK077(tsu)001:4759: po yin pa'i phyir dpyad par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4760: dpyad par byed pa gnyis su mi dmigs pas rtog
NK077(tsu)001:4761: pa dang dpyod pa rnams kyi gnyis 'dzin gyi lta
NK077(tsu)001:4762: ba mi 'tshol ba'i don yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4763: gdams ngag de brjod pa nyid kyis don de kho na nyid mngon sum du mthong bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4764: de nyid don la 'ching grol med par rtogs tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4766: brtag dpyad ma dgos par de brjod nyid kyis de nyid mthong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4767: 'khor ba'i dus na bcing ba med //
NK077(tsu)001:4768: mya ngan las 'das pa'i dus su grol ba med pa'i don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4769: 'ching byed kyi mkhan po dgra lta bu /
NK077(tsu)001:4771: 'ching byed kyi dngos po zhags pa lta bu'i bcing ba med de /
NK077(tsu)001:4772: bcing bar bya ba'i yul btson ra lta bu gang du'ang ngang gis yong pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4774: de la ltos pa'i rnam par grol ba'ang med pas
NK077(tsu)001:4775: de las grol bar mi 'dod cing rang grol du
NK077(tsu)001:4776: rtogs na bcings pa dang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4777: de so sor rtog pa'i gtan tshigs mchog yin pa'i nges tshig dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4779: yul so sor rtog pa'i ye shes rab kyi de
NK077(tsu)001:4780: nyid brtag dpyad ma dgos par so sor rtog lugs
NK077(tsu)001:4781: ni / so sor gang la'ang rtog pa dang dpyod
NK077(tsu)001:4782: pa med pas yul la sogs pa so sor snang
NK077(tsu)001:4783: ba kun gnyis med rang snang rtogs pa'i phyir so
NK077(tsu)001:4784: sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyi mchog yin te so
NK077(tsu)001:4785: sor rtog pa'i shes rab rtog dpyod kyi ming du
NK077(tsu)001:4787: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab mtshon pa'i bla dwags sam /
NK077(tsu)001:4788: dpyad du med pa'i gtan tshigs su brjod pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4789: dpyad pas go ba'i gtan tshigs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4793: dbang po rnon po dpyad du med pa'i go bas rtogs lugs bstan pa gong du song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4794: dbang po rtul po kha gcig phyi ma 'di tshig
NK077(tsu)001:4795: brtag dpyad byed pas grol bar byed pa ni 'di
NK077(tsu)001:4796: lta ste / tshig tu brjod pa'i gong du bshad
NK077(tsu)001:4797: pa'i gzhal bya'i yul dang dngos po zhen pa'i spyod
NK077(tsu)001:4798: yul la rang gi so sor rtog pa'i shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:4799: lta ste / kyi rgyu dang // 'og nas bshad
NK077(tsu)001:4800: pa'i gtan tshigs rnams kyi rkyen byas te don gtan
NK077(tsu)001:4801: lta ste / kyi rgyu dang // la phebs pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:4802: // de yang tshig don dang mthun pa'i gtan tshigs
