NK077(tsu)001:4803: lta ste / kyi rgyu dang // la phebs pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:4804: // dang / tshig don mi mthun gtan tshigs gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:4805: kyis don rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4807: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la bzhed /
NK077(tsu)001:4808: 'di rnams tshig mi 'dra yang don phal cher gnad gcig go //
NK077(tsu)001:4809: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs sgra ji bzhin pa'i sgo nas don gtan la phabs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4810: tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs sgra ji bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:4811: pa ma yin pa'i sgo nas gtan la dbab pa
NK077(tsu)001:4813: don la sgra don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4814: sgra don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs gnyis yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4815: 'ga' zhig bsgrub bya'i don dang gtan tshigs gnyis mthun pa'i gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:4816: bsgrub bya'i don dang gtan tshigs gnyis mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la bzhed /
NK077(tsu)001:4817: 'di rnams tshig mi 'dra yang don phal cher gnad gcig go //
NK077(tsu)001:4818: 'o na sgra don mi mthun pa gcig gis don gtan la phebs sam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:4824: 'di gsum skyon che shos su brtsi la /
NK077(tsu)001:4825: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyi 'gal bas kyang gtan la phebs te /
NK077(tsu)001:4826: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK077(tsu)001:4827: ci ste bcu drug gis gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:4828: 'jam dpal gshin rje la bshad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4831: snang ste ci'i phyir stong par 'dug pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4833: ma nges pas kyang gtan la phebs te /
NK077(tsu)001:4837: stong pa kho na min snang stong gnyis yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4839: snang stong ngo bo gcig yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4840: gcig kho na min pa'i sgo nas don rtogs pa lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4841: ma grub pas kya nga gtan la phebs te /
NK077(tsu)001:4843: mchog tu snang ba'i chos nyid ni //
NK077(tsu)001:4844: rna dbang gzhan la thos mi 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:4845: de bzhin lce'i dbang pos kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:4846: de la brjod pa rdul tsam med //
NK077(tsu)001:4848: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4849: tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4850: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4852: dpe yis nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4854: tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs 'di'i skabs la /
NK077(tsu)001:4857: mtshon byed kyis gtan tshigs mtshon du btub pa'i 'thad pa /
NK077(tsu)001:4858: grub mtha' dang drug tu 'chad pa'i lugs kyang snang /
NK077(tsu)001:4859: dang po dpe yis nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4860: mdor bstan gyi skabs na phyi ma tshig don dang mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:4861: mtshon par byed pa'i dpe 'byung chen gtos kyi nam mkha' 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:4862: mtha' dbus med pa gcig yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4863: rang gis yul khog gis lung srol gyi phye bas /
NK077(tsu)001:4864: nam mkha' mtha' dbus can du ngos bzung /
NK077(tsu)001:4865: de ltar nam mkha'i dbyibs dang che chung mi 'dra ba snang ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:4866: phyogs gcig tu nam mkha' yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4867: phyogs bral gyi nam mkha' gang yang min /
NK077(tsu)001:4868: min pa'i phyogs bral gyi nam mkha' de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:4869: phyogs can tha dad du shar ba dpe de ltar du /
NK077(tsu)001:4871: kun yin gang ma yin rnams go dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:4872: don rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:4874: gnas lugs mtshon pa'i yul las 'das pas bstan par dka' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4876: 'khor 'das kyis chos kun mtha' las 'das pa yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:4877: snang stong la sogs mtha' rnams gang yang dor ba
NK077(tsu)001:4878: med pas dpe 'di ltar don 'di zhes phyogs gcig
NK077(tsu)001:4880: chos thams cad rang gi ngo bor tshig tu bstan pa dang blos brtag dka' ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4881: chos nyid gnas lugs zab mo'i don rang byung gis
NK077(tsu)001:4882: ye shes de nyid mu bzhi mtha' brgyad ma spangs
NK077(tsu)001:4884: ngag thog tu brjod na tshig yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4886: gnas lugs kyi don la tshig dang blo gnyis kas ma bslad pa'i don ston pa byung /
NK077(tsu)001:4887: ji ltar mtshon pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4889: 'on kyang de'i don rgyas par mtshon pa don ci
NK077(tsu)001:4890: yang yin pas min pa'i 'dzin pa las grol ba
NK077(tsu)001:4891: dang / min pas yin pa'i 'dzin pa las grol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4892: stong pa'i mtha' bsal nas snang ba bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4893: snang ba'i zhen pa dgrol nas stong pa bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4894: de gnyis kyi mtha' bas la ba la dbyer med bshad dgos byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:4895: mtshon pa'i gtan tshigs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4897: kun yin gang ma yin gyi gtan tshigs lhun grub tu bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4899: de yang mdor bsdus na ji ltar rtag par chags bsam pa bzhin du snang zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:4900: cir yang 'gyur bas kun gyi ngo bor ston de
NK077(tsu)001:4901: mtshon par byed pa'i gtan tshigs phyogs re nas gang
NK077(tsu)001:4902: yang mi 'gal zhing ci yang yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4903: don sems kyi chos nyid la phyogs 'dzin can ci yang ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4904: de'i phyir phyogs 'dzin can gang yang ngam min phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:4905: med kun gyi ngo bo yin pas don gang yang
NK077(tsu)001:4906: dor ba med pas ci yang yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4907: des phyogs bral lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4908: ma spangs mi ldan gyi gtan tshigs mtha' bral du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4910: chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes de mtha' kun gyi phyogs dang ris su ma chad pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:4911: mtha' rang kha'i 'dzin pa dag pas mtha' dang bral ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:4912: mtha' ma spang pa'i cha nas ma bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4913: des na gang yang ma spang mi ldan yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4914: ma bral phyir na bral zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4917: de ltar chos nyid rang gi ngo bo nyid gtan la phebs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:4919: lta ba gtan la 'beb par byed pa la 'ga' zhig gis /
NK077(tsu)001:4921: kun yin gang ma yin 'di mi 'thad zer 'dug ste /
NK077(tsu)001:4923: gtan tshigs phyogs re ba rnams sun byung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:4924: phyogs med bsgrub pa'i chos skad yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4927: gzugs dang ldan pa yang ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4928: mi ldan pa yang ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:4929: ces pa nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar gsungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4930: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4934: tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la dgar bas
NK077(tsu)001:4935: gcig shos du gyur pa'i tshig don mthun par ston
NK077(tsu)001:4936: pa'i gtan tshigs la yang phyi nang gis bshad lugs
NK077(tsu)001:4937: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i bye brag yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:4938: mdor bsdus pa gtan tshigs kun la khyab pa lung man ngag rigs pa gsum mo //
NK077(tsu)001:4939: de yang rgyal bas gnas lugs kyi don sgro skur
NK077(tsu)001:4940: med par mngon gsum du phyung pa la lung tshad
NK077(tsu)001:4942: bla ma dam pa rnams kyi don nyams su lon
NK077(tsu)001:4943: pa de tshig tu phyung pa rnams la man ngag
NK077(tsu)001:4944: tshad ma zhes zer la de gnyis kyi don rang
NK077(tsu)001:4945: rig pas nyams su myong zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:4946: sgro 'dogs chod pa la rigs pa tshad ma zhes zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:4947: kun khyab gsum po de dag dang ldan pa'i don
NK077(tsu)001:4948: mthun pa'i gtan tshigs kyi rnam pa'i grangs bsam yas
NK077(tsu)001:4950: 'dir de dag gis brjod pa 'og nas 'byung ba 'di lta bu yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4951: rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4952: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4953: sgra mthun don dpag gi gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4956: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:4957: tshad ma dka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4958: sgra mthun don dpag gi gtan tshigs gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:4959: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs la /
NK077(tsu)001:4960: theg pa 'og ma'i chos skad kyis sel ma zhugs cing /
NK077(tsu)001:4961: gsang sngags rang gzhung gi chos skad smra ba gcig dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:4963: dus kyi 'brug char chos gsum pos //
NK077(tsu)001:4964: bka' yi tshad gsum skabs sbyar snang //
NK077(tsu)001:4967: 'og ma dang sgra mthun yang don dpag dgos pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4970: gtan tshigs dpag par ma yin par 'dod /
NK077(tsu)001:4971: de ni gsang sngags kyi don khong du ma chud pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:4972: 'dir gtan tshigs dang grub mtha' gnyis kas dpag dgos pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4973: mngon sum par rtogs pa grub mtha' /
NK077(tsu)001:4974: sgro 'dogs gcod par byed pa'i ngos nas gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:4975: dper na me dang tsha ba gnyis ngo bo gcig
NK077(tsu)001:4976: tsha zhing bsreg par byed pa'i phyir me yin byas
NK077(tsu)001:4977: pas / me ru nges shes skyes pa grub mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:4978: me yin par nges shes skye bar byed pa gtan
NK077(tsu)001:4979: pas / tshigs so // dag mnyam gyi gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:4981: 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams rang bzhin ni yang gi rnam par dag pa'i don de /
NK077(tsu)001:4982: dag pa rnam pa bzhi'i tshul gyis don gnyis med mngon sum du rtogs par byed pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4983: de la rnam bzhi ni snod 'byung ba lnga yum lngar dag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4984: bcud phung po lnga yab lngar dag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4985: rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:4986: khams skye mched rnams lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du dag par rtogs shing grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4987: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par gzhan du shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:4988: mnyam gnyis ni thun mong gi mnyam gnyis yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4989: kun rdzob tu sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad la mnyam /
NK077(tsu)001:4990: don dam spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral bar mnyam /
NK077(tsu)001:4991: lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis ni de ltar thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis las dpags pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:4992: kun rdzob tu snod bcud rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal bas 'khor 'das mnyam la /
NK077(tsu)001:4993: don dam chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su gcig cing rtogs pas 'khor 'das mnyam pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:4994: de ltar lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis kyis 'khor 'das
NK077(tsu)001:4995: kyi chos thams cad spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:4996: kun tu bzang po'i zhing zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5000: lam rim gyis pa ltar bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5001: gcig char ba ltar bshad pa gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:5002: dang po rim gyis pa ltar bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:5003: 'khor 'das kyi chos gzhal bya rgyu gcig pas gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5004: skye med du rtogs pa grub mtha' ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5005: des dngos po mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5006: skye med du zhen pa gzhal bya yig 'bru'i tshul gyis gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5007: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo rtogs pa grub mtha' ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5008: des stong pa phyang chad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5009: rtogs pa snga ma gnyis la zhen pa gzhal bya
NK077(tsu)001:5010: byin rlabs kyi gtan tshigs dang dbyer med du rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:5012: bden gnyis tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5013: bden gnyis dbyer med du zhen pa gzhal bya mngon sum par gtan la 'beb pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5014: spyod yul dang bral bar rtogs pa grub mtha' ste
NK077(tsu)001:5015: lta ba bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod yul du
NK077(tsu)001:5016: byed pa'i zhen pa dgrol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5017: bzhi pa 'di sbyor ngag du bkod na /
NK077(tsu)001:5018: ma rig pa dang log rtog gi rgyun las 'khor bar snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5019: sku dang ye shes kyi dal las mya ngan las 'das pa snang ba 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:5021: de dag rang bzhin dbyer med skye med kyi dbyings las g.yos pa med pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5022: brgyud rgyu sems nyid rang byung ye shes su gcig pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:5023: dper na rgyal po'i phru gu 'bangs su 'khyams pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:5026: chos nyid dbyings su tshul gcig las //
NK077(tsu)001:5027: ma lus rang snang chos thams cad //
NK077(tsu)001:5028: ma lus byang chub sems su rtogs //
NK077(tsu)001:5030: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs chos can /
NK077(tsu)001:5031: rol pa 'gags med lha'i sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5032: mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:5033: mtshon byed yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa lngar snang ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:5035: sku gsung thugs su snang ba yi //
NK077(tsu)001:5036: ma lus gsung gi rgyan du rtogs //
NK077(tsu)001:5037: thams cad gsung gi yi ge ste //
NK077(tsu)001:5038: thabs dang ldan pas rgyas gdab bo //
NK077(tsu)001:5040: rang bzhin skye med rol pa 'gags med gnyis chos can /
NK077(tsu)001:5041: tshig la snga phyi byung yang don la dbyer med de /
NK077(tsu)001:5042: dkon bdun ngo bo nyid kyis rgyur lhun gyis grub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5043: snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK077(tsu)001:5044: ye nas sangs rgyas pas byin gyis rlabs pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:5047: de nyid dbyer med byin rlabs las //
NK077(tsu)001:5048: de nyid de'i byin rlabs te //
NK077(tsu)001:5049: gnyis med tshul gyis rang snang ba //
NK077(tsu)001:5050: byin rlabs nas ngo mtshar bsam mi khyab //
NK077(tsu)001:5052: bden pa dbyer med chos can /
NK077(tsu)001:5053: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te rang rig
NK077(tsu)001:5054: pa'i mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:5057: rang byung rang snang chos nyid dag /gnyis med rang rig ma skyes par //
NK077(tsu)001:5058: gsal bar mngon gsum the tshom med //
NK077(tsu)001:5059: rtogs pa kun gyi mchog tu bshad //
NK077(tsu)001:5061: de ltar gtan tshigs bzhi gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi yis /
NK077(tsu)001:5062: chos thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal
NK077(tsu)001:5063: bar rdzogs shing rig pa la dbang bsgyur bas na
NK077(tsu)001:5064: rgyal po ste / sngags phyi rgyud dbu sems las
NK077(tsu)001:5065: khyad par du gyur pas na 'di las che ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:5067: yang gcig char ba ltar du bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:5068: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad don dam skye 'gags
NK077(tsu)001:5069: gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong dang bral bar rgyu gcig /kun
NK077(tsu)001:5070: rdzob skye 'gags gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong ltar snang bar
NK077(tsu)001:5071: rgyu gcig bden pa dbyer med du /
NK077(tsu)001:5072: skyes pa med na skye ba med pa sngar rgyu gcig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5073: 'o na yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gtan tshigs mi dgos sam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5075: rgyu gcig par rtogs pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:5076: yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gtan tshigs kyis mtshon nas rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5077: 'o na byin gyis rlabs pa mi dgos sam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5079: yig 'bru'i tshul gyis brten nas rtogs kyang mthu yi byin gyis rlabs pa yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5080: 'o na mngon gsum pa dgos sam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5082: dbyer med zhen pa la yang dgrol bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5083: de yang bzhi po rim par rtogs pa ni ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5084: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rgyu gcig par yig 'bru'i tshul gyis mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5085: byin gyis rlabs pa'i mthu dbyer med du /
NK077(tsu)001:5086: gtan la phebs pas rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5087: blo'i spyod yul las grol ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5090: rim gyis pa ltar bshad pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:5094: mtshon tshul 'dres pa'i skyon du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5095: skyon med de rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs kyis stong par rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5096: yig 'bru'i tshul gyis sgyu mar rtogs pa'i ngos nas grub mthar 'gro yang /
NK077(tsu)001:5097: snang ba dang stong pa gnyis la zhen pa'i cha nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5098: byin rlabs gtan tshigs kyis gzhal byar 'gro gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:5099: yang 'ga' zhig gis 'di ltar du 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:5100: bden gsum rang sa'i gzhal bya /
NK077(tsu)001:5102: grub mtha' gsum mtshon tshul 'dres na skyon du che yang gtan tshigs snga ma snga ma'i grub mtha' /
NK077(tsu)001:5103: phyi ma phyi ma'i gzhal byar song ba la skyon med do //
NK077(tsu)001:5104: khyod kyis mar 'dod gang yin pa //
NK077(tsu)001:5105: de ni nga yi chung ma yin //
NK077(tsu)001:5109: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:5110: sngags kyi lam stegs su bshad de /
NK077(tsu)001:5113: pad+ma can du gyur pas na //
NK077(tsu)001:5116: khyod kyi mthar phyin kun tu 'dod //
NK077(tsu)001:5117: thabs chen theg pa'i bstir gnas pa //
NK077(tsu)001:5119: yang mngon sum pa ni grub mtha' yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:5120: gtan tshigs su cis 'gro zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5121: zhor sel zhor bsgrub kyi cha nas 'gro ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5122: dper na mi ngan gcig gi bud med la bu skyes na /
NK077(tsu)001:5123: bu des dgra gnyen la phan gnod gang yang ma byas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:5124: pha ma'i dgra rnams mi dga' la gnyen rnams dga' ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:5125: mngon sum par rtogs pa'i dbyer med kyi zhen cha zhor la sel la /
NK077(tsu)001:5126: spyod yul dang bral ba zhor la grub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5129: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5131: rig pa rang byung gi ye shes nyid dbang bsgyur
NK077(tsu)001:5132: zhing rig pa bdag nyid chen po nyid la longs
NK077(tsu)001:5133: spyod pa'i phyir / bdag nang gi phung po lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5135: bar rtogs pa'i rgyun gzung 'dzin gyi rnam shes thams
NK077(tsu)001:5136: cad rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i ngang du rnam
NK077(tsu)001:5137: par dag pas bla na med pa'i byang chub theg
NK077(tsu)001:5138: pa'i mchog mthar thug gi dgongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5139: rang bzhin bden gsum gyi gtan tshigs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:5141: don dam ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5143: rnam par byang ba mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5144: ma 'das pa 'khor ba'i chos kyi bsdus pa thams
NK077(tsu)001:5145: cad kun don dam dngos po'i gnas lugs kun yang
NK077(tsu)001:5146: dag pa'i shes pas rab tu brtag na dngos po
NK077(tsu)001:5147: phyogs gcig pa'i rang bzhin du grub pa med pa
NK077(tsu)001:5148: las 'char lugs cir yang snang zhing cir yang 'grub
NK077(tsu)001:5149: / snang ba'i dus nyid na chos kyi dbyings nyid yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:5150: kun rdzob rig pa sgyu ma'i ngo bor snang yang rang rgyud du gang yang mi gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5152: de yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku sgyu ma lta bur snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5153: sems can la sogs par rtogs pa sgyu mar snang
NK077(tsu)001:5154: ba gnyis rang rig pa nyid las ma g.yos pa
NK077(tsu)001:5155: yin pa'i phyir / bskyed pa'i gzhi brtan pa'i rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:5156: ba med de rang bzhin rnam kun mchog ldan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:5158: de la 'khor 'das kyi rigs dang rgyud phyogs gcig tu brtag tu med do //
NK077(tsu)001:5159: bden pa dbyer med kyi chos kun gnyis med lhun grub du bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5161: rang byung ye shes la rigs so so dang kha
NK077(tsu)001:5162: dog dang dbyibs la sogs phyogs gcig tu grub pa
NK077(tsu)001:5163: med pa las 'gags med du phyi nang snod bcud
NK077(tsu)001:5165: snang ba'i dus nyid na rang bzhin med de chos
NK077(tsu)001:5166: kyi sku de nyid snang tshul cir yang thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:5167: de nyid du 'gyur zhing cir yang grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5168: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs 'di la don lnga yod pa'i dgos ched go dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:5169: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dag pa yin lugs bshad pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:5171: de nyid mnyam pa nyid du ngo sprod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:5173: mnyam pa de nyid shan 'byed cing rtogs par byed pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:5175: rtogs pa bzhi de nyid ngo bo dbyer med gcig tu chod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:5176: rig pa la rang dbang bsgyur bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:5177: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs de nyid kyi ngo
NK077(tsu)001:5178: bo la ma h+aa yo ga'i bden gsum dbyer med
NK077(tsu)001:5179: kyi lta ba rdzogs lugs bstan pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:5180: bden pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:5181: gong gi kun yin gang ma yin gyi gtan tshigs las /
NK077(tsu)001:5182: chos sku men shel la ngo sprod pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5183: men shel de nyid dwangs cha che ba'i don la /
NK077(tsu)001:5184: rkyen rdzas gang 'phrad gcig 'char du rung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:5185: shel de dkar ser dmar ljang gang yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5186: shel de'i ngo bo la dkar ser dmar ljang yod ma myong bas /
NK077(tsu)001:5187: dkar ser dmar ljang gang ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5188: dpe de bzhin du sems kyi ngo bo cir yang 'char bas kun yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5189: de nyid ngos bzung thams cad dang bral bas gang yang ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5191: drug gis 'gro ba thams cad kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:5192: sems nyid nor bu rin po che //
NK077(tsu)001:5193: cir yang bsam pa snang ba la //
NK077(tsu)001:5194: 'khrul gzhi yod med sgro bskur bral //
NK077(tsu)001:5196: kun yin gang yang ma yin gyi gtan tshigs 'di ma bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:5197: mtshan nyid theg pa rang la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:5199: lta ba bden gnyis lam tshogs gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5200: 'bras bu sku gnyis kyi ye shes gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5201: 'di rnams la 'gal zla la shor ba'i skyon 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:5202: ma spang mi ldan gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5203: dper na cha bram nyid chu yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:5204: chu'i dus su cha bram ma spang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5205: cha bram rang kha ma dang mi ldan pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:5206: chos nyid bden pa'i gnas lugs rtogs pa'i dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:5207: kun rdzob 'di nyid kyi ngo bo chod cing rtogs dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:5208: kun rdzob rang kha ma dang mi ldan /
NK077(tsu)001:5209: ma spangs mi ldan gyi gtan tshigs 'di ma bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:5210: 'khor 'das ra'i rwa co lta bu'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5211: 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis 'chang gi skyon 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5212: bcom ldan 'das kyi 'di la dgongs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5213: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar du ldan pa yang ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5214: mi ldan pa yang ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5216: sgra mthun don dpag la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:5218: sgra mthun don dpag gi gtan tshigs 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:5219: 'og ma dang sgra mthun pa tsam du 'bru non nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5220: don dpag gi gtan tshigs ngos ma zin pa'i rigs kyang 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5221: de bas 'di ltar du shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5224: nyon mongs pa rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5225: spyir bstan pa'i mtshan nyid dang gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:5229: thun mong gi rang spyi'i mtshan nyid rnams yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5230: spyi'i mtshan nyid ni mi rtag cing sdug bsngal ba /
NK077(tsu)001:5232: 'dod chags kyi mtshan nyid zhen cing gdung ba /
NK077(tsu)001:5233: zhe sdang gi mtshan nyid 'khrugs cing ma zhi ba /
NK077(tsu)001:5234: gti mug gi mtshan nyid kun rmongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5235: nga rgyal gyi mtshan nyid bdag lta la brten nas sems khengs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5236: phrag dog gi mtshan nyid blo'i phrag tu gzhan gyi yon tan mi shong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5237: gnyis pa ma nor ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5239: rang gi mtshan nyid yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5240: spyi'i mtshan nyid rang byung gi ye shes stong nyid spros bral du rdzogs la /
NK077(tsu)001:5241: rang gi mtshan nyid rig pa'i ye shes sgyu ma nyid nyon mongs pa ltar snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5242: de ltar mtshan nyid gnyis la khyad par spyi dang
NK077(tsu)001:5243: rang gi mtshan nyid de ma nor bar don rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:5244: na nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par byang ba mya
NK077(tsu)001:5245: ngan las 'das pa'i lam du 'gyur ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5246: nyon mongs pa lam du 'gyur ba de'i phyir khyad
NK077(tsu)001:5247: par rang spyi'i gtan tshigs te snyigs ma'i gdul bya
NK077(tsu)001:5248: rnams la shin tu gces so //
NK077(tsu)001:5250: dpe na thun mong gi rang dang spyi gnyis tha dad du 'byed la /
NK077(tsu)001:5251: shes bya ngos zin pa tsam yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5252: khyad par gyi rang spyi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su
NK077(tsu)001:5253: 'dod pas rang spyi sgra tsam mthun yang don dpag
NK077(tsu)001:5255: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par byang ba'i lam du
NK077(tsu)001:5256: 'gyur ba'i rgyu mtshan zhib tu ngo sprad rgyu yod
NK077(tsu)001:5261: sems nyid la yod med rtag chad la sogs pa'i mtha' te dman pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5262: dbus te de dag dang bral ba'i bzang po gcig
NK077(tsu)001:5263: med gcig dang du mar bral bas gcig dang du
NK077(tsu)001:5264: ma gang du yang ma grub pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5265: gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:5266: bden pa dbyer med pa'i tshul /
NK077(tsu)001:5267: de lam pas rtogs nas rnam par byang ba'i lam du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:5268: phyogs re ba'i mtha' dang dbus ma spang la bral
NK077(tsu)001:5269: ba'i gtan tshigs chos nyid mtha' bral du gtan la
NK077(tsu)001:5270: dbab pa'ang shin tu gces par gdams pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5272: snga ma rang spyi bstan pa de bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:5273: gcig du bral 'di la rtogs ldan pa'i dgongs pa mchan bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:5274: de yang rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa'i lugs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5275: chos can ka ba lta bu gcig la /
NK077(tsu)001:5276: gcig du bral gyi gtan tshigs kyis gcig dang du ma'i mtha' bkag nas bral bar 'dod la /
NK077(tsu)001:5278: gcig dang du ma'i mtha' ma spangs la bral bar 'dod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5279: dper na rgya mtsho gzugs brnyan bzhin yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:5280: de'i phyir theg pa 'og ma dang bshad lugs sgra mthun yang don dpag par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5281: rnam par dbye ba'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5284: 'byung ba chen po lnga rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:5285: rang rgyud par 'dzin pa'i rang bzhin grub pa med
NK077(tsu)001:5286: par gtan tshigs kyis gzhig par bya ba'i dgos ched
NK077(tsu)001:5287: yod pa'i phyir / sa lta bu gcig la'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:5288: rten byed cing thams cad bskyed pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5290: de nyid rdul phran du ma song bar phyogs gcig
NK077(tsu)001:5291: tu 'dus pa sa'i chu drod rang shugs kyis 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:5293: phan tshun g.yo zhing bskyod du btub pa go skabs 'byed pa nam mkha' /
NK077(tsu)001:5294: de ltar byed las kyi sgo nas 'byung chung lnga lngar dbye bar bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:5295: ngo bo ma grub ste tha ma yi ge mum
NK077(tsu)001:5296: gis rlung mtshon nas chos nyid skye ba med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:5298: mum gis mtshon pa'i chos nyid gang du smra ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5299: sems kyi bsam pa'i yul las 'das pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5301: chos can 'byung ba lnga so sor phye nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5302: ngo bo dang mtshan nyid tha dad du gtan la phab la /
NK077(tsu)001:5303: 'di 'byung ba nyi shu rtsa lngar phye nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5304: rigs med phyogs med rtsa bral du gtan la dbab pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:5305: rnam par dbye lugs sgra mthun te don dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:5306: mtshon pa'i dpe gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:5308: dper na nam mkha' la phyogs dang ris su bzung du med pa ltar don snang ba snod dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5309: srid pa bcud kyis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyis chos
NK077(tsu)001:5310: thams cad kyang 'di zhes bya ba'i ngos bzung gcig
NK077(tsu)001:5311: tu grub pa min pa de dang 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5312: thams cad kyis rten byed pas sa dang 'dra bar sems nyid kyis chos kyi rten byed /
NK077(tsu)001:5313: chu mnyen zhing dri ma 'khru ba ltar sems nyid
NK077(tsu)001:5314: cir yang 'gyur bas mnyen zhing de'i don rtogs nas
NK077(tsu)001:5316: gzung du med pa rlung ltar sems la ngos bzung du med /
NK077(tsu)001:5317: sems nyid 'od gsal zhing mtshan ma'i rtogs pa bsreg
NK077(tsu)001:5318: pas me gsal zhing rdzas kyi dngos po bsreg pas
NK077(tsu)001:5319: me ltar yang shes par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:5320: 'byung ba'i don gyis sems nyid kyi mtshan nyid mtshon
NK077(tsu)001:5321: pa de bzhin du gzugs la sogs pa'i phung po
NK077(tsu)001:5322: lnga dang / mig la sogs pa'i dbang po lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5323: gzugs la sogs pa yul lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5324: chags sdang la sogs pa nyon mongs pa lnga dang dkar dmar la sogs pa kha dog lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5325: dbyibs lnga la sogs pa thams cad kyis don phyogs re phyogs 'ga' mtshon par rtogs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5326: dpe de rnams kyang bsgrub bya'i don dam gtan tshigs
NK077(tsu)001:5327: gnyis ngo bo gcig kyang mtshon tshul ma 'dres pas
NK077(tsu)001:5328: / de'i phyir mtshon pa dpe yi gtan tshigs de
NK077(tsu)001:5329: yis chos nyid kyi don phyogs re mtshon zhing rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:5330: / par byed pa'o // de yang theg pa 'og ma pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5331: dpe kho nas chos nyid gtan la 'beb pa'i gtan tshigs med /
NK077(tsu)001:5333: 'dir dpe rang ngo na yin par 'dod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5334: de phyir sgra mthun ste don dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:5336: dpe bzhag nas don rtogs mi rung ngam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5337: dpe don ngo bo gcig kyang mtshon tshul ma 'dres par /
NK077(tsu)001:5338: dpe'i gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab btub ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5340: don dang ngo bo gcig ma 'dres //
NK077(tsu)001:5341: de phyir de yis mtshon rtogs byed //
NK077(tsu)001:5342: ces gsungs pa ltar shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:5345: dpe yi gtan tshigs 'di gsum la khyad ci yod zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5347: tshig tu brjod pa la ma brten par chos nyid kyi brdar 'char ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:5348: 'di ni gzhung na dpe'i don gtan la dbab par bshad pa la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5349: dpe mtshon zhing gtan la dbab pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5351: de la gong gi 'byung ba lnga'i dpe gzhung du bshad pa ltar yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:5352: phung po lnga la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5354: rigs lnga yab yum la sogs rigs sku ye shes la sogs pa mtshon pa'i dper bzhed la /
NK077(tsu)001:5355: 'dir 'ga' zhig gis 'di ltar du bzhed pa'ang 'dug ste de bzhin phung po zhes pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5356: 'byung ba lnga'i mtshon nas rtogs pa de bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:5357: phung po lngas mtshon nas kyang rtogs par byed de
NK077(tsu)001:5358: de'ang gzugs kyis snang stong dbyer med du shes tshor
NK077(tsu)001:5359: bas myong stong dbyer med du shes /
NK077(tsu)001:5361: 'du byed kyis dran pa dang dran stong dbyer med /
NK077(tsu)001:5362: rnam shes kyi rig stong dbyer med du shes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5363: mtshon nas rtogs par byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:5365: de bzhin gzugs dang tshor ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:5367: mtshan 'dzin rang rig nyid snang phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5368: snang stong dbyer med tshor stong bral //
NK077(tsu)001:5369: mtshan 'dzin yod med bya byed med //
NK077(tsu)001:5370: dran stong dbyer med rang rig phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5371: phung po bzhi po ye shes su //
NK077(tsu)001:5372: gcig pas rnam shes ye shes che //
NK077(tsu)001:5374: yang na gzugs kyi phung po 'di 'jig pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5375: chos nyid kyang phyogs ris thams cad phyogs med du 'jig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5376: tshor ba nyams su myong ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5377: chos nyid kyang myong bya myong byed med pa'i tshul gyis myong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5378: 'du shes kyis mtshan mar 'dzin pa ltar chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:5379: mtshan ma med pa'i don la mi 'da' bas mtshan
NK077(tsu)001:5380: mar 'dzin pa'o // 'du byed mngon par sems 'du byed pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5381: ye shes kyi chos nyid mngon du byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5382: rnam par shes pa ni rnam par rig pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5383: chos nyid rang gi rang rig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5384: dbang po lnga'i dpe mtshon pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5386: mig gi dbang po la sogs pa ste dbang po lnga dwangs pas mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5387: sems nyid mtha'i dri ma dang bral ste dwangs bar shes pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:5388: yang na rnam par shes pa'i rten byed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:5389: gzugs la sogs rang rang gi yul la dbang bsgyur bar byed pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5390: chos nyid kyi gzhi brten byed cing thams cad la rang dbang bsgyur ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5392: mig gis rang rig rang snang gi gzugs mthong bar mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5393: rna bas rang rig rang snang gi sgra thos par mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5394: snas rang rig rang snang gi dri tshor bar mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5395: lces rang rig rang snang gis ro myong bar mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5396: lus kyis rang rig rang snang gi lus la reg pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:5397: rang rig rang snang gi don la reg par mtshon pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5399: gzugs snang rang rig ye shes gzugs //
NK077(tsu)001:5400: sgrar brjod rig pa rang snang sgra //
NK077(tsu)001:5401: dri zhim chos kyi dri yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:5402: ro bro de bzhin nyid kyi ro //
NK077(tsu)001:5403: reg bya rang byung ye shes reg /log rtogs yul lnga'i ming tsam du //
NK077(tsu)001:5404: rang la rang rgyud med pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5405: rang rig rang snang spyod yul med //
NK077(tsu)001:5406: kun la de ltar 'byor par gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:5408: yul lnga'i dpes mtshon pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5410: gzugs snang stong dbyer med pas chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par mtshon te /
NK077(tsu)001:5412: ma bcos ye nas de ltar gnas //
NK077(tsu)001:5413: thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:5414: snang ba nyid na 'ja' tshon phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5415: rang bzhin med par kun tu snang //
NK077(tsu)001:5416: de nyid chos sku yin par bshad //
NK077(tsu)001:5418: sgra ni sgra dngos po med pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:5419: sna tshogs su grags la dngos po stong pas mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5420: chos nyid snang stong dbyer med du shes par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5422: sgra rnams ji snyed brjod pa yang //
NK077(tsu)001:5423: dngos po med la dngos po'i sgra //
NK077(tsu)001:5424: brjod kyang sgra'i dngos po min //
NK077(tsu)001:5425: chos rnams sgra ltar shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5430: chos thams cad skye med kyi dri tha dad du 'phros par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5432: snom bya dri yi dngos po yang //
NK077(tsu)001:5433: yod pa ma yin kun tu bsrungs //
NK077(tsu)001:5434: chos rnams thams cad dri dang ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:5435: dngos po med par chos rnams kun //
NK077(tsu)001:5436: the tshom med par shes par gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:5439: yul dang dbang shes 'tshogs pas dngos po med pa bzhin myong ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5440: chos thams cad skye med kyi ror shar bar shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5442: yul dang dbang shes dngos med par //
NK077(tsu)001:5443: 'tshogs pa ro yi dngos grub ltar //
NK077(tsu)001:5444: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK077(tsu)001:5445: gzhi rtsa med las thams cad byung //
NK077(tsu)001:5448: phung gsum rnam shes kyis dbang bsgyur na /
NK077(tsu)001:5449: reg bya sna tshogs myong ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5451: sna tshogs su snang la rang bzhin med par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5453: phung bzhi shes pas dbang bsgyur na //
NK077(tsu)001:5454: reg bya sna tshogs myong ba ltar //
NK077(tsu)001:5455: chos kun reg pas dbang bsgyur na //
NK077(tsu)001:5456: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin med //
NK077(tsu)001:5461: dri tshor stong dbyer med ro bro stong dbyer med /
NK077(tsu)001:5462: reg gis reg stong dbyer med pas mtshon par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5465: dbang po lnga'i so so'i gzung yul yin pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5466: chos thams cad rig pa'i ye shes kyi shes par bya ba'i yul du mtshon no //
NK077(tsu)001:5467: lnga pa nyon mongs pa lngas mtshon pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5469: 'dod chags yul dang 'bral mi phod pa chags pas mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5470: shes byed rig pa'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:5471: shes bya chos dbyings dang 'du 'bral med par /
NK077(tsu)001:5472: yang dag pa'i 'dod chags su rtogs dgos par mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5473: zhe sdang yul las mnar sems pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5474: sems nyid skye med rtogs pas mtshan ma sna tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:5475: la sdang ba'i gsal la rtog pa med par yang
NK077(tsu)001:5476: dag pa'i zhe sdang du rtogs par mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5477: gti mug rmongs pas bye brag mi 'byed pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5478: chos nyid bden pa dbyer med du mtha' dbus tha
NK077(tsu)001:5479: dad du 'byed pa med par yang dag pa'i gti
NK077(tsu)001:5480: mug tu mtshon / nga rgyal khengs shing 'bying ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:5481: ye shes kyis gang shing rgyas pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:5482: yang na chos nyid yon tan gyis mngon par mtho
NK077(tsu)001:5483: ba nyon mongs zil gyis mnon pa yang dag pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:5485: 'phrag dog gis gzhan gyi yon tan phrag du mi shong ste dog pa mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5486: lta spyod dman pa'i gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa rang
NK077(tsu)001:5487: rgyud pa chos nyid phyogs med gyi gongs par mi
NK077(tsu)001:5488: tshud / yang dag pa'i phrag dog tu shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5490: dngos po kun bcom zhe sdang nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:5491: ces pa la sogs pa'i mdo gzhung gis gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:5493: dngos po dngos pos bcom pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:5494: dug lngas dug lnga grol bar mtshon te /
NK077(tsu)001:5496: yang na thabs chen theg pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5497: dngos po dngos pos bcom par rtogs //
NK077(tsu)001:5498: nyon mongs dug lnga'i dug lnga grol //
NK077(tsu)001:5499: dug lnga rgyu rkyen ngo bo dag /rang byung ye shes rang snang phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5501: drug pa kha dog lngas mtshon pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5503: kha dog lngas mtshon nas sems nyid ye shes lnga'i ngo bor shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5504: de yang dkar po me long lta bu'i ye shes mtshon la /
NK077(tsu)001:5505: ser po mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:5506: dmar po so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:5507: ljang gu bya ba grub pa'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:5508: mthing ka chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mtshon par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5512: ma mthong rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK077(tsu)001:5513: ye shes mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5514: dkar dang ser dang dmar ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:5515: ljang gu la sogs nag por bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:5517: yang na dkar pos sems nyid nyes skyon dag pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5519: ser pos yon tan rgyas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5521: nag pos mi 'gyur ba mtshon pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5523: byang chub sems nyid dag pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5524: shin tu mdog ni dkar bar bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:5525: de rtogs bya phyir dkar po bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:5526: chags dang chags par bya ba med //
NK077(tsu)001:5527: chags med rtogs phyir dmar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5528: zad 'phel med rtogs bya ba'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5529: mdog ni gser gyi mdog tu bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:5530: phrin las kun rdzogs rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5531: ljang ku'i mdog tu bstan pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:5532: bsgyur du med par rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5533: kha dog nag por bstan pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:5534: de bzhin kun la shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5538: sogs khung nas phyogs lnga ye shes lngar mtshon te shar me long lta bu nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5539: dbus chos kyi dbyings ye shes kyi bar du sbyar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:5543: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:5544: dbyer med ngang du gnas pa las //
NK077(tsu)001:5545: ye shes rtogs pa'i don bya'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:5546: phyogs dang dbus su gnas par byos //
NK077(tsu)001:5549: shar phyogs kyis nyon mongs pa dang ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5550: ye shes shar ba mtshon la /
NK077(tsu)001:5551: nub phyogs kyis nyon mongs pa'am ma rig pa rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:5552: 'bras dang bcas pa gnyis med kyi dbyings su nub
NK077(tsu)001:5553: par mtshon / byang gis sdug bsngal dang bdag 'dzin la sogs pa byang bar mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5554: lho phyogs kyis gong gi yon tan de rnams rdzogs par mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5555: dbus phyogs kyis chos nyid de bzhin nyid du 'dus shing /
NK077(tsu)001:5556: de nyid mtha' gang la mi gnas par mtshon /
NK077(tsu)001:5558: de ltar ma lus thams cad la //
NK077(tsu)001:5559: thugs rje shar dang sgrib pa nub //
NK077(tsu)001:5560: rnam rtog mtshan nyid byang gyur bas //
NK077(tsu)001:5561: de'i yon tan chen po rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:5562: zhes pa dang rnam bkod las nyon mongs gsal bas ye shes shar /
NK077(tsu)001:5563: de phyir shar gyis mtshon pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:5564: nyon mongs ma rig rgyu 'bras nub //
NK077(tsu)001:5565: rang byung ye shes bdag gnyis dang //
NK077(tsu)001:5566: sdug bsngal gdod nas rang dag pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:5567: don rtogs bya phyir byang du brjod //
NK077(tsu)001:5568: de ltar rang rig rang shar nub //
NK077(tsu)001:5569: yon tan rdzogs pa mtshon phyir lho //
NK077(tsu)001:5570: de ltar chos rnams ma lus kun //
NK077(tsu)001:5571: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings su 'dus //
NK077(tsu)001:5572: phyogs rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK077(tsu)001:5573: de bzhin nyid du zlum pa'i tshul //
NK077(tsu)001:5574: phyogs rnams kun la de ltar blta //
NK077(tsu)001:5576: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas pa khong du chud 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:5577: na snyam pas lung sbyor dang bcas pa bkod ba'o
NK077(tsu)001:5578: // mjug bsdus te bstan pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:5580: gang gis phebs kyang don rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5583: sngon byung dang rjes 'jug gis gtan tshigs sam /
NK077(tsu)001:5584: sgra mthun don dpags kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5585: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs zhes yang nas
NK077(tsu)001:5586: yang du brjod pa de rnams kyis bsgrub bya'i ngo
NK077(tsu)001:5587: bo gang yin pa shes par byed pa'i don la
NK077(tsu)001:5589: gtan tshigs kyi nges tshig gi sgo nas gtan la dbabs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5590: de yang rang byung ye shes lta bu gcig la sbyar na /
NK077(tsu)001:5591: rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung sgrib byed med pas
NK077(tsu)001:5592: rang gsal bas ye shes byas pas nges tshig sgo
NK077(tsu)001:5594: de'i ngo bo snang ba dang stong pa dbyer med pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:5595: gsal ba rtogs pa med pa yin byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5596: ngo bo'i sgo nas gtan la phab rung /
NK077(tsu)001:5597: mtshan nyid kyi sgo nas snang stong la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5598: brjod pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba yin byas pas don rtogs kyang rung /
NK077(tsu)001:5599: sogs khung nas yon tan rin po che lta bu yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5600: rang bzhin 'gyur ba med pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5601: dpe nam mkha' lta bu yin bya ba la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:5602: pa rnams gang gi sgo nas don de gtan la
NK077(tsu)001:5603: 'beb kyang don rgyas par rtogs shing khong du chud
NK077(tsu)001:5604: par bya'o // shes pa'i dam tshig dang ldan par gdams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5606: de ltar gtan tshigs kyis gtan la pheb cing don
NK077(tsu)001:5607: rtogs na phyogs 'dzin zhen pa lta ngan thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:5608: 'jigs par byed cing phyogs med kyi lta ba rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:5609: pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5610: de ltar rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba las
NK077(tsu)001:5611: mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dang ldan par byos shig
NK077(tsu)001:5612: ces gdams pa'o // don tshig dang bral ba go bar gyis zhig par gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5614: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gtan tshigs kyis ma lus par gtan la 'phebs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:5615: grub mtha'i don 'byung ba'ang tshig gis mtshon pa las don gud na med /
NK077(tsu)001:5616: 'o na tshig don gcig go zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5617: tshig gis sgra nyid kyang don gyi dngos po min te /
NK077(tsu)001:5618: tshigs blo'i spyod yul du gyur cing /
NK077(tsu)001:5619: don blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:5620: 'o na sgra don tha dad dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5621: mtshan bya'i don nyid kyang mtshon byed gtan tshigs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:5622: sgra yis mtshon pa de las gzhan gud gcig na
NK077(tsu)001:5623: med de / tshig gis don mtshon pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:5624: de ltar na don de dang po rtogs par byed pa'i thabs tsam du tshig gis mtshon dgos la /
NK077(tsu)001:5625: mthar rtogs pa'i tshe yang dag par tshig lam chad dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:5626: des na btags pa'i ming dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5628: brjod pa'i sgra tsam la blo mi brten par rang
NK077(tsu)001:5629: gi blo'i gting du don phyogs re dang bral ba
NK077(tsu)001:5630: nam mkha' lta bu de go bar byos shig ces
NK077(tsu)001:5631: gdams pa'o // 'di ni rtogs chos khung du chud na /
NK077(tsu)001:5632: lung chos dor ba'i tshigs yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5633: dper na chu phar kha la phyin na gru gzing dor ba lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5635: bzhi pa gol sgrib thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5638: dang por mdor bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5640: de'i steng du gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad pa bsnan pa bzhi pa zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5641: gnyis po de'i lus kyis don brjod par bya ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5642: gsang sngags theg pa mchog bla na med pa ma h+aa yo ga'i don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5643: mtshan ma phyogs re ba kun tu mi rtog par
NK077(tsu)001:5644: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du chos kun thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:5645: shes 'khor 'das kyi theg pa'i chos kun kyang mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:5646: pa nyid yin par rtogs pas 'jig rten las 'das
NK077(tsu)001:5647: pa'i lta ba'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5648: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba'i skyon te so so'i lta
NK077(tsu)001:5649: ba rnam pa mi mthun pa tha dad du bzung
NK077(tsu)001:5651: de rnams mi mnyam pa 'og ma'i lta ba dgag
NK077(tsu)001:5652: cing mnyam pa gong ma'i lta ba gzhan nas blang
NK077(tsu)001:5653: bar bya ba med de thams cad mnyam nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:5655: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5656: gol sgrib kyis gdar sha bcad de dmigs dbye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5657: grub mtha' ma nor ba'i don nyid ngos bzungs ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5660: spyir gol gzhi ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5662: spyir ni gnas lugs de ma yin la der 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:5663: pa'i log rtog gis snang ba mi snang blos bsam
NK077(tsu)001:5664: yas pas 'di rnams ye gdod ma nyid nas gzhi
NK077(tsu)001:5665: gnas lugs la grub nas rang rgyud grub pa ma
NK077(tsu)001:5666: yin te / 'o na 'khrul pa 'di ci las byung zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:5667: 'gro ba so so'i gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:5668: gzung 'dzin gyi dra bas yang dag pa'i don nyid la sgrib par gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:5669: don dam par chos nyid rang gi ngo bo cir
NK077(tsu)001:5670: yang grub pa med pa las kun rdzob tu rtog
NK077(tsu)001:5671: pa'i snang ba cir yang snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5672: des na byang chub kyi sems sam /
NK077(tsu)001:5673: bde gshegs snying po'i gnas lugs gzhi dang dbyer med las gol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5674: de ma rtogs te 'khrul pa'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5676: so so skye bo'i spyod yul 'khrul snang 'di chos can /
NK077(tsu)001:5677: bde par grub pa min te /
NK077(tsu)001:5678: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma ma
NK077(tsu)001:5679: grol ba'i phyir zhes pa'i rig pa dang gcig /las
NK077(tsu)001:5680: dang nyon mongs pas rang gi rgyud bcings pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:5681: gnyis skye rgas na 'chi'i dus kyis dgras 'joms pa
NK077(tsu)001:5682: dang gsum / yang dag pa'i don gyis bslus pa dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:5683: mi rtag ste snga phyi 'gyur ba dang lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:5684: 'phags pa'i lam dang bral ba dang drug /lam de brtsal dgos pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5685: thar pa'i lam la brten dgos pa dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:5686: 'khor ba'i btson rar thar dka' bas btson dong ngam lcags dang 'dra bar chud pa dang brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:5687: sdug bsngal brgyad dang bcu gcig la sogs pa 'ga' myong yang /
NK077(tsu)001:5688: gnyen po mi 'jigs pa dang dgu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5689: de ltar gtan tshigs dgu'i phyir na gol zhing 'khrul ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5690: rgyu mtshan dgu'i 'khrul pa de bas na chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:5691: mnyam pa nyid kyi don phyogs 'ga' tsam yang ma
NK077(tsu)001:5692: rtogs pas gnyis 'dzin gyi dbang gis nyon mongs pa
NK077(tsu)001:5693: dug lngar rang rgyud pa la 'jol nyog tu spyod
NK077(tsu)001:5694: pas 'gro ba lam rgyud lngar 'khor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5695: gol ba'i dmigs dbye ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5696: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5697: 'das pa'i theg pa yo ga man chad gol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5700: khams gsum gyi lta bar gol ba la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:5702: 'dod khams lha mi'i lta bar gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5704: 'di la 'khrugs gcig sdebs nas bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:5705: bde 'gro'i rgyu las dkar po dge ba bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5706: ngan 'gro'i rgyu nag po sdig pa mi dge ba bcu las kyi rgyu 'bras mi mnyam pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5707: dad pa'i kun nas bslangs pa'i las dkar po dge ba /
NK077(tsu)001:5710: yid kyi gsum ste bcu po dag la bzang ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:5711: gtso bor bltas nas dang du len cing /
NK077(tsu)001:5712: sdig pa mi dge ba bcu po spang bar byed pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5713: de'i 'bras bu 'dod khams kyis lha drug dang gling
NK077(tsu)001:5714: bzhi mi'i skye gnas su skye ba ste des kyang
NK077(tsu)001:5715: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don ma rtogs par
NK077(tsu)001:5716: 'dod khams kyi lha mi mtho ris gnas bcur 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:5717: ba'o // gzugs khams kyi lta bar gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5719: chos nyid dbyer med mnyam pa chen po'i don nyid ma rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:5720: dge bcu'i steng du byams pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5723: btang snyoms te yul du dmigs pa'i tshad med bzhi sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5724: dang po rtog dpyod gnyis ka yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5725: gnyis pa la rtog pa med la dpyod pa yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5726: gsum pa la dpyod pa med la rtog pa yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5727: bzhi pa rtog dpyod gnyis ka med pas mi g.yo ba ste bsam gtan /
NK077(tsu)001:5728: bzhi po la rim pa bzhin du rang rang gi
NK077(tsu)001:5729: ting nge 'dzin so sor sgom pas bdag tu 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:5730: pa dang ma bral zhing rang rang gi gzung rnams
NK077(tsu)001:5731: kun la nga'am bdag tu rtog cing 'dzin pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:5732: bcas pa 'di ni tshangs pa la sogs bsam gtan
NK077(tsu)001:5733: mu bzhi'i skye gnas bcu bdun du rim par skye
NK077(tsu)001:5734: ba'o // bsam gtan gyi sgom 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:5736: bde gsal mi rtog gsum la mtshan mar 'dzin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5737: zhi gnas snyigs ma yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:5739: bsam gtan la shin tu dag pa thob cing /
NK077(tsu)001:5740: zhi gnas dwangs ba'i dwangs cha yin par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5741: 'di rnams ni tshogs lam chos rgyun chen po'i ting
NK077(tsu)001:5742: nge 'dzin gyi mnyam bzhag man chad la gol ba
NK077(tsu)001:5743: yin no // 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:5744: bsam gtan gyi nyer ldog yan lag bco brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5745: rgyu de bco brgyad sgoms pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5746: der skye ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5747: ting nge 'dzin rang gis ngo bo ngos bzung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5748: gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun gyi dbye bsal rnams gzhan du shes par gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5749: 'dir yi ge mang dogs pas ma bkod /
NK077(tsu)001:5750: spyir gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas lugs ma rtogs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:5752: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba gol sgrib kyi dmigs bsal lugs tsam gcig byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:5753: shes bya rab 'byed kyi dbye gsal mi spro'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5754: gzugs med kyi lta bar gol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5756: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don dang gzugs med 'khor ba'i chos yin par ma rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5761: ming bzhi'i phung po med par ma shes te /
NK077(tsu)001:5762: chos thams cad nam mkha' lta bu yin snyam pa'i nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5763: rnam shes mtha' yas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5765: yod min med min gyi skye mched kyi sgom bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:5766: la blo gnas par gyur pa de dag mtho srid
NK077(tsu)001:5767: pa'i rtse mo zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5768: skye mched mu bzhi'i sa ru skye'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5769: 'di rnams la skye mched mu bzhi'i dgongs pa ngos
NK077(tsu)001:5770: bzung ba lam gyi sa mtshams 'di nas gol lugs
NK077(tsu)001:5771: bstan pa ni / skye mched mu bzhi 'di rnams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5772: sbyor lam gyi drod yan chad gyi lhag mthong gi nyams las gol ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5774: gzugs kyi dmigs pa las 'das nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5775: nam mkha' mtha' yas zhes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5776: gzung ba'i dmigs pa las 'das nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5777: nam mkha' la dmigs pa rnam par shes pa mtha' yas so //
NK077(tsu)001:5780: nam mkha' la dmigs pa'i rnam par shes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5783: med pa'i dmigs pa las 'das nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5784: 'du shes rags pa med cing phra ba'ang ma yin snyam pa'i mos pa sngon du btang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5785: dngos po'i gzhi'i dus su de dag la rtse gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5786: tshod ni gzhan du shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:5787: mu stegs kyi lta bar gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5789: phyi rol rig byed mu stegs pa'i lta ba rtag par lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5790: chad par lta ba gnyis kar gang zag gang gis
NK077(tsu)001:5791: blos zhen pa de ni chos thams cad kyi don
NK077(tsu)001:5792: gyi snying po yang dag pa'i chos nyid las gol
NK077(tsu)001:5794: don la mu stegs 'di rnams kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5795: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa la gol gzhi byas nas rtag lta byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5796: chos nyid ngos bzung dang bral ba la gol gzhi byas nas chad lta byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5797: ngo bo nyid la gol ba med par la bzla ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5799: 'dod khams pa gcig /gzugs khams bsam gtan bzhi la sa bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:5800: gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi la sa bzhi ste
NK077(tsu)001:5801: khams gsum gyi sa dgu'i zhen pa dag sa yi
NK077(tsu)001:5802: sgrib med kyi ye shes ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5803: sa dgu'i snang ba ma spangs par chos nyid mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:5804: pa nyid kyi ngang du rtogs pas na bcom zhes
NK077(tsu)001:5805: bya'o // 'das pa'i theg pa gol ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5806: rgyu'i theg pa gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5810: nyan thos kyi theg par gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5812: chos nyid gnyis med mnyam pa nyid ma rtogs pas
NK077(tsu)001:5813: chos rnams thams cad la gzung 'dzin phra ba don
NK077(tsu)001:5814: dam pa la / sdug bsngal dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5816: lam gyi bden pa bzhi'i dngos po grub nas yod par lta zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:5818: kun 'byung gnyis 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras su byas nas spangs ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5820: lam gnyis 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras su byas nas mi
NK077(tsu)001:5821: spangs bar dang du len par byed par gyur pas
NK077(tsu)001:5822: na / de lta bu 'di ni bden bzhi nyan
NK077(tsu)001:5823: cing thos pa'i don gzhan la sgrogs par byed pas
NK077(tsu)001:5824: na / na / thos sgrogs nyan thos kyi theg
NK077(tsu)001:5825: pa'i sa pa zhes bya bar gol ba yin no
NK077(tsu)001:5826: na / na / // de la bden bzhi'i skabs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:5827: mi rtag la sogs skad cig bcu drug ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5829: 'bras bu'i rnam bzhag rnams gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5830: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg par gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5832: las gsum dang nyon mongs pa lnga po thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:5833: la gsang sngags ltar 'khor 'das mnyam pa chen po'i
NK077(tsu)001:5834: don nyid du ngo mi shes shing /
NK077(tsu)001:5835: rten 'brel bcu gnyis la snga ma rgyu dang phyi ma 'bras bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5837: lugs ldog gnyis yod par 'dzin cing de yang lugs 'byung dgag bya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5838: lugs bzlog bsgrub byar byed nas de lta bu gang
NK077(tsu)001:5839: zag 'di ni 'bras bu rang sangs rgyas kyi theg
NK077(tsu)001:5840: pa'i sa zhes bya bar gol ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:5841: rten 'brel bcu gnyis skabs 'dir bshad pa mang po yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:5842: rten 'brel bcu gnyis rang ngos bzung shing mtshan nyid bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:5843: ma rig pa'i mtshan nyid ni las rgyu 'bras dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5844: bden pa bzhi ma shes pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5846: las dge sdig lung ma bstan la sems mngon par 'du byed pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5848: kun gzhi sa bon gyi cha'i steng du 'gyur ba rnam smin gyi cha'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5850: mngal gyi gnas skabs kyi ming gzhi yi phung po dang gzugs kyi phung po yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5852: mngal gyi gnas skabs su skye mched kyi sgo drug dod pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5855: mi 'ong pas ldog pa gcod pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5857: bde sdug btang snyoms su nyams su myong ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5859: de ltar gyi lus dang longs spyod thob pa la chags pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5860: len pa ni ma 'ongs pa'i phung po la thob par 'dod pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5862: bag chags nus pa mthu can du bltas te /
NK077(tsu)001:5863: 'bras bu bskyed pa la ma reg par 'dug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5865: sngar ma byung ba'i dngos po gcig phyi 'byung ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:5867: smin cing rid pa shi ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5868: dbang rten khog pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5869: kun gzhi rnam shes bral te dbug rgyu ba rgyun chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:5870: rga shi gnyis gcig tu bsgrangs pas bcu gnyis kyi rigs bsdu ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5872: 'bras bu bsdus pa drug /dang po ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5876: srid pa gsum te drug go //
NK077(tsu)001:5877: de yang 'phen pa ste ring ba'i rgyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5878: 'grub pa ste nye ba'i rgyu tha ma gsum du grangs nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:5880: 'phangs pa ste nye ba'i 'bras bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5884: gzugs skye mched drug /reg tshor gnyis te bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5888: bzhi pa rgyu 'bras tshe dus bsdu ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5889: tha ma tshe du la rdzogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5890: spyir mthun pa mang na yang /
NK077(tsu)001:5892: rgyu'i drug po da ltar dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5893: 'bras bu'i drug po phyi ma la rdzogs par 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:5896: dang po brgyad pa dgu nyon mongs //
NK077(tsu)001:5897: gnyis pa bcu pa las yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:5898: lhag ma bdun ni sdug bsngal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:5902: dgu pa len pa gsum nyon mongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5904: bcu pa srid pa ni rkyen las so //
NK077(tsu)001:5905: lhag ma rnam par shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5911: rga shi dang bdun 'bras bu bsdu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5912: gnyis pa lugs bzlog ni sgoms pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5914: g.yung drung gi lha shugs la brten te /
NK077(tsu)001:5915: ma grub par rtsad chod do //
NK077(tsu)001:5916: rang rgyal ba kha gcig gis /
NK077(tsu)001:5917: 'bras bu ci la byung dpyad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5921: de sa bon las byung bar rtogs /
NK077(tsu)001:5928: de gang la yang rten rgyu ma grub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5929: snod kyi 'jig rten 'di nyan thos ltar rdul du'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:5930: ma grub ste bar snang gi sprin lta bu gcig tu mthong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5933: mkha' la rlung brten de la chu'i phung po brten //
NK077(tsu)001:5934: de la sa chen 'di brten de la 'gro ba brten //
NK077(tsu)001:5935: sems can las la spyod pa'i rdzu 'phrul de 'dra na //
NK077(tsu)001:5936: nam mkha' gang yin don 'di brtag par gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:5939: rang gi bla ma'i zhal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5941: de'i gnyen po dur khrod du song la mi sdug pa sgoms shig gsungs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:5943: ro 'di dag ci las byung brtag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5950: de skye mched drug la sogs pa bzlog pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5951: mthar ma rig pa la thug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5952: ma rig pa'i gnyen po rig pa ye shes bsten pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5953: ma rig pa 'gags de 'gags pas thabs kyi me sod na /
NK077(tsu)001:5954: rtsig khung gi du ba rang zhi ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:5956: de rnam shes la sogs pa 'gags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:5958: de ltar rten 'brel rgyu 'bras kyi dngos por yod par 'dzin no //
NK077(tsu)001:5960: de bas na don dam du gang zag gi bdag med pa'i steng du /
NK077(tsu)001:5961: chos kyi phyogs gcig la bdag med par rtogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:5963: dngos po thams cad rten 'brel 'byung ba bcu gnyis yin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:5964: gzugs kyi phung po rdul phra rab don dam du ma grub la /
NK077(tsu)001:5965: phung po lhag ma bzhi rig pa skad cig mar grub par 'dod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:5967: gzung ba'i yul la rnam rtog bcom //
NK077(tsu)001:5968: 'dzin pa'i shes pa ma spangs de //
NK077(tsu)001:5969: rang rgyal dag gi sa yin pas //
NK077(tsu)001:5970: nyan thos dag las khyad par 'phags //
NK077(tsu)001:5973: yig cha nang na ji ltar snang ba bzhin bris pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:5974: theg pa che chung gnyis 'dod pa 'dres par snang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:5975: byang chub sems pa'i theg pa gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5976: bden gnyis dang rgyu 'bras kyi chos la sogs mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:5977: pa nyid ro gcig pa'i don nyid mi shes shing
NK077(tsu)001:5978: ma rtogs te kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5979: don dam gyi bden pa gnyis tha dad du 'byed pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:5980: phra ba chos kyi bdag dang rags pa gang zag
NK077(tsu)001:5981: gi bdag gnyis med par rtogs na 'di ni byang
NK077(tsu)001:5982: chub sems dpa'i theg pa'i sa pa zhes bya bar
NK077(tsu)001:5987: mtshon bya'i sgra don rnams gzhan du shes par bya bas chog go //
NK077(tsu)001:5988: sngags phyi pa gol ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:5992: gong gis theg pa 'og ma rnams la ltos pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:5993: dbang du bla na med pa'i theg pa de'i nang
NK077(tsu)001:5994: nas phyi pa kri yog ni /
NK077(tsu)001:5995: don dam du ni dbyings ye shes dbyer med cing
NK077(tsu)001:5996: dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma dang bral bar 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:5997: de / kun rdzob tsam du chos rnams thams cad la /
NK077(tsu)001:5998: dag pa sku dang ye shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:5999: ma dag pa phung po khams dang skye mched gnyis kar 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6000: bye brag tu bstan pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6002: kri ya pa gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6004: 'di la 'khrug bsdebs nas bshad dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:6005: don dam kun rdzob gnyis su med cing chos kun mnyam pa nyid yin par ma shes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6006: don dam du dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma dang
NK077(tsu)001:6007: bral ba'i chos nyid tsam chos dbyings su 'dod la
NK077(tsu)001:6008: / de rtogs pa'i yon tan ye shes bzhi ru
NK077(tsu)001:6009: shar ba la de rtogs pa'i yon tan kun rdzob
NK077(tsu)001:6010: tu rig gsum lha'i dal du shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6011: ye shes sems dpa' la dngos grub tu re bar sgom pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:6012: bskyed rdzogs mtshan bcas mtshan med res mos su sgom
NK077(tsu)001:6013: zhing khrus dang gtsang sbra'i bya ba byed pa'i las
NK077(tsu)001:6014: kyi sa pa zhes bya ste kri ya las gol
NK077(tsu)001:6015: ba'o // yo gar gol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6017: yo ga bas gnas lugs mnyam pa nyid la sku
NK077(tsu)001:6018: dang ye shes lhun grub tu gnas pa'i lha rtog
NK077(tsu)001:6019: gam snang stong mnyam pa nyid kyi don ji lta
NK077(tsu)001:6020: bar ma mthong zhing ma rtogs pas 'khor 'das kyi
NK077(tsu)001:6021: chos kun rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyi byin
NK077(tsu)001:6022: brlabs kun rdzob tu rigs lnga la sogs pa rdo
NK077(tsu)001:6023: rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs sum cu rtsa bdun du
NK077(tsu)001:6024: sprul cing snang bas lha dang rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6025: dkar gsum dang dam rdzas la blang dor du byed pa'i rnal 'byor yo ga'i sar gol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6026: chos rnams ma lus thams cad la zhes pa nas rnal 'byor lta ba de ltar ltos /
NK077(tsu)001:6030: 'di 'brel yang ma 'brel 'di lung 'dren gzhung du drang ba yin min brtag par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6032: go sla bar snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6034: gru mtha' ma nor ba'i don nyid ngos gzung ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6036: kun rdzob tu yang nyon mongs pa dang byang chub sems dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6038: gsang sngags bla med kyi dgongs pa nyon mongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:6039: spang ma dgos par thabs kyi theg pa chen po ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6040: ji lta bu yin zhe na rnam par byang ba
NK077(tsu)001:6041: mya ngan las 'das pa dang 'khor ba sdug bsngal
NK077(tsu)001:6042: du snang ba dag /da res 'dir don dam stong
NK077(tsu)001:6043: pa'i thog tu dbyer med yin par mi 'dod de
NK077(tsu)001:6044: / kun rdzob 'khrul par snang ba'i dus de nyid
NK077(tsu)001:6045: du'ang byang chub sems su dbyer med de 'og ma
NK077(tsu)001:6046: dang lta ba'i khyad par mtho dman de tsam mo
NK077(tsu)001:6047: / // de rtogs pa'i lta spyod khyad par du dpag lugs la gnyis //
NK077(tsu)001:6051: nang pa thabs kyi theg pa'i lta ba dang spyod
NK077(tsu)001:6052: pa chen po'i mtshan nyid theg pa bas dpag pas
NK077(tsu)001:6053: / bla med theg pa ste kri yog dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6054: de las dpag pa ni gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga 'di nyid yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6055: tshul ji ltar du dpags na 'og nas ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:6056: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:6058: lta ba chos kun bden pa dbyer med mngon sum du rtogs pa'i khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6060: don dam du ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:6061: dbyings ye shes gnyis dang dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pas 'phags pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6062: kun rdzob tu ni chos kun rig pa sgyu ma'i
NK077(tsu)001:6063: ngo bor lha dang lha mor mnyam shing rdzogs te
NK077(tsu)001:6064: / dbyer med ni gsang sngags pa'i don rtogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6065: skyes mchog dam pa de yis don dam kun rdzob
NK077(tsu)001:6066: dbyer med pa de phyin ci ma la log par
NK077(tsu)001:6067: yang dag pa nyid dbyer med du rab tu rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:6068: / so // lta ba 'di rnams bshad pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:6069: 'bru gnon rkyang pas mi chog lta ba gal 'gags kyis bshad zer ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6070: theg pa 'og ma'i don dam stong pa phyogs gcig pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:6071: khyad par du gyur pa dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyis rgyur 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6072: 'og ma'i kun rdzob 'khrul snang rang kha ma las /
NK077(tsu)001:6073: khyad par du gyur pa 'dir rig pa ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:6074: sgyu mar lha dang lha mo'i dal du 'dod pa
NK077(tsu)001:6075: dang / 'dir dbyer med bshad pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:6076: gang zag rtogs pa'i shes rgyud gcig la dbyer med chod lugs shes par bya dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:6077: spyod pa mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos shing 'gags med cir yang ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6079: dgongs pa mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du spyod pa 'gags med du longs spyod /
NK077(tsu)001:6080: nyon mongs pa 'dod yon gyi phung po la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:6081: pa spangs pa med par lam du khyer ba la
NK077(tsu)001:6082: thabs kyi phyag rgya chen por cir yang ston pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:6083: // lta spyod gnyis med rnam dag chen por bstan pa de la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6085: ngo bo thabs shes rab gnyis med rnam dag tu bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6087: spyod pa thabs dang lta ba shes rab gnyis su med cing rnam par dag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6088: 'o na 'das pa phyogs gcig tu song ngam /
NK077(tsu)001:6090: 'og nas ston pa'i don yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6091: de nyid gnyis med rnam dag chen po la zla ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6093: spyod yul thams cad lta ba rtogs pa'i ngo bor
NK077(tsu)001:6094: dag ces bya ba'ang ma dag pa'i dngos po gcig
NK077(tsu)001:6095: bsal nas dag par byed pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6096: snang ba bde dang spyod pa de'i dus nyid na
NK077(tsu)001:6097: rnam par dag /de phyir kun rdzob kyi chos kun
NK077(tsu)001:6098: byang chub snying por snang bas rdzun par mi lta'o
NK077(tsu)001:6099: // gsum pa ma nor bar dmigs nas grub mtha' blang ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6104: gtan tshigs rnams kyis de ltar dngos po'i gnas lugs brtag shing gtan la phabs /
NK077(tsu)001:6105: gol sgrib kyi dmigs phye nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6106: ma nor bar don gyi grub mtha' blang ba ni 'og nas bstan pa 'di rnams yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6107: rgyas par bshad pa de la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:6109: dang po chos kun mnyam pa nyid byang chub sems su bstan pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6111: chos kun mnyam pa nyid du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6112: de byang chub sems su bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6115: chos kun rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid la nyams pa med par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6116: drang gong du bstan pa 'dis theg pa'i mtho dman thams cad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6117: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba thams cad kun rang byung
NK077(tsu)001:6118: gi ye shes chen por shes rab kyis rab tu
NK077(tsu)001:6119: brtag na rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu grub pa med
NK077(tsu)001:6120: pa la cir yang 'grub kyang rang bzhin mnyam pa
NK077(tsu)001:6121: chen po'i dbyings las nyams pa med de /
NK077(tsu)001:6122: 'khor 'das snang srid kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:6123: mnyam pa nyid ro gcig par rtogs nas ma nor
NK077(tsu)001:6125: mnyam nyid phyogs ris zhe 'dod med par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6127: 'o na mnyam pa'i don nyid rang ji lta bu yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6128: chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyis rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu gang yang med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6129: chos kun mnyam pa nyid yin la ngo bo 'drar phyogs gcig tu mtshon du med /
NK077(tsu)001:6130: mnyam pa nyid du 'dzin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6131: bzang ngan gyi rtog pa gang yang med do //
NK077(tsu)001:6132: de phyir mnyam pa nyid yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6133: de byang chub sems su bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6135: chos kun gnyis med rang grol bas byang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6137: byang chub dang sems la sogs pa rnam grangs thams cad ni 'di lta ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6138: blos shin tu brtag par dka' zhing ngo bo gting
NK077(tsu)001:6139: zab pas yul dang yul can du 'das pa ma
NK077(tsu)001:6140: dmigs da ltar bar mi dmigs ma 'ongs pa dmigs
NK077(tsu)001:6141: su med pas rnam par dag ste byang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6142: chos kun sems su 'dus pas chub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6144: byang chub sems zhes tha snyad du brjod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6145: dang po gang nas kyang ma 'ongs tha ma gar yang mi 'gro /
NK077(tsu)001:6146: da lta gang la yang mi gnas te yul dang
NK077(tsu)001:6147: yul can gyi rtog pa gang yang med pas rang
NK077(tsu)001:6149: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang khams gsum gyi sems
NK077(tsu)001:6150: can thams cad byang chub sems la gnas pas chub
NK077(tsu)001:6151: pa'o // sems dang byang chub gnyis med rang snang bas sems so //
NK077(tsu)001:6153: sems nyid de don ni ji lta bu zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6154: byang chub de ni sems nyid rang snang yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6155: de na sems nyid byang chub gnyis su med cing
NK077(tsu)001:6156: dbyer med pas khams gsum gyi sems can lus pa
NK077(tsu)001:6158: dus gsum gyi bsdus pa'i chos rnams thams cad rang gi ye shes rang snang yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6159: sems nyid byang chub sems su ngo sprad pa 'di
NK077(tsu)001:6160: nyid la byang ba stong pa'i rang bzhin dri med
NK077(tsu)001:6161: ka dag brjod bral gyi gnas lugs khong du chud
NK077(tsu)001:6162: dgos chub pa snang ba'i rang bzhin 'gags med lhun
NK077(tsu)001:6163: grub rang gsal gyi ye shes khung du chud dgos
NK077(tsu)001:6164: / sems rig pa'i rang bzhin dbyer med ro gcig gnyis med kyi don khung du chud dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:6165: don la snang rig stong gsum 'di byang chub sems yin par rtogs dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:6166: bya brtsal med par gnas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6168: nyid la gzhan du lta zhing 'tshol ba gol bar bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6170: sems nyid kyi ngo bo 'di la yod pa las brtsal na dngos por sgro btags pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6171: sgro btags kyi dngos po brgyad du ltung zhing gol bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:6173: yul shes bem rig tha dad du yod pas 'dod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6174: so so skye bo ltar sgro btags pa dang gcig /bdag rtag pa'i dngos por 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6175: mu stegs rtag lta ba ltar sgro btags pa dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6176: dus gsum rdzas yod dang gzung 'dzin phra ba don dam pa'i bden par 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6177: nyan thos ltar sgro btags pa dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:6178: gzung ba don dam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6179: rten 'brel rgyu 'bras su 'dod na rang rgyal ltar sgro btags pa dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:6180: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig skad cig skye 'gags can du 'don na /
NK077(tsu)001:6181: sems tsam ltar sgro btags pa dang lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:6182: snang ba sgyu ma lta bur bden par 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6183: dbu ma ltar sgro btags pa dang drug /kun rdzob
NK077(tsu)001:6184: sgyu ma lta bur bden cing don dam dbyings ye
NK077(tsu)001:6185: shes gnyis su med pa'i rig pa bden par 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:6186: na / kri ya ltar sgro btags pa dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:6187: kun rdzob byin rlabs kyi snang ba lha'i dal du
NK077(tsu)001:6188: 'dod la don dam dbyings ye shes gnyis mtha' bral
NK077(tsu)001:6189: du 'dod na / yo ga ltar sgro btags pa dang brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:6190: de rnams kyang gnyis med khung du ma chud cing /
NK077(tsu)001:6191: phyogs 'dzin dngos po'i mtha' dang ma bral bas /
NK077(tsu)001:6193: don dam pa'i ngo bo la yang dag pa ci
NK077(tsu)001:6194: yang med pa las btsal na chos rnams la bskur
NK077(tsu)001:6195: pas btab ste / bskur btab bcu'i gnas su gol zhing ltung bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:6197: chos nyid stong pa la yul shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6198: 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras gtan ma grub ste cir yang med par 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6199: 'gro drug gis snang ba'i rgyu 'bras la bskur bas btab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6200: bdag gtan nas med par 'dod na mu stegs rtag pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6201: yon tan la bskur pas btab pa dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6202: gzung 'dzin phra ba dang che ba'i yon tan med par 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6203: nyan thos kyi 'bras bu dang lta ba bskur pas btab pa dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:6204: rten 'brel gyi rgyu 'bras dang nang skad cig tsam yang gtan med par 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6205: rang rgyal gyi lta ba la bskur pas btab pa dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:6206: sems kyi snang ba tsam dang gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig tsam yang med par 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6207: sems tsam la bskur bas btab pa dang lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:6208: kun rdzob tu snang ba sems yin pa dang don
NK077(tsu)001:6209: dam skye ba med pa'i don gtan med par 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:6210: na / rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma la bskur
NK077(tsu)001:6211: pas btab pa dang drug /snang ba rag pa rdul
NK077(tsu)001:6213: kha dog ngo bo mtha' dang bral ba'i rig pa
NK077(tsu)001:6214: gtan med par 'dod na mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu
NK077(tsu)001:6215: ma la bskur ba dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:6216: lha dang lha mo'i dal dang dbyings ye shes gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:6217: su med pa'i rig pa tsam yang gtan nas med
NK077(tsu)001:6218: par 'dod na / kri ya'i grub mtha' la bskur pas btab pa dang brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:6219: rigs bzhi'i lha'i dal dang mtha' bral gyi ye shes tsam yang gtan nas med par 'dod na /
NK077(tsu)001:6220: u pa ya yi grub mtha' la bskur pas btab
NK077(tsu)001:6221: pa dang dgu snang ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dal
NK077(tsu)001:6222: dang mtha' bral gyi ye shes gtan med par 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:6223: na / yo ga la bskur pas btab pa dang bcu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6224: de ni shes bya ci yang ma grub pa'i gtan tshigs med pa chad stong du 'dod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6225: so so'i rgyu 'bras dang bder gshegs snying po la sogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:6226: shes bya'i dal snang tshad la bskur bas btab pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6227: bskur 'debs kyi log lta mkhan po de dmyal ba'i gnas su ltung bar gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:6228: de ltar ma yin te yod med gnyis las gzhan du brtsal bar byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6229: de nyid lung du ma bstan 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:6230: mu stug khas mi len du gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:6231: ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba bden gsum dbyer med
NK077(tsu)001:6232: kyi rang bzhin phyogs med ma gtogs pa rnams kyis
NK077(tsu)001:6233: sgro skur lung ma bstan 'di gsum la gol ba
NK077(tsu)001:6234: yin te / gong gi gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad pa rnams kyi mjug sdud yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6236: theg pa 'og ma rang gi 'dod pa la dam
NK077(tsu)001:6237: du 'dzin cing phyogs rer bzung ba ni phyogs med
NK077(tsu)001:6238: gnas lugs kyi don la sgro btags pa yin te
NK077(tsu)001:6239: skur btab ni / chos nyid ci'i ngo bor ma grub pa la blo rtse gtad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6240: lha mi'i theg pa nas bzung ste lam stegs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:6241: theg pa rnams kyi don 'gyur mi bden par 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:6242: nas / stong nyid rig pa'i snying po can yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6243: theg pa sna tshogs su shar ba ma shes nas bskur pas btab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6245: yod med gong du'ang nges shes ma skyes nas khas len du ma btub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:6246: sems nyid phyogs bral bya brtsal med par gnas pa dpe dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6248: yod med gnyis ka gsum po gang la brtsal kyang
NK077(tsu)001:6249: skyon 'dug pa de'i phyir dper na 'byung chen gtos
NK077(tsu)001:6251: la las yod do zhes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6252: la las med do zhes pa la sogs pa nam
NK077(tsu)001:6253: mkha'i mtshan nyid la mi mkhas pa'i blun po rnams
NK077(tsu)001:6254: ni yod med mi mthun par rtsod par gyur te
NK077(tsu)001:6255: / nam mkha'i mtshan nyid la mkhas pa rnams kyis
NK077(tsu)001:6256: nam mkha'i rang bzhin yod med la sogs pa mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:6257: las grol ba yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:6258: nam mkha' la cho 'phrul cir yang 'char zhing go skabs 'byed pas med par kyang mi 'dzin la /
NK077(tsu)001:6259: kha dog dbyibs su ma grub pas yod pa kho nar kyang mi 'dzin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6260: yod med kyi mtha' kun dang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6261: de kho na nyid ming gi rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6263: dgos ched kyi sgo nas ming gi rnam grangs gang yang mi 'gal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6265: sems nyid rang snang phyogs med kun tu 'char bas yod pa kun gyi ngo bo yang yin /
NK077(tsu)001:6266: sems nyid la dngos po ma grub pas med pa kun gyi ngo bo yang yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6267: des na sems nyid la yod med kyi sgra tsam
NK077(tsu)001:6268: du brjod du rung med kyi sems nyid kyi ngo
NK077(tsu)001:6269: bo 'di yin zhes tshig tu bstan cing blos dpag
NK077(tsu)001:6270: dka' la phyogs su 'dzin pas yod dang zhes ci
NK077(tsu)001:6271: byar yod de / phyogs med mnyam pa nyid du rtogs dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:6272: 'o na tshig tu mtshon du mtshon dus don mtshon pa'i ming grangs dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6273: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:6274: de min par 'dzin pa'i lta ba ngan pa las
NK077(tsu)001:6275: bzlog pa'i phyir gnyis can gyi zhen pa dag pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6276: don la gnyis med bshad dgos byung /
NK077(tsu)001:6277: mi mnyam pa la mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6278: nyon mongs pa ma spangs zhing ye shes ma rgyas pa la ye nas sangs rgyas pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:6279: de bzhin du bdag nyid chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6283: bla na med pa'i byang chub dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6292: rang byung ye shes la sogs su don la mtshon du med kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:6293: gdul bya'i ngor rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas gang yang
NK077(tsu)001:6294: mi 'gal bar bla dag tsam brjod pa yin no
NK077(tsu)001:6295: // don tshig la mi gnas pa la bazla'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6297: de ltar byang chub kyi sems de yang gzhi ye
NK077(tsu)001:6298: gdod ma nas tshig gis dngos po'i don de tshig
NK077(tsu)001:6299: gi mtshon pa bzhin mi gnas pas tshig lam don
NK077(tsu)001:6300: la chad pa'o // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6301: sems nyid chos kun gyi ngo bo'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:6302: de dag la sogs pa sgra tsam du brjod cing
NK077(tsu)001:6303: yod med la sogs pa'i tha snyad gdags su ci
NK077(tsu)001:6305: de bas na tshig tu bstan cing blos brtag par dka' ba rgyal bas gsungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:6306: skyes bu mchog gi spyod yul yin pas rtogs shing par gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6308: 'o na gang zag gis rtogs zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6309: blo phyogs zhen gyi mtha' la mi gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6310: tshig tha snyad brjod pa'i dus de nyid na /
NK077(tsu)001:6311: tshig gis dri mas gos ma myong ba la ma chags zhes zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:6312: dper na me tog pad+ma 'dam nas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:6313: 'dam gyis nyes skyon gyis dri mas ma gos pa
NK077(tsu)001:6314: dang 'dra ba'i rang byung gi ye shes mngon sum
NK077(tsu)001:6315: du rtogs pa can gyi spyod yul de /
NK077(tsu)001:6316: tshig gi tha snyad la brten pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6317: gzhan yang theg 'og kun dang thun mong de ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:6318: de lta bu ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6319: de ni skyes bu blo rtsal dang ldan pa shes rab can gyi rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6320: de phyir shes rab kyi blo rtsal can rnams kyis brtson par gyis zhig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6322: brgyad pa rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:6325: lta ba kun 'dir smos pa'i dgos ched do //
NK077(tsu)001:6326: dang po nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6329: lta ba'i ngo bo dngos po dang ming gi rnam grangs te dbye ba ston pa dang gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:6330: lta ba'i ngo bo'i rim pas rnam grangs rnam par phye ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6332: lta ba'i ngo bo dngos po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6338: snga ma lta ba'i ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6340: kha gcig dbang po'i mngon sum du snang ba 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:6341: rnam par shes pa tshogs drug gam /
NK077(tsu)001:6342: tshogs brgyad nyid ye shes lngar gnas su gyur pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:6343: 'og nas ston pa'i shes rab kyi dbang po drug
NK077(tsu)001:6344: gi tshul du gnas pa lta ba'i ngo bor brjod
NK077(tsu)001:6345: do don rang gis mtshan nyid nges par ma nor
NK077(tsu)001:6346: zhing yang dag pa'i lta ba mthong ba yang tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:6347: brgyad ye shes lnga ru gsal ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:6348: gtan tshigs de bas sgo lnga yul med rang gsal bar rtogs pa lta ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6349: dbyings dang rig pa dbyer med bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6350: shes bya chos dbyings dang shes byed rig pa'i ye
NK077(tsu)001:6351: shes gnyis su med par chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:6352: du dbyer med cing 'du 'bral med pas rdo rje'i
