NK077(tsu)001:6354: gzung 'dzin gnyis med dmigs med rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6356: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems dang
NK077(tsu)001:6357: bral ba'i rang rig pa'i ye shes byang chub kyi
NK077(tsu)001:6358: sems nyid dmigs bya dmigs byed med pa'i tshul du
NK077(tsu)001:6359: rang snang ba ni lta ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6360: chos kun lhun grub phyi nang rnam dag tu bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6362: chos nyid la phyogs ris med pas yangs shing rgya che la lhun gyis grub lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6363: phyi nang snod bcud ye nas kun gzhi rang snang du dag pa ni lta ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6364: rnam dag mnyam nyid chen por bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6366: de ltar dag par rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid kyang
NK077(tsu)001:6367: chos nyid dbyings nyid yin pa 'di ni dbyer med
NK077(tsu)001:6368: pas rdo rje bzang ngan med par mnyam pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:6369: yin no // shes bya shes byed gnyis med du bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6371: shes byed dang shes bya'i spyod yul gnyis su med
NK077(tsu)001:6372: pas 'khor 'das thams cad ma lus lus pa med
NK077(tsu)001:6373: par kun gzhi rang snang du gcig pa'i ngang du
NK077(tsu)001:6374: rtogs pa lta ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6375: lta ba'i ngo bo la dmigs drug yod pa'i don 'di rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:6376: dgos ched ma 'dres pa'i ngos nas don 'brel cha nas go dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:6377: tshogs brgyad lta ba'i ngo bor bstan pa la brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:6379: gzugs gsal stong dbyer med rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6381: chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gsal
NK077(tsu)001:6382: stong gnyis su med par gzugs rang snang ba ni
NK077(tsu)001:6383: / lta bya'i yul dang lta bar byed pa'i mkhan
NK077(tsu)001:6384: po gnyis su med par phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams
NK077(tsu)001:6385: cad skye med rang snang du mthong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6387: gang du'ang ma mthong gnyis med rang gsal du mthong
NK077(tsu)001:6388: bas spyan gyi mchog de ni shes rab spyan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:6389: lta ba'o // sgra grags stong dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6391: khyab bya khyab byed med par rang byung gi ye
NK077(tsu)001:6392: shes kyis khyab cing rig pa rang gsal ba rang
NK077(tsu)001:6393: bzhin gyi go ba'i sgra de ni thos par bya
NK077(tsu)001:6394: ba dang / thos par byed par gnyis med par
NK077(tsu)001:6395: thos pa ni thos pa'i phul du phyin pa ni
NK077(tsu)001:6396: shes rab snyan gyi lta ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6397: dri tshor stong dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6399: gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma med cing dngas bas shes
NK077(tsu)001:6400: rab kyi dbang po tshim par byed pa'i chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:6401: kyi dri yin te bsnam bya snom byed med par
NK077(tsu)001:6402: tshor ba'i shangs ni shes rab shangs kyi lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:6403: yin no // ro myong stong dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6405: chos nyid kyi don gyi bcud dam snying po chos
NK077(tsu)001:6406: nyid thams cad snang stong gnyis med rang rig pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6407: mngon gsum du nyams su myong ba ni chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:6409: de nyid myong bar bya ba'i yul ro dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6410: myang bya myong byed kyi shes pa gnyis rang kha
NK077(tsu)001:6411: ma med par don gnyis med rang gsal nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:6413: shes rab ljags kyi lta ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6414: reg reg stong dbyer med du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6416: de tsam na yang dag pa chos nyid kyi don
NK077(tsu)001:6417: la blos reg pa nyid ni chos nyid kyi reg
NK077(tsu)001:6418: pa yin la / de nyid reg pa kun gyi
NK077(tsu)001:6419: dngos gzhi yin te reg bya reg byed rang kha
NK077(tsu)001:6420: ma dang bral bas don gnyis med rang gsal du
NK077(tsu)001:6421: pa yin la / reg pa ni / shes rab lus kyi lta ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6422: de ltar sgo lnga yul dang bcas pa chos kyi dbyings su rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6423: mthar phyin pa'i dus su bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:6424: yid phyogs med ye shes rang snang du bstan pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6426: 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyii chos khams sna
NK077(tsu)001:6427: tshogs kun rang rig chos nyid gnyis med du mkhyen
NK077(tsu)001:6428: pa ni shes rab yid kyi lta ba yin la
NK077(tsu)001:6429: / rang rig pa de ni chos nyid gnyis med du dbang bsgyur bas rgyal por brjod la /
NK077(tsu)001:6430: gnyis med rang gsal du mkhyen pas rang snang ba'o zhes smos te /
NK077(tsu)001:6431: de ni shes rab yid kyi lta ba so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:6432: nyon yid bdag med gnyis med rang gsal du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6434: thams cad rang snang ba yin pa de bas kun
NK077(tsu)001:6435: gzhi la bdag tu 'dzin pa nyon mongs pa'i yid
NK077(tsu)001:6436: kyang rig pa gnyis med rang gsal ba nyid ni
NK077(tsu)001:6437: / de yang kun gzhi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dbyer med yin phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:6438: 'dzin pa ma spangs pas bdag tu 'dzin pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:6439: bcas pa ltar snang ba nyid na 'dzin pa rang
NK077(tsu)001:6440: kha mar mi gnas pa'i don gyi bdag rang rgyud
NK077(tsu)001:6441: par 'dzin pa dang bral ba'i yid gnyis med rang
NK077(tsu)001:6443: nyon yid bdag med rang gsal gyi lta ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6444: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi don yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6445: kun gzhir gsal ba ye shes thams cad mkhyen pa'i lta ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6447: phyi rol gyi don yul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6448: sems can thams cad kyi kun gzhi la rtog pa
NK077(tsu)001:6449: rang rgyud pa med par gsal ba de ni rang
NK077(tsu)001:6450: byung ye shes kyi chos thams cad rtog pa med
NK077(tsu)001:6451: par gnyis med rang gsal du mkhyen pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6452: kun gzhi thams cad mkhyen pa shes rab kyi lta ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6453: me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:6454: chos dbyings ye shes ni ye shes bzhi ka'i rten yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6455: de ni tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar ngo sprod pa'i lta ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6456: ming gi rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6461: lam zag bcas kyi lta grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6463: gong du lta ba'i ngo bo'i rnam grangs song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6464: 'dir ming gi rnam grangs brjod pas na yang ni zhes zer la /
NK077(tsu)001:6465: de rnams lam gyi lta grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6466: rgyud kyi lta grangs rim pa'i don ma nor bar grangs su brjod pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6467: don dam spros pa dang bral ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6468: kun rdzob ye shes sgyu ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6469: de gnyis dbyer med du mthong bzhin rtogs pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:6470: spyod yul dang bral ba rang rig pa'i mngon sum
NK077(tsu)001:6471: du byas pa dang bzhi yis rim pas rtogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6472: go rim 'di ltar shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:6476: mngon sum par rtogs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6477: 'di la go rim tshogs lam rnal 'byor rnam pa bzhi'i lam dang sbyar nas bshad dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:6478: don dam bden pa stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:6479: kun rdzob bden pa snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:6480: dbyer med bden pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:6481: spyod yul bral ba phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6482: de'i don rnam thar sgo bzhi yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6483: rnam thar sgo bzhi gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6484: chos thams cad rgyus stong pas stong pa nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6485: dngos po stong pas mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6486: 'bras bu stong pas smon pa med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6487: rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6488: sbyor lam bar chad med pa ste bsnyen bsgrub bzhi la sbyor ba'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6489: lam gong gi de rnams re re la yang rnam
NK077(tsu)001:6490: grangs su phye nas nyams su myong lugs bshad na
NK077(tsu)001:6495: mthar phyin pa'i nyams dang lnga lnga'i rim par gong du 'phel zhing 'bar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6496: lam kun gyi lta grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6498: chos nyid bden pa dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:6499: ngang la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa thob pas chos
NK077(tsu)001:6500: nyid kyi bden pa dbyer med gyi don rang rig
NK077(tsu)001:6501: pa'i mngon gsum du sgro 'dogs dang bral bar gnas
NK077(tsu)001:6502: pas yid ches nges pa'i gdeng rnyed pa'i shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:6503: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba dang gcig /rnam pa kun
NK077(tsu)001:6504: ldan stong pa chen po mthong ba'i ngang la gnas
NK077(tsu)001:6505: pa de bzhin nyid dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6506: yul yul can gnyis su med pa'i rang rig pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6507: snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:6508: kyis ye shes sgyu mar gzigs pa kun snang snying
NK077(tsu)001:6509: rje chen po'i lta ba dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:6510: 'di la 'bras bu'i 'dug sa bsgyur nas bshad dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:6511: 'bras bu dbyer med yi dam lha'i sku gcig snang
NK077(tsu)001:6512: stong gnyis med du gsal bar lta ba phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:6513: gcig pa'i lta ba dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:6514: rtog tshogs thams cad lha du ma'i dal du gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:6515: med du gsal bar rtogs pa phyag rgya spros pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6517: sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam du yo byad
NK077(tsu)001:6518: lnga snang la rang bzhin med par spyod pas bsod
NK077(tsu)001:6519: nams ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs par mthong
NK077(tsu)001:6520: ba sbyor lam tshogs bsgrub kyi lta ba dang drug
NK077(tsu)001:6521: /rig pa la rang dbang bsgyur zhing zag med mngon
NK077(tsu)001:6522: gsum du mthong ba mthong lam rnam smin tshe dbang
NK077(tsu)001:6524: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don la blo mi
NK077(tsu)001:6525: g.yo ba sgom pa la phyag rgya chen po'i lta
NK077(tsu)001:6526: ba dang brgyad / mnyam par bzhag pa'i ngang la
NK077(tsu)001:6527: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kun yul med du
NK077(tsu)001:6529: mthar lam lhun grub gyi lta ba dang dagu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6530: lam gyi lta grangs dgu 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:6531: gzhi yin tshul gyi lta ba gcig pu bshad pas
NK077(tsu)001:6532: mi chog /blo rim gyis pa'i mnyam bzhag la chod
NK077(tsu)001:6533: tshul dang / rjes shes kyi dri ma dag lugs /
NK077(tsu)001:6534: rnam shes tshogs brgyad dag ma dag gi sa mtshams /
NK077(tsu)001:6535: mtshan nyid kyi lam lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6536: gsang sngags kyi lam lnga sgra mthun te /
NK077(tsu)001:6538: 'di rnams kyi gsang rig dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:6539: deng sang snyigs ma'i nyan bshad phal cher /
NK077(tsu)001:6540: don gsang 'di lta bu mi dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:6541: don spyi'i 'bru gnon pa tsam yang /
NK077(tsu)001:6542: mi shes pa mang du mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:6543: rgyu dang gdams pa bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6545: dang po lta ba de rnams rgyu gang las byung zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6546: thos pa dang bsam pa'i so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab las /
NK077(tsu)001:6547: gzhi shes kyi lta ba byung /
NK077(tsu)001:6548: de la sgom byung gi shes rab byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6549: sgom byung gi thog mar mchog gi ting nge 'dzin rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6550: sbyor lam rim par bsgoms pa'i rgyu las mthong lam /
NK077(tsu)001:6552: de las mthar lam gyi lta ba skyes pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6553: de lta bas bsam na shes rab gsum gyi rgyu las lta ba skyes pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:6554: lta ba rtogs shing rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:6555: de'i rgyu thos bsam sgom gsum gyi shes rab gsum la 'bod /
NK077(tsu)001:6556: ces pa brtson 'grus gyis zhig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6557: rgyu don gyi lta ba bstan pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6560: dang por nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6561: yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po rgyud don
NK077(tsu)001:6562: dgu po lta ba'i gzungs gyi zin pa'i ngos nas
NK077(tsu)001:6563: lta grangs dgu bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6564: rgyas par bshad pa la dgu /
NK077(tsu)001:6566: mi 'da' ba dam tshig gi lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6570: yan lag gi dam tshig ces bya ba bshad pa de yang /
NK077(tsu)001:6571: gud na yod pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6572: khyad par du lam pa rang gi chos nyid lta ba'i ngang la mi 'da' ba dam tshig yin /
NK077(tsu)001:6573: de ci'i phyir na sgo gsum bsgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6574: bsrung ba'i dam tshig gi las mi 'da' bas sdom pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6575: de la yan lag dang du blang pa lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6578: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi sdom pa gsum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6579: yang na bcu gsum 'di la sum bcu'i bshad pa byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:6581: yan lag gi nyer lnga ste sum bcu'i bshad pa yang yod /
NK077(tsu)001:6582: thun mong spyi'i dam tshig mtha' yas pa yod kyang
NK077(tsu)001:6583: chos nyid thig le chen po rtogs pa'i ngang du
NK077(tsu)001:6584: thams cad 'dus shing dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang
NK077(tsu)001:6585: du gsal / spyod lam rnams de las ma g.yos
NK077(tsu)001:6586: na ji ltar spyad kyang dam tshig sdom pa las
NK077(tsu)001:6587: mi 'da' bas dam tshig mchog yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6588: blang dor med pa spyod pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6590: lam pa kun gyi sgo gsum gyi bya bar gyur
NK077(tsu)001:6591: pa'i spyod pa bdag don gzhan don rnam pa gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:6592: pa'i bye brag ji snyed pa yang chos nyid thams
NK077(tsu)001:6593: cad thig le chen po dbyer med pa'i ngang du
NK077(tsu)001:6594: nges par rtogs pas spyod bya spyod byed phyogs gcig
NK077(tsu)001:6595: pa ci la yang blo mi gnas par bdag gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:6596: gyi don kun la ma 'gags par spyod cing de
NK077(tsu)001:6597: ka'i dus na / spyod par byed pa'i mkhan po
NK077(tsu)001:6598: dang spyod par bya ba'i yul gnyis med par thams
NK077(tsu)001:6599: cad rig pa rang snang du mthong ba ni spyod
NK077(tsu)001:6601: rol pa phrin las kyi lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6603: bya byed med pa'i tshul gyis su las rnams kun la thogs pa med par spyad pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6604: lam pa'i zhi rgyas dbang drag gi phrin las bzhi'i
NK077(tsu)001:6605: las dang gcig po la kun tshang bas lhun gyis
NK077(tsu)001:6606: grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga yang sems nyid spros
NK077(tsu)001:6607: bral thig le chen po gnyis su med pa'i ngang
NK077(tsu)001:6608: du gsal bar rtogs pa'i steng nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6609: las kun byed pa ni phrin las kyi lta ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6610: gnas su stob pa mchod pa'i lta ba /
NK077(tsu)001:6612: mchod pa'i yo byad bla re dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6613: la sogs kyi rgyan rin po che dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6614: dar zab la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6615: phyi nang gsang ba'i longs spyod 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:6616: lnga'i dngos po ma lus pa kun kyang phyi rol
NK077(tsu)001:6617: gyi snang ba rang kha min te /
NK077(tsu)001:6618: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems chen po'i cho
NK077(tsu)001:6619: 'phrul chen por snang ba'i ngang du 'dus par rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:6620: pa'i phyir / mchod pa phul ba med pa gnas su stobs /
NK077(tsu)001:6621: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad mnyes pa ste mchod pa'i lta ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6622: bkod pa dal gyi lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6624: zhi ba'i lha bzhugs pa'i rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6625: brten pa lha'i dal zhe gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6626: 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:6627: la sogs pa pho nya'i 'du 'phro mang po yang
NK077(tsu)001:6628: log na yod pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6629: rang rig pa byang chub sems kyi cho 'phrul chen po de nyid de ltar du shar ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:6630: gata na tshigs de lta bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:6632: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6633: ting nge 'dzin lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6634: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:6635: de ltar dal rnam pa bdun po thams cad kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:6636: rang rig pa'i ngang du gcig pa rtog pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6637: dal gyi lta ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6638: rim pa dbang gis lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6640: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams ma lus pa thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:6641: rang bzhin nam ngang gis sems nyid gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:6642: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang la /
NK077(tsu)001:6646: zab mo'i dbang gsum dang lnga po ma brtsal bar
NK077(tsu)001:6647: rang gi sems la lhun gyis grub par rdzogs te
NK077(tsu)001:6648: / de ltar dbang bco brgyad kyang rang rig pa
NK077(tsu)001:6649: byang chub kyi sems kyi cho 'phrul du rang snang
NK077(tsu)001:6651: dbang gi lta ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6652: don du gnyer ba bsgrub pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6654: 'bras bu rang la yod pa ngo mtshar zhing ngam pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6656: rgyu rkyen gyis ma bsgyub par rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i grub pa chen po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6657: grub pa chen po rang gang yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:6658: grub pa chen po rang byung gi ye shes sems
NK077(tsu)001:6659: kyi gnas lugs thams cad kyi blar gyur pas che
NK077(tsu)001:6660: zhes bya'o // don du gnyer ba'i bsgrub pas 'bras bu mchog thun mong gnyis kyi rnam grangs kun /
NK077(tsu)001:6661: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems chen po yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6662: de ltar yin pa la yin pa ltar rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6663: bsgrub pa'i lta ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6664: nyams su len pa ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6666: ting nge 'dzin gyi lta ba'i ngang la gnas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6667: bye brag tu mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:6668: 'dzin kun rang rig pa nyid snang ba yin pas
NK077(tsu)001:6669: phyir chu chu bur lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6670: mtshan med nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin bas /
NK077(tsu)001:6671: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid las gzhan du brtsal zhing sgoms pa yin par rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6673: 'ching grol med par sngags dang phyag rgya'i lta ba bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6675: sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhir snang ba rnams sems nyid rang rig pa nyid snang ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:6676: sngags ni brag cha ltar grags stong dbyer med dang
NK077(tsu)001:6677: phyag rgya ni chu zla dang 'dra bar snang la
NK077(tsu)001:6678: ma grub par lta ba shes pa'i dus de nyid
NK077(tsu)001:6679: na / phyag rgya bcings ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6680: sngags brjod pa'i las nyid gang ltar snang yang mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6681: de bas na 'ching brjod kyi bya byed thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:6682: rang kha ma med par mnyam pa nyid du rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:6683: pa ni / sngags phyag rgya'i lta ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6684: lta ba kun 'dir smos pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6686: de bas lta ba'i rnam grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6687: lta ba'i ngo bo zhes bya ba lam gyi gtso ru brjod med kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:6688: nges pa'i don du shes rab kyi chos kun mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:6689: pa nyid du rtogs pa la lta ba zhes bya
NK077(tsu)001:6690: ba de ni / dper na tshong pa ded dpon
NK077(tsu)001:6691: gyi rgya mtsho'i phar kha nas nor bu rin po
NK077(tsu)001:6692: che len pa'i thabs la mkhas dgos pa'i 'du shes
NK077(tsu)001:6693: chu tshur kha nas shes dgos pa ji lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:6694: ba de ni / bzhin du / gdod ma rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:6695: shes pa'i lta ba nas mtha' ma 'bras bu ma
NK077(tsu)001:6696: thob pa'i bar gyi lam gyi lta grangs dgu la
NK077(tsu)001:6697: sogs pa bye brag nang tshan mi 'dra ba thams
NK077(tsu)001:6698: cad lta ba'i skabs 'dir phyin ci ma log par
NK077(tsu)001:6700: dgu pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6703: dang po mdor bstan ni thos bsam sgoms gsum shes
NK077(tsu)001:6704: rab kyis lta ba rtogs pas de' don du gnyer
NK077(tsu)001:6705: zhing byang chub par byed pa'i tshe bdag gi don
NK077(tsu)001:6706: dang gzhan gyi don gyi phyir sgo gsum spyad par
NK077(tsu)001:6707: bya ba spyod pa'i bye brag rnams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6708: ji ltar zhe na rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6709: bdag don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6715: rgyu shes pa lta ba'i gzhi las spyod pa kun kyang spyod la /
NK077(tsu)001:6716: de yang 'dir thos bsam gyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6720: yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po rgyud don
NK077(tsu)001:6721: bcu la spyod cing don ched du gnyer bar byed
NK077(tsu)001:6722: pa'o // spyod pa'i khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6724: rgyu shes pa lta ba'i spyod pa 'di la yang
NK077(tsu)001:6725: dbang bsgyur gyi spyod pa'i dpe 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:6727: 'dul zhing gi sa khams la chung yod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6728: de bzhin du gzhan don byed pa'i khyad par zag
NK077(tsu)001:6729: med rig 'dzin bzhi'i spyod pa la rgya che chung
NK077(tsu)001:6731: thabs kyis spyod pa'i dpe stobs chen glang chen tsam
NK077(tsu)001:6732: du 'dra yang rtsal che chung dang sgyid rags zhan
NK077(tsu)001:6733: yod pa dang / 'di ni glang chen chur zhugs pa'i tshe na chu la 'dam kha med de /
NK077(tsu)001:6734: thad kha na gcod pa thabs lam 'og sgo'i spyod pa'i dpe /
NK077(tsu)001:6735: de la cung zhig zhol phyogs su spyod pa thabs lam steng sgo'i dpe /
NK077(tsu)001:6736: ngo bo byin rlabs kyi spyod pa'i dpe nam mkha'
NK077(tsu)001:6737: tsam du 'dra yang yul gyi lung pa'i khyon rgya
NK077(tsu)001:6738: che chung gi dbyibs kyi nam mkha' la yang che
NK077(tsu)001:6740: gzhi shes pa lta ba'i spyod par gcig kyang gzhan don rgya che chung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6741: thabs che chung gis nyon mongs pa la spyod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6743: rtogs pa'i lta sgoms kyi gdengs che chung gi stobs kyis spyod pa rnams la khyad par yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6744: spyod pa'i lta ba dang drang /
NK077(tsu)001:6745: chos kun ye nas chos kyi dbyings su ro gcig
NK077(tsu)001:6746: pas chos dbyings de la nga dang bdag tu ma
NK077(tsu)001:6747: rtogs / ngo bo rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag
NK077(tsu)001:6748: cing gnyis su med pa la dkar gsum la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:6749: gtsang ba dang dam rdzas lnga la sogs pa sme
NK077(tsu)001:6750: ba mi gtsang ba'i blo gnyis su 'dzin par ma
NK077(tsu)001:6751: byed cig /ces gdams pa'i tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:6752: chos rnams thams cad ye nas bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6753: snying po yin de bas glo bur rnam dag rkyen
NK077(tsu)001:6754: gyi rdul gyis ga la gos /
NK077(tsu)001:6755: shes rab mchog gi de ltar goms zhing rtogs par gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6757: ma lus kun 'dus pas chos kyi dbyings su shes par byos shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6760: de ltar rtogs pa'i yon tan de bas na rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:6761: shes par bya ba lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs rnam
NK077(tsu)001:6762: par dag pa rags las mi 'da' bas sdom pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6764: bdag gi don dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:6765: spyod pa gtsor byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi
NK077(tsu)001:6766: dang po phog pa'i sdom pa rtsa ba yan lag
NK077(tsu)001:6767: kun kyang slob cing spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6768: bdag don gyi spyod pa 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:6769: lta ba rtogs nas chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas lugs kyi ngang la spyod thabs yin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:6770: rang don la lta ba bogs 'don thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6771: 'ga' zhig lta ba ma rtogs pa rtogs par byed pa'i thabs kyi spyod pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:6772: 'di rnams kyi dmigs ma 'dres par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6773: gzhan don gyi spyod pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:6775: shes rab chen po'i spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6777: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don shes pa'i shes rab chen po'i lta ba rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6778: gang la zhen pa med pas sbyin zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6779: de'i dus su rnam rtog gis mtshan ma dag pas bsregs /
NK077(tsu)001:6780: de lta bu'i sbyin bsreg gi bsregs rdzas srid pa
NK077(tsu)001:6781: gsum gyi mtshan ma bsreg par byed pa'i me ni
NK077(tsu)001:6782: lta ba rtogs pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6783: yin kyi rtogs pa'i rang rig ye shes nyon mongs pa bsregs pa'i me ru 'bar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6784: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas 'gro ba
NK077(tsu)001:6785: kun kyang chos nyid kyi ngang du chos kyi dbyings
NK077(tsu)001:6786: su bsgral ba'o // bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6788: gdod ma mtshogs lam dang po nas sems skyes nas
NK077(tsu)001:6789: mthar 'bras bu ma thob kyi bar du lam don
NK077(tsu)001:6790: du gnyer ba spyod pa yin cing spyod pa'i sgo
NK077(tsu)001:6791: nas the tshom gyi spros pa'i mtshan ma gcod cing
NK077(tsu)001:6792: de yang 'bras bu rang la grub par shes nas
NK077(tsu)001:6793: lam bgrod pa dang gzhan don la 'jug pa ni
NK077(tsu)001:6794: / bdag dang gzhan rnams sangs rgyas thob par bya
NK077(tsu)001:6795: ba'i phyir du spyod pa 'di rnams spyod dang snyam
NK077(tsu)001:6797: gtan tshigs de bas bdag nyid kyi don la'ang gzhan don rang shugs kyis yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6798: khyad par gyi spyod pa rang rang gis skabs las shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6800: de ltar gzhan don phun sum tshogs pa theg chen
NK077(tsu)001:6801: gyi lugs yin pas de bas na gzhan don mi
NK077(tsu)001:6802: 'byung bas byis spa nyan rang dang mi mtshungs te
NK077(tsu)001:6803: / lam kun gyi skabs las kyang bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6804: bcu pa phan yon la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:6806: gang rtogs pa'i yon tan mthar 'khor bar mi ltung zhing yon tan tshad las 'das pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6808: rnal 'byor pa gang gis chos nyid kyi don 'di ltar mthong zhing lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6809: thun mong gi dngos grub kyi blar gyur pa mchog gi dngos grub yin /
NK077(tsu)001:6810: de'i rgyu'am snying po lta ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6811: lta ba de rtogs nas dper na chu srin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:6812: phyag rgya ni chu srin gyi gre ba yin te
NK077(tsu)001:6813: / der rin po che chud na phyi rjes nas
NK077(tsu)001:6814: mi gtong ba ji lta ba bzhin du de'i don
NK077(tsu)001:6815: / ni / dang po lta ba'i don mngon gsum
NK077(tsu)001:6816: du rtogs na mthar 'khor bar mi gtong zhing byang
NK077(tsu)001:6817: / ni / chub thob pa'o // gzhan lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:6818: rtogs na spyod lam rnam bzhi thams cad dang yul
NK077(tsu)001:6819: du kun tu lta ba'i ngang la ma yengs par
NK077(tsu)001:6820: khyer bas thams cad chos sku'i ngo bor chod pa
NK077(tsu)001:6821: la yon tan tshad dpag tu med pa'o zhes brjod
NK077(tsu)001:6823: lta ba rtogs nas mar la mi ldog par bshad
NK077(tsu)001:6824: / ni / chub thob pa'o // do // pa dang / phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6825: tshogs lam chen por phyin nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6826: de phyir lam bzhir ldog zag yod byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6827: 'di gnyis 'gal lo zhe na mi 'gal te /
NK077(tsu)001:6828: 'di rnams dgongs pa can yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6829: lta ba rtogs nas dam tshig chags nyams kyi 'gal
NK077(tsu)001:6830: 'khrul ma byas shing lam mthar skyol zhing lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:6831: ji bzhin pa rtogs pa'i blo rab gcig la dgongs
NK077(tsu)001:6832: so // phyag rgya spros pa mthar phyin nas lta
NK077(tsu)001:6833: ba rtogs kyang rjes shes la nyon yid kyi 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:6835: gal te dam tshig chags nyams byung nas zag ldog yod dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:6836: nyon yid rtsa ba nas chad cing /
NK077(tsu)001:6837: gsang sngags kyi lta ba ji bzhin pa rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6839: 'di la zag ldog gnyis ka 'ong mi srid /
NK077(tsu)001:6840: spyir shes bya'i chos lam bsgrod tshul 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:6841: tshogs lam dang po nas sangs rgyas kyi sa'i bar la /
NK077(tsu)001:6842: lam la thang lhod mi shor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6843: ngan song la mi ldog cing /
NK077(tsu)001:6844: lha mi'i skye ba len nas lam gong nas gong du bgrod pa'i rigs kyang yod dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:6845: dbang po rab gcig tshogs lam chos rgyun chen po nas /
NK077(tsu)001:6847: 'bring rtse mo bzod pa gnyis nas phyir mi ldog pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6848: tha mas sa dang po chos nyid bden pa'i don
NK077(tsu)001:6849: rtogs nas phyir mi ldog /yang mtha' gcig pa bdun
NK077(tsu)001:6850: bar nyon yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su
NK077(tsu)001:6851: mngon du gyur ma nus pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6852: nyan rang du ldog pa'i rigs gcig kyang srid do //
NK077(tsu)001:6853: ji ltar spyad kyang rnam smin med cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6855: lta ba rtogs nas kun nas nyon mongs pa'i spyod pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:6856: ji ltar spyad kyang nya mo chu la longs spyod
NK077(tsu)001:6857: pa bzhin du mi bcing ste grol ba yin no
NK077(tsu)001:6858: // thun mong gi lam rgyu'i theg pa che chung gnyis kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6859: yang na rgyu mtshan nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6860: sngags phyi rgyud gnyis la spyod pa'ang grol ba de bzhin yin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:6861: rnam smin dge sdig gnyis kyi mi gos shing //
NK077(tsu)001:6862: med pas spyod pa la ma zhes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:6863: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6864: mtha' gsum bral zhing don gsum rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6866: rnal 'byor pa gang gi don de ltar lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:6867: rtogs par 'gyur ba rtogs par 'gyur ba ni sgro
NK077(tsu)001:6868: btags brgyad dang / bskur btab bcu dang lung ma bstan gyi mtha' gsum las grol te /
NK077(tsu)001:6869: lam du 'jug pa'i dgos pa'i don 'bras bu rnams mngon sum du 'byin cing thob par byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:6870: gtan tshigs de bas na lta ba rtogs nas bdag
NK077(tsu)001:6871: don gzhan don chos kyi don rnams yongs su rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:6872: pa'o // shes rab chen pos 'khor bar mi gtong zhing bde ba dang ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6874: de ltar lta ba rtogs pa'i gang zag de'i blo
NK077(tsu)001:6875: ni rgya che ba sa gzhi lta bu dang zab
NK077(tsu)001:6876: pa rgya mtsho yangs pa bar snang /
NK077(tsu)001:6877: shes rab rno ba ral gri /
NK077(tsu)001:6878: myur ba glog lta bu'i chos nyid zab pa'i don
NK077(tsu)001:6879: mngon gsum du rtogs pas 'khor bar phyir mi ldog
NK077(tsu)001:6880: la dgongs pa bde ba chen po gnas pa de
NK077(tsu)001:6881: la nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa med par blo
NK077(tsu)001:6882: gros yangs pas bde ba'i don dang ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6883: bcu gcig pa drod la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:6885: rnal 'byor pa brtson 'grus dang ldan pas lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:6886: rtogs pa kho na la lhur len par byed na
NK077(tsu)001:6888: rmi lam du chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6889: rin po che'i gling du phyin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6890: me tog dang 'bru'i char 'bab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6891: rin po che'i glegs bam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6892: chos kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa lag tu gtad nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor gcig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6893: dung dang rnga bo che'i sgra la sogs pa stong gsum gang bar bsgrags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6894: nyi zla lag tu thogs te 'jig rten gyi mun pa bsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6895: de la sogs pa rmis na chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:6896: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6897: sngar ma mthong ba'i yul khams chen po mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6898: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten la 'dzegs cing mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6899: ri bo'i rtse nas phyogs thams cad du lta zhing mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6900: nam mkha'i khams kun mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6901: rang las 'od byung nas snang srid thams cad 'od gsal ba la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6902: de lta bu'i mtshan ma rmi lam du mthong zhing 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6903: gzhan yang sgrib pa dag pa'ang 'byung bar gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6904: sgren mor bud nas lus kyi dri ma thams cad dag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6905: chu bo che la rkyal zhing khrus byas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6906: sna khrag dang nang rol la sogs pa thams cad phyir la songs kyi thon pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6907: lus mer bsreg te mi snang bar byas pa la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6908: lus ngag yid gsum rtsa ba'i drod chos nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:6909: don rtogs te rig pa klongs su pheb pa las
NK077(tsu)001:6910: yan lag gi drod yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6912: rtsa ba'i drod nang gi dgongs pa phyogs ris med pa rang bzhin gyi bde ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:6913: de'i yon tan yan lag gis drod ni /
NK077(tsu)001:6914: phyi'i drod lus kyi bzod pa phra mo thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6915: nang drod dbugs dal zhing dbang po gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6916: gsang ba'i drod sems rnal du phebs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6917: de dag kun lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung bar the tshom med do //
NK077(tsu)001:6918: bcu gnyis pa lta ba rtogs pa'i rtags bstan pa la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:6920: lta ba rtogs pa de la mtshan ma rtags 'byung ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6921: shes rab kyi stobs kyis lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang
NK077(tsu)001:6922: la rig pa klong du phebs shing rtogs pa'i don
NK077(tsu)001:6924: skye shi med par rtogs pas gzhan tshe 'pho 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:6925: mthong yang de la 'jigs pa med cing nyams nga
NK077(tsu)001:6927: snang srid chos sku shes pas 'bras bu'i khams la skye ba med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6928: sangs rgyas rang la yod par rtogs pas grub pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:6929: mtha' 'bras bu ste gnas gzhan la smon pa med
NK077(tsu)001:6930: dam / gzhan yang 'dod pa'i longs spyod lngas kyang chos nyid thams cad mnyam nyid la sbyor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:6931: sdug bsngal drag po nyon mongs ci skyes kyang chos
NK077(tsu)001:6932: nyid klong du shes pas bzod pa chen po thob
NK077(tsu)001:6933: ste / gzhan don gyi las rnams gang du'ang khur
NK077(tsu)001:6934: du mi lta bar rang don spyod dus nyon mongs
NK077(tsu)001:6935: pa ci shar yang de dang 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6936: tan tra ste rgyud gzhung nas bshad pa'i lung rnams
NK077(tsu)001:6937: dang rang gi bya spyod rnams 'gal ba med par
NK077(tsu)001:6938: spyod pas / so so skye bo tha mal pa'i spyod pa'i rang kha mar spyod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:6939: shin tu yang lhag par 'gyur te sgo gsum gyis spyod pa rgyun gyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6940: lta ba rtogs pa'i rtags 'dir mdo tsam smos pa yin gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:6941: mtha' dag brjod kyis mi lang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:6942: bcu gsum pa tshad la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:6944: thos bsam gyi lta ba mngon gsum du rtogs shing mthar phyin pa'i tshad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6946: dper na rgya mtsho dwangs ba'i nang du nyi zla
NK077(tsu)001:6947: gza' skar gyi gzugs brnyan 'char ba ltar tshig sgra
NK077(tsu)001:6948: la brten nas don spyi'i rnam pa yid la byed
NK077(tsu)001:6949: pa min par don rang gi mtshan nyid rang rig
NK077(tsu)001:6950: pa'i mngon sum du rtogs pa'i dmigs pa'i yul dang
NK077(tsu)001:6951: bral bar rtogs pa ni sems nyid rang gsal du
NK077(tsu)001:6952: mthong zhing sgro bskur lung ma bstan gsum dang bral
NK077(tsu)001:6955: lta ba'i dngos po gsum dang bral zhing grub mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:6956: gzhan gyi rkyen gyis mi brgul bas nges par blo'i
NK077(tsu)001:6957: gdeng nas rtogs shing gdeng du gang byas pa de
NK077(tsu)001:6959: thos bsam la brten pa'i lta ba mthar phyin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6960: ngo bo yang je gsal du 'gro ba'i rim pa dpe dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6962: 'on kyang thos bsam gyi sgo nas lta ba khong du chud na yang /
NK077(tsu)001:6963: sgoms pa goms pa las lta ba 'phel dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:6964: sa dang po'i rim pa ni 'di lta bu yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:6965: dper na mig gi dbang por rab rib dang bral
NK077(tsu)001:6966: bas dwangs ma'i spyod yul dang gzugs rang mtshan mthong
NK077(tsu)001:6969: drung na shin tu gsal ba bzhin du stobs 'phel
NK077(tsu)001:6970: bas snga mas phyi ma gsal ba'i stobs gang nas
NK077(tsu)001:6971: gong du lam rim pa bzhin du 'phel bas rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:6973: rkyen 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin gnyis kyis gong snga ma snga ma rgyu yin /
NK077(tsu)001:6974: 'og phyi ma phyi ma 'bras bur 'brel pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6975: rtogs pa gsal ba'i bye brag nang tshan mi 'dra
NK077(tsu)001:6976: ba rnams la gong nas gong du rim par je
NK077(tsu)001:6977: gsal je gsal 'gro ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:6978: de yang gang gi rim pa'i cha dbye bas skabs la gsal ba'i ming btags pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:6979: mi brjod pa yin gyi dngos po gcig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:6980: zag bcas bden pa mthong ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:6981: rang mtshan mthong ma mthong gi khyad par /
NK077(tsu)001:6982: mthong na lam gong 'og gi khyad par yod med /
NK077(tsu)001:6983: mthong lam la zag bcas zag med gnyis bshad pa'i khyad par /
NK077(tsu)001:6984: de la sgoms dgos mi dgos kyi rtsod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:6985: lam gong 'og la gsal mi gsal gyi khyad par rnams 'og rang rang gis skabs su 'chad //
NK077(tsu)001:6986: bcu bzhi pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:6988: blo ngan kyis ma rtogs par le lo byas pa'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6990: lta ba gang gi rang gsal gsum bral gyi don
NK077(tsu)001:6991: ltar ma rtogs pa'i gang zag rigs gcig blo ngan
NK077(tsu)001:6992: pas chos thams cad tshig gis mnyam pa'i khung phyung
NK077(tsu)001:6993: nas / don ma rtogs par dman pa las gyur pa'i le lo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6994: snyoms las las gyur pa'i le lo gnyis byas pas
NK077(tsu)001:6995: don thar pa ma grub par slar ngan song du
NK077(tsu)001:6996: 'agro'o // tshig gi lta bas sangs mi rgya bas tshig don ldan par gdams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:6998: des na sems kyi mnyam pa ma rtogs shing kha lta tshig gis mnyam pas sangs mi rgya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:6999: smra khams che yang sa chod chung ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:7000: ci tsam zab kyang blos byas yin /
NK077(tsu)001:7001: dper na glo tshod bskol ba dang 'dra bas /
NK077(tsu)001:7002: chos de kha nas bshad kyang khung nas med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7003: don ma rtogs na skyon 'dug pa de bas na
NK077(tsu)001:7004: don dang tshig tu 'brel cing ldan par gyis la
NK077(tsu)001:7006: 'on kyang lta ba mngon du ma rtogs na yang /
NK077(tsu)001:7007: theg pa chen po'i chos la mos pa tsam /
NK077(tsu)001:7008: thos pa tsam byas na skye ba 'ga' zhig brgyud nas the tshom med par don 'grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7009: lta ba med na lam kun zag cing 'ching bas lta ba rtogs zhig par gdams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7011: dper na spyan bzang te long ba lam du zhugs
NK077(tsu)001:7012: kyang 'gro sar mi phyin pa ji lta ba bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:7013: gyi phyir / don lta ba med na /
NK077(tsu)001:7014: lam kun 'khor bar zag cing rgyud 'ching bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:7015: bdag gzhan gyi 'bras bu thob pa'i don du mi
NK077(tsu)001:7016: 'gyur ba'i phyir na lam ngan song du brlag par
NK077(tsu)001:7018: lta ba med na skyon yod pa de bas lta
NK077(tsu)001:7019: ba rtogs pa'i don de la brtson zhing 'grus par
NK077(tsu)001:7020: gyis gcig pa'o // 'jug rtogs nas 'dris par gyis zhig par gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7022: gong du bstan pa de ltar lta ba ji bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:7023: pa rtogs pa'i don mthong ba'i gang zag 'ga' zhig
NK077(tsu)001:7024: gis gzhan du ci la yang mi bsams te /
NK077(tsu)001:7026: de bas rtogs pa lta ba'i don de yang nas yang du 'dris par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7027: skyes bu dam pa rnam mkhyen rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:7028: mchog thob par 'dod pas lta ba de la dus
NK077(tsu)001:7029: rtag tu brtson 'grus kyi lta ba'i ngo bo gsal
NK077(tsu)001:7030: ba mthar phyin par gyis zhig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7031: dper na lam shes nas lam du ma nor bar 'jug pa bzhin yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:7032: 'og nas ston pa'i 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin rnams
NK077(tsu)001:7033: dang rgyu snga ma lta ba rtogs pa sngon du
NK077(tsu)001:7034: song nas / rkyen 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin rnams 'bras bu'i tshul du 'phel lo //
NK077(tsu)001:7036: de ltar don mthong gang zag gis //
NK077(tsu)001:7038: gong du don bcu gzhir bstan pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:7040: de yang 'brel pa cung zad brtsi na /
NK077(tsu)001:7041: lta ba rtogs par 'dod pa la dgos ched med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:7043: gzhan sel ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7044: don du gnyer ba'i dgos ched du bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7045: de ltar dgos pa dang ldan pa'i lta ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:7046: bstan pa'i snod med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:7048: rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa dang sbyangs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:7049: snod du gyur pa gnyis la rang bzhin gyi snod
NK077(tsu)001:7050: du gyur pa la rim gcig char gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7051: sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa la yang rim gcig char gnyis ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:7052: de ltar snod ldan des lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i dus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7053: re smon sems kyis nyen pa la brtson 'grus kyis
NK077(tsu)001:7054: sbyor ba'i dus su lta ba rtogs par bstan no
NK077(tsu)001:7055: // dus de na snod ldan des lta ba rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:7056: par byed pa'i rgyu rkyen gang yin zhe na rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:7057: gnyis rkyen bzhi ru bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7058: de ltar rgyu rkyen de dang ldan pas lta ba rtogs par byed pa'i thabs la /
NK077(tsu)001:7059: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab nas don gyi dmigs bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7060: gol sgrib kyi gdar sha bcad nas don gyi dmigs bzung /
NK077(tsu)001:7061: rnam grangs rnam par phye nas don gyi dmigs bzung bar bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7062: de ltar thabs kyis gtan la phab pa'i lta ba rang gi ngo bo dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7063: rnam grangs thun mong du bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:7064: de la ngo bo'i rnam grangs la /
NK077(tsu)001:7065: lta ba rang gi ngo bo'i dngos nas rnam grangs su bzhag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7066: lam rim gyis ngos nas rnam grangs su bzhag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7067: rgyud don gyi ngos nas lta ba'i rnam grangs su phye ba rnams su bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7068: lta ba 'di la gnas pa'i dus kyi spyod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:7069: rtogs pa don du gnyer bya bdag don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7070: rtogs pa khong du chud pa gzhan don gyi spyod
NK077(tsu)001:7071: pa gnyis su phye nas gsung lta ba de la
NK077(tsu)001:7072: yon tan ji lta bu yod zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:7073: lta ba rtogs pas mthar mi gtong ba'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7074: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7075: don gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7076: mthar 'khor bar mi gtong ba'i yon tan du phye nas bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7077: rtogs pa de la drod 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7079: yan lag gi drod gnyis su phye nas gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:7080: 'o na lta ba rtogs pa la rtags 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7081: rmi lam gyi mtshan ma rnams bshad pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:7082: lta ba de rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i tshad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7083: thos bsam la brten nas lta ba rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i tshad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7084: ngo bo gcig kyang bgos su 'gro bar bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7085: lta ba de ma rtogs na skyon ji lta bu yod zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:7086: lta ba de ma rtogs ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7087: le lo dang snyoms las byas pa'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7088: tshig gis mnyam pas sangs mi rgya ba'i skyon /
NK077(tsu)001:7089: ma rtogs na lam kun zag cing 'ching ba'i skyon rnams su phye nas gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:7090: de ltar lta ba'i don mthong ba'i rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gis zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7091: 'di ni sh+aaka rdor pas mdzad zer ba'i 'grel ba gcig gi nang nas btus pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7092: don gnad mi che ba snang /
NK077(tsu)001:7097: gzhi gnas lugs don dam kun rdzob dbyer med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:7098: ye shes ye nas rang la gnas pa'i don rang
NK077(tsu)001:7099: rig pas mngon gsum du mthong ba lta ba ston
NK077(tsu)001:7100: par byed pa'i gzhung gi don rnams mtshams dang ris
NK077(tsu)001:7101: su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis
NK077(tsu)001:7103: de'i rnam grangs dgu yod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:7104: yas bgrang gnyis pa'i don du gda' 'o ////da ni
NK077(tsu)001:7105: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa sgom pa'i mtshan nyid ston
NK077(tsu)001:7106: te slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dgongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7107: lam spyi dang bye brag gi don thams cad dril na brgyad yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:7108: nyon mongs pa lam du khyer mi khyer gyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7110: blo che chung gi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7112: rim pa 'dor mi 'dor gyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7114: rang stobs dang gzhan stobs kyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7115: gdams ngag dang shes rab kyi stobs gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7116: dngos yul mos yul gyi dbang gis /
NK077(tsu)001:7117: rdzogs slob dang smin slob gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7118: skye ba len mi len gyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7120: spyod pa dus tshod kyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7122: mya ngan las 'das pa la sbyor tshul gyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7123: lhag ma yod med gnyis dang brgyad kyi sgo nas 'chad dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:7124: de yang dang po thabs lam grol lam gnyis don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7126: thabs dang shes rab lam nyid kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:7127: 'gro 'ong med par bde bar gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7129: gdul bya chags pa can dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7130: blo gros can gyi bsam pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:7131: mos pa tha dad pa'i dbang gis /
NK077(tsu)001:7132: thabs lam grol lam gnyis su bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:7137: rkyang pas lam bgrod tshul lam gyi sngon du gong 'gro rnams brtag cing don blang bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7138: spyir thabs lam la steng sgo 'jug 'dul gyi man
NK077(tsu)001:7139: ngag /rtsa rlung thig le la sbyangs nas rim gyis
NK077(tsu)001:7140: pa'i lam dang / 'og sgo bde ba bcud 'dus shes rab yum la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7141: dga' bzhi bde stong nyams su myong ba gcig char ba'i lam gnyis yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:7142: gzhung 'di nyid kyis kun rdzob gnas tshul gyis skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:7143: thabs lam rang la gnas tshul cung zad tsam ston kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:7144: lam la grol lam gtso cher ston la /
NK077(tsu)001:7146: nyon mongs pa ma spang lam du khyer ba gsang sngags kyi khyad par chos yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7148: longs spyod rig ma'ang ldan par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:7151: sbyor ba'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7152: 'bras bu'i skabs na rol pa'i ka ra bstan pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:7154: mthar phyin lam pa'i dri ma sbyangs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:7155: thabs lam gyi dbang bskur dgos par bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:7156: de yang gsang sngags kyi thabs lam yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:7157: khe nyen che bas gtan la 'bebs shing lam du slong ba shin tu dka' /
NK077(tsu)001:7158: 'di nyams su len pa la lung man ngag nyams myong gsum dang 'brel dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:7160: sgyu 'phrul bshad rgyud sde bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7162: ka ma la sha sh+ra dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7163: rgya gar mkhas grub rnams kyis mdzad pa'i man ngag rnams khong du chud pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7164: snyan brgyud gdam ngag gi gnad ma 'chug cing /
NK077(tsu)001:7165: rang nyid rtsa rlung la dbang thob pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7166: sgyu 'phrul thal ba nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:7167: sgo gsum gnad bdun gyi man ngag la mkhas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7168: de rnams kun 'dzam nas nyams su blang na /
NK077(tsu)001:7169: dus ring por mi thogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:7170: tshe 'di nyid la bde stong gi ye shes shar nas mchog gi dngos grub thob par gsungs /
NK077(tsu)001:7172: gcig char la don gnyis yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:7173: spyi dang bye brag gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:7174: spyir ni rdzus skyes kyis dpe mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7175: rang bzhin gyi rnon pos bden bzhi gcig chod du sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7176: mngal skyes kyi dpes mtshon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7177: sbyangs pa'i rnon pos bden bzhi rim par nyams su len pa gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:7180: srid pa 'khor lo'i tshul bzhin du //
NK077(tsu)001:7181: zhes tshig rkang gsum gyis gsal /
NK077(tsu)001:7182: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni 'og tu ston to //
NK077(tsu)001:7183: bye brag ni rim gyis lam re re la /
NK077(tsu)001:7184: rim dang gcig char gnyis yod pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7187: sgyu ma lam rim gcig char med de /
NK077(tsu)001:7190: lha sgoms pa'i thabs yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:7191: lam de gnyis la lha mi sgoms so zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:7193: blo 'jog thabs myur bul la zer ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7194: 'di gnyis la yang don gyis yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:7195: gdams ngag dang shes rab kyi stobs kyis 'jog pa la sogs pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:7197: de yang gdams ngag shes rab kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:7198: stobs kyis bzhag pas goms par byed //
NK077(tsu)001:7200: zung 'jug phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su lam lha sgoms thabs rim gcig gnyis byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7201: blo yi shes rab che chung gis /
NK077(tsu)001:7202: yang na phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK077(tsu)001:7203: chu la nya ldang ji bzhin du //
NK077(tsu)001:7206: sngon bzhin rim dang gcig char ba //
NK077(tsu)001:7209: zhi khro'i dal gyi lha sgoms pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:7210: rim gcig char gnyis byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7212: gcig nas spros pa'ang rnam gnyis te //
NK077(tsu)001:7215: tshogs bsgrub la rim dang gcig char med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7216: spros bcas su ting nge 'dzin brtan nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7217: tshogs bsgrub tu spyod pas bogs 'dod pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:7219: blo che ba phyag rgya gcig spros nas thod rgal 'byung la /
NK077(tsu)001:7220: blo chung ba mthar chags pa gcig tshogs bsgrub dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:7221: rnam smin rim gcig char med /
NK077(tsu)001:7222: tshogs sbyor gyi ting nge 'dzin las 'di stobs can du gyur yang /
NK077(tsu)001:7223: snang ba shugs bkag gi dri ma med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7224: lus kyi sgrib g.yog dang bcas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7225: snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin khyad par can mi skye ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:7227: sngar gyi bag chags kyi lus yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:7228: rdo rje'i lus su gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7229: sangs rgyas stong gi dal la sogs sgom nus kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:7230: ting nge 'dzin khyad par can rgyud la skye ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:7231: rim gcig char gnyis med do //
NK077(tsu)001:7232: rim pa'i rim pa med tshul gyi //
NK077(tsu)001:7233: stong khri la sogs grangs mang lha'i //
NK077(tsu)001:7237: de nyid brtan par byed pa la sgoms bya gzhan med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7239: shin tu brten pa'i blo gnas pas //
NK077(tsu)001:7240: grangs can 'khor lo mngon du snang //
NK077(tsu)001:7243: mnyam bzhag la rgyal ba nyid dang khyad med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7244: rim dang gcig char gnyis med do //
NK077(tsu)001:7245: bsam yas lhun grub kyi rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:7246: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan mchog 'chang //
NK077(tsu)001:7248: bye brag gi rim gcig char 'di rnams lam nang
NK077(tsu)001:7249: tshan gyis blo che chung yin par shes par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:7250: // gsum pa thod rgal thar chag gi go don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7251: 'og phyag rgya gcig pa thod rgal 'chad pa'i skabs su 'chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:7252: spyi don bzhi pa bla ma'i gdams ngag la rag lus che chung gi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7253: gdams ngag dang shes rab kyi sgo nas 'jog pa rtsol ba che chung gi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7254: rang gi ting nge 'dzin la blo chung ba gdams ngag stobs kyis bzhag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7255: blo che ba shes rab kyis 'jog pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7257: rang stobs kyis ting nge 'dzin ma gsal na /
NK077(tsu)001:7258: sgoms thabs la sogs pa bla ma'i gdams ngag gis khrid nas sgoms pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7260: dang po thos bsam gyis lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:7262: sgoms pa'i tshe gzhan la rag lus pa med par rang gi shes rab kyis sgom nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7263: de yang gdams ngag shes rab kyis stobs kyis 'jog pas goms par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:7266: blo chung ba so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis bzhag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7267: blo che ba lam lnga ma goms pa'i rjes la sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7269: so sor brtags rgyu'am rjes la thob ces so //
NK077(tsu)001:7271: blo chung gdams ngag gis stobs kyis sems sbyangs ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7272: blo che ba shes rab kyi stobs kyis sems sbyangs ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7274: snga ma gdams ngag shes rab kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:7275: 'jug pa'i bzhi po de nyid de //
NK077(tsu)001:7278: lta ba mthong ba'i rjes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7279: lam snga ma goms pa'i rjes la thob pa gnyis don gyi yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:7281: mthong dang snga ma'i rnal 'byor stobs //
NK077(tsu)001:7283: spyi don lnga pa rdzogs slob dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7285: spyir gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs kyi lam slob tshul gnyis yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7287: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa thun re la rdzogs par sgom nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7288: grub mtha' la sbyor ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7290: shes 'jug kun kyang gzhan don du //
NK077(tsu)001:7291: zhes sogs tshig rkang drug gis bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7293: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:7294: mthar phyin par sgoms nas grub mtha' la sbyor ba
NK077(tsu)001:7295: yin te / snga ma snga ma gang dang gang //
NK077(tsu)001:7297: sngon du stong gam rnal 'byor pas //
NK077(tsu)001:7298: zhes sogs tshig rkang bzhis bstan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7299: spyi don drug pa zag pa yod med kyi don la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7300: zag pa spyi'i go ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7302: yod med kyis mtshams rnams shes dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:7303: 'og phyag rgya spros pa zag ldog yod med kyi skabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7304: le'u brgyad pa tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyi skabs la sogs pa rnams su 'chad /
NK077(tsu)001:7305: spyi don bdun pa ldog pa yod med ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7306: spyod pa dus tshod kyi sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7307: spyod pa'i dus ma yin par /
NK077(tsu)001:7308: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa spyad na /
NK077(tsu)001:7309: ngan song du ldog cing zag pa yang yod la /
NK077(tsu)001:7310: ldog pa'ang yod la spros bcas man chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:7311: spyod pa'i dus tshod la bab pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7312: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa spyad kyang slar tshogs rdzogs /
NK077(tsu)001:7313: ngan song du mi ltung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:7314: zag pa yod kyang ldog pa med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7318: ngan song gsum du skye bar 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:7319: de yi sdug bsngal bzod glags med //
NK077(tsu)001:7320: de phyir lam bzhir ldog zag yod //
NK077(tsu)001:7323: bsod nams ye shes dpung tshogs kyi //
NK077(tsu)001:7324: zhes sogs tshig rkang gsum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7326: zag ldog yod pa'ang gnyis yod de //
NK077(tsu)001:7327: mthu yi ngan 'gror ldog mi ldog /sngon gyi shes 'jug brgyad la yod //
NK077(tsu)001:7329: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam pa ni mthong lam yan chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:7330: zag kun zad pa'i rigs can 'di //
NK077(tsu)001:7331: ji ltar spyod kyang ldog pa med ces so //
NK077(tsu)001:7332: des na zag pa dang ldog pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7333: ngo bo gcig la khyab che chung gi tshul tha dad par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7334: spyi don brgyad pa lhag bcas lhag med ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7335: 'bras bu la sbyor tshul gyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7336: lhag ma yod med du bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7337: de yang zag bcas tshogs sbyor gyi lus rgyun 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:7338: ma bor bar ye shes kyi sku ru 'gro ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7339: lhag bcas su 'da' ba tshe dbang yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:7340: 'di dor nas rig pa rkyang pa ye shes kyi sku ru 'gro ba /
NK077(tsu)001:7341: lhag med du 'da' ba rnam smin no //
NK077(tsu)001:7342: de yang lhag ma med dang yod pa yis //
NK077(tsu)001:7343: mya ngan 'das par mthar sbyor ba //
NK077(tsu)001:7344: thun mong lta bur zung du 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:7346: zhib tu le'u brgyad pa'i skabs su 'chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:7347: spyi don gnyis pa la rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7349: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7351: de yang le'u gnyis par 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK077(tsu)001:7352: cad rang rig pa'i mngon gsum du bdag nyid chen
NK077(tsu)001:7353: por lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang de la gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:7354: med par rtogs pas mos zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7355: lta ba rtogs pa de'i rjes su rkyen ting nge 'dzin goms par byed lugs bshad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7357: don rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7359: lam gyi dmigs rgyas par ro //
NK077(tsu)001:7360: spyir lam gong 'og gi 'brel pa yod lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7361: lam snga ma snga ma gang dang gang yin pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7362: lam phyi ma phyi ma thob pa'i thabs dang rgyu yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:7363: de bzhin du lam phyi ma phyi ma gang yin pa de ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7364: lam snga ma snga ma las byung ba'i 'bras bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7365: de yang lam 'di rim gyis pa'i dbang du bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:7368: de bzhin nyid goms shing rtogs pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:7369: snying rje rang shugs kyis skye bas de bzhin nyid ni rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:7371: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor 'di ngo bo la gnas pa gtsor mi ston cing /
NK077(tsu)001:7372: 'gyu ba yid kyi shes pa'i thog na chod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:7373: cir yang snang du rung ba rgyu yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7375: phyag rgya gcig pa ni rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:7377: 'di nyid las du ma gcig gi gsal byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7379: snang byed sems las su rung ba ni rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:7380: rkyen drag po dang bsre ba tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa ni 'bras bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7381: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:7382: tshe rnam gnyis thob pa 'bras bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7389: de bzhin du lam snga ma thams cad phyi ma thob par byed pa'i thabs sam rgyu yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:7390: phyi ma thams cad de'i 'bras bu'am thabs las byung ba yin par shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7391: lam gyi mig rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7395: gong du bstan pa de ltar lam snga phyi la
NK077(tsu)001:7396: rgyu dang 'brus bu'i thabs dang thabs las byung ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:7398: dper na srid pa 'khor ba'i skye gnas kyi 'khor lo la bardzusa skyes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7399: mngal skyes la myur bul yod pa'i tshul bzhin du shes rab dbang po che chung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7400: don du gnyer ba'i brtson 'grus bzang ngan gyis rnam par dbye ba gcig char ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7401: rim gyis pa'i lugs gnyis su bstan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7406: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7407: gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7408: dang po gcig char ba la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7410: gdod ma nyid nas rdzogs tshul du sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7412: gcig char ba srid pa rdzogs par smin pa de bardzusa skyes kyi tshul du lam bsgrod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7413: rim gyis ba'i lta ba bas lhag par rtogs shing gdeng dang ldan pa'i skyes bu yis /
NK077(tsu)001:7414: de ting don dam bden pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7415: kun ting kun rdzob bden pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7416: phyag rgya gcig pa dbyer med /
NK077(tsu)001:7417: spros bcas spyod yul dang bral ba'i sgom pa rnam
NK077(tsu)001:7418: bzhi ni zung dang ldan par dus gcig la rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:7419: pa yin te lta ba bden gsum dbyer med gcig
NK077(tsu)001:7420: chod du rtogs nas sgoms pa dbyer med gcig chod
NK077(tsu)001:7422: mi dgos te de nyid gzhi gdod ma nyid nas goms par byed pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:7423: de nyid don la ji ltar rdzogs tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7425: rang rig ye shes mtha' dbus med pa'i thig le
NK077(tsu)001:7426: chen po'i rang bzhin la sgom pa rnam gsum rnam
NK077(tsu)001:7428: thig le chen po de ni spros bral mtha' dbus med pas de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7429: de'i ngang la ma 'gags pa cir yang snang bas de ni kun tu snang gi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7430: de nyid chu dang chu'i brlab bzhin dbyer med cing
NK077(tsu)001:7431: ye shes chen po'i dkyil 'khor du rang gsal bas
NK077(tsu)001:7432: de ni rgyu'i rim par ldan par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7433: rdzogs pa'i don la gnas pa'i tshul la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7435: tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs pas lta sgom dbyer med gcig chod du gnas tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7437: rtogs pa 'di nyid kyi ngo bo tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7438: de yang blo chung ba la bye brag so sor ngo sprod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7439: blo che ba la mnyam nyid rang grol du ngo sprad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7441: sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:7442: yid so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:7443: nyon yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:7445: rnal ma don gyi kun gzhi chos dbyings ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:7446: ma dag kun gazhi'am sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi me long lta bu'i ye shes su rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7447: blo che ba'i don gyi ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7448: tshogs brgyad rang snang yul med rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7449: ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gsal ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7450: tshogs brgyad ma bsgrib rang gsal du rtogs pa'i me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:7451: yul dang yul can med par rang grol du rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:7452: pa stong pa nyid kyi ye shes de nyid gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:7453: su med cing phyogs med rang gsal du rtogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:7454: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:7455: ma 'dres cir yang gsal ba so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:7456: de la blang dor dang re dogs med de rtsol
NK077(tsu)001:7457: med lhun grub tu rtogs pa bya ba grub pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:7458: ye shes so // de ltar tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga'i ngo bor rtogs pa'i lta ba de la /
NK077(tsu)001:7459: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin rig pa la rang dbang
NK077(tsu)001:7460: bsgyur nas sgom pas ngo bo tshogs brgyad ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:7461: lnga yi ngo bo ru yul med du gsal ba
NK077(tsu)001:7462: nyid dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa rnam par
NK077(tsu)001:7463: mi rtog pa'i thugs kyi ye shes lnga'i ngo bor
NK077(tsu)001:7464: lhun gyis grub pa la mi 'da' bas phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:7466: mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7468: mnyam pa'i dam tshig las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7470: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la de ltar du rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:7471: te mnyam par sbyor ba'i 'bras bu mnyam pa'i dam
NK077(tsu)001:7472: tshig la gnas na 'bras bu mnyam rdzogs chen por
NK077(tsu)001:7473: mngon gsum du 'grub par 'gyur bas mnyam pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:7474: las 'das na sangs rgyas thob pa ma yin no
NK077(tsu)001:7475: // ji ltar spyod kyang dam tshig la gnas shing tshogs gnyis rdzogs par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7477: gong gi mnyam pa nyid kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:7478: dam tshig de la dgar bas na yang na dam
NK077(tsu)001:7479: tshig 'di lta bu chos kun mnyam pa nyid las
NK077(tsu)001:7480: ma g.yos shing de nyid rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7481: ji ltar spyad kyang sdom mi 'da' /
NK077(tsu)001:7482: de'i dus su lus ngag yid gsum gyis bya spyod thams cad ma 'gags pa bsod nams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7483: ma dmigs pa ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis su gyur pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:7484: spyod pas sangs rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7486: spyod lam mnyam pa nyid las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7488: rnal 'byor pa de 'gro chag gi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7490: nyal zhing gnyid la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7491: za zhing longs spyod pa'i dus na ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7492: spyod lam rnam bzhir bden pa chos nyid kyi ting
NK077(tsu)001:7493: nge 'dzin las mnyam par mnyam pa nyid de'i dbyings
NK077(tsu)001:7494: su gnas / de gang gis spyod cing nyams su blang na /
NK077(tsu)001:7495: lta ba gcig chod du rtogs pa'i shes rab mchog
NK077(tsu)001:7496: gi spyod bya spyod byed med par rtag tu spyod
NK077(tsu)001:7497: pa'o // lta spyod dang ldan pas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7499: de ltar rang byung gi ye shes kyis dbyings nyid
NK077(tsu)001:7500: la ni rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi dbyings nyid spyod
NK077(tsu)001:7501: pa'i phyir chos kyi dbyings nyid la shes rab mchog
NK077(tsu)001:7502: gi gnas lugs don la spyod pas de nyid mi
NK077(tsu)001:7503: gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das te sangs rgyas pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:7504: // gcig char ba'i rim gyis pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7506: rtogs pa lta ba'i yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7508: lta ba rtogs pa'i rang byung gi ye shes yid
NK077(tsu)001:7509: bzhin gyi nor bu ltar zad mi shes pa'i gter
NK077(tsu)001:7510: mdzod chen po las byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7511: thams cad la yang des me long bzhin du bltas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:7512: sems nyid rang snang gi 'bras bu ma gtogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:7513: yon tan gyi gzugs snang gzhan nas mi snang ngo
NK077(tsu)001:7514: // rtogs pa'i don la gzhag thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7515: rtogs pa'i don la sgom thabs dang skyon bcos thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:7518: rtogs pa'i don la bzhag pas 'bras bu thob tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7520: rang gi shes rgyu ci yin gang gis ngo shes
NK077(tsu)001:7521: shing rtogs pa'i sgom bya sgom byed las 'phags zhing
NK077(tsu)001:7522: rtsol med kyi brdar 'dug /byed pa de lta bu'i
NK077(tsu)001:7523: gang zag gang gi blo la nyams su len shing
NK077(tsu)001:7524: spyod pa ni 'bras bu byang chub thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7525: dgongs pa'i ngo bo dang drang /
NK077(tsu)001:7526: rang byung ye shes kyis sel med par rtogs pas rnam par dag pa'i lta ba /
NK077(tsu)001:7527: 'gyur ba med pas g.yung drung ltar ye nas sangs
NK077(tsu)001:7528: rgyas pa'i ngo bo la thams cad ye nas mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:7529: par gnas pas bsgom bya sgom byed med par rnam
NK077(tsu)001:7530: par dag cing yul yul can du mi rtog pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:7531: ngang la sa ler gnas pa la rtogs par mdzad
NK077(tsu)001:7532: do // gang zag phyogs rer 'dzin can 'ga' zhig gis /
NK077(tsu)001:7533: chos spong gis las bsags nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7535: rnam par dag pa'i g.yung drung sangs rgyas la /
NK077(tsu)001:7537: g.yung drung zer ba snang bas /
NK077(tsu)001:7538: rnying ma bon yin pa skad /
NK077(tsu)001:7539: 'o na g.yung drung gar smos pa bon yin na /
NK077(tsu)001:7542: g.yung drung zhi ba rtag brtan nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:7544: mkhan po b+ho d+hi sa t+was gsung pa'i sman chog yang /
NK077(tsu)001:7550: g.yung drung 'khyil pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK077(tsu)001:7551: dge ba'i 'khor lo la sogs bskor //
NK077(tsu)001:7553: si d+hu ra'i g.yung drung ris dgos cing 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:7554: de la sogs pa bka' bstan bcos kyi nang na g.yung drung gi ming smos pa mang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:7555: 'o na g.yung drung rang ci yin zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:7556: 'di la dpe dang don gnyis la /
NK077(tsu)001:7557: don 'gyur med kyi gnas lugs mtshon pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:7558: g.yung drung gi brda' chad byed pa yang yod /
NK077(tsu)001:7559: dpe ri rab kyi khong seng na /
NK077(tsu)001:7560: rdzas g.yung drung bya ba mi 'gyur ba gcig yod par /
NK077(tsu)001:7561: chos rje gtsang ston gyi gsang snying 'grel par bkod 'dug /bon pos g.yung drung zer ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7563: nam mkha' la g.yung drung zhes 'dogs pa byung /
NK077(tsu)001:7564: de phyir nam mkha'i dpe gar ston dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7565: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa gar mtshon pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:7566: g.yung drung gis ming smos pa 'dra //
NK077(tsu)001:7569: de ltar sgom pas yon tan 'byung tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7570: ngo bo phyogs gcig tu bsnyad du med pa las nyams yon tan sna tshogs 'byung ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:7571: nyams rtogs 'byung ba'i dus de nyid na /
NK077(tsu)001:7573: rig pa nang du yod pa lta bu'am nga dang
NK077(tsu)001:7574: bdag tu rtog pa med la rang byung ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:7575: las ma g.yos pas bdag nyid chen po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7576: de'i yon tan thams cad 'byung bas mi zad pa'i gter mdzod chen po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7579: rnam rtog ye shes yin pas gnyen po mi bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7581: tshogs drug ma bkag pa la sna tshogs rnam rtog
NK077(tsu)001:7582: rgyu zhing ngo bo sems las gzhan du 'byung ba
NK077(tsu)001:7584: rnam rtog skyes pa'i dus nyid na rang byung ye shes rang bzhin ngang gis gsal ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7585: rnam gsum ni rnam rtog ye shes rang grol /
NK077(tsu)001:7586: sgom gyi ngo bo gsum du snang zhing ngo bo
NK077(tsu)001:7587: rnam pa mchog ldan gyi stong nyid las snang ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:7588: phyir / rnam rtog ngang gi mi skye ba de nyid ye shes yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:7589: gzhan ye shes brjod du med de rnam rtog dang ye shes gnyis med rang grol du rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7590: blo thams cad 'dzin rtsol med par rang byung rang zhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7592: chos rnams thams cad sems kyi ngang yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7593: sems dngos po med cing 'dus ma byas yin pas
NK077(tsu)001:7594: sems zhes phyogs gcig tu ming gdags su med do
NK077(tsu)001:7595: // sems nyid 'di la ma bcos ma bslad par /
NK077(tsu)001:7596: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa lhun grub tu gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:7597: la 'bras bu ye nas byang chub snying po yin
NK077(tsu)001:7598: cing de las 'bras bu gzhan nas thob rgyu med
NK077(tsu)001:7599: pa ye nas bde bar gshegs kyi rang bzhin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:7600: yin no // dper na nam mkhar phyogs su bzung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:7601: sgrib byed kyi sprin gyis kheb par 'gyur ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:7602: nam mkha' la phyogs bzung du med par mkhas pa
NK077(tsu)001:7603: dag gi shes pa ni nam mkha' las gzhan pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:7604: sprin zhig byung zhing kheb par mi srid pa bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:7605: du sgom pa'i sems kyang sgom phyogs 'dzin can byas
NK077(tsu)001:7606: na skyon de dag 'byung bar 'gyur gyi sgom la
NK077(tsu)001:7608: thams cad rang byung ye shes su shes pas skyon de dag 'byung bar mi 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:7609: don de ltar blta bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7610: bcos bslad med par bzhag pas 'bras bu rang byung tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:7612: rtogs pa'i don ma bcos lhun gnas ji bzhin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:7613: ngang la bzhag pa dang 'bras bu rgyu 'bras dbyer
NK077(tsu)001:7614: med lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor rang las 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:7615: ba'o // ji bzhin mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:7617: chos nyid de bzhin nyid la gnas bcas shing sgom
NK077(tsu)001:7618: na yon tan nyon mongs pa dang sdug bsngal mi
NK077(tsu)001:7619: 'byung ste 'bras bu rtag tu chos nyid bde ba
NK077(tsu)001:7620: chen po'i ngang la gnas shing bla na med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:7621: byang chub bdag don chos sku thob cing /
NK077(tsu)001:7622: gzhan don longs sku dang sprul sku mtshan dang dpe byad kun dang ldan pa thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7623: spyir rim gcig char 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:7624: theg pa la 'jug pa'i rim gcig char dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7625: theg pa de nyid kyi sgo nas 'bras bu thob pa la rim gcig char dang gnyis yod /
NK077(tsu)001:7626: dang po ni le'u gnyis pa dus snod kyi skabs na bshad pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:7627: ma h+aa yo ga rang rtogs pa'i rten gyi gang zag yin /
NK077(tsu)001:7629: 'di nyid nas bshad pa'i rim gcig char nang chen bzhi yod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:7630: gcig char ba'i gcig char ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7631: rtogs grol thar pa dus mnyam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7632: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das //
NK077(tsu)001:7634: gcig char ba'i rim pa rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7635: sgoms pa'i ngang la gnyug bsring dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:7636: bya byed lhas 'phags kyi rdar 'dug byed pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7638: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7639: tshogs lam stong pa'i rnal 'byor nas bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7640: mthar phyin sangs rgyas kyi sa'i bar la mthar chags su bgrod pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7643: rim gyis pa'i cig char ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7644: zag bcas med kyi thod rgal ba rnams yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7646: rnam smin rig la the tshom med //
NK077(tsu)001:7649: snyoms las med par brtson byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7652: rgya dor gcig char mthar 'gro ba //
NK077(tsu)001:7662: dper na srid pa bcud kyis 'gro ba 'ga' zhig rim par mngal nas skyes pa'i smin tshul gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7663: sbyangs pa'i rnon po'i rim gyis pa'i rkyen 'jug pa sgoms pa'i yan lag de ting /
NK077(tsu)001:7667: tshogs bsgrub ste lnga ru lus rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7668: lam pa gang dag phyi nang gi dngos po'i bye
NK077(tsu)001:7669: brag kun rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK077(tsu)001:7670: yin pa'i phyir / shi ba'i tshe lus kyis 'brel
NK077(tsu)001:7671: thag chad pas rig pa brgyal ba ltar phyad kyis
NK077(tsu)001:7672: yin pa'i phyir / song ste / phyi yul gyi snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7673: nang 'dzin sems kyi rtog pa gnyis su med par
NK077(tsu)001:7674: spros med nam mkha' lta bur gsal la rtog pa
NK077(tsu)001:7675: med pa ni don dam bden pa sgom pa ste
NK077(tsu)001:7676: / de ting stong pa chen po dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:7680: de nas 'di phyi gnyis kyi skye ba bar ma ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7681: srid pa bar do'i dus su gdos pa can gyi lus med de /
NK077(tsu)001:7682: dwangs ma lnga las byung ba'i bag chags kyi lus
NK077(tsu)001:7683: dbang po kun gsal thogs med du 'gro ba de
NK077(tsu)001:7684: / kun rdzob gyi bden pa sgom pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7685: kun ting snying rje sgyu ma dang 'dra ba'i phyir dper brjod pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:7688: de nas las kyi rlung gis bdas te /
NK077(tsu)001:7689: skye gnas su dang po ma'i mngal du srid pa nying mtshams sbyor bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:7690: rten khu ba dkar dmar nyi zla'i gdan no //
NK077(tsu)001:7691: rnam par shes pa ni gsung yig 'bru dang 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:7692: brtun shing ltar skye drag tu gyur pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7693: thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje dang 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:7694: de nas kha mig dod pa ni sku phra mo dang 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:7695: de nyid a ham gi sngags brjod pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7697: skyes pa rang la'ang rim pa gsum yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:7698: skyes nas lo bcu gnyis lon pa man chad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7701: lo nyi shu rtsa lnga man chad dar la bab pa zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7702: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i dape'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7703: de nas 'jig rten gyi bya ba sna tshogs bsgrub pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7704: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub kyi dape'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7705: bden gnyis kha bral ba ltar snang nas sgom yang /
NK077(tsu)001:7706: don la bden pa dbyer med gnyis su med de /
NK077(tsu)001:7709: mngal du chags pa gsung yi ge'i dpe /
NK077(tsu)001:7710: de la rlung gis skul bas rdo rje lta bur gyur pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7712: de la yang rlung gis bskul nas lus su grub pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7713: sku yongs rdzogs kyi dpe zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:7716: mngal na gnas pa 'ba' zhig byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:7718: bya ba dang 'gal don dang yang 'gal /
NK077(tsu)001:7719: phyag rgya gcig pa kho na'i dper 'gyur gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:7720: lam gong ma gnyis kyi dper mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:7723: bu chung skyes ma thag phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7724: byis spa ni snang ba rnam 'byed /
NK077(tsu)001:7725: dar ma ni tshogs bsgrub gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7726: 'di yang stobs rdzogs ma rdzogs yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:7727: 'di rnams dpe kho na ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:7729: phyi snod 'jig rten gzhan yas khang /
NK077(tsu)001:7730: nang bcud lha dang lha mo'i dal gzhi gdod ma nas yin par 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7731: gong du bshad pa'i dpe de rnams don rtogs na
NK077(tsu)001:7732: dpe de rnams gnas su dag nas don ji ltar
NK077(tsu)001:7733: bzhin yin te / gdam ngag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:7734: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK077(tsu)001:7735: zhes sogs gsung pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:7736: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7737: tshogs lam gyi rnam 'byor bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7738: sbyor lam bar chad med par tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7739: dang po le'u bzhis bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:7740: de la de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7742: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7745: dang po lam lta ba la brten nas ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:7746: 'dzin sgom par byed pa don dam chos nyid de
NK077(tsu)001:7747: bzhin nyid du goms par bya ba'ang don bco lnga
NK077(tsu)001:7748: ste / spyi dang khyad par gyi sngon du bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7749: sgom pa'i dgos ched dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7750: sgom pa la blo bzhag pa'i thabs dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7751: sgom pa'i ngo bo dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:7752: ting nge 'dzin gyi mi mthun pa'i skyon ngos bzung ba dang lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:7753: skyon de dag bcos pa'i thabs dang drug /sgom pa'i nyams kyi rim pa dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:7757: rtags dang bcu gcig /rmi ltas kyi mtshan ma dang bcu gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:7758: ting nge 'dzin gyi yon tan dang bcu gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7759: 'da' ka ma'i man ngag dang bcu bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:7760: de ting rang gi 'bras bu dang bco lngas stong
NK077(tsu)001:7761: pa chen po'i rnal 'byor yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:7762: ro // mdor bstan gyi skabs su spyi don bco lngar bstan pa la bsdu na /
NK077(tsu)001:7766: dgos ched bstan pa dang gsum mo //
NK077(tsu)001:7774: 'da' ka ma'i gdams ngag dang bdun no //
NK077(tsu)001:7778: dgos ched la drug /dgos ched dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7783: 'di rnams brtag cing dpyad nas don blang bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7784: 'di rnams dmar mchan la brtag dpyad byed rgyu mi snang /
NK077(tsu)001:7786: brtsi bgrang gi rnam grangs rnams bris pa'i dbang gis nor zin /
NK077(tsu)001:7787: rgyas par bshad pa la don bco lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7790: thun mong spyi'i sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7791: khyad par 'di nyid kyi sngon du 'gro ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7793: sngon du dbang thob cing lta ba rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7795: gsang sngags kyi rigs can skyes bu gang zhig grogs ngan pa spang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:7796: gcig pu dben par gnas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7797: dper na gangs kyi seng ge bzhin du gcig pur
NK077(tsu)001:7798: 'jigs med du gnas shing rgyu bas don bsgrub pa
NK077(tsu)001:7799: yin te / seng ge la chos gsum yod /
NK077(tsu)001:7804: de bzhin rnal 'byor pas sgom pa'i dus su gcig pur gnas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7805: bar chad la sogs pa'i 'jigs pa dang bral ba /
NK077(tsu)001:7806: lta ba dman pa dang nyon mongs pa zil gyis gnon pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7807: sgom byed pa la las dang po bas /
NK077(tsu)001:7808: sems las su rung dgos shing /
NK077(tsu)001:7809: grogs bsten na chags sdang 'phel bas /
NK077(tsu)001:7810: rang nyid gcig pur seng ge lta bur rgyu bar bya dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:7811: de yang bsam gtan chos drug las //
NK077(tsu)001:7812: mang po rtag tu 'thab gyur te //
NK077(tsu)001:7814: gzhon nu ma yi gadu'u bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:7815: gcig pu rab tu rgyu bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:7817: lag pa la gadu'u mang na mi mthun /
NK077(tsu)001:7818: khra shad du gyur pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:7819: lung pa phu mda' na sgom chen mang na /
NK077(tsu)001:7820: 'gran zlar gyur cing chags sdang 'phel ba'i skyon yod pas ma dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:7822: rab kyi gangs kyis seng ge bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:7823: sgra tsam grags kyang mthong mi bya //
NK077(tsu)001:7824: 'bring gis brag gseb gla ba bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:7826: tha mas lug khyu'i ri bong bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:7827: grong las dpag ste gcig pur 'dug /ces gsung pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7828: rab gangs kyi seng chen bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:7829: mi skad khyi skad mi thos pa'i sar /
NK077(tsu)001:7830: rang nyid gcig pu sgom pa la brtson pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7831: 'bring nag gseb kyi gla ba bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:7832: grwa rog grogs mched mthong yang blo kha mi bstun nas rang nyid gcig pur sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7833: tha ma grong ltag gi ri bong bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:7834: bsod snyom la grong du rgyu dgos yang /
NK077(tsu)001:7835: de khur nas gangs brag shing drung du sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7836: de yang ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa'i sngon du
NK077(tsu)001:7837: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi ri mo
NK077(tsu)001:7838: phyi nang gsang gsum gyis dbang bco brgyad rim par
NK077(tsu)001:7839: bzhin du rdzogs par mnos shing zhus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7840: lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7842: le'u bdun pa nas bshad pa bzhin ston pa'i rang
NK077(tsu)001:7843: bzhin brgyad dang ldan pa'i bla ma rdo rje slob
NK077(tsu)001:7844: dpon de la sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo nas mnyes
NK077(tsu)001:7845: pa gsum gyis mchod cing brtson 'grus kyi sgo gsum
NK077(tsu)001:7846: gyis rgyud yongs su sbyongs pa'i sgo nas le'u gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:7847: pa ltar lta ba bden gsum dbyer med kyi don
NK077(tsu)001:7848: rtogs pa dang / dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7849: gzhan yang lhag pa'i yo byad lnga ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7850: spyi dang khyad par gyi rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7853: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems la mtshan ma'i spros pa dang bral ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7854: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems can thams cad sdug
NK077(tsu)001:7855: bsngal dang bral bar 'dod pa'i snying rje chen po
NK077(tsu)001:7857: de ltar lnga po de ni 'jig rten pa'i yo
NK077(tsu)001:7858: byad las lhag pa'i byang chub sgrub pa'i yo byad
NK077(tsu)001:7859: gong gis de lnga sngon du rdzogs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7860: 'di'i skabs na bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7861: lhag pa'i yo byad lnga sngon du rdzogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7862: stong pa chen po'i rnam 'byor la sbyang ci la dgos zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:7863: 'di ni sa bcad nang nas bstan pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:7864: lam thun mong spyi'i sngon 'gro yin par shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:7865: gzhan don du sgom par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7867: gong gi yo byad rnams 'tshogs pa de nas bu
NK077(tsu)001:7868: gcig pu la ma byams shing brtse ba lta bur
NK077(tsu)001:7869: gzhan la phan pa'i sems dang ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7870: khams gsum 'khor ba na gnas pa'i rig drug gis
NK077(tsu)001:7871: sems can thams cad thar pa mya ngan las 'das
NK077(tsu)001:7872: pa'i sar 'god par dam bca' ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7873: tshad med pa dang ldan pas gnas brtsig cing gdan bshams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7875: tshangs pa la sogs pa'i gnas su skye bar byed
