NK077(tsu)001:7876: pa'i tshad med bzhi sngon du song bas rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:7878: phyogs mtshams kyi dgra la sogs pa'i skyon med pa'i sa brtag cing brtsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7879: sa bslang ba la sogs pa cho ga'i rim pa
NK077(tsu)001:7880: rnams man ngag rdo rje las rims ltar rgyas par
NK077(tsu)001:7881: bya'o // gnas che chung ran cing 'tshams par byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:7884: byug pa la sogs pa gser chu gla chu rnams
NK077(tsu)001:7885: dang ldan par byas pa de ni dug sbrul la
NK077(tsu)001:7886: sogs pa'i 'jigs pa rnams bsrungs ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:7887: ras pi par ta'i stan 'jam shing 'bol ba nang tshang can dang ldan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7888: tshogs bsags shing 'brel thag bcad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7890: phyi nang gi bar chad bsal zhing lam yan lag rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:7891: tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7892: sbyin bsreg brgya rtsa la sogs bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7893: gsung rab 'bum la sogs pa 'don pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7898: phyag dang bskor ba la sogs dge ba'i dpung tshogs bskyed pa la 'bad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7899: byin rlabs dngos grub kun gyi gegs //
NK077(tsu)001:7900: sgrib pa rnam gnyis yin pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:7902: phyi nang gi 'brel thag bcad pa ni phyi'i bu
NK077(tsu)001:7903: lon dang nye du gnyen 'brel gyi 'brel ba rnams
NK077(tsu)001:7907: grogs mched la sogs pa'i bu lon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7908: 'brel chags pa thams cad kun ting nge 'dzin las /
NK077(tsu)001:7909: gzhan pa mi mthun pa g.yeng bar 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:7910: chod par byas nas dur rkun wa dang 'dra bar
NK077(tsu)001:7911: sdar te / bu lon dang 'brel chags la 'dzem
NK077(tsu)001:7912: shing bag yod dgos te sems kyi spros pa thams
NK077(tsu)001:7913: cad dor la ting nge 'dzin la brtson par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:7914: sdar te / // cha rkyen bsdus shing grogs brtsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7916: khams dang mthun pa'i sman dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7918: ting nge 'dzin skye ba'i skyon grogs nyams can dang gdams ngag la sogs pa bsdus la /
NK077(tsu)001:7919: bgegs la sogs bar chad bsrung ba sngon du rdzogs par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7920: gsang ba'i longs spyod rig ma'ang mtshan dang ldan pa brten par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:7921: 'o na gong gi skyes su seng ge bzhin rgyu ba dang 'gal /
NK077(tsu)001:7925: rnam g.yeng gi grogs ngan spang ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:7926: 'dir lta spyod mthun na ma spong gcig gsung pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7927: rig ma lam gyi grogs yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:7930: bde ba bskyed par byed pa'i cha rkyen yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7932: dgra bgegs nad gsum gyis 'tshe ba bzlog pa'ang nyer rdzogs su bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:7933: khyad par 'di nyid kyi sngon 'gro ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7934: de ltar thun mong spyi'i sngon du bya ba rdzogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7935: khyad par 'di nyid kyi sngon 'gro ni mchod pa
NK077(tsu)001:7936: 'bul ba'i rten dngos grub nye ba'i yi dam gyi
NK077(tsu)001:7937: lha sku'i gzugs brnyan lugs su blugs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7940: gang yang rung ba rab gnas can rang gi mdun du bzhugs su gsol la /
NK077(tsu)001:7944: dge ba la rjes su yi rangs /
NK077(tsu)001:7948: dam baca'i yan lag brgyad pa /
NK077(tsu)001:7949: de dag 'bul ba'i tshul yongs su bzung la /
NK077(tsu)001:7950: de tshar nas tshogs rten dbang po'i lha rnams 'od du zhu bas yongs su gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:7951: bdag gi spyi gtsug nas mar la thim par byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7952: bdag gi sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa bsreg te /
NK077(tsu)001:7953: rang nyid kyang 'od du zhu ba'i rjes la mi rtog pa'i ngang la 'dug par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:7954: gnyis pa dgos ched la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:7956: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7958: dag pa bden pa rnam gsum nor zhing rang rig
NK077(tsu)001:7959: rgyal po ting nge 'dzin nyams su blang zhing goms
NK077(tsu)001:7960: pa'i / bla na med pa'i byang chub rnam pa
NK077(tsu)001:7961: mchog ldan gyi chos sku 'di rnyed par 'gyur ro
NK077(tsu)001:7962: pa'i / // lam go rim nges pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK077(tsu)001:7964: gong gi gtan tshig de'i phyir lta ba mthong ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:7965: rjes de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin sgom mo
NK077(tsu)001:7966: // de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin de ni
NK077(tsu)001:7967: snying rje chen po kun tu snang gi ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:7968: 'dzin 'byung ba'i gzhi 'am rgyu ru bzhag ces bya
NK077(tsu)001:7969: // ste / snying rje la goms nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7970: phyag rgya gcig pa de goms nas spros pa 'byung ba'i gzhi ru 'gyur bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:7971: go rim 'byung ba'ang de bzhin du nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:7972: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi skabs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:7973: bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba ji bzhin pa rtogs nas sgom pa yin nam min /
NK077(tsu)001:7975: gang dag skal ba cung dman pas /
NK077(tsu)001:7978: bden gsum dbyer med kyi lta ba mkhas pa pan tri ta'i dpyad sgom la shor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:7979: don rgyud thog na don dam stong pa 'khrungs pa min no //
NK077(tsu)001:7981: dag pa rnam gsum ma nor zhing //
NK077(tsu)001:7984: lam spyi'i mtshan nyid ma nor bar rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:7985: rang mtshan la bden gsum dbyer med rtogs pa min /
NK077(tsu)001:7986: 'di ni mkhas pa pan tri ta'i dpyad sgom la dgongs pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:7987: spyir gcig char ba'i lta ba 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:7989: gzhi la bden gsum gnas tshul de /
NK077(tsu)001:7990: lam la bden gsum gcig chod du rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:7992: blo dman pa rim gyis pa'i gang zag des /
NK077(tsu)001:7993: bden gsum dbyer med yin tshul shes kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:7994: rtogs tshul la bden gsum rim pa ltar rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:7995: rims pa ltar sgoms pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:7996: de bas na tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:7997: dang po stong pa don dam skye med la sbyangs pa stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:7998: 'gags med kun rdzob snying rje la sbyangs pa snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:7999: dbyer med la sbyangs pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK077(tsu)001:8000: spyod yul dang bral bar sbyangs pa phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor dang bzhi 'byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:8001: des na gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:8004: spyod yul dang bral bar don dam pa lhag pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:8005: chos sku chen po de blo rim gyis pas phyag
NK077(tsu)001:8007: mngon gsum du slong thub pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:8010: zung du 'brel ba'i skyed mthar phyin //
NK077(tsu)001:8011: 'bras bu lam shes bstan pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:8012: gsung pa yang 'di la dgongs pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8013: de ltar ma yin bden gsum dbyer med de /
NK077(tsu)001:8014: gong gi lta ba'i skabs la rtogs dgos zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:8016: gcig char bas rtogs pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8017: de'i don gyi lam gyi go rim la /
NK077(tsu)001:8018: le'u gnyis par lta ba bshad pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:8019: rim gyis pas ma rtogs pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8020: lta ba rtogs so zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:8022: lam gyi thog mar bden gsum dbyer med rtogs /
NK077(tsu)001:8023: sgom pa la bden gsum kha phral nas sgom pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:8024: 'di rnams la 'bru gnon kho nas mi chog /don gyi 'brel tshul /
NK077(tsu)001:8026: mi mthun gyi tshig gang byung yang /
NK077(tsu)001:8028: 'di 'di la dgongs zer ba gcig dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:8029: de min sgo them la ma bardzisa par /
NK077(tsu)001:8030: phug gi lo rgyus bshad pa dang 'dra ba'i bshad pa 'ga' zhig la snying po med do //
NK077(tsu)001:8031: gzhan sel don gnyer la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:8035: gang zag skal ldan zhes pa 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:8037: lta ba rtogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:8039: gdul bya'i rims pa gang dag gsang sngags ma h+aa'i sgor 'jug pa'i skal ba dang ldan kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:8040: gcig char ba la ltos na /
NK077(tsu)001:8041: rim gyis pa 'di blo chung dman pas kun rdzob
NK077(tsu)001:8042: gnas lugs ma rtogs pas mi mthun pa'i phyogs snang
NK077(tsu)001:8043: zhen nyon mongs gzhan sel ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:8044: phyir dang / mthun pa'i phyogs sgrub bya 'bras bu
NK077(tsu)001:8045: chos sku don du gnyer ba'i dgos ched gnyis yod
NK077(tsu)001:8051: ting nge 'dzin la 'jug par byed pa de'ang mdor
NK077(tsu)001:8052: bstan gyi snga ma gzhan sel ba'ang bdag gzhan gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:8053: kyi don du sgom pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8054: gsal bya rgyud lhan gcig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8055: rkyen kun tu brtag pa'i ma rig pas phyin ci
NK077(tsu)001:8056: log tu 'khrul pa'i snang ba thar bar dka' bas
NK077(tsu)001:8057: na / 'dam rdzab dang 'dra ba'i dbyings su sel
NK077(tsu)001:8058: byed rang rig pa'i ye shes sgron me'i mda' 'phang
NK077(tsu)001:8059: nas ma rig pa gti mug gi mun pa rnams
NK077(tsu)001:8060: bsal te sems rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal zhing dgongs
NK077(tsu)001:8061: pa bde ba'i mchog thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8062: de yang mdor na sgrib pa'i tshogs mun pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:8063: 'dra ba'i nang du snang ba'i nyi ma shar ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:8064: tshul bzhin du ma rig pa'i mun pa sangs zhing
NK077(tsu)001:8068: chos nyid don du gnyer ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8070: chos kyi dbyings ni nam mkha'i dkyil ltar mtha' dbus
NK077(tsu)001:8071: phyogs ris med cing yangs pa la de nyid sgom
NK077(tsu)001:8072: byung shes rab kyi myur du don sangs rgyas kyi
NK077(tsu)001:8074: de yang don la 'gro ba med cing 'ong ba
NK077(tsu)001:8075: med de 'khor 'das kyi mtha' la mi gnas pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:8076: // mi gnas pa de nyid byang chub sems mchog
NK077(tsu)001:8077: skye ba med pa'i ngang du gnas pas a rab
NK077(tsu)001:8078: // bde zhes bya'o // dngos grub don du gnyer ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8080: rtogs pa ye shes su bsgyur ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8081: dper na mun pa nyid spangs pa med par snang bar bsgyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8082: dug nyid bdud rtsir 'gyur ba'i tshul bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:8083: mtshan ma rang kha'i rtog pa rnams spangs pa med par rig pa ye shes rtogs par /
NK077(tsu)001:8084: dbang bsgyur bar byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8085: de la mchog thun mong gi dngos grub 'byung ba
NK077(tsu)001:8086: ni dngos grub rnam gnyis don du gnyer ba gang
NK077(tsu)001:8087: dag kun de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di
NK077(tsu)001:8091: gal te stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor 'di med na /
NK077(tsu)001:8093: rgya mtsho 'jing gi pha 'ong rgyab gsher kyang nang skom pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:8094: bskal pa dpag du med par mtshan bcas kyi dge ba lam la brtsal bar byas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:8095: gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma ma chad cing 'khor ba
NK077(tsu)001:8096: las thar pa'i don med pas bla na med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:8097: byang chub kyi snying po sgom pa yin te 'bras
NK077(tsu)001:8099: gsum pa sgom thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8103: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di med na
NK077(tsu)001:8104: skyon yod pa de sgom pa'i phyir lhag ma'i lus
NK077(tsu)001:8105: 'di nyid 'byung ba'i cha snyoms dgos pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:8106: lus bde ba dang ldan zhing thar pa la bgrod
NK077(tsu)001:8107: pa'i chos bdun tshul 'di lus rnal la phab pa
NK077(tsu)001:8113: sems drang na sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la sleb pa'i dgos ched yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:8114: chos bdun rang gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:8115: rkang pa mnyam pa'i dkyil mo krung bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8116: lag pa mnyam bzhag gis phyag rgya lte 'og du bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8117: rked pa dong rtse brtseg pa ltar bsrang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8118: mgrin pa lcags kyu ltar yud tsam gug pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8120: lce yar rkan la sbyar ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8121: dpung pa rgod gshog ltar brkyang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8122: yang na so dang mchu tha mal du bzhag pa dang bdun yang zer /
NK077(tsu)001:8123: bsam gtan gyi chos bdun 'di rnams la sngon byung du 'di bca' shes pas grol ba'i gtam rgyud /
NK077(tsu)001:8124: rjes 'jug rnal 'byor pas bca' dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK077(tsu)001:8125: chos bdun po re re la'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:8126: dgos ched kyi don re re bshad rgyu yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:8127: 'dir gzhung bshad kyi dbang du yin pas ma bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:8128: man ngag khrid 'debs pa'i dus su shes par mdzod /
NK077(tsu)001:8129: de ltar lus kyi chos bdun dang ldan par byas pa de dper na /
NK077(tsu)001:8130: rje btsun rnam par snang mdzad gangs chen mtsho rgyal gyi bzhugs tshul bzhin du bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8131: sems kyi bzhag thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8132: bzhag thabs ma nor ba dang nor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8138: sems bsgom bya sgom byed kyi rtsol ba med pa'i sems kyi ting nge 'dzin la 'dug par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8139: de ltar ting nge 'dzin la 'jog pa de yang
NK077(tsu)001:8140: blo chung ba bla ma'i gdams ngag gi stobs kyis
NK077(tsu)001:8141: bzhag pa dang / blo che ba rang gi shes
NK077(tsu)001:8142: rab kyi stobs kyis lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang la
NK077(tsu)001:8143: blo bzhag pas de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:8144: la goms par byed pa gnyis yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:8145: rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8147: blo chung ba gdams ngag gi stobs kyis sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8149: sngon brjod bu ni bzhag thabs gnyis yong ba'i dang po /
NK077(tsu)001:8150: gdam ngag gi stobs kyis bzhag pa'i slob bu de yin par 'dod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:8152: skyes bu seng ge bzhin rgyu bas /
NK077(tsu)001:8153: zhes pa la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8154: yo byad sngon du brjod pa de dag dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:8155: pa'i bu de grong yul dang 'du 'dzi bya ba
NK077(tsu)001:8156: las dben pa'i sar zhes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8158: dus dben pa zla ba nya'i dus su lha 'dre thams cad gza' r+aa hu la la /
NK077(tsu)001:8159: dmag 'dren du 'gro bas dus dben pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8160: de'i dus su phyi rgyud la cha gsum btang /
NK077(tsu)001:8161: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i las gzhung bsrang zhing tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor /
NK077(tsu)001:8162: na rag dong sprugs kyi bshags 'bum 'don /
NK077(tsu)001:8163: de nas bla ma de nyid la rin chen gser g.yu mu tig la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8165: bza' btung la sogs pa'i longs spyod kyi bye brag
NK077(tsu)001:8166: sna tshogs kyis bla ma dam pa de mnyes par
NK077(tsu)001:8167: byas nas slob bu de slob dpon gyi dbang du
NK077(tsu)001:8168: ste mdun drang por bzhag la /
NK077(tsu)001:8169: bar chad kyi mi tshugs par bya ba'i phyir rdo rje drag po'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad /
NK077(tsu)001:8171: rag dung lta bu'i sbubs mchu'i man ngag rna ba
NK077(tsu)001:8172: g.yon par shes rab kyi rtsa yod pas de la
NK077(tsu)001:8173: zhib bur ni sgra chung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8174: gtim pa ni lan gsum brjod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8175: de yang gdam ngag dngos ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8176: mchog gi dngos grub dus myur du tshe gcig la
NK077(tsu)001:8177: 'grub par 'dod na bsgom bya sgom byed shin tu
NK077(tsu)001:8178: mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings su sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:8179: gdam ngag gi stobs kyis sgom pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:8180: ku su lu pa'i 'jog sgom byung /
NK077(tsu)001:8181: 'og ma shes rab kyi stobs kyis sgom pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:8182: mkhas pa pan tri ta'i dpyad sgom byung /
NK077(tsu)001:8183: blo che ba shes rab kyi stobs kyis sgom pa de la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8186: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8187: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma blo che ba shes rab kyi stobs kyis bzhag pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:8188: gcig char du rig pa nam mkha' la nyi ma
NK077(tsu)001:8189: shar ba bzhin ye shes spyi blugs su bzhag pa
NK077(tsu)001:8190: dang / lta ba mthong ba'i rjes su bzhag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8191: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8192: rig pa spyi blugs su sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8193: lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes su sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8196: bdag dang bdag gi med par rigs pa spyi blugs su sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8198: bdag dang bdag gi la sogs pa gzhan yul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8199: yul can rnams ni shin tu'ang mi dmigs par chos kyi dbyings su sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:8200: rang rig rtogs pa'i ngang nyid la gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin ces bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8201: de ni sus kyang ma byas rang byung gi ye shes rang la gnas pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:8202: des chos nyid de bzhin nyid du sbyor ba de
NK077(tsu)001:8203: nyid rnam pa mchog ldan gyi stong pa gnyis med
NK077(tsu)001:8204: chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang du thim mo //
NK077(tsu)001:8205: rang byung spro bsdu med par rigs pa spyi blugs su sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8207: rang byung ye shes rang bzhin dkyil 'khor gyi chos
NK077(tsu)001:8208: rnams ma lus chos nyid de bzhin nyid du sdud
NK077(tsu)001:8209: pa'o // sdud bya dang mi sdud pa gnyis ka min /
NK077(tsu)001:8210: rtogs pa'i don yang dag kho na nyid du sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8211: bsgom bya sgom byed med par rig pa spyi blugs su sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8213: sgom par bya ba'i yul dang sgom par byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis ma skyes na /
NK077(tsu)001:8214: chos nyid rang la sgom par bya ba'ang med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8215: de don gyi don dam las sgom par bya ba med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8216: yul dmigs bcas la mi 'jug a cang che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8217: gnyis med gang la'ang 'du shes mi 'jug /gang la
NK077(tsu)001:8218: mi 'jug pa'i blo nam mkha' lta bu de sangs
NK077(tsu)001:8219: rgyas kyi dgongs pa la zhugs pa'i mchog yin no
NK077(tsu)001:8220: // bsam bya bsam byed med par rig pa spyi blugs su sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8222: chos nyid bsam par bya ba'i yul gcig la /
NK077(tsu)001:8224: de nyid mi bsam par yang mi bsam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:8225: blo phyogs gcig pa gang la'ang rnam par mi sems pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8226: de ni rang rig pa'i ye shes mnyam pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:8227: kyi don la gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin nyid de
NK077(tsu)001:8228: / rig pa spyi blugs su sgom pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:8229: gcig char ba sgom pa'i mchog byang chub 'di rnams
NK077(tsu)001:8230: la 'bru gnon pa kho nas mi chog /rig pa
NK077(tsu)001:8231: skad gcig ma'i thog na ngo sprod kyi gsang la
NK077(tsu)001:8232: theb dgos / 'dir rgyas par ma 'grel lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8233: lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes su sgom pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8235: rtogs pa'i don la dmigs med rang snang gi bsgom par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8238: shes rab mchog gi rtogs par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8240: byang chub sems kyi de bzhin nyid ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8241: shin tu mi dmigs te ngo bo ngos bzung thams
NK077(tsu)001:8242: cad dang bral ba blos brtag par dka' bas de
NK077(tsu)001:8243: nyid blo yangs la rgya che gting zab pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8244: shes rab zab pa rnams kyis rtogs par 'gyur te //
NK077(tsu)001:8245: rtogs pa'i lta ba la 'gro 'ong dang mtha' dbus med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8247: de ltar sgom bya'i yul byang sems de dang po
NK077(tsu)001:8248: gang nas kyang ma 'ongs tha ma gar yang mi
NK077(tsu)001:8249: 'gro bas de ltar 'gro ba dang 'ong bar bya
NK077(tsu)001:8250: ba min / rang gi ngo bo shin tu brtag
NK077(tsu)001:8251: par dka' zhing yul yul can ma dmigs pas mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:8252: dang dbus kyang phyogs dang ris su brtag tu med
NK077(tsu)001:8253: ba min / do // rtogs pa'i don la dmigs med rang snang gi sgoms pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8255: 'o na ji ltar yin na gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig pa nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:8256: dmigs bya dmigs byed med pa'i tshul du der snang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:8257: sgom bya don dam spros bral chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8258: dbyings ye shes kyang rang rig kho na tsam du zad do //
NK077(tsu)001:8259: sems kyi bzhag thabs nor ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8261: dmigs pa gol zhing dmigs pa med pa sangs rgyas yin par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8263: lta ba ma rtogs pa'i blo chung ba gang zhig lta ba yul du dmigs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8265: don spyi mtshan go ba la dmigs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8266: rang mtshan lhag mthong gi nyams la dmigs pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8267: dang po ni mtshan nyid theg pa'i lugs la /
NK077(tsu)001:8268: tshogs lam chos rgyun chen po'i ting nge 'dzin man chad yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8269: gnyis pa sbyor lam gyi drod nas bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8270: 'jig rten chos mchog man chad pa rnams yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8271: de lta bu'i mnyam bzhag yul du dmigs nas ting
NK077(tsu)001:8272: nge 'dzin la 'jug pa ni dmigs pa yod pa
NK077(tsu)001:8273: de srid du 'jig rten rgyang 'phen pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8274: de ni 'jig rten pa'i sgom yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:8275: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sgom ni yul du 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:8276: bya 'jug byed med par rtsal bral du rtogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:8277: de sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin par ni thub
NK077(tsu)001:8278: pa'i dbang po nyid dang kun tu bzang po nyid
NK077(tsu)001:8279: kyis gsungs so // dmigs pas dmigs med mi mthong ba dpe dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8281: yang dag par ram nges par sgom bya chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:8282: blo'i yul du bsam zhing de la yul du byas
NK077(tsu)001:8283: nas dmigs su yod par 'dod na dper na phra
NK077(tsu)001:8284: rab khab mig du then thag skud pa 'dzud pa
NK077(tsu)001:8285: lta bu'i // don dam chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:8286: dmigs su med pa de yis don mi mthong ste
NK077(tsu)001:8287: lta bu'i // / then thag skud pa khab mig
NK077(tsu)001:8288: tu 'dzud pas nam mkha' mi mthong ba bzhin no
NK077(tsu)001:8289: lta bu'i // / // bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8290: mdor bstan pa dang rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8291: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8292: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor skye med du mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:8293: pa'i de bzhin nyid de ngo bo tha dad yod
NK077(tsu)001:8294: pa bzhin du de'i rnam grangs kyang 'jug cing zhor
NK077(tsu)001:8296: rnam pa gsum du nges par 'byung ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:8297: de bas na kun snang la sogs pa'i lam kun la yang ngo bo /
NK077(tsu)001:8299: nges tshig gsum gsum du 'byor par gyis shig /rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8301: de bzhin nyid kyi rnam grangs spyir bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8303: spyir rgyu'i theg par nyan rang la ltos na chen po dbu ma pa /
NK077(tsu)001:8304: gsang sngags kyi theg pa la ltos na dman pas
NK077(tsu)001:8305: na theg 'og dbu ma pas spros pa'i mtha' brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:8306: po bkag cing bsal ba'i chos nyid ma skyes de
NK077(tsu)001:8307: bzhin te rang bzhin nam ngang gi stong pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:8308: du 'dod pa'o // de yang sngar mi stong pa
NK077(tsu)001:8309: gcig 'phral du stong par 'dod pa yin te ye
NK077(tsu)001:8310: gdod ma nas stong pa la stong pa nyid bya
NK077(tsu)001:8311: ba'i tha snyad tsam dang yang bral bas /
NK077(tsu)001:8315: gcig du ma'i spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba tsam rang du'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:8316: ma h+aa yo ga 'dir 'dod pa ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:8317: sngags kri ya'i theg pa ba gang gi rang gi
NK077(tsu)001:8318: sems nyid dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:8319: de bzhin nyid rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:8320: 'dod pa dang / rnal 'byor yo ga'i de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:8321: nyid ni rnal 'byor yo ga ba'i chos kyi dbyings
NK077(tsu)001:8322: la spros pa'i mtshan ma med pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:8324: bzhi pa ma h+aa yo ga'i de bzhin nyid ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8325: ma h+aa yo ga'i snang stong gnyis med la snang
NK077(tsu)001:8326: ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:8327: snang stong ngo bo mnyam pa nyid kyi de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:8328: nyid do // khyad par ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid rgyas par bstan pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:8330: ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid dpag tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8332: de ltar dbu ma'i don dam stong nyid spros pa'i mtha' brgyad bral bar 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8333: kri ya'i sems dag pa mtha' bral dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8334: yo ga bas chos kyi dbyings spros bral dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8335: ma h+aa yo ga'i snang ba ma spangs pa'i stong chen te /
NK077(tsu)001:8336: rnam grangs bzhi'i go rim gyi rim pa tha ma
NK077(tsu)001:8337: ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid snga ma gsum las byin
NK077(tsu)001:8339: yon tan gyi khyad par du 'phags pa /
NK077(tsu)001:8340: ngo bo'i sgo nas bla na med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8341: de'i don rgyas par bshad na ngo bo dpag lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8343: yo ga'i don dam gyi ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8344: go rim ltar don dam spros bral mtha' brgyad dang bral ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8346: 'bras bu gang du'ang ma grub pa'i stong pa phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:8347: gcig pa sems dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dang bral ba
NK077(tsu)001:8348: dang / chos kyi dbyings la spros pa'i mtshan ma med pa sogs sngar bshad pa ltar 'dug la /
NK077(tsu)001:8349: ma h+aa yo ga pas snang ba gang yang ma spang pa'i stong chen du 'dug pas dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:8351: 'og ma'i don dam gsum la go rim ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:8352: byin rlabs cir yang mi 'char ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8353: rigs gsum tsam dang rigs lnga tsam las mi snang ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:8354: ma h+aa yo ga'i don dam la nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs pa snang bas dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:8355: yon tan gyis dpag pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8356: 'og ma'i don dam gsum la rtogs shing goms pa'i yon tan gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:8359: yo ga stug po bkod pa rang sa'i 'bras bu re las mi thob la /
NK077(tsu)001:8361: pad+ma spyan thob pas dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:8362: yang na don dril nas bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:8363: byin rlabs kyi yon tan ngo bos bla /
NK077(tsu)001:8364: 'di la yo ga man chad kyi de bzhin nyid kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:8365: thabs kyi phyag rgya zhi khro la sogs pa'i gzugs sku dpag tu med pa mi 'gyur la /
NK077(tsu)001:8366: 'dir ma h+aa yo ga'i de bzhin nyid la /
NK077(tsu)001:8367: kun rdzob kyi snang ba cir yang 'char zhing 'byung bas byin rlabs kyi blar gyur pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:8369: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK077(tsu)001:8370: skye ba med pa ni chos kyi dbyings yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:8371: skyes pa ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la 'char du rung ba'i don yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:8372: yon tan gyi blar gyur pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8373: yo ga man chad kyi don dam mtshan ma med par gnas pas yon tan chung la /
NK077(tsu)001:8374: ma h+aa yo ga'i don dam du /
NK077(tsu)001:8375: dkor bdun lhun grub kyis dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:8377: don dam du ni dkor bdun la //
NK077(tsu)001:8378: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK077(tsu)001:8380: ngo bos blar gyur pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8381: yo ga man chad kyi don dam stong pa phyogs gcig pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:8382: 'dir snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8383: ngo bo snang stong dbyer med yin pas dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:8385: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK077(tsu)001:8386: de kun ngo bo nyid rgyur gnas //
NK077(tsu)001:8387: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK077(tsu)001:8388: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK077(tsu)001:8389: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK077(tsu)001:8392: bden gnyis ye nas dbyer med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:8393: gsang sngags spyi'i lta ba yin //
NK077(tsu)001:8394: zer ba 'di la gol gzhi byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8397: gsang sngags thams cad don dam kun rdzob dbyer med yin par 'dod pa'i rigs kyang mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:8398: de bzhin nyid kyi rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8399: rnam grangs ma 'dres par yon tan gyi cha nas dmigs dbye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8401: bla mar gyur pa ma h+aa yo ga'i de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:8402: nyid 'di la'ang gnas skabs kyi ming gi rnam grangs
NK077(tsu)001:8403: su phye na / chos kun rang byung ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:8404: su gcig cing bzang ngan spang blang med pa'i don
NK077(tsu)001:8406: chos kun rang rig pa la lhun gyis grub pas lhun grub dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8407: mtha' gang yang ma spang zhing mi ldan pas mtha' bral dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8408: chos thams cad ngos bzung dang bral zhing brjod du med pas tha snyad med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8409: chos thams cad ngo bo stong pas stong pa chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8410: chos thams cad dngos po ma grub cing 'dus ma byas yin pas ma skyes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8411: chos thams cad rtsa bral gzhi ma med cing 'byung khungs su gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8413: de la sogs pa chos thams cad kyi yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:8414: gyi ldog pa'i bye brag cha re nas ming re
NK077(tsu)001:8416: de gang yang mi 'gal bar gtan tshigs gsum dang ldan par gnas tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8417: ming gi rnam grangs bdun po de dag re re'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:8418: gnas skabs kyi mtshon pa'i ming du brjod na gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:8419: thun mong ma yin pa rang gi ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8420: ming gi mtshon pa'i sgra don nam /
NK077(tsu)001:8421: nges tshig brjod pa de'ang sgrub par byed pa'i gtan
NK077(tsu)001:8422: tshigs kyi yan lag du dang ldan pa yin zhe
NK077(tsu)001:8423: na / lung man ngag rigs pa rnam pa gsum
NK077(tsu)001:8424: thams cad la 'phrug par sbyar ba rgyud las 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:8425: na / ba yin te / rdo rje me long las /
NK077(tsu)001:8426: lung dang man ngag rigs pa yis //
NK077(tsu)001:8427: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal ba //
NK077(tsu)001:8428: shes byed de yang tshad mar 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:8431: gzhi lam 'bras bu bcas pa'i chos //
NK077(tsu)001:8432: dri lan dam bca' mthar dbyung ba //
NK077(tsu)001:8433: lung dang man ngag rigs sgo nas //
NK077(tsu)001:8434: rtogs par bya phyir rnam bshad bya'ang //
NK077(tsu)001:8436: de ltar na ming bdun po re re ni lung rigs pa man ngag gsum gsum 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8437: mnyam pa nyid kyi lung ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8439: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yis //
NK077(tsu)001:8440: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK077(tsu)001:8444: mnyam pa'i don nyid ji lta bu //
NK077(tsu)001:8445: mnyam nyid rang bzhin gang yang med //
NK077(tsu)001:8448: bzang ngan che chung med pa'i phyir mnyam pa nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:8451: bcing med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:8452: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK077(tsu)001:8456: de phyir ma yin kun yin pa //
NK077(tsu)001:8457: ci yang yin no lhun gyis grub //
NK077(tsu)001:8461: cir yang snang ba'i phyir lhun gyis grub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:8464: gcig dang du ma bral ba yis //
NK077(tsu)001:8465: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:8469: mtha' dang bral phyir ma bral ba //
NK077(tsu)001:8470: ma bral phyir na bral zhes bya //
NK077(tsu)001:8473: mtha'i zhen pa dang dri ma med pa'i phyir mtha' bral lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8474: tha snyad med pa'i lung ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8477: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo la gnas pa'i skyon la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:8479: gol sgrib kyi skyon nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8482: zhes pa 'di la lta ba ji bzhin pa ma rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:8483: bla ma'i gdam ngag brjed pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8484: las dang po g.yo ba'i nyams kyi dus phan chad /
NK077(tsu)001:8485: dmigs med bzhag pa 'dren pas bzung shor te /
NK077(tsu)001:8486: sems yengs nas sgom bya'i don mi gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8489: gang zhig dmigs nas 'jug byed pa //
NK077(tsu)001:8491: zhes pa la sogs pa dmigs bya dmigs byed med par bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8496: stong nyid du dmigs nas yul du sgom na /
NK077(tsu)001:8498: de bzhin nyid mi mthong ba'i skyon yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8499: dmigs med du bzhag par bstan pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:8500: 'dir dran pa'i gdams ngag gi dmigs pa ma brjed par ma byas na sgom du mi 'jog cing /
NK077(tsu)001:8501: phyal bar song na ma dran nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8502: tha ma la du lus na skyon du bstan pa yin pas mi 'gal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8503: bying rgod drug zhes pa 'di la bshad lugs 'ga' zhig yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:8504: 'dir re zhig 'dir ltar byas na go bde /
NK077(tsu)001:8506: sgom bya'i don mi gsal ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8507: shes pa bying thibs se song ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8509: rang bzhin gyis bying ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8511: ched du byas pa'i bying ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8512: dang po rang bzhin gyis bying ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8513: shes pa rang bzhin gyis 'thib pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8514: gnyis pa rkyen gyis bying ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8516: dro sar bsdad pas bying ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8517: gsum pa ched du byas pa'i bying ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8518: shes pa nang du bsdus nas sgom pas bying ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8520: rig pa bzhag thog tu mi sdod par shes pa yul sna tshogs kyis rjes su 'phro ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8522: rang bzhin gyis rgod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8523: rkyen gyis rgod pa dang ched du byas pa'i rgod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8524: dang po rang bzhin gyi rgod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8525: rang shugs kyi shes pa 'phro ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8526: gnyis pa rkyen gyi rgod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8527: nyin par 'du 'dzi g.yengs pa mi chos kyi gtam rgyud /
NK077(tsu)001:8528: lha chos sgrung gling la sogs rnams kyi stobs kyis shes pa yul la 'phro ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8529: gsum pa ched du byas pa'i rgod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8530: sgom gyi ngo bo don gsal stong ched du gnyer /
NK077(tsu)001:8531: lta stangs bstod nas sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8533: bcos nas sgom pa ste shes pa bsgrim pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8535: le lo'i dbang du shor nas ting nge 'dzin du mi 'jug cing lhod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8536: lus ngag yid gsum ched du 'chos par byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8537: 'di gsum gyi sgom la gcun klod sprad ma shes pa'i skyon yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8538: 'di la bram ze mo'i skud pa bkal ba lta bu'i /
NK077(tsu)001:8539: ba mu 'tshos kyis gdam ngag shes dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:8540: sgom kyi ngo bo khams gsum sa dgu la grol dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8543: gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8544: gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi dang dagu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8545: mu stegs rtag chad du log gi dogs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8546: de gnyis dril bas bcu gcig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8551: u pa dang drug /yo ga dang bdun ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8552: gong gi bcu gcig dang bco brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:8553: de'i thog tu gol sgrib kyi skyon nyi shu rtsa lnga brtsi na /
NK077(tsu)001:8554: dmigs pa brjed dang gcig /rtsol mi rtsol gnyis bying rgod kyi khungs su rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8555: bying rgod drug ste bdun dang nyi shu rtsa lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8556: yang na 'di bco brgyad tsho 'di ltar du 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:8557: spyir gol du dogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8559: yo ga man chad thun mong gi theg pa bdun du gol dogs yod pa'i phyir te /
NK077(tsu)001:8561: gong gi bcu bzhi ste brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:8564: log pa ni rtag chad gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:8567: rtsol ba'i rkyen gyi rgod pa gsum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8568: mi brtsol ba'i rkyen gyis bying ba gsum dang bdun ste bco brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:8570: dmigs pa brjed dang bying ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8574: dge ba spyi nas bgrangs pa'i gcig dang log pa spyi nas bgrangs pa gcig dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:8575: bye brag nas bgrangs pas bcu gcig dang bco brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:8577: thun mong gi theg pa bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:8578: zhor byung gi mu stegs dgu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8579: gzhi bo'i rtag chad gnyis dang bco brgyad du 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:8582: gong gi sgrib pa de bzhin du gzhan yang ting
NK077(tsu)001:8583: nge 'dzin la g.yeng ba'i skyon rnam pa drug yod
NK077(tsu)001:8586: phyi rol gyis g.yeng ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8590: gnas ngan len gyis g.yeng ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8592: rang bzhin ngo bos yul 'phro ba'i g.yengs ba ni
NK077(tsu)001:8593: sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa lnga ni ngo bo'i
NK077(tsu)001:8594: g.yeng ba'o // gnyis pa phyi rol 'dod yon gyi
NK077(tsu)001:8595: yul lngar shes pa 'phros pas ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:8596: bar chad kyi rkyen byed pa ste phyi rol gyis
NK077(tsu)001:8597: g.yeng ba'o // g.yeng ba'o // bying ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8599: mnyam bzhag la g.yeng ba'i snyoms 'jug ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:8600: gyi ro myong bar 'dod pa nang gi g.yeng ba
NK077(tsu)001:8601: yin te / gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir dge sbyor byed pa ni mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8602: 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug gzhan yang theg pa gzhan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:8603: gzhung de yi lugs kyi ting nge 'dzin la sems
NK077(tsu)001:8604: 'phro ba ni / yid la byed pa'i g.yeng ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8606: snyoms pa'i bdag tu 'dzin pa'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK077(tsu)001:8607: snyoms par 'jug pa de ni gnas ngan len gyi
NK077(tsu)001:8609: de'i rkyen gyi 'khor bar skye ba len par the tshom med do //
NK077(tsu)001:8610: bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8612: sngar gyi yul lam rtogs pa'i dran pa byung nas
NK077(tsu)001:8613: de'i rjes su rtogs pa phyi ma lung btags shing
NK077(tsu)001:8615: gnyis pa ched du 'gog pa ste mnyam par 'jog pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:8616: rig pa ye shes kyi 'char sgo ma shes nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8617: tshogs drug ched du bkag nas 'gog pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8619: ther zug ces pa ni dper na mi 'gyur ba'i gdams pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:8620: nyams len gyi sna bsgyur ma shes par a 'thas su sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8622: bzhi pa ni phyal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8623: zhes pa ni sgom pa'i tshe gnad 'dzin mi shes pas nyams len rgyu ma rnyed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8625: ched du gsum chos yid la byed //
NK077(tsu)001:8627: lus ngag yid gsum ched du bkol nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8628: sgom bcos bslad dang bral ba bcos bslad can byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8630: ting nge 'dzin gyi ro nyams su myong bar byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8632: 'du shes kyi mtshan ma la gnas shing yul du dmigs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8634: shes pa nang du sdud pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8636: ting nge 'dzin gyi don je gsal du mngon du byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8638: ting nge 'dzin dang 'bras bu la re ba mang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8639: bar du gcod pa'i skyon 'di la sa bcad nang
NK077(tsu)001:8640: la bcu gcig byas zin pa 'di yi ge ma
NK077(tsu)001:8641: dag pa i yin brtag par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8644: ting 'dzin la sgrib pa'i skyon rtsa ba'i rtog pa lnga yan lag gi rtog pa bcu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8645: dang po rtsa ba lnga ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8652: yod med dang yin min la sogs pa sems spyi'i rnam pa la rtog pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8654: 'du shes kyi yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8656: de'i rjes su dran pa'i rgyun ring thung du rgyu ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8657: tshor ba ni nyams su myong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8659: rtog pa'i 'byung 'jug dus myur bul ltos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8660: gnyis pa yan lag bcu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8661: rtsa ba lnga po de dag re re la yan lag gnyis gnyis te bcu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8662: de yang rtogs pa sems kyi rnam pa'i sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8663: khras dang rtsed mo gzhan lta bu /
NK077(tsu)001:8665: mtshan ma 'dzin pa'i sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8666: dgos ched dang byis pa lta bu che chung gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8667: rgyu ba rgyun gyi sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8668: 'dod chags dang zhe sdang lta bu ring thung gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8669: tshor ba nyams myong gi sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8670: ngar gdongs dang snag po che lta bu gsal mi gsal gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8671: byung tshor goms pa'i sgo nas bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8672: kha 'don byang ma byang la myur bul lta bu yod pa gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:8673: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par shag rdor ba'i yig cha nang du gzigs mdzod /
NK077(tsu)001:8674: skyon dbang du song ba'i gol sa bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8676: 'jig rten gsum gyi dang po 'dod khams su gol ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8677: gong gi rtogs pa phra rags de la /
NK077(tsu)001:8678: mi dge ba bcu rang kha spyod na ngan song gnas bcu la gol la /
NK077(tsu)001:8679: dge bcu'i rtog pa phra rags bskyed na /
NK077(tsu)001:8680: mtho ris gnas bcu la gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8681: gzugs la bdag tu bzung bas gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhir gol bar bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:8682: de yang stong chen la mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe na gnas lugs kyi don ma rtogs par /
NK077(tsu)001:8683: mnyam bzhag ngo bo la 'di yin 'di min gyi rtog dpyod la shes pa 'jug na /
NK077(tsu)001:8684: bsam gtan dang por gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8685: de nas rtog pa zhi nas dpyod pa la gnas cing dga' bde shar ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8687: rtog dpyod gnyis zhi nas mnyam bzhag klong la brten pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8689: de yi spros pa yang zhi nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8690: sems mi g.yo btang snyoms su gnas pa ni bsam gtan bzhi par gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8691: ming bzhi'i phung po la bdag tu bzung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:8692: gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa skye mched mu bzhir gol te /
NK077(tsu)001:8693: de yang mnyam bzhag nam mkha' lta bu yin snyam nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8694: de la blo gnas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8695: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched du gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8696: de nyid sems rnam rang byung snyam nas sgom na /
NK077(tsu)001:8697: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8698: de'i spros pa yang zhi nas stong pa la blo gnas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:8699: ci yang med pa'i skye mched du gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8700: de chad ltar 'gyur dogs nas 'du shes phra ba yod pa yang ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8701: rtag ltar 'gyur dogs nas rags pa yod pa yang ma yin snyam nas sgom pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8702: yod min med min gyi skye mched du gol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8703: de ltar khams gsum pa sa dgu ste de dag du gol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8704: mu stegs rtag chad du log pa ni ther zug rtag par ltar ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8705: snga phyi'i mtha' chad pa ma grub par lta ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8706: de gnyis ni phyin ci log gi lta bar gol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8709: sgo gsum gyi 'jig rten gyi bya ba mang po byed /
NK077(tsu)001:8710: ting nge 'dzin la blo 'byung 'jug rkyen zhing sgom
NK077(tsu)001:8711: pa nyams su len pa la ngang thung ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:8713: rna bar du shang gi sgra thos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8714: yul khams dang gnas khang la rang gi mgo bo 'khor zhing sngo skya rlung ser skya mkhris pa /
NK077(tsu)001:8715: dmar smug bad kan la sogs pa'i kha dog mthong
NK077(tsu)001:8716: ba dag khams 'khrugs pa las gyur pa'i skyon gyi
NK077(tsu)001:8717: cha yang brtag shing shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8718: spyod lam sgom chen gyi skyon drug go //
NK077(tsu)001:8720: rnal 'byor pa de yis 'gro ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8723: zas nor la longs spyod pa'i tshe na'ang stong pa
NK077(tsu)001:8724: chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin dang bral
NK077(tsu)001:8725: ba ni / 'dug cing sdod pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:8726: yur rtse de bya ra ba khra lta bu'i sgom chen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8727: 'gro ba'i tshe mnyam bzhag dang mi 'bral ba mi byed bcing /
NK077(tsu)001:8728: bsgrub khang nang na don mang ste dper na dur
NK077(tsu)001:8729: rkun ste mis mi mthong ba'i lung srol nang du
NK077(tsu)001:8730: don mang wa lta bu'i sgom chen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8731: de bzhin du chu steng du mi mngon yang /
NK077(tsu)001:8732: chu zhabs su don mang ba nya lta bu'i sgom chen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8733: nyal ba'i tshe 'od gsal gnyid dang mi bsre zhing glang gnyid pa lta bu'i sgom chen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8734: zas nor la longs spyod pa'i tshe mnyam bzhag dran
NK077(tsu)001:8735: pas mi bzung zhing skam chags che ba tshong pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:8736: sems lta bur gyur te tshong pa lta bu'i sgom
NK077(tsu)001:8737: chen dang / ting nge 'dzin la sdod mi tshug
NK077(tsu)001:8738: cing bya byed mang ba spre'u gyi spyod pa bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:8739: chen dang / byed pa ni / bya byed mang ba spre'u lta bu sgom chen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8740: de rnams sgom chen gyi skyon che shos yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8742: mtshan ma tshig gi rnal 'byor pa //
NK077(tsu)001:8743: tshig la zhib cing don la rtsing //
NK077(tsu)001:8744: yang dag don la ma 'byor ba //
NK077(tsu)001:8745: 'dug na mtshan ma'i bya ra byed //
NK077(tsu)001:8746: 'gro tshe ma rab 'phyo zhing rgyug /nyal na mtshan ma'i bsam dpyod btong //
NK077(tsu)001:8747: 'dug tshe gnyid dang bying dbang sogs //
NK077(tsu)001:8748: za na skoms chags dbang gis spyod //
NK077(tsu)001:8749: 'tshogs na ga zha bre mo gtam //
NK077(tsu)001:8750: sgom khang nang na grong chog mdzad //
NK077(tsu)001:8751: rdzas kyi khas len rlom sems pa //
NK077(tsu)001:8752: bzhed pa mtho ris byang chub bzhed //
NK077(tsu)001:8755: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:8757: ting nge 'dzin ngo bo la gnas pa'i skyon bcos thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8759: g.yo thob blo'i rim pa dang sbyar te bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8761: gong gi de ltar skyon ngo shes pa'i rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:8762: pas skyon de dag spang bar byed pa'i 'du byed
NK077(tsu)001:8763: kyi yan lag brgyad brten pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:8777: le lo dang g.yeng ba drug la sogs pa'i skyon sel lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8778: dran pas dmigs pa brjed pa la sogs pa sel /
NK077(tsu)001:8781: dogs pa la sogs bco brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8782: byung tshor dbang gis g.yeng ba la sogs pa sgom
NK077(tsu)001:8783: chen spyod lam gyi skyon drug la sogs pa sel
NK077(tsu)001:8786: bying rgod la sogs pa sel lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8788: rtsol ba yid la byed pa la sogs pa sel lo //
NK077(tsu)001:8790: g.yo nyams kyi dus su bcos thabs yin /
NK077(tsu)001:8791: cung zhig brtan pa theg pa'i nyams la /
NK077(tsu)001:8792: skyon rnams nges bzung nas so sor cung zad ngo bo la bltas pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:8793: yang na skyon ci byung rdo tshan thog tu kha ba bab pa bzhin rang byung rang zhir bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8794: de yang las dang po pas spong ba'i 'du byed brgyad kyis bcos pa zab /
NK077(tsu)001:8795: de nas so sor cung zad bltas na /
NK077(tsu)001:8796: brtag cing dpyad nas sgom pa /
NK077(tsu)001:8797: mkhas pa pan tri ta'i dpyad sgom byed lugs byung /
NK077(tsu)001:8798: de nas sgom pa la thob pa'i nyams shar nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8799: skyon dang rnam rtog gang byung chos sku'i ngo bo la gcod thabs byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:8800: dgag bsgrub med pa'i bcos thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:8802: dper na ji ltar byis pa don la shed bye ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:8803: bya byed kyi g.yeng ba ltar lus ngag gi bya byed mang pos rang nyid g.yeng bar gnas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:8804: bya byed mang po de la bdag dang bdag gir
NK077(tsu)001:8805: med par rtogs pas ting nge 'dzin gyi rig pa
NK077(tsu)001:8806: la rang dbang bsgyur nas gnyis 'dzin gyi mtshan ma
NK077(tsu)001:8807: ci byung yang chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du grol
NK077(tsu)001:8808: zhing dbyings su gnas par bya des na skyon dgag
NK077(tsu)001:8809: pa dang yon tan bsgrub pa ga la yin te
NK077(tsu)001:8810: min no // khams kyi skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8812: cung zad khams las gyur pa'i skyon rnams kyis khams kyi cha nyams pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8813: sgom bya'i don mi gsal ba'i kha dog mi gsal ba mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8814: ting nge 'dzin la blo mi 'jug pa la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:8815: gong gi skyon tsho ngos zin nas spyod lam gang
NK077(tsu)001:8816: dang gang la dga' ba brtan par bya ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:8817: rang gi khams dang mthun pa'i zas dang sman dpyad
NK077(tsu)001:8818: la sogs kyis cho gas gso bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8821: spyod lam rnam bzhir ting nge 'dzin rnal du ma
NK077(tsu)001:8822: 'byor pa'i dus su de shes bzhin gyi bya ra
NK077(tsu)001:8823: bas so 'thas chod nas skyon de dag dor bar
NK077(tsu)001:8824: bya'o // rtogs pa'i ngang la dran pas thag pas bsdoms par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8825: spyod lam gyi rnam pa kun tu sgom pa las nyams par mi bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8829: de ltar skyon bcos shing lta sgom gyi don la mi 'da' bas nog thub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8831: sgom pa'i don la yun ring pas ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i stobs nyams kyis rim pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8832: gdod ma g.yo ba'i nyams nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8833: tha ma mthar phyin pa'i nyams kyi bar du gong
NK077(tsu)001:8834: nas gong du 'phel ba yang g.yo ba'i nyams dang
NK077(tsu)001:8838: mu lnga'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:8841: g.yo ba'i nyams la brtson 'grus bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8843: rnal 'byor pa gang dag /dper na ri gzar po la chu 'bab pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8844: dar gcig kyang mi gnas te 'gro ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:8845: ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i tshe sgom byung ma thag skyon dbang du 'gro ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8846: des na skyon dbang du 'gro na nyams la ci la brtsi zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:8847: tha mal gyi dus su skyon ngos mi zin shing /
NK077(tsu)001:8848: shes pa kha yan du shor ba las /
NK077(tsu)001:8849: 'dir rnam rtog ngos zin gyi nyams yin pas nyams su 'agro'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8850: sngar kun brtags kyi shes pa phyin ci log la
NK077(tsu)001:8851: thog ma med pa nas goms pa'i stobs kyis dper
NK077(tsu)001:8852: na rdza mkhan gyis 'khor lo bskor ba mi gnas
NK077(tsu)001:8853: pa ltar rnam rtog gyi dbang du 'gro bas skyo
NK077(tsu)001:8854: bar byed pa'o // de'i tshe dpe mgo la me
NK077(tsu)001:8855: 'bar ba gsod pa la brtson pa bzhin brtson 'grus
NK077(tsu)001:8857: thob pa'i nyams la 'byung 'jug bsre ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8859: skyon gyi rgyu brtag ste dor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8861: gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams bar 'gar skyon dbang du 'chor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:8862: bar du skyon dbang du mi shor nas thob pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8863: phu gsum gyi chu bran lta bu'i nyams 'ong ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:8864: ting nge 'dzin de'i 'phel bskyed byed thabs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8865: khams dang spyod lam la sogs pa'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin 'chor ba'i rgyu brtag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:8866: ting nge 'dzin mi skye ba'i rgyu rnams dor /
NK077(tsu)001:8867: ting nge 'dzin skye ba'i rgyu bsten nas mnyam bzhag gso ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8869: 'di la ting nge 'dzin 'chor ba'i rgyu khams kyis
NK077(tsu)001:8870: skyon dang 'chor ba'i rgyu rtog pa gnyis po gang
NK077(tsu)001:8871: yin brtag la khams skyon yin na khams gso /
NK077(tsu)001:8872: rtog pa'i skyon yin na dor bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8875: ting nge 'dzin cung zad yod la skyon de dag nyung ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:8876: de tshe dal bus sgom zhing ting nge 'dzin la
NK077(tsu)001:8877: 'byung 'jug byed pa'i dus su thun bsring shes dgos
NK077(tsu)001:8878: pa'o // goms pa'i nyams la btang snyoms bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8880: de ltar thob pa'i nyams de goms nas /
NK077(tsu)001:8881: ting nge 'dzin la brod pas ched du sgom par byed pa la sogs pa'i skyon byung na /
NK077(tsu)001:8882: dper na sa cha bde mor chu de 'gro ba mi mngon pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:8883: skyon dbang du cung zad 'gro yang 'gro ba mi tshor /
NK077(tsu)001:8884: goms pa'i skabs 'dir rnam rtog 'gog rgyu'i skyon yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8885: de chod par byed pa'i thabs la btang snyoms dang pos blang bar bya dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:8886: btang snyoms dang po gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:8887: btang snyoms la gsum yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:8888: rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang snyoms dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8889: rtsol ba med pa'i btang snyoms dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8890: dus phyad pa'i btang dang snyoms dang gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:8891: 'dir dang po'i don nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8892: brten pa'i nyams la mi sun par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8894: dper na ri bo rlung gis mi bsgul ba lta
NK077(tsu)001:8895: bur rnam par rtog pa'i rkyen gyis ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:8896: mi bsgul ba brtan pa thob pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:8897: nyin zhag gcig la thun gcig tu bskyang nas nyin mtshan 'brel par sgom nus na yang /
NK077(tsu)001:8898: ting nge 'dzin gyi thun ched du bzung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:8899: ha cang sun sun du sgom par mi bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8901: rab kyi nyin zhag gcig la brgyad du bgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8902: 'bring gi bcu drug /tha ma sum bcu so drug tu bgos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8903: mthar phyin pa'i nyams la dga' brod mi bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8905: ting nge 'dzin gyi ro myong yang zhen 'dzin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:8906: skyon dor bas stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:8907: de nyid mthar phyin par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8908: de'i tshe thun du bcad pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:8909: 'khor yug tu sgom pa'i shugs las snang ba brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:8910: mthong ba la dga' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8911: brod pa med par bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:8912: de yang shugs snang brgyad gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:8913: me long skar mdas brgyan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8914: snang srid rdul phra rab tu mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8916: kun dag'i ra ba mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8917: skyes mos tshal mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8918: glang chen la zhon pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8920: stong gsum lag mthil sar mnyam pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8923: ting nge 'dzin la shin tu ngang bsring nas yun
NK077(tsu)001:8924: ring bar brtson 'grus bskyed nas sgom pa yis yon
NK077(tsu)001:8925: tan ji lta bu byung na /
NK077(tsu)001:8926: nyams gong nas gong du rim pa bzhin du bogs chen po skye zhing 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:8927: brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8931: bdag dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir bya ba spyod pa kun /
NK077(tsu)001:8932: dang po slob pa g.yo ba nas bzung ste nyams
NK077(tsu)001:8933: lnga mthar phyin pa'i bar du gnyis 'dzin gyi rnam
NK077(tsu)001:8934: par rtog pa med pa'i tshul gyis ni spyod lam
NK077(tsu)001:8935: thams cad kun la 'dzin zhen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8936: chags zhen med par rol bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8937: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:8942: ting nge 'dzin dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8944: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin nyams su blangs
NK077(tsu)001:8945: pa'i tshe chos spyod dgu'i spros pa dor ba yin
NK077(tsu)001:8946: pa'i / gcig cha sgom yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:8947: de yang gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:8948: mtshan bcas bskyed rim sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8949: mtshan med rdzogs rim gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:8951: mtshan med sgom pa la yang mi dmigs zhing ting
NK077(tsu)001:8952: nge 'dzin dang mthun pas spyod pa zhes bya ste
NK077(tsu)001:8953: / sgom pa gcig pu don du gnyer ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8954: de la chos spyod bcu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8955: yi ge bri mchod sbyin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8956: nyan dang 'dzin dang klog pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8957: 'chad dang kha thon byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8958: de sems pa dang sgom pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8959: chos spyod bcu'i bdag nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:8960: de la chos spyod 'di bcu lus ngag yid gsum kyis spyod pa yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:8961: yi ge bri mchod sbyin pa gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:8969: sgom pa gnyis yid kyi chos spyod /
NK077(tsu)001:8971: bsam byung gi shes rab rtogs pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:8972: 'dir mtshan med pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa'i skabs su chos spyod dgu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8973: mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba yin pa'i phyir dor bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:8974: 'o na nya mo chu las mi 'da' bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:8975: dkar ba'i chos dang bral thabs med /
NK077(tsu)001:8978: chos spyod dgu dor ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8980: chos spyod dgu'i spros pa byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:8981: mnyam par bzhag mi thub pa'i skyon yod pa la dgongs so lung phyi ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:8982: gcig char ba bzhin lam gcig chod du rdzogs ma nus /
NK077(tsu)001:8983: rjes shes kyi mtshan ma shar ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:8984: mtshan bcas kyi dge sbyor la 'bad na /
NK077(tsu)001:8985: mnyam bzhag gi bogs su 'gro ba la dgongs so //
NK077(tsu)001:8986: spyod lam dang longs spyod kyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:8988: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di sgom pa'i skabs su /
NK077(tsu)001:8989: spyod lam ci byed 'di ltar du rtogs dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:8990: chos nyid thams cad 'gro ba dang 'ong ba med
NK077(tsu)001:8991: pa la spyod pa 'gro ba dang 'ong ba ltar
NK077(tsu)001:8992: snang ba'i dus de nyid na chos nyid thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:8994: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo la gnas pa med pa'i ngang la thams cad gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:8995: de ltar gtan la ci 'dug pa'i tshe gnas pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:8996: dus nyid na gnas pa rang kha mar 'dzin pa
NK077(tsu)001:8997: med / chos nyid thams cad la longs spyod bya spyod byed med pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:8998: zas za ba la sogs pa 'dod yon la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:8999: thams cad la spyod pa ltar snang spyod pa'i dus
NK077(tsu)001:9000: de nyid na spyod pa med pa'i ngang la ting
NK077(tsu)001:9001: nge 'dzin nyams pa med par spyod cing de nyid
NK077(tsu)001:9005: de ltar spyod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9006: spyod pa thams cad mi 'gog pa bsod nams kyi tshogs /
NK077(tsu)001:9007: mi 'dzin te zhen pa med pa ye shes kyi
NK077(tsu)001:9008: tshogs dang tshogs gnyis rdzogs ste bdag don ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:9009: 'dzin la gnas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9010: spyod pa kun la mi dmigs pa'i ngang du goms par byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:9011: rnal 'byor pas byang chub myur du thob par the tshom med do //
NK077(tsu)001:9012: gzhan don gyi spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9014: spyod lam chos nyid thams cad du slob zhing gzhan don rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9016: de yang rnal 'byor pa 'gro zhing 'ong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9020: dus kyis tshe gong du bstan pa de ltar du
NK077(tsu)001:9021: spyod pas ci spyod thams cad spyod lam chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:9022: du spyod do // de'i tshe byin rlabs kyis 'gro ba sgrol ba gcig shos te gzhan don yin /
NK077(tsu)001:9023: de'i rgyu mtshan gang yang gzhan gyi don du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9024: sems bskyed pas bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9025: thugs rje thabs kyis gzhan don bya ba de la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9027: skabs min kyang thugs rje bya bar gsung pa mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9029: rgyud gzhung las grags pa'i spyod pa rmad du byung ba phrin las la sogs pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:9030: stong pa nyid kyi don rtogs kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9031: skye ba la rang dbang thob pas skye bo kun gyi spyad gsungs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9032: mos pa phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9033: slob pa tshogs bsgrub skabs rnams la lta ci smos te /
NK077(tsu)001:9034: gdul bya'i don 'gyur gyi rkyen mthong na /
NK077(tsu)001:9035: mos pa slob pa de dag /rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9036: rkyen 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin gyi ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:9037: goms pa la gzhi blang nas mi dmigs pa'i ngang
NK077(tsu)001:9039: rgyas par gzhan don bya ba'i thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:9041: rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9042: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin kun kyang gzhan don du 'gyur na /
NK077(tsu)001:9043: phrin las bzhi spyod cing don gnyis bsgrub par byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9044: dbang bskur ba la sogs pa'i tshe lta ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:9045: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum la sogs pa'i lam
NK077(tsu)001:9046: kun skad cig ma re re tsam gyi chas rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:9047: par sgom nas / mthar zhi khro'i phyag rgya mos
NK077(tsu)001:9048: pa'i 'khor lo gang yin dngos su sgom pa'i spyod
NK077(tsu)001:9049: par sgom nas / yul min kyang / mos pa tsam gyi sgom zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:9050: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor 'og nas snyan gsan phab spyan drangs zhing bstims /
NK077(tsu)001:9051: brten par bzhugs su gsol ba rdzogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9052: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rim bzhin 'bul /
NK077(tsu)001:9053: bsnyen pa byed nas gzhan don phrin las bsgrub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9054: dbang la sogs pa'i skabs gang yin gyi spyod pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:9055: byed nus pa'i gzi byin dang ldan par byas nas
NK077(tsu)001:9056: gzhan don rdzogs par stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:9058: de nas rjes chog lhag ma yan chad bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9059: nus pa byin ldan rdzogs par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:9060: ces pa 'di la dmar mchan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9061: sku gsung thugs byin rlabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9062: ye shes lngas dbang bskur bar bzhed gda' ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9065: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9068: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9069: stong pa chen po rnal 'byor sgom pa de'i tshe dam tshig dang sdom pa thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:9070: mos pa'i sgo nas slob cing mi gtong bar bsrungs mod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9071: khyad par ting nge 'dzin gyi dam tshig las mi 'da' bar bsrung zhing ldan par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:9072: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9073: khyad par gyi lta ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9077: rang gi lta ba'i dam tshig yin pas lta ba 'di goms par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9080: yan lag gi dam tshig ces bya ba /
NK077(tsu)001:9081: logs na yod pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:9082: rang gi lta ba rtogs pa las mi 'da' ba dam tshig yin /
NK077(tsu)001:9083: lta ba'i gzungs kyis 'khor bar mi gtong ba'i phyir dam tshig ces bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9084: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi gzungs su gyur pas kyang dam tshig ces bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9085: lta ba rtogs pa'i don zer yang sngar lta ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:9086: skabs su ldan pa'i dam tshig de yang stong chen
NK077(tsu)001:9087: gyi skabs 'dir goms par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9088: lta ba'i dam tshig la mi nyams par bsrungs thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9090: lta ba dam tshig gi mchog yin pa de bas rang sems lta ba rtogs par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9091: dman pas gyur pa'i le lo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9092: g.yeng ba drug la sogs pa'i skyon kun yangs su spangs la /
NK077(tsu)001:9093: nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa med cing mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las mi 'da' bar bsrung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9094: de bzhin nyid las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig dag go //
NK077(tsu)001:9096: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin las 'da' bar mi byed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:9097: rnal 'byor pa gang yang de bzhin nyid dang ldan na dam pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:9098: de bzhin nyid de las 'das na rang gi byang chub kyi myu gu tshig par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:9099: lam spyi'i dam tshig la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9101: lam snga phyi dam tshig rim par gang du 'phar tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9103: de'ang lam snga ma snga mar lta ba'i skabs lta bur lam rang rang gi dam tshig rdzogs par /
NK077(tsu)001:9104: byas pa de yang lam gong ma gong ma de ting lta bu'i rgyud la ldan du yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9105: snga ma snga ma'i dam tshig stong pa chen po
NK077(tsu)001:9106: 'og nas gong du yongs su 'phar ba'i tshul gyi
NK077(tsu)001:9107: gcig spros la sogs phyi ma phyi ma mngon du
NK077(tsu)001:9108: spyod pa yin / de yang lam rim par 'og nas gong du /
NK077(tsu)001:9109: 'phar bas 'og ma 'og ma'i dam tshig gi spyod
NK077(tsu)001:9110: pa kun gong ma gong ma'i sngon du 'gro ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:9111: rgyu yin no // lam gong 'og ni dam tshig
NK077(tsu)001:9112: spyod pa la khyad par yod pa'i dpe bstan pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:9114: lam gong 'og gi lta spyod la rim pa yod
NK077(tsu)001:9115: pa de bas na lam gong 'og so so'i lta
NK077(tsu)001:9116: ba rtogs pa'i tshab che chung gi gzhi las bdag
NK077(tsu)001:9117: don gyi spyod pa dpes ston te /
NK077(tsu)001:9118: de yang dngos kyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9120: ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i khyad par yod pa'i dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9121: nam mkha' tsam du gcig kyang yul lam /
NK077(tsu)001:9122: lung pa'i khyon che chung gis nam mkha' la yang che chung 'ong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9123: 'dra bar lta ba rtogs tshab che chung gis rang don gyi spyod pa yang dogs 'ong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9124: gzhan don gyi spyod pa'i dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9125: gzhan don spyod pa'i gdul bya gdul ba'i zhing khams
NK077(tsu)001:9126: la rgya che chung yod pa ni mi'i dbang po
NK077(tsu)001:9127: gser dngul zangs lcags can gyi 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:9128: rgyal po las khams rgya che chung yod pa bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:9129: no // bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i spyod pa'i dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9132: ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i nus pa dang stobs che chung gi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9133: stobs ldan glang chen tsam du gcig kyang rtsal che chung sgyid pa rags zhan gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:9135: 'bring thad ka /tha ma gzhol phyogs su gcod pa dang 'dra ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9137: bcu gcig pa rtags bstan pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9139: dgos ched kyi mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9144: de yang nar smin pa lo nyi shu lon pa'i rigs de la /
NK077(tsu)001:9145: pha mas khyod la chung ma 'di lta bu len
NK077(tsu)001:9146: no zhes khyim thabs kyi ltas bstan na byis pa
NK077(tsu)001:9147: de khyim thabs de la brod pas bsu zhing rang
NK077(tsu)001:9148: gi zang zing gi nor mang po dag don du
NK077(tsu)001:9149: gnyer ba la brtson par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9150: dpe de bzhin du stong chen gyi rnal 'byor pa
NK077(tsu)001:9151: 'bras bu byang chub kyi bde ba chen po 'tshol
NK077(tsu)001:9153: rtags rnams mngon gsum du mthong ba'i 'bras bu la
NK077(tsu)001:9154: blo brod pa'i tshul gyi shin tu drod rtags de'i
NK077(tsu)001:9155: rgyu thar pa'i lam nyams su len pa la brtson
NK077(tsu)001:9157: de phyir drod 'di dag rjes su bstan pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9158: drod rtags ngo bo rgyas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9166: gong du bstan pa de ltar bsgom bya sgom byed med par yun bsring nas sgom na /
NK077(tsu)001:9169: gsang ba sems la myong ba'i drod gsum 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9170: rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:9172: drod gsum rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9175: phyi lus kyi drod na tsha med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9179: gdan la 'dug tshugs pa la sogs bzod pa phra mo thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9180: nang gi drod sems gnas pa'i tshe rlung rang shugs gis zin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9181: phyi nang du rgyu ba'i dbugs mi tshor ste btang
NK077(tsu)001:9182: bzung la rang dbang thob ste dbugs bde ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:9183: / gsang ba sems kyi drod don chos nyid la blo rnal du phebs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9184: rig pa mi g.yo bar 'byung ba ni the tshom
NK077(tsu)001:9185: med cing nges par phyi nang gsang gsum gyi drod
NK077(tsu)001:9186: rang gi nyams su myong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9187: phyi nang gi drod rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9189: sngar bstan pa'i drod gsum po de las /
NK077(tsu)001:9190: gzhan du ste phyi rol gyi snang ba rags par
NK077(tsu)001:9191: 'dzin pa zhig nas rdul phran tsam du mthong ba
NK077(tsu)001:9192: dang / zla ba tshes pa ltar snang ba thams cad skya lam me ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9194: kun d+ha'i zhing khams la sogs mtshan ma mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9195: gnyis pa nang sems la snang ba'i drod ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9196: mi sgom par 'dod pa'i yul la mi 'gro zhing
NK077(tsu)001:9197: rig pa rnam rtog gi ri rtse la ma yan
NK077(tsu)001:9198: pa chos nyid kyi klong du phebs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9199: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi yul lnga la sems mi
NK077(tsu)001:9200: 'phro ste mi 'gro zhing skye 'chi gnyis kyi 'pho
NK077(tsu)001:9201: 'gyur dag la nyams mi nga ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9202: phyi nang gi zhen chags thams cad dang bral zhing zhen pa chung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9203: sngar lta ba'i dus bas drod khyad par du dpag pa nyams su myong ba 'byung ba 'byung /
NK077(tsu)001:9204: sems can gzhan yul nyams thag mthong na thugs rjes sems 'phrog pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9205: chos brgyad mnyam par mgo bo snyoms pa phal cher 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:9206: chos brgyad gang zhe na theg chen rnal 'byor las /
NK077(tsu)001:9207: grags dang ma grags stod smad bde sdug dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9208: rnyed dang ma rnyed 'jig rten chos brgyad po //
NK077(tsu)001:9210: drod gsum rim par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9212: de ltar gong du bstan pa'i drod kyi rnam pa
NK077(tsu)001:9213: de dag kun kyang g.yo ba'i skabs su res yod
NK077(tsu)001:9214: res med la / thob pa'i skabs su phal cher yod /
NK077(tsu)001:9215: brtan pa'i skabs su mi 'gyur bar yod pa'i go rim gyi de ting gi skabs 'dir ma zad /
NK077(tsu)001:9216: lam gzhan gyi dus kun tu yang /
NK077(tsu)001:9217: de gsum 'khor bar 'byung ba yin no /
NK077(tsu)001:9218: yang na rtags de rnams nyams g.yo thob goms brtan kun tu 'khor bar 'byung ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:9224: drod kyi phyi ma'ang rtags la lam gyi nus pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:9225: stobs che chung gi cha las phyi nang gi rtags
NK077(tsu)001:9227: rdzu 'phrul dag kyang rnam par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:9228: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9232: rtags la gnyis nye bar bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9235: mdor bstan gyi gsum po de la snga ma rtags la dbye na phyi rtags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9236: nang rtags gnyis ste 'og nas ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:9241: phyi rol gyi spyod yul 'di dag chu lta bu
NK077(tsu)001:9242: gcig pur snang zhing gzhan zad pas na zad par
NK077(tsu)001:9244: me dang rlung la sogs 'byung ba bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9245: sngon po la sogs pa'i kha dog bzhi dang zad par brgyad dang dngos su mthong dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9248: kun d+ha'i zhing khams 'od sogs mthong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9249: yang na drod kyi skabs nas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9250: bzod pa phra mo thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9252: zla tshes la sogs mtshan ma mthong /
NK077(tsu)001:9255: phyi rol zad par skye mched dngos su mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9256: pad+mo'i 'od la sogs mthong bar bshad pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:9258: spyir drod rtags gnyis ngo bo gcig kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9260: drod ni rang gi nyams su myong ba'i cha nas bzhag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9261: nges par drod gsum myong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9264: gzhan la mngon du snang ba'i cha ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9265: zad par chu la sogs pa'i lo rgyus bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9271: nang du lus kyi na tsha la sogs pa bzod pa thob pa'i bye brag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9272: nyon mongs pa'i chu bo lnga rgyun la shar yang
NK077(tsu)001:9273: bag kyi bcad de shas chung ngu 'gro ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:9274: / rtags pa'i rkyen gyi ting nge 'dzin mi 'phrog shing /
NK077(tsu)001:9275: ye shes kyi lha mos tsan+dana gyi 'od gus byug kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9276: de la sems mi myos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9277: srin po'i rgyal pos sta re thogs nas byung yang
NK077(tsu)001:9278: mi skrag /ting nge 'dzin nyams su myong yang dga'
NK077(tsu)001:9279: drod med pa'o // sgoms pa'i shugs snang brgyad po mthong ba yang 'byung /
NK077(tsu)001:9280: rnam par snang mdzad kyi spyi bor phyag bzhag pa
NK077(tsu)001:9281: la sogs pa bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad kyi
NK077(tsu)001:9282: cha tsam yang mthong ba'i le'u drug pa ltar 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:9283: ngo // mngon par shes pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:9289: mngon par shes pa rnam pa drug rang bzhin gyis 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9291: spyan gyi mngon par shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9293: pha rol gzhan gyi sems shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9295: sngon gyi gnas shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9296: gdul bya dus la bab ma bab kyi mngon shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:9297: 'di la lam gyi zag pa yod pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9298: med pa'i mngon par shes pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9299: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9301: lam zag gi mngon par shes pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9303: lam gyi mngon shes ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9305: mngon shes la gnyis yod pa'i sngon la zag bcas kyi mngon shes la /
NK077(tsu)001:9307: snying rje'i skabs su yul la dmigs pa ste mdun
NK077(tsu)001:9308: gyi mi gcig la dmigs pa btad nas sgom pas
NK077(tsu)001:9310: de yis ming ni dmigs pa'i mngon shes bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9311: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi skabs su mngon shes nyi
NK077(tsu)001:9312: shu rtsa lnga grangs tsam yongs su rdzogs pa 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:9313: ba yin pas / de'i ming ni yongs su rdzogs pa'i mngon shes zhes bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9314: bar chad med pa'i mngon shes so zhes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9315: lam pa'i ming mngon shes la btags pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9316: tshogs bsgrub ni bar chad med pa'i lam pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9317: mngon shes kyi ming yang bar chad med pa'i mngon shes /
NK077(tsu)001:9319: tshogs bsgrub dang rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin gnyis thun mong gi mngon shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:9320: mngon shes kyi khyad par ro //
NK077(tsu)001:9322: mngon shes yul gyi khyad par /
NK077(tsu)001:9323: de ting gi skabs su lhan gcig drung na 'dug pa'i mi la dmigs pa gtad pas 'gal te /
NK077(tsu)001:9324: gcig gnyis gsum tsam gyi sems shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9325: kun snang gi skabs su de bas gong du 'phel ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9326: bcu tsam gyi sems shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9327: phyag rgya gcig pa las dbang po re res kyang yul lnga lnga gcod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9328: mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga'i grangs tsam rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9329: spros bcas rab kyi gling bzhi mthong zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:9330: 'bring dang tha mas kyang yul tshun chad dang mthong zhing thos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9331: bar chad med pa'i lam tshogs bsgrub pas rab 'bring
NK077(tsu)001:9332: gi gling grangs gnyis dang gsum dang bzhi tshun chad
NK077(tsu)001:9335: sngon gyi gnas shes pa la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9336: gcig spros bar chad med pa'i lam gyi blo'i rim pas phye ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9337: yang na 'dis rtsang nag gi 'brel par /
NK077(tsu)001:9338: de ting dmigs pa'i mngon shes ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9339: mngon shes drug po gcig 'byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:9342: kun ting la de bas gnyis 'gyur tsam du 'phel zhing 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9344: sgo lnga'i rnam shes gcig gis kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9345: yul lnga ka gcod pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:9346: re re la'ang lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK077(tsu)001:9347: rdzogs pa de rnams kyi tha mal pa'i sgo lnga'i
NK077(tsu)001:9348: yul du gyur tshad shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:9349: spros bcas kyi yul khams mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9350: tshogs bsgrub kyi gling grangs mthong zhing thos pas na lam gyi rim pas phye ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9352: de ting gi mngon shes kyi yul dmigs pa'i pha rol po de'i sems 'ga' tsam shes pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9353: yul ngo bo stobs che ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9354: kun ting gi de las gnyis 'gyur du 'phel ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9355: mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9356: yul khams rgya chung ba mthong ba phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9357: rgya che ba mthong ba spros bcas /
NK077(tsu)001:9358: gling grangs gsum tshun chad mthong ba tshogs bsgrub /
NK077(tsu)001:9359: bzhi char mthong zhing thos pa rnam smin te /
NK077(tsu)001:9360: de dag rim pa drug tu phye ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9362: zag med kyi mngon shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:9364: tshe dbang phyag rgya lhun grub kyi mngon shes kyi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9365: zag bcas mngon shes sngon du song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9366: 'dir phyi ma zag med kyi mngon shes la gsum yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9367: dang po mthong lam tshe dbang gi mngon shes kyi yul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9368: stong gsum la gling bzhi la sogs bye ba phrag brgya yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9369: de brgya phrag gcig tshun chad mkhyen pa'i yul du gyur pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9370: gnyis pa sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i mngon shes kyi yul la gnyis kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:9371: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9372: stong gsum gyi stong chen po rang stong phrag bcu la khri la sogs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9373: de'i rdul snyed mkhyen pa'i yul du gyur pa la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9374: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9375: stong gsum gyi stong chen po de nyid gcig du
NK077(tsu)001:9376: brtsis pas de stong phrag bcu la khri de'i rdul
NK077(tsu)001:9377: phra mo'i grangs de snyed dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9378: de yang gnas gzhan drug bcur brtsis pa'i grangs med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9379: grangs med pa de'ang brgya tshan bcu la stong /
NK077(tsu)001:9380: de stong phrag bcu de'i rdul gyi grangs de snyed
NK077(tsu)001:9381: tshun chad sgom lam pa'i mngon shes kyi mkhyen pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:9383: gsum pa mthar lam lhun gyis grub pa'i mngon shes ni rgyal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9384: mngon shes kyi rgya mnyam pas khyad med te /
NK077(tsu)001:9385: nam mkha'i khams chos kyi dbyings su mtha' klas pa tshun chad mkhyen pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9386: 'o na khyad med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:9387: bag la nyal gyi dri ma yod pa dang med pa'i phye bas khyad par yod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9388: mthar lam du smos pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:9389: de ltar na lam pa thams cad kyi mngon shes rdzogs pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9392: lhun grub mthar lam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9393: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi khyad yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9397: rgyu'i byang chub sems dpa' las khyad par du gyur pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9398: zag med kyi mngon shes kyi yul de tsam yin
NK077(tsu)001:9399: pa de bas na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:9400: byang chub sems dpa'i lam gyis dang po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9401: sngags kyi mthong lam tshe dbang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9403: phyag rgya chen po dang rgyu'i sa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:9404: lhun grub dang rgyu'i sa bcu par lam tshod kyi
NK077(tsu)001:9405: skal ba mnyam pa'i phyir na mthong lam sgom lam
NK077(tsu)001:9406: mthar lam gsum du brjod kyi 'on kyang yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:9407: nam khyad par gyi tshul mi 'dra zhing mi mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:9408: ste / ji ltar mi mnyam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:9409: mngon par shes pa'i khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9410: dgongs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9411: gzhi lta ba mtho dman gyi khyad par yod pa'i phye bas /
NK077(tsu)001:9413: 'bras bu'i rig 'dzin la khyad shin tu che ba yod par nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:9415: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho khyad par 'phags /
NK077(tsu)001:9416: lta ba'i sgrib pas phye ba yin ces so //
NK077(tsu)001:9419: de ting stong chen sgom pa 'di yi tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:9420: rdzu 'phrul gyi mthu nyi shu 'byin nus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9422: 'gro ba so so'i skad du chos ston nus pa rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9423: gzhi phyogs drug gi sa g.yo bas /
NK077(tsu)001:9424: nang du sems skyed 'phel bar byed pa chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9425: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad gsang sngags kyi rang
NK077(tsu)001:9426: sgra ti ri ri sgrogs pa kun brjod pa'i cho
NK077(tsu)001:9427: 'phrul te / de ltar cho 'phrul bzhi po yang /
NK077(tsu)001:9428: lam gcig char ba la bzhi ka rdzogs par 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:9429: gi lam rim gyis sgom pa de ting stong chen
NK077(tsu)001:9430: 'di'i tshe 'byung ba'i rgyu tsam yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9431: 'o na ma nges ste dngos su mi 'byung zhe
NK077(tsu)001:9432: na nyams lnga'i tha ma mthar phyin pa'i skabs su
NK077(tsu)001:9433: cho 'phrul bzhi'i cha gcig tsam 'byung ba yang srid
NK077(tsu)001:9434: do // bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:9436: sgrib pa dag cing bden pa mthong ba'i ltas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9438: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lam pa gang dag
NK077(tsu)001:9439: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor de bzhin nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:9440: ting nge 'dzin la blo gnas pa'i rmi lam na
NK077(tsu)001:9441: yang sgrib pa dag pa'i ltas su gcer bur phyungs
NK077(tsu)001:9442: shing lus kyi dri ma dag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9443: chu bo las brgal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9444: mtsho chu la rkyal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9445: gzhan gyi char rgyu gyi 'khru ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9446: gzhan gyi bum chus bdag gi lus la blugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9447: shin tu mtho ba'i ri rtse la lding nas rlung
NK077(tsu)001:9448: gi shin tu g.yeng ba rnams 'di dag sngar zhen
NK077(tsu)001:9449: gyi bag chags byang ba'i ltas yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9451: sgron mor byung dang rtag par 'khru //
NK077(tsu)001:9452: rnam dag chu bo 'bog dang rkyal //
NK077(tsu)001:9453: char rgyun bum chu 'byung ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9454: bsreg dang g.ying dang rnam par 'thor //
NK077(tsu)001:9455: 'di dag bag chags sbyang ba'i bltas //
NK077(tsu)001:9457: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas la byang chub chen po'i mchod rten mthong ba la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9458: de yang byang chub chen po'i mchod rten dkar po bang rim bzhi pa mthong ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9459: tshogs lam gsum pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i dus su bden pa dbyer med nyams su lon zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:9460: 'bras bu'i chos yongs su rdzogs pa thob pa'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:9461: de yang rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:9462: sa rnams thob pa'i snga ltas ni //
NK077(tsu)001:9463: khri rkang dag la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9464: phal pa'i skas la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9465: gyen du shin tu 'gro ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9466: ri bo'i rtse la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9467: mchod rten dag la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9468: nam mkha'i skas la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9469: 'di dag sngon gyi snga ltas yin //
NK077(tsu)001:9471: dbang bskur zhing lung bstan 'byung ba la sogs pa'i rmi ltas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9473: dam pa mchog sangs rgyas dang dam pa byang chub sems dpa' yis /
NK077(tsu)001:9474: dam pa sangs rgyas kyi sras su dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9475: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi spun du dgongs nas byin gyis rlubs so //
NK077(tsu)001:9476: 'di na med kyang lung gra chad la nyal ba zur la bslang ba /
NK077(tsu)001:9477: 'chad pa po'i gnyer bya ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:9478: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams kyi rje bor dgongs nas phrin las bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9479: gzhan yang rmi lam gyi mtshan mar nyams snang bla
NK077(tsu)001:9480: ma 'gro ba'i mgon po mngon sum du snang bas
NK077(tsu)001:9481: bdag nyid la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9483: sogs khung nas chos kyi lung ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9484: rin po che la sogs pa'i khri chen po'i steng la 'jog pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9485: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams ston pa ste byang chub kyi lam du 'dzud pa lnga byed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:9486: yang na khrus byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9491: bka'i gnyer du gtad pa la sogs pa lam du 'dzud pa lnga bya'o //
