NK077(tsu)001:9492: de yang tshogs lam du sgrib pa byang ba'i ltas su bla mas khrus byas ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9493: sbyor lam du chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas su dbang bskur zhing byin gyis rlobs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9494: mthong lam du bden pa mthong ba'i ltas su /
NK077(tsu)001:9495: bla mas khri gdan la bzhag nas chos 'chad pa mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9496: sgom lam du lung bstan thob pa'i ltas su /
NK077(tsu)001:9497: bla mas las dang bya ba gang yang rung ba /
NK077(tsu)001:9499: mthar lam du gzhan don nus pa'i ltas su /
NK077(tsu)001:9500: rang nyid kyi stan la bzhag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9501: gser gyi 'khor lo lag tu gtad nas chos shod cig pa bka' bsgo ba byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9502: byang chub bsgrub pa la bar chad 'byung mi 'byung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9504: nyes pa'i skyon 'byung mi 'byung la sogs pa'i sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9505: lam la brtson 'grus cher gyis shig pa la sogs pa'i lung ston pa rmi lam la 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:9506: de nyid bdun dang cha phye bar bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9508: lung ston pa'i mtshan ltas de yang /
NK077(tsu)001:9510: ting nge 'dzin lam rtags gnyis cha phye dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:9513: rang gi slob dpon du sprul nas byin gyis rlobs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9514: lung ston pa ltar snang ba yang /
NK077(tsu)001:9515: bdud kyi bar chad byung ba nyes byed du ma'i
NK077(tsu)001:9516: bdud slob dpon la sogs par sprul nas 'byung srid
NK077(tsu)001:9517: pa'i phyir / bdud kyi bar chad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9518: ting nge 'dzin gyi rtags gang yin cha brtag pa kun tu gces so //
NK077(tsu)001:9519: de yang phyi'i bar chad bdud la /
NK077(tsu)001:9520: dngos po lta bas ma chun pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9521: rmi lam rang rgyud par bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9522: ha cang re dogs che ba la sogs pas kyang 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:9523: 'o na gzhan la mi 'ong bar chos pa bzang
NK077(tsu)001:9524: po rnams la bdud 'byung ba ci yin zhe na
NK077(tsu)001:9525: / lam la ma zhugs pa dang tshul bzhin yid
NK077(tsu)001:9526: la mi byed pa rnams kho rang gi 'khor du
NK077(tsu)001:9527: / mthong bas / slar srung skyobs byed pa la
NK077(tsu)001:9528: chos pa rnams la mkhos ka ched po med kyang
NK077(tsu)001:9529: / mthong bas / / 'dod khams kyi gtso bo dga' rab dbang phyug gis bltas tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:9530: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa ltar gzhan yang mang po drangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9531: kho rang 'khor med kyi dogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9532: bar du gcod pa'i sbyor ba la brtson nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9533: dper na dgra'i bu chung des /
NK077(tsu)001:9534: de la gnod pa mi 'byung yang /
NK077(tsu)001:9536: bsam sbyor ngan pa byed pa dang 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9538: bdud ni gang las 'byung zhe na //
NK077(tsu)001:9541: ci phyir mi 'grus de nyid bdud //
NK077(tsu)001:9543: de'i bar chad bsal phyir bla ma la zhus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9545: de ltar bdud kyi bar chad de dag bsal ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:9546: phyir gong gi mtshan ma de dag kun gsang na
NK077(tsu)001:9548: rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma nyid la zhus pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:9549: gzhan du dri zhing smra bar bya ba min te gsang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9550: bcu gsum pa phan yon la drug /bgrang /
NK077(tsu)001:9551: dge sdig las kyis mi gos pa'i phan yon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9553: chos nyid de bzhin nyid du lta bas mthong zhing
NK077(tsu)001:9554: ting nge 'dzin goms nas dge sdig gi bag chags
NK077(tsu)001:9555: de dag dang / mi dge gnyis su med par rang 'grol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:9556: bde sdug la sogs pa gang la yang rnam rtog mtshan mar mi 'dzin te /
NK077(tsu)001:9557: chos thams cad rang bzhin ngang ngam ye nas sems
NK077(tsu)001:9558: nyid 'od gsal ba'i ngang du rtogs shing goms pas
NK077(tsu)001:9559: / dge sdig gi rnam smin med pa shin tu'ang bde ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9560: bde sdug gnyis su med par grol ba'i phan yon /
NK077(tsu)001:9562: des na bde ba dang mi bde ba gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:9563: med pas rang byung gi ye shes bde sdug gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:9564: 'dzin gyi chags pa med par rnam par dag pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:9565: // chos rnams thams cad dbyer med rang byung gi
NK077(tsu)001:9566: ye shes yin pa'i don la sems nyid yang phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:9567: 'dzin dri mas ma gos zhing dwangs bas a rab
NK077(tsu)001:9569: gtsang sme gnyis su med pa'i phan yon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9571: 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad la /
NK077(tsu)001:9572: gtsang dang sme ba'i blo ma 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:9573: de gtan tshigs ci'i phyir na thams cad chos nyid ro gcig pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9574: gtsang sme gnyis su med pa shin tu bde ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9575: 'khor ba ma spang rang sar grol ba'i phan yon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9577: shes rab chung ba rim gyis pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9578: chen po gcig char ba'i ting nge 'dzin gsal mi
NK077(tsu)001:9579: gsal lam brtan mi brtan gyi lta sgom spyod pa
NK077(tsu)001:9580: la sogs pa ma nor bar rgyud gzhung lugs bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:9581: rtogs shing sgom na 'khor ba ma spangs par rang
NK077(tsu)001:9582: sar grol bas sdug bsngal bsal du med 'khor 'das
NK077(tsu)001:9583: gnyis su med par rtogs shing yid tshim pas skye
NK077(tsu)001:9584: ba med pa'i don rtogs pas a rab bde zhes
NK077(tsu)001:9585: bya'o // chos nyid mngon gsum du mthong ba'i phan yon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9587: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma lus chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:9588: de bzhin nyid du gcig pa'i ngang yin pas don
NK077(tsu)001:9589: la lta bar bya ba'i yul dang lta bar byed
NK077(tsu)001:9590: pa'i mkhan po gnyis ka med /
NK077(tsu)001:9591: rtogs pa'i ye shes ma rig mun pa sel ba'i sgron ma rgyun mi chad par sbreng ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9592: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad ma bltas par shes
NK077(tsu)001:9593: rab spyan gyis chos nyid bden pa'i don mthong ba'o
NK077(tsu)001:9594: // ma bsgrod par sa non pa'i phan yon no //
NK077(tsu)001:9596: tshe 'di dang pha rol te phyi ma gnyis de
NK077(tsu)001:9597: bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo la gnyis su med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:9598: phyir 'gro dang 'ong bar bya ba min no //
NK077(tsu)001:9599: yan lag bzhi'i stobs chen gang yang ma mchong par
NK077(tsu)001:9600: rig pa mtha' dbus med par phyogs bcu'i khams thams
NK077(tsu)001:9601: cad gnyis su med par mnan no //
NK077(tsu)001:9602: yon tan gyi skabs 'dir sa dmigs drug gi nang na bstan bzhin don chod par gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9603: 'di tshig gis 'bru rgyas par ma byas so //
NK077(tsu)001:9604: bcu bzhi 'da' ka ma la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9608: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di sgom pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:9609: tshe spyod yul 'gyur te 'chi bar mthong na mtshan
NK077(tsu)001:9610: ma'i g.yeng ba ste phyi nang gi 'du 'dzi dang
NK077(tsu)001:9611: / nye 'brel gyi smre sngags la sogs thams cad kun bsal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9612: dngos po yo byad la sogs yod na chos phyogs su 'gro ba'i zhal da byed /
NK077(tsu)001:9613: bla ma dang grogs po bzang po bzhugs na /
NK077(tsu)001:9616: de nas gzhan ci yang yid la mi byed nas gnad gcod kyi zugs zer drag po de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9617: stong pa chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang la dbyer med du gcun cing /
NK077(tsu)001:9618: blo rtse gcig du lhan ne 'dug go //
NK077(tsu)001:9619: de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin de bran pas sngar gyi las ngan gyi bag chags rgyun bcad /
NK077(tsu)001:9620: de'i ngang la 'da' na 'bras bu 'dod khams lha mi'i skye ba khyad par can du skyes nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9621: theg pa chen po'i chos dang 'phrad cing ting nge 'dzin la sbyor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:9622: mtshan bcas kyi 'pho ba'i man ngag go //
NK077(tsu)001:9624: gong du mtshan med kyi 'pho ba song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9625: mtshan bcas ston pas na yang na zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9626: gsang ba'i gser sgrom du zhes pa snying kha chos
NK077(tsu)001:9627: kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab ma brgyad kyi dbus su
NK077(tsu)001:9628: kun gzhi 'od phung kha dog lnga'i ngo bo tshon
NK077(tsu)001:9629: gang ba gcig du bsam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9630: de'i steng du nyon yid zla ba'i dkyi' 'khor du bsam /
NK077(tsu)001:9631: de'i steng du yid shes h'u ring por gcig sgom
NK077(tsu)001:9632: zhing de gsum brtsegs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dmigs
NK077(tsu)001:9633: pa rtse gcig tu brtan pa thob nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9634: dbug gi rlung gis phar 'phro tshur 'dus h'u yig la thim de zla ba la thim /
NK077(tsu)001:9636: mthar 'od phung de nyid phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams cad la khyab par brdal te /
NK077(tsu)001:9637: snang srid thams cad 'od kyi ngo bor khyab cing stong pa'i ngang la 'dug go //
NK077(tsu)001:9641: sgo lnga la sogs skar khung can //
NK077(tsu)001:9642: sgo gcig phyag rgya chen po'i lam //
NK077(tsu)001:9643: sgo brgyad bkag nas sgo gcig phye //
NK077(tsu)001:9644: rnam par shes pa chos nyid 'das //
NK077(tsu)001:9645: ming yang 'pho ba'i gdams ngag zer //
NK077(tsu)001:9646: rlung dus su khegs sam lo tsa ba //
NK077(tsu)001:9648: rtogs ldan pa'i dgongs pa mchan ltar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:9649: yang na mtshan bcas kyi 'pho ba 'debs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:9650: gsang ba'i gser sgrom rtsa dbu ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:9651: rtsa 'di yar sna tshangs pa'i bu ga /mar sna lte 'og sor bzhi'i so na yod /
NK077(tsu)001:9652: tshon gong 'od dang zla ba h'u zhes pa bde rtsa dbu ma'i mar sna na /
NK077(tsu)001:9653: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor tshon gang ba /
NK077(tsu)001:9654: de'i steng du rnam shes kyi ngo bo yi ge h'u sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:9655: spyi bor mda' gang tsam gyi so na bla ma rdo rje 'chang gi rnam pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9656: bla ma'i thugs rje rnam pa 'od zer lcags kyu
NK077(tsu)001:9657: lta bu de char la byung nas h'u la 'khyud
NK077(tsu)001:9658: / h'u mos gus dang ldan pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:9662: bla ma de nyid nam mkha' la 'ja' yal ba bzhin du song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9663: stong nyid spros bral gyi ngang du bzhag pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:9666: gang du 'pho ba yul gyi gnad //
NK077(tsu)001:9668: 'pho tshul don la sbyor tshul gyi gnad gsum yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9669: bla ma'i zhal las shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:9670: las dang po pa la 'pho ba 'di gnad che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9671: las mi dge ba byas zin yin na /
NK077(tsu)001:9672: rlung dang rnam par shes pa yar 'grogs nas 'phos na /
NK077(tsu)001:9673: re zhig lha mi'i go 'phang thob par bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:9674: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9676: 'bras bu chos sku thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9678: don snang stong dbyer med stong chen gyi rnal 'byor la goms pa'i mtha' ma /
NK077(tsu)001:9679: stong pa'i ting nge 'dzin des mngon du byas pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:9680: 'bras bu dbu ma las lhag pa'i chos skur sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:9684: gong gi lhag pa'i chos skur sbyor /
NK077(tsu)001:9685: zer ba 'di brgyud rgyu la dgongs pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:9686: dngos su sbyor ba ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9688: snying rje chen po yan chad /
NK077(tsu)001:9690: mthar lam pa dang khyad med du 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:9691: zhes bsgal tshig khung nas phyung la /
NK077(tsu)001:9693: 'bras bu nyid la lam phyir te //
NK077(tsu)001:9695: spyir gsang sngags kyi lugs kyis 'bras bu lam du byed pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:9696: bye brag 'od gsal de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9697: chos sku'i lam du byed pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:9698: brgyud pa'i 'bras bu la dgongs pa yin gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9699: dngos su thob pa ma yin pas skyon med do //
NK077(tsu)001:9700: 'o na brgyud nas sku gsum mam lnga ka thob pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:9701: chos sku kho na smos pa ci yin zhe na //
NK077(tsu)001:9702: phyogs mthun brjod kyi rim pa yin zhes pas //
NK077(tsu)001:9703: de ting don dam skye med sgom pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:9704: skye med mngon du byed pa'i chos sku gnyis //
NK077(tsu)001:9705: skye ba med pa tsam du phyogs mthun pas //
NK077(tsu)001:9708: sku gzhan la mi sbyor ba'i rgya dang ris su chad pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:9711: rnam pa kun ldan gyi stong pa chen po'i rnal
NK077(tsu)001:9712: 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin bstan pa'i gzhung gi tshig
NK077(tsu)001:9713: don rnams gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don
NK077(tsu)001:9714: gyis na le'u zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9715: yas bgrang gsum pa'i don du gda' 'o ////stong pa chen pa'i rnal 'byor gyi skabs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:9716: lta ba rtogs nas sgom pa yin nam min /
NK077(tsu)001:9717: yin na lam je ngan du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:9718: lta ba bden gsum dbyer med rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9720: lta ba rtogs nas sgom pa min na /
NK077(tsu)001:9721: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid sgom pa ma yin par thal /
NK077(tsu)001:9722: lta ba ma rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9723: 'di rnams kyi mtha' bsal gong du thal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:9724: bco lnga pa 'bras bu 'di chos sku la sbyor ba yin nam min /
NK077(tsu)001:9726: yin na snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor la sogs pa lam gzhan 'gro don med par thal /
NK077(tsu)001:9727: sngon du 'bras bu chos sku thob pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9728: 'di'i mtha' bsal yang gong du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:9729: nyams mthar phyin pa 'di stong pa de bzhin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:9730: kyi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa yin nam min
NK077(tsu)001:9731: / min na gzhung rang dang 'gal te /
NK077(tsu)001:9732: ro myong dor bas de mthar phyin //
NK077(tsu)001:9735: stong pa nyid kyi 'bras bu chos sku thob par thal /
NK077(tsu)001:9736: de thob na lam gzhan bshad pa don med du 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:9738: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor la sbyar ba'i sa mtshams gang nas yin rnams shes dgos la /
NK077(tsu)001:9740: rnam shes tshogs brgyad sa 'tshams gang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9741: gang na dag ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9742: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi nyams mthar phyin pa'i tshad gang yin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9743: gong ma skyon rnams kyis mtha' bsal la sogs pa rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:9744: bshad pa mang po gcig dgos 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9745: yi ger ma bkod bshad pa byed dus ga dar mdzod /
NK077(tsu)001:9746: le'u bzhi pa kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:9748: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9750: don dam stong pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin chos
NK077(tsu)001:9751: kyi sku de nyid rtogs shing goms pa'i ngang la
NK077(tsu)001:9752: phyag 'tshal te / de nyid chos thams cad dngos po med cing stong par rtogs kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9753: stong zhen gyi dri ma bsal dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9754: gdul bya sangs rgyas kyi sa la dgod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9755: snying rje 'di la yul la dmigs pa'i snying rje dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9756: chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje /
NK077(tsu)001:9757: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje dang gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:9758: 'dir dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje yin pas chen
NK077(tsu)001:9759: po ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor bshad par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:9760: // yang na snying rje la dbye na bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9761: phyogs gcig pa'i snying rje dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9762: gtod pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9763: dmigs pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9767: khra dang spyang ku dang mi sdig can gyis kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:9768: bu smad kyi sdug bsngal mthong na snying rje nas rang gi srog 'dor phod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9771: rang rang gi bden bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9772: rten 'brel gyi lam la 'jug pa'i rigs mthun gyi gdul bya la chos ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9773: rdzu 'phrul gyi don shas 'ga' byas nas 'dren pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9774: 'o na snying rje med cing gzhan don mi byed par bshad pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:9775: snying rje ye med pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:9776: shas chung ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9777: gsum pa dmigs pa dang bcas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9779: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:9780: sems can thams cad kyi don mdzad pa de snying rje skye bya'i yul sems can dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9781: skye byed kyi mkhan po rang nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9782: snying rje'i ngo bo gdung ba dang gsum du dmigs shing 'dzin pa dang bcas pa de'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9783: bzhi pa rnam pa dang bcas pa'i snying rje ni ma h+aa'i ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9784: snying rje'i rnam pa tsam yod kyang 'dzin pa med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9785: de la ma h+aa'i rkyen byin na snying rje chen po zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9786: snying rje bya ba'i yul sems can yang rang rgyud pa med de /
NK077(tsu)001:9787: rig pa sgyu mar gsal ba pha rol na med /
NK077(tsu)001:9788: rje byed kyi mkhan po yang sgyu mar gsal bas tshu rol na med /
NK077(tsu)001:9789: snying rje'i ngo bo yang rig pa sgyu mar gsal bas gzhan na med de /
NK077(tsu)001:9790: mngon par gdung ba med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9792: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med gcig rtogs na //
NK077(tsu)001:9793: snying rje chen po skye zhes de la bya //
NK077(tsu)001:9795: de bas na dmigs pa'i zhen pa dang bcas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i snying rje man chad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9796: snying rje chung ngu zhes bya la /
NK077(tsu)001:9797: 'di'i snying rje rnam pa snang ba dang bcas pa
NK077(tsu)001:9798: de la 'dzin zhen med pas chen po zhes bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:9799: // de yang mdo'i brgyad pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:9801: chos thams cad stong pa nyid la rang bzhin gyi gnas pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:9803: snying rje'i yul med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9804: snying po byang chub tu yongs su bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9805: snying rje chen po yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:9806: byams pa'i snying rje dag gis /
NK077(tsu)001:9807: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i sems can srog bton pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9808: gar thar bar bton pa de ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9809: snying rje chung ngur rig par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9811: da res gnyis med kyi ye shes chen po la phyogs ris sam /
NK077(tsu)001:9812: yul yul can med par gsal bas snying rje /
NK077(tsu)001:9813: 'og ma'i snying rje las khyad par 'phags pas chen po'i don /
NK077(tsu)001:9814: rig pa sgyu ma bcos bslad dang bral ba'i rnal ma la /
NK077(tsu)001:9815: lam pa'i blo rtse gcig tu 'byor bar byed pas rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:9816: lus kun tu snang gi don rgyas par bshad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9819: lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9821: kun snang le'u bzhi pa 'di la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:9822: de bzhin nyid dang rjes su mthun pa'i lus don bco lnga nyid kyis mdor bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:9823: 'og nas yan lag rgyas bshad kyi sgo nas shes par gyis shig pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:9824: rgyas par bshad pa la bco lnga de la dang po sngon du 'gro ba la dbye ba med /
NK077(tsu)001:9825: snying rje sgyu ma'i sngon du de ting stong chen la goms pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9826: khams gsum gyi sems can rnams yul yul can du
NK077(tsu)001:9827: 'byed pa med pa'i thugs rje chen pos gnyis med
NK077(tsu)001:9828: du rjes su bzung ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:9829: / tshogs bsags pa'i yan lag brgyad pa sngon de
NK077(tsu)001:9830: ting bzhin du byas nas de'i rjes la ngo bo
NK077(tsu)001:9831: ye shes rang gsal gyi rnam pa sgyu ma lta
NK077(tsu)001:9832: bus khyab pa'i snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK077(tsu)001:9834: gnyis pa dgos ched la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:9837: chos dang gang zag gnyis kyi dri ma bsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9838: de bzhin nyid stong pa la zhen pa'i mdud pa bshig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9839: gdul bya rnams tshad med pa bzhis yang dag pa'i sa la dgod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9840: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rgyur sngon du thob par bya
NK077(tsu)001:9841: zhing gtan tshigs de'i phyir na snying rje chen po'i
NK077(tsu)001:9842: rnal 'byor ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:9843: ni don du gnyer bar bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9844: bden pa gnyis su tha dad du mi gtong ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9845: ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor 'di la gnas par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:9846: 'jug pa'i thun thun mtshams de ting mthar phyin pa'i dus kyi bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9847: yang na 'jug pa'i thun mtshams dus kyi bya /
NK077(tsu)001:9849: snying rje chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:9850: thun che chung gi mtshams nyams mtho dman gang yin
NK077(tsu)001:9851: gyi dus kyi dbye bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9853: 'di ltar g.yo ba'i nyams kyi skabs su /
NK077(tsu)001:9854: nyin zhag 'phrug gcig la dus drug bcu rtsa bzhir
NK077(tsu)001:9855: bcad pas sum bcu rtsa gnyis sgom pa la 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:9856: cing / sum bcu rtsa gnyis bar du ngal baso'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9857: de bzhin du thob pa la sum bcu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9860: mthar phyin pa la bzhir phye nas /
NK077(tsu)001:9864: gnyis la sogs par sgom pa la 'jug pa gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9865: goms brtan na dus kyi gnad chung /
NK077(tsu)001:9867: gong gi bdag gnyis dri ma bsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9868: stong pa'i mdud pa bshigs pa rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:9869: 'bru gnon pas mi chog don rgyud thog na ngos zin dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:9870: gsum pa bzhag thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9877: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor pa gang gi khams
NK077(tsu)001:9878: gsum 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK077(tsu)001:9879: thams cad / dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje chen
NK077(tsu)001:9880: po rigs pa sgyu ma'i ye shes su shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:9881: spyan gyis gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9882: rna bas sgra thos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9885: sna'i tshor ba'ang so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis brtag pa'i rgyus sgom pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:9886: de bzhin nyid sgom pa'i rjes la thob cing sgom par byed pa dang gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:9887: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9889: lta ba'am so sor rtogs pa'i rgyus sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9891: snying rje chen po sgom pa'i lam pa de yis
NK077(tsu)001:9892: 'khor 'das dus gsum gyi bsdus pa'i chos so cog
NK077(tsu)001:9893: lhag ma lus pa thams cad rtag pa ther zug
NK077(tsu)001:9894: pa'i snying po rang rgyud du grub nas yod pa
NK077(tsu)001:9895: ma yin te / ye shes rang gsal sgyu ma
NK077(tsu)001:9896: ltar rtogs pa'i ngang la blo mi g.yo bar bzhag
NK077(tsu)001:9897: ma yin te / pa'o // 'o na sgyu ma ltar rtogs pa ni ji lta bu zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:9898: sgyu ma'i dape'am dngos po drug gi tshul te /
NK077(tsu)001:9900: snang la rang rgyud med pa'i dben pa'i sgyu ma ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9902: snang la ngo bo med mi g.yor te rten 'brel gyi sgyu ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9903: cir yang nges pa sprul pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9905: snang la ma grub par smig rgyu ste dngos po sgyu ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9906: snang la rang bzhin med pas 'ja' tshon ste ye shes sgyu ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9907: gsal la ngos bzung med pas chu zla'i dpe ste phyag rgya sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9908: des na dpe drug gis mtshon pa'i tshul du gcig go //
NK077(tsu)001:9910: snying rje byed mkhan gyi rnal 'byor pa bdag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9911: snying rje'i yul 'gro ba ris drug gi sems can
NK077(tsu)001:9912: thams cad ye shes sgyu ma ru ngo bo gcig
NK077(tsu)001:9913: go // 'o na tha dad du snang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:9914: rkyen gyi 'khrul pa rnams la tha dad du mtshon tshul gyi bsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9915: rtog pa'i blo gnyis su brtags pas bdag dang 'gro ba tha dad pa'i phyir gnyis su snang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:9916: de yang don dam par na ngo bo gcig dang
NK077(tsu)001:9917: tha dad pa gnyis su dbye ba med pas gcig
NK077(tsu)001:9918: tha dad kyi mtha' las grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9919: gnyis su byar med cing gnyis su bya ba'i snang ba yang 'gog pa med par /
NK077(tsu)001:9920: lta ba'i don mthong ba'i ngang la ma shor tsam du bya /
NK077(tsu)001:9921: lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes sam rtog dpyod sngon du btang nas de nas goms par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9922: snga ma goms pa'i rjes su sgom pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9925: ye shes spyi blug tu sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9927: de bas rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9928: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor gnyis la goms pa
NK077(tsu)001:9929: ni snying rje sgyu ma'i rgyu la goms pa sngon
NK077(tsu)001:9931: ye shes sgyu ma sgom snyam du dran pa tsam
NK077(tsu)001:9932: gyis dus gcig char du ting nge 'dzin rang shar
NK077(tsu)001:9934: gcig char ba spyi blugs ltar skad cig gis ye shes sgyu ma yul med du gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9935: de'i sngon du lta ba dran pa'am rtog dpyod la sogs pa btang ba'i rtsol ba gang yang med /
NK077(tsu)001:9936: dper na nam mkha' yul du byar med pa ji bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9937: dmigs med mkha' ltar du sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9939: rang gi lus ngag sems dang phyi nang gi chos
NK077(tsu)001:9940: thams cad rig pa rang snang yin pas blo'i mtshan
NK077(tsu)001:9941: ma gang na'ang mi gnas yul du mi dmigs pas
NK077(tsu)001:9942: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor snang la rang bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:9943: med pas mi g.yor tshul du sbyor ba'i sems nyid
NK077(tsu)001:9944: ji lta bu'i ngo bo yang dmigs su med pa
NK077(tsu)001:9945: mtha' bral stong pa nam mkha' lta bur gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:9946: la ni / blos kyang mi dmigs par rang gsal
NK077(tsu)001:9947: ba sems nyid mtha' dbus dang bral ba nam mkha'
NK077(tsu)001:9949: ma 'gag pa thabs kyis sgom pa /
NK077(tsu)001:9952: chos rnams thams cad ma 'gags par rang snang ba thabs kyis mtshan nyid tsam yin par 'dod te /
NK077(tsu)001:9953: thabs ma 'gags pa la thabs ni ye shes sgyu
NK077(tsu)001:9954: ma'i ting nge 'dzin gnyis su med par rtogs pas
NK077(tsu)001:9956: ye shes sgyu ma thabs chen sgoms pas thabs de
NK077(tsu)001:9957: las ye shes sgyu ma mngon sum du 'byung ba
NK077(tsu)001:9958: yin / de ni bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK077(tsu)001:9959: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor dbyer med pas rdo
NK077(tsu)001:9961: snying rje'i khyad par la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:9963: tshad med pa bzhi'i khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9965: shes bya phyi nang gi chos thams cad du ni ye shes sgyu mar rang gsal ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:9966: ye shes sgyu ma ma yin pa'i chos 'ga' tsam
NK077(tsu)001:9967: yang yod pa min pas ma bu la gdung ba
NK077(tsu)001:9968: dang 'dra bar ma bsgral dus gcig bsgral ba de
NK077(tsu)001:9969: ni ye shes kyi mtshon gyis dngos su bsad pa
NK077(tsu)001:9971: de gnyis su med pa'i bsgral bas /
NK077(tsu)001:9972: gsang chen snying rje chen po'i rang bzhin te /
NK077(tsu)001:9973: de tsam na gdul bya gdul byed gnyis su mi
NK077(tsu)001:9974: 'byed par sems can rnams la phan pa rdzogs par
NK077(tsu)001:9975: byed pa'i cha nas tshad med pa'i byams pa chen
NK077(tsu)001:9976: po'o // thams cad ye shes sgyu mar mngon gsum par sangs rgyas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:9977: 'gro ba'i don la mi 'gyed cing dga' ba ni dga' ba'i chos ste dga' ba tshad med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9978: ye shes sgyu ma de dang 'du 'bral med pas na gtang snyoms tshad med pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:9979: 'di ye shes rang gsal nyid la tshad med bzhi rdzogs lugs yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:9980: de ltar tshangs pa'i rgyu tshad med bzhi dus gcig ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:9981: theg pa 'og ma ltar yul yul can gyi mngon par gdung ba de la med do //
NK077(tsu)001:9982: snying rje yul gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9984: theg pa 'og ma ltar yul yul can gyi mngon
NK077(tsu)001:9985: par gdung ba med pa de'i phyir theg pa 'og
NK077(tsu)001:9986: ma pa 'khor ba'i rgyu ma rig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9987: rkyen las dang nyon mongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9988: 'bras bu sdug bsngal zhing nyams thag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9989: dus thog ma med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9990: rang bzhin de ma yin la der 'dzin pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:9991: mi rtag skye 'jig can gyi 'khrul pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9992: 'khrul tshul rten 'brel bcu gnyis rgyun gyi 'khor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9993: nyes pa 'phags pa'i lam dang bral zhing sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9994: ngo bo 'gro ba ris drug gis snod bcud sna tshogs su zhen pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9995: dpe thar dka' bas na brtson gyi ra ba lta bu ste 'bras bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:9996: ngo bo gcig tu bsdus pas brgyad du 'dod pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:9997: de dang ldan pa'i yul sems can rnams la dmigs
NK077(tsu)001:9998: nas tshad med bzhi skye ba rgyu'i theg pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:9999: / sngags kyi snying rje chen po de yis yul
NK077(tsu)001:10000: yul can med par chos kun gcig par shes pas
NK077(tsu)001:10001: / / theg pa 'og ma'i tshad med bzhi sngags
NK077(tsu)001:10002: kyi tshad med bzhi'i snying rje chen po gcig gis
NK077(tsu)001:10003: rdzogs shing tshang bar 'byung ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10004: pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshad med pa bzhi ngo bo tha dad pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:10005: yul yul can du 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10006: sngags kyi tshad med bzhi ngo bo mi gcig cing /
NK077(tsu)001:10007: yul yul can gnyis su med par 'dod pa'i phyir de gnyis mtshungs pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:10009: bzhi pa sgom pa'i ngo bo la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10013: kun ting snying rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK077(tsu)001:10014: ting nge 'dzin de dag rang gi ngo bo nyid
NK077(tsu)001:10015: bstan pa'ang / gang zhe na don gyi rnam grangs
NK077(tsu)001:10016: bzhin du 'dir yang ming gi rnam grangs kyang 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:10017: bstan pa'ang / ste / de'i lugs ni ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:10018: bsgom bya don gyi ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10019: sgom byed rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel pa yis /
NK077(tsu)001:10020: bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis su phye bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:10021: zung gcig ya gnyis su 'gyur la /
NK077(tsu)001:10022: zhor la sgom pa'i nges tshig dang gsum du 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:10023: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10027: bsgom bya don gyi ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10028: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10030: sgyu ma'i ngo bo drug gis dmigs rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10031: sgyu ma rang snang gnyis med dgos ched dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10035: mdor bstan la gsum yod pa de la de ma
NK077(tsu)001:10036: yin la der 'dzin pa'i log rtog sgyu ma ni
NK077(tsu)001:10039: kun btags kyi dngos po rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:10040: ngo bo yod pa ni bdag dang srog dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10041: byed po la sogs kun tu brtags pa'i gnyis 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:10042: gyi rnam par rtog pa sgyu ma'i klong gyur pa
NK077(tsu)001:10043: / log rtog gis blo la skyes kyang rigs pas
NK077(tsu)001:10044: brtag cing don mthong na mi bden bslu bas sgyu
NK077(tsu)001:10048: dper na rten cing 'brel pa'ang shing rta'i 'khor lo
NK077(tsu)001:10049: bzhin te 'jig rten pa'i rnam rtog 'di rnams dngos
NK077(tsu)001:10050: por mi bden par gzugs brnyan dang 'dra ba'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:10051: / sgyu ma'i rta glang la sogs pa lta bur 'khrul pa'i rgyu rkyen las skyes pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10052: 'khrul snang gi bya ba me chus btso bsreg la sogs pa kun byed kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:10053: rtog can ste blo 'khrul pa can rnams la mthun par zad /
NK077(tsu)001:10054: gzugs brnyan 'dra phyir brtag pas dben /
NK077(tsu)001:10055: de phyir thams cad rdzun par tsam ni go sla'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10056: gtan tshigs de'i phyir na ming tsam las dngos po med de /
NK077(tsu)001:10057: rang rgyud du 'dod pa min no //
NK077(tsu)001:10060: yang dag nyid du bden par grags so cog gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:10061: su snang ba'i dus nyid na phyogs gcig pa gang
NK077(tsu)001:10062: yang min pas / sems nyid rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:10063: ji ltar snang yang ngo bo rgyu rkyen med par
NK077(tsu)001:10064: rang 'char bas rig pa sna tshogs su snang la
NK077(tsu)001:10065: rang gi ngo bo phyogs gcig pa gang du yang
NK077(tsu)001:10067: ji ltar ltas pa'i snang ba gang yang shar rung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10068: snang bzhin du don dang phyogs gcig par ther zug ste rtag pa med la /
NK077(tsu)001:10069: snang cha gang yang mi 'gags pas chad pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10072: rgyal ba'i sku yang rgyu rkyen gzhan gyis ma bskyed par /
NK077(tsu)001:10073: rig pa'i ye shes sgyu mar shar /
NK077(tsu)001:10074: khams gsum pa'ang de bzhin yin pas ma 'gags pa thabs chen sgyu ma /
NK077(tsu)001:10078: chos kun ye shes nyid la ni ye shes nyid rol /
NK077(tsu)001:10079: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang dngos po med pas gsog zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10082: rgyal ba'i sku mngon gsum du byung nas 'gro ba skyobs zhing phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10084: chos ston pa'ang gong gi de bzhin te ther zug pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:10085: rgyu ma gnyis med rang snang dgos ched dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10087: de rnams kyang rang byung ye shes rang snang bas
NK077(tsu)001:10088: rgyu rkyen rag lus pa med pa'i phyir snang ba
NK077(tsu)001:10089: nyid na 'jigs pa med pas sgyu ma rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:10090: ste btsan pa'i mchog des na 'dus ma byas kyi
NK077(tsu)001:10091: kun rdzob tu 'dus byas su snang ba'i dus de
NK077(tsu)001:10092: nyid na dbyer med rdo rje nyid yin pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:10093: / ngo bo bden gnyis tha dad med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10094: 'o na bden pa gnyis re mos su sgom pa ci yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:10095: dman pa la rim pa ltar stong pa chen po'i
NK077(tsu)001:10096: rnal 'byor la sogs pa snang bar goms byed tsam
NK077(tsu)001:10098: de ltar na sgom pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10099: don gyi rnam grangs thun mong du bstan pa 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:10100: sgyu ma'i dngos po drug /don dam la dbyer med du bstan pa dang bdun te /
NK077(tsu)001:10101: dang po sgyu ma'i dngos po drug ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10104: yang dag rig pa sgyu ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10108: de la log rtog sgyu ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10109: bdag gzhan dgra gnyen du snang bas log rtog go //
NK077(tsu)001:10110: mi bden zhing bslu bas sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10111: gnyis pa rten 'brel gyi sgyu ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10112: snang ba 'di dag rgyu rkyen rten 'brel las byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10116: yang dag par stong pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:10118: gsum pa yang dag rig pa sgyu ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10119: 'di ltar du snang ba thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:10120: rang rig ye shes kyi snang ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:10121: snang tsam na ngo bo grub pa med de /
NK077(tsu)001:10122: ther zug rtag chad kyi mtha' las grol bas sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10123: bzhi pa phyag rgya sgyu ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10124: rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgya chen por ma 'gags pa gsal la /
NK077(tsu)001:10125: lha rang rgyud par ma grub pas sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10126: lnga pa thabs sgyu ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10127: snang ba 'di 'gags med sna tshogs su shar bas thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:10128: de la rang rgyud pa med pas sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10129: drug pa ye shes sgyu ma ni thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes sgyu ma'i snang ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:10130: rang rig tu snang tsam na rang rgyud du med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10131: bdun pa don la bden pa dbyer med ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10132: sgyu ma'i rnam grangs ji snyed brjod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:10133: don la bden pa gnyis su med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10134: de dag chos can tshar non lta bu gcig la sbyar na /
NK077(tsu)001:10135: tshar non gyi dbyibs kha dog tu snang ba log rtog /de rang rgyud pa med pas sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10136: 'di ka rgyu rkyen rten 'brel las 'byung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:10137: rang rgyud med pas rten 'brel sgyu ma /
NK077(tsu)001:10138: de ka sems nyid snang ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10139: ngo bo med bzhin snang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10140: ther zug rtag chad kyi mtha' las grol bas /
NK077(tsu)001:10142: 'di ka bskyed rim lha sku sgom pa rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:10143: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por snang zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:10144: snang ba rang rgyud pa med pas phyag rgya sgyu ma /
NK077(tsu)001:10145: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid dbyibs kha dog du ma 'gags par shar bas thabs sgyu ma /
NK077(tsu)001:10146: 'di ka rang rig ye shes sgyu ma cis kyang
NK077(tsu)001:10147: ma sgrib par rang gsal ba las ma g.yos shing
NK077(tsu)001:10148: / rang rgyud pa med pas ye shes sgyu ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10149: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10151: 'gro ba sems can gyi rgyud la shes pa'i rgyu
NK077(tsu)001:10152: skad gcig ma gcig la nyon mongs pa dang ye
NK077(tsu)001:10153: shes gnyis mi ldan cing skad cig ma la rtog
NK077(tsu)001:10154: pa gnyis mi 'jug pas rgyun chad la rtog pa
NK077(tsu)001:10155: snga ma 'gags phyi ma ma skyes da lta skyes
NK077(tsu)001:10157: gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral ba'i rang rig pa nyid ye shes sgyu mar mi g.yo bas zhi gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:10158: ma bsgrib par rang gsal ba lhag mthong /
NK077(tsu)001:10159: dper na chu dang zla ba ji bzhin du zhi
NK077(tsu)001:10160: gnas lhag mthong mtshungs par gsal ba ye shes sgyu
NK077(tsu)001:10164: ji ltar snang yang sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos med phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:10165: ye shes sgyu ma gzhan na sgom du med /
NK077(tsu)001:10166: ye shes sgyu ma nyid kyang gnyis su med cing
NK077(tsu)001:10167: chags zhen bral ba'i ngang la gnas pas tha snyad
NK077(tsu)001:10169: lnga pa mi mthun pa'i skyon la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10173: kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin dang mi mthun pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:10174: sgrib pa'i skyon gyi dmigs bzung ba ni gsum ste
NK077(tsu)001:10176: skyon bskyed par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10177: skyon rang gi ngo bo dang skyon dbang du song
NK077(tsu)001:10178: ba'i nyes pa bstan pa dang gsum ni 'og nas
NK077(tsu)001:10180: rgyas dang bshad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:10184: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang la ma goms pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10185: ched du bcos nas brtson 'grus byed pa'i skyon 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10186: dper na rgyu me yod pa dang 'bras bu du
NK077(tsu)001:10187: ba'i tshul bzhin du ma goms pa dang 'bras bu
NK077(tsu)001:10189: bsgom bya sgom byed bdag tu 'dzin pa rnam gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:10190: kyi ting nge 'dzin la bsgrib pa'i skyon 'byung bar
NK077(tsu)001:10191: byed pa'o // ngo boo la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10192: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo la gnas pa'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10196: spyi'i skyon nyung dang 'bring bar bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10198: ye shes sgyu ma'i sngon du de ting stong pa
NK077(tsu)001:10199: chen po'i ting nge 'dzin ji bzhin pa nyid la
NK077(tsu)001:10202: 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig pa gnyis kyi mtshams sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:10203: ba'i snying rje sgyu ma 'di skyon ma rtul te
NK077(tsu)001:10205: skyon 'byung la 'on kyang de ting gi skabs su
NK077(tsu)001:10206: brjod pa'i skyon gyi bye brag kun de ting bas
NK077(tsu)001:10208: grangs bag tsam gyi nyung bar 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:10210: skyon gyi rkyen rnams sngar spang zhing de bzhin nyid
NK077(tsu)001:10211: goms pa'i tha mal gyi skyon rags pa sngar bas
NK077(tsu)001:10212: dkon no // khyad par gyi skyon /
NK077(tsu)001:10214: 'dir skyon ye med pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:10215: kun snang rang gi skyon cha shas tsam 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:10217: kun snang 'di nyid sgom dus su rgod pa'i skyon sems yul la 'phro ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10218: bying ba'i skyon nang du sdud pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10219: yul gang yin ma nges pa'i sa phyogs khang khyim bcas pa mthong nas sems shor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10220: me chu la sogs zad par gyi skye mched mthong nas slar sems bred pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10221: kha dog gcig tu ma nges pa'i mdog mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10226: sa bad kan ste 'byung ba bzhi'i khams kyi cha
NK077(tsu)001:10227: 'khrugs ste 'khrul bas don mi gsal bas kha dog
NK077(tsu)001:10228: gam mdog ste / mkhris pa la ser po'am ljang ku /
NK077(tsu)001:10230: rlung la sngo skya'am skya bo /
NK077(tsu)001:10231: bad kan smug po la sogs pa'i kha dog du mthong na khams 'khrugs pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:10232: rtog pa'i skyon gang yin blta bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10233: sa g.yogs pa mthong ba'ang 'byung ba bzhi'i sa g.yos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10234: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis g.yos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10238: khams 'khrugs pa gang yin gyi cha dbye bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10241: nam mkha' dwangs ba la sprin gyis nyi ma bsgrib pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10242: ling rtog gis mig bsgrib pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10243: mun pas rdzas mi gsal ba bsgrib pa bzhin du
NK077(tsu)001:10244: skyon gyi rnam pa gong ma gong yang rung ba
NK077(tsu)001:10245: de dag rgyud gzhung la grags pa thun mong dang
NK077(tsu)001:10246: khyad par gyi skyon gyi bye brag phra ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:10247: rags pa'i chas / ye shes sgyu ma'i don ngo
NK077(tsu)001:10248: bo mi gsal zhing nyams skye ba shin tu bul
NK077(tsu)001:10249: bar byed pa'i skyon yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:10250: drug pa bcos thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10251: ngo bo'i skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10255: nyams kyi blo la dang sbyar te bcos thabs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:10257: blo rab la rang byung rang zhir bzhag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10259: sngon de ting gi skabs su bstan pa bzhin du
NK077(tsu)001:10260: rnam par rtog pa'i nad skyon bcos pa ni 'di
NK077(tsu)001:10261: lta ste / rab la shes bzhin gyi bya ra
NK077(tsu)001:10262: bas so 'thas chod par byas la skyon ngos bzung
NK077(tsu)001:10263: lta ste / ngo // de ltar tshor bar 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:10264: na rkun po mthong ba dang bros pa'i tshul bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:10265: du skyon de rnams ched du ma bsal bar rang
NK077(tsu)001:10266: bzhin gyi shes pas dngas te med par 'gyur ro
NK077(tsu)001:10267: lta ste / ngo // // de ltar rnam rtog mtshan ma ci skyes kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:10268: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang phyir ting nge 'dzin la chags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10270: yon tan la re ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10271: skyon 'byung gi dogs pa mi 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10272: ci'i phyir na ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin las gzhan du min no //
NK077(tsu)001:10273: 'bring la rtog pa'i gnas yul bltas te bcos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10275: rab kyi skyon rnams rang zhi rang dag tu bstan pa de song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:10276: 'bring gi rnam rtog rang ngo la bltas ba ston pas yang na zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10278: rtogs pa'i gnas yul lta ste rtog pa de rang
NK077(tsu)001:10279: gang yin ltas pas de'i rang bzhin mthong bas skyon
NK077(tsu)001:10280: mun pa rnam dag ste sangs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10281: tha ma lo rgyus bya ste bcos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10283: gang gi de ltar ma ldan na /
NK077(tsu)001:10284: rnal 'byor pa gang dag gis skyon de dag gang
NK077(tsu)001:10285: byung tshor nas skyon de rnams dang po gang na
NK077(tsu)001:10287: ngo bo la gzugs dbyibs kha dog grub pa ci snang lo rgyus kyi dpyad pas zhi ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10288: rgod pa'i skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10290: sngon de ting bzhin sngar 'das kyi dran pa'i rjes su blo 'brang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10291: phyi ma 'ong pa'i sngon bsu bar byed pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:10292: gong gi de ltar rang bzhin gyi rkyen gyi rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:10293: shing rgod na shes bzhin gyi bya ra bas rtog
NK077(tsu)001:10294: pa tshor na 'khor ba'i thog mtha'i nyes pa bsam
NK077(tsu)001:10295: ste 'khor ba la skyo ba bskyed pas skyon rnams
NK077(tsu)001:10296: dor te / dran pa'i thag pas bcing ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:10297: bying ba'i skyon bcos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10299: gang zhig sgom pa'i tshe sems nang du thim ste bying rmugs su song na /
NK077(tsu)001:10301: bskor ba bya zhing lus bcags par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:10303: sgom pa'i drod rtags la brod pas ting nge 'dzin la 'jug cing sems /
NK077(tsu)001:10305: khams kyi skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10307: rang gi 'dod pa min pa'i kha dog lnga la
NK077(tsu)001:10308: sogs pa ma nges shing mi gsal ba mthong bas
NK077(tsu)001:10309: na / 'byung ba rlung mkhris bad kan 'du ba bzhi'i gnyen po ste sman dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10310: zas kyi bcos la gzhil bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10315: gong du bstan pa de ltar blo bzhag thabs kyis
NK077(tsu)001:10316: bzhag /skyon byung na bcos thabs kyis de ltar bcos
NK077(tsu)001:10317: shing brtson 'grus kyis sgom par 'gyur ba'i skabs su
NK077(tsu)001:10318: ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor nyid kyi nyams gong
NK077(tsu)001:10319: nas gong du 'phel ba'ang lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10325: mthar phyin pa'i nyams kyi bogs 'og nas gong du
NK077(tsu)001:10326: 'gro ba sgom bya don gyi ngo bo ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:10328: sgom byed blo'i sgrib pa rab rib dag ma dag
NK077(tsu)001:10329: gi tshogs che chung gi chas nyams kyi rim pa
NK077(tsu)001:10330: lngar brjod pa'o // rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:10334: ting nge 'dzin la blo rtse gcig tu mi sdod
NK077(tsu)001:10335: bar 'phro zhing yul so sor 'gyes pas rgod pa
NK077(tsu)001:10336: dang / nang du thim pas bying ba'i skyon rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:10337: dper na rlung drag pos ded pa'i chu'i gnyer ma dang 'dra bar don la blo gnas pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:10338: ting nge 'dzin dang rtog pa 'dres mar cung zad yod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10339: nyin zhag gcig la thun drug bcu rtsa bzhir phye
NK077(tsu)001:10340: ba'i thun gyi tshad gcig gi sum gnyis rtog pa
NK077(tsu)001:10341: rgyu ba dang / sum char rtog pa dang chos nyid 'dres mar yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10344: nyin zhag gcig la thun so gnyis bgos pa'i thun
NK077(tsu)001:10345: gcig gi bzhi cha'am lnga'i char rtog pa de med
NK077(tsu)001:10346: cing chos nyid 'ba' zhig rgyu la /
NK077(tsu)001:10349: rtog pa dang chos nyid 'dres mar rgyu bas na thob pa'i nyams so //
NK077(tsu)001:10350: 'o na thob pa'i nyams kyi skabs su /
NK077(tsu)001:10351: g.yo ba'i nyams las zhan du song ngam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:10352: zhan du song ba ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:10354: sum gnyis rtog pa kho na rgyu zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:10355: sum cha la yang chos nyid dang rtog pa 'dres mar rgyu la /
NK077(tsu)001:10357: thun yang gnyis 'gyur gyi che zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:10359: lnga char chos nyid 'ba' zhig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10363: rtog pa dang chos nyid 'dres mar rgyu bas dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:10367: nyams rtogs kyi ting nge 'dzin 'byung la /
NK077(tsu)001:10369: lnga char rtog pa'i dbang du 'gro ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10372: nyin zhag gcig la bcu drug tu bgos pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:10373: cha gcig la thun rer byas pas thun rkyang tsam
NK077(tsu)001:10374: du rtog pa med par sgom nus shing chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:10376: rtog pa'i dbang du cang du 'gro ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10379: phus btab pa'i tshul bzhin du gnas pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:10380: 'di la rnam rtog 'og 'gyu'i skyon yod pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:10383: sgo brten pa'i rdzas rkyang 'den bcug na rlung gis
NK077(tsu)001:10384: mi bsgul ba ltar zhag gcig la brgyad du bgos
NK077(tsu)001:10385: pa'i thun rer rnam par rtog pa'i rlung gi ting
NK077(tsu)001:10386: nge 'dzin mi 'gul bar gzhi ma rig pa sgyu
NK077(tsu)001:10387: ma la brten par gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10388: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams /
NK077(tsu)001:10390: chos nyid la gsal ba'i tshad mig gzugs la blta
NK077(tsu)001:10391: ba ltar dbang po'i mngon gsum du phyi rol gyi
NK077(tsu)001:10392: yul snang gang snang bar gsal bar byas pa de
NK077(tsu)001:10393: bzhin du / don ye shes sgyu ma la skyed
NK077(tsu)001:10394: 'don zhing bogs dbyung du bya ba med pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:10395: bzhin du / / nyams lnga'i tha ma mthar phyin pa'i nyams zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10396: yang na shes rab kyi dbang pa'i mngon gsum du gang byas pa skyed du byar med /
NK077(tsu)001:10398: brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10401: snying rje chen po ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10402: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems ni srid gsum
NK077(tsu)001:10403: 'khor ba'i sems nyid dam ye shes sgyu ma dang
NK077(tsu)001:10404: 'dra bar ni / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK077(tsu)001:10405: rgyas bla na med pa'i byang chub la mkhas pas
NK077(tsu)001:10406: shes pa ltar shes par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:10407: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems 'gro ba sems can rnams 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i ched du /
NK077(tsu)001:10408: gzhan don gyi go cha bgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:10409: 'gro ba drug po yang gong gi de ltar snga ma ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10410: ye gdod ma nas shes te /
NK077(tsu)001:10411: ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor du shes pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10412: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10413: ye shes sgyu mar shes pa'i gzhi la spyod pa
NK077(tsu)001:10414: dang de yang 'gro ba'i ched du spyod thabs so
NK077(tsu)001:10417: sngon byung rgyal ba'i rjes shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10419: gzung 'dzin gnyis kyi log par rtog cing der brtag
NK077(tsu)001:10420: cing kun brtag rnam par dag par rtog cing mkhyen
NK077(tsu)001:10421: pa'o // chos kun ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan pa'i phyir dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10422: sems can gyi las dang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje
NK077(tsu)001:10423: chen po 'brel pas na 'gro drug dus gnas ma
NK077(tsu)001:10425: sngon byung rgyal ba'i rjes su ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK077(tsu)001:10426: rnal 'byor 'jug pa la de bzhin du shes par
NK077(tsu)001:10427: bya'o // ye shes sgyu mar shes pa dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10429: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings de sna
NK077(tsu)001:10430: tshogs mang po ma 'gags pa'i thabs su cir yang
NK077(tsu)001:10431: snang / ma 'gag pa'i thabs su snang ba nyid
NK077(tsu)001:10432: rang rgyud pa gang yang med de sgyu ma dang
NK077(tsu)001:10434: chu zla gzugs brnyan gyi tshul bzhin du snang la rang bzhin med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10435: de nyid rang rig ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor
NK077(tsu)001:10436: snang bas gang yang chags pa med cing sna tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:10438: de la gnas pa'i yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:10440: snang ba thabs dang rang bzhin med pa shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:10441: dang ldan pa'i de nyid yon tan mchog gi gnas
NK077(tsu)001:10443: de ltar rtogs pa'i gang zag des //
NK077(tsu)001:10444: ji ltar spyad kyang yon tan zad med 'byung zhing
NK077(tsu)001:10445: tshogs gnyis kyis bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis 'grub pa
NK077(tsu)001:10446: dang / sgrib pa gnyis kyi gos par mi 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:10447: shes rab dang thabs chen po'i theg pa mchog gi
NK077(tsu)001:10448: don ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang ye nas rol pa
NK077(tsu)001:10449: yin no // 'gro ba'i ched du spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10454: chos kun byang chub sems su gcig pas rtsa ba'i snying rje dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10456: chos kun byang chub sems su rgyu gcig pas bdag
NK077(tsu)001:10457: dang 'gro kun gnyis su med par gzungs kyi zin
NK077(tsu)001:10458: pa'i rtsa ba'i snying rje chen po 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10460: de la snying rje'i nges tshig med do snyams pa la sangs rgyas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10461: sems can kun ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor gcig
NK077(tsu)001:10462: par rtogs na rtsa ba'i snying rje chen po skye
NK077(tsu)001:10464: de'i dus su rig pa la mtha' dbus med pas bdal chen blo ni kun tu snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10465: snying rjes phan 'dogs shing skyobs pas byams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10467: gdul bya 'dul ba'i ma 'gag pa thabs chen pos
NK077(tsu)001:10468: 'gro ba kun gyi don mdzad pa'i rig pa 'od
NK077(tsu)001:10469: gsal la byams pa tshad med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10470: 'gro ba thams cad dgyes par mdzad cing phyogs ris med pas dbyings ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10471: de yang byams pa chen po de chos nyid la
NK077(tsu)001:10472: ma g.yos bzhin du ma bu la gdung ba ltar
NK077(tsu)001:10474: 'gro drug gi sems can ma lus pa thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:10475: la brtse ba'i snying rje'i thag pa dang 'dra ba
NK077(tsu)001:10476: ma chad par 'gro ba nyon mongs 'khor ba'i lam
NK077(tsu)001:10477: de las mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam du 'gro
NK077(tsu)001:10478: bar byed cing byams pa dag gis phan thogs shing
NK077(tsu)001:10479: 'gro ba kun la skyobs pa'i sgo nas mnyes par
NK077(tsu)001:10480: gyis shig pa'o // 'gro ba'i don la mi skyo zhing dga' bas dga' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10482: de bzhin du 'khor ba'i brtson ra dang 'dra ba'i sems can la /
NK077(tsu)001:10483: chos nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du brtse ba'i snying
NK077(tsu)001:10484: rje'i zhags pa cher brkyang nas 'gro ba nyon mongs
NK077(tsu)001:10485: 'dam dang 'dra ba'i nang nas thar pa'i skam sar
NK077(tsu)001:10487: snying rje chen po zhags pa dang 'dra bar cher
NK077(tsu)001:10488: brkyang nas 'khor ba nyon mongs pa'i gnas nas 'dren
NK077(tsu)001:10489: par byed pa'i snying rje tshad med pa des /
NK077(tsu)001:10490: 'gro ba'i don byed pa la skyo bar ma byed
NK077(tsu)001:10491: cig /snying rje skye ba de bzhin du skye bo
NK077(tsu)001:10493: las kyi sgrib pas mi gos shing ngan song las thar ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10494: sems can thams cad mngon par sangs rgyas par bya
NK077(tsu)001:10495: ba'i don la dga' bas dga' ba dag la 'gyod
NK077(tsu)001:10496: par ma byed cig /phyogs ris med par snyoms pas
NK077(tsu)001:10498: khams gsum gyi sems can kun gzhi chos nyid la
NK077(tsu)001:10499: nga dang bdag med la rnal 'byor pa'i thugs rjes
NK077(tsu)001:10500: nga dang bdag gnyis su med rtog pas mi 'byed
NK077(tsu)001:10501: de / bu gcig pa la ma byams pa 'dra bar blo bzhag bya /
NK077(tsu)001:10502: sems can thams cad la phyogs ris dri med par btang snyoms la gnas par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10503: gong bzhin bdag don la gzhan don rdzogs par bstan pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:10505: lam gyi sngon du tshad med pa bzhi rdzogs ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10507: stong chen sngon du rdzogs pa'i don bya ba'i rkyen
NK077(tsu)001:10508: gdul bya dang 'phrad na gzhan don gyi spyod pa
NK077(tsu)001:10509: byed pa sngon de ting gi skabs bzhin du byas
NK077(tsu)001:10510: te / de yang snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:10511: sgom pa'i bdag don nyid la gdul bya gzhan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:10512: don shugs kyis rdzogs par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10513: 'og ma las khyad par dpag tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:10515: de yang rgyu'i theg pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10516: 'bras bu'i theg pa'i khyad par ston te /
NK077(tsu)001:10517: dmigs pa bdun gnyis gdul bya la //
NK077(tsu)001:10518: ngo bo las dang phan yon gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:10519: phyogs gtad med de thun mong gi //
NK077(tsu)001:10520: chen po dag la blar gyur yin //
NK077(tsu)001:10522: mtshan nyid theg pa'i snying rje dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10523: 'di nyid kyi snying rje gnyis shan phye ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:10524: 'di las nang tshegs su bcad na lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10525: dmigs pa yul gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10529: phyogs gtad yod med kyi khyad par ro //
NK077(tsu)001:10530: dang po ni rgyu'i theg pa /
NK077(tsu)001:10531: de phyir rgyu rkyen 'bras bu dang //
NK077(tsu)001:10532: dus dang rang bzhin 'khrul pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:10533: tshul gyi nyams dang ngo bo dang //
NK077(tsu)001:10534: brtson rar lta bur brgyad la dmigs //
NK077(tsu)001:10535: zhes 'byung bas 'khor ba'i sems can gyi rgyu gcig
NK077(tsu)001:10536: /rkyen gnyis 'bras bu dang ngo bo gcig tu brtsis
NK077(tsu)001:10539: nyes pa dang drug /rang bzhin 'khrul pa dang bdun
NK077(tsu)001:10540: po de la dmigs nas thugs rje skye ba'i yul
NK077(tsu)001:10541: rgya chung la / 'dir de'i steng du nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:10542: phyi rgyud sde gsum ste gnyis bsnan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10543: bdun gnyis bcu bzhi po de /
NK077(tsu)001:10544: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i gdul bya yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10545: dmigs pa yul rgya che ba'i khyad par yod te /
NK077(tsu)001:10546: dper na rjee 'bangs gnyis nor 'gran pa lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10548: 'dir 'gro ba drug /mu steg rtag chad gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10550: phyi rgyud sde gsum dang bdun gnyis bcu bzhi dmigs nas skye bar bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:10553: gdul bya'i yul dmigs pa bdun gyi sems can la snying rje byed kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:10554: mkhon nas yul du byed na skye bas tha dad la /
NK077(tsu)001:10555: 'dir rig pa sgyu ma'i ngang du yul yul can dbyer med du rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10558: rgyu'i theg pas gdul bya'i don byed tsa na /
NK077(tsu)001:10559: rtogs pa sngon du btang nas don byed pa /
NK077(tsu)001:10560: 'dir brtsis gdabs kyi rtog pa sngon du ma btang bar rtog pa med par don byed pa /
NK077(tsu)001:10562: yang rgyu'i theg pa'i snying rje ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10563: snying rje kho na'i don byed las mi nus la /
NK077(tsu)001:10564: 'dir snying rje gcig pus kyang tshad med bzhi ka'i don byed nus pas 'phags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10566: don byas pa'i 'bras bu la khyad par yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:10567: rgyu'i theg pas gdul bya drangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10568: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyis sangs rgyas sku gsum
NK077(tsu)001:10569: ye shes bzhi'i bdag nyid can las mi thob la
NK077(tsu)001:10570: / 'dir gdul bya sku lnga lhun grub gyi sa la drangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10571: phan yon gyi khyad par ro //
NK077(tsu)001:10573: rgyu'i theg pas 'di la skye la /
NK077(tsu)001:10574: 'di la mi skye ba'i phyogs gtad yod pa la
NK077(tsu)001:10575: ma h+aa'i thugs rje 'di la skye 'di la mi
NK077(tsu)001:10577: des na thun mong gi theg pa chen po las /
NK077(tsu)001:10578: de'i snying rje blar gyur cing 'phags pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:10579: 'o na le'u 'dir tshad med pa bzhi lan gnyis byung bas bldab zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:10582: mnyam bzhag gi dngos na dgongs pa thun gcig la /
NK077(tsu)001:10583: yon tan gyi cha nas tshad med bzhi yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:10585: rjes shes snying rje'i cha nas tshad med bzhi yin /
NK077(tsu)001:10586: yang na gong ma blo bzhag thabs skabs la /
NK077(tsu)001:10588: bdag don gyi spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10590: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang las mi d+ha ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10592: bdag gi don bya ba'i phyir phyi nang gi spyod lam thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:10593: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:10594: phyi nang gnyis su 'dzin pa'i sgrib pa med par
NK077(tsu)001:10595: rig pa rang gsal ba'i ngang la ye shes sgyu
NK077(tsu)001:10596: ma'i ting nge 'dzin la blo brtan zhing shin tu
NK077(tsu)001:10597: bde ba'o // longs spyod kyi spyod pa bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10599: 'dod pa'i yon tan longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad la gtsang dang sme ba'i blo 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:10601: thams cad ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor ro gcig
NK077(tsu)001:10602: pas gtsang sme gnyis su med pas shin tu bde
NK077(tsu)001:10603: / de bas na spyad par bya ba lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10605: dang du len pa lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10606: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa'i spyod yul thams cad la /
NK077(tsu)001:10607: ye shes la ye shes rol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10608: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10610: khyad par gyi dam tshig gi ye shes sgyu ma las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10612: dang po sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod ni thub
NK077(tsu)001:10613: pa chen po ston pa sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul
NK077(tsu)001:10614: ni / chos thams cad la dbang thob pas ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub /
NK077(tsu)001:10615: de bzhin du chos rnams thams cad yul yul can du dmigs su med /
NK077(tsu)001:10616: ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin la cir yang snang zhing cir yang 'grub /
NK077(tsu)001:10617: chos nyid zag pa med pa'i zab mo'i don rtogs
NK077(tsu)001:10618: na thams cad dag par ma gyur gang yang med
NK077(tsu)001:10619: / ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin ma bcos pa phyogs med kun tu gsal /
NK077(tsu)001:10620: rang bzhin ngang gi rnam par dag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10621: de'i phyir spyod yul thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:10622: sgyu ma lta bu'i ye shes su rang gsal bas 'da' bar mi bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10623: thun mong gi dam tshig snga ma dang mthun par 'phel bar bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10626: yang lag gi dam tshig thams cad kun spyir snga
NK077(tsu)001:10627: ma de ting stong pa chen po'i skabs bzhin yin
NK077(tsu)001:10628: te khyad par du stobs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10630: bcu pa drod la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:10632: de ltar ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin thob cing goms pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10633: 'khor ba'i chos sdug bsngal gyi phung po la tshad
NK077(tsu)001:10634: med bzhi shar bas byang chub sems dpa' rang dbang
NK077(tsu)001:10635: med par skyo ba'i sems kyi sems 'phrog par 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:10636: ro // sems rang snang la gzhan med pas ma
NK077(tsu)001:10637: 'khrul de ngo ma shes pas 'khrul pa de la
NK077(tsu)001:10638: ngo mtshar zhing ya mtshan skye ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10639: don med par le lor 'dug pa la de bzhin du snying rje skyes te /
NK077(tsu)001:10640: phyi nang gsang ba'i drod rnam pa gsum po de
NK077(tsu)001:10641: snga ma de bzhin nyid las brtan zhing 'phel bar
NK077(tsu)001:10642: snang ba'o // bcu bzhi pa rtags la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:10646: de ltar nyams kyi rim pa 'phel ba'i snga rtags ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10647: lus shing bal gyi 'dabs ma lta bur shin tu yang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10648: lus kyi na tsha la sogs pa bzod pa phra
NK077(tsu)001:10649: mo thob cing ting nge 'dzin yun ring ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:10650: / 'byung ba lus kyi phung po khams bde mi bde snyoms pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10651: dus skabs 'dir phal cher rtags de rnams yod cing
NK077(tsu)001:10652: 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad mgo snyoms pa 'byung ngo
NK077(tsu)001:10653: // lam gong ma bas 'phel zhing gsal ba'i rtags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10655: de bas lta ba'i skabs su ches /
NK077(tsu)001:10658: 'dir kun ting la chos brgyad mnyam ste phal cher 'go snyoms pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10659: rtags kun kyang sngar de bzhin nyid las grangs 'phel zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:10664: rang dang lhan cig du drung na 'dug pa'i gang
NK077(tsu)001:10665: zag pha rol po de'i sems rgyud la dmigs pa
NK077(tsu)001:10666: gtad de / ting nge 'dzin la bzhag pa tsam
NK077(tsu)001:10667: gyi pha rol po de'i sems rgyud shes pa'i mngon
NK077(tsu)001:10669: de ting bas 'dir grangs mang du 'phel ba dang ngo bo cung zad gsal zhing brtan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10670: de las gzhan pa sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran
NK077(tsu)001:10671: pa la sogs pa'i mngon par shes pa'i mig gis
NK077(tsu)001:10673: sgra shes pa la sogs cung tsam 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:10674: goms nas yon tan yod pa de bas na ye
NK077(tsu)001:10675: shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor la blo brten zhing 'dris
NK077(tsu)001:10676: par bya'o // bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la dbyer ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:10678: ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:10679: 'di yis tshe dbang drug gi spyod yul gyi snang
NK077(tsu)001:10680: ba ma lus pa thams cad kun dngos su sgyu
NK077(tsu)001:10681: mar snang ba smos ci dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:10682: gnyis pa'i rmi lam du'ang spyod yul thams cad snang
NK077(tsu)001:10683: la rang bzhin med pa sgyu ma lta bur mthong
NK077(tsu)001:10684: ba dang / rgyud snying rjes gang bar rmi lam du snying rje 'ba' zhig mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10685: rmi lam du bla ma dang sangs rgyas kyi byin
NK077(tsu)001:10686: gyis brlabs cing dbang skur ba la sogs pa lam
NK077(tsu)001:10688: bar chad legs nyes brtson lung ston pa rnams sngar bas mang du mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10689: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10690: mtshan ma lnga mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10691: de la sogs pa shugs snang brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10692: mtshan ma bzang ngan ci snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:10693: ye shes sgyu ma'i ngang du rtogs pas chags zhing zhen par mi bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10694: bcu gsum pa phan yon la gnyis bgrang yon tan tshad med par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10696: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor la goms par byas
NK077(tsu)001:10697: nas rnal 'byor pas bden gnyis dbyer med kyi don
NK077(tsu)001:10698: chen po rang snang gnyis med rtogs pa yis /
NK077(tsu)001:10699: dus mtha' med ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:10700: de ltar sgom de'i yon tan la tshad med pas
NK077(tsu)001:10702: spyod yul sangs rgyas nyid dang ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor gcig go //
NK077(tsu)001:10703: tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing phyag rgya gcig par sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10705: ye shes sgyu ma'i spyod pa bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:10706: chen dpal ldan de'i ming don gsal yang ma chags
NK077(tsu)001:10707: pas ye shes kyi tshogs chen dang ldan no //
NK077(tsu)001:10708: ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor 'di yid 'gyu thog
NK077(tsu)001:10709: na sems las su rung bas rnal 'byor phyi ma
NK077(tsu)001:10710: phyag rgya gcig pa btsal ba med pa rang shugs
NK077(tsu)001:10711: kyis 'char ba'o // bcu bzhi pa d+ha ka ma la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:10713: sems 'pho ba'i dpe nyi ma las ma g.yos par 'od 'jig rten du 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10715: sa bon ma g.yos par myu gu 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10716: ngag 'pho ba'i dpe bsgyur las ma g.yos par 'gram pa la chu ldang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10717: brag cha las g.yos pa med par sgra lhang lhang byed pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:10718: chos nyid thams cad rang byung gi ye shes dus gsum du 'gro 'ong med /
NK077(tsu)001:10719: gzhan du 'pho ba med kyang gong gi dpe bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:10720: 'khrul pa'i ngo la 'pho 'gyur ltar snang ste 'chi
NK077(tsu)001:10721: ba'i tshe / ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK077(tsu)001:10722: brtan par byas pa'i ngang la 'das na las kyi
NK077(tsu)001:10723: rgyun thams cad gcod cing dpe lha mi'i go 'phang
NK077(tsu)001:10724: thob nas / sngar gyi bag chags bzang po'i 'brel
NK077(tsu)001:10725: pas yang dag pa'i lam gsang sngags kyi theg pa
NK077(tsu)001:10726: 'di nyid dang mjal nas bskol bar mi 'gyur ste
NK077(tsu)001:10729: ye shes sgyu ma rang gzhung gi lugs yin la rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:10731: kun rdzob sems skyed sgom zhor la 'pho na 'di ltar yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:10732: theg chen 'pho ba'i gdams ngag ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10733: stobs lnga nyid de spyod lam bcas /
NK077(tsu)001:10735: chos 'di la sbyangs pa'i gang zag de 'chi nges pa'i nad kyis theb pa na /
NK077(tsu)001:10736: dang po dkar po sa bon gyi lag len ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10737: yo byad thams cad bla ma dkon mchog la mchod
NK077(tsu)001:10738: pa la sogs bsod nams gang che bar gtong la
NK077(tsu)001:10739: / de rnams la chags zhen med par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:10740: de'ang rang gi blo la 'di rang bsod nams che snyams pa de bya'o gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:10741: de nas smon lam gyi stobs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10742: bla ma dkon mchog la yan lag bdun pa phul bdag bar do dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10743: tshe rabs phyi ma thams cad du byang chub kyi sems gnyis 'byung bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK077(tsu)001:10744: chos 'di ston pa'i bla ma dang mjal bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK077(tsu)001:10745: zhes gsol ba drag tu gdab cing /
NK077(tsu)001:10746: de ltar smon lam yang gdab bo //
NK077(tsu)001:10747: de nas sun 'byin pa'i stobs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10748: bdag gces 'dzin gyi rnam rtog 'dis sngar yang sdug
NK077(tsu)001:10749: bsngal du bcug /da rung 'di dang ma bral na
NK077(tsu)001:10751: da lta yang bdag gi 'di la gces par bzung bas sdug bsngal bar 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10752: brtag na lus la gces 'dzin gyi rnam rtog spangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:10753: sems la bdag tu bzung rgyu mi 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10754: lus sems gang la yang bdag 'dzin spangs la bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:10756: nges par bar do la yang byang chub kyi sems
NK077(tsu)001:10757: gnyis sbyang bar bya'o snyam pa'i 'dun pa drag po
NK077(tsu)001:10758: yang yang bya'o // de nas goms pa'i stobs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10759: sngar gyi byang chub kyi sems gnyis spyod tshul de dran par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10760: spyod lam ni 'chi khar glo g.yas pa 'og tu bcug /lag pa g.yas pas 'gram pa brten /
NK077(tsu)001:10761: mthil chung gis sna bug g.yas bkab la /
NK077(tsu)001:10762: rlung g.yon nas rgyu bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10763: de nas byams snying rje sngon du 'gro ba'i rlung /
NK077(tsu)001:10764: 'gro 'ong la bskyon nas gtong lan gnyis po sbyangs /
NK077(tsu)001:10765: de'i rjes la 'khor 'das skye 'chi la sogs pa thams cad sems snang yin /
NK077(tsu)001:10766: sems nyid cir yang ma grub pa'i ngang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:10767: blos cir yang mi 'dzin par bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:10768: de ltar byang chub kyi sems gnyis po de /
NK077(tsu)001:10769: spel zhing sgom pa'i 'phro la 'chi bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10772: 'di bas ngo mtshar che ba med gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:10773: byang chub sems gnyis gang rung gi sgo nas 'pho ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10775: 'pho bya 'pho byed dang bral ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10777: bdag bas gzhan gces kyi 'pho ba'ang mchog yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:10778: ma smad gnyis chus khyer bas /
NK077(tsu)001:10779: mas bu mo 'di ma shi na /
NK077(tsu)001:10780: bu mos ma 'di ma shi na snyams pa'i bsam pa byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:10781: gnyis ka tshangs pa'i gnas su skye bar 'dug gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:10782: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:10784: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10786: blo che bas skye ba phyi mas blo chung bas
NK077(tsu)001:10787: lan grangs gzhan dag la 'khor bar mi ldog par
NK077(tsu)001:10788: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rigs su nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:10789: gzhung bzhin bsgrub pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10791: ye shes sgyu ma'i lam der cha rkyen kun rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:10792: shing rim par bsgrub pas thun mong dang thun mong
NK077(tsu)001:10793: ma yin pa'i mtshan bzang po sum bcu rtsa gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:10794: dang dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu kun dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:10795: pa'ang / dbang phyug chen po longs sku'i gnas nyid du /
NK077(tsu)001:10796: mngon par byang chub bar the tshom med do //
NK077(tsu)001:10797: de ltar 'bras bu longs skur thob par bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10798: rgyu'i chos mthun 'bras bu la sbyar ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:10799: de yang le'u gsum pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:10800: 'bras bu nyid ni lam phyir te //
NK077(tsu)001:10801: phyogs mthun brjod kyi ris ma yin //
NK077(tsu)001:10802: ces pa dang mthun par le'u bzhi pa 'dir yang /
NK077(tsu)001:10804: phyogs mthun gyi 'bras bu longs sku /
NK077(tsu)001:10805: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu lha mi mtshan rdzogs /
NK077(tsu)001:10806: nyer sbyor gyi 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10807: ma rtogs le lo byas pa'i skyon no //
NK077(tsu)001:10809: ye shes sgyu ma'i don lta ba ma rtogs te
NK077(tsu)001:10810: dman pa las gyur pa'i le lo snyoms las byas
NK077(tsu)001:10811: bdag gzhan nam 'bras bu bla med byang chub kyi
NK077(tsu)001:10812: don ma grub par slar yang ngan song gsum du
NK077(tsu)001:10814: de bas na sgom pa la brtson 'grus kyis gcig par shugs la gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10817: yul can gnyis su med pa'i snying rje chen po
NK077(tsu)001:10818: ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor bstan pa'i gzhung gi
NK077(tsu)001:10819: tshig don rnams gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:10820: don gyis na / le'u zhes bya ste yas bgrang
NK077(tsu)001:10821: bzhi pa'i don du gada'o ////le'u lnga pa phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:10824: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10826: sems nyid snang stong gnyis med ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK077(tsu)001:10827: ngang la goms pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis phyag 'tshal
NK077(tsu)001:10828: nas / snang stong dbyer med ci bzhin pa zhi
NK077(tsu)001:10829: khro phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor bshad par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:10832: lus snga ma dang mthun par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10834: snying rje sgyu ma goms pa'i rnal 'byor pa phyag
NK077(tsu)001:10835: rgya gcig pa sgom par 'dod pa'i gang zag lus
NK077(tsu)001:10836: sku rdo rje / ngag gsung rdo rje /
NK077(tsu)001:10837: yid thugs rdo rje gsum ldan du sgom pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:10838: de ting stong pa chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10839: kun ting sngar ltar snga ma 'das pa'i lus kyis shes ste don bco lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10840: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la don bco lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10841: dang po sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10843: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi'i spyi'i sngon du bya ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:10844: las dbang thob lhag pa'i yo byad lnga dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:10845: pa la sogs pa sngon de ting gi skabs su
NK077(tsu)001:10847: khyad par phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor 'di nyid
NK077(tsu)001:10848: sgom pa'i sngon 'gro la ye shes sgyu ma mthar
NK077(tsu)001:10849: phyin pa sngon du byas pa la goms shing /
NK077(tsu)001:10850: de nas dmigs pa'i rten rgyal ba'i sku gser la sogs pa la lugs su blug pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:10851: rba shing la 'bur du btod pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:10853: 'jim pa la 'der po byas pa la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:10854: yi dam lha'i mtshan ma'i sku phyag rgya rab gnas
NK077(tsu)001:10855: can mdun du bzhag pa de la yan lag brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:10856: pa 'bul ba sngon de ting gi skabs su bstan
NK077(tsu)001:10857: bzhin du bya'o // gnyis pa dgos ched la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:10859: dbyer med 'bras bu ngo bo yin pas de yongs
NK077(tsu)001:10860: su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir sgom zhing phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:10861: spros pa'i rgyu phyag rgya gcig pa 'di yis thob
NK077(tsu)001:10862: par bya zhing snying rje sgyu ma kun snang dang
NK077(tsu)001:10863: / stong pa de bzhin nyid kyi rtogs pa'i zhen pa /
NK077(tsu)001:10864: dbyer med du bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10866: 'byung ba lnga la sogs pa ltar gnas su dag
NK077(tsu)001:10867: par 'gyur zhing gdul bya gzhan dag smin par bya
NK077(tsu)001:10868: ba'i phyir / zhi khro phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnam par sgom pa'i shin tu gces pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10869: gsum pa bzhag thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10873: de yang phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la 'jug pa'i thabs la rnam pa gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:10875: lha sgom pa'i sngon du rnal 'byor pa'i sems kyi rtsal yi ge la sbyangs ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10876: de 'byung nas zhi khro'i lhar bskyed cing sgom pa'i thabs bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10877: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10878: yi ge la sems sbyang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10884: de la mdor bstan gyi snga ma'ang sems sbyang ba
NK077(tsu)001:10885: la blo chung ba gdam ngag gi stobs kyis sems
NK077(tsu)001:10886: sbyang ba dang / blo che ba rang gi shes rab kyi stobs kyis sems sbyang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10887: de ltar sems sbyangs pa gnyis ka la 'jug pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:10888: gzhi bo'i rtsa ba'i rgyu'i yi ge aa'am h'u 'di
NK077(tsu)001:10889: nyid de // rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:10891: a la sems sbyangs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10895: dkar ba ni byang chub kyi sems so zhes gsung pas stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK077(tsu)001:10896: rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo yi ge a dkar
NK077(tsu)001:10897: po gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan pa gcig
NK077(tsu)001:10898: sgom mo // de yang rab tu brtan pa'i tshad bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10903: cir yang bsgyur du btub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10904: rig pa ar gsal ba de nyid rtogs pa'i mthar mi g.yo ba /
NK077(tsu)001:10905: rkyen gyis dbang du mi 'gyur ba /
NK077(tsu)001:10906: rkyen dbang du mngon par mi 'gyur ba /
NK077(tsu)001:10907: ka kha la sogs pa yi ge zhe gnyis su 'char bas /
NK077(tsu)001:10908: cir yang bsgyur du btub par sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10909: 'o na bsgyur du rung ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:10910: brtan pa'i tshad du ci 'gro ce na cir yang bsgyur du rung ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10911: shin tu brtan pa thob pa'i tshad yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:10912: dper na skyes bus rta rkya ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:10914: de ltar rang rig ar snang ba de nyid gzung
NK077(tsu)001:10915: 'dzin dang bral shing nyes pa'i skyon gyi ma gos
NK077(tsu)001:10917: gsal ba'i tshad bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10923: de yang seng nge ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10924: sems nyid ar gsal ba de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:10925: rtog pa'i rnyogs ma med par shel lta bur seng ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10927: a nyid sgrib g.yogs med par sa le ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10929: de nyid skar ma pa ba sangs ltar gting lhang nge ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10931: de nyid me long la nyi ma shar ba ltar rgyang nas lhag ge ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:10932: de las a s+pha ra na phata /
NK077(tsu)001:10934: gzhi bo'i a de las shin tu phra ba'i a
NK077(tsu)001:10935: dpag tu med pa rnams spros pas phyogs bcu thams
NK077(tsu)001:10936: cad as gang bar gsal bar gyur nas sam ha
NK077(tsu)001:10937: ra na h'u / zhes bsdus kyang gzhi ma'i a la 'phel ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10938: phyogs bcu'i a la 'grib pa med par ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:10939: 'dzin brtan pa'i tshad ni gsal ba yul gyis mi
NK077(tsu)001:10940: 'phrog pa'o // 'di la brtsad spang gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:10941: spro bsdu'i tshad kyis brtsad spang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:10942: rgyu'i yi ge la 'phel 'grib med pa'i brtsad spang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:10943: dang po ni spar khab las /
NK077(tsu)001:10945: nam mkha' khyab par spro ba dang bsdu bar bya ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:10948: tshogs lam gyi spro bsdu blo chung na /
NK077(tsu)001:10950: blo che na sna'i dri tshor ba tshun chad spro bsdu bya ba gnyis byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:10955: mos slob kyi dbang yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:10956: mdo'i don ni dngos yul gyi dbang yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:10963: snang ba ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi gnad yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:10965: a grangs med spros kyang gzhi ma'i a la 'grib pa med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:10966: dper na nam mkha'i zla ba gzugs brnyan du ma shar yang /
NK077(tsu)001:10967: gzhi ma mi 'grib pa dang 'dra la /
NK077(tsu)001:10968: snang ba yongs su rdzogs kyang gzhi ma a la 'phel ba med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:10969: dper na phyogs bcu'i gzugs brnyan du ma bsdus kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:10970: gzhi ma'i zla ba la 'phel ba med pa lta bu yin gsung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:10972: dngos po rnams kyi spyi lugs kyi mang po spros na /
NK077(tsu)001:10973: gzhi ma la 'grib pa la mang po bsdus na gzhi ma 'phel ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:10974: 'dir yang bsdus na gzhi ma'i a la 'phel ba med pa med mi btub /
NK077(tsu)001:10975: spros na de la 'grib pa med pa mi btub ste /
NK077(tsu)001:10977: 'di ni don rtags gnyis su mi 'gal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:10978: don sems nyid sems byung gi chos du ma spros kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:10979: sems nyid la 'grib pa med la /
NK077(tsu)001:10980: sems byung gi chos du ma bsdus kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:10981: sems nyid la 'phel ba med pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:10982: rtags a nor bu rin po che lta bu las /
NK077(tsu)001:10984: gzhi ma'i a la 'grib pa med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10987: a du ma bsdus kyang 'phel ba med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:10988: a du ma sems nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:10990: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK077(tsu)001:10994: de ltar a de la sems sbyang ba'am zhi ba
NK077(tsu)001:10995: las yang na khro bo ltar na thugs ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:10996: lnga mtshon pa'i yi ge h'u mthing ga gsal brtan
NK077(tsu)001:10997: gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan pa sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:10998: de yang gong du a la 'phro 'du ci ltar
NK077(tsu)001:10999: byed pa de bzhin du h'u la spro bsdu yang
NK077(tsu)001:11001: goms pas h'u de nyid gsal brtan du las su rung bar gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11002: don ye shes lngar gsal ba las /
NK077(tsu)001:11003: ma rtogs pa'i chos gzhan med pa'i rtags su /
NK077(tsu)001:11004: snang zhing srid pa'i phyi snod dang nang bcud kyi
NK077(tsu)001:11005: dngos po thams cad yi ge h'u ye shes lnga
NK077(tsu)001:11006: ldan gcig tu gsal bar bsdu /
NK077(tsu)001:11007: 'o na rnal 'byor pa rang nyid mi sdud dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:11009: rang gi lus kyi yan lag lnga dang sems rnam
NK077(tsu)001:11010: par shes pa tshogs brgyad kyang rang rig pa'i ye
NK077(tsu)001:11011: shes lnga ye nas yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:11012: de dag kyang sems nyid rang snang gi yi ge h'u du shin tu yang 'dus par bsdu ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11013: h'u de nyid gsal ba'i tshad ni n+rihste mi'i snying po yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:11014: de rnal 'byor pa'i mig gi dbang po'i mngon sum
NK077(tsu)001:11015: du ltar yod pa ltar de ltar rnal 'byor pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:11017: 'dris shing goms nas bdag dang gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir spros pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:11018: 'phags pa mchod cing sems can gyi don rdzogs nas slar gzhi bo'i h'u la bsdu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11019: h'u nyid mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings su gsal /
NK077(tsu)001:11020: de ltar goms shing 'dris par bya ba shin tu gces so //
NK077(tsu)001:11023: phrin las rim pa bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11027: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11028: de yang mdor bstan gyi phyi ma lhar bskyed pa
NK077(tsu)001:11029: la tshangs pa phru gu'i tshul can zhi ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:11030: / srin po phru gu'i tshul can khro bo ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11031: de lta bu'i zhi khro'i lha'i ting nge 'dzin yongs
NK077(tsu)001:11032: su rdzogs par sgom par bya ba'i thabs zhi khro
NK077(tsu)001:11033: zung gcig tu ston par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11034: rtogs ldan pas sku rdzogs par bya ba'i thabs shes rab zung du 'gyur bar gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11035: gzhung la brtag na snga ma ltar 'thad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11036: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11037: zhi ba sgom pa dang khro bo sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11040: spyir gang mos su sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11042: dang po tshangs pa zhi ba'i lha'i tshul rdzogs par
NK077(tsu)001:11043: bya zhing sgom pa'ang yi dam gyi lha rigs lnga
NK077(tsu)001:11044: gang bsgrub kyang / sa bon gyi yi ge h'u
NK077(tsu)001:11045: swa am ham lnga po so so las bskyed pa
NK077(tsu)001:11046: gang bsgrub kyang / ste / de yang spyir ni
NK077(tsu)001:11047: yi dam gyi lha rigs lnga po gang bsgoms kyang
NK077(tsu)001:11048: rgyal ba la bzang ngan du grub pa med pas
NK077(tsu)001:11049: kun dang 'dra zhing mnyam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11050: bder gshegs gcig sgom rgyal kun gyi ngang /
NK077(tsu)001:11052: 'on kyang thugs sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs su rdo rje sems dpa' nyid du 'dus te /
NK077(tsu)001:11053: thugs kyi rigs dang rigs thams cad kyi gtso bo yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11055: blo chung ba rim gyis sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11056: blo che ba cig char du sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11058: rten gzhal yas khang sgom pa dang /
