NK077(tsu)001:11062: a sems sbyangs shing gdan sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11064: dang po mi rtogs pa'i ngang las rgyu'i yi ge sgom pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11065: de nyid thabs 'og nas bstan pa 'di ltar rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid goms par bya ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:11066: gzhal yas khang bskyed cing lha sgom pa'i sngon du
NK077(tsu)001:11067: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin cir yang mi
NK077(tsu)001:11069: snying rje chen po kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:11070: sgom pa'i ngang nyid las rang gi rig pa nyid
NK077(tsu)001:11071: a dkar po gsung yig 'bru dag gi phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:11072: 'od 'bar ba shin tu 'tsher bar gsal sgom la
NK077(tsu)001:11073: / phyogs bcu thams cad ar ni gyur par sgom pa rtags yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:11074: don skye med rang snang du shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11075: de bzhin nyid du 'dris shing goms par byas nas yi ge a las ma yi dkyil 'khor spro /
NK077(tsu)001:11076: de ltar spros pas phyogs bcu thams cad a dkar po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11077: ma dmar mo gnyis kyis gang bar gsal bar ting nge 'dzin gyi blo la 'byor par gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11078: bsdus te 'od du zhu ba las ma las nyi ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11079: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor nya gang ba bsgril ma ste brtsegs par sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:11080: de'i 'og tu h+r+aihdamara por gsal ba 'od du zhu
NK077(tsu)001:11081: ba las pad+ma 'dam skyon gyis ma gos pas chags
NK077(tsu)001:11082: pa med pa kha dog sna tshogs pa gcig sgom
NK077(tsu)001:11083: // gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11085: de'i 'og tu ye shes rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i gdan gyi 'od las /
NK077(tsu)001:11086: zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang sbra gur lta bur sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:11087: yang na b+h+r+aum las don ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK077(tsu)001:11088: rgyu rin po che sna lnga las grub cing 'od 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11089: de ltar nyi zla pad+ma rin po che'i gdan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11090: rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du /
NK077(tsu)001:11091: rin po che'i za ra tshag la sogs pa'i rgyan
NK077(tsu)001:11092: thams cad bsdus shing ngo bo cha phra bar rnam
NK077(tsu)001:11094: brten pa lha sgom pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11095: rtsa ba'i lha cho ga yan lag gsum gyis sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11096: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dagu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11101: gzhal yas khang gi nang na gdan de'i dkyil du
NK077(tsu)001:11102: yi ge h'u gnas par sgom ste kha dog mthing
NK077(tsu)001:11103: ka 'od zer 'tsher la rnam pa gsal ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:11104: 'od zer 'phro bar rnam par sgom h'u las 'od
NK077(tsu)001:11105: 'phros mchod don byas dbyings su slar nas thugs phyag
NK077(tsu)001:11109: 'od zer tshur 'dus nas h'u 'od du zhu ba las /
NK077(tsu)001:11110: thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga pa nas 'bras
NK077(tsu)001:11111: tsam gcig tu gyur pa ni shin tu rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:11112: phra ba sgom zhes brjod do //
NK077(tsu)001:11113: rdo rje de las 'od 'phro zhing kha dog gsal zhing 'od 'bar mchod /
NK077(tsu)001:11114: don byas nas slar bsdus nas chos kyi dbyings su
NK077(tsu)001:11115: yang ni bstim par bya ste rdo rje 'od du
NK077(tsu)001:11116: zhu ba'o // sku phyag rgya la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11120: snying po brjod pa tsam gyi rdo rje de nyid rdo rje sems pa'i skur gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11121: sku tshon gang ba shin tu phra zhing rgyan dang cha lugs 'dus par sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:11124: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11126: gong gi spro bsdu de bzhin nyid lha'i sku gsung thugs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11127: bdag gi sgo gsum gnyis su med par gsal bar
NK077(tsu)001:11128: gyur nas sku rags pa lus tsam zhal gcig phyag
NK077(tsu)001:11129: gnyis kyi g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril bu 'od 'bar
NK077(tsu)001:11130: ba bsnam tshul dgu dang ldan par sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:11131: zhal gsum phyag drug sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11133: gong gi zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa de bzhin du goms nas 'dris shing brtan par gyur pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11134: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:11135: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug pa nyid du sgom ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11136: de yang g.yas dang po rdo rje /
NK077(tsu)001:11139: g.yon bar ma rin po che /
NK077(tsu)001:11141: g.yon dang po dril bu 'od 'bar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11142: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dagu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11144: yan lag gi lha phra ba'i gzhal yas te nyi
NK077(tsu)001:11145: zla pad+ma'i gdan dang ldan par sgom ste gnas gcig
NK077(tsu)001:11146: ste snying khar thugs ye shes sems dpa' phyag mtshan
NK077(tsu)001:11147: med pa tshon gang ba tsam gcig sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:11148: spyi bor sku'i lha dkar po /
NK077(tsu)001:11149: mgrin pa gsung gi lha dmar po /
NK077(tsu)001:11150: tsit+ta thugs kyi lha mthing ka /gnas gsum du gong du bshad pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:11151: tha mal gyi lus ngag yid gsum de dang de'i
NK077(tsu)001:11152: sku gsung thugs su byin rlabs rdo rje gsum sgom
NK077(tsu)001:11153: bya / dbu'i gnas rnams su rin po che'i khang
NK077(tsu)001:11154: bu lngar yi ge lnga ye shes lngas dbang yongs
NK077(tsu)001:11155: su rdzogs pas dbu rigs lngas brgyan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11156: cig char ba'i sgom pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11158: cig char du sgom pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11160: cig char du sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11162: rnal 'byor blo'i shes rab che chung gi rim gyis
NK077(tsu)001:11163: pa la dgar bas yang na lha cig char du
NK077(tsu)001:11164: phyag rgya chen po'i skur sgom pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11165: snying rje brjod pa tsam gyis chu las nya ldang
NK077(tsu)001:11166: ba ci bzhin du rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid phyag
NK077(tsu)001:11168: de yang zhal gsum phyag drug phyag mtshan gong dang mthun par dus rtag du sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:11169: gzhal yas khang lhag pa'i lha snga ma dang mthun par ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11171: gzhal yas gdan sogs snga ma bzhin yin te 'dir cig char du sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:11172: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dagu'ang de bzhin yin la 'di cig char sgom pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11173: lha sgom tshul de la shin tu 'dres shing goms par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11174: khro bo sgom pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11176: sgom thabs rim dang cig char spyir zhi ba dang mthun par sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11178: rak+sha khro bo'i cha lugs 'dzin pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:11179: blo chung ba rim gyis sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11180: blo che ba cig char du sgom pa sngon zhi ba bzhin du sgom pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:11181: khyad par du zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur te sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11183: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje /
NK077(tsu)001:11184: cho ga gsum gyi sgo nas bskyed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11185: de rnams rigs kyi kha dog dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11186: gzhal yas gdan la sogs zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur te sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:11187: de yang thugs kyi rig la badz+ra he ru ka sgom pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:11188: de las gzhan rigs bzhi la mos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:11189: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i yi ge h'u /
NK077(tsu)001:11190: dkar ser dmar ljang gi yi ge 'bru bzhi sbyang ste rigs bzhi sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11191: gdan dang gnas dang ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11192: rdo rje rnam gsum rang rig tu bsgyur /
NK077(tsu)001:11193: rtsa ba'i sku dang yan lag gi lha bskyed pa bsgyur ba gong gi de bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11194: phrin las kyi rim pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:11196: phrin las kyi rim pa bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11198: de ltar zhi khro gnyis ka blo chung ba rim gyis pa la brtan pa thob pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:11199: blo che ba cig char ba sgom pa'i dus su gang ltar bskyed kyang rung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11200: phrin las kyi rim pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11201: de la dang po yan lag brgyad pa byas pa'i mthar mtshams bcad /
NK077(tsu)001:11204: byin phab h'u zhes 'od dang gzi byin rang la
NK077(tsu)001:11205: thim pa las yi dam gyi lhar bskyed la phyi
NK077(tsu)001:11206: nang gi mchod pa rnams gzhung bzhin du byin gyis
NK077(tsu)001:11207: rlabs nas / stong pa dang sgyu ma'i ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:11208: 'dzin cung zad tsam sngon du song bas rang rang
NK077(tsu)001:11209: gang sgom gyi lha'i skur rim cig char gyis sgom
NK077(tsu)001:11210: rlabs nas / ste / yan lag lhag pa'i lha
NK077(tsu)001:11211: dgu dang ldan par bskyed pa yan chad rdzogs nas
NK077(tsu)001:11212: rlabs nas / ste / / snyan gsan dbab /
NK077(tsu)001:11214: brtan par bzhugs su gsol nas de la phyi nang
NK077(tsu)001:11215: gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul bstod pa dang bcas pa
NK077(tsu)001:11219: de nas gang sgom gyi lha dang sngags kyi yan
NK077(tsu)001:11220: lag ma nyams par zhi khro'i rigs gang yin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:11222: de la spyir yan lag ma nyams pa la bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11223: dang po lam gyi yan lag ma nyams pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11225: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11226: sgyu ma goms nas sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11227: gnyis pa bsam pa'i yan lag ma nyams pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11228: sems nyon mongs dang g.yeng ba'i dbang du mi 'gro zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:11230: gsum pa lha'i yan lag ma nyams pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11231: bzlas pa'i rten phyag rgya bzhi ma nyams pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11232: rtsa ba'i lha dang yan lag gi lha gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11233: bzhi pa sngags kyi yan lag ma nyams pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11234: 'og nas ston pa ltar sgra la skyon med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11237: spyir dge bcu la bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11238: bye brag tu sngags la bsam dpyod kyi bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11240: bar chad kyi skyon bcu spangs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11242: mi dge bcu zhes gsung pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11243: ma byin len dang srog gcod g.yo //
NK077(tsu)001:11244: tshig gi ngag 'khyal phra ma rdzun //
NK077(tsu)001:11245: brnab sems gnod sems log par lta //
NK077(tsu)001:11246: dge bcu bar du gcod pa ste //
NK077(tsu)001:11247: yang dag don gyi dgra zhes bshad //
NK077(tsu)001:11249: spyir dge ba tsam la bar gcod byed la /
NK077(tsu)001:11250: phyag rgya gcig pa sgom pa'i skabs 'dir yang byed la /
NK077(tsu)001:11251: khyad pa du ngag gi bzhi po sngags la gnod pas spangs ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:11252: gnyis pa bsam spyod kyi bar du gcod pa'i skyon
NK077(tsu)001:11253: bcu ni nyon mongs pa lnga bsam pa'i skyon dang
NK077(tsu)001:11254: / brtson 'grus chung ba spyod pa'i skyon dang drug /
NK077(tsu)001:11255: 'dod chags che ba re dog gi skyon dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:11256: ting nge 'dzin dang bral ba g.yeng ba'i skyon dang brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:11257: yid ches med pa the tshom gyi skyon dang dgu /
NK077(tsu)001:11258: don dang mi ldan pa rang rgyud pa'i skyon dang bcu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11259: de yang nag po drug cu pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:11260: sngags kyi bsnyen pa byed dus su //
NK077(tsu)001:11261: me dang 'dra ba'i zhe sdang gis //
NK077(tsu)001:11262: sngags kyi 'bras bu bsregs par byed //
NK077(tsu)001:11263: kun nas 'khrig pa'i chags pa yis //
NK077(tsu)001:11264: yon tan rgyud rnams 'ching bar byed //
NK077(tsu)001:11265: mun pa lta bu'i gti mug gis //
NK077(tsu)001:11266: dngos grub ster ba rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:11267: sgang bu lta bu'i nga rgyal gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:11268: dngos grub chu 'dra rtse nas snyil //
NK077(tsu)001:11269: sngags kyi yon tan sprin 'dra la //
NK077(tsu)001:11270: phrag dog rlung gis 'thor bar byed //
NK077(tsu)001:11271: dngos grub chu bo'i rgyun bsdus la //
NK077(tsu)001:11272: brtson 'grus rdo rje brag med na //
NK077(tsu)001:11273: le lo rba brlab chen po 'khrugs //
NK077(tsu)001:11274: 'di ltar si ti kun ldan la //
NK077(tsu)001:11275: sngags kyi dngos grub 'dod pas spang //
NK077(tsu)001:11276: bzlas brjod me yi rgyun 'dra la //
NK077(tsu)001:11277: sdig pa chu dang 'dra bas gsod //
NK077(tsu)001:11278: ces pas bcu po de spangs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11279: gsum pa sngags bzla ba sgra'i skyon bcu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11287: mi tshig gis bar ma chod pa nyon mongs pa dang ma 'dres pa /
NK077(tsu)001:11288: sems gzhan du ma yengs pa dang bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11289: rngam klog gi le'u bcu pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:11290: sgra che ma yin chung bar min //
NK077(tsu)001:11291: mgyog par ma yin bul bar min //
NK077(tsu)001:11292: drag par ma yin dal ba min //
NK077(tsu)001:11293: yig 'bru'i yan lag nyams ma yin //
NK077(tsu)001:11294: yig med phyal dang bar chad min //
NK077(tsu)001:11295: rgyu ba'i sems pa spang bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:11297: rnam gsum gyis zhes pa 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:11300: bzlas pa grangs dam bca' bzhin rdzogs par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:11301: ting nge 'dzin spro bsdu bdag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11302: gzhan gyi don rdzogs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11303: phyi dam tshig sems dpa' dang ye shes sems dpa' la bskor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11304: nang rlung 'byung rngub tu bskor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11306: mkha' nas mkha' ru bskor ba gang mos su yi dam lha'i bzlas pa dus grangs /
NK077(tsu)001:11307: mtshan ma rnams tshad du phyin par bskyal bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11312: ye shes sems dpa' gnyis tha dad du gsal bar byas nas bzlas pa byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11314: bsgrub pa'i dus su de gnyis tha mi dad par gsal bar bzlas pa byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11316: bsgrub pa chen po'i dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:11317: bdag dam tshig pa'i thugs ka nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11318: yig 'bru byang sems 'od zer dang bcas pa 'phros te /
NK077(tsu)001:11319: ye shes sems dpa'i zhal du thim zhing klad pa'i rgyas su byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11320: a ba d+hu ti na mar zhugs te /
NK077(tsu)001:11321: gsang ba'i rdo rje nas bdag gi rdo rjer thim /
NK077(tsu)001:11322: a ba d+hu ti na yar zhugs te /
NK077(tsu)001:11323: bdag gi mkha' nas ye shes kyi zhal du thim
NK077(tsu)001:11324: mkha' nas mkha' ru thim zhing bzlas pa byed pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:11327: bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i dal du gsal /
NK077(tsu)001:11328: lha ye shes sems dpa' dal du gsal /
NK077(tsu)001:11329: de gnyis kyi bar gyi 'phro 'du gsal bas bzlas pa'i 'od zer phar 'phros pas /
NK077(tsu)001:11330: sgrib pa sbyongs shig par bskul /
NK077(tsu)001:11331: tshur 'dus pas bdag gi sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs par bsam zhing bzlas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11333: phar 'phros pas de ba'i sku gsung thugs mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK077(tsu)001:11334: bdag la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rtsol gcig par thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK077(tsu)001:11335: tshur 'dus pas ye shes can gyi dngos grub de
NK077(tsu)001:11336: bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i thob par bsam zhing bzlas
NK077(tsu)001:11337: pa bya'o // gsang ba'i bzlas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11338: bzlas pa'i 'od zer phar mi 'phro bar /
NK077(tsu)001:11339: mtsho la ser chen bab pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:11340: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub tshur la sib sib 'dus par bsam zhing bzlas pa bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11342: zhal nas zhal du 'phro 'du byed pa ni phyi /
NK077(tsu)001:11344: mkha' nas mkha' ru 'phro 'du byed pa ni gsang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11347: bdag dang lha gnyis ka'i ba spu'i bu ga nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11348: gsung yig 'bru'i 'phro 'du byed cing gdul bya'i bzlas pa byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11350: thugs ka nas thugs phyag mtshan gyi 'phro 'du byas
NK077(tsu)001:11351: nas dngos grub thob par bsam zhing bzlas pa byas
NK077(tsu)001:11352: pa'o // gsang ba'i bzlas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11353: mkha' zhal gyi 'du 'phro dang sku phra mo'i 'phro 'du byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:11354: dngos grub dbang du 'dus pa gnyis su med pa'i bzlas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11356: dang po gsung dang bar thugs dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11358: yang na rdo rje'i bzlas pa'am //
NK077(tsu)001:11361: bzlas pa tshad du phyin par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:11365: mtshan ma rtags kyi bsnyen pa rtags ma byung gi bar du bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11366: yang bye brag tu lam lnga po kun yang /
NK077(tsu)001:11367: rang rang gi bzlas pa tshad du phyin par byed de /
NK077(tsu)001:11368: tshogs lam sgyu stong gnyis mos slob kyi bzlas pa byed pas rtog pa rags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11369: gcig spros gnyis rtog pa bsrab pa'i bzlas pa byed de /
NK077(tsu)001:11370: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs bsgrub sgyu ma lta bu'i bzlas pa byed pas rgyun ma chad par bazla'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11371: mthong lam chos nyid yang dag pa'i bzlas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:11372: sgom lam mi g.yo ba ting 'dzin gyi bzlas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:11373: mthar lam rtsol bral mngon gyur gyi bzlas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11376: dang po rtogs pa'i bzlas pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11377: gnyis pa rjes mthun bsrab pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11378: gsum pa sgyu ma'i bzlas pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11379: bzhi pa gnyis med bzlas pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11380: lnga pa rgyun gyi bzlas pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11381: drug pa dag pa'i bzlas pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11382: bdun pa mi g.yo'i bzlas pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11383: brgyad pa dgu pa bcu pa ni //
NK077(tsu)001:11384: rtsol bral mi g.yo'i bzlas pa ste //
NK077(tsu)001:11385: tshad dang mthun dang ngo bos dbye //
NK077(tsu)001:11387: lam lnga sa bcu ngo bos bzlas pa'i tshad so sor bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11388: spyir bzlas pa kun la'ang 'di bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11389: thun mtshams kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11391: de ltar lha'i bzlas sgom gyi khams dub par gyur na nyal ba'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11392: snying kar dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi dbus su ye
NK077(tsu)001:11393: shes snying po'i thig le don dam spros pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:11394: bral ba de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin de
NK077(tsu)001:11395: la blta zhing mtshan mo yang de'i ngang la nyal
NK077(tsu)001:11398: ye shes kyi thig le de nyid la gsung yig
NK077(tsu)001:11399: 'bru'i cho ga h'u s+w+aa am ha la sogs zhi
NK077(tsu)001:11400: khro gang yin gyi cho ga gsum gyis bsgyur te
NK077(tsu)001:11401: sku phyag rgya gcig pa yongs su rdzogs pa la
NK077(tsu)001:11402: / las rim mchod bstod bzlas pa la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:11403: sngon gang du bstan pa bzhin sgom bzlas la sgo
NK077(tsu)001:11404: gsum rab tu brtson pas lha'i rnal 'byor la goms
NK077(tsu)001:11406: bzhi pa ngo bo la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:11408: lha dmigs med rang snang du gsal ba ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11411: brten pa lha'i dal sgom pa yang rang gi sems
NK077(tsu)001:11412: kyi cho 'phrul rig pa rang snang yin pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:11413: / lha la yul du dmigs nas sgom du med de rang gi rig pa nyid yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11414: phyag rgya bzhi rdzogs pa'i rgyal ba'i sku de rig pa rang snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11415: sgom bya don gyi ngo bo dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11417: thun mong gi rgyal ba'i yang rgyal ba sku lnga
NK077(tsu)001:11418: lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid rgyal ba rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:11419: sems dpa' la sogs pa rnams kyi sku ru gsal
NK077(tsu)001:11420: ba ni / dus dang gnas skabs kun tu dper
NK077(tsu)001:11421: na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta
NK077(tsu)001:11422: ba ni / bu yin te / yon tan thams
NK077(tsu)001:11423: cad lhun rdzogs su yod pas 'di la phan gdags
NK077(tsu)001:11424: ba ni / bu yin te / / 'di la
NK077(tsu)001:11425: mi gdags kyi rtog pa med par gdul bya'i re
NK077(tsu)001:11426: ba ni / bu yin te / / ba bskangs
NK077(tsu)001:11427: ba'o // de ltar yon tan zad pa dang 'phel
NK077(tsu)001:11428: ba med dgongs pa la 'gro 'ong med thugs rje
NK077(tsu)001:11432: lha'i sku phyag rgya gcig pa sgom pa'i tshe res 'ga' gsal bar yod /
NK077(tsu)001:11434: res skyon las grol res ma grol zhes bya ba gtan nas med de /
NK077(tsu)001:11435: de gtan tshig ci'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:11436: ci snang rig pa bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:11437: dgongs pa la phyogs ris med cing spyod pa la blang dor med do //
NK077(tsu)001:11438: lha'i sku sgom pa la bying ba dang rgod pa'i dbang du ma song bar snyoms tsam ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11439: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang la mnyam par bzhag pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11440: sgra don nam nges tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:11441: lnga pa mi mthun pa'i skyon la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11443: thun mong gi skyon phra ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11445: ting nge 'dzin ngo bo dang mi mthun pa'i skyon
NK077(tsu)001:11446: rnams phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:11447: 'di yi tshe skyon rnams dmigs ngos bzung ba ni
NK077(tsu)001:11448: / dang po yi ge la sems sbyangs pa nas
NK077(tsu)001:11449: bzung ste sku yongs su rdzogs par sgom pa'i bar
NK077(tsu)001:11451: bying rgod la sogs pa thun mong gi skyon rnams
NK077(tsu)001:11452: kun tu 'byung yang 'dir rags pa mi 'byung ste
NK077(tsu)001:11454: tha ma phra ba ste phyag rgya gcig pa'i 'di
NK077(tsu)001:11455: la so 'thas shes bzhin gyi bya ra bas bcad
NK077(tsu)001:11456: pas chig go // bye brag gi skyon dngos bzung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11458: phyag rgya gcig pa 'di nyid kyi khyad par gyi skyon ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11459: g.yo thob kyi skabs su lha'i sku smig rgyu ltar rab rib las mi snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11460: goms brtan gyi skabs su lha snang yang du ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:11461: gseb kyi rdzas ltar mog mog tu bdug pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:11462: / gsal shing 'grib nas 'gro ba grib ma lta bu'i nag nog gyi chod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11464: lha'i tshad rnal 'byor pa gang gi lus tshad tsam
NK077(tsu)001:11465: du dmigs nas sgom pa la che chung gi tshad
NK077(tsu)001:11468: gar dagu'am bzhengs pa dang bzhugs pa'i tshul 'gyur ba dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11471: zhi khro'i cha lugs dur khrod dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11472: rin po che'i rgyan 'gyur ba dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:11473: sku mdog dkar ser la sogs 'gyur ba dang lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:11474: zhi ba khro bo'i dbyibs 'gyur ba dang drug /kha
NK077(tsu)001:11475: dog ste sku gsung thugs 'ba' zhig las mi snang
NK077(tsu)001:11476: ste / sku'i dbyibs med pa dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:11477: dbu'i gtsug tor sgom na zhabs kyi gdan khri med pa rim par nub nas mi snang ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:11478: dbu'i gtsug tor nas rim par nub cing 'jam mi gsal bar 'gro ba dang brgyad 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:11479: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:11481: thun mong gi skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11483: de ltar 'gyur ba'i skyon rnams tshor bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11484: thun mong gi skyon dbang du gyur pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:11485: shes bzhin gyi bya ra bas bcos mtshan ma'i 'du
NK077(tsu)001:11486: byed rnam rtog gi rlung gis spyod par mi bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:11487: // khyad par gyi skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11489: 'di nyid kyi khyad par gyi skyon gong du bstan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:11490: de ltar skyon zin pa'i rnal 'byor pas skyon de dag kun bcos pa'i thabs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11491: 'di nyid kyi khyad par mi gsal ba'i skyon gsum
NK077(tsu)001:11492: la lam snga ma gnyis ma brtan pa'i skyon yin
NK077(tsu)001:11493: pas kun snang snying rje sgyu ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11494: de ting stong chen gyi ngang la yun ring du 'dug la /
NK077(tsu)001:11495: de goms pa'i rjes la phyag rgya gcig pa lha'i
NK077(tsu)001:11496: ting nge 'dzin rang shugs kyis thob pa de ha
NK077(tsu)001:11497: cang yun mi ring bar bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11498: thun tshod ma sun tsam du 'dug cing sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:11499: 'gyur ba'i skyon brgyad bcos thabs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11500: tshad nas dbyings yan chad kyi bar 'gyur ba'i skyon
NK077(tsu)001:11501: drug la sku ri bo ltar che zhing gdos bcas
NK077(tsu)001:11503: bdun pa kha dog 'bab zhig las dbyibs med pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:11505: sku'i dbyibs dang gnyis bsre ste sgom par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11506: brgyad pa rim par nub pa'i skyon la sku spyi'i
NK077(tsu)001:11507: rnam pa gsal ba min kyang bye brag tu zhal
NK077(tsu)001:11508: phyag gam / phyag gi sor tshig nas dpung pa
NK077(tsu)001:11509: tsam la sogs gang gsal ba la blo gnas par
NK077(tsu)001:11510: phyag gam / bya'o // spyod lam gyi skyon bcos thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:11512: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs 'dir bya ba min pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:11513: las yi ge bri mchod la sogs pa kun dor
NK077(tsu)001:11514: bar bya ste / spang la spyod lam bzhi rnal
NK077(tsu)001:11515: du ma 'byor pa'i skyon rnams ngos zin par byas
NK077(tsu)001:11516: la btang ste spang bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11519: nyams snga ma bzhin 'phel ba bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11521: de ting stong pa'i ngang ye shes sgyu ma gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:11522: la nyams lnga khug nas brtan mod kyang phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:11523: gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'di la goms pas /
NK077(tsu)001:11524: nyams rim lnga gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i tshul
NK077(tsu)001:11525: bstan pa'ang lam snga ma de ting kun gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:11526: bstan pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11527: nyams kyi snang ba dang sbyar te tshod bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11529: nyams lnga mtshan ma dang sbyar te /
NK077(tsu)001:11530: bshad pa ni g.yo ba'i nyams kyi dus su smig
NK077(tsu)001:11531: rgyu lta bu lha dngos su mi gsal cing rtog
NK077(tsu)001:11532: pa yul na brang bring yin snyam tsam du'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11533: thob pa'i dus su du ba lta bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11535: gsal zhor mi gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11536: goms pa'i dus su srin bu me khyer yud tsam gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11537: brtan pa'i dus su mar me lta bur rlung gi
NK077(tsu)001:11538: bskyod pa la sogs kyi skyon med na gsal ba
NK077(tsu)001:11539: dang / mthar phyin pa'i dus su nyi ma shar ba lta bur lha gsal ba mthar phyin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11540: de ltar nyams lnga mtshan ma'i tshul de dag dang sbyar te shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11541: de dag gis dus su rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i btang snyoms dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11542: rtsol ba med pa'i btang snyoms /
NK077(tsu)001:11543: dus phyed pa'i btang snyoms kyi rim pa dang gsum dang rtsol bcas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11545: dus phyad pa'i brtson 'grus te brtson 'grus kyi rim
NK077(tsu)001:11546: pa rab 'bring tha ma gsum po dag /g.yo thob
NK077(tsu)001:11547: la rtsol bcas kyi btang snyoms dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11549: goms brten la rtsol med gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11550: mthar phyin la dus phyad par gnyis blang la /
NK077(tsu)001:11552: de yang gnas skabs kyi ngang du gang blang /
NK077(tsu)001:11553: rgyab tu gang dor gyi bye brag rnams rang gi
NK077(tsu)001:11554: nyams lnga'i sa mtshams gar phyin pa las sbyar te
NK077(tsu)001:11555: shes par bya'o // brgyad pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11560: mtshams bcad cing bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pa bya thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11562: mtshams bcad cing bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pa bya thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11564: spyi mgrin snying kha lte ba bzhi ru yig 'bru h'u bzhis gshin rje gshed /
NK077(tsu)001:11567: 'khyil pa bzhir bskyed la dus rtag tu mtshams bcad /
NK077(tsu)001:11568: 'di la phyi nang gsang gsum du bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:11569: phyi mtshams ni khro bcus dgra bgegs sam sdig pa mi dge ba bcu gcod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11571: bdag yi dam gang yin du gsal ba'i gnas bzhir
NK077(tsu)001:11572: yig 'bru'i 'phro 'du las sgo ba bzhir bskyed de
NK077(tsu)001:11573: / ting nge 'dzin la bar chad kyi bgegs kyis mi tshugs par sgom pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11574: de yang rgyas par dmar mchan ltar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11576: sems rnam par rtog pa'i dbang du mi gtong ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11578: mtshams med pa la mtshams gcod pa //
NK077(tsu)001:11580: shes bya nang gi chos nyid la //
NK077(tsu)001:11581: don du mnyam par 'jog pas na //
NK077(tsu)001:11582: phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshan ma yi //
NK077(tsu)001:11585: ting nge 'dzin la bar mtshams med pa la bar
NK077(tsu)001:11586: du gcod pa rnam rtog yin pas de bskrad dgos
NK077(tsu)001:11587: par bshad do // chos kun rang byung ye shes la rang lus lha'i dal du gsal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:11589: rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i longs spyod kyi tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:11590: kyi mchod pa bya zhing chos nyid la chos kyi
NK077(tsu)001:11591: rol / nang gi sbyin sreg kyang zas tshogs ltar du blang bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11592: gzugs sgra dri ro reg chos sogs yul drug po
NK077(tsu)001:11593: mtshan med ltar na spros pa med pas thig le
NK077(tsu)001:11594: chos nyid la chos nyid rol pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:11595: mtshan bcas ltar na 'dod yon gyi lha mo drug
NK077(tsu)001:11596: tu shar bas lha la lha thim par rol zhing
NK077(tsu)001:11597: dbang po bzhi rnam shes bzhi dang brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:11598: sems dpa' brgyad yul bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11599: dus bzhi sems ma brgyad de /
NK077(tsu)001:11600: lha yab yum du sbyor bar shes par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:11601: de yang yi dam gyi lha zhi khro phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:11602: gcig pa gang yin pa'i skabs kyis sems dpa' sems
NK077(tsu)001:11603: ma la / ke'u ri sing ha la sogs pa'i tshul du bsgyur bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11606: bdag nyid chen po mchod pa'i phan yon ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11607: gong ltar snang srid kyi chos thams cad sems nyid
NK077(tsu)001:11608: kyi bdag nyid chen po yin pas 'bul bya 'bul
NK077(tsu)001:11610: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang khams gsum gyi sems
NK077(tsu)001:11611: can gnyis su med par shes par byas pas mchod
NK077(tsu)001:11612: pa phul ba yis sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma
NK077(tsu)001:11613: lus bdag nyid kyi rang rig pa'i ye shes la
NK077(tsu)001:11614: tha mi dad pas na mnyes shing rgyal ba rnams
NK077(tsu)001:11615: mnyes pa de'i byin gyis srid gsum ni 'dod khams
NK077(tsu)001:11617: gzugs med khams gsum yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:11618: des bsdus pa'i 'gro ba ris drug gis sems can de dag bskyed par byed pa'i sa bon /
NK077(tsu)001:11619: a r+n+ri sum tri pre du thams cad la byang
NK077(tsu)001:11620: chub kyi bde ba'i ro dga' ba chen pos khyab
NK077(tsu)001:11622: spyod lam kun du lha'i phyag rgya las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11624: rnal 'byor pa phan tshun du 'gro ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11627: kha zas la longs spyod pa'i tshe dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11628: nyon mongs pa dang chags sdang la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11630: sems kyi sdug bsngal byung ba'i tshe na yang /
NK077(tsu)001:11631: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi yi dam lha'i sku phyag rgya sgom zhing mi spang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11632: sngon bzhin lha sgom zhing dbang po yul dus kyi sbyor bas lha myur du 'grub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:11633: ting nge 'dzin gyi spyod pa la mi nyams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11635: de ting kun ting rgyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11636: 'bras bu spros pa dang tshogs kyi bsgrub pa /
NK077(tsu)001:11637: de gnyis kyi 'tsham sbyar bar byed pas phyag rgya gcig pa dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:11638: de rnams bar skabs kun du sgom pa ma yin
NK077(tsu)001:11639: pa'i yi ge bri mchod la sogs pa chos spyod
NK077(tsu)001:11640: dgu'i spros pa dor bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11641: shes shing rgyud la ldan yang blang bya min te /
NK077(tsu)001:11643: mtshan ma'i g.yeng ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11644: lus ngag yid gsum yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs
NK077(tsu)001:11645: rdo rje gsum du sgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:11646: la phyag dang skor ba la sogs mi bya /
NK077(tsu)001:11647: gal te 'tshal dgos na bla ma dang yi dam mdun du sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:11648: de ltar min na phyag 'tshal ba de sgrib par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:11649: spyir yang lci ba bzhi la /
NK077(tsu)001:11651: sgom chen lta dgongs can rnams sgo gsum lhar gsal
NK077(tsu)001:11652: ba'i phyag bla ma min pas blang du mi rung
NK077(tsu)001:11653: ngo // mkhas pa'i gong lci ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11654: chos rgyud sde mang po shes pa'i gang /
NK077(tsu)001:11655: rigs rgyud can gyi mi chen po chos mi shes pa de'i gong du 'gro na /
NK077(tsu)001:11657: mi mkhas mkhas pa'i gong na med //
NK077(tsu)001:11658: de'i phung po gzhob re mkhas /
NK077(tsu)001:11660: sgom bsgrub mkhan gyis zas lci ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11661: de'i zas ci yod thams cad tshogs su bsngosa pas /
NK077(tsu)001:11662: de'i zas phal pas mi chom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11664: sngags pa nag po'i nor ma 'bag na /
NK077(tsu)001:11667: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor spyod pa la lta
NK077(tsu)001:11668: ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyi don dang ldan zhing
NK077(tsu)001:11669: dam tshig mnyam la spyod pa dag par byas nas
NK077(tsu)001:11671: sgom na 'bras bu myur bar 'grub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:11672: tshogs kyi spyod pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11674: spyod lam thams cad du lha la lha rol bas bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:11675: de ltar spyod pa la ma chags shing gnyis su med pa ni ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11676: bdag don gyi spyod pa la dngos grub byung tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:11678: bdag gi don bya ba'i phyir thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11679: mchog gi dngos grub rnams phyag rgya gcig pa 'di
NK077(tsu)001:11680: brten nas dngos grub la sbyor bar the tshom med
NK077(tsu)001:11681: do // gzhan don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11683: gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir 'phro 'du'i rim par rdzogs par bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:11684: yang na gdul bya gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:11685: mnyam bzhag las lang ste bzlas pa'i 'od zer gyi
NK077(tsu)001:11686: 'phro 'du'i rim pas bdag gzhan gyi don rdzogs par
NK077(tsu)001:11687: byed do // gdul bya rkyen dang 'phrad pa'ang thugs rjes yal bar mi dor te /
NK077(tsu)001:11688: spros pa sgom pa'i dus min kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:11690: spros pa'ang mos sgom gyi sgo nas lan cing gdul
NK077(tsu)001:11691: bya gang dang mtshams par de'i don rdzogs par byed
NK077(tsu)001:11692: pa'o // dgu pa dam tshig la dbye ba med de /
NK077(tsu)001:11694: phyag rgya gcig pa 'di'i tshe la gzhi 'dra ba'i dam tshig kun rgyud la ldan med kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:11695: khyad par du gsung gi zhi sngags gsum phyag rgya bzhi la bslab bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:11696: phyag phyag chen po'i rnal 'byor du /
NK077(tsu)001:11697: spyod yul thams cad du lha'i nga rgyal las mi 'da' bas bsdom par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11698: bcu pa drod la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:11700: phyi lus dang nang ngag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11701: gsang ba sems kyi drod gsum po yang /
NK077(tsu)001:11703: 'dir drod ma thob pa thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11704: thob pa brtan pa'i char 'phel gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:11705: yang na de ting dang kun ting la thob pa dang 'dir brten pa'i char gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:11707: phyi'i drod 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga po la zhen
NK077(tsu)001:11708: pa phra ba las med de sngar bas chung ba
NK077(tsu)001:11709: dang / dbang po yul du snang ba kun lha'i ting nge 'dzin du goms pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11710: nang gi brod dbugs phyi nang du rgyu ba bar du chad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11711: gsang ba'i drod ting nge 'dzin la thun bzhi la sogs kyi mtshams dang bral te /
NK077(tsu)001:11712: gong du bstan pa ltar phyi nang gsang gsum gyi
NK077(tsu)001:11713: drod kyi bye brag ma lus pa kun dang gsal
NK077(tsu)001:11715: bcu gcig pa rtags la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:11719: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rtags chen po goms shing brten nas mthar phyin pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:11724: nyi ma lta bu'i mtshan ma lnga po de rnams dngos su mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11725: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum gyi gsung yig 'bru thugs phyag mtshan /
NK077(tsu)001:11726: sku'i skye mched dngos su mthong ba rnams lha grub pa'i rtags kyi mtshan ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:11727: dngos grub thob pa la dang po'i rtags 'byung ba yin zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11728: gong gi skye mched kyi skabs na zad par la 'bru gnon pa yang yod /
NK077(tsu)001:11729: gong gi mtshan ma rlung rtags lnga'i skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:11730: sems dang rlung sems gnyis med rten dang rten pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:11731: sems gnas pa'i tshe rlung zin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:11732: rlung la sa chu me rlung nam mkha'i rlung lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:11733: de la rtsa ro brkyang gnyis la lnga gnyis bcu rgyu ba de nang du zin pa'i rtags su /
NK077(tsu)001:11735: du ba lta bu kha dog dkar ser ma nges pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11736: smig rgyu lta bu la sogs chu 'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11737: srin bu me khyer dang me stag lta bu la sogs me'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11738: mar me 'bar ba lta bu gcig nas mang pa 'bar ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11739: sprin med pa'i nam mkha' lta bu rgya che chung med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11740: 'od dkar po dmar po ser po lam lam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11741: snang ba med pa'i mu nag lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11742: nyi ma dang zla ba 'od can dang 'od med dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11744: bar snang sbrang mda' lta bu skya rtsig rtsig pas gang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11745: 'od kyi thig le kha dog sna lnga gang rung
NK077(tsu)001:11746: la 'od zer gyi thag pa brkyangs pa lta bu
NK077(tsu)001:11747: dang / 'od lnga'i rnam pa rig pa ci rig
NK077(tsu)001:11748: pa mthong ste de yang rlung gi mtshan ma rnam
NK077(tsu)001:11749: dang / lnga yang / du ba lta bu lang lung dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11750: smig rgyu lta bu gya gyu dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11751: srin me lta bur dmar 'phro dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11752: mar me lta bur dmar kham gsal //
NK077(tsu)001:11753: mkha' la nyi shar lta bur snang //
NK077(tsu)001:11757: dmigs pa'i yul gyi rgya chen po dang ldan pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i mngon shes kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:11758: ting nge 'dzin snga ma gnyis las grangs mang ba nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11759: yul sngar bas rgya che ba gnyis kyi lam snga
NK077(tsu)001:11760: ma'i mngon shes las khyad par du 'phags pas bla
NK077(tsu)001:11762: gzhan yang sgo lnga'i dbang po re res yul lnga
NK077(tsu)001:11763: lnga gcod nus pas nyi shu rtsa lnga'i mngon shes
NK077(tsu)001:11764: rnams kyang / phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs 'dir g.yo thob tsam du 'byung ba the tshom med do //
NK077(tsu)001:11767: ngag ni rtags kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul /
NK077(tsu)001:11768: sems kyi rtags rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul mthu yi rtags byin rlabs kyi cho 'phrul rnams kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:11770: de rnams kyang g.yo thob tsam du 'byung bar byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:11771: rtags sngar bas gsal zhing brtan par 'byung tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:11773: brod rtags de dag gzhan yang sngon ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:11774: gnyis pas gsal cha che la ngo bo brtan pa
NK077(tsu)001:11775: ni / rgyu ci las 'byung zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:11776: ting nge 'dzin gong ma gnyis bden pa kha phral nas sgom pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:11777: 'dir phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor lhag pa dbyer med sgom pa'i stobs kyis thob pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11778: bcu gnyis pa mtshan ma rmi lam gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11782: nyal ba gnyid kyis spyod lam rmi lam nyid du /
NK077(tsu)001:11783: lam sgrub pa la legs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11784: nyes pa skyon 'byung ba'i bye brag kun lam snga
NK077(tsu)001:11785: ma las kyang 'dir gsal bar 'gyur zhing sngar bas
NK077(tsu)001:11786: kyang shin tu brtan par 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11787: yi dam lha zhi khro gang yin gyi bsam gtan la brtson 'grus kyi 'bad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11788: sngags kyi bzlas pa byas pa yi /
NK077(tsu)001:11789: bsgrub pa pos ni rmi lam khyad par can rtags su mthong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11790: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11792: legs pa'i yon tan gyi rmi ltas bcu bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11795: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:11796: sangs rgyas mthu dang mtshungs shing mnyam par mthong ba
NK077(tsu)001:11798: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dpes brgyan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11799: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid tha dad med par ni
NK077(tsu)001:11800: dus myur du thob par 'dug snyams du mthong ba
NK077(tsu)001:11802: sems dpa' chen po rnams dang tshangs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11803: brgya byin la sogs pa khams gsum pas rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:11804: pa bdag la mchod pa byed par rnal 'byor pa
NK077(tsu)001:11805: des rang gi rmi lam na mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:11807: gnyis med kyi ye shes chen po 'od 'dra'i gzugs
NK077(tsu)001:11808: skur snang ba'i sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' gzugs
NK077(tsu)001:11809: la sogs pa'i 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga po rnams
NK077(tsu)001:11810: kyi dus rtag tu bdag la mchod par byed par
NK077(tsu)001:11811: mthong ba dang / lnga pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11812: rdo rje sems pa'i gzugs chen dang //
NK077(tsu)001:11813: grags chen phyag na rdo rje gzugs mchog dgas su /
NK077(tsu)001:11814: gnyid log pa'i rmi lam dag na rnal 'byor pa
NK077(tsu)001:11815: rang gi gzugs lha de dag tu mthong ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:11817: sangs rgyas kyi zhing du grags chen rdo rje gsang ba lhun gyi grub pa'i rin chen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11818: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa rnam par
NK077(tsu)001:11819: sel ba la sogs pa rnams chos kyi 'khor lo
NK077(tsu)001:11821: sangs rgyas chen po rnam par snang mdzad la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:11822: pa rnams kyis phyag 'tshal ba'i rmi lam 'di 'dra
NK077(tsu)001:11823: bsgrub pa pos mthong bar gyur pa de ni lus
NK077(tsu)001:11824: lha'i sku ngag gsung sems thugs kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:11825: sgom pa'i mathu'am byin rlabs las skyes pa yin no
NK077(tsu)001:11827: rin po che'i dbu rgyan la sogs pa rgyan rnams
NK077(tsu)001:11828: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pas brgyan pa lha'i bu
NK077(tsu)001:11829: mo yid du 'ong ba dang mi'i khyi dang bu
NK077(tsu)001:11830: mo yid du 'ong ba dag gis 'dod yon lngas
NK077(tsu)001:11831: bdag la mchod pa byed pa mthong na rtags de
NK077(tsu)001:11832: ni dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur ba'i bltas
NK077(tsu)001:11834: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad rnams rang rang gi
NK077(tsu)001:11835: zhing na gnas pa bdag gi nges par mthong ste
NK077(tsu)001:11836: / de rnams bdag la thugs ni rjes par gyur nas kyang chos mdzad cig ces pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11837: yid du 'ong ba'i gtam la sogs pa ston pa mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11839: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:11840: mthu yis sems can kun gyis kyang chos kyi 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:11841: lo yongs su bskor ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11842: rnal 'byor pa lha'i bsam gtan lus ngag yid gsum
NK077(tsu)001:11843: rdo rje gsum las dbyer mi phyed par gnas pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:11844: dam tshig las mi 'da' bas sbyor bas mthong bar
NK077(tsu)001:11846: skyed mos tshal la sogs pa nyams dga' ba'i phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:11847: sna tshogs pa kun gyi bdag lha'i bu dang bu
NK077(tsu)001:11848: mo la sogs pa'i brgyan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11849: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag la byin gyis
NK077(tsu)001:11850: rlabs las snang ba'i bsam gtan ting nge 'dzin dang
NK077(tsu)001:11851: dam tshig can gyi mthong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11852: bcu gcig pa ni sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' yis /
NK077(tsu)001:11853: de ni bdag la mngon par dbang bskur bar mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11855: rig 'dzin bzhi dang rgyal po chen po bzhi yis
NK077(tsu)001:11856: bdag la mchod par byed pa rnal 'byor pa de
NK077(tsu)001:11859: lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:11860: gsum du sgom las byung bas yon tan sna tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:11861: pas / rmi lam yang dag par gsal ba la
NK077(tsu)001:11862: skyon gyi dri ma med pa de dag mthong na
NK077(tsu)001:11863: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsum
NK077(tsu)001:11864: sgom pa las skyes pa'i 'bras bu bla na med
NK077(tsu)001:11867: chos kun yi ge dang lha'i sku phyag rgya rnam
NK077(tsu)001:11868: gnyis kyi skye mched thams cad gsal bar mthong ba'ang
NK077(tsu)001:11869: de bzhin no // de yang don 'grub par 'gyur ba dang bcu bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11872: gdol pa khyi'i sbyor la sogs /
NK077(tsu)001:11873: tshigs rkang bzhi po 'di yon tan du bshad pa dang skyon du bshad pa gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:11875: khyi sha za ba la sogs rnams rdo rje 'dzin pas rmi lam du mthong na ni //
NK077(tsu)001:11876: spang blang med pa'i don rtog pa'i ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:11877: skyon du bstan pa ni dmar mchan bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11878: 'di gzhung rang la brtag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11879: dam pa bde bar gshegs kyi lam chung gi dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11880: 'grel tig gzhan 'ga' nas yon tan du bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:11881: skye mched mthong ba'ang de bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11882: zhes pa'i tshigs rkang gnyis po 'di zad par gyi skye mched mthong ba la bzhag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11883: rmi ltas bcu bzhi la mi the bar 'dod pa mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:11884: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs 'dir nyes pa'i rmi ltas 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:11885: don dang gzhung gnyis ka la brtag na med par rtogs so //
NK077(tsu)001:11886: bcu gsum pa phan yon la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:11887: lha sgom pa'i phan yon dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11888: ma sgom pa'i skyon gyi ngos nas brtson 'grus kyis cig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11889: zhal mthong mos shing bsgrub pa'i phan yon no //
NK077(tsu)001:11892: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11894: rnal 'byor pas yi dam lha'i sku ni gsal la
NK077(tsu)001:11895: ma 'gags par sgom na rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:11897: lha de nyid chu zla'i tshul du snang la rang
NK077(tsu)001:11898: bzhin med par shes par gyur na 'bras bu ye
NK077(tsu)001:11899: shes tshogs chen rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11900: yon tan chung yang bsgrub na 'grub pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11902: rnal 'byor pa ba dag nyid kyi sgo gsum yi
NK077(tsu)001:11903: dam lha'i sku gsung thugs dang tha dad med par
NK077(tsu)001:11905: de las gzhan pa'i yon tan thun mong zer yang
NK077(tsu)001:11906: thos pa chung yang mchog thun mong dngos grub par
NK077(tsu)001:11907: 'gyur ba la the tshom med do //
NK077(tsu)001:11908: de nas lha sgom par gdam pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:11909: de yang lha zhes bya ba gcig gzhan nas grub
NK077(tsu)001:11910: pa med ye gdod ma nas lha dang bdag gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:11911: ngo bo dbyer med pas mnyam pa nyid du sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:11912: bas su / yi dam gyi lha gang yin nyid du ni dus rtag tu sgom par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11913: lha gcig sgom pas 'bras bu kun thob pa'i yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:11915: lha gcig sgom na bder gshegs kun dang mnyam sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:11916: bas nye ba'i dkyil 'khor kun dang mnyam par 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:11917: / nye ba'i dkyil 'khor kun dang mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:11918: 'bras bu rgyal ba'i sku lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11920: ye shes lnga ste thugs lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11921: gzhan yang yon tan lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11922: phrin las lnga rdzogs shing 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11923: 'di rnams la lha gcig sgom pas yon tan kun 'grub pa'i rgyu mtshan go dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:11924: grub thob tshem bu pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11926: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang gnyis kyi gtam rgyud bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:11927: ma sgom pa'i skyon gyi sgo nas brtson 'grus gyis shig pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11931: yi dam lha'i mtshan nyid ni gang zhe na phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:11932: bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK077(tsu)001:11933: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag po yin pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:11934: / yi dam gyi lha spang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11935: gzhan dge ba ci spyad kyang 'dod pa'i don 'bras bu med par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:11936: dper na nad tshab po ches theb pa la sman pa spang nas mi bos pa dang 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11937: brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:11939: brtson 'grus gyis shig par gdams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11941: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig bsrung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11942: skyon bcu spang ste sngags bzlas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11943: lha'i sku phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11945: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni sku nyid phyag rgya chen po ba zhi sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:11946: de ltar dam tshig bsrung zhing lha sgom pa la
NK077(tsu)001:11947: brtson 'grus che zhing blos brtan par byas la bzung
NK077(tsu)001:11948: ngo // de ltar ma yin te rnal 'byor brtson
NK077(tsu)001:11949: 'grus chung gyur na 'dod pa'i 'bras bu mi 'grub
NK077(tsu)001:11950: ste slar ngan song du 'gro bas nyen yang che
NK077(tsu)001:11951: ngo // bar gsung ste / rgyud las /
NK077(tsu)001:11952: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:11954: gal te nan tan ma byas pa'i skyon dpe don dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11957: ral kha 'gyed pa'i tshe ral gri'i so la nan
NK077(tsu)001:11958: tan du yu ba nas legs par ma bzung na
NK077(tsu)001:11960: de bzhin du rnal 'byor pa dam tshig dang lha
NK077(tsu)001:11961: sgom pa la nan tan med pa'i gsang sngags pas
NK077(tsu)001:11963: yang na phyi mar bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub med par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11966: skyon 'jug pa de bas lha'i sgom bzlas la bar chad cing brtson 'grus med na /
NK077(tsu)001:11967: dper na sa bon tshig pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:11969: bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu mchog thun mong gang yang med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11970: mi khom pa'i gnas brgyad la sogs pa kha 'khor bar brgyud par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11971: zhal mthong ba la mos shing bsgrub pa'i phan yon no //
NK077(tsu)001:11973: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gi yi dam lha'i zhal mthong ba'i lha la /
NK077(tsu)001:11975: lha la bsnyen bskur byas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:11976: mchod pa byas pa'i bsod nams kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:11977: mi dge ba bcu dang 'tsham med pa lnga ste
NK077(tsu)001:11978: bco lnga la sogs pa las ngan thams cad rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:11979: ba nas sbyangs te rig 'dzin la sbyor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:11980: bcu bzhi 'da' ka ma la dbye ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:11982: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang gis mi
NK077(tsu)001:11983: rtag ste tshe 'pho ba'i dus mthong na yang yi
NK077(tsu)001:11984: dam lha'i sku phyag rgya ma nyams pa ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:11985: 'dzin gsal bar yid la bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:11986: sngar mi dge ba bsag pa'i las kyis ngan song
NK077(tsu)001:11987: la sogs mi 'khol bar rang nyid gang 'dod pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:11988: sangs rgyas kyis zhing khams khyad par can du a
NK077(tsu)001:11989: las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK077(tsu)001:11990: sku tshon gang ba gcig gsal bar byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:11991: dbugs kyi rta la bskyon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:11992: yam las rlung gi stobs kyis bskul bar byas te sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams su 'phang bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:11993: yang na a yang stobs kyis bskul bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:11995: rang gi rig pa yi dam lhar gsal ba de
NK077(tsu)001:11996: a las zla ba'i dal gyi steng du bzhag /yam
NK077(tsu)001:11997: las rlung gis btegs te a yam u ti phata
NK077(tsu)001:11999: rang shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams su mos nas der 'phang /
NK077(tsu)001:12000: nub phyogs pad+ma can du 'phos na der 'phang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12001: rang gang mos kyi gnas su bskul bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12002: bco lnga pa 'bras bu la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:12004: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin la sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12006: thod rgal ba rnam smin gyi rig 'dzin thob pa la the tshom med de /
NK077(tsu)001:12007: nyams mthar ma phyin cing blo chung na 'on te
NK077(tsu)001:12008: rnam smin du ma gyur na yang nyams mtho dman
NK077(tsu)001:12009: dang / blo rtsal che chung brtson 'grus drag zhan
NK077(tsu)001:12010: rim pa yis rnam smin rig 'dzin de nyid bar
NK077(tsu)001:12011: de'i tshe phyi ma'am skye ba'i lan grangs gzhan brgyud
NK077(tsu)001:12013: nyams mthar phyin cing rtsal dang brtson pa rab yin
NK077(tsu)001:12014: na tshe dbang yang tshe phyi ma la thob pa'am
NK077(tsu)001:12015: / lan grangs gzhan du thob par nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:12016: de yang phyag rgya gcig pa 'di'i lam ma nor
NK077(tsu)001:12017: ba tshul bzhin nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu ni
NK077(tsu)001:12018: / phyogs mthun du gzugs sku gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12019: thun mong du lha mi'i lus khyad par 'phags thob pa ni spyi tsam yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:12020: bye brag tu nye sbyor ni blo rtsal dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12021: brtson pa che na thod rgal du rnam smin rnams rig 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12022: blo rtsal dang brtson pa chung na /
NK077(tsu)001:12023: thar chag spros pa phyag rgya la sbyor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:12024: spyir gyi thob rgal gyi 'byung sa go ba /
NK077(tsu)001:12025: 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan dang gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:12026: dang po thod rgal 'byung sa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12027: zag bcas kyi lam gyi skabs su /
NK077(tsu)001:12029: spros bcas gnyis nas 'byung srid kyis khyab pa ni med /
NK077(tsu)001:12030: zag med lam gyi skabs su /
NK077(tsu)001:12031: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12032: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gnyis kyi sa nas 'byung ba srid kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:12034: gnyis pa thod rgal gyi go ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12035: lam bar nas bor nas grangs kyi 'og ma /
NK077(tsu)001:12036: don gyi gong ma la sbyor ba zhig yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12037: gsum pa thod rgal 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12038: lam rim gyis pa gang zhig /lam bar nas bor
NK077(tsu)001:12039: du yod pa dang gcig /ngang gi blo che ba
NK077(tsu)001:12040: dang gnyis / stong pa dang snying rje dbyer med sgom pa'i lam pa yin pa dang gsum mo //
NK077(tsu)001:12042: de las gzhan du mi 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:12044: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12045: snying rje sgyu ma sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gnyis ngang gi blo che ba yin yang /
NK077(tsu)001:12046: lam phyag rgya gcig spros tshom bu tshogs bsgrub dang gsum bar nas bor du yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:12047: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med sgom pa'i lam pa ma yin pa'i phyir thod rgal mi 'byung la /
NK077(tsu)001:12048: zag bcas bar chad med pa'i lam /
NK077(tsu)001:12049: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa blo che shos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12050: zag med mthar lam lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gnyis ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12051: ngang gi blo che ba yang yin /
NK077(tsu)001:12052: stong pa dang snying rje dbyer med sgom pa'i lam pa yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:12053: lam bar la bor du med pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:12055: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin stong pa dang snying rje dbyer med sgom pa'i lam pa yang yin /
NK077(tsu)001:12056: lam bar nas bor rgyu yang sgom lam dang mthar lam gnyis yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:12057: ngang gis blo chung ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:12059: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12061: rnal 'byor pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i rig 'dzin las
NK077(tsu)001:12062: su rung rnams kyis lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po
NK077(tsu)001:12063: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba rdzogs par
NK077(tsu)001:12064: 'gyur zhing ting nge 'dzin lhar gsal ba'i tshad yul
NK077(tsu)001:12065: gyis mi 'phrog pa la brten pa thob nas yid
NK077(tsu)001:12066: gnyis dang the tshom med par gyur na /
NK077(tsu)001:12067: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs
NK077(tsu)001:12068: kyis dkyil 'khor gyi dngos grub chen po 'bar ba
NK077(tsu)001:12069: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen nyid du 'grub par
NK077(tsu)001:12070: 'gyur ro // ma thob kyang ngan song dang theg dman du ltung myur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:12072: 'di ltar bshad pa bzhin sgom zhi bsgrub par byas
NK077(tsu)001:12073: na 'bras bu tshe 'di la mngon sum du ma
NK077(tsu)001:12074: byung yang / tshe rabs skye ba thams cad du
NK077(tsu)001:12075: lha mi'i mtshan bzang po khyad par can dbang po
NK077(tsu)001:12076: gsal la tsham pa rdzogs shing bdag gzhan gyi sdug
NK077(tsu)001:12077: bsngal sel bar byed pa'i gang zag la skye ba
NK077(tsu)001:12078: byung yang / blang ngo // bde bar gshegs pa sprul pa'i sku 'jig rten du 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12079: gnas dang dus kyis mi bskol zhing 'phrad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12080: 'phrad nas kyang mtshan nyid kyi theg par 'jug par mi 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:12081: theg mchog gsang sngags bla na med pa'i byang chub las mi ldog pa'i gzung la zhugs pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:12082: de lta bu'i yon tan yod pa de bas na
NK077(tsu)001:12083: gsang sngags kyi lam phyag rgya gcig pa 'di dang
NK077(tsu)001:12087: bden gsum dbyer med lha phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting
NK077(tsu)001:12088: nge 'dzin ni ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig
NK077(tsu)001:12089: don rnams gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don
NK077(tsu)001:12090: gyi na le'u ste yas bgrang lnga pa'i don du
NK077(tsu)001:12091: gada'o // le'u drug pa spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:12093: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12095: rang gi yi dam gyi lha zhi khro phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:12096: gcig pa rtogs shing goms pa'i ngang la phyag 'tshal
NK077(tsu)001:12097: te / lha gcig las du ma spros pa'i tshul
NK077(tsu)001:12098: du sgom pa phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:12099: rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa bshad par
NK077(tsu)001:12100: te / bya'o // gzhung gi don la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12102: lus snga ma dang mthun par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12104: phyag rgya spros bcas sgom pa'i gzhi bo'i lus mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12105: sngar de ting gi skabs su don bco lnga bshad pa de lta bur /
NK077(tsu)001:12106: 'dir yang don bco lnga bzhag pa de rnam par grol ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:12107: yan lag rgyas par bshad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12108: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la don bco lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:12109: dang po sngon bya ba la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:12111: sngon du rten bzhengs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12113: de ting stong pa chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12115: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor rnam pa gsum phyag rgya spros pa'i sngon du rdzogs par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12116: sa la sogs pa'i khung nas gser dngul ra shing
NK077(tsu)001:12117: la sogs pa rnams la gsal ba'i sku gsung thugs
NK077(tsu)001:12125: rba shing la sogs pa 'bur du brkos pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:12126: gser dngul zangs gsum la lugs su blugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12127: 'jim pa las 'der po byas pa la sogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:12128: dkyil 'khor ni las dang bya bas lhag pa'i gzugs
NK077(tsu)001:12129: brnyan gyi bsgrub pa'i khang bu dang bcas pa dngos
NK077(tsu)001:12131: ye shes kyi byin rlabs dang rab gnas ldan par byas la rten du gzung bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12132: de yang gong gi ri mo rgyu bzhi 'bur lugs 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:12134: shing shun ras kyi dur khrod kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:12135: zhing chen ras la kha dog lngas //
NK077(tsu)001:12136: phyag rgya 'bar ba'i gzugs bris nas //
NK077(tsu)001:12137: de ni mtshan ma 'byung ba'i rten //
NK077(tsu)001:12138: rdo dang shel rdo la sogs pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:12139: dung dang ba so'i rgyu las ni //
NK077(tsu)001:12140: mkhas pas 'bur du btod byas nas //
NK077(tsu)001:12141: mtshan ma 'byung ba'i rten du bya //
NK077(tsu)001:12142: gser dngul rin chen la sogs pa //
NK077(tsu)001:12143: zangs lcags 'bar ba'i rgyu dag las //
NK077(tsu)001:12144: mtshon gyis blugs te ma nyams na //
NK077(tsu)001:12146: klag sha byang chub shing la sogs //
NK077(tsu)001:12147: klu shing yal ga mnyen pa la //
NK077(tsu)001:12148: phyag rgya'i lugs te legs sbyar nas //
NK077(tsu)001:12149: de yang rten du mkhas par bshad //
NK077(tsu)001:12150: mnyen zhing spyin pa'i mchog rnams la //
NK077(tsu)001:12151: gzhan dang 'brel khug legs sbyar te //
NK077(tsu)001:12152: phyag rgya chen po'i gzugs byas nas //
NK077(tsu)001:12157: ma h+aa b+ha ling te gtor ma chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12158: a mri ta bdud rtsi sman dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12160: phyi'i mchod pa rnam lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12161: nang gi mchod pa gsum po rnams dgra bcom lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12162: sems can rnams kyi dug gsum bsdus nas //
NK077(tsu)001:12163: dpa' chen po'i zhal g.yas dkar ba la bdud rtsi g.yas /
NK077(tsu)001:12164: g.yon dmar ba la rak+ta g.yon /
NK077(tsu)001:12165: dbus mthing ka la gtor ma 'bul ba yin pas gtor chen dbus su'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12166: rol mo'i bye brag mi 'dra ba'i mchod pa rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12172: dad ldan dwangs ba 'dren pa'i dmigs pa'i cha rkyen yod byad rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:12173: ci ltar 'os pa bzhin du bsdu bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12174: phrin las kyi sngon du bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12177: rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i tho brtsig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12178: khro bcus bsrung ba'i gur chen phub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12179: de nas yan lag brgyad pa nas bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12182: byin phab yan chad kyi rim pa rdzogs par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12183: rang nyid las kyi bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:12184: yi dam gyi lha gang yin pa'i rnal 'byor dang
NK077(tsu)001:12185: ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyi nang gi mchod
NK077(tsu)001:12186: rdzas rnams tshul bzhin byin gyis rlabs par byas la
NK077(tsu)001:12187: / de yang thog mar bdud rtsi'i chus bsang ba
NK077(tsu)001:12188: gzhung bzhin du bya zhing bgegs bskrad de mchod pa
NK077(tsu)001:12189: byin gyis rlabs la bstan la 'dug go //
NK077(tsu)001:12190: gnyis pa dgos ched la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12194: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs par bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:12195: spyod yul thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du byin gyis
NK077(tsu)001:12196: rlabs pa dang yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi
NK077(tsu)001:12197: sa mthar dbyung ba ste thob par bya ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:12198: / tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa la spros pa mthar
NK077(tsu)001:12199: phyin pa'i dus kyi bsgrub dgos pa'i phyir sgom pa
NK077(tsu)001:12201: dgug pa ni dbang du bsdu ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12203: yul khams la sogs pa dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12208: dgra bgegs gzhan du bskrad cing btang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12209: mi mthun pa'i dgra'i yul khams gzhan du bskrad cing btong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12211: gcan gzan gyi kha bcing ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12212: ma mo'i jag cing bla bzung la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12214: byad du bcug pa dgrol ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12215: pha rol gyi gdug pa'i mthu thams cad dgrol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12217: lcags brtson dong nas dgrol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12223: srin bu lo thog gso ba la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12225: dgra bgegs la sogs pa gsod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12228: bdud kyi dpung pham par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12231: phyogs thams cad las rgyal bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12232: de rnams phyag rgya spros pa snang 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin 'dis byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:12233: rnal 'byor pa gang dag gdul bya ci snyed pa rnams phyag rgya spros pa'i sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12234: phrin las kyi gdul bya 'khor ba nas 'don dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:12235: de don gyi phyag rgya spros pa la dgos ched yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12236: gsum pa sgom thabs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:12237: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor ba skyed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12238: ye shes kyis dal spyan drangs shing bstim pa dang de la mchod cing phrin las kyi rim pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12243: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor la brtan pa thob
NK077(tsu)001:12244: nas phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor sgom pa'ang rnam
NK077(tsu)001:12245: pa gnyis te / gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:12246: phyag rgya gcig pa dang rjes su mthun par zhi ba spros bcas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12247: khro bo spros bcas gnyis ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:12248: zhi khro de gnyis gang rung re re la rim
NK077(tsu)001:12249: dang cig char gyi tshul gnyis kyi gdul bya'i blo
NK077(tsu)001:12250: che chung gi rim pa dang ldan par gang 'tshams
NK077(tsu)001:12252: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12253: zhi ba la bslab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12259: snga ma zhi ba de la rim gyis pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12260: cig char ba gnyis yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12265: mdor bstan gyi skabs su rim cig char gnyis phye
NK077(tsu)001:12266: bas phyi ma cig char du 'jug pa de song
NK077(tsu)001:12267: / phyag rgya gcig pa bzhin du cig char du 'jug pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12268: dper na nam mkha' la nyi zla gza' skar dus
NK077(tsu)001:12269: gcig gsal ba de chu dkyil rgya mtsho dwangs bar
NK077(tsu)001:12270: gzugs brnyan gsal bar 'char ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:12271: phyag rgya spros pa'i sku gsal ba de yang gcig gis 'od du 'bar ba sgom pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:12272: snying po brjod pas zhi ba'i 'khor lo lha'i dkyil
NK077(tsu)001:12273: 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang yin de gsal ba'o
NK077(tsu)001:12278: de sngon phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs na bstan pa bzhin spros bcas rim gyis 'jug pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12280: lam snga ma'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin gsum ka'i
NK077(tsu)001:12281: phyag rgya gcig pa goms pa'i stobs kyis phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:12282: spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12283: dper na shes bya gcig shes nas du ma la
NK077(tsu)001:12284: slob pa'i tshul du phyag rgya spros pa lha'i dkyil
NK077(tsu)001:12285: 'khor du ma'ang / phyag rgya gcig pa la goms pa'i dbang gsal bar byed pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:12287: zhi ba las khro bor ma bsgyur ba'am ma bcos rnal ma zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12288: 'khor lo ste dal spros pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12291: zhal phyag spros pa dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12292: rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12294: dal spros pa la bslab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12296: dal la rgyas bsdus 'bring gsum yod pa la dang po dal bsdus pa lha brgyad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12297: rigs lnga yab yum bcu sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:12298: 'bring po la bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni go sla'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12299: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor la lha brgyad cu rtsa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12300: rigs lnga re res rigs kyi gtso byas pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:12301: yab yum bcu bcu ste lnga bcu tham pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12302: sems dpa' sems ma bcu drug ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12304: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de don bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12306: thub pa drug ste brgyad cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:12307: dkyil 'khor spros pa de gsum rim par slob pa'i tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:12308: tshom bu spros pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:12310: tshom bu gcig pa la bslab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12312: dal spros pa gang du song nas gnyis pa tshom bu la bslab pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12313: bdag ste rigs kyi bdag po rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12314: gnas pa'i gzhal yas 'khor lo rtsib bzhi pa lte
NK077(tsu)001:12315: ba mu khyud dang bcas pa gru chad la sgo
NK077(tsu)001:12316: dod pa gsal bar bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12317: gdan seng ge'i khri la sogs sum brtsegs dang lnga brtsegs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12318: ldan pa'i dbus kyi lte ba na rigs kyi bdag
NK077(tsu)001:12319: po gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gnas
NK077(tsu)001:12320: pa de la rdo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' yab
NK077(tsu)001:12321: yum brgyad / phyogs bzhi'i khro bo yab yum brgyad kyis bskor te /
NK077(tsu)001:12322: tshom bu gcig pa la lha bco brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:12323: lha'i ming ni dmar mtshan bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12326: de ltar tshom bu gcig pa la blo brtan pa thob nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12331: thugs rdo rje sems dpa' rnams la lha bcu bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12332: 'khor lo'i pho brang du lha sum cu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12333: phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo bcu drug ste lha zhe drug rdzogs par sgom pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:12334: yi ge +aahmh'u 'bru gsum sku gsung thugs kyi barda'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12335: tshom bu lnga pa la bslab pas gsum pa lha nyung /
NK077(tsu)001:12336: ting nge 'dzin ni blo stobs chung bas mi'i dbang
NK077(tsu)001:12337: du zhe drug tshom bu gtso bo gsum pa de
NK077(tsu)001:12338: la shin tu ting nge 'dzin goms shing 'dris par
NK077(tsu)001:12340: lha'i rnam grangs mchan bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12343: de ltar tshom bu gsum pa la blo brtan pa
NK077(tsu)001:12344: thob nas gtso bo zhal shar du gzigs pa'i g.yas
NK077(tsu)001:12345: lho'i rtsibs dang / g.yon byang gi rtsibs nyid du /
NK077(tsu)001:12346: yon tan gyi rigs rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12347: phrin las kyi rigs don yon grub pa yab yum
NK077(tsu)001:12348: dkyil du gnas pa la 'khor rang rang gi sems
NK077(tsu)001:12349: dpa' yab yum brgyad kyi 'khor dang bcas pa bzhag
NK077(tsu)001:12350: ste pho brang gi lha bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:12351: phyogs mtshams steng 'og gi khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste lha bdun cu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12352: de'i steng du kun bzang yab yum gnyis thub pa
NK077(tsu)001:12353: drug /sgo ba bzhi dang brgyad cu yin yang zer
NK077(tsu)001:12354: / 'di rnams kyi ming gi rnam grangs dmar mchan du gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:12355: tshom bu gsum pa bas lnga pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:12356: stobs che bas rnal 'byor dbang du sku gsung thugs
NK077(tsu)001:12357: yon tan phrin las bsgrub pa'i tshom bu lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:12358: de la shin tu 'dris te spros pa'i ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:12359: 'dzin mthar phyin nas bsgrub pa dus kyi tshogs bsgrub
NK077(tsu)001:12360: la sbyar ro // skabs 'dir tshom bu dang dkyil 'khor gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:12361: sgom bya lha'i khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12362: sgom byed rnal 'byor pa'i khyad par gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:12364: gtso bo'i ngos nas bzhag pa tshom bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12365: gtso bo'i rigs gcig gi byas pa tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12366: gtso bo'i rigs gsum gyis byas pa tshom bu gsum pa /
NK077(tsu)001:12367: gtso bo'i rigs lngas byas pa tshom bu lnga pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12368: de dag kyang gtso bo 'khor lha grangs /
NK077(tsu)001:12369: gral nges pa can yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12370: lha'i rnam grangs byung rdzogs kyis ngos nas bzhag pa dal ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12371: lha grangs dang gral ma nges pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12372: yang rigs 'gyur gyi ye shes mi 'gyur ba tshom bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12373: rigs dang ye shes gnyis ka 'gyur ba dal du bzhed pa yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12374: de dag gi go don ni sku sgyu 'phrul gyi
NK077(tsu)001:12375: skabs su gtso bo dbus kyi rnam snang gi byed
NK077(tsu)001:12376: la / gsung sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs su dbus kyi
NK077(tsu)001:12377: gtso bo mtha' yas kyi byed pa la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:12378: la / ni / rigs 'gyur ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:12380: dbus kyi gtso bo'i thugs stong pa nyid kyi ye shes yin pa la sogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12381: rigs 'gyur yang ye shes mi 'gyur ba zhes bya la /
NK077(tsu)001:12382: dbus kyi gtso bo rnam snang gi byed na /
NK077(tsu)001:12383: de'i thugs me long lta bu'i ye shes yin pa la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12384: dbus kyis gtso bo mtha' yas kyi byed na /
NK077(tsu)001:12385: de'i thugs so sor rtags pa'i ye shes yin pa la sogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12386: rigs dang ye shes gnyis ka 'gyur zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12387: de'i phyir na thugs sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:12388: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa kun gyi gtso bo rdo rje'i rigs yin pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:12390: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa kun gtso bo /
NK077(tsu)001:12391: de bzhin rigs yin pa la sogs pa'i bzhed pa'ang yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12392: gnyis pa sgom byed rnal 'byor pa'i khyad par ni
NK077(tsu)001:12393: lha dang rnal 'byor pa brang sprad du sgom pa
NK077(tsu)001:12395: rnal 'byor pho mo gang rung gcig gis kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:12396: lha'i dkyil 'khor byung rdzogs su sgom pa dkyil 'khor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:12397: yang na pho mo zung du 'brel ba'i sgo nas bsgrub pa ni tshom bu /
NK077(tsu)001:12398: pho rkyang mo rkyang gi bsgrub tu rung ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12399: dkyil 'khor zhes bzhed pa yang yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:12401: dkyil 'khor dang tshom bu 'di gnyis gang rung gi chog na /
NK077(tsu)001:12402: gnyis la bslab pa don med du thal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12403: gnyis ka la bslab dgos na /
NK077(tsu)001:12404: gcig spros nas mthong lam la sbyor mi srid par 'gyur zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:12405: blo chung na gnyis ka dgos shing /
NK077(tsu)001:12406: che na dal kho nas sbyor srid do //
NK077(tsu)001:12407: de bzhin du tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung gcig gis kyang 'bras bu la sbyor na /
NK077(tsu)001:12408: brten nas mdun rgyab bsgrub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12410: brten pa g.yas dang g.yon nyid du /
NK077(tsu)001:12411: zhes rim par sbyar bar gsung pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:12412: gsum ka sgom dgos na yang na sku gsung thugs nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:12413: zhes 'dam kar gsung pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:12414: slob dus su rim par sgom la /
NK077(tsu)001:12415: bsgrub dus su gang rung sgom pas 'bras bu la sbyor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:12419: rtsa ba'i rnam grangs spros pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12421: mdor bstan gyi gsum pa rnam grangs spros bcas la bslab pa'i dang po ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12422: rtsa ba'i lha gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa'i sku
NK077(tsu)001:12423: nyid du gsal ba'i ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa
NK077(tsu)001:12424: thob nas sku rnam snang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12425: gsung gi snang ba mtha' yas 'khor med pa'i ngo bor gsal bar bya /
NK077(tsu)001:12426: de ltar gsum po la ting nge 'dzin 'tshor ba med par brtan pa thob na /
NK077(tsu)001:12427: yon tan rin chen 'byung ldan dang //
NK077(tsu)001:12428: phrin las don grub ste rigs lnga char sangs rgyas rdzogs par sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:12429: de yang yab yum zung du 'brel par sgom pa
NK077(tsu)001:12430: la blo brtan pa thob par byas nas bzhi bcu
NK077(tsu)001:12432: gtso bo rigs lnga po'i don la rang rang gi
NK077(tsu)001:12433: rigs su spros pa'i sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:12434: su byed pa gang gis kyang ma bcos ngang gis
NK077(tsu)001:12435: gnas pa la de ltar rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi
NK077(tsu)001:12436: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor du sgom
NK077(tsu)001:12437: mo // yan lag gi rnam grangs spros pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:12439: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor bslab pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12443: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu tham pa rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par sgom ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12444: de yang bdag rtsa ba'i lha mi bskyod pa yab yum yin pa'i dbang brtsan du byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12446: gzhan yan lag gi lha yab nyi shu rtsa gsum
NK077(tsu)001:12447: rtsa ba'i lha yab la dgod de dbu la rnam
NK077(tsu)001:12448: snang dang / lag pa gnyis kyis 'dam rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la kun bzang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12449: g.yon gyi cha la rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12450: rkang pa gnyid kyi 'dam rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la don sgrubs /
NK077(tsu)001:12451: g.yon gyi cha la mtha' yas /
NK077(tsu)001:12454: lce rnams kyi 'dam rtsa'i g.yas kyis cha rnams su rim pa bzhin sa snying phyag rdor nam snying /
NK077(tsu)001:12455: spyan gzigs g.yon gyi cha rnams su /
NK077(tsu)001:12470: sum mdo rnams su lha la sogs pa'i thub drug bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12471: de bzhin du yan lag lha yum bcu bdun rtsa ba'i lha yum la bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12472: bkod tshul sngar gyi yab dang mtshungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:12473: rtsa ba'i lha rnam snang yab yum dbang ba can du byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12474: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu bkod na /
NK077(tsu)001:12475: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dam rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la mi bskyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12476: g.yon gyi cha la kun tu bzang po bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12477: de bzhin du rin 'byung yab yum la sogs pa'i rtsa ba'i lha yab yum /
NK077(tsu)001:12478: rang rang gi bskyed pa gang yin du /
NK077(tsu)001:12479: kun bzang yab yum bkod la /
NK077(tsu)001:12480: gzhan rnams sngar mi bskyod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:12481: yan lag gi lha bkod pa dang mtshungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:12482: yang thub drug re re'ang rtsa ba'i lha yin pa'i dbang btsan du byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:12483: thub drug la yum med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12484: g.yas kyi cha la yab nyi shu rtsa gsum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12485: g.yon gyi cha la yum bcu bdun bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12486: spyi bo'i g.yas kyi cha la rnam snang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12487: g.yon gyi cha la spyan ma /
NK077(tsu)001:12488: lag pa g.yas kyi 'dam rtsa'i mdun dang rgyab la /
NK077(tsu)001:12491: rkang pa g.yas kyi 'dam rtsa'i mdun dang rgyab tu /
NK077(tsu)001:12495: lce rnams kyi rtsa'i nang du /
NK077(tsu)001:12497: phyi ru phyi'i sems ma bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12498: lag mthil g.yas kyis mdun dang rgyab tu /
NK077(tsu)001:12501: rkang mthil g.yas kyi mdun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12507: mtshog mar kun tu bzang po //
NK077(tsu)001:12508: lta zur la sogs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:12509: lha ma yin la sogs pa'i thub pa dgod pa sngar dang mtshungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:12510: mdor na rtsa ba'i lha gang yin yang /
NK077(tsu)001:12511: yum dang bcas pa rnams rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis ka la /
NK077(tsu)001:12512: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu dgod pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:12513: yum med thub pa rnams rtsa ba'i lha re re
NK077(tsu)001:12514: la yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu bzhi bcu dgod
NK077(tsu)001:12515: pa yin te / yan lag gi lha kun bzang yab yum ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12516: rtsa ba'i lha gang dang gang yin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:12517: de dang de'i gnas su dgod pa ni kun mthun pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12518: de ltar yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12519: rags pa'i cha nas thabs kyi lhar bzhag la /
NK077(tsu)001:12520: de nyid yan lag ces pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12521: mi gcig grub na snying gcig grub pa'i tshul du /
NK077(tsu)001:12522: thabs kyi lha re re'i yang srog gis sgor /
NK077(tsu)001:12523: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba re re sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:12524: phra ba'i cha nas shes rab kyi lhar bzhag pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12525: de ltar thabs dang shes rab kyi lha brgyad cu la /
NK077(tsu)001:12526: shes rab kyis lha bzhi bcu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12527: bu mos pha'i rab mi zin pa'i tshul du rgyan dang cha lugs rnam par spangs pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:12528: thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu po rtsa ba'i lha yab
NK077(tsu)001:12529: yum gnyis la bkod pa rnams re re la yang
NK077(tsu)001:12534: sku gsung thugs kyi lha re re ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12536: de ltar thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu dang bcas pa brgya drug cu po re re yang /
NK077(tsu)001:12537: gong gi bdag ste zhes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12538: rang rang gi rigs kyi bdag pos gtso byas pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:12539: dbu brgyan rigs kyi lha lnga ste brgyad bargya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12540: mdor na thabs dang shes rab kyi lha brgyad cu
NK077(tsu)001:12541: sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK077(tsu)001:12542: brgya nyi shu / dbu brgyan gyi lha brgyad brgya ste kun dril bas /
NK077(tsu)001:12543: rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la /
NK077(tsu)001:12544: yan lag lhag pa'i lha stong sgom pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12545: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12546: de ci ltar ldan tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:12548: rtsa ba'i lha stong ste yab rdo rje sems dpa'
NK077(tsu)001:12549: dang dpyal te yum nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:12550: kyi sku phyag rgya dang de la bkod pa'i sangs
NK077(tsu)001:12551: rgyas stong gi dal yang sku ri rab tsam la
NK077(tsu)001:12552: rgyan til 'bru tsam bkod pa'i tshul bzhin du thun
NK077(tsu)001:12553: mong dang / thun mong ma yin pa'i dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12554: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi brgyan cing spras pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12555: nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12557: gong gi lha stong tsho ltar de ltar rigs kyi gtso bo lnga yod pa'i nang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12558: thugs kyi rigs chos kyi ye shes mchog tu gyur
NK077(tsu)001:12559: pa rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la ldan par
NK077(tsu)001:12560: byas nas / chos bya ba mo yid byed pa po kun bzang yab yum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12561: rgyal ba rigs bzhi'ang yab yum la /
NK077(tsu)001:12562: stong tsho re sgom par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12563: stong tsho drug go bcu gnyis ni sems dpa' yab yum zung brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12564: sgo ba yab yum zung bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12565: de ltar yab yum zung bcu gnyis la stong tsho bcu gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:12566: gong gi stong tsho drug gi steng du stong tsho bcu gnyis bzhag pas stong tsho bco brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:12567: drug gi 'od 'phro ba 'bar zhes pa 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:12568: thub pa drug la stong tsho drug go //
NK077(tsu)001:12569: gong gi stong tsho brgyad po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12570: stong tsho nyi shu rtsa bzhi po thams cad kyang
NK077(tsu)001:12571: 'od zer 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar ba dang bcas
NK077(tsu)001:12573: gnyis khri bzhi stong gi dal la bslab pa la
NK077(tsu)001:12574: gnyis khri bzhi stong dus gcig gsal zhes brjod do
NK077(tsu)001:12575: // bsam yas lhun grub kyi dal la bslab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12577: phyi snod phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams ma lus
NK077(tsu)001:12578: pa thams cad lha'i gzhal yas su sgom pa la
NK077(tsu)001:12579: nyi zla gza' skar thams cad gdan dang rgyan du
NK077(tsu)001:12580: gsal zhing / nang bcud sems can thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i dal ma lus par sgom pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12581: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i ti nga nge 'dzin de nyid la slob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12582: zhal phyag spros pa la bslab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12584: grangs kyi bzhi pa zhal phyag spros pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12585: dang po tshom bu gcig pa la zhal gsum drug sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:12586: gcig pa la brtan pa thob nas tshom bu gsum
NK077(tsu)001:12587: pa la'ang zhal gsum phyag drug sgom pa gong gi
NK077(tsu)001:12588: de bzhin de la brten nas tshom bu lnga pa
NK077(tsu)001:12589: la'ang / zhal gsum phyag drug pa snga ma'i rjes su mthun por goms nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12590: de ltar phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i skabs
NK077(tsu)001:12591: su lha kun la zhal gsum phyag drug par rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:12592: par mos slob tsam du gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12593: de yang slob rim tsam la 'ga' zhig dngos kyi spyod yul ma yin par go dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:12598: zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur ba'i 'khor lo sgom pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:12599: zhi ba'i skabs ltar de bzhin te /
NK077(tsu)001:12604: rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12606: dal spros pa la bslab pa dang /
