NK077(tsu)001:12608: dang po khro bo bsdus pa lnga bcu rtsa brgyad sgom pa ni go sla'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12610: dal 'bring po khro bo bcu bsnan pa ste drug cu rtsa brgyad sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:12611: rgyas pa la de bzhin zhi ba ltar yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:12612: khrag 'thung rigs lnga la pho brang gi lha lnga bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:12613: gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu bsnan pas bdun cu /
NK077(tsu)001:12614: khro bo bcu ste brgyad cu /
NK077(tsu)001:12615: dbang mo nyer brgyad dang brgya rtsa brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:12618: gcig pa dang gsum pa la bslab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12620: dang po tshom bu gcig pa la bslab pa na /
NK077(tsu)001:12621: dbus kyi lte ba la gtso bo badz+ra he ru
NK077(tsu)001:12622: ka yab yum gyi gzhi bo byas pa la thugs
NK077(tsu)001:12623: kyi rigs khro bo yab yum brgyad kyis bskor bas
NK077(tsu)001:12624: bcu dang / dbang mo yan chad bsnan pas lnga bcu rtsa brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:12626: gtso bo las 'khor khro mo nyi shu /
NK077(tsu)001:12628: khro bcu yab yum nyi shu dang bcas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12630: lha bdun cu don brgyad 'dod pa yang yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12631: tshom bu gsum pa la bslab pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12632: dbus su thugs kyi rigs badz+ra he ru ka yin
NK077(tsu)001:12633: pa la sku'i rigs b+hud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum
NK077(tsu)001:12634: bcu / gsung gi rigs pad+ma he ru ka yab yum bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:12635: gtso bo yab yum bcu yod pa'i mdun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12636: rgyab ste shar nub gnyis kyis rtsibs la pho brang
NK077(tsu)001:12637: gi khrag 'thung sum cu gsal bar sgom de la
NK077(tsu)001:12638: brten nas 'khor gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu /
NK077(tsu)001:12640: khro bo khro mo nyi shu dang bcas pa sgom ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12641: tshom bu gsum pa la lha dgu bcu go brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:12644: de ltar gong gi sku gsung thugs kyi tshom bu
NK077(tsu)001:12645: la ting nge 'dzin brtan par byas nas gtso bo'i
NK077(tsu)001:12647: lho byang gi rtsibs la yon tan gyi rigs rat+na he ru ka dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12648: las kyi rigs kyi khro bo karma he ru yab
NK077(tsu)001:12649: yum ste gtso bo yab yum gsal bar sgom nas
NK077(tsu)001:12650: de dag la rang rang gi rigs chung gis he
NK077(tsu)001:12651: ru ka brgyad brgyad kyis bskor te /
NK077(tsu)001:12652: pho brang 'khor lo'i lha lnga bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:12655: khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12656: tshom bu lnga pa la lha brgya dang bco brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12658: brgya rtsa brgyad yang zer de thams cad yongs su
NK077(tsu)001:12659: rdzogs par sgom pa'i rim pa bzhin du sgom par
NK077(tsu)001:12660: gang byas pa de la tshun thun tshod ma sun
NK077(tsu)001:12661: par je gsal du gyen du 'phar zhing brtan par
NK077(tsu)001:12662: sgom pa'o // rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12664: rtsa ba'i rnam grangs la bslab pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12666: zhi ba dang rjes su mthun pa'i 'jigs byed khro
NK077(tsu)001:12667: bo'i rnam grangs spros pa dag kyang rigs gcig rdo
NK077(tsu)001:12668: rje'i rigs badz+ra he ru ka dang gnyis de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:12669: gshegs pa'i rigs b+hud+d+ha he ru ka dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12671: bzhi rin po che'i rigs rat+na lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:12672: las kyi rigs kar ma he ru ka ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12673: gtso bo rigs lnga yab yum bcu la ting nge 'dzin gsal ba sgom pa mthar phyin nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12674: de re re la'ang 'khor lo lnga'i rtsibs kyi chas
NK077(tsu)001:12675: rigs chung gi he ru ka brgyad kyis bskor ba
NK077(tsu)001:12676: / de ltar pho brang gis lha bcu thams cad pa'i tshom bu la gnas ma brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12677: yul ma brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12678: slas mo dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12679: h'u chen la sogs pa'i khro bo bcu ste brgya rtsa brgyad kyi lhar gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12680: yan lag gi rnam grangs la bslab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12682: gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gnyis la
NK077(tsu)001:12683: yan lag gi lha bkod pa thabs kyis lha lnga
NK077(tsu)001:12685: de la shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' re sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12686: nga brgyad pa cha lnga'i grangs ni nyis brgya dang dgu bcu'i lha rnams kyi yan lag tu ldan /
NK077(tsu)001:12687: de rnams la dbu brgyan gyi lha lnga lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:12688: de ltar lnga bcu rtsa brgyad po kun la brtsis pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12689: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu tham pa yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12692: thabs kyi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12693: shes rab kyi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12694: sku'i lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12695: gsung gi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12696: thugs kyi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12697: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad cha lnga'i grangs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12698: gnyis brgya dang dgu bcu zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12700: de re re la yang dbu rgyan rigs kyi lha lnga dang ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12701: ye shes kyi dal 'ba' zhig stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu yod la /
NK077(tsu)001:12703: stong bdun brgya bzhi bcu dang ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12705: de ltar brtsir mi btub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12706: 'dir badz+ra he ru ka yab yum la /
NK077(tsu)001:12707: gzhan lha lnga bcu rtsa drug bkod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12708: rags pa thabs kyi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12709: de dag gis thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' sgom pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12710: phra ba shes rab kyi lha dang brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12714: nga brgyad phrag lnga la gnyis brgya dgu bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:12715: de la phra ba ye shes sems dpa' nga brgyad la /
NK077(tsu)001:12717: nga brgyad phrag bzhi pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:12718: dbu brgyan ye shes kyi lha lnga lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12719: ye shes sems dpa' stong dang brgya drug cu yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12720: de'i steng du rtsa ba'i lha gnyis brgya dgu bcu bsnan pas stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:12721: de bzhin du b+hud+d+ha he ru ka /rat+na /
NK077(tsu)001:12723: karma ste rigs lnga yab yum cha re la /
NK077(tsu)001:12724: stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu po re re ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12725: dbang mo yan chad lnga bcu rtsa gsum po re
NK077(tsu)001:12726: re stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu po re re ste
NK077(tsu)001:12728: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12729: yang na dmar mchan ltar brtsi na //
NK077(tsu)001:12735: zhal phyag spros pa ni dang po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12736: de nas zhal gsum phyag drug /de nas dbu dgu
NK077(tsu)001:12737: dang phyag bco brgyad phyag kun phyag mtshan dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:12738: pa dang / de nas dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12739: de nas dbu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya de ltar zhabs brgyad brgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12740: de nas zhal phyag grangs med pa'i bar du slob par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12741: de lam pa gang gis spyod yul yin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12743: zhal phyag gi rnam grangs de dag /gang zag rim
NK077(tsu)001:12744: gyis pa slob pa'i thabs su brjod kyi dngos kyi
NK077(tsu)001:12747: tshogs lam phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis su zhal gsum phyag drug dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12748: sbyor lam du dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12749: thun mong du dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig /phyag bzhi bcu zhe gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12750: sgom lam du dbu dgu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12751: zhal phyag grangs med par sgom pa de mthar phyin
NK077(tsu)001:12752: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi spyod yul yin par ltar
NK077(tsu)001:12754: phrin las kyi rim pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12756: phrin las gzhung gis rim pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12758: gong du bstan pa de ltar mthong lam lhag pa
NK077(tsu)001:12759: ting nge 'dzin gyis spros bcas la bzhi yod pa
NK077(tsu)001:12760: rnams la / dang po ting nge 'dzin la zhugs bar du slob /
NK077(tsu)001:12761: tha ma mthar phyin par byas nas bar skabs su dam tshig gi dal bskyed /
NK077(tsu)001:12762: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dal gyi yul 'og min nas /
NK077(tsu)001:12765: gnyis su med bzhugs shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol
NK077(tsu)001:12766: ba la sogs pa'i cho ga dang ldan par bya
NK077(tsu)001:12767: ste / de nas phyag legs pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12772: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pas gzhung bzhin du mchod par byas nas bstod pa bya /
NK077(tsu)001:12774: ldan nas 'dzab dang bsnyen pa dang tshogs rnams gzhung bzhin du bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12775: lhag ma dang 'jug gis rim pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12777: bar skabs su lhag ma la dbang ba'i gnas re
NK077(tsu)001:12778: ba bskangs nas dang po dam bsgrag phrin las bcol
NK077(tsu)001:12779: cing rang rang gi gnas su so so'i las la
NK077(tsu)001:12780: dagye'o // 'khor lo de la bsdus zhing lus srung go bgo /
NK077(tsu)001:12781: spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin kun /
NK077(tsu)001:12782: khro bo gang yin gyi man ngag sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12783: snang ba dam pa rgyan la sogs pa'i gzhung nas 'byung ba bzhin du bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12784: des na lta ba stong phyogs kha lta smra mkhan 'ga' zhig gis /
NK077(tsu)001:12785: chog khrigs la rtsis su mi byed de /
NK077(tsu)001:12787: bder gshegs mnyes byas las rnams la //
NK077(tsu)001:12788: yan lag tshigs su ma dag na //
NK077(tsu)001:12789: nyes byas las kyi rgyu des ni //
NK077(tsu)001:12790: dran pa'i dbang po nyams par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:12793: rang gi sgo gsum yi dam gyi //
NK077(tsu)001:12794: sku gsung thugs su rab sbyar la //
NK077(tsu)001:12795: rtag tu bzlas pa byed pa ni //
NK077(tsu)001:12796: byang chub gzungs la zhugs pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:12799: skye med kyi ngang la 'gags med kyi rtsal sbyangs zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:12800: gnyis med du rang grol ba'i thabs yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12801: 'di la yan lag brgyad pa nas bzung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12802: lus bsrungs go bgo yan chad la dgongs gzhi dgos
NK077(tsu)001:12803: ched lam tshod theg chen thun gyi nyams len byed
NK077(tsu)001:12804: lugs 'di dag la bsnyan rgyud kyi gdam skor chen
NK077(tsu)001:12805: mo rje btsun gong ma'i thugs dam man ngag gnad
NK077(tsu)001:12806: kyi lha khrid zhes bya ba las shes par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:12807: // lha sgom nas rtog pa lam khyer 'di rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:12810: nga rgyal brtan pa 'di gsum 'dzom dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:12811: de ma 'dzom na grol ba mi srid do //
NK077(tsu)001:12812: dal 'di nyid nyams su len pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:12813: blo rab kun bzang yab yum la brten te sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12814: blo 'bring rigs lnga yab yum la brten te sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12815: blo tha ma sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la brten te sangs rgyas pa yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:12816: 'di rnams kyi gnad rtogs dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:12817: 'di lta bu ma yin pa'i gsang sngags yin par khas ches pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:12818: khyer bskul 'ga' zhig ngag 'khyal yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:12820: mkhas pa chen po nyi ma rdo rjes /
NK077(tsu)001:12821: mu stegs rgyang 'phen gsang sngags bon gyer dang //
NK077(tsu)001:12822: dgongs pa gsal 'debs phrin las gyer sgom gnyis //
NK077(tsu)001:12825: bzhi pa ngo bo la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12827: ngo bo lha rang snang yul med zhi gnas lhag mthong zung 'brel du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12829: phung po lnga la sogs pa rtogs pa'i tshogs thams
NK077(tsu)001:12830: cad lha'i dal rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:12832: dper na rgya mtsho'i nang na nyi zla'i gzugs brnyan
NK077(tsu)001:12833: snang ba ci bzhin du phyi nang gi chos kun
NK077(tsu)001:12834: gyi dngos po thams cad rang rig pa nyid lhar
NK077(tsu)001:12835: gsal ba la / gcig dang du ma yongs kyis med de /
NK077(tsu)001:12836: lha 'gags med du spros tshogs sna tshogs su shar bas /
NK077(tsu)001:12838: shar ba'i dus de nyid na rang byung ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:12839: rig pa nyid las ma g.yos pas du ma'i mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:12840: dang bral ba'o // rtogs tshogs lha'i dal du gsal bas lhag mthong yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:12841: yul dang yul can med cing mi g.yo bar gnas
NK077(tsu)001:12842: pas zhi gnas de rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:12843: gyi ngo bor rgyal bas gsungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:12844: spros bcas sgom pa'i nges tshig /drang /
NK077(tsu)001:12845: rang bzhin gzhi nas bden gsum du spros pas de
NK077(tsu)001:12846: nyams su len pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin yang
NK077(tsu)001:12848: lha de yang gdul bya gdug pa can dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12849: 'dul ba'i ngo bo la khro bo dang zhi ba
NK077(tsu)001:12850: gnyis su spros de gnyis yang 'khor lo ste dal
NK077(tsu)001:12851: spros pa dang / phyag rgya ste rnam grangs spros pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12854: de ltar na gzhi lam kun nas spros pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:12855: gzhi mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu la yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12856: de yang lha du ma'i dkyil 'khor du spros pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12857: de ltar spros pas mnyam bzhag la gsal bas phyag
NK077(tsu)001:12858: rgya rnal 'byor gyi sgra don nam nges tshig 'grub
NK077(tsu)001:12859: pa'o // lnga pa skyon la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12861: le lo mtshan ma'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12863: spros pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas pa 'di yi tshe dman pa'i le lo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12864: snyoms las kyi le lo rnam pa gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12865: du ba la sogs pa mtshan ma'i mtha' lnga po
NK077(tsu)001:12866: dngos su 'byung ba mthong zhing de la bden par
NK077(tsu)001:12867: 'dzin na skyon du gyur pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:12868: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12870: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor pas 'chad par 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:12871: ba'i spyod yul 'di dag la dam par bzung na
NK077(tsu)001:12872: / bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad mthong ba rang 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12874: sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa grangs med pa 'jig rten
NK077(tsu)001:12875: du 'gyed pa mthong ba dang gcig /bdag gzhan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:12876: nang nas rang dam pa 'dug par mthong ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:12877: gnyis / bdag la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK077(tsu)001:12878: dpa' thams cad kyi dam par smra ba dang gsum
NK077(tsu)001:12879: gnyis / / rgyal bas gsung pa'i chos kun mngon sum du gsal bar mthong ba dang gzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12880: dus gsum gyi chos kun skad cig ma la gsal bar shes shing mthong ba dang lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:12881: rgyu drug gi lam dang gnas kun mthong ba drug /
NK077(tsu)001:12882: de la snying rje shugs las 'byung ba dang bdun /
NK077(tsu)001:12883: snod bcud kun kyang nyin mtshan med par gsal bar mthong ba dang brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:12884: ri brag la sogs ci la'ang bdag gi lus thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang dgu /
NK077(tsu)001:12885: nam mkha' la bya bzhin du 'gro zhing 'dug nus dang bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:12886: rgyal bas phyag brkyang nas bdag gi mgo la byug ste lung ston pa dang bcu gcig /
NK077(tsu)001:12887: 'gro ba kun gyi skad du chos smra ba dang bcu gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:12888: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad kyi bdag la bkur
NK077(tsu)001:12889: sti dang rim 'gro'i gnas su mthong ba dang bcu
NK077(tsu)001:12890: gsum / ting nge 'dzin gyi shugs la stong gsum
NK077(tsu)001:12891: lag mthil ltar mnyam par bkod pa dang bcu bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:12892: gsum / / de nyid rang bzhin sems nyid du gsal bar snang ba dang bco lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:12893: ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba'i spyod pa ci
NK077(tsu)001:12894: la yang thogs pa med par spyod nus so snyam
NK077(tsu)001:12895: pa dang bcu drug /dam pa'i don thar pa'i lam
NK077(tsu)001:12896: la zhugs par gyis shig /ces pa sangs rgyas byang
NK077(tsu)001:12897: sems rnams kyi bdag la bka' bsgo ba dang bcu
NK077(tsu)001:12898: bdun / 'jig rten pa'i gtso bo lha srin sde
NK077(tsu)001:12899: brgyad kyi bdag la mchod pa 'byung ba rnams te
NK077(tsu)001:12900: bdun / bco brgyad do // rang bzhin sems nyid rang snang du rtogs na dam pa'i rtags /
NK077(tsu)001:12901: de ltar du mi shes pas sems dga' brod phyogs 'dzin byed pa bdud yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12902: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du bdud kyi spyod yul ngos bzung bas mi 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:12903: bco brgyad po 'di lam gyi yon tan dang rtags yin pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:12904: nga rgyal khe drag gi skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12906: 'jig rten gyi khe dang snyan grags thob par 'dod pas sems rang dbang med par 'phrogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12907: 'jig rten pa rnams kyi bdag la skyes bu dam
NK077(tsu)001:12908: pa zhes sngags pa thob nas de'i rjes su 'du
NK077(tsu)001:12909: 'dzi longs spyod kyi mtshan mas sems g.yeng ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:12910: / 'bras bu thob tu re ba dang ma thob kyi dog pa cung zad yod //
NK077(tsu)001:12911: nga'am nga lta bu med ces nga che phyung bas nga rgyal 'phel ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:12912: 'o na sngar gyi lam skabs rnams dang khyad ci yod ce na //
NK077(tsu)001:12913: thun mong gi skyon phra bar bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12915: phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs 'dir thun mong gi skyon
NK077(tsu)001:12916: tha mal pa'ang sngar bas grangs nyung la ngo bo
NK077(tsu)001:12917: cha phra ba las mi 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:12918: rtog pa rgyu ba'i gzung 'dzin gyi bye brag rnams 'dir shes par gyis shig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12919: drug pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:12921: le lo'i skyon bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12923: phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs 'dir le lo rnam gnyis chad dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:12924: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:12925: ma skyes mi 'gags dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:12926: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan ting nge 'dzin la /
NK077(tsu)001:12927: blo rim gyis pas bden pa bzhi'i don tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi la gcod dgos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12928: 'di lta sgom gnyis 'byor pa g+hom thob cing de
NK077(tsu)001:12929: bas na lta sgom gnyis zung du 'brel bas nyams
NK077(tsu)001:12930: len gyi skyed tshogs lam bzhi mthar phyin /
NK077(tsu)001:12931: de'i tshe na bden bzhi'i ngo bo sku bzhi'i dgongs pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12932: 'bras bu lam du shes pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:12933: de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin de brten pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:12934: ched du le lo rnam gnyis kyi bya ba med
NK077(tsu)001:12937: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad bcos thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12939: mtshan ma lnga la sogs par rang rig pa'i cho
NK077(tsu)001:12940: 'phrul 'byung ba ni sems nyid rang snang yin pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:12941: phyir / mtshan ma mthong ba'i dus la yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:12942: la re ba dang skyon la dgos pa med do
NK077(tsu)001:12943: phyir / // dper na nam mkha' dwangs pa'i rang bzhin la nyi zla gza' skar glog 'gyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12945: nam mkha'i dbyings las gzhan du 'gyur zhing nyams pa med pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:12946: chos kyi dbyings ni bsam yas par /
NK077(tsu)001:12947: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:12948: rmad du byung ba'i ltas ngo mtshar can dang bdud
NK077(tsu)001:12949: kyi spyod yul mtshan ma sna tshogs pa ci ltar
NK077(tsu)001:12951: chos nyid de bzhin nyid la nyams pa dang gzhan du 'gyur ba med de /
NK077(tsu)001:12952: nga rgyal dreg pa'i skyon bcos thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:12954: bdag med rtogs pas nga rgyal med pa ni spros
NK077(tsu)001:12955: pa'i rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs dang
NK077(tsu)001:12956: / yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:12957: bas gang zag dang chos thams cad bdag gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:12958: med par shes shing rtogs pas nga rgyal med de
NK077(tsu)001:12959: / / mdor na bdud kyi spyod yul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12960: mtshan ma sna tshogs gang mthong yang rang gi ye shes rang nyid du rtogs shing sbyar bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12965: snang byed spros pa'i nyams gong nas gong du 'phel
NK077(tsu)001:12966: bar byed pa'i rim pa yang gong du bshad pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:12967: shes bya bslab pa'i rim pa snga ma goms nas
NK077(tsu)001:12968: phyi ma slob pa ci bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:12969: nyams kyi rim pa yang 'phel te /
NK077(tsu)001:12971: phyag rgya gcig par nyams lnga sngon du brtan zhing mthar phyin mod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:12973: da gzod slob pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:12974: sngar snang byed la ma goms pa'i dbang gis g.yo
NK077(tsu)001:12975: thob goms bstan mthar phyin pa'i nyams rnam pa lnga
NK077(tsu)001:12976: 'byung ba'o // rgyas par nyams lnga ye shes mthar phyin par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12978: dang po tshom bu gsum pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:12979: lnga pa'i lha gsal ba'i tshe cung zad rtog pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:12980: dbang du g.yo bas ting nge 'dzin la rtog pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:12981: bar chad 'byung ba de nyams lnga'i dang po g.yo
NK077(tsu)001:12982: ba'o // thob pa'i nyams ni lha de gsal ba
NK077(tsu)001:12983: ni nyin zhag 'phrug gcig la thun bzhir bgos pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:12984: cha gcig tsam skyon du 'gyur zhing cha gsum tsam
NK077(tsu)001:12985: du lha'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba mi g.yo ba
NK077(tsu)001:12988: rkyen med na rtogs pa med par thun rkyang gcig
NK077(tsu)001:12989: sgom nus pa ni gsum pa goms pa'i nyams yin
NK077(tsu)001:12991: thun rkyang nus pa de nyid rtog pa mi mthun
NK077(tsu)001:12992: pa'i skyon rkyen gyi dbang du mi 'gro zhing lhar
NK077(tsu)001:12994: bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams yin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:12995: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12996: de nas nyin zhag gi dus khyad par lha'i rnal
NK077(tsu)001:12997: 'byor la gang zhig gnas pa de ni shin tu
NK077(tsu)001:12998: gsal zhing rkyen gyi mi 'phrog pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:12999: lnga pa mthar pa'i nyams ste //
NK077(tsu)001:13003: nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs pa rnams spros pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13004: dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig la sogs pa zhal phyag
NK077(tsu)001:13005: spros pa grangs la nyams kyis dngos su sbyar na
NK077(tsu)001:13006: mthar lam par thal bar 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:13007: de bas na dal dang tshom bu spros pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13008: rnam grangs spros pa la sogs pa'i nyams tshod zin pa shin tu gces te /
NK077(tsu)001:13009: tshom bu lnga pa man chad sgom nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13010: brgyad pa spyod pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:13012: lta dgongs chos nyid kyi spyod pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:13014: lta dgongs nyams pa med par spyad pa dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13016: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor chen po'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13017: spyod pa'i tshul ni 'dod yon la ci ltar spyad kyang spyod pa'i dus nyid na /
NK077(tsu)001:13019: dper na nam mkha' la bya chen khyung ldengs pa bzhin g.yang mi za /
NK077(tsu)001:13020: chu la rkyal chen po 'phyo ba nya mo bzhin nyams nga med /
NK077(tsu)001:13021: nam mkha' la rlung chen po 'phyo ba thog char
NK077(tsu)001:13022: dang phyogs ris med pa bzhin du spros pa'i rnal
NK077(tsu)001:13023: 'byor pa'i spyod pa'i lta ba dpe gsum po de
NK077(tsu)001:13024: ltar g.yang mi za nyams ming thogs pa med par
NK077(tsu)001:13026: lta ba'i don la mi 'da' bas ci spyod tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13028: phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor chen po'i sgo gsum
NK077(tsu)001:13029: gyis spyod pa ni spyod pa ci la yang thogs
NK077(tsu)001:13030: chags med par lta bas zin par byas nas chos
NK077(tsu)001:13031: rnams thams cad kun la spyod bya spyod byed gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:13032: su med pa'am / dbyer med pa de ltar spyod
NK077(tsu)001:13033: pas snang ba ma 'gags pa ting nge 'dzin bde
NK077(tsu)001:13034: ba chen po'i ro mchog myong bar 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:13035: myong yang de las su zhig zhen pa dang chags par mi byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13036: spyod bzhin ma chags pas ye shes kyi tshogs chen rdzogs pa yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:13037: ting nge 'dzin bde ba'i mchog nyid ma 'gags pas bsod nams kyi tshogs chen rdzogs pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13038: spyod pa ci spyod de lta bu'i ngang nas spyod /
NK077(tsu)001:13039: 'di ni spyod pa brlab chen yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:13040: lta spyod dang 'brel par gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13042: lta ba dang spyod pa ya char ma gyur te
NK077(tsu)001:13043: lta spyod 'brel bas sngags 'chang rnams kyi dus rtag
NK077(tsu)001:13044: tu spyod do // rmad byung thabs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13049: 'dod yon lnga ste lnga tshan bzhi po 'di rnams theg pa 'og ma'i spang bya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13050: smad pa'i spyod pa kun 'dir lta ba dang thabs
NK077(tsu)001:13051: kyis zin pa'i rnal 'byor pas bdag dang gzhan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:13052: don yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir 'jol nyog
NK077(tsu)001:13053: tu spyad te / spyod pa gang yang byas la
NK077(tsu)001:13054: skyon gyis ma thogs shing slar la tshogs gnyis rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:13055: par 'gyur zhing dper na 'dam skyes pad+ma bzhin spyod
NK077(tsu)001:13056: pa'i dus nyid na gang gis kyang ma gos pas
NK077(tsu)001:13058: khyad par thabs kyi spyod pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:13060: spyod lam lha'i dkyil 'khor du spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13061: rgyas par bshad pa dang mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13064: dbang po rnam shes la sogs pa kun yab kyi dal du bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13068: rnam shes tshogs brgyad po kun tu rang rig rang snang bar shes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:13069: de dag rtog pa rang kha ma'i rnam pa min
NK077(tsu)001:13070: te yi ge du mtshon pa'i ye shes lnga ru
NK077(tsu)001:13072: des mtshon pa'i sku dang ye shes lnga ma 'gags
NK077(tsu)001:13073: pa'i rtsal yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu rigs lnga
NK077(tsu)001:13074: la sogs lha yab yum gyi dal nyid du sgom
NK077(tsu)001:13075: mo // zhi ba la dgar bas yang na khros
NK077(tsu)001:13076: pa khro bo rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du sgom mo
NK077(tsu)001:13077: mo // // yul dus la sogs pa kun bzang yum gyi dal du sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13079: de bzhin du gzugs dang sgra dang dri dang ro
NK077(tsu)001:13080: dang reg la sogs pa yul gyi rtog pa kun
NK077(tsu)001:13081: / rang ka ma'i rnam pa min te yi ge
NK077(tsu)001:13082: mum du mtshon nas mnyam nyid kyi lta ba'i dbyings
NK077(tsu)001:13084: mnyam pa nyid kyis dbyings des mtshon pa'i dbyings lnga
NK077(tsu)001:13085: ma 'gags pa'i rtsal lha yum gyi dal nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:13086: sgom mo // zhi ba las dgar bas yang na khro mo'i yum gyi dal nyid du sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:13089: mdor na spyod yul 'di ltar du snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mor gsal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:13092: chos nyid la chos nyid rol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:13093: spyod yul 'dod pa'i lha dang lha mor spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13095: gzugs sgra dri ro reg la sogs pa'i 'dod yon lnga po thams cad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13096: gzhan yang rtogs pa sna tshogs su snang ba thams
NK077(tsu)001:13097: cad kun 'bras bu de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i
NK077(tsu)001:13098: dal dang gzugs mdzes pa'i lha mo la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:13099: 'dod yon gyi lha dang lha mor brtag /spyod yul
NK077(tsu)001:13100: kun tu bzang po'i longs spyod du spyod pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:13102: rtog pa thams cad spyod yul lhar dag pa kun
NK077(tsu)001:13103: tu bzang po yis rang bzhin du shes pas 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:13104: pa'i yon tan lnga rnams thams cad la /
NK077(tsu)001:13105: thogs pa dang 'dzin chags med par ma bgags par spyad par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13106: de kho na bsod nams kyi tshogs chen po yin par brtag go //
NK077(tsu)001:13107: yang na 'dod yon lnga po de bzhin gshegs pa
NK077(tsu)001:13108: rigs lngar yang brtag /chos kun spyad thabs rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:13111: gzhan yang stong gsum gyi stong gi 'jig rten gyi
NK077(tsu)001:13112: khams thams cad na srid tshad rang gsal bas ye
NK077(tsu)001:13113: shes mtha' dbus med pas dbyings dang 'od zer 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:13114: pa'i yon tan lnga rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:13115: snang 'byed kyi blo rab 'bring tha ma thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:13116: chos nyid la chos nyid lha la lha rol cing
NK077(tsu)001:13117: spyod pa'o // yang na 'di la shes bya'i chos
NK077(tsu)001:13118: srid tshad dang 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa bzang
NK077(tsu)001:13119: ngan rab 'bring tha ma thams cad chos nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:13120: rba klong du longs spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13121: dgu pa dam tshig la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13126: gzhan don du gang ltar 'tsham par bsrung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13127: dang po la gnyis rim gyis pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13128: cig char ba'i dam tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:13129: dang po rim gyis pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13131: mi spang zhing dang du blang ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13133: dang du blang ba'i dam rdzas lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13134: mi spang ba nyon mongs pa lnga po kun kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:13135: spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i dus rtag tu spyod par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13136: de ltar 'dod pa la spyad pa'i dus de nyid
NK077(tsu)001:13137: na'ang chags pa dang zhen pa med pa gyur pa
NK077(tsu)001:13138: dang yon tan gang 'byung na mchog thun mong gi
NK077(tsu)001:13139: dngos grub ngo mtshar bas ya mtshan chen po 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:13140: ba ni / spyir sum brgya drug bcu las rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:13141: ba'i dam tshig lnga mdo tsam du bshad pa rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:13143: le lag gi gnyis brgya brgyad cu gya bdun pa'i nang nas 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13145: dngos grub ya mtshan chen po ni //
NK077(tsu)001:13146: tshe la dbang dang rig pa 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:13147: mkha' la spyod dang thogs med 'grub //
NK077(tsu)001:13148: mthar ni skye shi med pa'i sa //
NK077(tsu)001:13149: gzhan yang ci ltar dmigs pa bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:13152: spyod lam kun du spros pa'i rnal 'byor las mi 'da' bar bsrungs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13154: dbang po'i spyod yul du mthong thos thams cad kun la /
NK077(tsu)001:13155: 'gro ba dang 'dug pa dang nyal ba la sogs pa'i tshe na /
NK077(tsu)001:13156: zhi khro'i dal gnyis sgom pa spros bcas kyi rnal
NK077(tsu)001:13157: 'byor la mnyam par ting nge 'dzin de'i dbyings su
NK077(tsu)001:13158: gnas par lam pa'i shes rab kyi dbang po mchog
NK077(tsu)001:13159: dang ldan pa dag gis dus rtag tu spyod par
NK077(tsu)001:13160: bya'o // cig char ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13162: rim gyis pa la dgar bas yang na cig char
NK077(tsu)001:13163: bar dam tshig 'di lta bu rtogs shing snang bar
NK077(tsu)001:13164: byed pa'i rnal 'byor pas ci ltar spyod kyang sdom
NK077(tsu)001:13166: de'i gtan tshigs ni snang srid kyi chos thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:13167: lhag ma ma lus par lha'i dal du ye nas
NK077(tsu)001:13168: sangs rgyas par rtogs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:13169: 'bras bu bsgrub cing dam tshig bsrung bar bya ba med de /
NK077(tsu)001:13170: de bsrung ba la dge ba dang ma srung bas
NK077(tsu)001:13171: mi dge ba'i rnam pa gnyis kar dbye ba med
NK077(tsu)001:13172: pa rmi lam ltar rtogs tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:13173: ye nas dbyer med du sangs rgyas pa de la
NK077(tsu)001:13174: dam tshig gi bsrung du rdul phra mo tsam yang
NK077(tsu)001:13175: med do // gzhan don du gang ltar 'tsham pa ltar srung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13177: gdul bya gzhan don bya ba'i phyir rgyud las grags
NK077(tsu)001:13178: pa'i rtsa ba yan lag gi bsrung bya'i dam tshig
NK077(tsu)001:13180: gdul bya gang la mos ltar blo dang 'tsham par
NK077(tsu)001:13181: 'da' bar ma byed par srungs shig /ma bsrung ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:13183: ston pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa'i bka' nas
NK077(tsu)001:13184: bshad pa'am sdom pa'i rtsa ba lnga dang yan lag
NK077(tsu)001:13185: gi dam tshig gi thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:13186: gzhung nas bshad pa'i lta spyod dbyer med kyi de
NK077(tsu)001:13187: bzhin nyid du ni ma bsrungs na skyon ci lta
NK077(tsu)001:13189: dbang bskur ba'i dus su dam chu blud pa de
NK077(tsu)001:13190: yak+sha khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin tsha ba me'i
NK077(tsu)001:13191: dbal lta bu / lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu par gyur pa can gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13192: khyod kyi snying la tshang bcas nas tshe 'di la
NK077(tsu)001:13193: snying gi rtsa brgyad nas drang ste khrag thung nas
NK077(tsu)001:13194: dus ma yin par 'chi zhing tshe thung ba yin
NK077(tsu)001:13195: la / phyi ma ngan song gsum du skye bar
NK077(tsu)001:13196: 'gyur zhing de yis sdug bsngal tsha grang bkres skom
NK077(tsu)001:13197: glan lkug la sogs bzod pa'i klag chad de tshad
NK077(tsu)001:13199: de yang lam bzhir ldog zag yod par bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13200: dam nyams na ngan song du ltung ba de'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:13203: spros pa dang lam bzhir 'khor bar ldog cing ngan song du ltung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13204: zag pa gsum yod par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13205: de ltar spros pa ngan 'gror ldog srid na /
NK077(tsu)001:13207: chi srin phyag rgya ci bzhin du //
NK077(tsu)001:13208: dang po'i don rtogs mthar mi gtong //
NK077(tsu)001:13210: zag pa'i don rtogs mi ldog ces bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:13212: re zhig ltung yang mthar mi bslu ba la dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13213: ltung yang rtogs pa'i yon tan gyis sdug bsngal drag po yun ring mi myong ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:13215: ci ltar pho lang brdab pa bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:13218: de'i sdug bsngal bzod klag chad //
NK077(tsu)001:13219: ces lung gnyis dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:13221: nyen che ba la dgongs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13222: yun ring ba ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:13223: dam tshig ngo bo lta ba yin pa de rtogs na nyams mi srid pas /
NK077(tsu)001:13224: de rkyen gyi ltung ba med la /
NK077(tsu)001:13226: lta ba ma rtogs pa'i sgom pa zhig la /
NK077(tsu)001:13227: nyams pa 'byung srid pas rkyen gyi ltung ba yin no gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13228: 'dir rnal 'byor bzhi la lta ba rtogs pa'i gsal cha med na /
NK077(tsu)001:13233: des na rtogs pa rgyun chags pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:13235: res 'ga' ba rnams 'gal rkyen gyi ltung srid pa la dgongs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:13236: snga phyi gnyis ka dang mi 'gal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:13237: des na spros bcas man chad la ldog zag gnyis ka yod pa'i mu yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:13239: ldog med zag pa yod kyi mu yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13240: mthong lam yan chad zag ldog gnyis med pa'i mu /
NK077(tsu)001:13241: zag med ldog yod kyi mu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13242: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i rten gyi gang zag zhig
NK077(tsu)001:13243: /theg chen gyi tshogs sbyor gyi lam la gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:13244: de'o // bcu pa drod la dbye ba med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13246: phyi'i drod lus shing bal gyi 'dabs ma lta bur shin tu yang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13247: nang gi drod dbugs kyi phyi nang du rgyu yun ring du bral ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13248: gsang ba sems kyi drod ni rnal 'byor pa'i ting
NK077(tsu)001:13249: nge 'dzin mkha' la gza' skar shar ba de ma
NK077(tsu)001:13250: 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gsal ba bzhin du
NK077(tsu)001:13251: / zhi khro'i dal gyi lha rnams ma 'dres yongs su gsal bas lhag mthong la /
NK077(tsu)001:13252: rtogs pa mthar mi g.yo ba zhi gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:13253: sgom bya sgom byed kyi spyod yul du zhen pa
NK077(tsu)001:13254: med par zhi gnas lhag mthong zung 'brel du gsal
NK077(tsu)001:13255: ba'o // de yang drod gsum po de'i zhor las
NK077(tsu)001:13256: byung ba'i drod kun kyang tshogs lam chen po 'dir
NK077(tsu)001:13258: drod dang yon tan 'di zhes grangs kyi cha las 'das te dpag tu med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13259: bcu gcig pa rtags la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:13262: spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba'i rtags rnams kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:13264: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su 'byung ba 'di ru slobs su gyur pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13265: ngo bo gsal brtan du 'phel ba'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:13266: khams bde mi bde snyoms shing rang gi lus ting nge 'dzin gyi bde bas rgyas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13267: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa'i nad 'du ba rnam
NK077(tsu)001:13268: pa bzhi dang bral nas lus kyi bzod pa tshab
NK077(tsu)001:13269: cher thob pa'i che rtags gzhan rnams 'byung ba yin
NK077(tsu)001:13272: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa la sogs pa'i mngon par shes pa drug dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13273: dbang po'i sgo res kyang yul lnga lnga gcod pas
NK077(tsu)001:13274: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i grangs kyang rdzogs par 'gyur zhing
NK077(tsu)001:13276: mngon shes rab 'bring gi cha yis 'bring gi yul khams /
NK077(tsu)001:13277: rab kyi gling gcig tshun chad kyi mngon shes kyi
NK077(tsu)001:13278: gsal zhing dgongs la thugs rjes 'dul bar byed do
NK077(tsu)001:13279: // de rgyu ci las byung zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:13280: 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa tshogs drug rang rgyud
NK077(tsu)001:13281: par tha dad du 'dzin pa'i rtogs pa dag cing
NK077(tsu)001:13282: dngas pa'i stobs las 'byung bar 'gyur ba yin no
NK077(tsu)001:13285: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul nyi shu'i cha ro tsam du g.yo ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13286: thob pa tsam du 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13287: lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa 'gro ba thams
NK077(tsu)001:13288: cad la rang rang gi skad dang mthun par chos
NK077(tsu)001:13289: ston nus pa rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang
NK077(tsu)001:13290: / gling gcig chad pa g.yos shing ltas 'byung bas chos snang bar byed pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13291: dngos po kun yi ge'i sgrar brjod par byed pa kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:13292: spyod yul bco brgyad shugs snang mthong tshul gdams pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13294: de ltar cho 'phrul bzhi po 'di dag mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13295: gong ltar bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13296: glang po che zhon pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13297: grur zhugs la sogs ting nge 'dzin gyi shugs las snang brgyad mthong ba yang 'byung /
NK077(tsu)001:13298: de dag ci byung yang re ba dang dog pa'i rtogs pa dor la mnyam par bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:13299: bcu gnyis pa rmi lam la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13301: rmi lam snga ma dang mthun zhing rdzogs par 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13303: spros pa'i skabs 'dir rmi lam gyi mtshan ma yang
NK077(tsu)001:13304: phyag rgya gcig pa dang chos mthun te ngo bo
NK077(tsu)001:13305: gcig par / grub pa'i rmi ltas bcu bzhi la sogs 'byung ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:13306: 'o na khyad med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:13307: ngo bo gsal ba dang brtan par 'gyur bas khyad par phye ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:13308: gzhan yang rgyud gzhung kun las mtshan ma bzang po'i ltas su rgyal bas lung bstan pa kun /
NK077(tsu)001:13309: tshogs lam chen po spros pa'i skabs 'dir thams cad rdzogs par 'byung ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:13310: mi rtags kun 'byung 'byung ba'i gtan tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:13312: bsgrub pa'i rig 'dzin spros bcas kyi lam 'di nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:13313: mthar phyin rig 'dzin rgyu yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:13314: rmi lam gyi ltas bzang po mtshan ma 'byung ba'i sa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:13315: bar chad med par tshogs bsgrub pa'i skabs su'ang rmi ltas bcu bzhi po 'di dag 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13316: bcu gsum pa yon tan la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:13318: rtogs tshogs lhar gsal ba'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13320: gzugs la sogs pa'i phung po lnga nyid de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:13321: gshegs pa rigs kyi yab lnga sa la sogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:13322: 'byung ba lnga po nyid rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:13323: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po bzhi rnams ni phyi nang gi byang chub sems dpa' brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:13324: mig gi yul gzugs la sogs pa bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13325: 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13326: byang chub sems ma chen mo brgyad yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:13327: bdag tu rtog pa rags pa las skyes pa'i lus
NK077(tsu)001:13328: kyis chos rnam pa bzhi khro bo sgo ba bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:13329: yin / rtag chad bdag 'dzin mu bzhi khro mo bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:13330: yid chos kun bzang yab yum /
NK077(tsu)001:13331: nyon mongs pa thub pa drug yin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13332: de rnams rang snang du bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13333: rtogs tshogs thams cad lha'i dal du gsal ba de
NK077(tsu)001:13334: yang sems rang gi rig pa nyid lha dang lha
NK077(tsu)001:13335: mo'i dal du snang ba yin zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13336: de bzhin du thams cad mnyam nyid du rdzogs pas dpal lhun gyis grub pa'i sa ste //
NK077(tsu)001:13337: lha sems nyid rang snang du bstan pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13339: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga dang ye shes lnga la
NK077(tsu)001:13340: sogs pa'i rtogs tshogs lha'i dal thams cad rang byung
NK077(tsu)001:13341: ye shes chen po'i dal nyid las ma g.yos shing
NK077(tsu)001:13342: mi 'da' bas sgom zhes brjod do //
NK077(tsu)001:13343: ci ltar bsam pa bzhin 'grub pa'i yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:13345: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa gnyis dang bral ba'i spros
NK077(tsu)001:13346: pa'i rnal 'byor pa thabs mkhas kyi rtogs tshogs thams
NK077(tsu)001:13347: cad zhi khro'i lha ru gsal la de yang 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:13348: med du shes pas dngos po rang rgyud pa med
NK077(tsu)001:13349: par sgom na / mig gi gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13350: rna bas sgra thos pa la sogs pa spyod yul
NK077(tsu)001:13351: 'di dag rang rgyud pa med pa'i tshul du dag
NK077(tsu)001:13352: par 'gyur ro // lha de dag kyang rang gi rig pa'i ye shes su gsal bar sgom na /
NK077(tsu)001:13353: don dam par lha'i rang bzhin cir yang grub pa med pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:13354: kun rdzob tu ci ltar bsam pa ltar snang bas bsgrub na cir yang 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:13355: bcu bzhi pa 'da' ka ma la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13357: 'das tshul yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13359: phyag rgya spros pa 'di sgom pa'i dus na rkyen
NK077(tsu)001:13360: gyis bsgyur ba'i dus 'chi ltas byung na zhi khro
NK077(tsu)001:13361: phyag rgya spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin gang yin dran
NK077(tsu)001:13364: las ngan gyi rnam smin dang lam gyi zhen rgyun
NK077(tsu)001:13365: cad nas thod rgal du srid pa bar ma do'i
NK077(tsu)001:13366: phyi mar blo chung na rnam smin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13367: blo che na tshe dbang gnyis gang rung du byed la sbyor te /
NK077(tsu)001:13368: mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13369: nus pa zhan cing man ngag sgom pa'i skabs med kyang gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13371: spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa blo chung ba gang zhig
NK077(tsu)001:13372: ting nge 'dzin dang brtson 'grus kyi nus pa zhan
NK077(tsu)001:13373: pas 'da' kha ma'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa'i skabs
NK077(tsu)001:13375: sngar gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi 'phen pa'i 'brel ba
NK077(tsu)001:13376: spros bcas sgom pa'i sa bon rgyud la yod pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:13377: rkyen gyis tshe rabs 'di dang phyi ma kun tu
NK077(tsu)001:13378: bde 'gro lha dang mi'i go 'phang phun sum tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:13379: pa thob nas / lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:13383: dus kyi mi skol bar gsang sngags rdo rje theg
NK077(tsu)001:13384: pa'i lam la spyad pas thar chags su brgyud nas
NK077(tsu)001:13388: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13390: snyoms las las gyur pa'i le lo med par brtson par byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:13391: tshe 'di nyid la lam du 'bras bu rig 'dzin thob pa'ang chos nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13392: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams par bsrungs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13393: rkyen rmi lam rnam dag btab pa'i mthu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13394: lam gyi cha rkyen gyi yan lag cho ga lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:13396: sngags kyi yan lag lnga la sogs pa rdzogs pas
NK077(tsu)001:13397: bsgrub na 'bras bu mthong lam rig 'dzin nyid thob
NK077(tsu)001:13398: par 'gyur ba'o // mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13400: zhi khro phyag rgya spros pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:13401: 'dzin yang nas yang du rgyun chag par sgom pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:13402: // bsod rnams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i longs spyod kyis dpe mun pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13403: ma spangs par snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13404: dug ma spangs par sman du 'gyur ba'i tshul ci bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:13405: rtog tshogs ma spangs par 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK077(tsu)001:13406: shes su gsal ba yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK077(tsu)001:13407: gyi sa mchog brnyes te dngos su thob pa ltar
NK077(tsu)001:13408: snang ba ni / phyogs mthun sbyar ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:13409: de nyid kyi ngo bo lam du byed pa la dgongs pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:13411: blo che na rnam smin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13412: blo chung na tshogs bsgrub thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13415: zhi khro'i lha phyag rgya du mar spros nas sgom
NK077(tsu)001:13416: pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin la bslab pa'i thabs
NK077(tsu)001:13417: ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams gcod
NK077(tsu)001:13418: cing 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u zhes
NK077(tsu)001:13419: bya ste yas bgrang drug pa'i don du gada'o /
NK077(tsu)001:13421: spyi don gnyis pa bar chad med par tshogs bsgrub pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:13423: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13425: phyag rgya spros pa zhi khro'i dal gnyis goms pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:13426: rtogs pa'i ngang la phyag 'tshal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:13427: zag bcas zag med bar chad med par 'bras bu rig 'dzin la sbyor ba yis /
NK077(tsu)001:13428: spros pa tshogs lam mthar phyin pa'i dus kyi rjes thog tu /
NK077(tsu)001:13429: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa bshad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13434: bar chad med pa'i lam tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:13435: bsnyen pa dang ni nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13436: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub pa chen pos bar chad
NK077(tsu)001:13437: med pa'i lam bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'o don la rdzogs pa'ang
NK077(tsu)001:13439: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi 'di yang lam rim 'jug gi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13440: bsgrub pa gzhung gi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13441: sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi yod pa las //
NK077(tsu)001:13442: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum lam gyi bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13443: sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub mchod pa'i skabs su bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13447: de ltar bsnyen sgrub bzhi cha gsum yod pa'i dang po la lam rim 'jug gi bsnyen sgrub bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13448: de la yang bzhi yod pa'i dang po bsnyen pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13449: thog mar don dam dang kun rdzob byang chub sems
NK077(tsu)001:13450: bden pa dbyer med du lta ba rtogs shing ting
NK077(tsu)001:13451: nge 'dzin sgom pa la brtson 'grus byed nas de
NK077(tsu)001:13452: ni / grangs dus rtags kyi bsnyen pa gsum yod
NK077(tsu)001:13453: pa'i nang nas dam pa las byas pa chud mi
NK077(tsu)001:13454: ni / za ba dang / 'grus par lta ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:13456: sems gnyis kyi chas phye bas /
NK077(tsu)001:13458: kun ting snying rje chen po man chad bsnyen par brjod do //
NK077(tsu)001:13459: gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13460: de la brten pa lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po gcig dang du mar gsal ba sgom pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13461: gong ma bas kyang 'bras bu la nye ba'i phyir nye ba'i bsnyen pa yin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:13462: gtan tshig de'i phyir zung 'jug phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13463: snang byed phyag rgya spros pa gnyis nye ba'i bsnyen pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13465: bsgrub pa nyid ni sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam du tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13466: bzhi pa bsgrub pa chen po ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13467: dus kyi tshogs bsgrub pa'i mtha' /
NK077(tsu)001:13468: mtshan ma rtags kyi bsnyen pa rdzogs nas nub tha
NK077(tsu)001:13469: ma dngos grub len pa de bsgrub pa chen po'o
NK077(tsu)001:13470: // de las su rung nas 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid mthong lam rnam smin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13471: tshe dbang gnyis gang rung thob pa de 'bras bu grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13472: sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub mchod pa'i skabs su bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13474: mdor bstan gyi gsum pa sbyor ba'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13475: zhi khro'i ta na g+ha na yi mchod pa'i skabs
NK077(tsu)001:13476: su 'og tu ston pa ltar shes par bya'o zhes
NK077(tsu)001:13477: kha 'phong pa'o // 'on kyang bsnyen bsgrub gnyis po
NK077(tsu)001:13478: la ngos bzung tsam byed na sbyor ba'i bsnyen bsgrub
NK077(tsu)001:13479: kha 'phong pa'o // bzhi ni / yum mtshan ldan
NK077(tsu)001:13480: btsal nas khrus byas chas su zhugs lus bsrung ba
NK077(tsu)001:13481: kha 'phong pa'o // bzhi ni / ni / bsnyen pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13482: dam tshig 'bog byin gyis rlabs 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13483: nye bsnyen phyag rgya bzhi pa rol ba bsgrub pa
NK077(tsu)001:13484: byang sems mkha' la phab pa bsgrub pa chen po
NK077(tsu)001:13485: / bsgrub pa'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13486: zla gcig gi dbang du brtsi na /
NK077(tsu)001:13487: gnas gzhal yas khang mthun par rdzas bsogs /
NK077(tsu)001:13488: dal bris nas rten rdzas bkod /
NK077(tsu)001:13489: rgyal chen phyogs skyongs mchod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13491: zhag bco lnga yan chad cho ga gzhung srong ba nye bsnyen no //
NK077(tsu)001:13492: zhag bco lnga man chad zhag bcu bzhi bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13493: nub tha ma dngos grub len pa ni bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13494: bsgrub pa'i bsnyen sgrub la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13498: mdor bstan gyi gnyis pa bsgrub pa dus kyi bsnyen
NK077(tsu)001:13499: bsgrub bzhi gtso bo byas te tshogs bsgrub kyi skabs
NK077(tsu)001:13500: 'dir rgyas par bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:13502: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13503: bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhis bsgrub pa'i gzhung bsrang ba
NK077(tsu)001:13504: dag gi sbyor lam tshogs bsgrub rdzogs par 'gyur te
NK077(tsu)001:13506: yo byad la sogs phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung la /
NK077(tsu)001:13507: bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhi'i bsgrub pa'i gzhung bsrang bar bya ba'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:13509: rnal 'byor pa gang dag gcig spros kyi skabs su zhi khro gang la mos pa ji bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:13510: 'dir yang zhi ba tshogs bsgrub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13511: khro bos tshogs bsgrub par bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13512: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13513: zhi khro gang mos su tshogs bsgrub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13522: spyir bstan la zhi khro gnyis yod pa de la
NK077(tsu)001:13523: yang snga ma zhi ba'i sgo nas tshogs bsgrub pa
NK077(tsu)001:13524: la gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang gcig /dus phun
NK077(tsu)001:13526: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:13527: ston 'khor bsgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:13528: bsgrub pa'i thabs phun 'dir ma dpe ldeb gcig chad
NK077(tsu)001:13529: 'dug pas dpe gzhan la bsdur dgos /ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:13532: spyir thams cad dang ldan zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:13533: khyad par du bsgrub pa la mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig go //
NK077(tsu)001:13534: bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:13535: chu bo bzhi rdzogs dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:13537: bka' brgyud 'dus pa lung gi chu bo /
NK077(tsu)001:13538: bla ma brgyud pa byin rlabs kyi chu bo /
NK077(tsu)001:13539: yongs su rdzogs pa dbang gi chu bo /
NK077(tsu)001:13540: rang rig pa nyams kyi chu bo dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13541: dbang gi chu bo la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:13542: yi dam lha'i dbang thob pa ku ku ra tsa lta bu /
NK077(tsu)001:13543: po ti glegs bam gyi dbang thob pa rgyal po dza lta bu /
NK077(tsu)001:13544: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang thob pa pad+ma 'byung gnas lta bu /
NK077(tsu)001:13545: thams cad kyi dbang thob pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:13546: mkhas pa pan tri ta'i dbang thob pa b+hi ma la lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13547: yang na chu bo bzhi'i brgyud pa bar ma chad pa lha'i dbang bskur nas thob pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13548: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i brgyud pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13549: gang zag gis dbang skur nas thob pa b+hi ma la'i brgyud pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13550: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur nas thob pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13552: po ti glegs bam gyi dbang bskur nas thob pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13553: rgyal po dza'i brgyud pa zhes kyang zer /
NK077(tsu)001:13554: yang na dbang gi chu bo bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13555: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo /
NK077(tsu)001:13557: bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo /
NK077(tsu)001:13558: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13561: dbang gi chu bo rdzogs pa dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:13562: zhan 'dzin pa'i gnyer dang ldan pa dang lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:13563: rgyud sde la mkhas shing lung gi don khrol ba
NK077(tsu)001:13564: dang drug /phrin las te bsgrub pa'i chog 'grigs la
NK077(tsu)001:13566: snyan rgyud nyams myong man ngag drod 'chang ba dang brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:13567: ston pa de'i rgyud la 'chang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13568: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor spros bcas mthar phyin cing
NK077(tsu)001:13569: dgongs pa dang ldan pa'i ston pa shin tu yang
NK077(tsu)001:13570: gces pas te brten par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13573: gong du bshad pa de lta bu'i ston pa'i rang
NK077(tsu)001:13574: bzhin brgyad dang ldan pa'i bla ma rdo rje slob
NK077(tsu)001:13575: dpon la / sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo nas mnyes pa gsum gyis mchod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:13576: phan nus zab mo'i dbang rim pa bzhin thob par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13577: brtson 'grus kyis sgo gsum gyi rgyud yongs su sbyangs pa'i sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:13578: rtogs pa'i lta ba dang ldan pa bden pa dbyer med mngon du byas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:13579: de bzhin nyid sogs kyi ting nge 'dzin bzhi gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13580: bla med mi spangs pa la sogs pa rtsa ba lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13581: mi spang mi 'dor ba yan lag bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13582: rtsa ba yan lag bco lnga la sogs pa'i dam tshig ma nyams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13583: rgyu ma nor rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13584: bskyed pa rkyen gyis sngags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13585: bzlas pa lam rim gyi sngags te gsum mam /
NK077(tsu)001:13586: sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13587: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13590: sku phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi po rnams shes shing /
NK077(tsu)001:13591: gong du bshad pa bzhin dam tshig ma nyams shing /
NK077(tsu)001:13593: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad rgyan dang bgo ba'i glu tshig /sgra'i bro gar 'du 'phro'i /
NK077(tsu)001:13594: a li ka li'i yo byad lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13595: de lta bu'i 'khor grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:13596: don de dang mi ldan na mi 'grub ste brlag par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:13599: gnas btsal shing sa chog bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13601: dgra bgegs kyi sde dpung gi bar chad chen pos mi tshugs pa'i gnas btsan shing /
NK077(tsu)001:13602: rdo rje las rim nas 'byung ba ltar sa gzhi
NK077(tsu)001:13603: dang bar snang gi mtshan nyid la sogs pa bkra
NK077(tsu)001:13604: shis pa dang / mi chos gtsug lag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13605: lha chos kyi lo rgyus rnam pa gnyis ka shis pa dang ldan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13606: rang nyid shin tu yid du 'ong ba'i sa phyogs btsal ba der /
NK077(tsu)001:13607: las rim nas 'byung ba ltar sa yi cho ga rgyas par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13611: rdo rje las rim nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:13612: sa dang bar snang shis pa'i mtshan nyid bzang po
NK077(tsu)001:13613: dang ldan pa dang gcig /lha chos dang chos kyi
NK077(tsu)001:13614: gtsug lag gi rnam pa gnyis ka shes pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:13615: gnyis / rnal 'byor pa nyams dga' zhing yid du
NK077(tsu)001:13616: 'ong ba bar chad med pa'i phyogs brtsal bar bya
NK077(tsu)001:13620: gnam dang sa dang bar snang dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13621: legs par brtag ste las rnams bya //
NK077(tsu)001:13624: nam mkha' yon tan bzhi dang ldan pa dang bar ri'i sgron brtag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13628: 'khor lo'i rad na zur brgyad dam /
NK077(tsu)001:13629: rtse mang tsa tra rtsibs stong dang ldan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13630: chu bo bzhin ma bo ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13631: slang nga'i kha bzhin mnyam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13632: bar snang 'o ka'i chu ltar dwangs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13633: mtshon cha lnga'i dbyibs dag tu /
NK077(tsu)001:13634: brtag nas mngon par nam mkha' shis //
NK077(tsu)001:13637: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mong dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13638: chu bo bzhin du ma bo zhing //
NK077(tsu)001:13639: mnyam zhing 'o kha chu ltar dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13640: nyi ma shin tu gnas pa ni //
NK077(tsu)001:13641: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid shes par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:13644: phyogs kyi rigs brtags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13646: dang po ni shar gyi ri rgyang ring zhing bgas kyis gzhol ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13647: lho phyogs kyi ri 'jam zhing nags tshal mthug po skyes pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13649: byang ri bskyob cing 'dud pa lta bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13650: shar lho 'jam zhing gzhol ba la //
NK077(tsu)001:13651: mtho dang 'dud pa nub byang yin ces gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:13652: gnyis pa mtshams kyi dgra ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13653: shar lho na gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse lta bu rno zang nge ba 'dug na /
NK077(tsu)001:13654: gtso bo slob dpon gyi tshe la gnod pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:13655: lho nub mtshams na srin po dus pa'i mchi rjes
NK077(tsu)001:13656: g.ya' dang / bye ma bshal ba 'dra 'dug na /
NK077(tsu)001:13657: 'khor du yug sa mang du 'byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13658: nub byang mtshams na ma mo rngam pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:13659: spar zhad kyi brab pa grog po sha shur mang po 'dug na /
NK077(tsu)001:13660: gtso 'khor gyi nor la gnod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13661: byang shar mtshams na 'byung po rkun mo'i 'jol pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13662: mdong drud pa'i shol lta bu 'dug na /
NK077(tsu)001:13663: byis pa dang 'gab la gnod pas spang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:13664: gzhan yang gdug pa klu'i rgyu srang /
NK077(tsu)001:13665: skyon can rgyu ba'i lam srang /
NK077(tsu)001:13666: zhang blon gdug pa'i 'dug sa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13667: nyes pa dang 'brel ba'i gnas rnams spang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:13670: spang bar byed pa'i gnas ngan ni //
NK077(tsu)001:13671: gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13672: srin po ngus pa'i mchi rjes dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13673: 'phros pa'i gnod sbyin spar rjes dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13674: ma mo rngams pa'i spar rjes dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13676: gdug pa klu'i rgyu srong dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13677: skyon can rgyu ba'i lam srong dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13678: zhang blon gdug pa'i 'dug sa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13679: nyes dang 'brel pa'i gnas rnams ni //
NK077(tsu)001:13680: sbrul gdug pang du 'ong ba ltar //
NK077(tsu)001:13681: wa'i brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK077(tsu)001:13682: lo yis bshugs te rab tu spang //
NK077(tsu)001:13685: rgyal ba yang dgon pa'i ri chos nang du //
NK077(tsu)001:13686: nyal sa gru bzhi 'dom gang la //
NK077(tsu)001:13690: gsum pa gzhi brtag pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13693: chu bo nub nas shar du 'bab pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13697: me tog gi gseb nas bya skad snyan pa rnam pa sna tshogs pa sgrogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13698: mi chos kyi lo rgyus kyi bkra shis pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13699: gtsug lag gi lha bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13700: shar na stag skya bo ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13702: lho na g.yu 'brug sngon mo ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13704: nub na bya dmar po ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13706: byang na rus sbal nag po ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13707: shing rkang gcig gam chu mig yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13708: lha chos kyi bkra shis pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13709: ston pas zhabs kyi bcag pa'i sa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13710: gang zag khyad par can gyi grub pa mnyes pa'i sa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13712: lhun sdug ri bo nags tshal ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:13713: rab tu mnyam zhing snum bag ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:13714: chu bo dbang gi phyogs yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:13715: cung zad kyi ni rlung nyung zhing //
NK077(tsu)001:13716: me tog shing tshal bya skad btags //
NK077(tsu)001:13717: lo rgyus shis pa mchog tu gsungs //
NK077(tsu)001:13719: gzhan yang dgra'i bar chad kyis dben te /
NK077(tsu)001:13720: mi rgod kyi 'du sar ma song ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13721: bgegs kyi bar chad kyi dben te /
NK077(tsu)001:13723: nad kyi bar chad kyi dben te /
NK077(tsu)001:13724: dug dang chu nad la sogs pa med par sa phyogs tsha grang snyoms pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13726: bdag nyid rtogs shing nyams dga' dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13727: bsam gtan dgra la ring gyur pa //
NK077(tsu)001:13728: rang khyim la sogs de bzhin te //
NK077(tsu)001:13729: nan tan nus mthu ldan phyir yin //
NK077(tsu)001:13731: sa nang gi brtag pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:13733: sa chu'i brtag pa gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:13734: de nas sa bslang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13737: sa bsrungs rnams gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13738: gzhan yang o rgyan pad+ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13739: rgyal ba yang dgon sa gnyis kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:13740: dam pa'i chos bsgrub pa'i gnas kyi legs nyes 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK077(tsu)001:13741: brag phug ma mo dang srin mo'i gnas yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13742: reg pa dang thabs lam la dga' /
NK077(tsu)001:13743: nags khrod klu dang gnod sbyin gnas yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13747: gshin rje dang sha za mkha' 'gro'i gnas yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13750: sa phug thel rang dang dam sri'i gnas yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13752: ma mo bsgrub pa la dga' /
NK077(tsu)001:13754: lha rten yod sa mu stegs kyi gnas yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13755: de yang dbang phyug chen po bsgrub pa la daga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13756: de'i khongs su sdod pa rnams gnas brtag shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13757: de la skyon yon brtsi ba la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:13758: mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'i skyon /
NK077(tsu)001:13761: dang po ni shar ri mtho na tshe la gnod /
NK077(tsu)001:13762: nub ri had por song na bkra mi shis /
NK077(tsu)001:13763: ri sna mdung tshugs su zug na bar chad 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:13764: tsha grang ma snyoms na nad 'jug gdon gdug pa can yod na bar chad 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:13765: rgyu srang zug na mi'i 'tshe ba 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:13766: gzhan yang steng na brag lhung la khad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13767: ngus pa'i mchi ris 'dra ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13768: sder sen gyi brad pa 'dra ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13770: sgo la grog mdo zug pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13771: sgo la mi longs ba lta bu byung na /
NK077(tsu)001:13772: sa dgra yin pas skyon can yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:13774: brag skyil krung bca' ba 'dra na /
NK077(tsu)001:13776: pad+ma kha phyes pa 'dra na rtogs pa 'char /
NK077(tsu)001:13777: sa dang lam gru gsum yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:13778: grub thag nye rgyab ri mtho na bag dro /
NK077(tsu)001:13779: byang ri mtho na bkra shis /
NK077(tsu)001:13780: lho skyobs mdud pa 'dra na longs spyod 'du /
NK077(tsu)001:13781: sa dgra gang yang med na bkra shis te yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:13782: gsum pa ldan tshul ngos bzung ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13783: sa pad+ma 'dab brgyad du yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13784: gnam 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad du yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13785: rgyab ri mtho ba byang ri 'thug pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13786: g.yas dar dkar gyi yol ba 'dra ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13787: g.yon rin chen spungs pa 'dra ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13788: mda' phyag rgya bsnol ba 'dra ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13789: ri thams cad snum zhing khengs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13790: mdor na mtho ba yangs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13794: chu bo dbang gi phyogs nas 'bab pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13795: nyi ma rtag cing gangs mtho ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13796: gsal cha che zhing so thub pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13797: tsha grangs snyoms shing gzhi bdag 'jam pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13798: thag nye ring ran cing sa btsan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13799: bkra shis shing grub thob kyi zhabs kyis bcag pa gcig btsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:13803: dkyil krung 'dra na bsnol mtshams na /
NK077(tsu)001:13807: mig tshil dang lto tshil la /
NK077(tsu)001:13808: mkhal ma 'dra ba'i steng du gdab bo //
NK077(tsu)001:13812: mdor na sa'i snying non pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13815: de las gzhan pa phag gi ze ba /
NK077(tsu)001:13817: mi'i gsus bshal la mi gdab bo //
NK077(tsu)001:13818: sa dgra bsrung ba'i rten 'brel ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13820: mdog sngon po la sa dgra byung na /
NK077(tsu)001:13822: grog po re hrul du chad pa la chu'i ri mo bya /
NK077(tsu)001:13824: zhing pags brkyangs pa 'dra ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:13826: steng du lhung la khad pa la mchod rten brtsigs /
NK077(tsu)001:13827: mtshan ma zod pa 'dra ba 'dug na /
NK077(tsu)001:13828: pho rtags btsug /brag rta tsam sgo'i thad ka na 'dug na /
NK077(tsu)001:13829: sa dgra che bas rten 'brel mang du bya /
NK077(tsu)001:13830: gzhan yang sems can gyi gzu 'dra ba 'dug na /
NK077(tsu)001:13831: de'i gnyen po gang 'gro ba'i gzugs bya'o /
NK077(tsu)001:13833: shar du mchod rten mi brtsegs /
NK077(tsu)001:13836: lho mig /gdung ro 'don pa'i khri lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13837: nad pa'i khri lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13841: sne gdung thug yod pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:13843: de'i thad kar bkra shis pa'i mtshan ma dang snying po bri /
NK077(tsu)001:13844: de nas lho gshin rje ru sgo ma bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:13845: lho nub srin po'i steng du mal mi bca' /
NK077(tsu)001:13846: nub byang rlung lha'i steng du g.yos mi bya /
NK077(tsu)001:13847: shar lho me lhar thab btsug go //
NK077(tsu)001:13848: byang shar dbang ldan du mal baca'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13850: ri la mgo bo thur bstan /
NK077(tsu)001:13852: gdung gi mal gyi sked pa bcad pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13857: de rnams dgra sa yin pas mi bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13858: de nas mal sa gru bzhi 'dom gang la /
NK077(tsu)001:13859: dge sbyor 'phel mi 'phel gyi gdan yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:13860: phyi nang snod bcud snang sems gcig gi ngo bo yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:13861: rten phyi rol gyi skyon gang yin pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:13862: brten pa nang gi sems rgyud la 'ong ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:13865: bar chad mi 'byung ba'i rten 'brel yin /
NK077(tsu)001:13866: mal 'og du sa dkar gyi g.yung drung ris bris /
NK077(tsu)001:13867: 'dug tshug pa'i rten 'brel yin par gsungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:13868: gnas brtsegs shing byug bsrung bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13870: gnas rnyed nas tshom bu gcig gsum pa lnga pa
NK077(tsu)001:13871: gang byed pa'i lha'i grangs gang yod kyi rim pa
NK077(tsu)001:13872: bzhin du / gnas khang che chung gi tshad yang
NK077(tsu)001:13873: rkyen bsgrub pa po mang nyung gi rim pa bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:13875: de yang 'khor khang phyi mar yo byad bsog cing g.yos byed /
NK077(tsu)001:13876: nang mar gsang spyod kyi mchod pa 'bul /
NK077(tsu)001:13877: bar ma tshogs bsgrub pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13878: rim pa gsum dang ldan pa'i khang par /
NK077(tsu)001:13879: rin chen gser dngul la sogs pa dang tsan+da dang
NK077(tsu)001:13880: gla rtsi la sogs pa byug pas gnas khang gi
NK077(tsu)001:13882: rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis mdzes par spral
NK077(tsu)001:13883: pa'i gzhal yas khang rang nyams dga' zhing yid du
NK077(tsu)001:13884: 'ong bar bya ba shin tu gces /
NK077(tsu)001:13887: bsgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13889: de la bsgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus kyi tshe
NK077(tsu)001:13890: grangs ni zla ba yar gyi ngo'i tshes brgyad la
NK077(tsu)001:13891: lha'i tshogs 'dus pa'i dus yin pas brtson par bya
NK077(tsu)001:13892: ste / shin tu yang tshes grangs de dang skar
NK077(tsu)001:13893: ma rgyal dang gza' phur bu rnams sa ga zla
NK077(tsu)001:13895: de'i dus su bla na med pa'i byang chub bsgrub
NK077(tsu)001:13896: pa'i spyod pa brlab po cher spyod pa ni rang
NK077(tsu)001:13897: bzhin gyis nus pa yod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:13898: gsang sngags mchog gi dngos grub dus myur du thob pa'i rten 'brel yod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:13899: tshes grangs dang gza' dang skar ma rgyal la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:13900: pa bzang po rnams bkra shis pa yin pas blang
NK077(tsu)001:13903: lta ba dang dam tshig ma nyams par brtson pa
NK077(tsu)001:13904: la gnas na blo dang brtson 'grus rab kyi zhag
NK077(tsu)001:13905: ni sum cu pa phrag drug ste zla ba drug
NK077(tsu)001:13906: gam / 'bring gi zla ba bcu gnyis te lo gcig gam /
NK077(tsu)001:13907: yang na zla ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig dang
NK077(tsu)001:13908: zla ba gnyis sam tha mas kyang zla ba bcu
NK077(tsu)001:13909: drug gis te lo gcig dang zla ba bzhis /
NK077(tsu)001:13910: dbang po brtul na rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin nam /
NK077(tsu)001:13911: dbang po rno na tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig
NK077(tsu)001:13912: 'dzin rnams kyi nang nas dam pa ste mchog tu
NK077(tsu)001:13913: gyur pa lus mi 'dor bar lam mchog yongs su
NK077(tsu)001:13914: rdzogs pa'i tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:13915: 'grub pa'i phyir / sbyor lam gyi rnal 'byor pa
NK077(tsu)001:13916: blo dang brtson 'grus che chung rab 'bring tha ma'i
NK077(tsu)001:13917: chos dus nye ring rig pa bzhin du 'grub pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:13918: 'grub pa'i phyir / // spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:13920: yo byad tshogs par bsags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13922: gos rgyan bza' btung gsang ba dang bsgrub pa'i spyod lnga rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13924: rgyan dang bgo ba'i yo byad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13928: gsang ba +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad dang lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13936: kun la khyab pa'i chos gos la sogs pa'i rgyan bdun no //
NK077(tsu)001:13945: zan la sogs pa'i gza' ba'i bye brag rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13952: sbrang chu la sogs pa btung ba'i bye brag rnams so //
NK077(tsu)001:13954: rnal 'byor pho mo rigs lnga spyi'i dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13955: ye shes rgyan gyi bro'i bye brag la mkhas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13957: de dag gi glu'i bye brag la mkhas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13958: rol mo'i sgra sna tshogs ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13959: de yang bsgrub mchog gsang ba'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK077(tsu)001:13960: skyo ba'i yid rnams bsang phyir dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13961: gti mug mun pa gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:13962: dung dang mkhar rnga rdza dang //
NK077(tsu)001:13963: cang te'u pi wang ko ki la //
NK077(tsu)001:13964: snyan par sgrogs pa'i rdzas rnams kun //
NK077(tsu)001:13965: sna tshogs 'byung ba'i rol mo ste //
NK077(tsu)001:13966: nyer rdzogs su ni sbyor bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:13971: de ltar sgrub pa'i yo byad rnam lnga dang ldan pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13972: mda' ral gri me long la sogs dkyil 'khor gyi
NK077(tsu)001:13973: rgyan yo byad dang phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:13974: rdzas rnams dang / dngos grub rten gyi yo byad
NK077(tsu)001:13975: thod sku mar me rdor dril la sogs pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:13976: rdzas rnams dang / / dgra bgegs dang nad kyi bar chad rkyen bzlog gi yo byad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:13979: sman dang sman par bcas pa rnams bsdu zhing bsags par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13980: 'tsho ba'i yo byad byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13983: dam nyams kyi lag nas lon pa lta bu ma yin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:13986: phud pa nyams pa ma yin pa bsdu bar bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13987: de la tsho gsum du bcad la yang dag bzhin byin gyis rlabs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13988: de yang tsho gsum du bcad pa'i tsho dang po
NK077(tsu)001:13989: tram las rin po che'i mchod sdong 'od 'bar ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:13990: rtse la yi ge gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:13991: phyi nang gsang ba'i longs spyod 'byung bar bsam ste /
NK077(tsu)001:13992: phyi nang gi gtor ma bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:13994: nyi zla'i steng du dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i 'phro 'du las /
NK077(tsu)001:13995: 'dod yon gyi lhar brlab ste rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis rol /
NK077(tsu)001:13996: tha ma la sogs las nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas /
NK077(tsu)001:13997: yangs shing rgya che bar spel te /
NK077(tsu)001:13999: bsgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14001: bsgrub pa'i thabs ni bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang sbyar bas bsgrub pa'i gzhung bsrang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14002: dgra dang bgegs kyi 'grims srang med pa mi'i dbang ma byas pa bar chad med pa'i gnas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14003: gong du bshad pa'i yongs spyod rnams dang ci bde ba ste lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14004: dam tshig ma nyams pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14005: sgrub pa'i nyams su len pa'i lta ba ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:14006: 'dzin gyi blo ni rab tu ldan pa'i tshom bu
NK077(tsu)001:14007: gcig gsum lnga pa'i dang po dam mnos bzhin du
NK077(tsu)001:14008: bya / 'bras bu ma thob bar du bsgrub par
NK077(tsu)001:14009: dam bcas pa'i ldan pas rnal 'byor pho mo 'dus
NK077(tsu)001:14011: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrung ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14012: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14013: khyad par du spyod lam dang mchod pa'i ting nge 'dzin bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14016: dang po bsnyen pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:14018: dkyil 'khor bri zhing rdzas dgod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14020: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la dgar bas
NK077(tsu)001:14021: yang na 'dir ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dpag
NK077(tsu)001:14022: tshad rgyang grags su bsgom nus pas sam /
NK077(tsu)001:14023: de yang rgyang grags dpag tshad la sogs pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:14024: sbyor lam mthar phyin pas gzhan don dbang bskur la sogs pa la dgos pa yin gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:14025: las dang po pa'i spyod yul ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:14027: slob dpon mthar nye'i lam gnas pa //
NK077(tsu)001:14028: rgyang grags dpag tshad la sogs par //
NK077(tsu)001:14029: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:14032: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dal bri ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14033: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa so sor gang byed mtshams pa'i gzugs brnyan bri /
NK077(tsu)001:14034: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan dang phyi gsang ba'i mchod pa
NK077(tsu)001:14035: la sogs pa dkyil 'khor gyis tha ma 'khor ba
NK077(tsu)001:14036: dang / phyi mchod bya zhing mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14038: phyi rol tu cha gsum btang la mchod pa'i las
NK077(tsu)001:14039: rdzogs par bya ste phyi mtshams rgyal chen gyi tho
NK077(tsu)001:14040: chog dang / phyogs skyong bcu'i mtshams bcad /
NK077(tsu)001:14042: bsrung sgo ni sgo byang phyi nang gdams pa rnams rim pa bzhin du bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14043: sngon du bya ba'i rim pa rdzogs par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14046: dus rtags bya ba las kyi rim pa'i bsnyen pa dang bzhi las /
NK077(tsu)001:14047: 'dir bya ba las kyis bsnyen pa'i don du sngon bya ba /
NK077(tsu)001:14048: rdzogs pa'i las rnams gong du bshad bzhin zin par byas la /
NK077(tsu)001:14049: nye ba'i bsnyen pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14051: nye ba'i sngon du bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14053: rnal 'byor pa rnams nang du 'dus pas tshul phyag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14058: mchod rdzas phyi nang thams cad byin gyis rlabs nas dal sgom pa la 'jug par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14059: gzhung rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:14061: ting nge 'dzin gyis dal bskyed pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14065: rnal 'byor pas lha spyir sgom pa'am yang na rnal
NK077(tsu)001:14066: 'byor pho mo re res lha re rer sgom zhing
NK077(tsu)001:14067: / tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i 'khor lo ste
NK077(tsu)001:14068: dal rgyas bsdus 'bring gsum blo che chung gi rim
NK077(tsu)001:14069: / bzhin sgom mo // rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14071: dbang bskur zhing byin rlabs bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14074: so so bye brag tu sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14078: de bzhin gshegs pa yab rigs lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14080: 'khor pho mo rnams kyis sems dpa' sems ma nyid du sgom //
NK077(tsu)001:14081: de rnams so so'i rigs dang phyag rgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14082: ting nge 'dzin yang dag par so sor gsal bar sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14083: spyir dril te sgom pa de la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:14087: de sa'i rigs ci snyed thams cad kyi 'dus tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14089: de yang bsdu na thugs sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:14090: rigs kyis gtso bo rdo rje'i rigs su 'dus pa
NK077(tsu)001:14091: yin no // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:14092: de sa thams cad kyi thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:14093: bsam gyis mi khyab brjod kyis mi lang pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:14094: / rigs bsdu na thugs ye shes lngar 'dus pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:14095: ye shes lnga po de yang thugs kyi mchog stong
NK077(tsu)001:14096: pa nyid kyi ye shes kho nar 'dus pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:14097: ro // des na rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum /
NK077(tsu)001:14098: rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum dang bcas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14100: khro bo sgo ba yab lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:14101: yum bzhi'i tshogs dang ldan pa'i tshom bu gcig pa'i lha bco brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:14102: de ltar gtso bo rigs gcig gi byas pa tshom
NK077(tsu)001:14103: bu gcig pa'i lha bco brgyad kyi tshogs rnams bsnyen
NK077(tsu)001:14105: nye bsnyen gyi dus su sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14108: gong gis tshom bu las lho byang gnyis bzhag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:14109: mdun gyi shar gyi phyogs su de bzhin rigs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:14110: tshom bu yab yum cha lnga ste ya bcu dang
NK077(tsu)001:14111: / dbus su rdo rje'i rigs kyi tshom bu ya bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14112: rgyaba'am nub tu pad ma'i rigs kyi tshom bu ya bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14113: de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi tshom bu cha gsum gyis mthar /
NK077(tsu)001:14114: phyogs mtshams brgyad du khro bo brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:14115: yum brgyad de bcu drug zhal sbyor ba'i tshogs dang
NK077(tsu)001:14116: ldan pa'i tshom bu gsum pa'i lha zhe drug go
NK077(tsu)001:14117: // de ltar gtso bo rigs gsum kyis byas pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:14118: tshom bu gsum pa'i lha bzhi bcu zhe drug gi
NK077(tsu)001:14119: tshogs rnams bsnyen pa'i dus su bris /
NK077(tsu)001:14120: nye bsnyen gyi dus su sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14124: gtso mo yum lnga yis thabs shes rab gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:14125: med par zhal sbyor ba can du bzhugs pa yis
NK077(tsu)001:14126: tshul ni / ci lta bu zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:14127: 'og gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa lnga po re re la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:14129: lte ba dang bcas pa re re ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14131: dbus kyis 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:14132: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum /
NK077(tsu)001:14133: rtsibs bzhi la rdo rje rigs kyi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad rnams kyi bskor ba /
NK077(tsu)001:14134: rdo rje rigs kyi tshom bu'i lhar gsal ba'i rnal 'byor pa yab yum bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14135: de bzhin du shar lho nub byang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:14138: don 'grub yab yum gyi gtso bo byas pa rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:14142: las kyi rigs kyi rigs chung gis sems dpa' yab yum brgyad kyi bskor ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14143: rigs bzhi'i tshom bu la lha bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:14144: gong gi dbus kyi tshom bu la lha bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14145: de ltar tshom bu cha lnga yis lha lnga bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:14146: rnal 'byor pho mo lnga bcus gsal bar sgom pa bkod la /
NK077(tsu)001:14147: tshom bu cha lnga po de'i mthar /
NK077(tsu)001:14151: rnal 'byor yab yum cha bcu la /
NK077(tsu)001:14153: khro mo yum bcu ste lha nyi shu gsal bar bkod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:14154: tshom bu lnga pa lha bdun cu tham pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14155: de ltar gtso bo rigs lngas byas pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:14156: tshom bu lnga pa'i lha bdun cu po de dag
NK077(tsu)001:14157: kyang dal gyi 'khor lo'i tshul du bsnyen dus su
NK077(tsu)001:14158: bris la / nye bsnyen gyi dus su rnal 'byor sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14159: dbang bskur zhing byin rlabs bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14160: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs te lha gsum sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14161: ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14162: rigs lnga'i dbu brgyan pa dang ldan par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14163: ye shes kyis dal spyan drang zhing phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14165: rang bzhin 'og min gyi gnas nas snyan gsan dbab pa dang spyan drangs par byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:14166: gnyis su med par bzhugs shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:14167: phyag 'tshal ba nas gzhung bsrang ste phyi nang gsang
NK077(tsu)001:14168: ba'i mchod pas rim bzhin mchod pa rdzogs nas glu
NK077(tsu)001:14170: smon lam gdab nas bsnyen pa bya /
NK077(tsu)001:14171: bzlas pa zin nas dal bsdu ste rnal 'byor pas tshogs tshul bzhin du mchod pa'i phrin las bya /
NK077(tsu)001:14172: de nas nang nub mkha' 'gro rnams mchod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:14173: lhag ma gzhung bzhin du sbyin no //
NK077(tsu)001:14174: rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi brod nyul bar
NK077(tsu)001:14175: byed pa'i nyul le ma'i bar chad bzlog phyis bsnyen
NK077(tsu)001:14176: pa bya / de la dus tshad bcu gnyis kyi nyug le ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14178: dgong mo nyi ma nub kha'i zer la nyug le bya ram skad bsgyur ma 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14181: srod la brang rkun nag mo 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14185: nam gong la gti mug rgyan med pa 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14186: rtags su mar me bkrags nyams /
NK077(tsu)001:14189: nam phyed na 'dod chags dmar mo dril bu can 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14191: zhing lpags mgo mthur nas bstan pa gong nas srungs mar bardzusa te /
NK077(tsu)001:14192: chags pa spyod tshul ston du 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:14193: phyed yol nam smad du gtun ser tser 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14196: tho ras skya rengs shar tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:14202: nyi ma gros pa la klu srin sngon mo 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14203: rtags su snying chu hril byed /
NK077(tsu)001:14204: bsgrub mched la nad drag po gtong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:14205: nyi ma phyed tshod la klu chen bzhi 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14209: nyi ma phyed yol nas sa bdag ma yam 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14210: rtags su nyams chung zhing bying bying byed pa 'ong //
NK077(tsu)001:14212: bdud the rang stong sde 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14216: de yan chad ni dus bcu gnyis nyu le mas bar du gcod pa'i rtags yin la //
NK077(tsu)001:14221: bon po mthar lhung la sogs shi 'dre nyams pa rnams bdud kyi bskul nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14222: dus thams cad du yang bar chad btsal /
NK077(tsu)001:14223: bzang bar ston yong nyams mi dga' ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14224: dgong kha bya mchu nag mo 'ong ba shas che bas /
NK077(tsu)001:14225: de dag gi ltas ni dri log pa ting nge 'dzin mi gsal byin chung /
NK077(tsu)001:14229: the tshom phyogs med la skye /
NK077(tsu)001:14230: bla ma dang mched la snang ba log /glu gzhas la dga' /
NK077(tsu)001:14231: sems las su mi rung ba the tshom pa thams cad do //
NK077(tsu)001:14232: de tsho nyu le bskrad pa ni /
