NK077(tsu)001:14234: ging chas thogs la 'jigs pa la zhugs /
NK077(tsu)001:14235: mi rkang mi lpags 'bras mchan sngags ldan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14237: 'ug mgo skam po'i tho ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14238: ku ku la sbyor ba yang bsham ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14240: e gru gsum dong nang du /
NK077(tsu)001:14241: nyu le ma rnams kyi ming gi tri la bskor bar byas le /
NK077(tsu)001:14243: pho nya btang nas bskrad dgos par gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:14244: nye ba'i bsnyen pa'i tshad ting nge 'dzin no //
NK077(tsu)001:14246: zla ba gcig dbang du brtsi na /
NK077(tsu)001:14247: gnas gzhung dang mthun par rdzas bsag go //
NK077(tsu)001:14248: dal bris nas rten rdzas bkod /
NK077(tsu)001:14249: phyogs skyongs mchod pa ni bsnyen pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14250: zla ba phyed kyi phyed zhag bdun nyer bsnyen yin zer yang /
NK077(tsu)001:14251: zla ba gcig la phyed du bgos pa'i phyed po
NK077(tsu)001:14252: de la zhag bco lnga yod pa de nye ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:14254: bdag lhar gsal 'od zer kha dog dkar po phar 'phro mchod pa 'bul /
NK077(tsu)001:14255: tshur 'dus nas dngos grub kyi snod rung bar byas /
NK077(tsu)001:14258: de nas zhag bco lnga mar phyed nub tha ma la gtogs pa bsgrubs pa byed pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14259: 'od zer kha dog dmar po phar 'phro thugs dam
NK077(tsu)001:14260: bskul tshur 'dus te dngos grub thob pa'i 'od zer
NK077(tsu)001:14264: de ltar bsnyen bsgrub kyi zhag grangs nyer dgu tshang
NK077(tsu)001:14265: nas mtshan ma rtags kyis bsnyen pa bsgrub pa'i rtags
NK077(tsu)001:14267: sku gzugs la sogs pa byung na /
NK077(tsu)001:14268: bdud cha brtag la ma nor na nub tha ma
NK077(tsu)001:14269: na ye shes lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub
NK077(tsu)001:14270: / bzlas pa'i 'phro 'dus 'od zer kha dog mthing ka'i sgo nas blang ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14272: 'o na zla ba gcig gis chog gam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:14274: bsnyen bsgrub kyi yun de bzhin du cha brtsi la
NK077(tsu)001:14275: rgyud kyi zhag grangs sum cu phrag drug la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:14276: pa bzhin bar chad med par tshom bu tshogs bsgrub
NK077(tsu)001:14277: par bya'o // khyad par spyod lam dang mchod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14280: tshogs bsgrub pa'i tshe spyod lam du spyod rnam lnga la spyir longs spyod cing rol par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14281: dngos su mchod pa sbyor sgrol rnam gnyis po'ang //
NK077(tsu)001:14282: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14284: sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa khro bo'i skabs su spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14286: gtso ru dgos pa gang yin pa'i sbyor sgrol ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14287: phyi ma gdug pa 'dul ba khro bo'i skabs su dgos par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14288: lha dang spyod la spyad thabs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:14290: spyad thabs spyir dril te mi dmigs pa chos nyid du spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14292: snga ma spyod lam du yo byad lnga la spyod
NK077(tsu)001:14293: thabs rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bya ba 'di
NK077(tsu)001:14294: lta ste / gos dang rgyan gyi spyod dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14299: rang rig pa'i ye shes yi ge h'u gi rang
NK077(tsu)001:14300: bzhin du shes pas yo byad rnams la spyod bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:14301: ma chags pa'i tshul gyis rab tu spyod na /
NK077(tsu)001:14302: ngo mtshar ba'i 'bras bu tshogs chen gnyis 'byung ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:14303: dal thams cad bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pas mnyes
NK077(tsu)001:14305: des grub pa'i don ni gsang ba a li ka
NK077(tsu)001:14306: li la sogs yo byad lnga po rnams rang rig
NK077(tsu)001:14307: pa nyid yin pa'i phyir na don dam pa ma
NK077(tsu)001:14308: skyes pa'i chos rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo
NK077(tsu)001:14309: bor gsal bas / mi rtog pa'i chos nyid la chos nyid thim la /
NK077(tsu)001:14310: kun rdzob tu ma 'gags pa'i ye shes gnyis med kyi rol par sgom zhing spyod /
NK077(tsu)001:14311: zhi ba las gcig shos khro bo'i tshogs bsgrub pa'i yo byad la spyod pa'i tshe na'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:14312: mtshan ma med pa'i spyod thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin de bzhin du sgom pa bya ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:14313: bye brag so so nas rgyas par spyad thabs la gnyis spyod pa lha'i dal du spyod thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14314: bye brag so so nas spyod thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:14316: snod bcud rgyal ba'i dal du sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14317: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin dal sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14320: phyi snod rgyal ba'i dal yin tshul ltar sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14322: phyogs bcu mtha' yas dus bzhi'i bsdus pa'i snod bcud
NK077(tsu)001:14323: kyi 'jig rten thams cad rang rig par dbyer med
NK077(tsu)001:14324: pa'i man da la ste dal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:14325: thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i phyir nyi zla
NK077(tsu)001:14326: 'bar ba'i gdan dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas khang de
NK077(tsu)001:14327: la / pad+ma ltar chags pa med pa'i gdan bting nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14328: rgyu ye shes rin po che yon tan zad pa
NK077(tsu)001:14329: med par 'byung ba'i pho brang gi lha'i gzhal yas
NK077(tsu)001:14330: dbus kyi lte ba la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14331: de yang rgya che chung gi tshad blos dpag tu med pa yis phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:14332: lha'i ngo bo rang rig byang chub bde ba chen
NK077(tsu)001:14333: po dang ldan pa bzhugs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi
NK077(tsu)001:14334: dal la / thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i bde
NK077(tsu)001:14335: ba chen po dang ldan pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK077(tsu)001:14336: lha dang lha mo'i dal te /
NK077(tsu)001:14337: tshom bu gang yin gyi lha'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rab tu bkod na dgos pa ci byed na /
NK077(tsu)001:14338: yo byad la longs spyod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:14339: snod bcud ma lus thams cad chos kyi dbyings su bsdus nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14340: nang bcud kyi yin tshul ltar sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14342: spyod pa lus spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14343: yan lag bsgul cing bsigs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14344: mig la sogs pa dbang po lnga yi spyod yul lha rigs lnga'i dal du gsal ba kun kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:14345: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po nyid du ye nas yin par bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:14347: mi da bi don gyi na phyag rgya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14348: lhag pa lha'i dal sgom la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:14350: gdan gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14352: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dal 'ba' zhig goms
NK077(tsu)001:14353: yang na bro gar la sogs yo byad bzhi la
NK077(tsu)001:14355: gzhal yas khang sgom pa yang /
NK077(tsu)001:14357: rtsa sngags b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang /
NK077(tsu)001:14358: tsa tra rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i dal du /
NK077(tsu)001:14359: gdan nyi zla gnyis zung du 'phrug par brtsegs pa'i 'og sa gzhi yi steng la /
NK077(tsu)001:14360: pad+ma chags med kyi gdan bting nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14361: gong gi gdan zla ba thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14362: nyi ma shes rab pad+ma 'dzin chags med pa'i tshul du sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14363: yang na gdan de'i steng du rnal 'byor pa thabs lha yab dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14364: shes rab yum du gsal bas 'dzin chags med pa'i tshul du sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:14365: zhes lha yab yum du 'chad de /
NK077(tsu)001:14366: 'di ni gzhal yas khang sgom pa'i skabs yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:14367: gzhung la brtag na mi 'thad par mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:14368: brten pa lha'i dal sgom la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14372: lus kyi yan lag bzhi mgo dang lnga po thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:14373: rang rgyud pa'i rnam pa min te /
NK077(tsu)001:14374: rang bzhin nam ngang ngam yongs kyis lha rigs lnga'i dal du rnam par dag pa yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14375: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga la sogs par sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14376: rgyas par rtogs tshogs lha'i dal du sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14378: ye nas rang rig lnga yin pa ma bcos par yongs kyis grub pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14379: gzhi ye nas de ltar yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:14380: yin pa ltar sgom pa lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dal gyis kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:14382: rnal 'byor pa tshom bu'i lhar gsal ba'i dbu la
NK077(tsu)001:14383: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi gtso 'khor gyi bcu
NK077(tsu)001:14384: sgom yan lag bzhi la rigs bzhi'i gtso 'khor gyi
NK077(tsu)001:14385: / lha bcu bcu ste bzhi bcu sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14386: de yang lag pa g.yas rdo rje'i rigs kyi lha bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:14387: g.yon rin chen rigs rkang pa g.yas pad+ma g.yon las kyis rigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:14388: lha de dag gis kha dog dang dbyibs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14389: phyag rgya phyag mtshan rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14390: thabs yab dang shes rab yum tshom bu lnga bcu gsal bar sgom ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14391: lha la 'od zer phyogs bcur spro zhing ngan song gsum la sogs pa'i sgrib pa sbyongs /
NK077(tsu)001:14392: de nas slar rang rang gi gnas su bsdu zhing dal la gnyis su med par bstim mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14395: de ltar 'phro 'du byas pa'i yon tan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14396: 'das pa sangs rgyas dang ma 'das pa 'khor ba thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:14397: bder gshegs rgyal ba'i dal gyi zhing du lhag pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:14398: ting nge 'dzin gyi dal gyi rnal 'byor sbyongs pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:14399: // yan lag bskyod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14400: rnal 'byor pa'i yan lag chen po lnga bskyod na /
NK077(tsu)001:14401: rigs lnga'i dal ma lus g.yo zhing bskyod do //
NK077(tsu)001:14402: 'gro ba lnga byang chub kyi lam du 'dren cing 'dzud /
NK077(tsu)001:14403: snyigs ma lnga yang rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i zhing du sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14404: bye brag so so nas spyad thabs la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:14408: a li ka li la spyod thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:14416: rgyu bzang zhing dbyibs mdzes pa kha dog legs pa'i gos bgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14417: ting nge 'dzin gyi ye shes lnga'i 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro bar 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:14421: des na mthar thugs med kyi bar /
NK077(tsu)001:14422: ye shes lnga'i rgyan gyi brgyan par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:14427: dbu rgyan dang 'gur chu la sogs pa'i rgyan mchog mdzes pa'i lus brgyan nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14428: ting nge 'dzin gyi tshom bu'i lha tshogs la 'od zer 'bar zhing gsal sgom ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14429: de las phyogs bcu gang bar dal la 'od zer spros /
NK077(tsu)001:14430: spyod yul thams cad rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i ngang la ma g.yos pa'i dal la /
NK077(tsu)001:14431: mi dmigs dbyings nas dal thams cad rang bzhin ting nge 'dzin gyis mchod //
NK077(tsu)001:14434: 'dod pa lnga'i longs spyod ma 'gags pa thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14435: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab gnas dgongs pa zag med
NK077(tsu)001:14436: bde ba mchog gi ro yang myong bar byed pa
NK077(tsu)001:14437: bsod nams kyi tshogs bde ba de nyid la ma
NK077(tsu)001:14438: chags ye shes kyi tshogs te tshogs gnyis dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:14439: pa'o // bro gar glu tshig la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14440: spyad thabs dang yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:14443: tshom bu'i lha la spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14445: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14446: lha rgyas bsdus 'bring pho gsal ba'i yum rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:14448: 'dus shing bdag la bstim par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14449: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin de la 'od 'bar te 'od chag gsal bar sgom gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14450: bdag rnal 'byor pa dang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis dgongs pa gnyis med du sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:14451: mngon shes sgrub pa'i thabs yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14453: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po lnga la la sogs pa'i yi ge lnga sgom tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14459: de rnams gsal ba'i yi ge 'phro 'dus mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs so //
NK077(tsu)001:14460: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la chags pa med par
NK077(tsu)001:14461: rol pa'i yon tan des bdag gi don dang gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:14462: gyi don yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:14463: lus kyis bro gar gyis spyad thabs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14465: gtso bo la spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14467: rnal 'byor pa pho mo lhar gsal ba'i thabs yab dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14468: shes rab yum thams cad kun langs la gar bya
NK077(tsu)001:14469: zhing gtso bo dbus nas shar gyi phyogs su kha
NK077(tsu)001:14470: lta zhing rigs chung rnams kyang dbus kyis phyogs su
NK077(tsu)001:14471: kha blta ste / rtogs pa zil gyis gnon pa seng ge'i mchong stabs chen pos mchong par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14472: gang gis dbang po lnga la yi ge lnga sgom
NK077(tsu)001:14473: nas 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga lam du khyer nas
NK077(tsu)001:14476: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14477: shar phyogs su ni kha bltas te //
NK077(tsu)001:14478: seng ge'i stabs chen 'chong bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:14479: lce dkyil yi ge hri sgom nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14480: lce ni bsam gyis mi khyab dang //
NK077(tsu)001:14481: h+r+aihyanga bsam gyis mi khyab spro //
NK077(tsu)001:14482: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mtha' yas su //
NK077(tsu)001:14483: gsung gi da la rab 'jam par //
NK077(tsu)001:14484: gsung gcig da la lan lag ni //
NK077(tsu)001:14485: bsam gyis mi khyab kun dang grags //
NK077(tsu)001:14486: sgra dang ming tshig so sor gsal //
NK077(tsu)001:14487: ljags kyi dbang po bkram las gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:14488: thar dang tha mar gnyis ka brjod //
NK077(tsu)001:14489: nges par kho nar yang dag 'dus //
NK077(tsu)001:14490: de bzhin nyid kyi gcig ma gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:14491: rna ba'i dbang po'i dal dal du //
NK077(tsu)001:14492: tram gi yi ge gsal sgom na //
NK077(tsu)001:14493: mtha' yas bsam gyis mi khyab spros //
NK077(tsu)001:14495: phyogs dus da la ma lus thos //
NK077(tsu)001:14497: sgra dang thos pas gnyis med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14498: de bzhin dri dang ro reg rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:14499: so so'i mtshan nyid gsal sgom na //
NK077(tsu)001:14500: yig 'bru'i snying po ci bzhin dgod //
NK077(tsu)001:14501: sangs rgyas da la ma lus dang //
NK077(tsu)001:14502: 'gro drug ma lus thams cad kun //
NK077(tsu)001:14503: chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis rol //
NK077(tsu)001:14504: dri la sogs pa bde mchog gis //
NK077(tsu)001:14505: kun la tshim par yang dag mchod //
NK077(tsu)001:14506: 'gro drug ma lus thams cad la //
NK077(tsu)001:14507: ci ltar mtshams pa'i don yang byed //
NK077(tsu)001:14508: thabs mkhas thugs rje de ltar gtso bo ston //
NK077(tsu)001:14511: rigs so so'i spyad thabs yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14513: de nas rigs lnga po dbus nas shar /
NK077(tsu)001:14517: las byang phyogs la sogs la rang rang gi phyogs su rim pa bzhin kha bltas te /
NK077(tsu)001:14518: dbus su thugs rdo rje'i rigs dang shar du sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14519: nub tu gsung pad+ma'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14520: lhor yon tan rat+na'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14521: byang du las kyi rigs don yod grub pa'i glu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14522: bro'i tshigs rgyas pa'i rgyud nas 'byung ba ltar brjod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14523: de nas ye shes lngas brgyan pa'i bro glu bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14524: de yang rigs lnga spyi yis glu tshig brjod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14530: rnam pa lnga'i stobs lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14532: rang rang gi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14533: de ltar ting nge 'dzin gyi srog dang ldan pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:14534: bro glu'i bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis rdzogs par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:14535: // de yang dbus su rdo rje sems dpa' bro tshig brjod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14537: dbus nas shar du kha bltas te //
NK077(tsu)001:14538: rkang pa'am stabs chen bskyod byas shing //
NK077(tsu)001:14539: lag gi 'du byed kun bskyod nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14540: bro dang gar gyi phyag rgya bya //
NK077(tsu)001:14542: byang chub sems su rnam par dag /shin tu gsal dang 'od zer 'bar //
NK077(tsu)001:14543: thabs dang shes rab bde ba 'grub //
NK077(tsu)001:14544: cis kyang mi tshugs rdo rje yin //
NK077(tsu)001:14545: bdud bzhi dag ni 'joms par byed //
NK077(tsu)001:14546: theg mchog rdo rje rig 'dzin pa //
NK077(tsu)001:14547: thabs dang shes rab bde 'grub shog /sems nyid rigs pa rdo rje yis //
NK077(tsu)001:14548: nyon mongs sdug bsngal med par byed //
NK077(tsu)001:14549: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi //
NK077(tsu)001:14550: thabs dang shes rab gsal 'gyur shog /nyon mongs sdug bsngal rtsad bcad nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14551: ma rig mun pa med par shog /thugs rje'i 'od zer nyi shar bas //
NK077(tsu)001:14552: thabs dang shes rab 'od 'bar shog /shin tu sra zhing skye shi med //
NK077(tsu)001:14553: rdo rje thugs kyis rol ston pa //
NK077(tsu)001:14555: thabs dang shes rab byams ldan shog /de nas sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i bro glu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14558: bde gshegs ma lus thams cad kun //
NK077(tsu)001:14559: phyogs dus da la bdag nyid tshe //
NK077(tsu)001:14560: mi dmigs thugs kyi da la ru //
NK077(tsu)001:14561: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /thabs chen da la yang dag pa //
NK077(tsu)001:14562: bder gshegs kun la rnam par 'phro //
NK077(tsu)001:14563: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:14564: bde ba'i dkyil du mkhas pas bsdu //
NK077(tsu)001:14565: thams cad ma lus rigs bzhi yi //
NK077(tsu)001:14566: nang du ma 'dus gang yang med //
NK077(tsu)001:14567: de ni bder gshegs da la nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:14568: thabs dang shes rab bde 'grub shog /de nas yon tan rin chen 'byung ldan gyi gro glu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14569: rta mchog gi stangs stabs bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:14570: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur pas //
NK077(tsu)001:14571: yon tan phyogs su kha bltas te //
NK077(tsu)001:14572: lus bsig yan lag bskul bskyod nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14573: stobs chen dag kyang brdungs bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:14574: da la ma lus 'byung ba'i gter //
NK077(tsu)001:14575: zag med nor bu rin po che //
NK077(tsu)001:14576: ma lus kun gyi re ba bskong //
NK077(tsu)001:14577: thabs dang shes par bde 'grub shog /de nas gsung snang ba mtha' yas kyi bro glu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14578: rma bya'i stangs stabs bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:14579: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14580: nus phyogs su ni rab bltas te //
NK077(tsu)001:14581: yan lag lnga po bskyod byas nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14582: gar rnams shin tu mdzes byas nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14583: stobs chen dag kyang brdungs ba bya //
NK077(tsu)001:14584: chos rnams ma lus kun spyod kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:14586: chags pa gsum tshogs pa dang lnga yis bsnyen bsgrub
NK077(tsu)001:14587: yan lag bzhi dang sbyar bas zhi ba tshogs bsgrub
NK077(tsu)001:14589: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14590: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14591: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14593: bsgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14597: bsgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14600: spyir bsgrub pa'i mtshan nyid ldan zhing phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14602: tshogs bsgrub pa de la spros pa mthar phyin pas bsgrub dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:14603: de bzhin nyid kyi cho ga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14604: kun tu snang gi phyag rgya gcig pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:14605: phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:14606: rags pa lha sku la bslab pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:14607: phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:14608: cho ga lnga ni mngon rdzogs par bya zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:14610: glu tshig sgra'i rgyan dang bgo ba'i /
NK077(tsu)001:14612: a li ka li'i yo byad dang lnga ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14613: tshogs bsgrub pa'i mngon du rdzogs par ldan par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:14615: yid skyobs dang byin rlabs 'byung ba'i phyir na sngags zhes bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14616: yan lag lnga ni thugs ye shes sems dpa' /
NK077(tsu)001:14617: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:14618: dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga po de gcig tu dril bas lnga po de /
NK077(tsu)001:14620: rnal 'byor tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis bsgrub pa'i nges
NK077(tsu)001:14621: par legs pa'i dgongs pa zag med kyi rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:14624: ston pa'i rang bzhin dam pa'i mdzod gsum dang ldan pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:14630: bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14631: mkhyen gnyis ka la bsgrib pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14632: shes sgrib kyis rnam mkhyen kho na la sgrib par bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:14633: de ltar na lam pa gang la sgrib pa gang yod zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:14634: 'di yi lugs kyis tshogs lam la las sgrib /
NK077(tsu)001:14636: mthong lam la kun 'gro'i sgrib pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14637: sgom lam la lhan cig gnas pa'i sgrib pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14638: mthar lam la bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa rnams yod par 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:14639: sgrib pa de dag spongs tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14640: gsang sngags pas lta ba rtogs na goms byed pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:14641: shes sgrib thog mar spong bar 'dod la /
NK077(tsu)001:14643: nyon mongs pa dag nas ye shes 'phel bas nyon sgrib thog mar spang bar 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:14644: 'di rnams la mnyam bzhag dang rjes spangs tshul /
NK077(tsu)001:14646: sgom spangs 'ong pa'i rgyu rkyen rnams rigs dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:14647: bro yi sgo nas bden pa mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14648: glu yis snyan pa dang grags pa thob cing /
NK077(tsu)001:14649: bsod nams kyi tshogs chen po 'grub la /
NK077(tsu)001:14650: de la yang ma chags shing mi 'dzin pas ye
NK077(tsu)001:14651: shes kyi tshogs chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro
NK077(tsu)001:14654: bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pa bya thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14656: gza' ba dang bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14657: mur ba dam btung ba'i bye brag yo byad rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:14658: de dag tu snang ba ma 'gags pa thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14659: rang bzhin med pa shes rab ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14660: de gnyis gnyis su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin nyid kyi tshul du gnas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:14661: mchod bya mchod byed tha mi dad par shes pas
NK077(tsu)001:14662: bdag nyid chen po gnas su stobs pa'i mchod pa
NK077(tsu)001:14663: phul ba yis // yon tan la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14665: mchod sbyin mchog tu gyur pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14667: bdag dang sangs rgyas gnyis su med pas dus gsum gyi med pa'i tshul gyi gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:14668: thabs dang shes rab bde 'grub shog /de nas phrin las don 'grub kyi bro ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14670: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur pa //
NK077(tsu)001:14671: byang phyogs su ni kha bstan nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14672: lus bskyod yan lag gar byed cing //
NK077(tsu)001:14673: phyag rgya so sor gsal gyur nas //
NK077(tsu)001:14674: rkang pas stabs chen brdungs bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:14675: yang dag rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:14676: bskal pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:14677: sgrib pa thams cad byang byas te //
NK077(tsu)001:14678: thabs dang shes rab myur 'grub shog /bro gar gyi yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:14680: rkang pa'i bro stabs dang lag pa'i gar gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14681: ngag gi snyan pa'i glu dbyangs bden pa'i tshigs ting
NK077(tsu)001:14682: nge 'dzin dang ldan pa dag gi sgra bsgrags nas
NK077(tsu)001:14683: / yon tan gang 'byung snyam pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:14684: phyogs bcu'i 'gro drug gi skye gnas bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can ma lus pa kun /
NK077(tsu)001:14685: sku lnga lhun grub drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen po'i sku ru mthong bar 'gyur zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:14686: lhun grub rdo rje'i sku'i la /
NK077(tsu)001:14687: lhun grub rig 'dzin du ngos bzung ba yod /
NK077(tsu)001:14688: klu'i yon tan sgra skad thams cad gsung lnga lhun
NK077(tsu)001:14689: grub dam pa chos kyi dung chen po'i sgra yang
NK077(tsu)001:14691: nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib gnyis byang nas
NK077(tsu)001:14692: lhag pa'i 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK077(tsu)001:14694: de yang sgrib pa gnyis po de /
NK077(tsu)001:14697: blo la chos thams cad gsal du mi ster ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14698: shes bya'i sgrib pas shes bya la ye shes 'phel du mi ster ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14700: nyon sgrib kyi tshogs kyi chos thams cad gsal du mi ster ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14701: shes sgrib kyi mthong sgom yan chad du /
NK077(tsu)001:14702: chos thams cad gsal du mi ster ba'ang yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:14704: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa bsgrib /
NK077(tsu)001:14705: ces pas nyon sgrib kyi thar pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14706: rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas kyi dal ma lus pa thams cad la mnyes pa'i khyab cing /
NK077(tsu)001:14707: bdag dang sems can dbyer med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14708: srid pa gsum gyi sems can ma lus pa thams cad la /
NK077(tsu)001:14709: dga' ba dang bde ba chen po khyab par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:14710: bdud rtsi mchog tu gyur cing dngos grub 'byung ba'i yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:14712: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK077(tsu)001:14713: zas dug can la yi ge a bkod de 'ju
NK077(tsu)001:14714: 'dul byas pa tsam gyis bdud rtsir 'gyur zhing de'i
NK077(tsu)001:14721: 'dus pa bzhi re re la'ang brgya rtsa gcig bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:14722: bdud rtsi'i 'od zer las longs spyod phun gsum tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:14723: pa 'byung zhing ngan song gsum du skye ba'i sa
NK077(tsu)001:14724: bon / tri pre du rnams sbyong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14725: de las gzhan du ci yang gzhan du ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14727: sol ba la ljon shing du 'gyur ba dang skom
NK077(tsu)001:14728: sar chu 'byung ba la sogs pa phan tshun mi
NK077(tsu)001:14730: a li ka li la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14732: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14734: de ltar yo byad bzhi po dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK077(tsu)001:14736: shes par lha yum du ldan par 'gyur nas phung po khams dang skye mched lha dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14737: mkha' gsang rdo rje pad+ma byin gyis brlab cing 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:14738: pa'i sbyor ba'i bcos kyi bde ba rgyas pa'i cha
NK077(tsu)001:14739: rnams kyang rdzogs par bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14740: gsang ba sbyor ba'i bsnyen pa nye bsnyen bsgrub pa
NK077(tsu)001:14741: bsgrub chen po dang bzhi yi rim pas rtogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:14742: thams cad gsal stong gnyis su med pas bde ba
NK077(tsu)001:14743: chen po'i dbyings su sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14744: spyod pa'i yon tan la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14745: mchog gi yon tan 'byung tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14746: thun mong gi yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:14749: zab mo'i dbang rnams rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14751: yab yum gnyis med dbyings nas byang chub sems kyi 'od zer 'bar /
NK077(tsu)001:14752: lus la 'od zer 'phros shing bde ba 'bar bas
NK077(tsu)001:14753: ting nge 'dzin phyogs bcur gsal chags pa'i thig le
NK077(tsu)001:14754: bde ba'i lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes mtshon pas
NK077(tsu)001:14757: shes rab ye shes kyis dbang dang bde mchog ni bde ba chen po'i dbang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14758: shin brtan pa'i dbang rnams dang ldan zhing rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14760: bde ba'i ye shes su gsal ba ma 'gags pa thabs che la /
NK077(tsu)001:14761: nyes skyon gyi ma gos pas thabs kyi mchog ste gsang dbang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:14763: rang bzhin med par shes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14764: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:14765: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i bde ba'i ye shes /
NK077(tsu)001:14766: bde stong gnyis med rgyud la skyes pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:14767: gong ma gnyis las khyad par 'phags te /
NK077(tsu)001:14768: shin tu brtan pa bde ba chen po'i dbang yang ldan zhing rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14769: mchod pa rdzogs shing ye shes skyes nas rgyal ba'i dal 'byung tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:14771: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14772: yum mkha' dril bu gnyis srub pa'i sbyor ba las
NK077(tsu)001:14773: byung ba yang dag pa'i bde ba dang ldan pa
NK077(tsu)001:14774: la sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgya bzhi dang phyi sgeg
NK077(tsu)001:14775: nang sgeg gi lha mo brgyad rdzogs shing rol dus
NK077(tsu)001:14776: su / mkha' la nyi zla dus gcig ldan thabs
NK077(tsu)001:14777: gnyis med zung du 'brel gyur na 'bras bu bde
NK077(tsu)001:14778: bar gshegs pa'i dal mngon sum du ma lus 'byung
NK077(tsu)001:14779: su / zhing 'char ba'o // 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par dmar mchan bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:14780: thun mong gi yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:14782: de'i dus su yab yum gyi thig le nyi zla
NK077(tsu)001:14783: gnyis slar bzlog pas rlung dang 'dres pa'i skye 'jigs
NK077(tsu)001:14784: med pa rdo rje'i gzugs su chags pas thabs gyur
NK077(tsu)001:14786: de sbyor ba'i mchod pa chen po de'i yon tan thun mong du tshe ring ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14787: mkha' la bya bzhin 'gro ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14789: gsum pa 'bras bu byung tshul la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14790: spyod yul rgyal ba'i dal du spyod pa'i 'bras bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14791: bro gar 'du 'phro la sogs pa'i bye brag so so'i byung tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:14794: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sangs rgyas byung tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14796: sgyu 'phrul gyi dal lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14797: lha yab yum dra ba'i dal rang rig pa'i mngon gsum du rdzogs pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:14798: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa'i dal thams cad 'grub
NK077(tsu)001:14799: par 'gyur te yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis
NK077(tsu)001:14800: sa thob pa'o // ye shes bla ma'i 'bras bu 'byung tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:14802: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i ting nge 'dzin brtan pa'i sa /
NK077(tsu)001:14803: phyogs bcu dus bzhir de bzhin gshegs pa yis sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14804: khams gsum 'gro rnams rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gyur te ye shes bla ma'i sa thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14805: bro gar 'du 'phro la sogs pa so so'i byung tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:14807: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sngon rdzogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:14808: dal dang tshom bu la goms shing brtan pa'i ting
NK077(tsu)001:14809: nge 'dzin gyi bro gar 'du 'phro yis phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:14810: yis ri brag la 'dzul nam mkhar 'gro bar 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:14812: glu tshigs sgra yis phyag rgya yis chos kyi dngos
NK077(tsu)001:14813: grub 'byung ste chos la dbang thob par 'gyur ro
NK077(tsu)001:14814: // rgyan dang bgo ba'i phyag rgya yis mtshan dang
NK077(tsu)001:14815: dpe byad dang 'od zer 'bar ba'i sku rgyal po
NK077(tsu)001:14816: bdud kyi dpung bzhi pa mi tshugs pas thub pa
NK077(tsu)001:14818: bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK077(tsu)001:14819: thun mong gi dngos grub yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK077(tsu)001:14820: rin po che lta bu'i sku mdangs dang ldan pa
NK077(tsu)001:14821: dang / zas thams cad bdud rtsir 'grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14822: yum a li yab ka li'i phyag rgya yis /
NK077(tsu)001:14823: thun mong dngos grub thams cad dang mchog gi dngos grub thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:14824: spyi don gnyis pa khro bo bsgrub pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14825: phun sum tshogs pa lngas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14830: dang po mdor bstan ni gdug pa'i 'dul khro bo'i dal gyis tshogs bsgrub par bya ba'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:14831: bsgrub pa po'i gnas dang zla yum dang grogs po rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14834: bsgrub thabs rnams ni tshogs bsgrub pa'i cha rkyen mchog tu dmigs pas bzhag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14837: gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14840: rtsi shing gi nags tshal chen po yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14841: grongs las dpag tshad rgyang grags kyi ring ba /
NK077(tsu)001:14842: bar chad gsum gyis dben pa'i sar /
NK077(tsu)001:14843: rngams glog dang rdo rje las rim la sogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:14844: gzhung nas bshad pa dang mthun pa'i gnas rnyed nas
NK077(tsu)001:14845: ni / gnas der sa'i cho ga bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:14846: dang por sa phyogs de'i gnod bgegs la zhi bas
NK077(tsu)001:14847: glud gtor byin la khro bo'i phur pas bskrad cing
NK077(tsu)001:14848: / sa la gter gnan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14849: sa gzhi dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK077(tsu)001:14850: ye shes rin po che byin gyis rlabs pa la sogs pa gzhi mnyam pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:14851: cho ga rnams rdo rje las rim ltar rgyas par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14854: spyir ting nge 'dzin mthu mnyam pas bsgrub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14856: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste khro bos lha yab yum
NK077(tsu)001:14857: zung 'brel mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pas khrag
NK077(tsu)001:14858: 'thung khro bo'i dal gyi lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:14859: la sogs sgom pa la spros pa'i skabs su blo
NK077(tsu)001:14860: brten pa thob pa'i stobs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:14863: sngags kyi yan lag lnga ste chos bco lnga tshang
NK077(tsu)001:14864: zhing rdzogs pa khro bo spros pa mthar phyin pa
NK077(tsu)001:14865: yis / rnal 'byor pa pho mo don brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14867: brgya dang bco brgyad la sogs pa sbyor ba mthu
NK077(tsu)001:14868: dang skal ba mnyam pa 'dus pas tshogs bsgrub na
NK077(tsu)001:14869: nges par ste the tshom med par mthong lam gyi
NK077(tsu)001:14871: bye brag tu ston 'khor mtshan nyid dang ldan pas bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14873: de yang ston pa rdo rje rgyal po dam pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:14874: mdzod gsum dang ldan pa dbang gi chu bo rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:14875: pa can mthar nye lam las gong ltar yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:14876: brgyad dang ldan pa dang rdo rje rgyal tshabs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:14877: skyes bu yang / rdo rje rgyal por yon tan dang lta dgongs mtshungs shing mnyam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14878: kar ma las mkhan skad kyi gdangs chen po snyan
NK077(tsu)001:14879: la phrin las kyi khrigs kyi rim pa ma nor
NK077(tsu)001:14881: yum ljon shing ma ni kha dog dkar zhing mtshan dang ldan la /
NK077(tsu)001:14882: ri mo rin po che'i gzugs su yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14883: srin lag gi rtsa ba la sogs ri mo 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:14884: lo'i tshul du yod pa zhi ba'i gzung ma ste
NK077(tsu)001:14886: dkar mo bung chung skad che ba //
NK077(tsu)001:14887: bzhin lus gtsug phud g.yas su 'khyil //
NK077(tsu)001:14889: bslu khar lci ba'i zhi bar bya //
NK077(tsu)001:14892: kha dog dkar ser mtshan dang ldan pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:14893: ri mo rin po che'i gzugs su yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14895: zla dang yan lag mang ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:14896: phra zhing yan lag zongs su rings //
NK077(tsu)001:14897: bzhin lus ser zhing gru bzhir gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:14898: rna 'phyang sha dang nu ma rgyas //
NK077(tsu)001:14902: sha mdog dkar la rtsa dmar na //
NK077(tsu)001:14903: ri mo pad+ma'i dbyings su yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14905: bzhin mdog pad 'dra seng kha ma //
NK077(tsu)001:14906: smig dkyus ring la stod smad 'byed //
NK077(tsu)001:14907: lus dang chu klung dri zhim zhing //
NK077(tsu)001:14908: bde ba ldang zhing yal ka med //
NK077(tsu)001:14914: ri mo zur gsum du yod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14916: nag mo gru gsum rtsi mgo ma //
NK077(tsu)001:14917: khro gnyer byis pa'i lus ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:14918: gtum zhing barlanga tshig 'dzem bag med //
NK077(tsu)001:14919: gtsang sme rtog pa gsod par byed //
NK077(tsu)001:14921: de lta bu'i rig ma mtshan nyid dang ldan zhing yon tan rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14927: rdul phyag skyes bu'i 'khor la sogs pa rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:14928: pho mo sems nyon mongs pa dang ldan pa'i chags
NK077(tsu)001:14929: sems ma yin pa ming po dang sring mo'i tshul
NK077(tsu)001:14930: du brtse gdung dang ldan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14931: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa tshang ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:14932: yang na tshom bu gang bsgrub kyang yab yum zung du 'brel pa gcig gi kyang bsgrub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:14934: yo byad rnams tshogs par bsags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14935: de ci ltar spyod thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14939: bsgrub pa rdzas kyi spyod dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14941: dkar rtsi ste yab kyi byang sems dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14942: dmar rtsi ste yum gyi rag ta dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14946: rdo rje dung chen thod pa rak+ta dmar gyi bkang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14947: gsol bya gi snod du thod dkar po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14949: thod rnga'am mi rkang gi dung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14950: srog shing ste mi'i sgal tshig gsar rnying dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14951: lha'i rten du khro bo'i sku gzugs bris sku la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14952: lugs su blug pa'i dpal chen sku'am /
NK077(tsu)001:14953: dung mchog ste thod sku dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14954: dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14957: bsgrub pa po'i 'tsho ba'i yo byad bza' btung gi bye brag rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14958: sku gsung thugs kyi bsgrub pa'i rdzas kyi yo byad
NK077(tsu)001:14959: rdo rje dril bu mar me la sogs pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:14960: / dal gyi mchod rdzas phyi nang gi bye brag rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14962: bkra shis dag pa'i zhing du gyur pa mchog skye ba bdun pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14963: mchog phran tsa ra dang shel sgong la sogs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14964: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa /
NK077(tsu)001:14965: mchog ni mi las gyur pa bdun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14966: mchog phran ngan song gsum dang //
NK077(tsu)001:14967: bar chad rkyen bzlog gi yo byad do //
NK077(tsu)001:14970: sdang ba dgra bzlog pa'i yo byad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14972: 'du ba nad bzlog pa'i yo byad do //
NK077(tsu)001:14973: de la bgegs kyi rkyen bzlog pa yungs dkar rgyal po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14975: lce sog ste ku kul nag po'i /
NK077(tsu)001:14977: nad kyi rkyen bzlog bsil drod sman dang de sbyor shes pa'i sman par bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14978: dgra'i rkyen bzlog pa'i rdo rje'i go cha dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14979: rdo rje'i mtshon cha mda' gzhu dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14981: gzhan yang khro bo bsgrub pa la dgongs pa'i ci snyed pa'i rdzas rnams kun //
NK077(tsu)001:14982: de ci ltar spyod thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:14984: rnal 'byor pa rang nyid 'jigs byed dpal chen po'i
NK077(tsu)001:14985: skur gsal ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan zhing thams
NK077(tsu)001:14986: cad sems su shes pas gong gis rdzas de rnams
NK077(tsu)001:14989: the tshom re dogs dang 'jigs pa med pa'i sems kyis spyad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:14990: yo byad kyi dgos ched do //
NK077(tsu)001:14992: yo byad de rnams bsdus te de rnams la brten
NK077(tsu)001:14993: nas khro bo'i tshogs su bsgrub par bya ba'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:14994: / rang ci 'dod pa'i yo byad dgos pa snang bar bdag gis mtshams shing rdzogs par bkod do //
NK077(tsu)001:15000: blo chung bas sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam /
NK077(tsu)001:15001: rab kyi zhag drug cu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15003: 'bring zhag dgu cu rtsa drug ste zla ba gsum dang zhag drug gi bar du /
NK077(tsu)001:15004: 'jigs byed chen po khro bo'i tshom bu tshogs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:15005: dkyil 'khor gsum po gang mos su ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:15006: gsal ba dang ldan pa sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:15007: de yang skabs 'dir zhi khro gnyis la /
NK077(tsu)001:15008: dus nye ring byung ba ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:15009: gsang sngags nyon mongs pa lam du byed pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15010: khro bo nye ba ltar bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:15012: khro bo la bar chad nyung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:15013: spyod pa brlabs che bas dus myur ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:15014: gzhan yang ting nge 'dzin stobs che chung yod pas 'byung ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:15015: zhi ba'i tshom bu gcig pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:15017: gsum pa la zhe drug /lnga pa la bdun cu las med pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:15018: khro bo'i tshom bu gcig pa la bdun cu rtsa brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:15019: gsum pa la dgu bcu go brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:15020: lnga pa la brgya bco brgyad sgom nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15022: gsang sngags bla med kyi lta ba ci bzhin par rtogs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:15023: bzang ngan dang gtsang rtsog med cing mnyam nyid ro gcig tu rtogs dgos pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:15024: rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa tshe rnam gnyis yin /
NK077(tsu)001:15025: thog mar mgo zug nas sbyang dgos pa tshom bu tshogs bsgrub 'di yin /
NK077(tsu)001:15026: 'di la khro bo bsgrub pa'i rten gyi gang zag des /
NK077(tsu)001:15027: gding dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen la sogs pa'i rdzas smre ba 'di rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15028: chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes gnyis dbyer med ro gcig tu rtogs pa la blo sbyongs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15029: khro bo bsgrub pa'i rten gyi gang zag de dus myur bar 'thad par sems so //
NK077(tsu)001:15030: dus la re dogs med par bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15032: sgyu 'phrul dra ba khro bo yab yum zung du 'brel ba'i dal la /
NK077(tsu)001:15033: lta ba rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin gsal lta dgongs kyi gding dang bcas pa'i bsam pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15034: 'bras bu thob tu re ba ma thob kyi dogs
NK077(tsu)001:15035: pa med par rab tu brtson 'grus bskyed la bsgrub
NK077(tsu)001:15036: pa'o // bsgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o /
NK077(tsu)001:15038: rgyas pa'i le'u don brgyad pa ltar tshogs bsgrub pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:15039: glu tshig sgra dang bro gar 'du 'phro dang phyag
NK077(tsu)001:15040: rgya dang / shes rab thabs su sbyor shes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15041: thabs shes gnyis su med pa rol pa'i nyi zla
NK077(tsu)001:15042: byang chub sems kyi bde bas gzhan la mchod pa
NK077(tsu)001:15043: dang / bsgrub pa dus kyi lus ngag kyi brda
NK077(tsu)001:15044: la sogs pa'i yon tan ni ci ltar zhe na
NK077(tsu)001:15045: dang / / sbas pas grub rtags nye /
NK077(tsu)001:15048: phal pas mi rig pa'i dgos ched yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:15052: ngag gi brda la tha dad pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15059: a nu ra ga ya ham /
NK077(tsu)001:15060: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK077(tsu)001:15075: tsa ra ma na ga du bya ba la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15078: lag g.yas yab dang g.yon pa yum //
NK077(tsu)001:15079: spyi bor byug pa phyag 'tshal te //
NK077(tsu)001:15080: dpral bar byug pa phyag len yin //
NK077(tsu)001:15081: lag pa g.yas brgyang mgo btud pas //
NK077(tsu)001:15082: khams bde dri ba'i brda' ru bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:15083: lag g.yon brkyang ste btud pa ni //
NK077(tsu)001:15084: bde zhes bya ba len gyi brda' //mig gnyis reg
NK077(tsu)001:15085: pa gzugs ston brda' //g.yas pa skyes pa g.yon pa
NK077(tsu)001:15086: ni // bud med bzang mo'i brda' ru bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:15087: rna ba g.yas pa lag pa reg /tshig bsnyan smra
NK077(tsu)001:15088: dang g.yon glu'i brda' //zhes pa la sogs rgyas par
NK077(tsu)001:15089: bshad do // de'i yon tan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15090: kun 'dus brda'i le'u nas 'byung ba ltar shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15092: bca' ba dang btung ba rnams ro zhim pa bgo ba reg bya 'jam legs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15096: 'dod pa'i yon tan longs spyod lnga dang ldan pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:15097: rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin mthun pa thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:15098: ni / mdo don dril na khro bo tshogs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:15099: dal tshom bu gcig gsum lnga po rnams mngon sum
NK077(tsu)001:15101: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrangs ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15102: spyi'i bsnyen bsgrub sngon bzhin dang bsgrub pa'i bsnyen bsgrub pa dang po /
NK077(tsu)001:15104: spyi'i lam rim 'jug gi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi sngon zhi ba'i skabs bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15105: bsgrub pa'i bsnyen bsgrub la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:15106: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi pa gzhung bsrong ba dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15107: sbyor sgrol gsang ba'i mchod pa la spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15108: yo byad bzhi la spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15109: skabs dang 'jug gi las bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15114: 'dir khro bo tshogs bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi bsnyen pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15118: rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:15125: dal brtsig cing bri ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15127: dang po bsnyen pa byed pa'i dus kyi tshe na
NK077(tsu)001:15128: gong du bshad pa'i gnas chen po dben pa'i phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:15130: tshul ci ltar du bzhengs zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:15131: blo rab 'bring gis lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dal rgyang grags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15133: gzugs brnyan gyi dal tshom bu gcig pa la lus gang tshom bu gsum pa la lus do //
NK077(tsu)001:15134: lnga pa la lus gsum ste 'dam gsum gyi tshad /
NK077(tsu)001:15135: rnal 'byor pa rang gi rig pa tsam sgom nus par phyag rgya lha'i gzugs dang snying po rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:15136: thal chen la sogs pa kha dog lnga'i mtshon gyis kha bsgyur te bris par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15137: yo byad byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15139: bsgrub pa'i yo byad rnams sngon zhi ba'i skabs bzhin byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15140: phyi mchod bya zhing mtshams bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15141: cha gsum dpal bsdom ma ltar phyi mchod rnams kyis
NK077(tsu)001:15142: 'phags pa'i rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' la lha
NK077(tsu)001:15143: mo bcu gnyis kyis bskor ba mchod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:15144: bstan pa bsrung bar dam bcas pa'i phyi rol pa
NK077(tsu)001:15145: phyogs skyongs bar bcu dang rgyal chen bzhi gtor ma
NK077(tsu)001:15146: dang pos mnyes par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15147: snying rje lan chags kyi mgron gnyis po yang /
NK077(tsu)001:15149: tha mas sbyin pas shes pa'i rgyud tshims par byas la /
NK077(tsu)001:15150: chos skyong la bstan pa bsrung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15151: 'byung po la rang gi gnas su deng cig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15152: bgegs la bar chad ma byed ces bka' bsgo ba bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15155: de la bsrung ba 'khor los mtshams phur gdab pa
NK077(tsu)001:15156: ni 'jigs byed zhe sdang rdo rje'i dbang ngam ting
NK077(tsu)001:15157: nge 'dzin du rnal 'byor bdag nyid zhugs te h'u
NK077(tsu)001:15158: ka ra dang / ta ki ra tsa la sogs pa rim pa bzhin bskul nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15159: snying po brjod pa tsam gyis khro bo bcu dang khro mo bcu 'khor du byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:15160: gdan nyi ma'i steng du phyogs skyongs bcu gzir zhing
NK077(tsu)001:15161: stod khro bo bcur brlabs pa'i phur bus phyogs skyongs
NK077(tsu)001:15162: bcu la bdud rtsi 'khyil pas gdab /
NK077(tsu)001:15163: de yang rang bzhin gyi gnas 'og min nas ye
NK077(tsu)001:15164: shes kyi khro bo bcu yab yum la snyan gsan
NK077(tsu)001:15167: bsgrub pa'i bar chad byed pa'i bgegs thams cad khro
NK077(tsu)001:15168: bo bcu'i ting nge 'dzin mchog gis bzlog par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:15169: // de ltar bsnyen bsgrub kun gyi thun mong gi mtshams bsrungs ba'i 'khor lo bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15170: nye ba'i bsnyen pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15173: dang po sngon du bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15174: bsnyen pa song ba de nas gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa la dal gyi rgyan /
NK077(tsu)001:15177: dal sogs te 'go log gi rgyan rnams dgod pa
NK077(tsu)001:15178: dang rdo rje dril bu dang thod sku la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:15179: pa bsgrub pa'i rdzas gang yin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15180: phyi nang gsang gsum gyis mchod pa'i rdzas rnams dgra bcom pa rdzogs nas phyi mtshams rta mgrin /
NK077(tsu)001:15182: gsang mtshams khro bo bcur gsal bas bar chad bsrung bar byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:15183: spyir phyi nang gsang gsum gyis mtshams de ltar du bcad kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:15184: lag lan du 'di rnams thams cad phyi mtshams yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:15185: nang mtshams dge bcus mi dge bcu gcod de /
NK077(tsu)001:15186: spang bya sdig pa mi dge ba bcu la /
NK077(tsu)001:15187: spang byed dge ba bcus bcad pas 'bras bu dbang bcu thob ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15188: gnas gyur khro bo bcur 'gyur ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15190: srog gcod skyon spang tshe la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK077(tsu)001:15192: des nas de gal che ste de med na da lta'i phyi mtshams des /
NK077(tsu)001:15193: ci la yang mi phan te /
NK077(tsu)001:15195: gsang mtshams bdag tu 'dzin pa gcod pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15196: gnyen po gang gis gcad na /
NK077(tsu)001:15197: bdag med rtogs pa'i mtshon chen gyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:15198: ye shes 'khor lo skad cig mas //
NK077(tsu)001:15199: rnam rtog log 'dren bgegs rnams bsgrad //
NK077(tsu)001:15201: des na bdag 'dzin la mtshams gcig ma chod na sangs rgyas mi srid do //
NK077(tsu)001:15202: de nas las kyi srin po'i rgyal po ma tang dgug pa dang bsgral ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15203: dal bskyed pa la sogs gzhung nas 'byung ba'i tshul bzhin du mnan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15204: de yang sngon 'byung du dpal chen po rdo rje srin pos /
NK077(tsu)001:15205: ma tam bsgral ba'i rjes su rnal 'byor pa rnams 'jug pa yin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:15206: pha'i las kha gang yin pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:15208: seng ge'i ro la gcan gzan gzhan gyi nye ba mi nus pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:15209: ma tam gi khog par gzhal yas khang bskyed pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15210: bgegs kyis nye mi nus pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:15211: bdag 'dzin dug gsum sgrol ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:15214: yang dag thar lam gcod byed pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:15215: 'byung po gtum po gdos pa can //
NK077(tsu)001:15216: khyod ni de bzhin don la sgrib //
NK077(tsu)001:15217: yang dag nges pa'i blo gros kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:15218: khung bcad rtsad bcad bdag las byung //
NK077(tsu)001:15220: phyin ci log stobs brtson 'grus kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:15221: gnas ngan len pa'i brtson 'grus byed //
NK077(tsu)001:15222: de nyid bdag rtog yin pas na //
NK077(tsu)001:15223: bdag med nam mkha'i stobs kyis gzhom //
NK077(tsu)001:15225: de na rtags gsum dang ldan par //
NK077(tsu)001:15226: bshags pas sdig sgrib sbyang ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:15229: de nas phyi nang gi mchod rdzas rnams byin gyis rlabs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15230: gzhung bzhin bya ba la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15231: ting nge 'dzin gyi dal bskyed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15232: ye shes kyi dal spyan drangs shing phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15236: tshom bu'i lha bskyed pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15240: sngon 'gro rdzogs pa dang de nas 'khor tshom bu gcig pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:15241: tshom bu gsum pa dang lnga ru sgom par bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15242: pho brang gis 'khor lo dang bar 'khyam dang sgo rnams su /
NK077(tsu)001:15243: 'jigs byed badz+ra he ru ka 'khor lo rigs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:15244: gtso bo mdzad pa'i btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par
NK077(tsu)001:15245: sgom // rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15249: yang na 'khor lo bar khyams zhes pa 'di phan chad rgyas bshad la btang nas bshad na //
NK077(tsu)001:15250: tshom bu gcig pa'i dal la sa nang tshegs su bcad na gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:15251: de bzhin rigs kyi gtso bo byas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15252: de rigs bzhi la sbyar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15253: dang po la bzhi gang du sgom pa'i gnas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15254: gtso bo sgom pa'i lha dang 'khor gyi sgom pa'i lha dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15255: ci ltar sgom pa'i thabs so //
NK077(tsu)001:15258: 'og gzhi 'khor lo gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung ba gcig bar khyams gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15260: bskal pa'i me ri rnams su //
NK077(tsu)001:15261: gnyis pa gtso bo sgom pa'i lta ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15264: khro bo'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang ldan pa'i dbus
NK077(tsu)001:15265: kyi lte ba la rigs kyi gtso bo btsun mo'i
NK077(tsu)001:15266: mchog dang ldan par sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:15267: gsum pa 'khor gyi lha sgom pa'i lha ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15268: de yang zhi ba'i phyogs shar gyi rtsibs bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15271: rgyas pa ste lho'i rtsibs bzhi po der /
NK077(tsu)001:15272: gdul bya 'jigs par byed pa'i tshogs chen b+hud+d+ha he ru ka dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15275: rat+na he ru ka dang bzhi po de bzhugs pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:15276: de'i dbus kyi lte ba'i steng na rtsibs bzhi lte
NK077(tsu)001:15277: ba dang bcas pa gcig yod pa'i lte dbus su
NK077(tsu)001:15278: // bzhi pa ci ltar sgom pa'i thabs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15279: de yang gang ltar sgom na /
NK077(tsu)001:15280: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid zhi ba las drag por
NK077(tsu)001:15281: bcos pa badz+ra he ru ka'i tshul du gsal bas
NK077(tsu)001:15282: / rang gi sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi dal du gsal bar sgom //
NK077(tsu)001:15283: gnyis pa de rigs bzhi la sbyar ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15284: gtso bo khro bo tshul du sgom pa de bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:15285: 'khor lo rtsibs chung gi shar gyi rtsibs la rdo rje'i rigs kyi de bzhin rigs chung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15286: nub tu rdo rje pad+ma'i rigs chung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15287: lhor rdo rje'i rin chen rigs chung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15288: byang du rdo rje'i ral gri ste las kyi rigs kyi yab yum gnyis te bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:15289: tshom bu gsum kar gyi dbus 'gyur mtha' mi 'gyur bas /
NK077(tsu)001:15290: mtha'i 'khor rnams kyi lha'i rnam grangs 'dir ma smos kyang shugs la tshangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15295: khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15296: tshom bu gcig pa la lha bdun cu don brgyad sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:15299: tshom bu gcig pa las gzhan pa sku gsung thugs
NK077(tsu)001:15300: rdo rje'i tshom bu gsum pa la mos pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:15301: na mdun du sku b+hu d+ha'i tshom bu /
NK077(tsu)001:15302: rgyab tu gsungs pad+ma'i tshom bu /
NK077(tsu)001:15303: dbus su thugs rdo rje rigs kyi 'jigs byed /
NK077(tsu)001:15304: khro bo'i tshom bu de dag re re la lha bcu bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15305: pho brang gi lha sum cu 'khor drug cu rtsa brgyad de /
NK077(tsu)001:15306: tshom bu gsum pa lha dgu cu go brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:15307: tshom bu lnga pa'i lha bskyed cing sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15309: 'jigs byed khro bo'i tshom bu lnga po nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i dal sgom pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15310: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad rigs lngar 'dus pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:15311: tshom bu cha lnga'i rigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:15312: de ltar rgyal ba he ru ka rigs lnga po re re la'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:15313: rigs chung dang bcas pa yab yum nyi shu rtsa lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15314: de la 'khor cha lnga la bkod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15316: gsung gi tshom bu bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15317: thugs kyi tshom bu bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15318: yon tan gyi tshom bu bcu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15319: phrin las kyi tshom bu bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15321: tshom bu lnga pa la lha brgya dang bco brgyad rdzogs par sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:15322: rgyan dang cha lugs rdzogs par sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15324: de dag kyang dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad dpal gyi
NK077(tsu)001:15325: chas brgyad dang 'bar ba'i gar dgu'i cha lugs la
NK077(tsu)001:15326: sogs la / gdul bya gdug pa can 'jigs par byed pa'i khro bo'i tshogs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15327: rang bzhin gyi gnas 'og min nas bzhugs pa'i 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dal /
NK077(tsu)001:15328: ji bzhin par bsgrub pa po yab yum zung gcig gis lha thams cad spyir sgom pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:15329: yang na rnal 'byor pa re res lha re re ru sgom pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15330: de dag kyang 'tsham rngam chen po rol pa khro bo'i cha lugs su gsal bar sgom pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15331: yan lag gi lhas dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15333: de nas lha thams cad la yan lag lhag pa'i dal /
NK077(tsu)001:15336: ye shes sems dpa' dang dgu dgur lha re re
NK077(tsu)001:15337: la ldan pa ste de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:15338: byin rlabs dang / ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba
NK077(tsu)001:15339: thob pa'i bdag nyid dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la
NK077(tsu)001:15340: byin rlabs dang / // ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:15341: spyan drang zhing phrin las kyi rim pa la bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:15343: rang bzhin dal spyan drang zhing bstim pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15345: rang bzhin ye shes pa'i dal /
NK077(tsu)001:15346: snyan gsan phab spyan drangs la lcags kyu'i rgyag rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:15347: 'gug /zhags pas gzhug lcags sgrog gis bcings dril bus
NK077(tsu)001:15348: dgyes par bskyed nas brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK077(tsu)001:15349: mchod pa'i rim pa bya zhing bdud rtsi dngos grub blang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15351: de nas phyag 'tshal ba nas sman mchod yan chad kyi rim pa bzhin mchod par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15352: bdud rtsi'i dngos blang ba'i sngags ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15367: ka ya ba ga tsi ta sku gsung thugs /
NK077(tsu)001:15369: h'u h'u h'u thugs kyi gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15370: swa swa swa yon tan gyi gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15371: am am am gsung gi gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15372: ham ham ham phrin las kyi sku gsung thugs /
NK077(tsu)001:15381: dpal khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga'i sku gsung thugs kyis dngos grub rtsol cig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15385: sh+ri dpal he ru ka khrag 'thung /
NK077(tsu)001:15386: a me me tog /du me spos /
NK077(tsu)001:15388: b+ha we gyur cig /sam ha ra na bsdus cig
NK077(tsu)001:15389: /h'u h'u h'u sdud cig ma h+aa chen po yo
NK077(tsu)001:15390: ga rnal 'byor / ad d+ha ma h+aa sa ma
NK077(tsu)001:15391: ya dam tshig /ru lu ru lu hub gsum btung
NK077(tsu)001:15392: ga rnal 'byor / ba'o // a la la ngo mtshar /
NK077(tsu)001:15394: don la sman gyis bde bar gshegs pa thams cad mchod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:15395: dngos grub blang zhing hub gsum rang gi btung ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:15400: rang lus rgyal ba'i dal mchod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15401: bdud rtsi gsang nan gyi mchod pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15402: gtor ma 'bul zhing mchod bstod bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15404: +aahmh'u sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo /
NK077(tsu)001:15411: sa ma na dam tshig /dz+wa la ni 'bar ba /
NK077(tsu)001:15415: kha hi gsol cig /a la la ho dgyes pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15416: de ltar mchod pa'i rim pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15417: bstod pa smon lam yan chad rdzogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15418: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15422: bzlas pa'i bsnyen pa bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15423: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15424: lha ye shes sems dpa' mdun gyi thad ka dbugs
NK077(tsu)001:15425: kyi sleb tshad tsam du ste lhag pa nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:15427: bar gyi bzlas pa'i 'phro 'du'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15428: de ltar gsal ba gsum ldan gyi bsnyen pa bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15431: gang bsnyen gyi lha gang yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:15432: da res badz+ra he ru ka /badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka /yab kyi snying po /
NK077(tsu)001:15439: ru lu ma h+aa sa ma ya h'u /
NK077(tsu)001:15441: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK077(tsu)001:15445: de ltar 'dzab rdzogs pa ni rigs bzhi bzlas bsnyen dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15447: zhag bdun gyi 'od zer phar 'phros par thugs dam bskul ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15448: tshur 'dus pas dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15449: bsgrub pa'i dus su 'di bzlas pas bsnyen pa'i dal rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15450: de yan chad bsnyen pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:15453: mdun yin par mngon ste ye shes kyi lha mdun gyi bar snang la bzhugs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:15454: bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i thugs ka nas 'od zer byung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15455: ye shes sems dpa' thugs kar 'phros /
NK077(tsu)001:15457: tshur 'dus bdag dam tshig sems dpa' sgo gsum gyis
NK077(tsu)001:15458: sgrub pa sbyangs nas dngos grub kyi snod du rung
NK077(tsu)001:15463: ye shes mdun lhag pa la gnas pa gsal ba gsum gyi bya /
NK077(tsu)001:15467: tshom bu'i lha de nyid la nye ba'i bsnyen pa
NK077(tsu)001:15468: dang de bzhin du bsgrub pa bya ba'i dus su
NK077(tsu)001:15469: yang / bzlas pa'i 'od zer kha dog dmar po
NK077(tsu)001:15470: 'phros pas dngos grub stsol cig par rgyud bskul ba
NK077(tsu)001:15471: yang / dang / tshur la 'dus pas bdag la dngos grub bsdud par bsam zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:15472: bzlas pa'i skyon bcu spang ste bsgrub pa bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15473: de ltar bsgrub pa byed pa'i dus su dgos par shes par bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15474: bsgrub pa chen po la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15476: bsgrub pa bya ba dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15478: gcig ni bsgrub chen po la rdzas dang mchod pa ltar dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams bshams la /
NK077(tsu)001:15479: 'od zer phar mi spro tshur bsdu ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15480: bsgrub pa chen po yin par shes par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:15481: spyir 'dzab dgongs kyi ting nge 'dzin bya thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15483: bsnyen pa dang nye bsnyen la shel ltar kha dog dkar po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15484: bsgrub pa'i dus su bye ru ltar kha dog dmar po bung ba lding ba ltar dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15485: bsgrub pa chen po la mthing gi bung ba lta bu mang po dag tshur 'dus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15486: bsnyen bsgrub kyi rim pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:15487: bsnyen pa dang bsgrub pa la bcud bsdus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15488: bung bas me tog 'jib cing tshang du bsogs pa'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15489: bsgrub chen dus mtsho la ser chen 'bab pa bzhin phar mi 'phro tshur la thim pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:15490: 'di dag gi don rgyas par bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:15491: bsnyen bsgrub rnams la rim pa bzhin du gong ma rnams la /
NK077(tsu)001:15492: dper na bung ba phar phyin nas me tog 'jib /
NK077(tsu)001:15494: phar 'phro tshur 'gro zing zing byed pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:15495: bsgrub pa'i dus su bzlas pa'i 'od zer ye shes pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:15496: bdag gi sgrib pa sbyong la /
NK077(tsu)001:15497: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol cig par rgyud bskul /
NK077(tsu)001:15498: tshur 'dus bdag sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar byas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:15499: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par sems pa'i dape'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15500: 'og ma mtsho la ser ba 'bab pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:15501: phar mi 'phro bar tshur la 'bab cing 'dug pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:15502: bsgrub pa chen po'i dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:15503: bzlas pa'i 'od zer phar mi 'phro bar /
NK077(tsu)001:15504: tshur sku gsung thugs kyi gnas nas dngos grub bdag
NK077(tsu)001:15505: gi sgo gsum la sib sib tshur 'du ba'i dape'o
NK077(tsu)001:15506: // de yang dper na ston mo gcig byed pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:15507: sngon du yo byad chang thams cad 'tshags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15508: de nas bud med gshim par rdzas yo byad bsogs 'khrud pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15511: chang tshur rgyang rgyang 'ong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15512: de nas mgron rnams la drang pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15513: tim tim 'thung bar byed pa de bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:15514: dang por bsnyen pas yo byad bsogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:15516: de nas nye bsnyen gyis bsgrub pa zhag grangs du byed kyi phyed du /
NK077(tsu)001:15517: cho ga gzhung bsrangs shing bzlas pa'i 'phro 'dus sgrib
NK077(tsu)001:15518: pa sbyang zhing dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar
NK077(tsu)001:15519: byed pa'o // de nas bsgrub pa'i dus su zhag du byed kyi phyed man chad du /
NK077(tsu)001:15521: bdag gi sgrib pa sbyong la /
NK077(tsu)001:15522: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol cig rgyud bskul /
NK077(tsu)001:15523: tshur 'dus pas dngos grub thob par bsam zhing zlos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15524: de nas nub tha ma bsgrub pa chen po'i dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:15525: bzlas pa'i 'od zer phar mi 'phro bar /
NK077(tsu)001:15526: tshur sib sib 'du bar bsam zhing si ti len pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15527: rtags byung na bar chad brtag cing dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15528: 'od mi brtan cing mi gsal ba bar chad kyi rtags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15529: 'od dwang zhing gsal ba brtan pa dngos grub kyi rtags /
NK077(tsu)001:15530: dri mi zhim pa gseb dri la sogs pa bar chad kyi rtags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15531: dri zhim zhing dwangs pa dngos grub kyi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15532: sgra mi bsnyan pa bar chad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15533: snyan pa dngos grub kyi ltas so //
NK077(tsu)001:15534: lha'i gzugs la sogs pa rnams 'gyur zhing mi brtan
NK077(tsu)001:15535: cing shes pa mtho dman che ba bdud kyi dang
NK077(tsu)001:15536: / gzugs brtan cing shes par ra nga bzhin gyi gnas pa dngos grub kyi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15537: 'od la sogs pa bsgrub pa po la 'khor ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:15538: phyag mtshan dang rdzas nam mkha' la 'khor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15540: me rta mgo tsam cher 'bar ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15541: sman rag la sogs khol zhing lud pa byung na
NK077(tsu)001:15542: de dag bdud kyis kyang byed pas bar chad yin
NK077(tsu)001:15543: nam lha'i grub rtags kyi cha rnams gang yin /
NK077(tsu)001:15544: thod pa tshar gsum gyis phyag rgya dang sngags dang rang nyams kyis brtag par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15545: bar chad yin na bskrad de bdag bsrung ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15546: bar chad yin na rdo rje drag pa'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang rdzas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15548: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid lhar gsal ba la go bgo lus bsrung byas la /
NK077(tsu)001:15549: de la dngos grub blang thabs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15550: zhag tshig dus kyi bsnyen pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15551: bzlas brjod grangs kyi bsnyen pa tshang zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:15552: mtshan ma rtags kyis bsnyen pa gong gi rtags rnams
NK077(tsu)001:15553: byung na brtag pas ye shes lha'i grub rtags yin
NK077(tsu)001:15554: nges na / dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15555: rtog pa'i gnas su lha bstim pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15556: tshom bu dkyil 'khor gang bsgrub kyang sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:15557: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum rtog pa'i gnas su mthun pa nyid du sbyar zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:15558: mngon shes dbang po lnga la /
NK077(tsu)001:15560: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa la bstim pa la sogs /
NK077(tsu)001:15561: rtog tshogs kyi gnas lha'i dngos grub bstim zhing ka ya ba ka tsi ta tish+tha badz+ra dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15562: sems can don phyir gyi dngos grub brtan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15564: rtags dang ldan na dngos grub blang ba des na dgos pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15565: sngon zhi ba tshogs bsgrub kyi skabs su bstan pa bzhin sku gsung thugs rnam pa gsum mam /
NK077(tsu)001:15566: yi ge 'khor lo ye shes bla ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15567: yo byad la spyad pa so so'i yon tan dang gsum thob par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:15568: sbyor sgrol gsang ba'i mchod pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15572: zhi ba'i skabs na khas blangs pa'i gsang ba sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:15573: grol gyi mchod pa rgyas par bshad par bya ba
NK077(tsu)001:15575: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15580: sgrol bas mi gos pa'i gtan tshigs /
NK077(tsu)001:15582: sbyor sgrol don la tha dad med par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15583: dang po grol ba'i dbye ba la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:15585: rang bzhin gyi ni sbyor sgrol dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15586: dbang po yul gyi sbyor sgrol dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15587: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor sgrol dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15588: thabs chen po'i sbyor sgrol dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15589: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor sgrol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:15591: rang bzhin gyi sbyor sgrol ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15592: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams rang bzhin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:15593: phra rags kyi chas thabs shes rab gnyis su med
NK077(tsu)001:15595: tha mal gyi rtog pa ngang gi grol ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15596: rang bzhin gyi sbyor sgrol te rtogs pa lta ba dang sbyor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:15597: dbang po yul dus kyi sbyor sgrol ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15598: phyag rgya gcig pa dang spros pa mthar phyin pa'i spyod pa'i dus te /
NK077(tsu)001:15599: dbang pos yul mthong zhing thos tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:15600: de nyid lha yab yum du sbyor bas dbang po yul gyi rtog pa kar dag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15601: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor sgrol ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15602: ting nge 'dzin la rig la lha yab yum du gsal bar sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15604: dngos po thams cad sbyang sems kyis chos nyid mthong bar bsam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15605: skabs kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod par yang 'agro'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15606: thabs chen po'i sbyor sgrol ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15608: dpal chen pos thugs rjes po'i sgo nas tshar bcad rjes bzung dang bcas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15609: gdug pa can pho mo rnams sbyor zhing bsgral bas mi gos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15610: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor sgrol ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15611: sbyor lam pas 'dod yon gyi mchod pa'i skabs su /
NK077(tsu)001:15612: dbang po'i mngon sum mi mo'i rigs kun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15613: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'i thabs la mkhas pas sbyor zhing sgrol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15614: mngon du byung ba'i sgrol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15616: de yang bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa ni gnyis yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:15617: bkra shis dag pa'i zhing dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15618: thugs rjes bzung ba'i zhing ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:15619: snga ma ni bram ze skye ba bdun pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:15620: de'i sha rus la sogs pa dngos grub kyi rdzas khyad par can yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:15624: zla ba nya'i nub mo grib ma bdun 'ong ba /
NK077(tsu)001:15625: mi tshe bdun rgyud du bar ma chad par mi lus blangs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15626: skye bdun yin na byad bdun shar //
NK077(tsu)001:15629: tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas pa dang gcig /rdzas gcig
NK077(tsu)001:15630: la brten pas mkha' 'gro ma dbang du 'dus shing
NK077(tsu)001:15631: dam tshig chag nyams bskang ba dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15632: sngags gcig bgrangs pas ye shes myur du 'grub cing /
NK077(tsu)001:15633: yi dam lha'i zhal mthong ba dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15635: phyi nang gsang gsum de kho na nyid dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:15637: dra ba ma yin nang rdzas ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15638: skye ba bdun pa'i sha yin /
NK077(tsu)001:15640: bya rgod kyi rkang la bud par yod par byas la /
NK077(tsu)001:15643: g.yon pas rkang gi bug na phar bltas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15644: chu'i nang du grib ma bdun du snang ba 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:15645: de'i sha zos na bdag nyid kyang skye ba bdun
NK077(tsu)001:15646: par gyur pa dang gcig /tshe 'di la thun mong
NK077(tsu)001:15647: gi dngos grub thob pa dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15648: tshe phyi ma la mchog gi dngos grub thob pa dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15649: da ki dbang du 'dus shing dam tshig gis nyams pa bskang ba dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15651: bdud rtsi dri chen gyi bcud len no //
NK077(tsu)001:15652: de kho na nyid kyi rdzas ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15653: chos nyid ngo bos grub pa rnams yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:15654: sngags gcig bgrang nas sangs rgyas pa las zab rgya lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15657: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK077(tsu)001:15658: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:15660: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK077(tsu)001:15661: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK077(tsu)001:15662: rnal 'byor kun gyi dang du blangs //
NK077(tsu)001:15663: zhes gsung pas bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15664: shin tu snying rje bas na phan gdags pa'i phyir du bsgral ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:15665: de yang mchog ni mi las gyur pa brgyad dang mchog phran ni ngan song gsum po rnams so //
NK077(tsu)001:15666: 'o na bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gcig yod dam snyam na /
NK077(tsu)001:15667: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15669: yang na mchog gi sgral bya gang yin pa la ngos 'dzin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:15671: shel chen rnams la bkug nas sgrol zhes bshad pa yang yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:15672: mdor na gang bsgral bar byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15673: bsgral bya bcu gcig po de rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:15674: bdag gzhan chos kyi don du bsgral bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15676: bar chad med pa'i lam pa des bsgral bar bya /
NK077(tsu)001:15677: dus nam gyi tshe bsgral na /
NK077(tsu)001:15678: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub kyi nub tha ma'i nam gung gi dus su bsgral bar bya /
NK077(tsu)001:15680: rdo rje slob dpon bsgral ba'i thabs la mkhas pa dang ldan pas bsgral bar bya ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:15681: de yang rang bzhin sgrol ba lta ba'i thabs la mkhas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15682: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgrol ba sgom pa'i thabs la mkhas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15683: dbang po yul dus kyi sgrol ba spyod pa'i thabs la mkhas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15684: thabs chen po'i sgrol ba bdag gi thabs la mkhas
NK077(tsu)001:15685: pa mngon du phyung ba'i sgrol ba mdzad spyod kyi
NK077(tsu)001:15686: thabs la mkhas pa lnga dang ldan pas bsgral bar
NK077(tsu)001:15687: bya ste / dal gyi lho phyogs su drag pa'i dal gru gsum bris la /
NK077(tsu)001:15688: e ram gyis drag po'i dal bskyed la /
NK077(tsu)001:15689: a dang ma las byung ba'i nyi zla'i gdan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:15690: steng du sgrol ba'i thabs la mkhas pa bdag nyid
NK077(tsu)001:15691: gong dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin la ma yengs
NK077(tsu)001:15692: par / sgrol bya de nyid sngags dang ting nge 'dzin nus pas dngos su bkug la /
NK077(tsu)001:15695: rkang pa byang shar du bstan du bstan te /
NK077(tsu)001:15696: 'khor ba ru bzlog pa'i tshul gan rkyal du bsgyel ba'i snying dkar rdo rjes mnan la gzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:15697: tshul ci ltar du bsgral na /
NK077(tsu)001:15698: nga rgyal rnam pa lnga dang ldan pa'i tshul gyis sgrol bar bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15699: de yang sgrol byed kyi bla ma dpal chen por
NK077(tsu)001:15700: nga rgyal bas kun brtags kyis rtog pa zil gyis
NK077(tsu)001:15702: sgrol ging ta ki ra tsar nga rgyal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:15704: gri 'jam dpal rnon por nga rgyal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:15705: ma rig pa'i rgya mo 'drel ba'i /
NK077(tsu)001:15706: king gi lag sor dpa' bo 'bru lngar nga rgyal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:15708: sgrol bya ru trar nga rgyal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:15709: dug gsum rtsad nas chod pa'i dgos ched dang ldan pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15710: de ltar nga rgyal dang ldan pa'i tshul gyi lag gi 'du byed kyi bsgral lo //
NK077(tsu)001:15711: sgrol ba'i ting nge 'dzin gang sgom na /
NK077(tsu)001:15712: gri 'jam dpal rnon po gsal ba des /
NK077(tsu)001:15713: bsgral bya'i khog pa shag gi gshag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15714: ma rig pa'i dbugs kyi rgya mo 'dral bar sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:15715: lag sor dpa' bo 'bru lngar gsal ba des /
NK077(tsu)001:15717: snying gi rtsa chen bzhi la gnas pa'i sa bon zung gsum gnyis dang bcas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15718: dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i 'phro 'du'i 'od zer gyis bsreg nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15719: bsgral bya'i shes pa yig 'bru h'u drug tu gyur
NK077(tsu)001:15720: pas 'khor bar skye ba'i sa bon drug bag chags
NK077(tsu)001:15721: dang bcas pa rnam par dag cing /
NK077(tsu)001:15723: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes su gcig pa las ma 'das pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:15725: h'u dkar po gcig tu gyur par sgom ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15727: bsgral bya'i khog pa bkral kho'i tsi ta dngos su phyung ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:15728: nang ltar thos bsam shes rab kyis gzung 'dzin gyi rgya bkral nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15729: bdag med rtog pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15730: bdag 'dzin drung nas phyung ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:15731: shes pa chos nyid du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15732: de nas h'u dkar po de /
NK077(tsu)001:15733: bdag nyid rdo rje rgyal po lhar gsal ba yab
NK077(tsu)001:15734: yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i shangs khung g.yon gyis rngub
NK077(tsu)001:15737: srog dag pa rdo rje'i lam nas phyungs /
NK077(tsu)001:15738: yum gyi mkha' la phab pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15739: gsang ba'i dbyings su thim par sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:15740: de ni shes pa yum gyi mkha' la bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15741: de nas yum gyi mkha'i gsung yig 'bru yongs su gyur pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:15742: thugs phyag rgya rdo rje 'od zer 'bar ba gcig tu gyur /
NK077(tsu)001:15743: rdo rje de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:15744: sku yongs su rdzogs pa rdo rje sems dpa'i sku phra mo gcig tu gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:15745: de yang nyon mongs pa lnga rnam par dag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15746: 'khor 'das gnyis su med par longs spyod pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:15747: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15748: 'od zer sna lnga 'phro bas rab tu brjid pa dang ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15749: rdo rje sems dpa'i spyi gtsug tu /
NK077(tsu)001:15750: 'khor ba las rnam par rgyal ba mtshon pa rigs
NK077(tsu)001:15751: kyi bdag po mi bskyod pa tshon gang ba zhig
NK077(tsu)001:15754: zhes rnam par snang mdzad sgom pa'ang bzhed do //
NK077(tsu)001:15755: de ni rdo rje sems dpa' mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa la bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15756: de ltar bsgral bya'i shes pa de nyid de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:15757: gshegs pa rdo rje sems dpa' byin gyis brlabs pa
NK077(tsu)001:15758: de yang as zla ba'i dal gyi steng bzhugs /
NK077(tsu)001:15759: yam las rlung gi dal gyis btegs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15760: a yam s+pha ra na phata /
NK077(tsu)001:15761: ces dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyis bzhugs gnas 'og min du 'phang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15762: 'og min gyi rgyal ba rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum sbyor mtshams su bstims te song nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15763: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dbang yang bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:15765: h'u badz+ra d+hig /mum da du shwa ri /
NK077(tsu)001:15767: rgyal ba'i rigs nges pa'i sras su gyur pa rdo rje sems yab yum gyi skur gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:15769: yab yum sku rags pa mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa gcig tu gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15770: gnas de nyid du bzhugs par sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:15771: de ni shes pa 'og min du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15772: de nas sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs rnams bsko btab
NK077(tsu)001:15773: nas dal gyi lha tshogs rnams la mchod pa phul
NK077(tsu)001:15775: de dag gi phung po dur khrod du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15776: thabs chen po'i sgrol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15778: de yang sngon byung du bsgral ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15779: sku gsung thugs shin tu 'khros pa'i khro bo dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis /
NK077(tsu)001:15780: thugs rje dang bsgral ba'i thabs kyis lha chen po ru tra 'khor bcas bsgral ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:15781: rjes 'jug gi rnal 'byor pa chos nyid lta ba'i don rtogs pa'i gding dang ldan cing /
NK077(tsu)001:15782: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor lam mthar phyin pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15785: rang gzhan gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i thabs kyis
NK077(tsu)001:15786: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyings su bsgral bar
NK077(tsu)001:15787: bya'o // dbang po yul dus kyi sgrol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15789: de yang gang gis bsgral na lam pa'i thugs rje chen po'i sgo nas dgongs pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15791: a n+ri sum tri pri du dza /
NK077(tsu)001:15792: zhes lam rgyud lnga'i sems can ma lus pa'i shes
NK077(tsu)001:15793: pa kun bkug nas bsgral bya de la bstim ste
NK077(tsu)001:15795: sems can kun kyang bdag 'dzin can yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:15796: de gnyis su med pa'i ngang la bsgral te rtsad
NK077(tsu)001:15797: bcad pas na thams cad ma lus bsgral bar bya
NK077(tsu)001:15798: ba'o // rang bzhin gyi sgrol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15801: nang bcud kyi 'jig rten ci snyed pa na gnas
NK077(tsu)001:15802: pa'i 'gro ba drug gis sems can phra rags ma
NK077(tsu)001:15803: lus pa kun gyi rang bzhin sems nyid gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:15804: med pa'i ye shes kyi bdag nyid chen por lta
NK077(tsu)001:15805: ba rtogs pa sbyor lam gyi rnal 'byor pa yis
NK077(tsu)001:15806: / rtogs pa thams cad chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyis dbyings su yang ni rtogs pas bsgral la /
NK077(tsu)001:15807: gnyis 'dzin gyi rtogs pa mi dmigs par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15811: phyi ltar na dbus kyi ri rab chen po'i phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:15812: bzhi gling bzhi gling phran brgyad la gnas pa'i sems
NK077(tsu)001:15813: can bsgral bya ma lus pa kun bsgral ba'i mkhan
NK077(tsu)001:15814: po thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa'i sbyor lam
NK077(tsu)001:15815: gyi rnal 'byor pa lta ba rtogs shing sgom pa
NK077(tsu)001:15816: ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i byin rlabs kyis bsgral
NK077(tsu)001:15817: ba'i thabs ni / rang rig pa nyid ram du gyur pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:15818: ye shes kyi me chen po 'bar ba'i ting nge 'dzin sgom par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15819: ye shes kyis me des ri rab gling bzhi la
NK077(tsu)001:15820: sogs la gnas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi rgyud
NK077(tsu)001:15821: la yod pa'i rnam par rtogs pa'i mtshan ma dang
NK077(tsu)001:15822: bag chags ma lus pa bsreg par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15823: de rnams chos nyid skye ba med pa'i dbyings su
NK077(tsu)001:15824: yang ni rang grol du bstim pa ste rtogs par
NK077(tsu)001:15825: bya / de ltar rtog pa de dag /phyi ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:15828: nang ltar lus ngag yid gsum gyi mtshan ma thams cad bsreg pa'i me yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:15829: de yang me rang rgyud pas srid gsum dngos su bsreg pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:15830: rnal 'byor pa'i yid kyi rnam par shes pa lta sgom las su rung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:15831: ye shes kyi me ru 'bar te bsreg pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:15832: ye shes kyis me bskyed pa'i sa bon ni ram yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:15833: sgrol bas mi gos pa'i gtan tshigs la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:15835: bden pa gnyis kyi tshul du rtogs pas sbyor sgrol gyis mi gos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15837: de lta bu'i sbyor sgrol ba'i thabs khyad par can ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15838: bdag la sgrib pa mi sogs gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyed pas ngo mtshar zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:15839: las ngan spyad pas gnas ngan par 'gro ba'i rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:15840: bstan pa'i spyi dgra la sogs pa bdun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15841: ngan song gsum du song ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15842: zhing bcu po thams cad kyang thar par byed pa'i thabs khyad par can /
NK077(tsu)001:15843: 'di las lhag pa gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:15844: de yang sgrol ba 'di dag logs 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:15845: nyon mongs pas kun nas bslangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15846: sems can gyi srog gcod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15847: byed du bcug na skyon du 'gyur bas 'bras bu sdug bsngal 'byung mod kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:15849: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba ye nas skye ba med pa don dam bden pa de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:15850: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta bas de bzhin nyid kho nar rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:15851: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid kyi nyams su blangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:15852: kun rdzob sgyu mar snang ba 'di yang /
NK077(tsu)001:15853: dpe tho yor la mir 'dzin pa de nyid ngo shes pas grol ba bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:15854: snang ba thams cad mig g.yor gyi tshul du shes nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15855: dngos grub rnam gnyis bsgrub pa'i don du /
NK077(tsu)001:15856: sbyor ba dang sgrol ba'i bya ba kun byas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:15857: tha mal pa'i sbyor sgrol rdul phran gyi cha tsam yang rang rgyud du byas pa med pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:15858: sbyor sgrol gyi nyes pas mi gos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15859: phung po la rnam par dbye ba'i gtan tshigs bsgral bas mi gos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15861: tshul de ltar rtogs na kun rdzob tu zhing bcu
NK077(tsu)001:15862: la sogs sgrol ba'i bya ba kun nam yang na
