NK077(tsu)001:15863: sgrol ba'i thabs lnga po kun gang byas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:15864: don dam par sgrol ba'i dngos po rang rgyud pa gang yang med do //
NK077(tsu)001:15865: de la rnam par dbye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15866: de yang gong gis bsgral ba'i dngos po gang yang med pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:15868: log rtog gi ngo la snang ba'i phung po lnga
NK077(tsu)001:15869: nyid rigs pas brtag na rang bzhin med par bshig
NK077(tsu)001:15870: par bya / bye brag tu gzugs phung bshig na
NK077(tsu)001:15871: yang 'byung ba lnga'i bag la zha ste 'byung ba
NK077(tsu)001:15873: ma bshig na yang 'byung ba 'dus pa'i phung po
NK077(tsu)001:15874: yin te rang sar dag /rnam shes la dmigs su
NK077(tsu)001:15875: med pas sgrol bas mi gos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15877: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad rang rgyud par
NK077(tsu)001:15878: gzugs su grub pa med par shes pas bsad par
NK077(tsu)001:15879: byas na / dper na rmi lam du srog bcad
NK077(tsu)001:15880: par snang yang don la ma grub pas nyes pa
NK077(tsu)001:15881: med pa'i tshul ci bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:15882: 'khrul ngor srog gcod bya gcod byed du gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:15883: nyid na yang dag pa'i don la dngos po rang
NK077(tsu)001:15884: rgyud par grub pa med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15885: sems kyi rang bzhin la bsgral du med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15887: 'o na sems nyid bsgral lam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:15888: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems kyi rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba de la ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15889: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad dgrar langs kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:15890: gnyis snang rang rgyud du grub pa med pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:15891: sangs rgyas la sogs pa sus kyang zin cing sod pa med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15894: 'o na dngos su bsgral rgyur du grub pa med
NK077(tsu)001:15895: na rnal 'byor pa'i thugs rjes gang bsgral ba yin
NK077(tsu)001:15896: zhe na / gdul bya'i bdag 'dzin la sogs par rtog pa'i mtshan mar zhen pa thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:15897: 'khrul pa'i log rtog phyin ci log tu zhen cing
NK077(tsu)001:15898: 'dzin pa las bzlog par bya ste sgrol ba'i dgongs
NK077(tsu)001:15899: pa ting nge 'dzin dang sngags dang phyag rgya dang
NK077(tsu)001:15900: gsum las blo shin tu gom shing gding du gyur
NK077(tsu)001:15901: pas bsgral bya'i shes pa la dbang bskur te /
NK077(tsu)001:15902: mthar thug gi 'bras bu byang chub kyi zhing la dgod par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:15904: de ltar log rtog rgyun bcad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:15905: byang chub kyi sa la dgod pa de tsam la ni 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i don gyi na /
NK077(tsu)001:15906: bsgral ba zhes bya ba tha snyad du gdags so //
NK077(tsu)001:15907: sbyor sgrol don la tha dad med pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK077(tsu)001:15909: de yang gnyis 'dzin gyi rtogs pa de sgrol ba'i dus nyid na /
NK077(tsu)001:15910: gnyis med chos nyid du sbyor ba yin te de yang ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:15911: bsgral bya'i rgyu nyon mongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15912: 'bras bu sdug bsngal ma lus pa kun rtsad bcad
NK077(tsu)001:15913: nas 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi
NK077(tsu)001:15915: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi sangs rgyas dang sems
NK077(tsu)001:15916: can gnyis su med pa'i dbyings su bsgral bya sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:15917: ba'ang yin no // g+ha na sbyor ba la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:15919: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor ba la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:15920: sbyor ba'i mchod pa dngos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15921: de'i yon tan dang sbyor sgrol don la tha dad med par bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15926: de la gang la sbyor ba'i yum 'di la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:15927: lo grangs kyi sgo nas dbye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15928: byang sems kyi sgo nas dbye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15929: rtsa'i sgo nas dbye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15930: sbyor thabs kyi sgo nas dbye ba bzhis ston pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:15932: lo bcu gnyis ma mtshan dang ldan pa lha mo
NK077(tsu)001:15933: ste rab bcu drug ma mtshan dang ldan pa klu
NK077(tsu)001:15934: mo ste 'bring / nyi shu ma mtshan dang ldan pa rigs ngan mo ste tha ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15935: gnyis pa rtsa'i sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15936: rtsa 'dud can ma yod pa lha mo /
NK077(tsu)001:15938: zhar ma can rigs ngan mo /
NK077(tsu)001:15939: gsum pa byang sems kyi sgo nas dbye na ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15940: nyi zla gnyis kar 'dzags pa lha mo /
NK077(tsu)001:15942: gnyis gar mi 'dzag pa ni rigs ngan mo /
NK077(tsu)001:15943: bzhi pa sbyor thabs kyi sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15944: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i bde ba sbyor thabs shes pa ni lha mo /
NK077(tsu)001:15946: bdag bde ba tsam rigs ngan mo'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15947: yang na lha mo ni lha mo dngos /
NK077(tsu)001:15948: klu mo ni klu mo dngos te /
NK077(tsu)001:15949: de dag sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dngos su dgug pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:15951: rigs ngan mo ste mi'i bu mo yang rung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:15952: slob dpon nus pa chung ba ste dgongs pa mi gsal na /
NK077(tsu)001:15953: phyag rgya'i mtshan bzang ngan brtag nas bzang rigs brten cing /
NK077(tsu)001:15955: yang na slob dpon nus pa che zhing dgongs pa gsal na /
NK077(tsu)001:15956: bzang ngan mi dbye bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15957: de lta bu'i yum de la sbyor ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:15958: yum mtshan nyid dang ldan pa de la khrus gsum bya /
NK077(tsu)001:15961: sta gon du gnas pa ni bsnyen pa'i yan lag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:15965: 'dod pa'i stobs rtsal drug cu rtsa bzhis bde ba rgyas par byed pa ni nye ba'i bsnyen pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15966: phyag rgya bzhis rol pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:15968: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces len pa ni bsgrub pa chen po ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15969: nub tha ma la mthong lam gyi ye shes chen po rgyud la skye bar byed pa /
NK077(tsu)001:15970: dngos grub chen po yum gyi mkha' las blangs pa'i dbang du'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15971: rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:15974: drang shes rab sam dbyings kyi cha 'dzin pas yum
NK077(tsu)001:15975: gzungs ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa phyi nang gsang
NK077(tsu)001:15977: rgyan gsum brtags pa la sogs pas chas su bcug la //
NK077(tsu)001:15980: de nas yum gyi lus la bde bar gshegs pa
NK077(tsu)001:15981: yum lnga'i dal la sogs pa kun bkod de phung
NK077(tsu)001:15982: po khams dang skye mched kyis rtog tshogs rnams byin
NK077(tsu)001:15983: rlabs pa'am yum gyi mkha' gzhal yas khang du bskyed
NK077(tsu)001:15984: pa de bla ma bde gshegs lha'i dal tshom bu
NK077(tsu)001:15985: rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang rung kun bkod la /
NK077(tsu)001:15986: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyi rig pa rdo rje sems dpa' lta bu'i lha sgom ste /
NK077(tsu)001:15989: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par rol zhing bde ba'i thabs dang ldan par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:15992: yab kyi rdo rje yum gyi dril bu pad+ma gnyis su med par ldan byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:15994: bde ba thugs kyi dal yab kyi byang sems spro
NK077(tsu)001:15995: dga' ba bcu drug g.yo ldang la sogs pa sems
NK077(tsu)001:15996: lnga'i rim pa thabs kyi zin pa yis //
NK077(tsu)001:15999: rgyal ba'i dal mnyes shing sems can bde ba'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16001: byang chub sems 'phros pa'i mchod pas sangs rgyas dal ma lus la /
NK077(tsu)001:16002: bde bas dgyes shing dgongs pa mnyam nyid mchog gi
NK077(tsu)001:16003: sbyin pas ris pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i dal gyi
NK077(tsu)001:16004: sku gsung thugs gsum mnyes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16005: 'gro ba mang po la sbyin pa tshims shing bde ba thob nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16006: slar yang tshur bsdus te bzlog pas gnyis su med par dbyings su thim //
NK077(tsu)001:16007: rgyal ba'i sku ru gsal zhing tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16009: de ltar thims par gyur nas yum gyi dbyings nas lha'i sku phyag rgya 'bar /
NK077(tsu)001:16010: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa thabs dang shes rab rdzogs /
NK077(tsu)001:16011: phyag rgya'i dal rigs lnga kun tu bzang drug dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16012: shes bya'i gnas lugs yang dag par rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16013: ma 'gags pa bde ba bsod rnams kyi tshogs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16014: ma dmigs pa ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16015: dngos grub blang zhing thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub pa'i yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16017: bde ba'i ye shes chen po bsgrub pa'i thabs yab
NK077(tsu)001:16018: yum gnyis su med pa rol pa las byung ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:16019: thig le nyi zla gnyis 'dres pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:16020: yon tan thabs kyis bcud 'dus pa'i snying po de /
NK077(tsu)001:16021: dal thams cad kyis bdag nyid ye shes lhar gsal bar byed pa'i rten yin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:16024: bar chad med pa'i lam pas dus nam gyi tshe na /
NK077(tsu)001:16025: tshogs bsgrub kyi nub tha ma'i tho ras kyi dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:16030: gsang ba'i rdo rje nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:16032: lce rdo rje rtse lnga par sgom de yis so //
NK077(tsu)001:16033: tshul ci ltar na bung bas me tog 'jig pa'i tshul gyis blangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:16034: dgos ched ci'i phyir blang na /
NK077(tsu)001:16035: dngos grub gnyis bde blag tu thob pa'i phyir du'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16037: thun mong gi dngos grub nam mkha' la bya bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:16038: du 'gro zhing lha'i bu mo la spyod pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:16041: tshe lo grangs med pa thub pa la sogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16042: sogs khung nas yal byi ba bzhin du 'dzul nas
NK077(tsu)001:16043: klu'i bu mo la spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16044: gzhan yang mngon par shes pa drug dang rdzu 'phrul du ma thob bo //
NK077(tsu)001:16045: mchog gi dngos grub ni yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:16046: dgos 'dod char bzhin du 'byung bas na srin gyi tshogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:16047: dpe de dang 'dra ba'i rigs thams cad kyi bdag
NK077(tsu)001:16048: po rgyal ba drug pa yang thob par 'gyur ro
NK077(tsu)001:16049: // yang na snga ma gsang ba'i rdo rjes blangs
NK077(tsu)001:16050: pas yon tan ni yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag po
NK077(tsu)001:16051: mchog gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur la /
NK077(tsu)001:16052: phyi ma lce rdo rje rtse lnga par sgom nas blangs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16053: mkha' 'gro gsal 'bar tshe la sogs pa thun mong gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16054: ngan 'gro las grol zhing sangs rgyas 'grub pa'i yon tan no //
NK077(tsu)001:16056: 'gro drug gi dus dang gnas na yang tha mal
NK077(tsu)001:16057: pa'i bde ba la sbyor ba'i ye shes yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:16058: de dag snang zhing yod pa yin yang /
NK077(tsu)001:16059: ngo ma shes pas thabs kyis ma zin pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16060: sbyor ba'i mchod pa byas pas mtshon cing ngo shes
NK077(tsu)001:16061: par byed pa'i thabs kyi zin nas gsang ba byang
NK077(tsu)001:16062: sems kyi mchod pa chen po'i bde ba yab yum
NK077(tsu)001:16063: mnyam sbyor zhing / rtog pa thams cad bde stong gnyis med kyi dbyings su sbyor bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:16064: de'i yon tan ngan 'gro gsum por mi ltung zhing
NK077(tsu)001:16065: yang dag pa'i 'bras bu mthong lam nas sangs rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:16067: sbyor sgrol don la tha dad med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16069: sbyor ba'i sgo nas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16070: ye shes kyi chos nyid kyi don rtogs pa 'di
NK077(tsu)001:16071: ni / gnyis 'dzin gyi rtogs pa rang ka ma
NK077(tsu)001:16072: rnams sgrol ba chen po'am ngan song las sgrol ba
NK077(tsu)001:16073: ni / yang yin la / rtog pa sgrol ba
NK077(tsu)001:16074: nyid na chos nyid du'am byang chub la sbyor ba
NK077(tsu)001:16075: ni / yang yin la / yang yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16076: de ltar sbyor ba'i dus nyid nas rtog pa rang
NK077(tsu)001:16077: kha ma lus sgrol ba'i phyir sbyor sgrol gnyis don
NK077(tsu)001:16079: rang bzhin gyi sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16081: gzhi ye gdod ma nas rtog pa rags pa thams
NK077(tsu)001:16082: cad lha yab dang phra ba thams cad yum lha
NK077(tsu)001:16083: mo'i dal du gsal bar gnas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16084: yang dag pa'i sa la sbyor ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:16085: dbang po yul dus kyis sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16087: dbang po rnam shes brgyad nang nas 'jug pa ni lha sems dpa' yab brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:16088: yul dus brgyad phyi nang 'jug pa ni lha sems ma brgyad du gsal ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16089: de gnyis 'phrad pa ni lha yab yum gnyis med
NK077(tsu)001:16090: du sbyor ba te dbang po yul dus kyi sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:16091: ba'o // de'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:16092: gzugs la sogs pa'i phung po lnga po nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:16093: rigs lnga'i de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16094: sa sogs 'byung ba lnga nyid rigs kyi yum lnga nyid du sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16095: dbang po bzhi dang rnam shes bzhi sems ma brgyad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16096: yul bzhi dang dus bzhi lha mo sems ma brgyad nyid du sbyor /
NK077(tsu)001:16097: bdag rtog rnam bzhi khro bo bzhi dang rtag chad
NK077(tsu)001:16098: mu bzhi khro mo bzhi yid chos gnyis kun bzang
NK077(tsu)001:16099: yab yum nyon mongs pa drug thub pa drug /de
NK077(tsu)001:16100: las gzhan pa khro bo'i dal du yang sbyor //
NK077(tsu)001:16101: ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16103: rtog tshogs thams cad ma lus par 'byung ba kun /
NK077(tsu)001:16104: chos nyid mnyam pa'i dbyings dang de rtogs pa rang
NK077(tsu)001:16105: rig pa'i ye shes su lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:16107: thabs chen po'i sbyor ba phan yon 'jug bsdus bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16109: sngon byung du dpal chen pos ma chags thams kyis sbyor bas srin mo skem ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16110: dbang mo rnams la rol kyang rang la nyes pas
NK077(tsu)001:16111: ma gos pa ltar rjes 'jug rnal 'byor pa yab
NK077(tsu)001:16112: yum gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i dus nyid na
NK077(tsu)001:16113: sbyor thabs la mkhas pas dga' bde'i ro la chags
NK077(tsu)001:16114: pa dang ka ma na pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16115: dngos po thams cad sems nyid du rang snang bas yul sems gnyis med du gsal ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16116: ma chags pa'i ye shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:16117: de la pho mo gnyis su zhen cing chags pa ni log pa'i chos so //
NK077(tsu)001:16118: de ltar 'dod chags rang kha ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16120: de dag sems nyid du shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16121: 'du shes gsum ldan gyi sgom pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16122: thabs kyis zin pa'i spyod pa dang gsum ldan gyis sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16123: chags pa ma 'gag par spyod pa'i 'du nyid na /
NK077(tsu)001:16124: chags pa'i ro nyid ye shes su gsal bas sems nyid mi rtog pa'i ngang du chags shing /
NK077(tsu)001:16125: chags pa tha mal pa'i nyes skyon gyi dri mas gos pa med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16126: de ltar chags pa'i nyes skyon gyis ma gos pa
NK077(tsu)001:16127: 'di ni tshangs par spyod pa'i chog /bde ba'i ye
NK077(tsu)001:16128: shes la dbang bsgyur bas rgyal po yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:16129: de ni shin tu yang dag pa'i chags pa chen po spang gnyen ro gcig tu gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16130: de pa'i dgongs pa ngo bo nyid yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16131: rang kar spyod pa'i skyon no //
NK077(tsu)001:16133: de ltar gsang ba'i mchod pa sbyor sgrol gnyis po'i don /
NK077(tsu)001:16134: chos nyid don gyi lta ba ma rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:16135: kha 'byams tshig gis lta ba ste sgra'i rjes su 'brangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16136: sbyor sgrol gnyis rang kha mar spyod par gyur na /
NK077(tsu)001:16138: sbyor ba'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu yid btags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16139: ro myag gi 'dam gyi dmyal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16140: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu mngal gyi srin bur skye bar bshad cing /
NK077(tsu)001:16141: sgrol ba'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu yang sos kyi dmyal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16142: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu srin po'i gnas su skye bar bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:16143: sbyor sgrol rang kha ma de la log pa'i lam du 'gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16144: rgyu mtshan des na gsang sngags kyi lam nyams su
NK077(tsu)001:16145: len pa'i rnal 'byor pa gang zhig /sems nyon mongs
NK077(tsu)001:16147: 'dod chags tha mal du spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16148: sems can gyi srog la 'tshe ba byas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16149: byed du bcug na nyes skyon chen po 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16150: de dag brtson 'grus chen pos spong la /
NK077(tsu)001:16151: yang dag pa'i lta sgom spyod gsum dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16152: mchog tu gyur pa'am gsang spyod thun mong ma yin pa'i sbyor sgrol gnyis la /
NK077(tsu)001:16153: bdag gzhan chos gsum gyi don du longs spyod par gyis shig /ces gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16154: yo byad la spyad thabs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:16156: spyad thabs kun zhi ba dang mthun par spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16158: mchod pa 'bul ba'i spyod lam rnam bzhi la sogs pa thams cad du /
NK077(tsu)001:16159: zhi ba dang mthun pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:16160: khyad par du dur khrod chas brgyad kyi rgyan rnams bgo zhing gdag par bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16161: chas brgyad ni dmar chen bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16162: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad kyang zhi ba'i tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:16163: bsgrub kyis rjes su mthun par mtshan med kyi ting
NK077(tsu)001:16164: nge 'dzin dang ldan par longs spyod cing rkang pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16165: bro dang / lag pa'i gar ngag gi glu tshig
NK077(tsu)001:16166: rnams kyang mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal ba
NK077(tsu)001:16168: bro gar gyis spyod thabs rgyas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16169: spyod thabs spyir bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16170: spyad thabs so so'i yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16173: bro gar gyi lta ba'i ngang la mi 'da' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16175: dbang po dang rnam shes yul dus dang rig pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:16176: thabs yab dang shes rab yum gnyis su med par ldan gyur zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:16177: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang nyid lta ba rtogs shing
NK077(tsu)001:16178: ting nge 'dzin gsal na 'khor 'das snod bcud thams
NK077(tsu)001:16179: cad dgongs pa bde ba ye shes mchog gi phyag
NK077(tsu)001:16180: rgya dal ro // spyir spyad thabs yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16182: yan lag lnga bskyod chen lus 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su /
NK077(tsu)001:16183: lha rigs kyi khro bo khro mo thams cad kun /
NK077(tsu)001:16184: ting nge 'dzin sku gsung thugs gsal zhing 'od zer
NK077(tsu)001:16185: 'phro bar sgom na lus kyi bskul yan lag bskyod
NK077(tsu)001:16186: pa thams cad lha'i phyag rgya yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16187: spyad thabs so so'i yon tan dang bcas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16188: yan lag so sor bskyod pa'i yon tan nam /
NK077(tsu)001:16189: yan lag kun spyod thabs yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16192: gom pa spyod thabs yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16194: thabs g.yas dang shes rab g.yon ldan pa'i zhabs /
NK077(tsu)001:16195: dus rtag tu zhabs la rdo rje rtse lnga 'od
NK077(tsu)001:16196: 'bar bar 'gyur bar sgom thabs chen po goms pa
NK077(tsu)001:16197: re re sa la bskyod cing dor bar byas na
NK077(tsu)001:16198: / don chags pa med pa'i rtags su rkang rjes la me tog pad+ma re re 'byung bar sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:16200: sa gzhi'i pad+ma de gnyis ting nge 'dzin gsal bar 'byor na /
NK077(tsu)001:16201: de'i bar du song ba'i sems can bla na med
NK077(tsu)001:16202: pa'i byang chub kyi zhing du skye bar 'gyur ro
NK077(tsu)001:16205: rang bzhin gyi dal dang zhi ba'i lha rnams kyang
NK077(tsu)001:16206: zhi ba las 'dir khro bo'i dal du bsgyur te
NK077(tsu)001:16208: de yang dbu'i dal la b+hud+d+ha he ru ka la
NK077(tsu)001:16209: de bzhin rigs kyi khro bos bskor ba yab yum
NK077(tsu)001:16210: sgom ste bsgul bskyod na phyogs dus kyi sangs rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:16211: dal thams cad thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don la g.yos
NK077(tsu)001:16212: nus pa'o // rkang pa'i stobs bya thabs yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16213: lag pa spyod pa'i thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16215: lag gi 'du byed de phyag g.yas badz+ra he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16216: g.yon rat+na he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa sgom ste bskyod byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16217: rig 'dzin gyi zhing khams thams cad ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:16218: gyi nus pa skye nas rang don la sa 'og
NK077(tsu)001:16220: gzhan don du thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don la g.yo bar nus so //
NK077(tsu)001:16222: rkang pa'i g.yas karma he ru kar /
NK077(tsu)001:16223: g.yon pad+ma he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa sgom ste stabs chen mnan cing mchong na /
NK077(tsu)001:16224: g.yon gyi 'gro drug gi sems can gyi sdug bsngal mi bzad thams cad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16225: g.yas kyi bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang log 'dren thams cad mnan nus so //
NK077(tsu)001:16226: de ltar dbu dang phyag zhabs bskyod pa'i yon tan gyi rim pa de dag ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16227: sangs rgyas rigs lnga lus kyi mgo dang phyag zhabs
NK077(tsu)001:16228: rnams la mthu che chung gi khyad par yod pa
NK077(tsu)001:16230: lus kyi gnas rim nas smos pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:16231: de yang chos can yan lag mtho dman gyi cha nas bzhag pa yin gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:16232: chos nyid rig par rang byung gi ye shes la bzang ngan med do //
NK077(tsu)001:16233: yan lag kun bskyod thabs yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16235: spyir lus dang yan lag thams cad dus gcig la bsgul zhing bsigs na /
NK077(tsu)001:16236: bdag gi ba spu'i bu ga re re nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16237: khro bo'i sprul pa rdul snyed grangs med pa spro /
NK077(tsu)001:16238: khro bo de'i sprul pa grangs med pa rnams kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:16239: don bya ba'i gnas phyogs bcu'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams na /
NK077(tsu)001:16240: dag ma dag bar ma rnams rdul phra rab kyi grangs de snyed du /
NK077(tsu)001:16241: khro bo'i gdul bya'i don mdzad pa rnams kyang rdul
NK077(tsu)001:16242: phran gyi grangs de snyed rnams nas don byed tshul
NK077(tsu)001:16243: / de dag gi thugs rjes gdul bya rnams 'dul zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:16244: slar rang gi ba spu'i bu ga'i chos kyi dbyings su bstim mo //
NK077(tsu)001:16245: spyad thabs kun zhi ba las khro bor gyur te spyad thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16247: khro bo la khyu mchog dang ma he la sogs pa'i bro stabs sam /
NK077(tsu)001:16251: ngag gi glu tshig dang khro bo'i mig gis lta
NK077(tsu)001:16252: stangs dang sems kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi yo byad
NK077(tsu)001:16253: lnga la spyod pa'i thabs la sogs pa kun sngar
NK077(tsu)001:16254: gyi zhi ba tshogs bsgrub kyi dkyil 'khor skabs su
NK077(tsu)001:16255: bstan pa las / bro gar rtse 'jo la sogs khro bor bsgyur la bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16256: skabs dang mjug gi las bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16259: de nas dpal chen po'i 'khor gyis phra man dbang
NK077(tsu)001:16260: mo rnams lhag ma phud kyis mchod pas tshig par
NK077(tsu)001:16261: bya ste / rta mgrin gyis phyag rgyas dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16263: las la bka' bsgo ba la sogs pa rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:16264: las gzhung ltar rgyas par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16265: las la bkye la brten ma bskyang dal bsdu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16266: spyod lam bzhir lha'i ting nge 'dzin dang mi 'bral bar spyad /
NK077(tsu)001:16267: tshul bzhin bsgrub pas 'bras bu mthong lam rig 'dzin 'grub pa la the tshom med do //
NK077(tsu)001:16269: tshogs bsgrub pa'i rtags kyi 'bras bu la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:16273: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes rab yum thams cad kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16274: gong gi ting nge 'dzin gyi tshul de lta bu
NK077(tsu)001:16275: dang ldan pa'i yo byad lnga la longs spyod na
NK077(tsu)001:16276: / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams rnal 'byor pa'i rig par tha dad med pa'i phyir ram /
NK077(tsu)001:16277: mchod pa'i longs spyod gnas su stobs pas na sangs
NK077(tsu)001:16278: rgyas kyi dal ma lus pa rnams kyang mnyes par
NK077(tsu)001:16279: mchod pa yin la srid pa khams gsum gyi 'gro
NK077(tsu)001:16280: ba sems can thams cad la 'dod yon gyi 'od
NK077(tsu)001:16281: zer spros pas bde ba'i ro'i dga' ba chen pos
NK077(tsu)001:16283: de yang rang bzhin gcig pa la dgongs pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16286: lam grub pa'i drod rtags kyi cha rnams kyang sngon spros pa'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin 'byung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:16287: 'on kyang khyad med pa ni ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:16289: drod rtags de rnams grangs du 'phel la ngo bo gsal zhing yun ring du brtan par 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16290: mngon shes ni tha ma gling grangs gcig gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16292: rab kyi gling bzhi tshun chad la sogs pa'i grangs 'phel ba mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16293: mngon shes drug kyang 'phel la brten par 'byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:16295: rna bar sgra snyan du thos pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:16296: gnyid kyi rmi lam dag tu yang /
NK077(tsu)001:16297: bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:16298: pa sangs rgyas kyis gzhal yas khang gnas kyi zhing
NK077(tsu)001:16299: khams rnams su skye bar lung ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16300: lha mi la sogs pa'i skye ba rnam dag gang
NK077(tsu)001:16301: yang rung ba dag 'dzin pa lung ston pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:16302: / rig 'dzin du lung ston pa la sogs 'byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:16303: de rnams yang dag pa'i rtags ma nor ba yin nam /
NK077(tsu)001:16304: bdud kyi bar chad yin brtag par bya ba shin tu gal che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16307: lhag bcas tshe dbang thob tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16308: lhag med rnam smin thob tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16310: bsgrub pa mthar phyin pas tshe 'di la tshe dbang thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16311: mthar ma phyin kyang phyi ma thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16312: lan grangs gzhan la tshe dbang thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16315: tshe dbang thob nas sangs rgyas tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16317: tshe dbang thob pa dngos ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16318: zhag grangs sum cu pa phrag drug gam /
NK077(tsu)001:16321: bcu drug tshun chad kyis tshogs bsgrub pa'i dus kyis
NK077(tsu)001:16322: 'byung ba'i lus 'di nyid ma spangs par skye 'jigs
NK077(tsu)001:16323: med pa rdo rje'i skur gyur te tshe la dbang
NK077(tsu)001:16324: ba'i rig 'dzin gyis sa non par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16326: de lta bu'i tshe dbang des rang don du lo
NK077(tsu)001:16327: stong phrag brgya la sogs pa yun ring por zag
NK077(tsu)001:16328: med mthong lam pa'i chos kyi bde ba la longs
NK077(tsu)001:16329: spyod na / lam thar chags sam /
NK077(tsu)001:16330: thod rgal gang rung gi sgo nas bla na med
NK077(tsu)001:16331: pa rdo rje sems dpa' yi mtshan yongs su rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:16332: pa'i sangs rgyas sa thob ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16334: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i dpe byad
NK077(tsu)001:16335: brgyad cu dang mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:16337: zag pa med pa'i mngon par shes pa drug dang ldan la shes bya ci lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16338: ci snyed pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mnga' ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16339: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen po gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:16340: kyang mngon du rdzogs par rol pa'i bde ba de
NK077(tsu)001:16341: nyid / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis
NK077(tsu)001:16342: longs sku'i zhing khams kyi gdul bya la rang dbang
NK077(tsu)001:16343: nyid / bsgyur te / spyod yul ma lus pa
NK077(tsu)001:16344: kun tu sku dang ye shes kyi ma da la
NK077(tsu)001:16345: te dal gsal ba yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK077(tsu)001:16346: gyi sa non pa yin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:16347: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang bas ci ltar dmigs shing dgongs bzhin du lhun gyis 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16348: de'ang las dang sa la rag lus pa med pa tshe gcig sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16350: gong gi de bas na sngags kyi las dang 'bras bu dus la rag lus pa med de /
NK077(tsu)001:16351: re dogs dor bar byas nas don dang ldan pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16352: brtson 'grus chen po'i zag pa med pa'i don la
NK077(tsu)001:16353: sbyar ro // mthong ba'i tshe 'di la mya ngan 'das te sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16354: phyi ma la tshe dbang thob pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16356: mjug bsdus te the tshom med par thob tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16359: phyi ma la lha mi khyad par can thob cing theg mchog mi brjed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16361: sangs rgyas mi bzhugs pa'i zhing du mi skye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16362: gal te tshe 'di la mthong lam ma thob nas
NK077(tsu)001:16363: lhag bcas lhag med kyi mya ngan las ma 'das
NK077(tsu)001:16364: na / ci ltar 'byung na tshogs lam rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:16365: bzhi las su rung ba'i lam pa rnams kyis sbyor
NK077(tsu)001:16366: lam tshogs bsgrub pa 'di lta bu'i las la 'bad
NK077(tsu)001:16368: blo dang brtson 'grus zhan pas 'bras bu mthong lam tshe 'di la mngon sum du ma gyur kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:16369: bar der bag chags kyi lus blang nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16370: lus ngag yid gsum la rang dbang thob ste rang
NK077(tsu)001:16371: ngo shes pas skye gnas khyad par can du skyes
NK077(tsu)001:16372: nas / sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku 'jig rten du
NK077(tsu)001:16373: 'byung ba dang skal ba mnyam ste dus dang gnas
NK077(tsu)001:16374: kyi ma bskol bar ci nas kyang mjal bar 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:16375: nas / ro // theg pa dman par mi skye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16376: sngar gsang sngags la sbyang zhing tshogs bsgrub pa'i las 'phro dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16377: thugs rje dang smon lam gyi 'brel pa'am byin rlabs
NK077(tsu)001:16378: kyis gsang sngags 'di nyid dang 'phrad de theg pa
NK077(tsu)001:16379: dman par nyan rang la sogs pa'i sgor 'jug la
NK077(tsu)001:16381: ngan song du mi skye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16382: yo byad lnga la spyod pa'i bsod nams dang thams
NK077(tsu)001:16383: cad sems nyid du shes pas ye shes kyi tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:16384: chen gnyis dang ldan pa'i dpung tshogs kyis skye ba
NK077(tsu)001:16385: snga ma phan chad kyi rgyu las kyi sgrib pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16386: mun pa rnams sbyangs pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:16387: 'bras bu dmyal ba la sogs ngan song gsum gyi gnas su yong mi ltung bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16388: ngon song du mi skye mir skyes kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:16389: mi khams gnas brgyad du mi skye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16390: mtho ris su skyes na yang gzhan pa'i gnas ngan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16392: mi bde zhing sdug bsngal ba'i yul /
NK077(tsu)001:16393: dam pa'i chos bya bar mi khams pa'i gnas ngan par /
NK077(tsu)001:16398: dbang po ma tshang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16399: ngan song gsum ste brgyad po dag tu 'gro bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16400: gzhan yang dran pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16402: mchog dam pa lta ba rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin goms pa dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:16403: skye ba bar chad kyang gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg
NK077(tsu)001:16404: pa mchog gi brjod bya brjod byed brjod par mi
NK077(tsu)001:16405: 'gyur ba de la 'jug cing nyams su len nus
NK077(tsu)001:16406: pa'i dran pa phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:16407: ro // tshe phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16408: des kyang tshe ring zhing nad med pa dang bde
NK077(tsu)001:16409: zhing 'byor pa phun sum tshogs pa dang gzhan la
NK077(tsu)001:16410: rag ma lus pa thob bo //
NK077(tsu)001:16411: mtshan dang ldan zhing yon tan rdzogs tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16413: lha dang mi'i skye gnas kyi mchog stod rigs thob pa'i sa'i gnas skabs der /
NK077(tsu)001:16414: lus dang byad bzhin bzang bzhin mdzes la yan lag chad lhag med par rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16415: dbang po lnga tshang zhing nying lag la lhag chad
NK077(tsu)001:16416: med pa ste gzugs phun sum tshogs pa thob par
NK077(tsu)001:16417: 'gyur ro // skad kyi gdangs bzang la snyan zhing
NK077(tsu)001:16418: phun sum tshogs pa tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu dang
NK077(tsu)001:16419: ldan pas 'gro don byed nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16420: bdag gi 'byor pa'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:16421: ni thams cad kun 'gro ba sems can gzhan la
NK077(tsu)001:16422: gnod pa dang 'tshe ba med pa dang ldan pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16423: sgo nas rnam par dag pa'i 'tsho ba dang longs
NK077(tsu)001:16424: spyod rtsol med du 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16425: tshan po che'i mthu stobs dang ldan pa phyag na rdo rje lta bur 'gyur zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:16426: de yang 'gro ba'i don du 'gyur ba'i mthu stobs
NK077(tsu)001:16427: phun sum tshogs pa yang dag dang ldan pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:16428: / 'gro ba sems can gzhan la lus ngag yid
NK077(tsu)001:16429: gsum gyi sgo nas gnod pa yang mi byed pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16430: bsam pa phun sum tshogs pas sems can la snying
NK077(tsu)001:16431: rje che zhing gsang sngags kyi don la shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:16432: phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par 'gyur ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:16433: / / tshogs bsgrub pa'i mthu stobs che zhing yo
NK077(tsu)001:16434: byad la spyod pa'i thabs mkhas pa dang ldan pas
NK077(tsu)001:16435: rnal 'byor pa bdag dang gdul bya gzhan gyi don
NK077(tsu)001:16436: rdzogs par byed nus pa'i phrin las phun sum tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:16438: der tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16440: dbang po rab kyis de lta bu'i lus de la
NK077(tsu)001:16441: brten nas zag bcas kyi lam rnams mthar phyin pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16442: 'bras bu skye shi med pa tshe la dbang ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:16443: rig 'dzin gyi sa thob nas sangs rgyas sprul pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16444: sku che ba'i yon tan dgos pa 'byung ba'i yid
NK077(tsu)001:16445: bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bu bkod
NK077(tsu)001:16446: pa'i zhing khams tshad gzhal ba las yas pa thams
NK077(tsu)001:16447: cad la / dper na 'dod khams na lha ris
NK077(tsu)001:16448: drug yod pa'i drug pa gzhan 'phrul gyi lhas longs
NK077(tsu)001:16449: spyod rang las sprul nas rang gi longs spyod pa
NK077(tsu)001:16450: cad la / ci lta bar / dbang bsgyur zhing
NK077(tsu)001:16451: longs spyod pa'i mthong lam gyi dngos grub dam pa
NK077(tsu)001:16453: mjug bsdus te the tshom med par thob tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16455: 'bring gis phyi ma la tshe dbang du 'gyur ba
NK077(tsu)001:16456: de'i phyir tshe la rang dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:16457: tshe phyi ma'i dus nyid du sbyor ba dang smos
NK077(tsu)001:16458: ci dgos te gdon mi za bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16459: lan grangs gzhan la'ang tshe dbang thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16461: gong du bstan pa'i tshul de ltar tshogs bsgrub pa
NK077(tsu)001:16462: la sgo gsum brtson 'grus dang ldan pas ni dbang
NK077(tsu)001:16463: rab brtson 'grus rab kyis mthong chos tshe 'di la
NK077(tsu)001:16464: thob pa dang 'bring gi phyi ma tshe dbang thob
NK077(tsu)001:16465: pa dang / de ltar thob par ma gyur na'ang
NK077(tsu)001:16466: tha mas kyang skye ba brgyud pa'i lan grangs gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:16467: du'am mi tshe ste skye ba bdun nyid las /
NK077(tsu)001:16469: tshe dbang rang la bzhi yod pa'i nang nas rig
NK077(tsu)001:16470: 'dzin gyi dam pa lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16471: tshe dbang rig 'dzin nyid 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16472: rnam smin thob tshul la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16473: bsgrub pa mthar phyin nas tshe dbang ma thob kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:16474: tshe 'di la rnam smin thob pa dpe don dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16477: de yang cho ga lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16478: sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang yo byad lnga po
NK077(tsu)001:16479: dag ste cho ga lnga gsum du bco lnga po
NK077(tsu)001:16480: de dag sbyor lam gyi mngon du rdzogs par byas
NK077(tsu)001:16481: nas dam tshig ma nyams pa dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK077(tsu)001:16482: 'byor pa rnams nges par 'tshogs te zhi khro'i tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:16483: bsgrub shing yo byad lnga la longs spyad par gyur
NK077(tsu)001:16484: na / blo chung ba'i dbang gis 'bras bu tshe
NK077(tsu)001:16485: dbang tshe 'di la mngon sum thob par ma gyur
NK077(tsu)001:16486: na / na yang / rnam smin gyi yid lha'i
NK077(tsu)001:16487: sku phyag rgya chen por smin pa'i 'bras bu de
NK077(tsu)001:16488: na / na yang / / tha mal pa'i lus kyi bsgrib nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16489: mngon sum du lhar mi snang bas na ma gyur yang zhes smos /
NK077(tsu)001:16490: de'i dpe ni dper na rgyal po chen po zhig
NK077(tsu)001:16491: gis bran mo ngan ma gcig dang bshos pa ste
NK077(tsu)001:16492: sbyor yang / rgyal po'i sras 'byung ba'i sa bon
NK077(tsu)001:16493: nur nur po bran mo'i mngal du chags pa'i bu
NK077(tsu)001:16494: de yang rgyal po'i rig 'dzin par byed de /
NK077(tsu)001:16495: de skyes pa mthong ma thag nas rgyal bu de
NK077(tsu)001:16496: rmongs phal pa thams cad kyi bla ste gong ma
NK077(tsu)001:16498: rgyal sar bton nas 'khor kun la dbang bsgyur ba'i stobs dang ldan pa de la /
NK077(tsu)001:16499: 'jig rten pa'i lha rnams kyang gsol mchod la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:16500: pa re ba'i mathu'am bsam pa skye ba'i dbang gi
NK077(tsu)001:16501: rang rang gi mthu stobs bskyed pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16502: rgyal bu de la bsrungs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16504: mchod pa byed pa'i dpe ltar du /
NK077(tsu)001:16505: don ni tshogs bsgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa yang dag
NK077(tsu)001:16506: pa'i lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs dang
NK077(tsu)001:16507: ldan pa rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi skur gyur na
NK077(tsu)001:16508: / gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i dam can ma
NK077(tsu)001:16509: mkha' 'gro la sogs pa'i chos skyongs srungs ma mang
NK077(tsu)001:16510: po kun gyi dam tshig gi /
NK077(tsu)001:16511: dgongs pa lhar smin pa de'i dbang gis spyi gtsug tu khur zhing bsrungs bar byed la /
NK077(tsu)001:16512: rnam smin gyi lus kyis spyod yul dor nas shi
NK077(tsu)001:16513: 'phos ma thag tu yid lha'i skur smin pa de
NK077(tsu)001:16514: dngos su gsal ba phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:16515: nyid du nges par rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16516: mthar ma phyin kyang phyi ma thob pa gdams pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16518: dbang po tha ma'i nang na blo che ba la
NK077(tsu)001:16519: la gong du bstan pa de ltar tshe 'dir rnam
NK077(tsu)001:16520: smin thob nas / phyi mar phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba de lta bur nges na yang /
NK077(tsu)001:16521: blo chung ba la la dag de ltar ma gyur
NK077(tsu)001:16522: pas phyi ma bsod nams bsags pa'i sa la gnas
NK077(tsu)001:16523: par 'gyur te / de yang tshe rabs skye ba
NK077(tsu)001:16524: thams cad kyi bar du las ngan par gyur pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16528: log pa brgyad la sogs pa'i sa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16529: gnas kun tu tshogs sgrub kyi rnal 'byor pa de der skye bar mi 'gyur la /
NK077(tsu)001:16530: de bas lhag pa lha mi'i theg pa la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:16531: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi la'ang 'jug cing spyod
NK077(tsu)001:16533: thob pa'i 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rig mchog 'dzin pa kho na 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:16534: skye ba phyi ma'am lan grangs gzhan la rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16535: sngon du bstan pa'i spyod yul dor nas phyag rgyar rdzogs /
NK077(tsu)001:16537: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor bar 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:16539: gong du bstan pa'i don 'di la the tshom dang
NK077(tsu)001:16540: sam nyi ldan pa min te the tshom med pas
NK077(tsu)001:16541: / las 'phro dang skal bar ldan pa'i rnal 'byor
NK077(tsu)001:16542: pa kun gyi dus rtag tu tshogs bsgrub pa la
NK077(tsu)001:16543: brtson 'grus chen po bskyed par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16545: tshe dbang rig 'dzin bar do la thob pa yod dam med /
NK077(tsu)001:16547: 'di nyid kyi le'u drug pa spros bcas kyi skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:16548: bar ma'am phyi mar gnyis sbyor 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:16549: rnam smin tshe dbang gang rung la sbyor bar bshad pa dang 'gal la /
NK077(tsu)001:16550: bar do la thob pa yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:16551: rnam smin de cha lugs ci ltar yod /
NK077(tsu)001:16552: lha'i cha lugs su yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:16553: phyag rgya chen po dang cha lugs khyad med par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16556: med na yid lhar ma smin par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16557: tshe dbang bar do la thob par 'dod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:16559: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang cha lugs khyad med du 'gyur ba'i skyon dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16560: yang lus snga ma ni dor zin la gzhan med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16561: lhag bcas su mi 'gyur ba'i skyon 'ong ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16562: de la nye'u ston chos kyi seng ges na re /
NK077(tsu)001:16563: tshe dbang bar do la thob pa'i cha lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16564: bar do la 'byung ba dwangs ma 'od kyi lus gcig yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16566: tshe dbang bar do la thob par 'dod la /
NK077(tsu)001:16568: 'di 'am phyi ma la bar dor thob par mi 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:16569: mi yi lus la phyag rgya che //
NK077(tsu)001:16570: rgya mig rgya pa khyung phrug bya //
NK077(tsu)001:16571: gsal rdzogs smin nas bar chad med //
NK077(tsu)001:16572: ces slob dpon b+hi ma las gsungs pas mngon gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:16573: de dag la rigs pas brtag na /
NK077(tsu)001:16574: rnam smin tshe dbang gnyis bar do la thob pa'ang mi 'gal te /
NK077(tsu)001:16576: bar do'i 'byung ba dwangs ma 'od kyis lus su
NK077(tsu)001:16577: yod pa de dor nas phyag rgya la sbyor bas
NK077(tsu)001:16579: 'od kyi lus de nyid mi 'dor par khyer bas /
NK077(tsu)001:16580: lhag bcas tshe dbang gnyis su mi 'gal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16581: zhes chos rje zur pa tshang gis gsung 'dug kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:16583: rnam smin bar do la thob pa'i lung 'dug /tshe
NK077(tsu)001:16584: dbang bar do la thob pa'i lung mi 'dug ste
NK077(tsu)001:16585: le'u lnga pa phyag rgya gcig pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:16586: rnam smin bar do la thob pa'i lung ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16587: de nyid bar phyi'am lan grangs gzhan gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:16588: tshe dbang bar do la thob pa'i lung mi 'dug ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16592: 'o na phyag rgya spros pa'i skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:16593: bar ma'am phyi ma gnyis sbyor 'dzin 'di dang 'gal lam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:16597: rnam smin bar do na thob lugs byung /
NK077(tsu)001:16600: rnam smin tshe dbang gnyis phyi ma la thob lugs byung /
NK077(tsu)001:16601: 'o na rnam smin bar do la thob lugs ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:16602: tshe 'di nyid kyi thog na kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag ma nus /
NK077(tsu)001:16603: de ma nus pa'i don gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16604: phyag chen bar do na ma thob /
NK077(tsu)001:16605: de sbyangs pa'i don la bar do na /
NK077(tsu)001:16606: yun ring po gcig sbyangs dgos par sems so //
NK077(tsu)001:16607: rnam smin rig 'dzin de bar do la /
NK077(tsu)001:16609: tshe dbang bar do la thob pa yod dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:16610: de don gyi 'di rnams brtag par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16613: zag bcas zag med du sbyor ba la bar chad
NK077(tsu)001:16614: med pa'i sbyor lam la tshom bu tshogs bsgrub kyi
NK077(tsu)001:16616: mthong lam bsgrub par byed pa'i thabs ston par byed pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:16617: gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:16619: yas bgrang bdun pa'i don du gada'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16620: da ni 'phags pa'i lam gsum ston te de la zag med kyi rig 'dzin bzhi yod /
NK077(tsu)001:16621: de la thog mar rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi stong thun brjod na /
NK077(tsu)001:16622: rnam smin la yang don brgyad las /
NK077(tsu)001:16626: thar chag pa'i rgyu tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:16628: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub kyi sa na /
NK077(tsu)001:16629: rab zla ba drug /rab 'og lo gcig /mtha' ltag lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16630: tha mas lo gcig zla ba bzhi nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16635: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam /
NK077(tsu)001:16637: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK077(tsu)001:16639: tshe dbang gi dus kyi skabs su gsung //
NK077(tsu)001:16641: mi 'thad pa'i lugs dgag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16644: dang po rnam smin gyi ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16645: yid lha'i skur smin pa rnam smin yin zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:16646: snang 'byed mthar phyin pa 'di yang rnam smin du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16647: tshe dbang yang rnam smin du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16648: yid lha'i skur smin pa tsam de gnyis la yang yod pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:16649: yang yid dam lhar smin pa la lus lha dang mi'i cha lugs su yod pa yin zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:16650: tshe dbang yang rnam smin du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16653: yid lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por rdzogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:16654: ming bzhi dang bcas pa'i lus nyid lha'am mi'i cha lugs su yod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:16655: lus de nyid dang 'bral ma thag /bar na lam
NK077(tsu)001:16656: gzhan med par phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba
NK077(tsu)001:16657: gang yin pa'o // de yang de nyid las yid kyi lha yi gzugs bzung nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16659: gzugs rdzogs stobs chen de kho na /
NK077(tsu)001:16662: ngo bo la rtsod pa spang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16663: cha lugs la rtsod pa spangs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16664: zag pa yod med rtsod pa spang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16665: tshe dbang dang khyad yod med kyi sgo nas rtsod pa spang ba dang bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16666: dang po ni rnam smin gyi ngo bo de yid
NK077(tsu)001:16667: lha'i sku phyag chen por stobs rdzogs shing lus lha'am
NK077(tsu)001:16669: lus dang bral ma thag phyag rgya chen por sbyor ba yin na /
NK077(tsu)001:16670: tshom bus tshogs bsgrub pa thod rgal ba phyag rgya chen po la sbyor nges pa /
NK077(tsu)001:16671: de yang rnam smin du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16673: tshogs bsgrub thod rgal ba de zag med du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16674: rnam smin rig 'dzin yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:16676: sbyor lam zag bcas ma yin par thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16678: tshom bu tshogs bsgrub thod rgal ba de la yid lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por stobs rdzogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:16679: lus lha'i lus su yod la /
NK077(tsu)001:16680: lha mi'i lus dang bral ma thag phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba tsam gcig yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:16681: bar na lam gzhan med par phyag rgya chen po la dngos su sbyor ba med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16683: 'di ni gong gi mtshan nyid gnyis kyi kha bar na /
NK077(tsu)001:16684: lam gzhan med par dngos su phyag rgya chen po
NK077(tsu)001:16685: la sbyor ba'i chos gsum ldan de nyid rnam smin
NK077(tsu)001:16686: yin pas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16687: 'o na rnam smin pa'i cha lugs ci ltar yod byas pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:16691: lhag med 'byung med las lus med //
NK077(tsu)001:16692: mya ngan 'das par smin chas brjod //
NK077(tsu)001:16694: lha mi'i lus su yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:16695: zag bcas su 'gro bas na skyon med do //
NK077(tsu)001:16696: de ci ltar yin zhe na zag pa med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16697: skye 'jig gi chos dang bral ba'i mya ngan las 'das pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16698: des na lhag ma'i lus 'di yod pa'i phyir ro zhes zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16701: rnam smin lha'i sku'i phyag rgya chen por yod na tshe dbang bas bzang bar thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16702: tshe dbang ni lha mi'i lus su yod la rnam smin lha'i skur yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16704: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang khyad med par thal te /
NK077(tsu)001:16705: rnam smin de'i lus su lha'i skur yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16707: bka' spyi nas zag pa med pa'i mthong lam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16708: 'dir yod par bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16712: tshe dbang bas bzang ba'i skyon mi 'ong ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16713: rnam smin lus lha'i skur yod pa'i don gyis slar ngan pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:16714: lhag ma'i lus 'di nyid mya ngan las 'das par khyer ma nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16715: tshe dbang gi khyer nus pas bzang ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16716: yang phyag rgya chen po dang khyad med par thal ba'i skyon ma 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16718: mkhas pa pan tri ta gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16719: mi tsam du gcig kyang khyad yod pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:16720: lha'i sku tsam du gcig kyang dgongs pa la khyad yod pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:16722: bka' spyi nas bshad pa'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16723: bka' spyi nas zag pa med pa'i mthong lam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16724: lha mir yod par bshad pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:16725: tshe dbang la dgongs pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16728: rnam smin gyi lus lha'i skur yod pa mi 'thad de /
NK077(tsu)001:16731: phyi ma la thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16732: lan grangs gzhan la thob par bshad pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:16733: rnam smin gyi lus lhar yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:16734: tshe 'di la thob pa rgyun chad med par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:16735: lus rang yang snang bas so //
NK077(tsu)001:16736: lha ma'i lus 'dor dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16738: rnam par smin pa'i nges tshig kyang med de /
NK077(tsu)001:16739: nges tshig ni rnam pa lha ma'i lus su yod la /
NK077(tsu)001:16741: yid lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por stobs rdzogs par smin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:16742: lus dang bral ma thag lha'i skur gsal ba de nyid yin pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:16744: phyag rgya chen po la thod rgal ba 'ong ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:16745: rnam smin gyi cha lugs yin zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:16746: 'o na dgongs pa lha dang khyad med par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16749: rnam smin dag gi cha lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16750: dper na khyung sgong la khyung phyug mi zer ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16751: ma'i mngal la seng phrug mi zer /
NK077(tsu)001:16752: mngal gyi nang la phru gu la seng phrug zer ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:16753: lus lha mir yod pa la rnam smin mi zer /
NK077(tsu)001:16755: rnam smin gyi cha lugs yin zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:16756: 'o na dgongs pa lha dang khyad med par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16759: lus lha mir yod pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:16760: 'di yang rnam smin gyis lus yin /
NK077(tsu)001:16761: lha'i skur yod pa 'di yang min /
NK077(tsu)001:16763: lus 'di bral ma thag gi bar gyis skad gcig ma de rnam smin gyi lus yin /
NK077(tsu)001:16764: zer ba dag kyang yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:16765: de yang mi 'thad ci'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:16766: 'o na rnam smin gyi gzhan don byed dam mi byed /
NK077(tsu)001:16767: mi byed na byed par bshad pa dang 'gal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16768: byed na skad cig ma la gzhan don rdzogs par thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16769: 'o na rnam smin gyi cha lugs ci ltar yod ces pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:16770: lha mi'i cha lugs su yod pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16771: 'o na rnam smin de lhag bcas su thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16774: mya ngan las 'das pa la gnyis yod pa la phyogs gcig pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16775: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16776: phyogs gcig pa'i mya ngan la 'das pa /
NK077(tsu)001:16777: zag med kyi mya ngan la 'das pa de yin kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:16778: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan 'das pa de ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16779: mya ngan la 'das pa de rang gi yang mtha' la mi gnas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:16780: thugs rjes 'khor ba la 'gro don byed pa'i sangs rgyas la zer ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16781: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan la 'das sangs rgyas kyi
NK077(tsu)001:16782: sa la lhag mi'i lus 'di khyer nus mi nus
NK077(tsu)001:16783: la / lhag bcas lhag med zer ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16784: rnam smin de ni mi gnas pa'i mya ngan la
NK077(tsu)001:16785: 'das pa'i sar lus khyer mi nus pas lhag med
NK077(tsu)001:16788: 'o na rnam smin de zag bcas yin nam /
NK077(tsu)001:16790: zhes pa la zag bcas yin na /
NK077(tsu)001:16791: zag med kyi mthong lam du mi 'thad /
NK077(tsu)001:16792: zag med yin na lus la 'dor bas lus kyi zag pa 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16796: zag bcas su 'dug kyang zag med kyi khongs su 'deb ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16797: dper na nya lcags kyus 'dzin pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:16798: skyes bu'i rgyu zhabs su mtshon rgyab pa lta bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16800: lus de dang bral ma thag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin du 'gyur bas /
NK077(tsu)001:16801: zag med yin gsung skad do //
NK077(tsu)001:16802: de yang mi 'thad de ci'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:16803: zag bcas su 'dug na zag med du mi 'thad /
NK077(tsu)001:16806: de gnyis ka 'gal ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16807: de gnyis kyi bar na phung po gsum pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:16810: rnam smin zag med yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:16812: zag pa'i rtsa ba skye gnas yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16813: zag pa'i rtsa ba med pas zag med yin gsung yang /
NK077(tsu)001:16814: 'ga' zhig gis lus 'dor ba tsam 'dug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16815: lus kyi zag par mi 'gro ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16819: lus kyi zag pa yod par thal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16820: 'o na lus kyi zag pa gang la zer byas pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:16821: las sam nad kyi sdug bsngal dang bcas nas lus 'dor ba dang bcas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16822: lus 'dor ba'i sa bon dang bcas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16824: de min na lus kyi zag pa med pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16827: nad kyi sdug bsngal med par lus 'dor ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:16828: yid lha'i skur smin pas stobs rdzogs nas yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16829: dper na rdzu 'phrul ngan kog tu 'dor ba dang 'dra ba'i tshul du /
NK077(tsu)001:16830: lus 'di dor nas phyag rgya chen po la sbyor bas byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16832: 'o na lhag bcas tshe dbang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16833: rnam smin gnyis kyi mthong lam la khyad par yod dam med /
NK077(tsu)001:16835: tshe dbang la thod rgal 'ong ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:16836: rnam smin la yang thod rgal 'ong bar thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16838: zag med kyi mthong lam gyi ngo bo yang gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16839: zhes pa la khyad par yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:16840: 'o na mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba'i skyon mi 'ong ngam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:16842: ngo bo mthong la du ma khyad par len la /
NK077(tsu)001:16843: nus pa la khyad par yod pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:16844: ci ltar yod na rgyu la khyad par yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16845: mthong lam gyi 'bras bu la yang khyad par yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:16846: dgongs pa la khyad par yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:16847: dgongs pa la khyad par yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:16848: don shes pa la rgya che chung yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16850: ngo bo rang la yang khyad par yod pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16851: 'o na mthong lam la gnyis su mi 'agro'am zhe na mi 'gro ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16852: gnyis ka mthong lam du gcig pa yin pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:16854: rdo rje rigs kyi rnam par smin pa la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:16855: rig 'dzin gyi rnam grangs yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:16857: lnga pa dgongs pa ni rig pa lha sku gcig dang du ma las /
NK077(tsu)001:16858: grol ba'i phyag rgya chen por gsal ba stobs rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16860: dal ral ba'i tshul spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16862: de nyid spyod pa thams cad lha la lha rol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16864: chos nyid la chos nyid rol pa'i tshul du spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16865: bdud pa mngon par shes pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16866: de nyid kyi mngon shes la'am /
NK077(tsu)001:16867: nyi shu rtsa lngas gling bzhi tshun chad gsal bar mkhyen pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16868: sa lam gang ma la sbyor tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16869: rnam smin gyi tshe thos bsam sgom gsum gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:16870: kun 'gro'i dri ma dag ma dag la phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16871: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu zag med kyi lam la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:16873: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16875: dngos grub ces pa thun mong dang thun mong ma
NK077(tsu)001:16876: yin pa'i dngos grub gnyis las 'dir lhag pa'i zhes
NK077(tsu)001:16877: pas / thun mong bas mchog tu 'gro ba zag
NK077(tsu)001:16878: pa med pa'i mchog /gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu de
NK077(tsu)001:16879: pas / nyid la / bsnyen bsgrub rnam pa bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:16880: yis gzhung bzhin du bsgrub pa la mos par byas
NK077(tsu)001:16881: pas / nyid la / pa ni / brjod bya
NK077(tsu)001:16882: don gyi phyogs nas zhes pa 'brel mtshams sbyar ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:16883: pas / nyid la / pa ni / tshig go
NK077(tsu)001:16884: // 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal med pas bde chen rig
NK077(tsu)001:16885: 'dzin gyi sa la dgod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:16886: spyir lam las mtshan nyid gsum pa zag bcas tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:16887: sbyor gnyis kyi lam mthar phyin pa'i gnas skabs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:16889: zag med mthong sgom mthar lam gyi rig 'dzin bzhi po bshad par bya /
NK077(tsu)001:16898: phyag rgya spros bcas mthar phyin nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16899: zla ba bcu drug la sogs pa rab 'bring tha
NK077(tsu)001:16900: ma'i dus tshogs zhi khro tshom bu bar chad pa
NK077(tsu)001:16901: bsgrub pa'i sbyor lam zag bcas zag med dam /
NK077(tsu)001:16902: ngan song du ldog pa'i bar chad med pa'i sa nas zhes pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:16903: yang na thod rgal gyi dbang btsan du /
NK077(tsu)001:16904: ting nge 'dzin bar chad med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:16905: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi sa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16906: sngar 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas brgyud pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:16907: las las grub pa'i phung po lus 'di nyid lhag
NK077(tsu)001:16909: yod pa'i tshul gyis mya ngan las 'da' bas /
NK077(tsu)001:16910: mthar thug gi 'bras bu la thar chags dang thod rgal gyi tshul gnyis kyis sbyor ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16912: 'di la lhag ma yod med ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16913: chos rje zur pa tshang gis 'di ltar du gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16914: 'byung ba dngas ma las grub pa'i lus ni lhag ma ma yin gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:16915: 'byung ba rags pa snyigs ma'i cha las grub pa lhag ma'i lus zhes bya gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16917: tshe dbang bar do nas thob pa de lhag med du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16918: 'byung ba rags pa snyigs ma'i lus la med pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16920: rnam smin bar do na thob pa 'di chos can /
NK077(tsu)001:16922: 'byung ba rags pa'i lus med cing /
NK077(tsu)001:16923: dngas ma'i lus de ma dor bar phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16927: de sogs gong du skye 'gyur ba'i //
NK077(tsu)001:16930: bar do'i lus de phyi ma gar len gyi lus kyi cha lugs su yod par bshad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16931: de yang phyag chen gi cha lugs su yod dgos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:16935: bar do nas rig 'dzin de gnyis thob pa rgyun chad du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:16936: 'byung ba dngas ma'i lus mi 'dor ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16939: 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas brgyud pa'i lhag ma /
NK077(tsu)001:16940: rig 'dzin thob pa'i lus 'di yin pas lhag ma'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16941: 'di sangs rgyas kyi sa la khyer nus mi nus gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16943: bar do nas thob pa'i rnam smin de /
NK077(tsu)001:16944: lhag bcas su 'gyur ba'i skyon 'ong bar mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:16945: de'i lus mi 'diir ba'i phyir ro snyam ste dpyod do //
NK077(tsu)001:16946: 'o na 'di ni 'byung ba dwangs snyigs gang la grub kyang lhag ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:16947: thob pa gang na thob kyang rnam smin ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16948: rang gi lus rgyun sbrul lpags ltar dor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16950: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar /
NK077(tsu)001:16951: rig pa rkyang pas 'gro ba lhag med du bshad de /
NK077(tsu)001:16954: bdag nyid sgo gsum lhar gsal zhing //
NK077(tsu)001:16955: 'byung ba bsags pa'i lus la grol //
NK077(tsu)001:16956: ting nge 'dzin ni phyag rgya chen por smin //
NK077(tsu)001:16957: khyung phrug sbub dang bral ba bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:16958: ma lus phyag rgya sgyu ma'i mchog /rnam par smin zhes de la brjod //
NK077(tsu)001:16961: stobs chung rkyen smon zhan pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:16962: zhes pa gsum gyis gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16965: thob pa gang nas thob cing dwangs snyigs gang yang rung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16966: rang gi lus rgyun gyi lhag ma 'di skye 'jig med pa rdo rje'i lus su gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:16967: de nyid sangs rgyas kyi sa la khyer nus pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:16970: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe'i rigs //
NK077(tsu)001:16971: zhes pa gsum gyis gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:16973: de gnyis rang gi ngo bo'i dus na /
NK077(tsu)001:16974: lhag bcas lhag med du sbyor /
NK077(tsu)001:16976: de gnyis rang gi dus na gnyis kyi lhag ma'i lus dang bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:16978: spyir lhag ma dang bcas ma bcas sam /
NK077(tsu)001:16979: lhag ma yod med zhes bya bar 'jog pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16980: thob pa'i ngos nas brtsi ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:16981: sbyar ba'i ngos nas brtsi ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16983: 'khor ba'i gnas su phung po'i lhag ma ma lus par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16984: lhag med du sangs rgyas zhes zer la /
NK077(tsu)001:16985: ro lus nas spur sbyangs dgos pa rnams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:16986: lhag ma ma lus par grags so //
NK077(tsu)001:16987: de ni 'jig rten pa la grags pa'i dbang du'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16988: gnyis pa ni de la go bzlog nas 'ongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16989: de la 'di tha ma sbyar sa nas brtsis pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:16990: mthong lam rig 'dzin gnyis po rang rang gnas skabs
NK077(tsu)001:16991: dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i rtogs tshogs kyis lus
NK077(tsu)001:16992: rgyun khyer nus mi nus bzhag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:16993: thun mong gi theg pa nyan thos la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:16994: lhag bcas lhag med gnyis yod pa lta bur /
NK077(tsu)001:16995: rig 'dzin gyi skabs 'dir yang lhag bcas lhag med gnyis zung du ston par 'gyur /
NK077(tsu)001:16997: lam snga ma la zag bcas tshogs sbyor rnams la thun mong zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:16998: de gnyis la'ang blo che chung yod pa'i dbang gis /
NK077(tsu)001:16999: rim cig char gnyis yod pa lta bur /
NK077(tsu)001:17002: de'i don rgyas par bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:17003: thun mong lta bur zhes pa dpe ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17004: thun mong gi theg pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:17006: bar chad med pa'i lam gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:17007: tha ma nas dgra bcom thob tshul gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:17008: phung po lhag ma dang bcas pa dbyings mya ngan
NK077(tsu)001:17009: las 'das pa dang lhag ma med pa'i dbyings su'o
NK077(tsu)001:17011: rgyu kun 'byung gi bden pa spangs kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17012: 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi bden pa ma spangs pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17013: sngar gyi las kyi rnam smin las grub pa'i rten phung po 'di dang ni ma bral /
NK077(tsu)001:17014: sems nyon mongs pa tha dag dang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17015: de bas dgra bcom pa la mdze byung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17016: g.yang du lhung ba la sogs pa yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:17017: sngar gyi las smin pa yin skad /
NK077(tsu)001:17019: nyon mongs zad kyang de dag la //
NK077(tsu)001:17020: las kyi nus pa mthong ba yin //
NK077(tsu)001:17023: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
NK077(tsu)001:17024: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
NK077(tsu)001:17025: 'tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
NK077(tsu)001:17031: de yang 'di skad du phung po dag dang ma bral bar //
NK077(tsu)001:17033: de tshe der ni spang bya na /
NK077(tsu)001:17036: gnyis pa lhag ma med pa'i dbyings su mya ngan 'das pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17038: sems nyon mongs mtha' dag dang bral nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17039: rnam min gyi lus nyid kyang mtsho la 'khyag zhu ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17040: nam mkha' la sprin dengs pa ltar gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17041: de'ang gong la 'phags pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17044: tshor ba rnam pa bral 'gyur zhing //
NK077(tsu)001:17045: 'du byed nye bar zhi ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:17046: rnam par shes pa nub 'gyur tshe //
NK077(tsu)001:17047: sems ni rnam par grol gyur te //
NK077(tsu)001:17048: mar me shi ba'i ro bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17051: ci srid yid kyi lus yod kyi bar /
NK077(tsu)001:17052: lhag bcas la yid gyi lus dang bral nas lhag med de /
NK077(tsu)001:17053: de ltar nyan thos la lhag bcas lhag med gnyis yod pa lta bur /
NK077(tsu)001:17054: 'dir yang mthong lam lhag med du mya ngan la 'da' ba'i rnam smin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17055: lhag bcas su 'da' ba'i tshe dbang gnyis yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17056: mthong lam zung du 'gyur zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17057: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:17058: mthong lam rnam pa gnyis su 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:17061: gong ma rnams kyi rnam smin lhag med /
NK077(tsu)001:17062: gzhan gsum ka lhag bcas su bzhed do //
NK077(tsu)001:17063: mthong lam gnyis yod pa'i dbang gis /
NK077(tsu)001:17064: de gnyis na yang sbyar ba'i lam gong ma gnyis po la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:17065: lhag bcas lhag med gnyis gnyis yod zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17066: don la lhag bcas lhag med gnyis kyi go //
NK077(tsu)001:17067: nyan thos la lus mal na bzhag pa la lhag bcas /
NK077(tsu)001:17068: lus ma bor bar dgra bcol thob pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17070: 'dir tshe rnam gnyis kyi lhag bcas /
NK077(tsu)001:17071: med ni de las go bzlog pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17073: lhag ma de rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17074: lhag bcas tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17077: rnam smin thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17079: dang por bshad par khas blangs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17080: de ltar gnyis yod pa de la thog ma rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17083: thod rgal gyi dbang btsan du /
NK077(tsu)001:17084: rab phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17086: lha du ma'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin la nyams
NK077(tsu)001:17087: brtan zhing mthar phyin par byas pa nyid kyi sa
NK077(tsu)001:17088: nas rnam smin la sbyor ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17089: thar chags pa'i dbang btsan du phyag rgya spros pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:17090: rnal 'byor de mthar phyin par brtan pa thob nas
NK077(tsu)001:17091: / sbyor lam du blo rab 'bring tha ma'i phye bas zla ba drug gam bcu gnyis sam /
NK077(tsu)001:17094: bsnyen bsgrub pa'i tshe rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:17097: tshe dbang ltar skye shi med pa rdo rje lta
NK077(tsu)001:17098: bu'i lus su smin cing grub par ma gyur pa
NK077(tsu)001:17100: sgom pa goms pa'i stobs chung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17102: smon lam gyi mthu zhan pa'i phyin na /
NK077(tsu)001:17104: rnam rtog rang gzugs kyis lus yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:17105: dug lnga'i rang gzugs la rgyud lnga'i sems can snang ba lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17108: lhag ma'i lus ni 'ga' zhig gis 'byung ba rags pa snyigs ma'i cha las grub pa la zer /
NK077(tsu)001:17109: sngar gyi las kyis 'phan pa las grub pa las kyi lus de bzhag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17110: 'bras bu rdo rje 'chang chen po'i sangs rgyas kyi sar phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17111: lhun grub brgyud nas rig pas 'gro bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17112: lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17117: tshogs bsgrub nas thob pa de'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:17118: rab kyi tshe 'di la thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17119: 'bring gi bar do dang tshe phyi ma ste gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17120: tha mas kyang skye ba'i lan grangs brgyud pa gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:17121: bdun tshun chad du blo dang brtson pa rab dang
NK077(tsu)001:17122: 'bring tha ma'i tshul dag gis rnam smin thob par
NK077(tsu)001:17123: 'gyur gyis dus bskal pa grangs med la sogs par
NK077(tsu)001:17124: mi 'gyang ste / de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:17125: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gsal ba tshogs kyis spyod lam brtul zhugs dang ldan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17126: sgo gsum gyi brtson 'grus bskyed pa rnams gtso cher byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17128: dgongs pa ni 'bras bu lam du byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17130: rmad byung thabs kyis spyod pa nyams su blangs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17131: brtson pa de dag dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17134: rnam smin ngo bo'i dpe don dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17136: yid lha'i sku'i rnal 'byor du ting nge 'dzin gsal
NK077(tsu)001:17137: zhing yid lhar rdzogs par smin pa la lus kyi
NK077(tsu)001:17138: dra bas bsgrib par 'gyur ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17139: dper na ka la ping ka sgong rgyas bsgrib /
NK077(tsu)001:17140: mi 'jigs seng ge'i mngal rgyas bsgrib pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:17141: 'byung ba lus rgya dang bral nas lha'i sku mngon
NK077(tsu)001:17142: sum du snang bar byed pa de rnam par smin
NK077(tsu)001:17144: rnam smin gyi nges tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17146: yid kyi lha'i gzugs bzung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:17147: lus kyi rgya mdud dang 'dra ba ma grol bar gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17148: lha'i sku nyid mngon du gsal bar gyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17149: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin zhes de la gdags so //
NK077(tsu)001:17152: dper na rgya mig skol phor rgya pa tsh+wa tsh+wa
NK077(tsu)001:17153: ci lta bar lus rgyas bsgrib ste phyag rgya chen
NK077(tsu)001:17154: po'i rig 'dzin thob la ma rag pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:17155: yid lha'i gzugs su rdzogs shing dgongs pa stobs chen de kho na rnam smin rig 'dzin yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17156: bzhi pa dang lnga pa dgongs spyod thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17157: dgongs spyod snga phyi dang phyogs mthun par spyir bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17158: bye brag so so nas bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17160: rnam smin de yang lta dgongs bzang ngan dang spyod
NK077(tsu)001:17161: pa zab mi zab rnams lam gang gong 'og kyis
NK077(tsu)001:17162: phye bas khyad par gnyis yod pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17164: de yang phyag rgya gcig spros nas thob pa yi rnam smin dgongs spyod dma' zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:17165: tshogs bsgrub nas thob pa'i rnam smin dgongs spyod bzang zhing mtho ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17167: gcig spros nas thob pa de dgongs spyod rgya mtsho
NK077(tsu)001:17168: snga ma phyag rgya gcig spros dang rgyu mthun la
NK077(tsu)001:17169: / tshogs bsgrub nas thob pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:17170: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho de phyi ma tshogs bsgrub dang rgyud mthus pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17171: de ltar dgongs spyod rnams stobs che chung gi chas rnam smin du ming grags pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17172: yang na spyod pa rgya mtsho snga ma tshogs bsgrub dang rgyud mthun /
NK077(tsu)001:17173: dgongs pa rgya mtsho phyi ma phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang rgyud mthun /
NK077(tsu)001:17174: 'o na gong 'og dang khyad med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:17175: spyod pa tshogs bsgrub pas stobs che /
NK077(tsu)001:17176: dgongs pa phyag chen pas stobs chung /
NK077(tsu)001:17177: che chung gi chas phye bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17178: 'di rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi ming du grags pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17181: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo la
NK077(tsu)001:17182: lhag ma'i lus med 'byung ba'i lus med las kyi
NK077(tsu)001:17183: lus med par dgongs pa mya ngan las 'das pa
NK077(tsu)001:17184: yi lha'i skur smin pa'i cha nas dgongs pa'i rgyud
NK077(tsu)001:17185: phyag rgya chen po dang mthun par brjod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17188: de la bdag gzhan gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:17189: dang po rang don du ci spyod zhi khro'i dal du gsal bas lha la lha'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17190: dal la dal rol pa'i tshul ma 'gags par spyod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17191: bsod nams dang de la ma zhen pa ste rang bzhin ma dmigs par shes pas ye shes te /
NK077(tsu)001:17192: tshogs gnyis zung 'jug tu rdzogs par byed pa de
NK077(tsu)001:17193: ni rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi bdag gi don gyi
NK077(tsu)001:17195: yid lha'i skur smin pas phrin las /
NK077(tsu)001:17197: gzhan don rdzogs par byed pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:17198: gdul bya gang yang yal bar mi 'dor bar yang dag pa'i sa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17199: don la dgod pa ni gzhan don gyi spyod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17202: sbyor lam bar chad med pa'i lam pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17203: mthong lam rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin gyi mngon
NK077(tsu)001:17204: par shes pa lam de nyid kyi ming can te
NK077(tsu)001:17205: / bar chad med pa'i mngon shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17206: rnam par smin pa'i mngon shes zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17207: 'o na khyad par med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:17208: tshogs bsgrub las mngon shes kyi grangs dang yul la khyad par yod par mi 'gyur kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17210: tshogs bsgrub tu 'gyur srid pa la 'dir mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17211: 'dir yul dang ngo bo gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17212: zag med kyi nus pa stobs che bas nges pa nyid du khyad yod par 'gyur ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:17215: thob pa'i rnam smin gyis dpags tshad /
NK077(tsu)001:17216: spros pa nas gling khams gcig /tshogs bsgrubs nas gling bzhi'i yul khams la sbyor ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17217: yang na mngon par shes pa dpag cing shes pa'i tshul gyi tshad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17218: gling khams kyi yul sbyor zhing shes pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17219: lam gang ma la sbyor ba'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17221: gang rnam smin rig 'dzin de lus rgya dang bral ma thag pa'i dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:17222: yid lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po la sogs pa
NK077(tsu)001:17223: bzhi rdzogs pa'i lha'i sku bdag nyid dngos su 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:17228: don 'grub dang lnga la sogs pa rigs gang yin pa de rig pas 'dzin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17229: de ka la phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17230: rnam smin gyi gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17231: rig 'dzin gyi don bshad na gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17236: zag med gyi mthong lam yan chad la gnas pa'i rten gyi gang zag mnyam rjes la lha dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17239: dbye ba ni rig 'dzin gyi sa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17243: gzhan dag gi phyir ting nge 'dzin rig pa yul gyis mi 'phrog pa nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:17246: phyag rgya'i rnal 'byor la sogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17247: so so'i rig 'dzin pa kho na'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17250: rig 'dzin du grags pa ni mang la /
NK077(tsu)001:17253: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:17256: rig pa'i skyes bur lung thob bo //
NK077(tsu)001:17259: rig pa 'dzin pa chen po zhes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17262: mthong goms mthar ldan rig pa nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:17263: ces pa gsum gyis gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:17265: rig pa 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17266: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa rang gis rig pa la rdzogs pa mi gtong bar 'dzin pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17267: zag med kyi mi rtogs pa yul gyi mi 'phrog par 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17269: yi dam gyi lha rigs lnga gang byed kyi rigs mi gtong bar 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17271: mkhas rtog goms spyod rig pa 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:17274: me chu rlung gi rigs gnas bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:17275: gang rigs zin pa mi gtong ba //
NK077(tsu)001:17276: dang po 'byung dang bya byed dang //
NK077(tsu)001:17280: rang gi ngo bo yongs su smin pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:17281: de nyid kyi 'bras bu yongs su len pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:17283: de yang phyag rgya chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17284: so so'i rig pa 'dzin pa kho na'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17285: de'ang rnam smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:17287: de'i shugs kyis tshe dbang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17288: lhun grub gnyis rig pa 'dzin pa gtso bos mngon no //
NK077(tsu)001:17292: ye shes kyi rnal 'byor gnyis su yang bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:17293: de yang rig 'dzin mtshan bcas yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:17294: rig pa 'dzin pa ni mtshan med do //
NK077(tsu)001:17295: rig pa 'dzin pa la lnga yod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:17296: da lta thams cad mthun pa rdo rje'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17300: las kyi rigs dang ldan grag po 'di'i don rigs lnga kun la brtags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17301: tha dad du grags tshul brgyad de /
NK077(tsu)001:17302: gsung sa bon las rigs su brtag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17309: las las rigs su brtags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17311: lha bskyed yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las rigs su phye ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17313: phyag na rdo rje bsnam pa la rdo rje'i rig /de bzhin 'khor lo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17316: ral gri bsnams pa dag gis rigs su grags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17322: don yod grub par brtags shing rgyas gdab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17323: bzhi pa ni mi 'khrugs pa'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17327: phrin las kyi rigs su grags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17329: brten pa mdun rgyab sku gsung thugs //
NK077(tsu)001:17330: 'khor lo rdzogs pa 'bru gsum brda' //zhes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17331: brten nas g.yas dang g.yon nyid du //
NK077(tsu)001:17332: yon tan phrin las dal bzhag /ces pas sku gsung
NK077(tsu)001:17333: thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rigs lngar bzhag go
NK077(tsu)001:17335: dbus dang shar lho nub byang la rigs su brtag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17337: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las te /
NK077(tsu)001:17352: lhun gyis grub pa'i las dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17356: drag po'i rigs zhes brtags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17359: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rig 'dzin 'di gang las brtag pa'i rig 'dzin lnga po yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:17360: de rnams rang bzhin tha dad pa ma yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17361: 'di ni phyag mtshan las brtags pa'i rigs lnga'i rig 'dzin te /
NK077(tsu)001:17363: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK077(tsu)001:17366: rnam smin dang tshe dbang gnyis kyis dbye ba dang 'du ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17368: de'i phyir phyag rgya chen po dang sbyor lam bar chad med pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17369: lam mchog mthong lam rnam smin tshe dbang gnyis kyi
NK077(tsu)001:17370: rigs gnyis su dbye ba'i sa dang 'du sa gcig
NK077(tsu)001:17371: yin pas lam 'ur rdo'i dkyil lta bu yin no
NK077(tsu)001:17374: de phyir phyag rgya chen po thob pa la bar
NK077(tsu)001:17375: chad med pa'i lam mchog zag med mthong lam gnyis
NK077(tsu)001:17378: tha ma tshogs bsgrubs nas thob pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:17380: 'du sa phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gcig po yin /
NK077(tsu)001:17381: da ni tshe dbang gi stong thun la /
NK077(tsu)001:17388: lam gong ma la sbyor tshul dang brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:17393: yo byad thabs kyi stobs las skyes pa gcig dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:17396: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK077(tsu)001:17398: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK077(tsu)001:17399: ces pa'i bar du gsung pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17400: rnam smin du gsung pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17401: rnam smin thob pa'i dus kyang gnyis su sbyor ba de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17404: de la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17406: ming bzhi dang bcas pa'i lus nyid rdo rje'i lus su 'grub /
NK077(tsu)001:17407: ming bzhi'i lhag ma'i lus kyi ngo bo ma spangs par gong ma la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17409: 'o na tshogs bsgrub pa tshe 'di la /
NK077(tsu)001:17410: tshe dbang thob la ma rag pa'i tshe dbang sgres po de yang tshe dbang du thal /
NK077(tsu)001:17411: lus de nyid mi 'dor ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17415: ma thob pa'i ngos nas thal zer /
NK077(tsu)001:17417: lus mi 'dor ba tsam gcig yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17418: lus dngos su yod pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:17419: zag pa'i sa bon cha phra ba yod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:17421: ci sto ste khyab pa ma grub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:17425: tshe dbang tsam gyi rnam grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17426: lam mchog yongs su bsgrub pa'i tshe dbang gi rnam grangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:17429: ngo bo sman dang thabs rig 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:17434: lam mchog yongs su bsgrub pa'i tshe dbang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:17435: phyi ma ni gzhung na gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:17437: ma 'gags pa phyag rgya'i dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17438: ma dmigs pa chos nyid kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17441: dgongs pa la mthar phyin gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17443: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid ci bzhin pa yul
NK077(tsu)001:17444: med rang gsal du rjes shes dang skye 'gags bral
NK077(tsu)001:17447: bdag gzhan gyi spyod pa gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:17449: tshe dbang de nyid kyi shes rab rnam gsum gyis kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17451: phrin las rnam lngas gzhan don rdzogs par byed pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17452: gshin rje la la'i zhal nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17453: stong gsum gyi stong chen po la 'dzam bu'i gling bye ba phrag brgya yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17454: de dag nyid 'dul ba yin gsung skad /
NK077(tsu)001:17456: stong gsum gyi stong chen po /
NK077(tsu)001:17458: bdun pa mngon par shes pa bdun nam nyi shu
NK077(tsu)001:17459: rtsa lngas stong gsum 'jig rten brgya tshun chad mkhyen
NK077(tsu)001:17461: tshe dbang de nyid gyi sa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17462: gong ma la sbyor tshul gnyis las thar chags pa ni tshe dbang gi tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:17463: kun 'gro sgrib pa dang bral ma thag /phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin kho na la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17465: de nyid kyi sa nas shes rab rnam gsum gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17466: kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag par byas pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:17467: lhun gyi grub pa'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba de ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17468: lhan cig skyes pa'i dri ma spang zhor dag pa de nyid la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17471: chos nyid dam tshig sman mthu yin //
NK077(tsu)001:17474: la la dag gi tshe dbang thod rgal dbang dag la gnyis su byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17475: gcig ni lhun grub rig 'dzin la sbyor zhing de bas blo che ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17476: lam gnyis bor nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor bar 'dod pa yang yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:17477: rgya dor cig char mthar 'gro ba //
NK077(tsu)001:17481: rgya dor cig char mthar 'gro ba //
NK077(tsu)001:17483: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17484: mthar 'gro zhes pas mthar lam pa kho na la sbyor ba yin gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:17485: lam gnyis dor nas sangs rgyas la sbyor ba'i tshig ma yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17486: lam gnyis dor nas sangs rgyas la sbyor ba'i thod rgal ba de mi 'thad gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17487: de yang rtsa rgyud le'u bcu gnyis pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17488: sangs rgyas la sbyor bar bshad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17490: gzhan yang spyir rig 'dzin la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:17492: rig 'dzin gang yin ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17493: rig 'dzin gsum gyi nges tshig la rtsod pa spangs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17495: dngos kyi phyi mo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17498: tshe dbang dngos sam phyi mo ni sprul sku ste skye shi la dbang thob pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:17499: phyag rgya chen po dngos ni longs sku ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17500: ye shes sku'i phyag rgyar bzhugs pas //
NK077(tsu)001:17502: chos sku kun tu bzang po rgyal ba drug pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17503: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pas so /
NK077(tsu)001:17504: de dag so so'i rig 'dzin lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17505: dang po la tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin cing gdung 'tshob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17506: zag med kyi mthong lam mo gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17508: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17509: zag med kyi sgom lam pa'o //
