NK077(tsu)001:17510: de lhun grub kyi rig 'dzin ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17512: de yang tshe dbang gi skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:17513: mi gtongs bzungs la ming thob pa /
NK077(tsu)001:17516: cha byad rgyal ba nyid du ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17518: snga rabs pa rnams rig 'dzin 'chad cing /
NK077(tsu)001:17519: dngos sam phyi mo ngos ma zin pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17520: pha myes ngo ma shes par bu tsa'i cho 'brang 'chad pa lta bu'o gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:17521: gnyis pa nges tshig gi brtsad pa spang la gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:17522: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyis nges tshig ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17523: kha cig tshe la dbang thob ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17524: bsgres rgud med pa yin zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17525: de ltar phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17526: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gnyis kyang tshe dbang du thal te /
NK077(tsu)001:17527: shin tu yang tshe la dbang thob pa'i phyir zhe na 'di don ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17528: sbyor lam man chad ni tshe la dbang ma thob la /
NK077(tsu)001:17529: rnam smin gyi ngo bo la /
NK077(tsu)001:17531: lus 'dor dgos pas tshe dbang du ma grags so //
NK077(tsu)001:17532: zag med kyi mthong lam yan chad na /
NK077(tsu)001:17533: tshe la bsring bstung gi dbang yod pa'i 'go zug pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17536: lhun grub pa gnyis ni tshe dbang thob par ma zad /
NK077(tsu)001:17537: bskal par gnas kyang bskul mi dgos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17538: dbang bsgyur zhing brtan pa yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17539: tshe dbang du ming mi 'dogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17540: longs sku dang lhun grub kyi rig 'dzin pa la brtags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17541: phyag rgya chen po'i nges tshig ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17542: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs zhes pa /
NK077(tsu)001:17543: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17545: rang lus gdod nas phyag rgya che //
NK077(tsu)001:17547: de ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17548: phyag rgya chen por thal te /
NK077(tsu)001:17549: rgyal ba'i skur yod pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:17551: rigs lnga'i cha lugs su yod cing 'dzin la /
NK077(tsu)001:17553: drug pa'i cha lugs su yod pas mi 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17554: lhun grub rig 'dzin ni sku lnga lhun grub kun bzang gi rigs 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17555: de yang cha byad rgyal ba nyid du ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17556: zhes pa la sogs pas gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:17557: lha mi rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:17559: 'o na rgyu'i sa dang po rab dga' yang /
NK077(tsu)001:17560: lha mii'i rgyal po'i cha lugs su bzhugs par bshad pas khyad med du 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17561: zhes brgal tshig khung nas phyungs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:17562: lan dkyus kyis 'debs pa ni lha dang mi dang zhes pa nas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17563: zhes pa'i bar gyi myur te /
NK077(tsu)001:17564: cha lugs dang mthong lam tsam du 'dra mod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17569: zag med kyi yon tan 'byung ba'i cha chung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17570: rgyu 'bras dbyer med kyi don mthong la /
NK077(tsu)001:17571: 'bras bu'i mthong lam bsod nams gter gyi sa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17572: dbyer med mthong bas yon tan 'byung ba'i stobs che bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17573: dper na zhing sa gshin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17574: mi gshin pa'i ston thog bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17575: de gnyis kyis khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17581: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma lhag bcas tshe dbang ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17583: zhag sum cu phrag drug la sogs pa'i dus kyi
NK077(tsu)001:17584: grangs dang ldan pas tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pas rnal
NK077(tsu)001:17585: 'byor ba'i lta ba dang dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:17586: gsal ba dang / tshogs kyis spyod pa a li ka li la spyad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17587: bsgrub pa la brtson 'grus bskyed pa chen po dang ldan pa'i stobs kyis sbyangs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:17588: lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang dang //
NK077(tsu)001:17589: gsang ba'i yo byad a li ste sbyor ba thabs
NK077(tsu)001:17590: lam rkyang ba las byung ba thabs kyi tshe dbang
NK077(tsu)001:17591: dang / steng 'og gi rlung bzung ba'i thabs kyis
NK077(tsu)001:17592: nus pa'i stobs rdzogs pa las skyes pa sgrol ma
NK077(tsu)001:17593: rlung las gyur pa'i tshe dbang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17594: lam sbyangs pa de dag las gzhan pa'i sman gyi sgo nas tshe dbang bsgrub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17595: dza gad 'brang rgyas la sogs pa'i yo byad la
NK077(tsu)001:17596: brten nas tshe bsgrub pas 'grub pas 'grub pa'i rtags
NK077(tsu)001:17598: dngos grub la rol cing longs spyod pa'i nus mthu
NK077(tsu)001:17599: las 'byung ba bdud rtsi sman las gyur pa'i tshe
NK077(tsu)001:17600: dbang dang / de dag rang rang gi thob par
NK077(tsu)001:17601: byed pa'i thabs sam rgyus phye bas tshe dbang bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:17602: po so so tha dad pa byung na /
NK077(tsu)001:17604: 'dir tshogs sbyor gyi lam sbyangs pa'i stobs las skyes pa'i tshe dbang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17605: tshe dbang gzhan gsum po las mchog tu gyur pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:17606: zag pa med pa'i rig 'dzin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17607: gong gi gzhan pa'i yo byad rtags ldan pa /
NK077(tsu)001:17610: lam mchog tshe dbang gi rgyu la ngos bzung thabs rgyu /
NK077(tsu)001:17612: tshe dbang gsum pa'i rgyud la ngos bzung /
NK077(tsu)001:17615: bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17620: rang thob pa sangs rgyas la sbyor ba'i dus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17621: tshe dbang gi ngo bo dang don dang ming gi rnam grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17622: lta ba dang dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17623: bdag gzhan gyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17624: mngon shes kyis gzigs nas cho 'phrul bzhi pa don mdzad tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17625: thar chag thod rgal gnyis kyis 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17626: de ltar bzhi tshan gnyis te brgyad kyi lus rnam
NK077(tsu)001:17627: bzhag mdor bstan pa'i rnam grangs kyis tshe dbang rig
NK077(tsu)001:17628: 'dzin gyi don yongs su rdzogs par bshad par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:17631: tshe dbang thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17633: 'di las nang tshigs su bcad na gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17634: de la spyir bstan ni nges don du rgyu 'bras dbyer med kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17635: lam pa gang dag 'bras bu thob par byed pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:17636: thabs dang 'bras bu la mos pa drang ba'i don
NK077(tsu)001:17637: tsam du tshe dbang thob pa'i rgyur bya ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:17639: rig 'dzin gsum pa'i rgyu gong ma'i rig 'dzin thob par byed pa'i thabs sam /
NK077(tsu)001:17641: nges don du zag bcas tshogs bsgrub yan chad kyi
NK077(tsu)001:17642: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab rnam pa gsum yin
NK077(tsu)001:17643: pas / de dag la rim dang cig char gyi blo goms par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17644: bye brag so sor bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:17645: de yang lam cig char ba'i dbang du /
NK077(tsu)001:17647: zhes pa gong du blang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17648: bden pa gnyis su med pa lta bas chos nyid mnyam pa'i don ma nor ba gcig chod du /
NK077(tsu)001:17649: thos pa'i shes rab kyis thos /
NK077(tsu)001:17650: de bsam pa'i shes rab kyis rtogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:17651: bden pa gnyis med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi dgag bsgrub dang bral bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17652: dus dang gnas skabs kun tu chos nyid mtha' bral
NK077(tsu)001:17653: yang pa chen por cig char du sgom pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:17654: la / lam rim gyis pa'i dbang du rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17660: lam tshogs sbyor gyi rnal 'byor lnga po /
NK077(tsu)001:17661: lta ba'i skabs su thos bsam gyi shes rab kyis rtogs /
NK077(tsu)001:17662: ting nge 'dzin rim gyis goms par gyur nas tshogs bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17663: zla ba dang zhag grangs rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i le'u dgu pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17664: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK077(tsu)001:17665: la sogs gsung pa bzhin du tshogs bsgrub par byed pa blo che bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17666: 'bras bu ni tshe la dbang ba grub nas skye
NK077(tsu)001:17667: 'chi med pa rdo rje lta bu'i lus su 'grub
NK077(tsu)001:17669: de yang lus 'di mi dor te /
NK077(tsu)001:17673: las kyi lus te ming bzhi dang ldan pa'i lus
NK077(tsu)001:17674: nyid ma spangs par skye 'jig med pa rdo rje'i
NK077(tsu)001:17679: tshe dbang thob pa'i dus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17681: bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs ni sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam /
NK077(tsu)001:17682: 'bring zla ba bcu gnyis te lo gcig gam /
NK077(tsu)001:17683: zla ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis sam /
NK077(tsu)001:17684: tha mas kyang zla ba bcu drug ste lo gcig zla ba bzhi po dag gis /
NK077(tsu)001:17685: blo dang brtson 'grus rab 'bring tha ma'i rim pa
NK077(tsu)001:17686: gzhung nas bshad pa ci bzhin du ma nor bar
NK077(tsu)001:17687: nyams su blang zhing bsgrub na /
NK077(tsu)001:17689: tshe la rang dbang bsgyur cing lus mi 'dor ba
NK077(tsu)001:17690: sprul sku'i rig 'dzin pas rig 'dzin gyi dam pa
NK077(tsu)001:17691: lam mchog tshe dbang 'grub par 'gyur ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17692: bdag don du lam gong ma la sbyor te sangs rgyas pa'i dus so //
NK077(tsu)001:17694: rgyu lam dang 'bras bu sangs rgyas gnyis snga phyi
NK077(tsu)001:17695: dbyer med dus gcig tu gzhi la ye gdod ma
NK077(tsu)001:17697: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems nyid la rang dbang thob par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:17698: de'i rang don gyi tshe tshad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17699: tshe lo brgya pa'i dbang du lo brgya phrag bcu dang drug ste stong drug brgya gnas pa'i bar /
NK077(tsu)001:17700: lo brgya brgya nas byis pa gzhon nu lo brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:17701: lon pa dag tu bsnur zhing 'jig rten du gnas
NK077(tsu)001:17702: nas / mthar da ltar gyi lus 'di ma bor
NK077(tsu)001:17703: par yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa
NK077(tsu)001:17704: la khyer nas 'gro ba'i nus pa dang ldan pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:17705: nas / // gsum pa ngo bo la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:17707: zag med rdo rje'i lus su gyur cing tshe gcig la sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17709: don mthong ba lta ba dang 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams mthar phyin pa'i rjes la /
NK077(tsu)001:17710: tshogs spyod bsgrub pa'i dngos grub kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17711: lus kyi zag pa med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17712: lus 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus su gyur pas rgas rgud dang 'chi ba med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17713: khams kyi zag pa med pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17714: lus kyi zag pa khams las byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17715: bshang lci la sogs pa mi 'byung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:17716: khams kyi bde dog gtan nas med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17717: skye gnas kyi zag pa zad pa ni skye ba la rang dbang bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17718: las dbang gi srid pa gsum du mi skye ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17719: lus kyi skye 'jig med pa 'byung ba rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:17720: lus su 'gyur ba tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:17721: mthong ba'i chos tshe 'di la mya ngan las 'das
NK077(tsu)001:17722: / lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas pa la 'gro ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17723: skabs 'dir zag pa'i don la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:17724: zag pa yod med kyi sa mtshams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17728: kha gcig tshogs bsgrub man chad zag bcas /
NK077(tsu)001:17729: tshe dbang yan chad zag med /
NK077(tsu)001:17730: rnam smin rtsod pa yin zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17732: rnam smin phung gsum yin zer ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17735: mthong lam rnam smin yan chad zag med du bzhed do //
NK077(tsu)001:17736: gnyis pa zag pa'i go ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17740: theg pa thun mong ba ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:17741: las dang nyon mongs pa gnyis la zag pa zhes zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:17742: zag pa dang bcas pa thams cad sdug bsngal /
NK077(tsu)001:17744: las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad sdug bsngal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17747: zag pa dang 'dra ba'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:17752: las nyon gyi rgyud gang tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:17754: bu ga dgu nas 'khor ba'i phung po lnga zag par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17758: ci ltar phung po 'dzin pa de //
NK077(tsu)001:17759: de srid de la ngar 'dzin rten //
NK077(tsu)001:17760: ngar 'dzin yod na'ang las yin te //
NK077(tsu)001:17761: de la yang ni skye ba yin //
NK077(tsu)001:17764: las dang nyon mongs pa dang bcas pas khams gsum du 'pho zhing 'dzag pa'i phyir na zag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17766: zag pa dang bcas pa ni sdug bsngal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17769: gang zag gi bdag gi skabs nas gang zag lnga phung rgyu yin /
NK077(tsu)001:17772: las dang nyon mongs pas gang nas 'bras bu phung por zag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17775: gsum pa zag pa'i dbye ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17779: des bskyed pa'i chos rnams su bshad do //
NK077(tsu)001:17784: zag pa dang bcas pa thams cad sdug bsngal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17789: kha cig /khams kyi zas la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17790: bshang lci la sogs dam rdzas lnga 'dor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17794: lus kyi zag pa zad par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:17795: khams kyi zas dang bral bshang lci med pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:17797: bshang lci dor ba med pa khams kyi zag med yin /
NK077(tsu)001:17798: 'dir ni las dang nyon mongs pa'i phra rag kyi kun nas bslangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17799: 'khor ba lus rang dbang med par blang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17801: las dang nyon mongs pa phra rags kyi kun nas bslangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17802: 'khor ba'i bde sdug rang dbang med par myong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17804: las dang nyon mongs pa phra rags kyis kun nas
NK077(tsu)001:17805: bslang nas skye gnas bzhir rang dbang med par 'jug
NK077(tsu)001:17808: phyi dang nang gi zag pa rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:17809: thams cad thams cad kun zag par //
NK077(tsu)001:17812: rtogs pa'i rtsa ba phyi nang gi //
NK077(tsu)001:17813: kun nas zag pa rnam gnyis yin //
NK077(tsu)001:17815: phyi nang gnyis su yang bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17816: mngon pa kun las btus pa las //
NK077(tsu)001:17817: zag pa'i sgo drug tu bshad de /
NK077(tsu)001:17818: zag pa de'i bdag nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17821: zag pa'i rjes su 'brang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17822: zag pa'i rjes su mthun pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17823: zag pa'i rgyu las 'byung ba'i phyir zag bcas su lta'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17825: de la zag pa'i bdag nyid ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17826: nyon mongs nye nyon rnams so //
NK077(tsu)001:17829: mtshungs ldan grogs su 'grel pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17831: nyon mongs nye nyon rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17832: lhan cig tu 'byung ba'i sems sems byung rnams so //
NK077(tsu)001:17834: nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis 'byung ba'i las so //
NK077(tsu)001:17836: khams gsum gzhan gyi bag chags la /
NK077(tsu)001:17837: gzhan gyi nyon mongs kyi gnas ngan len dang ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17838: rjes mthun ni tshogs lam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:17840: dgra bcom lhag bcas kyi phung po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17841: des na 'og ma lnga ni bcas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17843: gzhan yang khams gsum du zag pas zag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17844: zhes slob dpon seng ge bzang pos gsung pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17846: dper na rma'i bu ga nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17848: chu ser la sogs pa zag pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:17849: skye ched drug gi rma nas /
NK077(tsu)001:17851: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa zag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17856: ma rig pa'i zag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17859: 'dod khams su gtogs pa'i nyon mongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:17860: gnyis pa gzugs med khams su gtogs pa'i nyon mongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:17861: gsum pa khams gsum char du gtogs pa'i nyon mongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:17862: bzhi pa lta ba lnga la bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17864: lam ma gtogs pa'i 'dus byas rnams zag bcas gang phyir de dag las /
NK077(tsu)001:17865: zag rnams kun tu rgyas par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:17867: des na zag pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17869: rtog pa'i rtsa ba phyi nang gi //
NK077(tsu)001:17870: kun nas zag pa rnam pa lnga //
NK077(tsu)001:17873: nye ba'i nyon mongs rnams te /
NK077(tsu)001:17874: des khams gsum du zag pa'i phyir zag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17877: skyon las grol zhing cho 'phrul bzhi rdzogs pa'i tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17879: nyon mongs pa lnga'i 'jigs pa kun dang bral shing cho 'phrul bzhi mngon shes drug rdzogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17880: cha lugs kyis chos ston tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17882: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi cha byad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:17883: lha dang mi'i rgyal po'i rigs tshangs pa dang brgya
NK077(tsu)001:17884: byin dang 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:17885: pa skye ba rnam par dag pa rang dbang can
NK077(tsu)001:17886: 'dzin cing / 'dod khams kyi lha rigs drug dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17887: mi'i dbang po 'khor lo bsgyur ba la sogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17888: gzugs khams kyi lha tshangs pa la sogs pa cha lugs su gnas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17889: de rnams kyi skye ba rnam par dag pa rang dbang can /
NK077(tsu)001:17891: zha grum la sogs pa med pa 'dzin pa yin mod kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:17892: 'o na de rnams dang khyad med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:17893: kyang zhes pas khyad par yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:17894: de dag khyad par ni sa la gnas pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:17895: mi gnas par 'gyur ba'i khyad par yod pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:17896: no // de yang rgyu'i theg pa mthong lam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17897: tshe dbang la khyad par yod dam med zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:17898: rgyu'o theg pa'i mthong lam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17899: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17900: mthong lam tsam du skal pa mnyam yang /
NK077(tsu)001:17901: dgongs pa sa brgyad pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:17902: gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang skal mnyam par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17903: de bzhin du rgyu'i theg pa'i sa brgyad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17904: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gnyis sgom lam tsam du skal ba mnyam yang /
NK077(tsu)001:17905: dgongs pa rgyu'i mthar lam pa dang mnyam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:17906: rgyu'i theg pa'i sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17908: mthar lam tsam du skal ba mnyam yang dgongs pa kun tu 'od dang mnyam pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17910: de yang dang po'i dang po dang //
NK077(tsu)001:17911: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog de //
NK077(tsu)001:17912: brgyad pa'i sa dang skal ba mnyam //
NK077(tsu)001:17913: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam med //
NK077(tsu)001:17914: dgongs spyod rgya mtshos khyad par 'phags //
NK077(tsu)001:17916: cha byad lha dang mi'i rgyal po'i cha byad de nyid kyi gdul bya de'i rig 'dzin can la /
NK077(tsu)001:17917: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi chos ston pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:17918: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku'i rgyal tshab byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17919: de ltar na tshe la dbang ba'i rig de'i /
NK077(tsu)001:17920: rtsa ba'i lus lha mi skye ba khyad par can
NK077(tsu)001:17921: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i lus su khyer ba'o
NK077(tsu)001:17922: // de yang sgyu 'phrul gyi bshad rgyud rdo rje las /
NK077(tsu)001:17923: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa med //
NK077(tsu)001:17924: lha mi skye ba 'dzin mod kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:17925: zhing dang longs spyod dag pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:17926: gang nas gang du mnyam par sbyor //
NK077(tsu)001:17927: rdo rje rig pa 'dzin gyi sku //
NK077(tsu)001:17928: zhing khams kun la gnas par byed //
NK077(tsu)001:17930: zag pa zad pa rdo rje'i lus //
NK077(tsu)001:17932: bde ba chen por lung thob pas //
NK077(tsu)001:17933: zag bcas bslab pa'i chos dang bral //
NK077(tsu)001:17935: bsgrub pa'i nus pa gang ldan pa //
NK077(tsu)001:17937: 'jigs pa lnga bral zag pa zad //
NK077(tsu)001:17938: dbang bsgyur gsum la dbang thob pas //
NK077(tsu)001:17939: bde ba'i longs spyod dpag tu med //
NK077(tsu)001:17942: 'dul ba'i dbang gis ma nges te //
NK077(tsu)001:17944: zhing la dbang bsgyur sprul pa'i lus //
NK077(tsu)001:17945: ting 'dzin longs spyod dpag tu med //
NK077(tsu)001:17947: skyon bral yon tan rdzogs shing 'dul zhing gi tshad dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17949: dper na gang dag dug sbrul gyi mi 'jigs pa'i rtsi ma gi 'chang ba ltar du /
NK077(tsu)001:17950: tshe la dbang bsgyur bas 'jigs lnga sogs bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17952: 'tsho ba med dang mi basngagasa 'khor ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:17953: 'khor gyi 'jigs bral 'chi ba'i bag chags spangs //
NK077(tsu)001:17956: mi basngagasa pa'i 'jigs pa dang 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi 'jigs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17960: khams kyi zas dang phral zhing zag pa med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:17961: bde bas rgyas la nam mkha' mdzod la mnga' brnyes
NK077(tsu)001:17964: bdag gi 'dzin pa med cing chos kun mnyam pa
NK077(tsu)001:17965: nyid du rtogs pas gzhan gyi nyes skyon la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:17966: pa'i tshig ci brjod kyang nyes pa med pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:17968: nyon mongs pa gtan nas grol zhing 'khor ba la dbugs phyung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:17969: 'khor bar 'khyams kyi dog pa'i 'jigs pa med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17971: shes rab stobs chen du gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:17972: sha ri'i bu la sogs pas dus gcig tu dris kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:17973: the tshom gyis lan dus gcig la theb pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17975: rig pa la dbang thob cing /
NK077(tsu)001:17976: rdo rje'i lus su gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:17978: de yang sogs khong du 'khor ba'i nyes skyon thams cad dang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17979: mngon shes drug dang cho 'phrul bzhi po 'di dag
NK077(tsu)001:17980: yan lag nyer lnga dang nyi shu la sogs kun
NK077(tsu)001:17981: gyi rtsal dang grangs yongs su rdzogs shing tshe'am rig
NK077(tsu)001:17982: pa dang skye ba la rang dbang bsgyur ba'i stobs
NK077(tsu)001:17983: kyi lha mi'i rgyal po'am skye ba rnam dag khyad
NK077(tsu)001:17985: gzhan don du stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig
NK077(tsu)001:17986: rten gyi khams gyi gling bzhi pa phrag brgya yis
NK077(tsu)001:17987: gdul bya rnams 'dul bar byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:17988: rgyu yi theg pa chen po yis sa dang po rab dga' dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17989: tshe dbang gnyis mthong lam tsam du skal ba mnyam pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:17990: don gyi mi mnyam pa ni gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:17991: sku tshe'am bzhugs pa'i tshad bstan pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:17993: bdag don du brgya phrag bcu drug dang /
NK077(tsu)001:17995: bdag gi don gyi phyir thos bsam la sogs pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:17996: lam don du gnyer ba'i 'bras bu thob pa'i dus
NK077(tsu)001:17997: ni / lo brgya phrag bcu drug stong dang drug
NK077(tsu)001:17998: brgya tshe yis rang don rdzogs nas 'bras bu la
NK077(tsu)001:17999: ni / sbyor ba'o // gzhan don du nges pa med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18001: gdul bya gzhan gyi don du tshe la rang dbang thob pa yin pa'i phyir tshad bzung du med /
NK077(tsu)001:18002: bzhugs par bzhed na yang dus bskal pa grangs med
NK077(tsu)001:18003: pa'i bar du 'jig rten gyi khams su gnas par
NK077(tsu)001:18004: gyur kyang / bsgres rgud mi mnga' ba sku ni
NK077(tsu)001:18005: shin tu gzhan pa lo brgyad pa'i tshul du snang
NK077(tsu)001:18006: gyur kyang / ste / de yang lo brgyad lon pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18007: lo brgyad len pa bsgyur nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18008: rtsa ba'i lus la skye 'chi med kyang gdul bya rtag 'dzin can dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18009: le lo can 'dul ba'i dus kyi sprul pa'i lus la 'chi 'pho ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18010: mi 'dul na 'dug par yang byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:18011: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gnyis spyir tshe dbang tsam gyi grangs phyes te khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18012: khyad par du lam mchog bsgrub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18017: tshe dbang gi ngo bo'i rnam grangs la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:18019: sman gyi sgo nas bcud lan la brten nas tshe ring bar 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:18022: rdo rje'i tshe bsgrub pa la brten nas sman mar zos pas tshe ring bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18025: 'og sgo rgya mo la brten te /
NK077(tsu)001:18026: thig le dbab bzlog pa tsam la brten nas tshe ring bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18027: rnal 'byor sgrol ma ni steng sgo 'khor lo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18028: sgrol ma rlung la brten te /
NK077(tsu)001:18029: tshe dbang gi rig 'dzin thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18031: 'o skol la nyin zhag 'phrug re re rlung nyi
NK077(tsu)001:18032: khri gcig stong drug brgya rgyu ba'i rlung grangs ni
NK077(tsu)001:18033: thim tsa na 'chi ba yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:18036: bar du rlung bzung zhing sgom pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18037: rlung grangs nur bas 'gog pa snyoms 'jug ltar tshe bskal pa'i bar du gnas pa 'ong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18040: phal cher des mi mdo ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18041: chu tshod la sogs pa zin pa 'ong ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18042: lam tshogs rdzogs pa ni lta ba rtogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:18043: rtogs pa'i don la rim dang cig char gyi zag
NK077(tsu)001:18044: med mngon sum du thob pa'i rig 'dzin dang rim
NK077(tsu)001:18048: dbang bcu'i dang por tshe dbang thob par 'dra zhing mtshungs mod ces bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18049: kyang zhes pa mi mthun pa ston pa'i tshig rgyan te /
NK077(tsu)001:18050: lam mchog 'di nyid kyi rig 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18051: rig 'dzin gzhan gsum po la khyad yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18054: tshe la dbang bas 'khor bar ci srid bzhugs //
NK077(tsu)001:18055: skye la dbang bas rigs kyi sprul skur ston //
NK077(tsu)001:18056: yo byad dbang bas 'dod yon lnga la rol //
NK077(tsu)001:18057: smon lam dbang bas bdag gzhan mos bzhin snang //
NK077(tsu)001:18058: rdzu 'phrul dbang bas rdzu 'phrul cho 'phrul ston //
NK077(tsu)001:18059: chos la dbang bas chos skad so sor sgrogs //
NK077(tsu)001:18060: ye shes dbang bas shes bya kun ma rmongs //
NK077(tsu)001:18061: sems la dbang bas ting 'dzin 'bum phrag rol //
NK077(tsu)001:18062: las la dbang bas 'byor pa'i phrin las mdzad //
NK077(tsu)001:18064: de nyid mthu yis zag mi zag /ces pa bzhis /
NK077(tsu)001:18066: byin rlabs kyi mthu la che chung dang //
NK077(tsu)001:18068: bskyod pa rgyu'i khyad par dang thob bya'i ngo bo la mtho dman dang zag pa yod med dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18074: tshe dbang bzhi po de dag nyid la nus mthu
NK077(tsu)001:18075: che chung yod de gsum pos bdag don kun 'gro
NK077(tsu)001:18077: rdzu 'phrul nyi shu sogs ston mi nus la /
NK077(tsu)001:18078: 'dis spang nus shing rdzu 'phrul nyi shu sogs ston nus /
NK077(tsu)001:18079: gzhan don sprul sku'i rgyal tshab nus mi nus yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18082: gsum po la zag pa yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:18083: lta dgongs kyi rtsis ma zin par /
NK077(tsu)001:18084: 'phral gyi thabs rkyang pa las byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18086: zag pa zad pa mthong ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18088: rgyu dang zhes pa gsum po sman dang thabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18090: 'di ni theg mchog gi lam nyams su blangs pas gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18093: gsum po ni zag bcas pas skye bo'i sa las ma thob la /
NK077(tsu)001:18094: 'di ni zag pa med pas 'phags pa'i go 'phang thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18096: rgyu dang ngo bos zag bcas zag med rnam pa gnyis su 'gyur ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18099: rgyu dang ngo bo gnyis la khyad yod pa de bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:18100: lta dgongs la khyad yod med smos ci dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:18102: zag med kyi dgongs pa med la /
NK077(tsu)001:18103: 'di ni zag med kyi chos nyid rang mtshan la mnga' brnyes pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18105: spyod smos ci dgos zhes pa /
NK077(tsu)001:18107: bdag gzhan gyi don rgya chen po spyod mi nus la /
NK077(tsu)001:18108: lam mchog rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang zhes bya ba 'dis ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18109: rang don du rigs mthun mchog rgya sprul pa las
NK077(tsu)001:18110: chos nyan cing kun 'gro'i sgrib pa 'joms nus la
NK077(tsu)001:18111: / gzhan don du sprul sku'i rgyal tshabs nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18114: rlung la sogs pa las grub pa ste lam mchog rdzogs pa'i rig 'dzin pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18115: khyad par du lam mchog rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang gi rnam grangs la drug /bgrang /
NK077(tsu)001:18116: lhag bcas kyis mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18118: lam mchog la'ang yon tan gyi mtshan gyi rnam grangs kyi cha nas brjod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18119: lhag ma'i lus te gzugs kyi phung po dang ming bzhi'i phung por bcas pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:18120: bskal pa grangs med la sogs pa rang ci tsam
NK077(tsu)001:18121: gnas par 'dod pa la rang dbang thob pas tshe
NK077(tsu)001:18122: la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:18126: las kyi lus dang bcas nas mya ngan las 'das
NK077(tsu)001:18127: pas lhag bcas kyis mya ngan las 'das pa zhes
NK077(tsu)001:18128: bya'o // zag ldog med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18130: zag pa gsum po la sogs kun zad pa rig
NK077(tsu)001:18131: 'dzin chen po 'di spyod pa ci ltar spyad kyang
NK077(tsu)001:18134: sa brgyad pa'i rtogs pa rgyud thog na 'khrungs /
NK077(tsu)001:18135: nyon yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes mngon du gyur pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18136: ldog pa med pa'i don yin /
NK077(tsu)001:18137: sa bdun pa man chad la byang chub sems dpa' ldog pa'i skyon yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18138: theg dman nyan rang gi ltung 'jigs 'ong ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18139: sha ri'i bu'i gtam rgyud lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18140: ci ltar sa brgyad ma thob par /
NK077(tsu)001:18141: de srid theg pa dman gyi 'jigs zhes gsung pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18143: sa brgyad lon nas da rung ldog nyen yod /
NK077(tsu)001:18145: sa brgyad pa mthar phyin nas ldog pa'i lung ma yin /
NK077(tsu)001:18146: sa bdun mthar phyin nas brgyad pa g+ho zug gi gang zag de la dgongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18147: dbugs phyin cing mthong lam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18149: tshe la rang dbang thob pas 'khor la dbugs phyung ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:18150: dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18151: lam las skyes pa'i tshe dbang gi skabs 'dir bden
NK077(tsu)001:18152: pa bar ma 'grib pa med pa la 'phel ba
NK077(tsu)001:18153: yod par mthong lam pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18154: zag bcas kyi skabs su 'phel 'grib can gyi mthong lam yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18155: sprin bar nyi 'dra gsal yid ches /
NK077(tsu)001:18157: rgyal ba'i sras dang shing sna'i me //
NK077(tsu)001:18158: rang mtshan mthong yang stobs ma rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:18160: sangs rgyas kyi sa na 'phel 'grib med pa'i ye shes mngon du gyur pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18166: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid la mkhas lta
NK077(tsu)001:18167: ba rtogs rkyen ting nge 'dzin gyi goms spyod pa
NK077(tsu)001:18168: rmad du byung ba'i tshe la dbang ba'i rig pa
NK077(tsu)001:18169: 'dzin pa yi dam gyi lha mi bskyod pa la
NK077(tsu)001:18171: rdo rje'i rig 'dzin pa la sogs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18172: des na rang rig mi gtong bas rig 'dzin lta
NK077(tsu)001:18173: dgongs kyis gzungs la rig 'dzin gyi ming thob pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:18174: // gzhan yang yon tan gyi cha nas mtshan gyi rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab ste //
NK077(tsu)001:18175: lung ston cing dbang bskur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18177: rgyal bas dngos su sa khams te khyod kyi zhing 'di yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18178: zhes lung ston thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18179: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang gi gsang mtshan rdo rje che ge mo zhes bos nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18181: rig 'dzin pa nyid gzhan don du rnam 'phrul ma nges pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18183: lta ba mthong zhing ting nge 'dzin goms pas 'bras
NK077(tsu)001:18184: bu mthar phyin pa dang ldan pa'i rang gi rig
NK077(tsu)001:18185: pa nyid / phyi nang med pa'i snang ba rig
NK077(tsu)001:18186: pa 'dzin pa'i gnas gdul bya rigs dang mthun par
NK077(tsu)001:18187: pa nyid / snang tshul dang / gnas la nges
NK077(tsu)001:18188: pa med skye ba dang cha byad gdul ba'i don
NK077(tsu)001:18189: gyis 'gyur zhing cir yang ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:18190: lnga pa dgongs pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:18191: mi dmigs pa chos nyid kyi dgongs pa dang ma 'gags pa phyag rgya'i dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18192: dgongs pa la gnas pa'i dus so //
NK077(tsu)001:18195: dgongs pa mthong bya mthong byed med pa chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:18196: mngon sum du mthong ba'i ngang la gnas pa'i tshul
NK077(tsu)001:18198: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams bdag nyid chen por snang ba'i phyir dmigs bya dmigs byed med pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:18199: chos can kun yul yul can du mi mthong chos
NK077(tsu)001:18200: nyid kyang yul dang yul can du mi mthong ngo
NK077(tsu)001:18201: // sangs rgyas thugs nyid kyang yul du dngos por mi mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:18202: snod bcud yul dang yul can du mi mthong zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:18203: de ltar gnyis med yul bral du gang mthong ba /
NK077(tsu)001:18204: de ni yang dag pa'i don chos nyid kyi bden pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18205: de bas na rna bas sgra thos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18207: reg pa la sogs pa kun gnyis med yul bral
NK077(tsu)001:18208: du shes pas lam gol med kyi mthong lam mo
NK077(tsu)001:18209: // snga ma'i rgyus chos nyid mngon sum du mthong zhing zag pa med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18211: rgyu shes pa'i lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18212: rkyen 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzhi bar chad med
NK077(tsu)001:18213: par tshogs bsgrub pa las tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:18215: de'i phyir chos kun rang gi shes rab mngon sum
NK077(tsu)001:18216: du lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang lam mchog tshe dbang
NK077(tsu)001:18217: ni / rig pa la rang dbang thob nas sngon bzhin lus ma dor bar sangs rgyas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18218: zag gsum lus khams skye gnas kyis zag pa lam
NK077(tsu)001:18219: mchog gi tshe dbang 'di la med ces pa tshe
NK077(tsu)001:18220: dbang gzhan gsum la zur zos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18221: ma 'gags pa phyi'i dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18223: sngon 'chad zag bcas kyi skabs bzhin ting nge 'dzin la lam gyi rtsol ba'i 'du byed med de /
NK077(tsu)001:18224: de'i rgyu mtshan ci yin zhe na rtsol ba de'i don la re ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18225: dog pa'i 'dzin chags dang bral bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18226: blo che chung gi dbang gis /
NK077(tsu)001:18227: chung na rim pa sgom pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:18228: che na rim med par cig char du rdzogs tshul
NK077(tsu)001:18229: gyis sangs rgyas stong dang nyi khri bzhi stong gi
NK077(tsu)001:18230: dal la sogs / grangs mang po'i 'khor rang gi rig pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:18231: gsal bar rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin la
NK077(tsu)001:18232: gnas nas zhi khro'i dal rnam pa gnyis kyis rang
NK077(tsu)001:18233: bzhin gyi don thams cad 'grub par mdzad do //
NK077(tsu)001:18234: dgongs pa la gnas pa'i dus so //
NK077(tsu)001:18236: dgongs pa de'i ming ni tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:18237: rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ba yin te
NK077(tsu)001:18238: / rang don du lo brgya phrag bcu drug gi cha rdzogs kyi dus kyi bar du /
NK077(tsu)001:18239: rang gi shes rab gsum la goms par byed nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18241: mthar lam lhun grub gnyis rim par thob pa'i mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:18242: yis skad cig ma gcig gi cha yi rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:18243: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'jom pas dpa' bor
NK077(tsu)001:18244: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sbyor ba'o
NK077(tsu)001:18246: goms byas gnyis thob mtha' skad cig /ces pa 'di la tshe dbang rig 'dzin thar chag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18247: phyag chen la sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18248: thod rgal bas lhun grub la sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18249: de bas blo che ba gcig sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor bar gsung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18250: kha cig dbang bsgyur rig nyid las //
NK077(tsu)001:18251: bcu drug thun gyi sku la rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:18252: kha cig phyag rgya chen po las //
NK077(tsu)001:18253: bla med kun tu bzang por 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:18255: drug pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18257: bdag don du shes rab gsum gyis kun 'gro'i sgrib pa sbyangs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18260: tshe dbang nang na slob dpon bca' ste rang bas
NK077(tsu)001:18261: dgongs pa mchog tu gyur pa la chos nyan pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:18262: // gzhan yang phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18263: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku rnams las //
NK077(tsu)001:18264: gsang sngags kyi don zab mo zag med kyi thos pa'i shes rab kyi thob par byas /
NK077(tsu)001:18265: bsam pa'i shes rab kyi don rig cing rtogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18266: sgom pa'i shes rab kyi rgyud sbyongs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18267: dper na dkyus sar phyin pa'i rta cang shes zhugs
NK077(tsu)001:18268: nas dkyus g+hos mthong bas 'jug shes pa bzhin 'dir
NK077(tsu)001:18269: kun du 'gro ba'i sgrib pa dag par byed cing
NK077(tsu)001:18270: / lam gong ma rnams kha 'og tu tshud par
NK077(tsu)001:18271: byed pa ni bdag po'i don gyi spyod pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:18272: / no // gzhan don yon tan dang bcas pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18278: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18279: kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul te cho 'phrul bzhi po de dag dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18280: mngon par shes pa drug shes shing /
NK077(tsu)001:18282: dbang bsgyur ram mi ldog pa de nyid kyi ming can la ldan pa yis /
NK077(tsu)001:18283: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i lam sa de'i rtsa ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:18284: lus skye 'chi med pa rdo rje lta bu'i sku
NK077(tsu)001:18285: las ma g.yos par sprul pa'i lus lha mi'i rgyal
NK077(tsu)001:18287: bdag gzhan gyi gdul bya ma lus pa'i don phrin
NK077(tsu)001:18288: las rnam bzhi'i sgo nas byed pa thams cad yongs
NK077(tsu)001:18289: su rdzogs par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18292: cho 'phrul bzhis gzhan don bya ba la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:18294: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyi don mdzad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18296: cho 'phral bzhi'i thog ma'i rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyis don spyod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:18298: ting nge 'dzin nus mthu can du rang dbang bsgyur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18299: rdzu 'phrul nyi shu la spyod pa'i tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18302: lus shing bal lta bur yang bas nam mkha' la bya bzhin 'phyo ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18303: rig 'dzin gyi gnas thams cad du bgrod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18304: ngag gi bden pa grub pas chu bo'i rgyun gyen
NK077(tsu)001:18305: la bzlog par gyur cig /ces brjod pa tsam gyis
NK077(tsu)001:18306: bzlog pa dang / rlung zhi bar gyur cig byas
NK077(tsu)001:18307: pa tsam gyi ming 'gul bar 'chi nus pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:18308: bzlog pa dang / / ri dang brag la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:18309: pa la thogs pa med par 'dzul nus pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:18310: bzlog pa dang / / / chu la mi bying ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18311: rdo rje'i lus su grub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18313: dug dang mtshon gyi 'jigs par mi 'gyur te mi tshugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18314: lus 'di mngon sum du mi snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18315: lus gcig las mang por sprul pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18316: de dag las gzhan pa yang rang nyid yid la ji ltar bzhin du 'grub ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18318: 'jig rten gyi khams lha ma srin sde brgyad rnams la bdag gi dbang bsgyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18319: rang gzhan gyi tshe dang dus la bsring bar nus la /
NK077(tsu)001:18320: bstung bar 'dod na bstung bar nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18321: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK077(tsu)001:18322: thams cad yungs 'bru gcig gi nang du shong ba
NK077(tsu)001:18323: dang / yungs 'bru gcig gi stong gsum gcig po thams cad gang bar nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18324: ba spu nyag gcig gis stong gsum gang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18325: stong gsum ba spu'i bu gar dgang ste bsdu ba'ang gong gi yungs 'bru'i dpe de bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18326: snod bcud thams cad bsreg par byed pa'i me'i bskal pa chen po yang gzhil bar nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18327: rang gi lus la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'bum dus gcig la 'gyed par nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18328: sa phyogs skam po'i sar chu dbyung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18329: bye ma las gser du sgyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18330: sol ba ljon shing du dbyung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18331: 'byung ba stobs chen du bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18332: nam mkha' la h'u zhes rdo rje'i brag sgra sgom
NK077(tsu)001:18333: pas rdo rje'i brag ltar sra ba'i sgra 'byung zhing
NK077(tsu)001:18335: ting nge 'dzin yul yangs pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK077(tsu)001:18336: ces bla ma gong ma rnams kyis gsungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:18337: lag mthil du yi ge ram bkod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18338: de la ye shes kyi me 'bar nas tha mal gyi me yang tshig par 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18339: yi ge kham las ye shes chur 'gyur 'bab pa'ang dpe gong ma de bzhin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18340: tha mal gyi chu yang dag par byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18341: yi ge yam las ye shes kyi rlung byung bas 'jig rten gyi khams 'thor bar ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18342: yi ge e bkod de 'phro 'du byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18343: thams cad stong par bsam la /
NK077(tsu)001:18344: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad stong zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:18345: snod bcud thams cad steng nas 'og tu ltung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18346: 'og nas steng du 'phen par bya ba la sogs pa'ang 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18347: las kha tshar ba brgyad ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18348: dgug dang btang dang bcings dang dgrol //
NK077(tsu)001:18349: gso dang gsad dang pham dang rgyal ni go sla'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18350: rang gi ji ltar dmigs shing bsam pa bzhin tu 'grub ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18351: ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18352: gdug pa can dbang du 'du ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18354: stag dom la sogs pa'i gcan gzan gdug pa can rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18355: khyi la zan byin pa bzhin du bdag gi phyi bzhin du rjes su 'brang bar 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18356: gzhan yang bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18357: gnod sbyin dang lha srin lus sems gdug pa can la sogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:18358: bdag la bar chad kyi tshugs par mi 'gyur gyi
NK077(tsu)001:18359: slar bran g.yog bzhin du bdag gi bka' nyan pas
NK077(tsu)001:18360: phrin las ci bcol ba thams cad thogs pa med
NK077(tsu)001:18362: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18364: lhag ma'i lus ma bor bar tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi sar gnas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18365: de'i thugs rje sprul pa'i 'byung ba'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18366: 'gro ba lha klu la sogs pa so so'i skad dang mthun pa yis /
NK077(tsu)001:18367: 'gro ba'i so sor thar pa'i lam yang ston /
NK077(tsu)001:18368: ngan song gsum la sogs pa stong zhing dge ba'i las la bskul ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18369: de nyid lam stegs kyi theg pa la dgod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:18370: lam stegs kyi lam de dag nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:18371: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi lam la dgod par mdzad /
NK077(tsu)001:18372: nyan thos thar pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i don la
NK077(tsu)001:18373: bskul zhing zhi ba nyan thos 'gogs pa las slong
NK077(tsu)001:18374: ba dang / sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub
NK077(tsu)001:18375: sems dpa' de'i ston pa byed nus shing gsang sngags
NK077(tsu)001:18376: kyi don bstan des shes bya sbyong bar byed cing
NK077(tsu)001:18377: bde gshegs sprul pa'i sku'i 'khor la'ang chos ston zhing
NK077(tsu)001:18380: mthar lam pa sa bcu'i sgrib pa sbyongs ba mi 'thad zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:18382: bden gsum dbyer med lta ba chos kun mnyam pa
NK077(tsu)001:18383: nyid kyi gnas lugs khong du chud pa yin te
NK077(tsu)001:18384: / 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:18385: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:18386: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:18388: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sa bcu pa'i mnyam bzhag snang ba shugs bkag dbyings rkyang la song ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18389: 'dir mngon sum du rtogs pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:18390: gtan tshigs des na gsang sngags kyi mthong lam tshe dbang des /
NK077(tsu)001:18391: sa bcu'i slob dpon byed dgos par gsung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:18392: 'ga' zhig gis lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas kyis thob /
NK077(tsu)001:18393: de nas 'og ma rnams kyi don byed lugs yin /
NK077(tsu)001:18395: de na tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyi spyod pa la'ang don ci yod /
NK077(tsu)001:18399: stong gsum gyi stong chen po gcig la gling bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:18400: bye ba phrag brgya yod pa'i yul 'jig rten rnams
NK077(tsu)001:18401: / phyogs cha drug tu g.yo ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:18403: kun tu khyab cing tshab cher shin tu g.yo ba
NK077(tsu)001:18404: la sogs pa chos snang ba'i tshad pa snang ba
NK077(tsu)001:18405: / de yon tan ni zhing khams de na gnas
NK077(tsu)001:18406: pa'i sems can rnams mi rtag pa rgyud la skye
NK077(tsu)001:18407: / zhing / lam la zhugs pa rnams phyi ltar sa g.yos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18408: nang ltar ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams g.yos nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18409: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin pa'i rim pa 'og nas gong du g.yo bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18410: kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyi don mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18412: mthong lam tshe la dbang ba de nyid kyi gsang ba sngags kyi rang sgra bsgrags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18413: sgra skad kun kyang yon tan rmad du byung ba gsang sngags kyi sgrar ti ri ri grags pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18415: phyi nang gi bdud bzhi la sogs pa dang mu stegs rnams 'dul zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:18416: sems can rnams kyi rgyud la ngan song gsum gyi
NK077(tsu)001:18417: rgyu las dang nyon mongs pa yod pa rnams sbyong
NK077(tsu)001:18418: la / 'gro ba drug gi sems can lhag ma
NK077(tsu)001:18419: lus pa'i don yang rang rang gi blo dang ji
NK077(tsu)001:18420: ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:18421: gzhan don mdzad nas 'bras bu la sbyor tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18423: bdag gzhan gyi las rnams thams cad kun byas nas 'bras bu skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung thob /
NK077(tsu)001:18424: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18425: dpe byad brgyad cu kun gyis brgyan pa'i lam mthar
NK077(tsu)001:18426: phyin pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin bya ba
NK077(tsu)001:18427: med par sangs rgyas kyi sa 'grub bo //
NK077(tsu)001:18428: rmad du dbyung ba'i spyod pas gdul bya 'dul bar bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18430: rgyas pa la sogs pa'i rgyud las gsung pa'i mi spang ba lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:18433: lnga tshan bzhi yi spyod pa la bye brag bcu
NK077(tsu)001:18434: tshan gnyis te 'khor ba'i chos nyi shu la spyod
NK077(tsu)001:18435: pa dang / phrin las rnam pa bzhis gzhan don byed pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18436: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba thob pa'i skabs 'di nyid du thogs par med par 'byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18437: sngon cho 'phrul gyi skabs su bstan pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:18438: gling bzhi la sogs pa bye ba phrag brgya'i yul
NK077(tsu)001:18439: khyon de dag gi gdul bya ma lus pa 'dul
NK077(tsu)001:18440: bar byed do // bdun pa mngon shes la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:18442: mngon shes 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18444: phung khams skye mched dang dbang po rnams ni rang
NK077(tsu)001:18445: bzhin bcos bslad dang bral bas ye shes yin pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:18446: phyir / de nyid bye brag ma 'dres pas gcig pa dang bral la /
NK077(tsu)001:18447: rang byung ye shes su gcig pas du ma'i mtha'
NK077(tsu)001:18448: gcig dang du ma gnyis su med par lta bas
NK077(tsu)001:18449: mngon sum du rtogs shing ting nge 'dzin goms /
NK077(tsu)001:18450: de nas zag med mngon du mthong ba'i tshogs drug gi dri ma drug sbyang ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18451: dper na chu'i snyogs ma dwangs pa mthar phyin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:18453: tshogs drug gi snang ba mtshan ma'i gzung 'dzin dag na mngon shes 'char bar gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:18454: mngon shes nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18456: de snyed stong gsum gyis stong chen po brgya tshun chad kyi spyan gyi gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18460: lus kyi reg bya tshor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18461: de re re la'ang lnga lnga tshang bas shes pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:18462: bye brag re re la yang lnga lnga ste rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:18463: lngar shar ro // des dbang po gcig gi kyang yul lnga gcod par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:18464: dbang po tshang ba dang ma tshang ba'i 'jigs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18465: tshang ma tshang gi dog pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:18466: mngon shes drug rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18468: nyi shu rtsa lnga las gzhan du stong gsum tshun chad lha'i rna ba'i mngon shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18469: rang gzhan gyi sngon tshe rabs mang po nas gnas
NK077(tsu)001:18470: dang skye ba ci blangs rjes su 'dran pa'i mngon
NK077(tsu)001:18472: sems can pha rol po rnams kyi rtog pa ci rgyu shes pa'i mngon shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18473: rang dang 'gro ba gzhan 'di tsam na 'chi 'pho
NK077(tsu)001:18474: dang skye ba gang du len pa mkhyen pa'i mngon
NK077(tsu)001:18475: shes dang rdzu 'phrul gyi bya ba shes pa ste
NK077(tsu)001:18476: mi mthun pa brgyad la sogs pa ston pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:18477: gong gi spyod yul de rnams la 'dzin pa na /
NK077(tsu)001:18479: zad pa'i mngon shes dang drug go //
NK077(tsu)001:18480: mngon shes kyi yul dang ming gi rnam grangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:18483: mngon shes kyis mthong tshad de snyed tshun kyi yul dang gdul bya'i bye brag rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:18484: tshe dbang gi mngon par shes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18485: gdul bya mos pa tha dad pa gang dang gang
NK077(tsu)001:18486: yang rung ba rnams gang la gang 'tsham gyi sgo
NK077(tsu)001:18488: mngon shes de'i ming gi rnam grangs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18489: 'khor bar mi ldog pa'i mngon shes zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:18490: zag pa med pa'i mngon shes zhes bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18491: tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin gyi mtshan las mngon shes kyi ming yang brjod pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18492: des tshe dbang ba'i mngon shes zhes pa la sogs mtshan gyi rnam grangs las /
NK077(tsu)001:18493: mngon shes kyi ming grangs kyang brjod pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18494: brgyad pa lam gong ma la sbyor ba la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18498: tshe la dbang ba gang zag bdag gam gdul bya
NK077(tsu)001:18499: gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir tshe la rang dbang
NK077(tsu)001:18501: rang don du sku tshe'i tshad lo stong drug brgya
NK077(tsu)001:18502: nyid dam gzhan don du bskal ba'i grangs ci snyed
NK077(tsu)001:18503: par / 'jig rten du bzhugs pa'i tha ma rang
NK077(tsu)001:18504: gi grub mtha'i 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i tshul ni
NK077(tsu)001:18505: par / / sngon gyi lam snga ma phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:18506: gcig spros yan chad la blo che chung byung ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:18507: par / / dbang gis / thar chags rim gyis pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18508: thod rgal cig char ba gnyis gnyis yod pa bzhin du 'dir yang /
NK077(tsu)001:18509: 'bras bu la sbyor ba la thar chags pa rim gyis sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18510: thod rgal ba cig char du sbyor ba gnyis 'byung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18511: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18513: rim gyis bgrod pa thar chags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18515: de'ang mdor bstan gyi snga ma thar chags pa rim gyis pa'i sbyor tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18518: tshe dbang rang gi zag med kyis thos bsam sgom
NK077(tsu)001:18519: pa'i shes rab gsum la blo goms par byas pas
NK077(tsu)001:18520: / mthong spangs kyi sgrib pa dag pa tshe dbang
NK077(tsu)001:18521: rang gi rtsa ba'i lus skye 'chi med par rdo
NK077(tsu)001:18522: rje'i lus de rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgya chen por
NK077(tsu)001:18523: / / lam gyi dus na yi dam zhi khro
NK077(tsu)001:18524: rigs lnga gang gom pa de mngon sum du gsal
NK077(tsu)001:18525: bar gyur pa'i lha'i sku'i cha lugs 'dzin pa phyag
NK077(tsu)001:18526: rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin sgom pa de nyid du
NK077(tsu)001:18527: / / / gnas yongs su 'gyur nas sgom spangs kyi sgrib pa dag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18528: mthar lam lhun gyi grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18529: cig char du 'gro ba thod rgal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18531: mdor bstan gyi phyi ma thod rgal cig char du sbyor ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18532: mthong lam gyi rig mchog lam sbyangs pa'i tshe dbang de nyid nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18533: sngon rim gyis skabs bzhin du rang gi shes rab gsum la goms par byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18534: mthong spang sgom spang dus gcig la dag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18535: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po bar du dor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18536: cig char du mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin du /
NK077(tsu)001:18538: de'i rgyu mtshan ci phyir zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:18539: rgyu lta ba chos nyid rtogs tshab che ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18540: rkyen dam tshig tsang mar bsrung ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18541: smon lam gyi nus mthu btsan pa'ang yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18542: de ni gnas skabs kyi cig char ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:18544: skabs 'dir tshe rnam gnyis kyis lam gong ma la
NK077(tsu)001:18545: sbyor tshul gyi brgal len cig char brjod par bya'o
NK077(tsu)001:18546: // rnam smin rig 'dzin bar do na phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba yin nam min /
NK077(tsu)001:18549: spyod yul dor nas rgyag rgyar rdzogs /
NK077(tsu)001:18551: bral nas snang byed de rnam smin /
NK077(tsu)001:18552: zhes la sogs pa'i bar do la phyag chen la sbyor ba'i lung mong /
NK077(tsu)001:18553: bar do la sbyar ba yin na /
NK077(tsu)001:18554: tshe dbang bas rnam smin bzang bar rnam smin gyi tshe gcig la phyag chen thob la /
NK077(tsu)001:18555: tshe dbang gi bdag don la lo stong drug brgya dgos pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:18557: stobs chung rkyen smon zhan pa'i phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:18560: rnam smin stobs chung dgos zer na /
NK077(tsu)001:18561: 'bras bu nye bar sbyor ba rnams stobs che ba'i dam bca' nyams /
NK077(tsu)001:18562: yang tshe dbang gi lo stong drug brgya sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor ram /
NK077(tsu)001:18565: mthar chags pas kyang sbyor bar thal /
NK077(tsu)001:18567: tshe dbang gi tshe tshad du bzhag pa dang 'gal te /
NK077(tsu)001:18569: bdag phyir don du gnyer ba yi //
NK077(tsu)001:18570: brgya phrag bcu drug tshe yi rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:18573: phyag rgya chen po dang lhun grub de'i khungs su 'dus sam /
NK077(tsu)001:18576: de gnyis bgrod dgos sam mi dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:18578: mthar chags nyams lam gnyis po bgrod mi dgos pa'i phyir dgos na /
NK077(tsu)001:18579: lo stong drug brgya la sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor ba'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK077(tsu)001:18581: tshe dbang rab kyi lo stong drug brgya nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18582: sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor /
NK077(tsu)001:18583: 'bring gi bcu drug nas lhun grub la sbyor /
NK077(tsu)001:18584: tha ma bcu drug nas phyag chen la sbyor /
NK077(tsu)001:18586: de nas sangs rgyas la sbyor ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18587: 'o na phyi ma ltar gzhung dang 'gal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:18591: kha cig dbang bsgyur rig 'dzin nas //
NK077(tsu)001:18592: bcu drug rgyun gyi sku la rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:18594: kha cig phyag rgya chen pos /
NK077(tsu)001:18595: bla med kun tu bzang por 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:18597: kha cig rnam gsum bgrod pa'i mthar //
NK077(tsu)001:18598: lhun grub rig la rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK077(tsu)001:18601: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:18602: sku lnga lhun grub rdzogs pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:18603: zhes gsung pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:18605: de ni thod rgal ba'i lung yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18606: tshe dbang bas rnam smin bzang ba ma yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18608: bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18612: bar do la thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18613: phyi ma la thob pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18614: lan grangs gzhan du thob pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18616: 'di rnams rim pa bzhin tshe rnam gnyis tshe dbang bzang bar shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18618: tshe dbang thar chags pa 'di dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18619: rnam smin tshe 'di la thob pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18620: rnam smin phyag chen la sbyor ba la lam thag nye ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18621: sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor ba la yun bsring dgos par gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:18622: zag bcad nas phyag rgya gcig spros nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18623: rnam smin thob pa de dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18624: tshogs bsgrub nas nam smin thob pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18625: lam gong ma la sbyor ba la stobs che chung yod par bshad pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:18627: tshogs lam la las sgrib sbyangs /
NK077(tsu)001:18628: sbyor lam la nyon sgrib sbyang /
NK077(tsu)001:18629: mthong lam la kun 'gro'i sgrib pa sbyongs /
NK077(tsu)001:18630: sgom lam la lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma /
NK077(tsu)001:18631: mthar lam la bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa sbyangs nas sangs rgyas dgos pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:18633: kun bzhi bag chags las gang bsags rnams yin //
NK077(tsu)001:18634: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18635: nyon mongs pa dug gsum dug lnga rnams yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18636: 'phags pa'i lam gyi sgrib pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18638: shes bya la shes su mi ster ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18639: shes bya dam du 'dzin pa'i sgrib pa gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18640: shes bya la dam du 'dzin pa'i kun 'gro'i sgrib pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18641: lta ba la ched 'dzin pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18642: lta ba de nyid lam kun gyi sngon du 'gro bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18644: lta ba la ched du bzang 'dzin byas pa na sgrib pa /
NK077(tsu)001:18645: de'i phyir kun 'gro'i sgrib pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18646: shes bya la shes su mi ster ba'i sgrib pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18647: sgom lam lhan cig gnas pa'i sgrib pa /
NK077(tsu)001:18648: sgom pa la ched du 'dzin pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18649: de yang sgom gyi thugs de nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18650: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo de gnyis la /
NK077(tsu)001:18651: phan tshun tha dad par gnas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18652: lhan cig gnas pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18653: sgom pa la ched du bzung bas bsgrib par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:18654: des na lhan cig gnas pa'i sgrib pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18655: bag la nyal gyi bsgrib pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18656: kun bzhi rnam shes snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:18657: gzung 'dzin la ma shar ba de'i cha phra ba /
NK077(tsu)001:18658: yun se gol brdab pa tsam gcig go //
NK077(tsu)001:18659: de la rnam smin kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dang lnga yang /
NK077(tsu)001:18660: lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma sbyang ba la yun ring po gcig dgos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18661: tshe dbang bas bzang bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18662: 'di rnams la zhib tu ngo sprad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18663: gnas 'gyur dag ma dag gi sa mtshams /
NK077(tsu)001:18664: snang ba la shugs bkag yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:18665: de rnams kyi don go dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:18666: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la'ang don brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:18669: kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag pa de nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:18670: phyag rgya chen po'i skur gsal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18671: de nyid kyi ni kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag pa kho na ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18673: kun 'gro'i sgrib dag ngo bo'i rgyu //
NK077(tsu)001:18678: kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag pa'i dus //
NK077(tsu)001:18679: de'i tshe phyag rgya chen po la sbyor bas de nyid dus kyang yin pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:18681: tshogs bsgrub pa'i thod rgal bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18682: phyag rgya chen po la sbyor dus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18683: tshogs bsgrub kyi sa na dngos su ma smos kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:18684: rnam smin tshe dbang thob pa'i dus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18685: mtshungs pas shugs kyi shes zer yang /
NK077(tsu)001:18686: tshogs bsgrub las thod rgal mi 'byung ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18687: de thog na rnam smin thob nas phyag chen la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18688: mthong lam nas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba'i dus kyang gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:18689: rnam smin gyis sgom lam la sbyor ba'i dus kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:18690: de nyid kyi tshe shes rab gsum gyis sgo nas kun 'gro'i sgrib pa'i dus de nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:18691: tshe dbang gi phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba'i dus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18692: rang don du lo stong drug brgya yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18693: gzhan don du ma nges te /
NK077(tsu)001:18695: bskal pa grangs med gnas 'gyur kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:18696: sku ni shin tu gzhon pa'i tshul //
NK077(tsu)001:18698: de tshe sku tshe'i tshad med do //
NK077(tsu)001:18702: yi dam gyi lha'i rigs gang yin pa de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:18703: goms pa mthar phyin pa'i stobs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18704: sgo gsum lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por gsal ba de nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:18705: 'o na lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dang khyad ci yod ce na /
NK077(tsu)001:18706: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin ni /
NK077(tsu)001:18707: sku lnga lhun grub kyis cha lugs su bzhugs pa 'di yin zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:18709: rigs lnga rkyang bkar gyi cha lugs su bzhugs pas khyad yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:18711: phyag rgya chen po tsam gyi rnam grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18712: ma h+aa rang gzhung gi phyag rgya chen po'i rnam grangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:18715: u pa ya'i rigs bzhi'i dang yo ga'i rigs lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18716: ma h+aa'i rigs lnga'i dang bzhi'o /
NK077(tsu)001:18718: phyag rgya chen po nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18720: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor la sogs pa gzhung nyid na gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:18722: rdo rje rigs kyi phyag rgya la sogs pa lnga gzhung nyid na gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:18724: ma 'gag pa phyag rgya'i dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18725: ma dmigs pa chos nyid kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18727: sangs rgyas nyi khri bzhi stong gcig dang du ma las grol bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18728: ngo bo nyid yul lus med du rang gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18730: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'i ngo bo nyid mtha' dbus las grol bar gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18732: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i bdag nyid yin pas phan tshun tha dad du mi bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18734: bdag gzhan gyi spyod pa gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:18736: shes rab gsum gyi sgo nas lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag par byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18738: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i sgo nas gdul bya'i don mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18740: mngon shes kyi tshad dang mthun no //
NK077(tsu)001:18742: stong gsum 'jig rten brgya stong phrag bcu'i zhing khams rdul snyed du /
NK077(tsu)001:18743: zhing grangs med par brgya stong phrag /ces pa la sogs pa de nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:18745: de yang mngon shes lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18746: nyi shu rtsa lnga mkhyen pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18751: de nyid kyi tshe shes rab gsum gyis lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:18752: bag la nyal gyi dri ma yang shugs kyi dag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18753: lhun gyi grub pa'i rig 'dzin bor nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18754: rgyal ba nyid la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18757: lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag nas lhun gyi grub pa'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18758: gnyis pa sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18760: lus snga ma dang mthun par bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18762: de nyid zag med lam la gsum yod pa'i bar
NK077(tsu)001:18763: la sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin bshad
NK077(tsu)001:18764: par bya ba'ang / sngon gyi tshe dbang gi lus bzhin don brgyad kyis rdzogs par bya ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18765: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la brgyad /
NK077(tsu)001:18769: tshogs lam phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18770: du ma sgom pa spros pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:18771: rang gi 'byung bzhi 'dus pas lus kyang ngo bo sems nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:18772: rtog tshogs thams cad rang bzhin lha'i dal du /
NK077(tsu)001:18773: lta bas mngon du mthong ba'i don la ting nge 'dzin goms par byas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:18774: spyod pa tshogs gnyis bsags pa'ang mthar sbyor lam du tshogs bsgrub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18775: mthong lam du rnam smin tshe dbang gnyis thob nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18776: lta ba la ched du 'dzin pa kun 'gro'i sgrib
NK077(tsu)001:18777: pa mthong lam pa'i rgyud la yod nas dag pa
NK077(tsu)001:18778: de nyid sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:18779: gyi ngo bo'i rgyu yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18780: rgyu'i khyad par ni rgyu las kyi rnam par smin
NK077(tsu)001:18781: pa'i lus kyi tshul gyis 'bras bu phyag rgya chen
NK077(tsu)001:18782: por dus phyi'i grub pa rgyu 'bras tha dad pa
NK077(tsu)001:18785: bskyed bya bskyed kyi rgyu 'bras sa bon dang myu
NK077(tsu)001:18786: gu ltar snga ma dang phyi ma rgyu 'bras tha
NK077(tsu)001:18787: dad du 'dod pa ni min te /
NK077(tsu)001:18788: rgyu 'bras dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:18791: sgom lam thob pa'i dus kyi rim pa la snga phyi gnyis su 'dod pa min te /
NK077(tsu)001:18792: dus gsum rgyu 'bras dbyer med du gcig par 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:18793: rgyu 'bras ngo bo dbyer med gcig yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18794: gcig pa de nyid la lam du byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18795: tshe dbang rang gi lhag ma'i lus dang bcas pas lo brgya brgya nas /
NK077(tsu)001:18796: brgyad brgyad lon par bsnur zhing bsgrub pa'i mtha' ma la /
NK077(tsu)001:18797: tshe dbang nyid phyag rgya chen po de nyid du 'gyur bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18798: tshe dbang nyid phyag rgya chen po nyid du sbyor ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:18799: nges pa gcig tu bzung du med do //
NK077(tsu)001:18800: de ltar na tshe dbang de phyag rgya chen po la 'byung lus dang bcas pa sbyor na /
NK077(tsu)001:18801: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las grol //
NK077(tsu)001:18805: zhes pa dang 'gal zhes brjod na /
NK077(tsu)001:18807: 'byung lus kyi rgyun dang bcas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:18808: ldog pa dang bral nas sbyor bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18809: snga phyi'i lugs gnyis ka dang mi 'gal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:18812: ngo bo longs sku dang tshul mthun pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18814: mthong lam pa rang gi sems nyid lha'i sku phyag
NK077(tsu)001:18815: rgya chen por ye nas rang gyur pa yin te
NK077(tsu)001:18816: / de'i don rtogs shing lam gcig spros gnyis su
NK077(tsu)001:18817: lha sgom pa'i mthar yi dam gyi lha gang yin
NK077(tsu)001:18818: pa de nyid mngon sum du gyur pa'i sku la
NK077(tsu)001:18819: / / thun mong dang mchog gi mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18820: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa longs sku'i rig 'dzin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18821: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku 'dra bas na longs sku
NK077(tsu)001:18822: gnyis pa lta bu sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i
NK077(tsu)001:18823: rig 'dzin no // rigs lnga gang yin gyi rig 'dzin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:18824: mtshan dpe mngon shes dang cho 'phrul rnams rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18828: rdo rje rigs kyi phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18829: de bzhin du 'khor lo de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18832: las kyi rigs kyi phyag rgya chen po ste phyag
NK077(tsu)001:18833: mtshan lngas mtshon nas yid rigs lnga gang yin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:18834: sku phyag rgya chen po'i rigs dang cha byad 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:18835: par 'gyur bas na phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:18836: no // de yang rang gi lus nyid ye gdod
NK077(tsu)001:18837: ma nas lha sku phyag rgya chen po gnas pa
NK077(tsu)001:18839: ting nge 'dzin gyi yang dang yang du sgom pas
NK077(tsu)001:18840: yi dam gyi lha gang yin pa dbang po'i mngon
NK077(tsu)001:18841: sum du gyur pa'i lha'i sku la /
NK077(tsu)001:18842: mtshan dpe gnyis gnyis te bzhi ni cho 'phrul bzhi la ngos bzung yang rung bas bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18843: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa la sogs mngon
NK077(tsu)001:18844: shes drug dang nyer lnga la sogs rdzogs pa ste
NK077(tsu)001:18845: / longs sku'i phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:18846: de ka la phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin zhes grags so //
NK077(tsu)001:18847: ye shes sku'i cha lugs 'dzin cing tshe dbang dang khyad phye ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18849: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku longs sku'i cha lugs can te /
NK077(tsu)001:18850: rnam smin ltar 'byung ba'i lus dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18851: tshe dbang ltar skye 'jigs med pa 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus bgres rgud can las kyang grol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:18852: de'i phyir ye shes sgyu ma'i sku la bgres rgud dang 'pho 'gyur med pa thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18853: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi sku tshe'i tshad bzung du med te /
NK077(tsu)001:18854: tshe dbang ltar lo brgya nas brgyad ltar bsnur zhing
NK077(tsu)001:18855: 'bras bu mngon du thob par bya ba'i rtsol ba
NK077(tsu)001:18856: dang bral bas tshe dbang bas dpag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18857: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:18859: phyag rgya chen po'i rnam grangs phyir bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18861: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin de nyid la kri ya rigs gsum gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18862: u pa rigs bzhi'i phyag rgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18863: yo ga rigs lnga'i phyag rgya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18864: mchog ma h+aa yo ga'i rigs lnga'i phyag rgya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18865: lha de rnams kyi rigs dang cha byad 'dzin pas na phyag rgya chen po'i ting 'dzin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18867: rnam grangs rigs rnam pa bzhi ru sngon tshe dbang la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:18868: ngo bo sman dang thabs rig 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:18870: rnam grangs bzhi yod pa bzhin du phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi skabs 'dir yang /
NK077(tsu)001:18872: khyad par du ma h+aa yo ga'i phyag rgya chen po'i rnam grangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:18874: de ltar phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi
NK077(tsu)001:18875: nang nas mchog tu gyur pa ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK077(tsu)001:18876: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dag gi ming gi
NK077(tsu)001:18877: rnam grangs gnyis pa dang gsum la lnga 'byung ba
NK077(tsu)001:18879: gang gi tshe dbang gi skabs su ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:18880: dgongs pa chos nyid dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:18881: rang mtshan rtogs pa nyid las dgongs pa gzhan du
NK077(tsu)001:18883: mi g.yo grub pa'i rnal 'byor zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:18884: tshe la rang dbang bsgyur ba'i skabs kyis rtsol ba'i 'du byed dang bral ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:18885: lta ba la ched du 'dzin pa kun 'gro'i sgrib pa'i 'du byed dang bral bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18886: mthong lam 'du byed bral ba'i lam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:18887: mthong lam du zag pa med pa chos nyid rang mtshan mthong ba'i rgyun la gnas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18888: sgom pa'i lam pa zhes kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:18889: dgongs pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo bas mi g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:18890: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin nyid du'ang brjod de ming gi rnam grangs lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18892: mchog ma ha yo ga'i rig 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:18893: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin 'di yis ming gi
NK077(tsu)001:18894: rnam grangs ni ci lta bu yod na /
NK077(tsu)001:18895: de yang rgyal ba longs sku gnyis pa de la ming gi rnam grangs la gsum ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18897: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:18898: tshe la dbang bsgyur bas bsnur zhing mngon du byed pa'i 'du byed dang bral bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18899: zag pa med pa'i lam pa zhes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18900: sgom pa'i lam pa zhes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18901: mi g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor zhes pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18902: rnam grangs gsum po nyid du brjod do //
NK077(tsu)001:18903: de la rgyal bas 'gro bar lung ston pa'i sangs rgyas longs spyod pa'i sku dngos su 'byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:18904: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18906: bdud dang cha dbye zhing brtag pa'i bye brag zag
NK077(tsu)001:18907: med kyi sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:18908: 'di las dog pa med de mi dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:18911: longs sku ye shes sgyu ma'i sku'i cha lugs su
NK077(tsu)001:18912: yod pa'i sgom lam gyi rnal 'byor pa phyag rgya
NK077(tsu)001:18914: sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi gnyis pa longs spyod rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:18915: pa'i shes rab lta ba'i spyan dang dgongs pa ting
NK077(tsu)001:18917: longs sku dang khyad med pa rang ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18918: phyag rgya chen po dang longs sku de gnyis dgongs pa'i rgyud mthun par snang mod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:18921: phyag rgya chen po mnyam pa nyid la mi g.yo ba thob cing /
NK077(tsu)001:18922: ting nge 'dzin shin tu brtan pa'i rig pa klong du bab par gnas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18923: nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs pa'i //
NK077(tsu)001:18924: grangs can gyi lha'i 'khor lo mngon sum du gsal bar snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:18926: sangs rgyas longs sku dang khyad med dam snyam pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:18927: 'on kyang da rung lam pa yin pas sgom pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:18928: rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par 'jog dgos
NK077(tsu)001:18929: pa'i rtsol ba can yin pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:18930: rtsol ba yod med kyi khyad par yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:18932: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku'i cha lugs su yod pa'i rnal 'byor pa /
NK077(tsu)001:18933: sangs rgyas longs sku'i cha lugs can gnyis pa phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:18935: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin rnams kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:18937: lta dgongs rang mtshan rtog pa tsam du /
NK077(tsu)001:18938: rgyud thun mong yang khyad med pa ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:18939: tshe dbang gis mi g.yo ba tsam thob pa las med la /
NK077(tsu)001:18940: 'dir dgongs pa mi g.yo ba shin tu brtan pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:18941: de'i klong du gnas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:18942: nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs pa grangs tshig can gyi lha'i 'khor lo mngon sum du snang ba'o /
NK077(tsu)001:18943: 'on kyang mthar lam lhun grub pa la ltos na /
NK077(tsu)001:18944: sgom lam gyi rnal 'byor phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin 'di yang /
NK077(tsu)001:18948: rang don du dgongs pa mnyam par bzhag pa'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:18949: gzhan don du stong gsum stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams /
NK077(tsu)001:18950: gling bzhi sogs bye ba phrag brgya brgya lo 'di
NK077(tsu)001:18951: grangs kyi gzhir byas pa de nyid brgya stong phrag
NK077(tsu)001:18952: bcu yi 'jig rten gyi khams rnams rdul phra rab
NK077(tsu)001:18953: tu bsil ba'i grangs de snyed de dag dang mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:18954: pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams gyi gdul bya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18955: sangs rgyas sprul sku'i zhing khams de lta bu grangs
NK077(tsu)001:18956: kyi gnas gzhan drug cu las 'das pas bgrang du
NK077(tsu)001:18957: yod pa gcig gzhir bzhag nas bgrangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:18958: grangs med brgya stong phrag bcu'i rdul phra rab snyed
NK077(tsu)001:18959: kyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams
NK077(tsu)001:18960: rnams su / cha lugs rngon pa dang smad 'tshang
NK077(tsu)001:18961: gi 'dul ba de dang des 'dul ba la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:18963: mtho dman gyi bye brag sna tshogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:18964: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin de nyid kyi rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:18965: ba'i lus ye shes sgyu ma'i sku las ma g.yos
NK077(tsu)001:18966: pas sprul pa'i lus kyis gdul bya rnams gang la
NK077(tsu)001:18968: phrin las kyi cho 'phrul bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18970: rdzu 'phrul gyi mthu nyi shu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18971: mngon shes nyer lnga la sogs pas don byed pa'i yul yang gong du bstan pa de bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:18974: mngon par shes pa drug dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18975: dbang po sgo yis mngon shes re re la'ang yan
NK077(tsu)001:18976: lag lnga lnga nyer lnga dang bcas pa'i tshul gyis
NK077(tsu)001:18977: shes pa'ang tshe dbang dang 'dra mod /
NK077(tsu)001:18978: 'o na tshe dbang dang phyag rgya chen po gnyis mngon shes khyad par med dam zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:18981: mngon shes drug la sogs pa kun gong ltar stong gsum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18982: zhing grangs med la sogs de snyed kyi 'dul zhing
NK077(tsu)001:18983: gi yul la rgya che chung gi khyad par yod
NK077(tsu)001:18984: pa dang / zag med kyi sgom lam du mthong lam gyi don rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18986: gdul bya'i don yongs su rdzogs par byed pa nus mthu che chung gi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18988: phyag rgya chen po'i gdul byar gyur pas gdul bya
NK077(tsu)001:18989: rgya che chung gi khyad par gyi sgo nas kyang
NK077(tsu)001:18990: dpags so // 'bras bu la sbyor tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:18992: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po rang gi dgongs pa
NK077(tsu)001:18993: mi g.yo ba'i don lta bas mthong zhing ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:18994: 'dzin gyis goms par byas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18995: don du gnyer ba bsgrub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18996: rim pa dbang dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa lam la brtson 'grus kyis rtsol ba'i /
NK077(tsu)001:18997: lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud don bcu po kun rdzogs par nyams su lon pa'i byin brlabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:18999: mi g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin la ched
NK077(tsu)001:19000: 'dzin gyi rtsol ba can sgom pa dang bral nas
NK077(tsu)001:19001: / mthar lam lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la sbyor te /
NK077(tsu)001:19004: de la ched du 'dzin pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19006: de ltar na sgom pa la ched du 'dzin pa lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19007: ched du brtsal ba med par gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19008: de yang lam pa de blo che chung gis /
NK077(tsu)001:19009: mthar thug sangs rgyas dang lhun grub la sbyor ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19010: skabs 'dir lhun grub rig 'dzin gyis stong thun brjod na don brgyad de /
NK077(tsu)001:19012: sgom lam la gnas pa'i tshe de nyid kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19013: shes rab gsum gyis lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19014: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin du snang ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19015: de ltar lhan gcig gnas pa'i dri ma dag pa ni rgyu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19018: thar chag gi dus gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:19020: tshe dbang nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:19022: tshe dbang gi rang don du lo stong drug brgya yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:19023: gzhan don du mi ma nges so //
NK077(tsu)001:19025: sgom lam gyi sgrib pa dag pa'i dus /
NK077(tsu)001:19026: de'i tshe 'di nyid la sbyor ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19029: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19030: bag la nyal gyi dri ma dag pa dang sangs rgyas la sbyor ba nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:19033: rang rgyud pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19034: lam gyi mthar rgyal ba la sbyor ba /
NK077(tsu)001:19035: mthar sbyor ba la sogs pa grangs dkyus na gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:19038: ma dmigs pa chos nyid kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19040: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK077(tsu)001:19041: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i ngo bo nyid yul med rang dag dal ba mthar thug pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19043: gnas lugs dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba nyid mtha' dbus med par gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19044: dgongs pa de gnyis kyang thun mong ma yin par
NK077(tsu)001:19045: dbyer med yin pas tha dad du mi bsam mo
NK077(tsu)001:19047: bdag gzhan gyi spyod pa gnyis las /
NK077(tsu)001:19049: shes rab gsum gyi bag la nyal gyi dri ma sbyongs bar mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19051: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi zhing khams mtha' las grol ba'i don mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19053: lnga dang nyi shu rtsa lnga'i mngon par shes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19055: rgyal ba nyid dang mnyam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:19058: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan mchog 'chang //
NK077(tsu)001:19061: sangs rgyas dang khyad med zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:19062: mkhyen yul la khyad med pa yin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19063: mkhyen tshul la cung zad khyad yod de rgyal ba nyid ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19064: shugs 'byung gi mnyam rjes cha phra ba yang bral ba'i tshul gyi mkhyen pa yin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19066: mdo gcig tu bsdu ba po nam mkhan gyi lo thog bsdu ba ltar bsdu ba dang bcu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19068: dgongs 'dus le'u drug cu re drug pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19069: don lnga'i bar gyi le'u bcus bstan to //
NK077(tsu)001:19071: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu tshogs lam du'ang rdzogs par bya dgos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19076: bslab pa bcu rang rang gi gnas skabs kyi khyad yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:19081: rim pa de ltar snang ba yin //
NK077(tsu)001:19084: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu sgra gcig la //
NK077(tsu)001:19085: zag bcas bzhi dang bar chad med //
NK077(tsu)001:19086: zag med lnga'i bslab pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19087: slob pas lugs dang lob pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19088: rtsal dang ngo bo khyad par dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19089: bslab bya yul gyi khyad par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:19092: dang po slob lugs kyi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19093: zag bcas tshig dang yi ge la rten nas slob la bar chad med pa tshig dang yi ge'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19095: ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas slob la /
NK077(tsu)001:19096: zag med chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa la slob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19097: gnyis pa lob pa'i khyad par ni zag bcas kyi
NK077(tsu)001:19098: skabs su chos thams cad kyi rgya mtsho ltar lob
NK077(tsu)001:19099: pa la / bar chad med pas mngon sum du lob ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19100: zag med kyi rang rig mngon sum du lob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19101: gsum pa nus pa'i khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19102: zag bcas kyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag cing gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob la /
NK077(tsu)001:19103: bar chad med pas las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib
NK077(tsu)001:19104: pa'i sgrib pa 'bring po dag ste mthong lam la
NK077(tsu)001:19105: sbyor ro // zag med kyi shes bya'i sgrib pa
NK077(tsu)001:19106: cha phra ba dag nas sangs rgyas rig 'dzin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:19107: sbyor ro // skabs 'dir ni / shugs 'byung gi
NK077(tsu)001:19108: mnyam rjes dang bcas pas mkhyen pa yin pas skyon
NK077(tsu)001:19109: sbyor ro // skabs 'dir ni / med do // brgyad pa 'bras bu la sbyor tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19110: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:19111: bag la nyal gyi dri ma cha phra mo'i sgrib pa dang bral ba'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:19115: lus snga ma dang mthun par mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19117: thod rgal du mthong lam tshe dbang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19118: thar chag tu sgom lam phyag rgya chen po des mngon du byas pa yis 'bras bu /
NK077(tsu)001:19119: rtsa ba'i lus sku lnga lhun grub kyi cha byad
NK077(tsu)001:19120: dam rig 'dzin pas lhun gyi grub pa'i rig pa'am
NK077(tsu)001:19122: rang gi rgyud la lhan gcig gnas pa'i dri ma dag pa'i sangs rgyas zhes kyang bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19123: de la yang sngon tshe dbang gi skabs su bstan
NK077(tsu)001:19124: pa bzhi zung bzhi ya brgyad kyi lus rnam bzhag
NK077(tsu)001:19126: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa la brgyad /
