NK077(tsu)001:19130: lam snga ma phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la lta sgom gyi nus pa'i mthu rdzogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19131: sngon sgom lam gyi skabs su bshad pa bzhin du lhan gcig gnas pa'i dri ma sbyangs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19132: sangs rgyas longs sku'i cha byad can gnyis pa /
NK077(tsu)001:19133: phyag rgya chen po'i thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:19134: gsum la goms pa'i nyid 'bras bu lhun gyi grub
NK077(tsu)001:19135: pa'i rig 'dzin dngos su 'byung ba'i rgyu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19138: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa'i gnas skabs
NK077(tsu)001:19139: der sngon du bstan pa'i phyag rgya chen po'i rig
NK077(tsu)001:19140: 'dzin bzhin shes rab gsum po rdzogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19141: rgyal ba longs spyod chen po'i sku grub pa las gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lung thos shing /
NK077(tsu)001:19142: lhun grub rang gi dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin dang
NK077(tsu)001:19143: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyod lam sa'i nus pa mthu can
NK077(tsu)001:19145: sangs rgyas kyis mthar skad gcig gnyis pa la dbyung
NK077(tsu)001:19146: ba'i dus la bab pa ste sangs rgyas thob pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:19147: dus so // yang lugs gcig la /
NK077(tsu)001:19148: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi gnas skabs dor /
NK077(tsu)001:19149: sngon tshe dbang gi skabs su bstan pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:19150: sgom lam pa'i shes rab rnam pa gsum rdzogs pas sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la /
NK077(tsu)001:19151: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lung brda'i gsung las thos shing /
NK077(tsu)001:19152: sgom lam pa rang gi lta dgongs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19153: spyod pa nus pa mthu stobs can du gyur pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:19154: slob pa'i sa mthar phyin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19155: mthar lam lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin du 'byung ba'i dus la bab ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19156: 'di la'ang dus tshad bzung du med do //
NK077(tsu)001:19159: ngo bo sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin cing sgrib pa sbyangs tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19161: de ltar kun 'gro dang ldan cig gnas pa'i /
NK077(tsu)001:19162: rang rgyud kyi dri ma dag pa'i shes pa de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:19163: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid grub pa'i rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19165: dgongs pa lhun grub mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:19166: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa nyid du mnyam par bzhag nas bzhugs pa yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19167: bag la nyal ba'i sgrib pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19169: nyin par gyi skar ma lta bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19170: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi 'jom par byed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19171: sangs rgyas sa la skad cig la rags las pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19172: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin mthar lam pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19173: cha lugs dang rgyal tshabs kyi nges tshig dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19175: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin de'i sku'i cha byad
NK077(tsu)001:19176: ni rgyal ba drug pa kun bzang rdo rje 'chang
NK077(tsu)001:19177: chen nyid kyi cha byad du gnas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19178: rigs sam sku lnga po gcig la dbyer med du lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:19179: rgyal ba drug pa'i sku de nyid dang 'dra bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:19180: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid drug pa
NK077(tsu)001:19181: de nyid kyi rgyal tshabs kyi skyes bu byas nas
NK077(tsu)001:19182: 'khor gdul bya rnams la chos ston pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19184: sku lnga lhun grub kyi bdag nyid rgyal ba drug
NK077(tsu)001:19185: pa de'i rgyud mi gtong bas na lhun grub rig
NK077(tsu)001:19187: nges tshig rnams 'grub pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19190: de nyid la skye shi mi mnga' ba'i phyir skye 'jig med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:19191: rdo rje'i sku yang gdul bya'i ngo la sprul pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:19192: sku rnams ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul du
NK077(tsu)001:19193: ston / de yang rgyal bu don 'grub la sogs ci lta ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19194: bzhi pa rnam grangs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19197: bya ba kri ya'i lhun grub rig 'dzin /
NK077(tsu)001:19198: rnal 'byor yo ga'i lhun grub kyi rig 'dzin dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19199: rnal 'byor chen po nang pa'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19202: sngags phyi pa'i rnam grangs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19204: snga ma kri ya'i rigs gsum gyi lhun grub dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19205: yo ga pa'i sems dpa' dang so bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:19206: de dag dbyer med du lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19207: kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyi cha lugs 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:19208: cing rang rang gi bstan pa de gnyis kyi rgyal
NK077(tsu)001:19209: tshabs dang de gnyis kyi sdud pa po yang byed
NK077(tsu)001:19210: do // ma h+aa yo ga'i lhun gyis grub rnam grangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:19212: de ltar don gyi rnam grangs la gsum yod pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:19213: grangs kyi tha ma rnal 'byor chen po nang pa
NK077(tsu)001:19214: ma h+aa yo ga pa'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig
NK077(tsu)001:19215: 'dzin gyi ming gi rnam grangs ni lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19216: lam zad par skyol bas mthar phyin pa'i lam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:19217: rang gi rgyud la sgrib pa mngon rgyu med pa rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19218: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ba de nyid dang ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19219: sangs rgyas la dngos su sbyor bas mthar sbyor ba'i lam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK077(tsu)001:19220: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug la kun bzang gi rgyal tshab byed pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:19221: rgyal tshab kyi skyes bu zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19222: ming gi rnam grangs lnga po de dag go //
NK077(tsu)001:19225: dgongs pa dang mkhyen pa sangs rgyas dang mnyam la shes sgrib phra mos phye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19227: chos nyid dam lha'i dal gdul bya'i blos bsam yas
NK077(tsu)001:19228: pa lhun gyis rdzogs shing grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:19229: gsal ba'i phyir / shes bya'i chos ci lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19231: thams cad lta ba mnyam bzhag la mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis spyan mchog tu gyur pa 'chang /
NK077(tsu)001:19232: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa la rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum du gzigs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19233: de'i dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin chos nyid mi g.yo
NK077(tsu)001:19234: ba'i don la blos gang du yang mi rtog par
NK077(tsu)001:19237: da rung mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang mi rgya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19238: dus nam gyi tshe sangs rgyas na /
NK077(tsu)001:19239: dus kyi mtha'i skad cig ma gcig la rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:19240: lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bag la nyal gyi
NK077(tsu)001:19241: sgrib pa bcom nas sangs rgyas de nyid kyi sa
NK077(tsu)001:19242: la gshegs pa'o // de la skad cig ma'i ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19244: kha cig ni mi rtag pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19245: de'i don ni skad cig ma gnyis la mi sdod pa'o zer /
NK077(tsu)001:19247: shin tu myur ba'am thung ba gcig la bya'o zer /
NK077(tsu)001:19249: tol skyes kyi skad cig ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:19251: shes bya la shes pa skye ba ste gang ma 'ga' zhig bar du 'ong gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:19253: bya rdzogs kyi skad cig ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19257: kha cig gi mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs sangs rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:19258: kyi mdzad pa tshar gcig rdzogs pa la zer te
NK077(tsu)001:19259: / don grub lta bu dang por sems bskyed pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19260: sangs ma rgyas kyi bar du bskal pa grangs med gsum du 'dod la /
NK077(tsu)001:19261: kha cig tshad ma gcig gis byed pa rdzogs pa zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:19262: sbyor skor gcig gi tshad ma ma yin pa'i shes pa cig char chod la 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:19264: gyad kyi se gol gcig la brgya nyi shu dbye ba'i cha shas gcig la 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:19265: da res 'dir bshad pa'i dus mtha'i skad cig ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19267: dus mtha' ni lam gyi bya ba mtha' phyin pa la dus zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19269: tol skyes kyi skad cig ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:19271: skad cig gcig gis bye brag phyed //
NK077(tsu)001:19272: skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK077(tsu)001:19274: dgongs pa'i ming grangs bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19277: don gyi go rim bsdebs na /
NK077(tsu)001:19278: de yang lta ba dang dgongs pa sngar bstan pa
NK077(tsu)001:19279: ltar yin la des na mthar lam lhun grub rig
NK077(tsu)001:19280: 'dzin gyi dgongs pa rgya mtsho lta bur zab cing
NK077(tsu)001:19282: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal rdzogs pa zhes bya ba'i dgongs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19283: mthar phyin pa'i lam pa'i dgongs pa zhes bya ba
NK077(tsu)001:19284: la sogs pa dgongs pa'i ming gi rnam grangs dang
NK077(tsu)001:19285: / spyod pa rgya mtsho ltar zab cing brlab che ba kun /
NK077(tsu)001:19286: lam snga ma'i rtsol ba'i bya ba byed pa'i spyod pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19287: bya byed kyi rtsol ba dang bral bas bya bral
NK077(tsu)001:19288: lhun grub kyi spyod pa zhes bya ba la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:19289: pa spyod pa'i ming gi rnam grangs brjod pa de
NK077(tsu)001:19290: dag kun lta spyod kyi yon tan gyi cha las
NK077(tsu)001:19291: brjod par zad // drug pa spyod pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19293: bdag don sgrib pa bcom nas sangs rgyas tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19295: mthar lam pa bdag nyid kyi don phyir sku la
NK077(tsu)001:19296: lhun grub drug pa rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po
NK077(tsu)001:19297: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la /
NK077(tsu)001:19298: dus mtha'i skad cig ma'i dus kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:19299: thag lta bas bcad pa la sogs bslab pa'i mtha' bcu yongs su rdzogs par byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19300: lam mthar phyin na tha ma lhun grub rig 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:19301: gyi rgyud la yod pa'i bag la nyal gyi sgrub
NK077(tsu)001:19302: pa cha phra ba de dag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19303: mnyam par bzhag ma bzhag las 'das te bcom ldan
NK077(tsu)001:19304: 'das kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas par gyur pa
NK077(tsu)001:19305: yin no // de la bslab pa'i mtha' bcu ni //
NK077(tsu)001:19306: dam tshig gzhi dang rgyud dgrol dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19307: sgo bsdur ba dang phul dbyung dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19308: thag bcad pa dang mnyam blangs dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19309: la dor spyod dang dbang rim dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19310: man ngag dor dang mdor bsdus ni //
NK077(tsu)001:19311: rnal 'byor bslab pa'i mtha' bcur bshad //
NK077(tsu)001:19314: gzhi dam tshig bzung ba sa gzhi gshin mo lta
NK077(tsu)001:19315: bu la bslab pa dang gcig /rgyud thos pas dgrol
NK077(tsu)001:19316: ba kyi ling cang shes sgrogs /
NK077(tsu)001:19317: bkrol ba ltar bslab pa dang gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19318: sgo kun nas bstur ba bong ba tshangs tshol ba ltar bslab pa dang gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:19319: phul mkhas dbyung ba'i ri mthon po'i rtse mor 'dzegs pa ltar bslab pa dang bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:19321: rgyal rigs rgyal sar dbyung ba ltar bslab pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:19322: lnga la spyod pas don ba glang po che chur
NK077(tsu)001:19323: 'jug pa ltar bslab pa dang drug /thag lta bas
NK077(tsu)001:19324: bcad pa khyung nam mkha' lding ba ltar bslab pa
NK077(tsu)001:19325: bdun / nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba
NK077(tsu)001:19326: rgya mtsho'i gling nas nor bu len pa ltar bslab
NK077(tsu)001:19327: bdun / pa dang brgyad / don man ngag gis bsgrub pa gser 'gyur gyi rtsi'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19328: sman ma ki ta ltar bslab pa dang dgu /
NK077(tsu)001:19329: mdo gcig tu bsdu ba po nam mkhan gyi lo thog bsdu ba ltar bsdu ba dang bcu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19331: dgongs 'dus le'u drug cu re drug pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19332: don lnga'i bar gyi le'u bcus bstan to //
NK077(tsu)001:19334: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu tshogs lam du'ang rdzogs par bya dgos pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19339: bslab pa bcu rang rang gi gnas skabs kyi khyad yod te /
NK077(tsu)001:19341: de'i de nyid gcig pa las //
NK077(tsu)001:19344: rim pa de ltar snang ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19347: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu sgra gcig la //
NK077(tsu)001:19348: zag bcas bzhi dang bar chad med //
NK077(tsu)001:19349: zag med lnga'i bslab pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19350: slob pas lugs dang lob pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19351: rtsal dang ngo bo khyad par dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19352: bslab bya yul gyi khyad par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:19355: dang po slob lugs kyi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19356: zag bcas tshig dang yi ge la rten nas slob la bar chad med pa tshig dang yi ge'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19358: ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas slob la /
NK077(tsu)001:19359: zag med chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa la slob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19360: gnyis pa lob pa'i khyad par ni zag bcas kyi
NK077(tsu)001:19361: skabs su chos thams cad kyi rgya mtsho ltar lob
NK077(tsu)001:19362: pa la / bar chad med pas mngon sum du lob ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19363: zag med kyi rang rig mngon sum du lob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19364: gsum pa nus pa'i khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19365: zag bcas kyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag cing gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob la /
NK077(tsu)001:19366: bar chad med pas las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib
NK077(tsu)001:19367: pa'i sgrib pa 'bring po dag ste mthong lam la
NK077(tsu)001:19368: sbyor ro // zag med kyi shes bya'i sgrib pa
NK077(tsu)001:19369: cha phra ba dag nas sangs rgyas la sbyor ro
NK077(tsu)001:19370: sbyor ro // // bzhi pa ngo bo'i khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19372: zag ldog dang bcas pa'i lam pa'i bslab pa yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19373: bar chad med pa zag pa yod la /
NK077(tsu)001:19374: ldog pa med pa'i lam pa'i bslab pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:19375: tshe dbang yan chad zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam pa'i bslab pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19376: lnga pa bslab pa yul gyi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19378: gang zag chos kyi mig can nam //
NK077(tsu)001:19379: lta dgongs kyi drod can la slob la /
NK077(tsu)001:19383: rang rang gi rigs mthun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19384: sangs rgyas sku gsum la slob bo //
NK077(tsu)001:19385: des na tshogs lam gyi mtha' bcu po ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19386: zag bcas kyi lam mthar phyin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:19388: g.yo thob la sogs pa'i mtha' bcu rim pa bzhin yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:19389: 'di ni zag med yin pas 'phags so //
NK077(tsu)001:19390: don la bslab pa'i mtha' bcu 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:19391: lam mthar phyin nas lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi dgongs pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:19393: cig char du rdzogs lugs yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19394: phar phyin pas skad cig ma'i sbyor ba'i thog na /
NK077(tsu)001:19395: lam chos phar phyin bcu la sogs pa rdzogs lugs kyang 'di dang 'dra'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19396: gzhan don gyi mdzad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:19400: sku'i mdzad pa la gnyis bgrang /
NK077(tsu)001:19401: sku'i mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas gang la gang 'dul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19403: de'i tshe shes bya'i sgrib pa cha phra mo tsam yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:19404: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi sar zhugs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19405: gdul bya'i yul zhing khams mtha' thug med pa dag
NK077(tsu)001:19406: tu 'dul bya 'dul ba'i phyir sprul sku mdzad pa'ang
NK077(tsu)001:19408: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i 'gro ba mtha' yas su /
NK077(tsu)001:19409: thugs rje'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas gdul bya'i don dang mthun pa 'ba' zhig ston /
NK077(tsu)001:19410: gdul bya drag po la gnas skabs blo dang mi
NK077(tsu)001:19411: mthun pa drag pos tshar bcad pa logs pa'i sgo
NK077(tsu)001:19412: nas thugs rje'i zhags pa'i 'khor ba'i rgyun lam gcod
NK077(tsu)001:19413: par byed pa'o // mdzad pa bcu gnyis don mdzad tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:19415: dus dang gnas skabs la lar dga' ldan gyi gnas nas 'pho ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19416: yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19419: la lar btsun mo brgyad khri bzhi stong khab tu bzhes pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19420: rgyal srid lo nyi shu rtsa dgur bskyongs pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:19421: la lar mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du rab
NK077(tsu)001:19423: chu bo nee rany+dza na dka' thub lo drug mdzad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19424: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19426: cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19427: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19428: gdul bya la chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor ba ston pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19429: grong khyer rtsa mchog tu mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19430: sku gdung cha brgyad du bgos pa la sogs pa ston pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19431: thugs kyi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas gang la gang 'dul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19433: gnas skabs res 'ga' zhi bas 'dul ba la zhi bar ston la /
NK077(tsu)001:19434: res 'ga' drag pos 'dul ba la drag po khro bo la sogs su snang bas 'dul /
NK077(tsu)001:19435: gdul bya g.yem pa chags can la g.yem par ston cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19436: zhe sdang can la zhe sdang can du ston /
NK077(tsu)001:19437: dreg pa ste nga rgyal can rnams la nga rgyal ri bo lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19438: mun pa ste gti mug can la mun ltar 'thib pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19439: 'phrag dog rlung ltar 'tshub pa de la'ang 'dul thabs
NK077(tsu)001:19440: kyi gnyen po'ang de bzhin du bstan pa gdul bya
NK077(tsu)001:19441: dang / mthun pa'i sgo nas 'dul zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:19442: gdul bya dang mi mthun pa'i sgo nas kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:19443: 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs mdzad do //
NK077(tsu)001:19444: rgya mtsho lta bur thabs zab cing rgya che ba'i spyod pa brlabs po che dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19445: mdzad pa'i phrin las gong du bstan pa de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:19446: du mthun pa dang mi mthun pa sna tshogs kyis
NK077(tsu)001:19447: sgo nas 'gro ba 'khor ba las sgrol bar 'gyur
NK077(tsu)001:19448: ro // gsung gi mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas gang la gang 'dul du mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19450: lha gnas gsum du sngar gsung pa'i gsang sngags rdo
NK077(tsu)001:19451: rje theg pa'i tan tra ste rgyud 'chad pa'i ston
NK077(tsu)001:19453: de bzhin du 'og min du rgyud kyi don bsdus
NK077(tsu)001:19454: pa mdzad pa'i gsang bdag lta bur snang nas don
NK077(tsu)001:19455: mdzad pa dang / 'gro ba dman pa lha mi
NK077(tsu)001:19456: la sogs pa'i lus sems dam pa'i go 'phang can
NK077(tsu)001:19457: mdzad pa dang / dang / bsod nams phun sum
NK077(tsu)001:19458: tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i gnas ma la ya la
NK077(tsu)001:19460: 'khor lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa sna tshogs
NK077(tsu)001:19461: pa'i lus can dam pa'i rigs can lnga la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:19462: pa rnams la gsang sngags kyi chos 'khor bskor bar
NK077(tsu)001:19463: mdzad do // bdun pa mngon shes ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19464: kun mkhyen gyi ye shes cing gzigs tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:19466: mngon par shes pa drug dang ldan pa mtshan bzang po sum cu so gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19467: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcu rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:19468: 'og ma phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin man chad las 'dir khyad par dpag ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19469: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po rgyal ba drug pa kun tu bzang po'i cha byad 'dzin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19470: kun mkhyen gyi ye shes mnga' ba rgyal ba drug pa nyid dang mtshungs pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:19471: mngon shes kyi yul khyon dang gdul bya'i grangs tshad
NK077(tsu)001:19472: bzung du med de rgyal ba drug pa nyid dang
NK077(tsu)001:19473: gcig go // de yang ci ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:19474: gsal la rtog pa med par mkhyen pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:19475: dper na me long lta bu'i tshul du rgyal ba
NK077(tsu)001:19476: drug pa mnga' ba ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i rig
NK077(tsu)001:19479: me long nyid dbyibs dang kha dog tu shar ba ltar chos sku nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:19480: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi rig par shar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:19481: brgyad pa 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sbyor tshul la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:19483: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi shes bya'i
NK077(tsu)001:19484: sgrib pa sbyangs nas sangs rgyas la sbyor tshul dang
NK077(tsu)001:19486: rang rgyud la spang bya mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyis
NK077(tsu)001:19487: mtshan ma shes sgrib bag la nyal cha phra ba
NK077(tsu)001:19489: gnyen por gyur pas 'bigs shing 'joms pa rdo rje pha lam lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19490: spang byar gyur pa shes bya bdag tu rtog pa'i sgrib pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19491: mtshan ma cha phra ba bag la nyal gcig yod
NK077(tsu)001:19492: pa de kun rtsa ba nas bcom nas mthar rdo
NK077(tsu)001:19493: rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin nyid kyang chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:19494: kyi dbyings su thim par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:19495: de sgom bya sgom byed las 'das so //
NK077(tsu)001:19498: mthar thug gi 'bras bu gnyis su med pa rdo rje'i dbyings su rang grol bas thim par byed /
NK077(tsu)001:19501: mthar phyin lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa bcom pa 'thad kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:19502: bdag rtog gi mtshan ma bcom pa 'di mi 'thad /
NK077(tsu)001:19504: rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa bas /
NK077(tsu)001:19506: sbyor lam nas rags pa chod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19508: ngar 'dzin phra ba sa brgyad thob nas dag cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19509: dag pa sa gsum la bdag rtog mtshan ma dag par 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19511: bdag rtog /sbyor lam man chad du bcom nas mthong lam skyes pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19512: 'dir lhun grub kyi skabs la mi 'thad snyam na /
NK077(tsu)001:19513: rags pa tshogs sbyor ma chad nas bcom /
NK077(tsu)001:19514: 'bring po phyag rgya chen po la spang thub kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:19515: 'di ni bdag rtog gi sa bon phra ba'i phra ba bcom pa la dgongs /
NK077(tsu)001:19516: 'ga' zhig gis lam gyi chod tshul dag lugs kyi skabs 'dir /
NK077(tsu)001:19517: spang bya dang gnyen po ye shes bshad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19518: mtshan nyid theg pa dang khyad mi snang zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:19520: mtshan nyid theg pa bas bden gnyis kha phral nas lam khyer byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19521: 'dir spang gnyen ro gcig rtogs nas lam du khyer ba gnyis mi 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:19522: 'dir lam cig char du ni rdzogs ma nus /
NK077(tsu)001:19523: blo rim gyis la rjes shes la mtshan ma shar /
NK077(tsu)001:19524: bag chags ngan pa shog dril rnying pa 'dra gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:19525: de ltar rjes shes mtshan ma shar yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19526: mtshan ma'i rtogs pa de nyid spang sangs med par lam du khyer nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:19527: 'og 'bras bu sbyor tshul gyi skabs na /
NK077(tsu)001:19528: mun snang dug rtsi ma ki ta //
NK077(tsu)001:19529: ci bzhin ma spangs de nyid 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:19530: 'khor ba ma spang rang sar dag /rtogs pa thams cad ye shes tshogs //
NK077(tsu)001:19532: bdag med rang rig ye shes kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:19533: dngos por 'dzin pa dang dngos med du 'dzin pa'i bag chag phra zhing phra ba yang bsreg ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19534: rang dang spyi'i chos rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19535: sems kyi 'dzin pa'i phrag dog kun //
NK077(tsu)001:19536: dngos por med par rang byung ye shes su sgom
NK077(tsu)001:19537: lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin man chad la
NK077(tsu)001:19539: des na lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi dgongs pa la
NK077(tsu)001:19540: gnyen po gang gis kyang mi tshugs pas dpa' bar
NK077(tsu)001:19543: 'dus ma byas kyi rdo rje lam mthar phyin pa'i rtse /
NK077(tsu)001:19545: don de yid tshod min pa theg pa 'og ma pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19546: 'di'i sgom man chad kyi zhen pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19547: bdud bzhi sde dang bcas pa rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:19548: tshar bcad cing gtan nas bcom pas dpa' ba zhes
NK077(tsu)001:19549: bya de'i rjes la 'bras bu mi zad pa rgyan
NK077(tsu)001:19550: dal rang bzhin la dgongs pa bsam yas lhun rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:19552: dbang bsgyur nas 'bras bu thob tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19554: lhun gyi grub pa'i mnyam bzhag chen po'i ngang las
NK077(tsu)001:19555: ma g.yos par dang rang rig pa'i ye shes la
NK077(tsu)001:19556: dbang bsgyur zhing 'bras bu don du gnyer ba'i smon
NK077(tsu)001:19557: lam dang shes rab kyi mthu'i 'bras bu'i chos nyi
NK077(tsu)001:19558: shu rtsa lnga gzhan las min te rang las thob
NK077(tsu)001:19559: pa'o // 'bras bu gzhan na med rang las 'byung ba la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:19561: 'bras bu rang gnas mngon du gyur pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19563: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19564: phrin las la sogs rmad du byung bas 'bras bu
NK077(tsu)001:19565: kun tu grags pa ste sems las yod pa zhig
NK077(tsu)001:19567: rang byung ye shes gnas bya gnas byed med pa ni mngon du snang ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19568: de gzhan nas yod 'ong gzhan las ma yin te lam gyi rang gnas mngon du byas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19570: de bas na ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i cho
NK077(tsu)001:19571: 'phrul 'bras bu'i chos rnams gzhan las yod pa 'dir
NK077(tsu)001:19572: thob pa lta bu ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:19573: thabs khyad par can la brten shes rab gsum nyid
NK077(tsu)001:19574: kyi 'bras bu gong gi don rnams de lta bu'i
NK077(tsu)001:19575: ngang du snang / 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar grol bas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19577: sgron me mun pa ma spangs par snang bar 'gyur ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19578: gser 'gyur rtsis lcags ma spangs par gser du 'gyur ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19579: rtsi ma g+hi ta'i dug ma spangs par sman du 'gyur ba ci bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:19580: rtog pa ma spangs par 'bras bu de nyid mngon du 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:19581: des na 'khor ba ma spangs 'khor skyon rang sar grol bas rnam par dag pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:19582: da bzod mya ngan las 'da' ba ma yin pas na ma h+aa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19583: ye gdod ma nas 'bras bu sangs rgyas nyid rang la gnas pa'i don /
NK077(tsu)001:19584: de bas na 'khor ba nas 'das pa sangs rgyas kyi sar 'gro ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19585: sa de la gnas par bya ba'i rtog pa min te /
NK077(tsu)001:19586: 'o na ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:19587: rtog pa thams cad rang bzhin dbyer med sku dang ye shes kyi tshogs su gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19588: 'bras bu sangs rgyas pa'i tshe rig 'dzin gyi tha snyad dang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19590: gzhi la 'khor 'das kyi chos kun rang bzhin 'khrul ngo na 'das pa'i lam la mnyam pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19591: 'khor ba la mi mnyam par snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19592: gzhi bden pa dbyer med la /
NK077(tsu)001:19593: 'khor 'das rgyu 'bras kun mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa med par ngo bo dbyer med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19595: lam yang nyams su blang bar bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19596: don chos nyid la rtsol ba dang bral bas mi bya ba ltar snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19597: gzhan du nyams su blangs bar bya ba med pa de ka nyams su blang bar byas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19598: gzhi lam gnyis de ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:19600: gdul bya'i ngo la 'grub par snang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19601: gshis rig pa nyid yin pa las gzhan du ma grub par snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19602: ye gdod ma nas rig pa nyid 'bras bu yin par mngon du gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19603: 'bras bu'i che ba'i yon tan thams cad grub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19604: gzhi lam 'bras gsum du tshul gcig pa de'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:19605: na mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi tha snyad
NK077(tsu)001:19606: tsam yang bral te mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:19608: mnyam dang mi mnyam mnyam dang mnyam //
NK077(tsu)001:19611: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19612: ma bzhag tsa na mi mnyam pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19614: de kun dang mi mnyam ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19615: mnyam pa la ma bzhag pa'i dus su yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19616: dgongs pa mnyam nyid yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19617: mnyam pa la 'jog pa'i rtsol bas dgongs pa bzung mi dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19618: bya dang mi bya thams cad byas //
NK077(tsu)001:19619: rig 'dzin mnyam par bzhag par bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19622: mnyam par 'jog pa'i bya ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:19623: mnyam par bzhag 'jog med par dus thams cad du /
NK077(tsu)001:19624: dgongs pa mnyam pa la gnas par bya ba'i dgongs pa rtsol bas bzung mi dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19625: grub dang ma grub thams cad grub /
NK077(tsu)001:19626: rig 'dzin ni mnyam par bzhag tsam na dgongs pa grub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19627: ma bzhag tsa na ma grub pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19628: sangs rgyas ni mnyam par bzhag 'jog med pa dus thams cad du /
NK077(tsu)001:19629: dgongs pa grub pa rtsol bas dgongs pa bzung mi dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:19630: de phyir rig 'dzin tha snyad bral //
NK077(tsu)001:19631: rgyu mtshan gsum po de'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:19632: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'i tshe rig 'dzin gyi tha snyad dang bral bar bstan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19633: skabs 'dir rig 'dzin gsum kyi khyad par la don bcu gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:19634: sku lnga mthong tshul gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19638: ston 'khor du ma gyur pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19639: rgyu la brgyud pa'i nye ring dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19640: dus la nges pa yod med ring thung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19641: ngo bo sku gsum gyis rgyal tshab byed lugs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19642: rnam grangs la sa lam mtho dman dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19643: dgongs pa la mtshan bcas mtshan med dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19644: spyod pa la rang don gzhan don dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19645: mngon shes la rgya che chung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19646: 'bras bu sbyor tshul rim dang cig char gyi khyad par ro /
NK077(tsu)001:19648: tshe dbang gis sprul sku'i zhal mthong /
NK077(tsu)001:19649: phyag rgya chen pos longs sku /
NK077(tsu)001:19650: lhun grub kyis sku lnga dang grub pa'i zhal mthong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19652: sprul pa longs spyod drug pa yi //
NK077(tsu)001:19653: rim par zhag mthong zhen mod kyang //
NK077(tsu)001:19656: tshe dbang la sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19657: sgrib pa gsum po spang dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:19659: lhun grub la bag la nyal gcig pus chog go //
NK077(tsu)001:19661: tshe dbang rtsa ba'i lus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19662: dbang bsgyur rtsa ba rdo rje'i lus //
NK077(tsu)001:19664: skye 'a chi med pa rdo rje'i lus so //
NK077(tsu)001:19666: lha mi'i rgyal po phyag rgya chen po rtsa ba'i lus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19667: ye shes sku'i cha lugs can //
NK077(tsu)001:19669: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK077(tsu)001:19671: ye shes kyi sku rigs lngar yod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19673: bzang po lha mi'i rgyal po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19674: ngan pa rngon pa dang smad 'tshong la sogs par yang sprul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:19676: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa //
NK077(tsu)001:19677: sprul pa'i lus kyi 'dul bar byed //
NK077(tsu)001:19679: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi rtsa ba'i lus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19680: cha byad rgyal ba nyid du ste //
NK077(tsu)001:19681: lnga po lhun gyis grub phyir na //
NK077(tsu)001:19685: sna tshogs par rang snang nas 'dul te /
NK077(tsu)001:19686: dman lus bsod nams ldan gnas su //
NK077(tsu)001:19687: sna tshogs lus can rigs la bskor //
NK077(tsu)001:19690: tshe dbang gi ston pa phyag rgya /
NK077(tsu)001:19691: de'i ston pa lhun grub yin gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:19692: bzlog pa ni ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19695: gcig gi ston pa gcig gyur pas //
NK077(tsu)001:19696: rig pa bzhin du slar gyur pas //
NK077(tsu)001:19697: khyad par che ba de ltar nges //
NK077(tsu)001:19701: rgyu la brgyud pa'i rgyu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19703: de la tshe dbang thob pa'i rgyu dngos ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19704: tshogs bsgrub tha ma pa blo che ba yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:19705: spros pa man chad brgyud pa'i rgyu //
NK077(tsu)001:19706: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos kyi rgyu //
NK077(tsu)001:19707: rnam smin dang lam mchog rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19708: brgyud rgyu tshogs bsgrub man chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:19709: lhun grub dngos kyi phyag rgya chen po /
NK077(tsu)001:19710: brgyud pa'i rgyu tshe dbang man chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:19712: gong gi stong thun gsum gyis skabs bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19714: tshe dbang sangs rgyas pa'i dus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19715: brgya phrag bcu drug tshe yi rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:19719: tshe dbang bas nye ba'i rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i gzhung kun las 'byung la /
NK077(tsu)001:19722: gcig pa de nyid lam byas pas //
NK077(tsu)001:19723: lhag ma bcas pa mthu bsgrub mtha' //de nyid gyur pas nges pa med //
NK077(tsu)001:19725: skad cig gcig gis sangs rgyas pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19726: dus mtha'i skad cig nyid kyis gshegs //
NK077(tsu)001:19727: zhes 'ga' zhig gis dus 'di ltar du 'dod pa snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19729: rang rang skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19733: lhun grub bzhi la nang rim gyi khyad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19737: sa yang mtho dman yod pa shugs la sbyar ro //
NK077(tsu)001:19739: mtshan bcas kyi dgongs pa'i khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19740: spros pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i sangs rgyas stong dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19741: nyi khri sgom pa tshe dbang yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:19742: stong khri la sogs grangs mang lha //
NK077(tsu)001:19747: lha ther 'bum la sogs pa grangs kyis gnas gzhan gyi bgrang du yod tshad sgom mo //
NK077(tsu)001:19749: grangs can 'khor lo mngon du snang /
NK077(tsu)001:19751: lhun grub kyi lha grangs med sgom yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19752: zhal phyag spros pa ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:19753: dbu nyer gcig phyag zhe gnyis sgom nus pa tshe dbang /
NK077(tsu)001:19754: dbu dgu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya sgom nus pa rgya chen /
NK077(tsu)001:19755: phyag grangs med du sgom nus pa lhun grub ste /
NK077(tsu)001:19757: nyi shu rtsa gcig dbu brgya dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19758: grangs med mthar lam rim par ldan //
NK077(tsu)001:19760: mtshan med kyis dgongs pa'i khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19761: chos nyid rang mtshan mngon sum du mthong ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19762: de las mi g.yo ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19764: bcu pa la gnyis bdag don gyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19767: tshe dbang bdag don gyi spyod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19768: rigs mthun mchog rgya sprul pa la chos nyan cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19773: lnga phrag bzhi sogs thabs lam gyi spyod pa yang ston no //
NK077(tsu)001:19774: phyag rgya chen po'i bdag don gyi spyod pa ni
NK077(tsu)001:19775: rigs mthun lhun grub longs sku la chos nyan cing
NK077(tsu)001:19776: / lhan gcig gnas pa spang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19777: gzhan don ni mnyam bzhag las ma g.yos par /
NK077(tsu)001:19778: stong gsum bcu la sogs pa'i rdul snyed tshun chad 'dus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19779: lhun grub bdag don gyi spyod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19780: rigs mthun mchog dang drug pa la nyan cing bag la nyal spong ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19784: mngon shes kyi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19785: drug dang lnga'i yan lag bca' /
NK077(tsu)001:19786: shes pa'ang 'dra mod bzhin la sogs kun /
NK077(tsu)001:19787: de snyed lus kyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19788: don rdzogs mthu dang gdul bya dpag /ces pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19790: de bzhin mngon shes spyod pa'am //
NK077(tsu)001:19792: rnam gsum yul dang zhing khams dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19793: byin rlabs la sogs khyad par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:19796: don bya ba yul gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19798: bdag gzhan gyi don rdzogs ma rdzogs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19800: gdul bya yin min gyi khyad par ro //
NK077(tsu)001:19802: tshe dbang gi gdul bya'i yul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19803: sprul sku'i 'khor sbyor lam la gnas pa man chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:19805: longs sku'i 'khor phal pa dang mthong lam la gnas pa man chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:19808: sgom lam la gnas pa man chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:19809: zhing khams kyi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19811: stong gsum brgyad cu'i 'jig rten rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:19812: g.yo dang rab g.yo shin tu g.yo //
NK077(tsu)001:19814: phyag rgya chen po'i zhing ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19815: stong gi 'jig rten brgya stong phrag /bcu yi rdul snyed zhing rnams dang //
NK077(tsu)001:19816: zhing grangs med pa brgya stong phrag /bcu yi rdul snyed zhing rnams su //
NK077(tsu)001:19819: yul dang tshad med rgyal ba nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:19821: 'dul phyir sprul sku'i mdzad pa'ang ston /
NK077(tsu)001:19828: lam la mtshan nyid gsum yod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:19829: mthar phyin pa'i lam 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid rnams mngon
NK077(tsu)001:19830: par bstan pa'i gzhung gi tshig gi don rnams gcod
NK077(tsu)001:19831: cing / mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na
NK077(tsu)001:19832: le'u zhes bya ste yas bgrang brgyad pa'i don du
NK077(tsu)001:19833: cing / gada'o // 'dir rim gyis pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK077(tsu)001:19834: dang po thog mar stong pa chen po'i don rtogs dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:19836: don dam kun gyi rgyu yin phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:19837: lhag pa'i don de dang po sgom //
NK077(tsu)001:19839: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin don dam bden pa stong pa goms par byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19840: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin kun rdzob ma 'gags pa shugs las 'byung ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19841: kun snang ye shes sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor 'gyu ba
NK077(tsu)001:19842: rang grol du sgom pas lha'i sku phyag rgya gcig
NK077(tsu)001:19843: pa rang shugs kyis shar ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19844: lha phyag rgya gcig pa de spyod lam rnam bzhir mi 'phrog nas brtan pa thob na /
NK077(tsu)001:19845: phyag rgya spros pa lha du ma rang shugs kyis 'char ba bab yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19846: 'di bzhi mtshan nyid theg pa dang go bstan na
NK077(tsu)001:19847: sbyor lam drod nas sa drug pa'i bar du mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:19849: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs bsgrub ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19850: snang ba so ma 'di nyid lam du khyer nas gcod pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:19851: sa bdun pa thabs kyis pha rol tu phyin pa dang mthun /
NK077(tsu)001:19853: bden pa dbyer med ci bzhin pa khong du chud pa /
NK077(tsu)001:19854: 'du shes gnyis kyis mi g.yo ba sa brgyad pa'i mngon rtogs yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19855: gsang sngags kyi mthong lam ci bzhin pa 'di yin /
NK077(tsu)001:19856: 'on kyang tshe rnam gnyis kyi khyad par la /
NK077(tsu)001:19857: snang ba shugs la bkag pa'i don gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19858: rnam smin pas lus dor dgos byung /
NK077(tsu)001:19859: tshe dbang gis de nyid spangs pa med par /
NK077(tsu)001:19860: rtogs pa'i lus sangs rgyas kyi sa la khyer nus pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19861: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19862: sgom pa klong du gyur pa sa bcu pa dang skal ba mnyam mo //
NK077(tsu)001:19864: ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ci bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:19865: pa bcu gcig kun tu 'od dang cha mnyam pa'o
NK077(tsu)001:19867: tshogs lam chos rgyun chen po'i rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19868: nyan rang gnyis kyi mthong lam /
NK077(tsu)001:19871: sa dang po rab dga' don dam bden pa rtogs pa 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:19873: sa brgyad pa'i mngon rtogs snang mnyam stong mnyam 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:19874: gsang sngags kyi mthong lam sa bcu pa ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:19875: kyi pha rol du phyin pa nyin mtshan chos sku'i
NK077(tsu)001:19876: 'khor yug 'di / 'jug bya'i yul zad pa rdzogs chen gyi mthong lam /
NK077(tsu)001:19877: sbyor theg chen gyi sa dang lam gyi rim pa
NK077(tsu)001:19878: gcod lugs 'di rnams la mnyam bzhag phung po lnga
NK077(tsu)001:19880: rjes shes tshogs brgyad kyi dri ma dag lugs rnams shes shing khung du chud dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:19881: mnyam rjes go log /mtshan ma rjes shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19883: lam gyi chod tshul rjes shes /
NK077(tsu)001:19884: rjes shes kyi dag lugs 'di rnams shes shing /
NK077(tsu)001:19887: thod pa bor chog gi kha po byed pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19888: brtson lcags zhabs na kha po byed pa dang 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:19889: 'di rnams yin pa'i rgyu mtshan zhib tu ngo sprad rgyu yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:19890: yi ge mang gi dog pa'i phyir ma bkod /
NK077(tsu)001:19891: spyir gang zag gcig gis rgyud thog na /
NK077(tsu)001:19893: de 'dzom ni mi grol mi srid /
NK077(tsu)001:19895: yin tshul kho na bshad pas mi chog /
NK077(tsu)001:19897: dper na rgyal po'i phru gu de sprang mo nu zho can gyi bu la snang dus /
NK077(tsu)001:19899: da bdag gzhan gnyis kyi nges shes skye nas rtogs dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:19900: rtogs pa tsam gyis mi chog /gdan sa la bzhag nas dbang ma thob na /
NK077(tsu)001:19901: rgyal srid la dbang mi bsgyur /
NK077(tsu)001:19903: dpe de bzhin du yin tshul gcig shes dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:19904: yin tshul kho nas mi chog /yin tshul chos spyi mtshan gyi go ba yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19905: nyams la mi phan pas rtogs dgos /
NK077(tsu)001:19906: rtogs pa kho nas mi chog /dbang ma thob na zha bo mig rgyang ring ba dang 'dra /
NK077(tsu)001:19908: dbang thob pa kho nas mi chog /
NK077(tsu)001:19909: 'jig rten pa'i sgom rnams la dbang thob nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19910: bskal pa'i bar du gnas kyang ldog dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19911: nyams kyi sems la dbang thob nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19912: zad par ldog pa nus kyang ldog dgos pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19913: de bas na yin rtogs dbang gsum 'dzom dgos so //
NK077(tsu)001:19914: da ni mthar thug 'bras bu'i don la drug /dang po thob pa'i tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19916: rang las thob pa gnyis te /
NK077(tsu)001:19917: gzhan las thob zhes bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19918: sems nyid 'bras bu'i rgyu byas nas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i rkyen gyis thob par 'dod pa nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:19919: rang las thob pa'i tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19920: sems nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor byas nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19921: de nyid thos bsam sgom gsum rkyen gyis mngon du 'char bar byed pa nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:19922: gnyis pa thob pa'i dus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19924: bskal pa chen po grangs med pa bdun nam gsum gyi thob par 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:19926: rgyu lam du byas pas gol ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:19927: 'o na 'bras bu thob par mi rigs snyam na /
NK077(tsu)001:19928: sems nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bo yin bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:19929: de ltar ma rtogs te sems nyid 'bras bu'i rgyur
NK077(tsu)001:19930: 'dod pa'i ngos nas 'bras bu thob pa ma yin
NK077(tsu)001:19931: no // 'on kyang bdag med tsam gcig rtogs pa'i ngos nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19932: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu thob pa la 'gal ba med do //
NK077(tsu)001:19933: gsang sngags pas 'bras bu thob pa'i dus ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19939: de yang dang po kri ya'i lugs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19940: sems kyi rang bzhin don dam par dbyings ye shes
NK077(tsu)001:19941: gnyis su med pa dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral
NK077(tsu)001:19942: bar 'dod / de lam du byas pas mi tshe bdun la thob pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19943: bdun thog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19944: lta ba bden pa dbyer med ma rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19945: lha ye shes sems dpa' bzang po gcig la dngos grub re bar 'dod la /
NK077(tsu)001:19946: spyod pa blang dor du spyod pas so //
NK077(tsu)001:19947: yo ga bas ni blo che chung gis mi tshe lnga dang gsum la 'bras bu thob pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19948: don dam rnam snang chen po dbyer med lam du byed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19949: ting nge 'dzin gtso che ba kho nas thob pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19950: mi tshe lnga dang gsum thog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19951: don dam rnam snang chen po yin gyi kun rdzob tu 'khor 'das dbyer med ma rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:19952: lha ye shes sems dpa' gzhan du dmigs nas de la dngos grub thob par re'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19954: lta ba dbyer med bdag nyid chen por rtogs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:19955: spyod pa blang dor med pas tshul bzhin du spyod nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19956: tshe 'di nyid du grol ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:19957: de yang blo cig char ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19958: rtogs pa'i ngang la gom pa rnam pa zung dang ldan zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:19959: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:19960: mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig dpal ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19961: sa dang lam gyi grangs rtsol ba med par grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19963: lta spyod ting nge 'dzin dam tshig dang ldan par tshul bzhin du bsgrub na /
NK077(tsu)001:19964: tshe 'di nyid la tshe dbang thob cing /
NK077(tsu)001:19965: de'i ngang la thod rgal dang /
NK077(tsu)001:19966: mthar chags kyi tshul du 'bras bu thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19967: tshe gcig 'bras bu thob ces bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19968: a nu yo ga bas kyang lta ba dbyings ye
NK077(tsu)001:19969: shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde ba chen po
NK077(tsu)001:19971: ma yengs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19972: spyod pa'i rtsol ba med pas blo che chung gi tshe 'di nyid la grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19974: zhen pa'i snang ba 'di nyid kho na ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:19975: ma bcos ma bslad par 'bras bu'i ngo bor 'dod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:19976: de ci lta bar rtogs pa'i dus na grol bar 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:19978: ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pa'i rtsol ba las grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:19980: 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po la //
NK077(tsu)001:19981: sa yi rim pa gang yang med //
NK077(tsu)001:19982: ces pa la sogs pa gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:19984: rab 'bring tha ma gsum yod pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:19986: blo rab kyi 'bras bu la sbyor ba'i dus zur tsam smos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19987: gsum pa 'bras bu thob pa'i dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19988: gsang sngags nang pa'i lugs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19989: rgyal po phru gu'i dmigs phye nas /
NK077(tsu)001:19990: lus kyi mtshan dpe rang la rdzogs pa gsal ba lta bu'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19991: dbul pos gter rnyed pa lta bu'am /
NK077(tsu)001:19992: gyad kyi nor bu lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:19993: de yang bka' bskyed rdzogs gsum dpe mthun yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19994: rtsol che chung lhun gyis grub pa'i khyad par yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:19995: bzhi pa 'bras bu thob pa'i rnam grangs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:19996: spyir theg pa rim pa dgu la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:19997: rang rang gi 'bras bu rnam grangs yod med kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:19998: khyad par du bka' bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis 'bras bu'i rnam grangs spyir mthun pas /
NK077(tsu)001:19999: rgyas par 'bras bu mi zad pa dang rgyu rgyan
NK077(tsu)001:20000: gyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid yin
NK077(tsu)001:20002: bsam gyis mi khyab par yang zung zhig /ces pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20004: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK077(tsu)001:20005: ces pa la sogs pa gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:20006: de yang cung zad gcig bsdu na //
NK077(tsu)001:20014: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20016: rnam par brjid pa'i sku nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:20017: zhes pa la sogs pa gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:20018: lnga pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid bka' bskyed rdzogs gsum
NK077(tsu)001:20019: gyi lugs kyis gcig dang du ma'i snang ba ma
NK077(tsu)001:20020: spangs pas / gcig dang du ma bral ba'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20023: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK077(tsu)001:20024: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:20025: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang /
NK077(tsu)001:20028: theg pa rim pa dgu'i 'bras bu gcig gam tha dad zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:20029: la la dag ni theg pa rim pa dgu'i gzhi 'bras la khyad med /
NK077(tsu)001:20030: thabs kyis khyad par yod pa tsam gcig yin zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:20031: 'o na gzhi ci bzhin pa'i ngos nas zer ram /
NK077(tsu)001:20035: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la blang dor med pa
NK077(tsu)001:20036: yin pas theg pa la yang rim pa'i phyogs su
NK077(tsu)001:20038: 'bras bu gcig gam mi gcig rtsod pa las grol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:20040: bka' bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi lugs kyi gzhi de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:20041: rang chos thams cad bdag nyid chen po dbyer mi phyed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:20043: de bzhin du mtshan nyid pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20046: nyon mongs pa dgra dang 'tsher ma dug bzhin du spang bar 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:20047: nyid blang dor med pa mi 'dod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:20051: 'bras bu mya ngan las 'das pa grub par 'dod /
NK077(tsu)001:20052: de ltar gzhi la khyad byung bas /
NK077(tsu)001:20053: thabs la yang khyad byung ba yin zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:20054: 'bras bu la yang khyad shin tu che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20055: rang rgyal yang de dang rjes su mthun no //
NK077(tsu)001:20056: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20057: don dam pa stong pa kho nar 'dod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:20058: kun rdzob tu 'khor ba nyon mongs pa'i chos rnams sbyangs nas brgyud de /
NK077(tsu)001:20059: de la brten nas 'bras bu sku gsum thob par 'dod cing /
NK077(tsu)001:20060: nyon mongs pa dang byang chub la blang dor med par ma rtogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:20062: de ltar gzhi la mnyam pa nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:20063: blang dor med par ma rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20064: thabs sam lam la yang khyad par 'byung ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:20065: de'i phyir 'bras bu la yang khyad par shin tu che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20068: mtshan nyid gsang sngags kri yog la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20069: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum ka'i khyad yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:20071: gzhi don dam stong pa kho nar 'dod la /
NK077(tsu)001:20073: don dam dbyings ye shes dbyer med du 'dod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20074: stong pa kho nar mi 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:20075: snang stong dbyer med yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20076: stong pa'i ngang las phyogs su ma lhung bas khyad che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20078: lam la brgyud thag nye ring dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20079: rtsol ba che chung gi khyad par byung bas so //
NK077(tsu)001:20080: de'i phyir 'bras bu sku gsum gyi ngo bo yang khyad che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20081: mtshan nyid pa'i sku gsum gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20082: don dam phyogs lhung can yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:20083: kri yog pa'i 'bras bu sku gsum gyis dgongs pa
NK077(tsu)001:20084: ni don dam dbyer med kyi dgongs pa dang ldan
NK077(tsu)001:20085: zhing / stong pa kho na'i phyogs su ma lhung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20086: de'i phyir dgongs pa phyogs su lhung ma lhung gi khyad par yod med /
NK077(tsu)001:20087: kri yog gnyis pa rang rang dang khyad yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:20088: kri ya pa'i don dam pa'i bden pa nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:20089: dbyings gnyis med tsam gcig yin yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20090: blang dor med pa rnam snang chen po ma rtog la /
NK077(tsu)001:20091: yo ga bas don dam gnyis med blang dor med
NK077(tsu)001:20092: pa rnam snang chen po'i ngo bor 'dod pas khyad
NK077(tsu)001:20093: che'o // de bzhin du 'bras bu la yang khyad che ste 'bras bu'i grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20094: dgongs pa phyogs lhung yod med kyi khyad par yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:20095: dang po kri ya'i rigs gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:20096: rigs lnga dngos su rdzogs par mi 'dod do //
NK077(tsu)001:20097: yo ga ni rigs lnga yongs su rdzogs par 'dod pas grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs khyad che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20099: kri ya'i 'bras bu'i dgongs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20100: don dam dbyings ye shes gnyis med kyi dgongs pa dang ldan yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20101: blang dor med pa'i dgongs pa dang mi ldan pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20102: dgongs pa phyogs gcig pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:20104: don dam gnyis med rnam snang chen po blang dor
NK077(tsu)001:20105: med pa'i dgongs pa dang ldan pas dgongs pa phyogs
NK077(tsu)001:20107: de'i phyir dgongs pa la phyogs lhung yod med kyi khyad yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:20108: sngags phyi pa nang pa yin yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20109: gzhi dang 'bras bu la yang khyad shin tu che ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20111: gnas lugs nyid don dam par dbyings ye shes gnyis med yin kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:20112: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba lhun gyis grub par mi 'dod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20113: don dam dbyer med stong pa'i phyogs su lhung zhing
NK077(tsu)001:20114: gnas lugs bden pa dbyer med du khas len ma
NK077(tsu)001:20115: nus pas / bden pa tha dad kyi phyogs su lhung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:20116: kun rdzob 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid blangs dor med par ma rtogs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20117: blang dor gyi phyogs su lhung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20118: 'di nyid las don dam du yang dbyer med kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:20119: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK077(tsu)001:20120: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK077(tsu)001:20123: gzhi dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs don dam nyid la /
NK077(tsu)001:20124: snang ba lhun gyis grub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20125: stong pa'i phyogs su ma lhung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:20126: gnas lugs kun rdzob nyid la /
NK077(tsu)001:20127: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid la blang dor med par 'dod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20128: bzang ngan blang dor gyi phyogs su ma lhung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:20129: bden pa gnyis kyang dbyer med du 'dod pas tha dad kyi phyogs su ma lhung ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20130: des na gzhi phyogs lhung can yin min gyi khyad yod do //
NK077(tsu)001:20133: grub pa'i mtha' la khyad par ba //
NK077(tsu)001:20134: lta ba'i sgrib pas phye ba yin //
NK077(tsu)001:20137: lam gyi grub pa'i grub mtha' 'bras bu la ngos 'dzin te /
NK077(tsu)001:20140: grangs rdzogs ngo bo byin rlabs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20141: snang dang don byed che chung gis //
NK077(tsu)001:20142: dpag pa ngo bo nyid kyis gsal //
NK077(tsu)001:20144: 'bras bu rnam grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20145: ngo bo lhun gyis grub ma grub kyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:20146: 'dus byas yin min gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20147: bye brag tu chos nyid la byin rlabs snang mi
NK077(tsu)001:20148: snang gi sgo nas stong pa'i mthar lhung ma lhung
NK077(tsu)001:20150: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la dgongs pa blang dor
NK077(tsu)001:20151: gyi phyogs su lhung ma lhung gi khyad par dang
NK077(tsu)001:20152: / sprul pa'i skus 'gro don byed tshul gyi khyad par rnams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20154: des spyi don song nas gzhung don bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20155: spyi don gsum pa mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa bstan pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:20157: phyag 'tshal zhing bshad par dam bca' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20159: rang bzhin bcos bslad thams cad dang bral ba sku
NK077(tsu)001:20160: dang ye shes rang la gnas pa nyid ci lta
NK077(tsu)001:20161: ba bzhin du mngon sum du rdzogs par byas pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:20162: dbyer med rdo rje 'dzin pa nyid la mos te
NK077(tsu)001:20164: 'ga' zhig gis 'di nyid mthar thug sangs rgyas la mchod brjod yin par 'dod pa snang ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20165: gong gi mchod brjod rnams la brtags na /
NK077(tsu)001:20166: 'di lhun grub rig 'dzin yin par mngon no //
NK077(tsu)001:20167: dper na srid pa 'khor bar skye ba len lugs la mngal skyes rim gyis smin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20168: bardzusa skyes rdzogs tshul cig char gyi smin pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:20169: lam rim dang cig char gyi gzhi don ci lta ba bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:20170: mngon du byed pa don yod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:20171: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa bshad par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20176: spyir lam la mtshan nyid gsum yod pa'i tha ma
NK077(tsu)001:20177: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid gnas skabs kyi
NK077(tsu)001:20179: de'i grangs kyi tha ma mthar thug 'bras bu sangs rgyas ni 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20181: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu'i khyad par bstan
NK077(tsu)001:20182: pa gsum gyi 'bras bu'i lus rnams bzhag la don
NK077(tsu)001:20183: gsum gyi tshul du snang ba rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:20184: yan lag rgyas bshad kyi sgo nas ci ltar bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20185: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:20190: mdor bstan pa dang rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20192: de ltar lus rnam bzhag la don gsum yod pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:20193: dkyus kyi snga ma 'bras bu'i ngo bo brjod par
NK077(tsu)001:20194: bya ba ni / rten byed pa'i ngos nas sku dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20195: brda' sprad pa'i ngos nas gsung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20196: dgongs pa zab pa'i ngos nas thugs nyid dang dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i ngos nas yon tan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20197: bya ba byed pa'i ngos nas phrin las ngo mtshar
NK077(tsu)001:20198: rmad du 'byung ba'i chos te de ltar lnga po'am
NK077(tsu)001:20199: / de re re la yang lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga nyid kyi ngo bor gnas so //
NK077(tsu)001:20201: ngo bo yongs rdzogs lhun grub dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20202: rnam grangs rnam par phye ste rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20205: sangs rgyas kyi ming grangs kyi sgo nas khyad par
NK077(tsu)001:20206: du dpag ste ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa
NK077(tsu)001:20210: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:20211: 'bras bu rang gnas mngon du gyur pa la ngo mtshar zhing ngam pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20212: yang dag pa'i don shes bya'i gnas lugs ci lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pas rdzogs zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20213: zhen mtha' ma lus pa grol bas sangs /
NK077(tsu)001:20214: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa la sogs pa yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs pas rgyas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20215: rgyal ba ni 'khor ba'i g.yul las rgyal ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20216: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sangs rgyas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20217: yo ga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas te /
NK077(tsu)001:20219: rgyal ba'i rgyal ba ni gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i sangs rgyas so //
NK077(tsu)001:20222: lha'i lha ni zhi ba chen po'i /
NK077(tsu)001:20223: ngang las bdag gzhan gyi dpal du gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:20224: yon tan phyogs med rdzogs pas lha'i lha ste sangs rgyas so //
NK077(tsu)001:20225: 'phags pa ni theg pa thun mong gis 'phags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20227: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las cher 'phags pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20228: theg pa 'og ma'i sangs rgyas pas kyang cher 'phags /
NK077(tsu)001:20229: 'dir dgongs pa phyogs bral mnyam nyid du rdzogs pas dpal kun tu bzang po'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20231: de bzhin nyid rtogs pas na gshegs pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:20232: 'og ma'i de bzhin gshegs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20233: phyogs bcur dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20234: de las lhag pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20235: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba rtogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20236: de bzhin nyid du 'gro 'ong med par gshegs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20237: ma ha'i ma chags pad ma spyan gyi sangs rgyas so //
NK077(tsu)001:20239: sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu med pas bde ba /
NK077(tsu)001:20240: spangs 'gegs sbyangs bsgyur gyi sgo nas zug rngu bral te /
NK077(tsu)001:20241: rang gi 'bras bu bde ba thob cing gshegs pa
NK077(tsu)001:20242: 'og ma yo ga man chad kyi bde bar gshegs
NK077(tsu)001:20243: so // de las kyang lhag pa'i bde bar gshegs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20244: nyon mongs pa shes bya'i sgrib pa la sogs te /
NK077(tsu)001:20245: zhen mtha' ma lus pa las grol nas /
NK077(tsu)001:20246: bde ba chen po'i ngang la gshegs te /
NK077(tsu)001:20247: dgongs pa phyogs bral bde ba chen po'i ngang las
NK077(tsu)001:20248: 'gro 'ong gsal 'grib med par bzhugs pas ma ha'i
NK077(tsu)001:20250: ngo bo lhun grub kyi dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20251: nor bu rin chen la yon tan lhun grub tu yod pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:20252: 'dir ma h+aa'i sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs
NK077(tsu)001:20253: rgyas la yon tan thams cad lhun grub tu yod
NK077(tsu)001:20254: cing bzhugs pa'o // chos drug nor bu'i mtshon pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20255: nor bu rin po che la chos drug gi mtshon nas bshad dgos te /
NK077(tsu)001:20259: rgyun mi chad pa rtogs pa med pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20262: 'dir yang yon tan ma lus rdzogs pas dgos pa
NK077(tsu)001:20263: tshangs bas gdul bya gang la gang 'dul du chos
NK077(tsu)001:20264: ston pas / gdul bya'i re ba skong ba thugs rje dang phrin las la rgyun mi chad pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20265: yon tan zad mi shes pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20266: gzhan don byed pa la rtog pa med pa sangs rgyas kyi sa la dgod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20267: de ltar chos drug nor bu'i dpe mtshon pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20268: 'bras bu'i chos nyi shu rtsa lnga rdzogs pas gcig pa'i mtha' dang bral ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20269: de ltar 'bras bu'i chos nyi shu rtsa lngar shar ba'i dus de nyid na /
NK077(tsu)001:20270: rang byung ye shes las ma g.yos kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:20271: du ma kun dang yang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20272: des ni du ma gnyis ka'i bdag nyid ldan pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20273: rigs phyogs med lhun grub tu bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20275: gcig du bral gyi don de nyid rgyal ba'i rgyal
NK077(tsu)001:20276: ba thams cad kyi ngo bor gnas pas rigs kun
NK077(tsu)001:20277: gyi dngos gzhi ste phyogs gcig tu ma grub pas
NK077(tsu)001:20279: 'bras bu'i chos nyi shu rtsa lngar ldan pas kun ngo bo //
NK077(tsu)001:20280: de nyid gdul bya'i mos pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:20281: de'i rigs lnga gdul bya dang mthun par snang la /
NK077(tsu)001:20282: yang dag nyid du na rigs 'di kho na'i zhes phyogs gcig tu nges pa med /
NK077(tsu)001:20283: 'di la 'khrugs gcig bsdeb nas bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:20288: rgyu mtshan dgongs pa'i sgo nas sangs rgyas kyi rnam grangs /
NK077(tsu)001:20290: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga po nyid
NK077(tsu)001:20291: re re la'ang bye brag tu lnga lnga ste nyi
NK077(tsu)001:20292: shu rtsa lngar ldan zhing snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:20293: rig pa thams cad kyi bdag po yang dag par
NK077(tsu)001:20294: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug pa kun tu bzang po
NK077(tsu)001:20295: / de'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:20296: zag bcas lam gyi mtshan nyid gsum gyis tha ma
NK077(tsu)001:20297: 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid rig 'dzin bzhi po de'i yang
NK077(tsu)001:20298: tha mar / mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin des
NK077(tsu)001:20299: skad cig ma la rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge
NK077(tsu)001:20300: 'dzin gyis bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa bcom pas
NK077(tsu)001:20301: phyogs zhen tha dag dang bral ba'i phyir sangs /
NK077(tsu)001:20302: rang byung gi ye shes kyis 'gro 'ong med par 'khor 'das kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:20303: chos dbyings kun tu khyab pas na rgyas zhes pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:20304: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis 'gro 'ong med
NK077(tsu)001:20305: par shes bya kun la khyab pas na rgyas pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:20307: chos nyid thams cad snang stong gnyis su med pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:20308: rang byung gi ye shes ni ma bcos par lhun
NK077(tsu)001:20309: gyis grub pas de bzhin nyid do //
NK077(tsu)001:20310: ci bzhin pa de'i ngang nyid du 'gro 'ong med
NK077(tsu)001:20311: par sgrib pa'i zhen pa dang bral ba nar son
NK077(tsu)001:20312: pas gshegs pa'am / rtogs pas na de bzhin gshegs pa zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20313: de bzhin du chos nyid la spros pa'i zug rngu bde ba chen po'i ngang nyid du /
NK077(tsu)001:20314: rtsol rtog gi zug rngu kun dang bral te /
NK077(tsu)001:20315: bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir gshegs pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:20316: bde bar gshegs pa 'o zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20318: khams gsum gyi sems can gyi bsdus pa thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:20319: gnyis su med par sems nyid la nar son te
NK077(tsu)001:20320: / 'khor 'das thams cad mi spang bar thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:20321: la rol cing dbang bsgyur ba dbang phyug chen po
NK077(tsu)001:20322: drug pa nyid longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur bzhugs pas
NK077(tsu)001:20323: na dbang phyug chen po zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20324: yab yum gyi gsang ba'i dbang po thabs dang shes
NK077(tsu)001:20325: rab dbyer med rig pa 'du 'bral med pas gsang
NK077(tsu)001:20327: dngos po 'khor 'das gnyis kyi bsdus thams cad la
NK077(tsu)001:20328: bde bar longs spyod pas longs spyod rdzogs pa zhes
NK077(tsu)001:20329: bya'o // de dag ni drug pa kun tu bzang po de'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs so //
NK077(tsu)001:20330: rnam grangs phye ste rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:20343: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa spyi'i gzugs
NK077(tsu)001:20344: can rigs kyi bdag po de nyid kyi yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:20345: gyi cha las / sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga po //
NK077(tsu)001:20346: cha re re nas phye ste nyi shu rtsa lngar
NK077(tsu)001:20347: brjod pa ni gang zhe na 'di sku lnga kho
NK077(tsu)001:20349: rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:20353: 'jig rten las 'das pa rnam par byang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20354: ma 'das pa 'khor ba'i chos kun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20355: dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos can ma lus pa
NK077(tsu)001:20356: kun chos nyid don dam par dbyer med du gcig
NK077(tsu)001:20357: pa'i / rgyal ba chos sku nyid yin pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:20358: 'khor 'das sna tshogs pa'i chos su ma 'gags par kun rdzob tu snang la /
NK077(tsu)001:20359: snang ba'i dus nyid na don dam par rang bzhin med de stong pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:20360: snang stong gnyis med mngon du byas pa de nyid d+harma ni chos ka ya ni sku ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20361: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i chos skur gnas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20362: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang drangs /
NK077(tsu)001:20363: chos thams cad rang rig pa kho na'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:20364: sgrib g.yog med par mngon sum du snang bas na mngon par te /
NK077(tsu)001:20365: de nyid phyogs gang du yang zhen pa med de /
NK077(tsu)001:20366: zhen mtha' kun dang bral bas byang /
NK077(tsu)001:20367: rig pa'i ye shes su kun chub pa'i phyir chub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20368: rig pa de nyid rgyun dang byed pa po med par rang byung zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:20369: sgrib g.yog med par rang gsal ba'i rig pa chen
NK077(tsu)001:20370: po nyid sku bzhi po kun gyi gzhi byed cing
NK077(tsu)001:20371: gdul bya ci ltar 'dul ba ltar rang snang ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:20372: phyir mngon par byang chub pa'i sku de sku bzhi
NK077(tsu)001:20373: po las mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20374: zhes smos pa ste rang sa'i che ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20377: tha ma 'dod pa'i khams kyi gnas kyi mtha' ma dmyal ba nas /
NK077(tsu)001:20378: ya tha yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi bar du /
NK077(tsu)001:20379: dmyal ba la sogs pa'i ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal kun dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20380: 'dod khams mtho ris lha mi'i 'dod yon gyi bde ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20381: gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20382: gzugs med khams kyi snyoms 'jug bzhi dang nyan rang gi 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20383: dgra bcom pa'i zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i bde ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20384: byang sems las phye ba'i dbu sems kyi btang snyoms dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20385: gsang sngags kyi bde chen bzhi dang sogs khung nas
NK077(tsu)001:20386: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la yul yul can
NK077(tsu)001:20387: du zhen pa med par kun la rol pas longs
NK077(tsu)001:20388: spyod rdzogs pa'am / che ba ste longs spyod chen po'i sku'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20391: rlung gi rta bdun pa nyi ma ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20392: sngon gling bzhi la mnga' mdzad pa'i 'khor lo bsgyur
NK077(tsu)001:20393: bas shing rta'i bam 'gros bdun dang mnyam pas rta
NK077(tsu)001:20395: nyi ma kho rang rlung 'gros gcig phyogs bzhi steng 'og gnyis dang drug ste bdun zer /
NK077(tsu)001:20399: zla ba'i dal gang ba la deng sang du'ang ri bong gzugs /
NK077(tsu)001:20401: byang chub sems dpa' ri bong nyid kyi gzugs lha'i
NK077(tsu)001:20402: dbang pos zla ba bris nas yod pa ri bong
NK077(tsu)001:20405: de las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:20406: chu skyog tha dad pa kun tu gzugs brnyan tha dad du mar snang ba ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:20407: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa'i dgongs pa la phan tshun du 'gro 'ong med par /
NK077(tsu)001:20408: gdul bya'i zhing khams kun tu gdul bya ci ltar mos pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:20409: thub pa drug la sogs par snang nas 'dul ba de kun sprul pa'i sku'i mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20413: 'dus byas kyi nam mkha' la skye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20415: 'dus byas mi rtag par snang ba'i chos can de
NK077(tsu)001:20416: dag kun gyi dngos gzhir gyur pa ther zug rgyun
NK077(tsu)001:20417: las grol ba ngo bo nyid kyi rtag pa chen
NK077(tsu)001:20419: snang stong gnyis su med pa rdo rje'i sku ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20420: mchog tu gyur pa de la skye 'jig med pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20421: de ni grangs kyi lnga pa dbyer med rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:20422: sku nyid du le lag la sogs pa'i rgyud kun
NK077(tsu)001:20426: de ltar sku lnga pos so sor 'dul ba'i 'khor lnga bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20427: chos sku'i 'khor ye shes lnga'i gzugs brnyan mchog gi rigs lngar shar bas /
NK077(tsu)001:20428: ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs zhes bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20429: longs sku'i 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho zhes bya ba ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20430: shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes la sgrib par gyur pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20431: sgrib pa'i mtha' ma shes sgrib cha phra ba spang
NK077(tsu)001:20432: ba sa bcu pa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems
NK077(tsu)001:20434: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin rnams so //
NK077(tsu)001:20435: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i 'khor /
NK077(tsu)001:20436: yo ga'i rgyal po rigs lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20437: u pa ya'i rigs bzhi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20439: pha rol phyin pa'i kun tu 'od kyi sangs rgyas
NK077(tsu)001:20440: la sogs pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs pa theg pa 'og
NK077(tsu)001:20442: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs zhes bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20444: rgyal po lnga sogs 'di phyag rgya chen po'i rig
NK077(tsu)001:20445: 'dzin la ngos bzung 'dug /de'i dgongs pa mchan bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:20447: mos pa spyod pa'i sa tshogs sbyor ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20448: rgyu'i mthong lam pa sa dang po rab tu dga' ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:20449: sngags kyi mthong lam tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rig 'dzin rnams te /
NK077(tsu)001:20450: mos pa rgya mtsho'i tshogs zhes bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20452: dbyer med rdo rje'i tshogs zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20453: des gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje'i don mthong zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:20454: dbyer med rtogs pa'i phyir na de'i ming yang dbyer med rdo rje'i tshogs zhes bya ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:20455: dbyer med rdo rje'i tshogs zhes bya bar 'grub pa ste lhun grub rig 'dzin pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:20456: lhun grub rig 'dzin la rdo rje'i tshogs kyi sgra 'jug ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20458: rdo rje 'dzin pa nyid la mos //
NK077(tsu)001:20462: gsung lnga go tshul gyi sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20464: 'khor lnga po de la ston pa sku lnga po de'i dgongs pa gsung lnga bshad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20465: sprul pa'i skus tshig tu brjod pas go ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20466: sku bzhis tshig du ma brjod kyang brjod pa dang
NK077(tsu)001:20467: 'dra ba'i phyir don gyi gsung du nges pas ni
NK077(tsu)001:20468: / tshigs dang yi ge ru brjod pa med par don go zhing brda' mjal bar byed pa'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:20469: chos sku longs sku mngon byang gi sku rdo rje'i sku dang bzhi yis gsung yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:20470: sprul sku'i gsung tshigs dang yi ge yin /
NK077(tsu)001:20471: de la sprul sku'i gsung la yan lag sum brgya drug cu bshad dgos pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:20472: de la yi ge'i gsung rtsa ba drug ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20479: de la dung nge ba'i gsung ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20480: tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20481: lha rnams kyis yid mos pas 'dul ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20483: rol mos sil snyan dang 'dra ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20484: lha ma yin rnams mos shing 'dul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:20486: dbyangs dang glu gar dang 'dra ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20489: ka la ping ka'i sgra dang 'dra ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20490: byol song rnams mos shing 'dul lo /
NK077(tsu)001:20493: yid btags rnams mos shing 'dul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:20495: sgra snyan pa lta bu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20496: dmyal ba rnams mos shing 'dul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:20497: de la drug cur rtsi lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20498: rtsa ba drug la yan lag bcu bcur phye bas drug cu tham pa yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:20505: ci la gzigs snyoms pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20509: khyad par du zhugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20511: de ltar gsung dbyangs kyi yan lag drug cu tham pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20512: yan lag bcu la mun pa'i cho ga las 'di ltar du bshad /
NK077(tsu)001:20513: gdul bya'i sems 'jug pas 'du shes skye bar byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20514: don gyi rnam par so sor rig par byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20515: gdul byas rang gis 'dod pa'i don 'grub par byed pas mnyan par 'os pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20516: so so'i bsam blo dang mthun pas nyi rtse ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20517: gsung gi don dpag par dka' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20518: gang don gyi rjes su mi 'gal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20519: phyir rgol mu stegs dang bdud kyi mi tshugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20520: gdul bya'i rna bar shin tu snyan pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20521: gsung gi don ma 'dres par gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20522: ldab ldib la sogs pa spangs pas shin tu gsal ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20523: de la sum brgya drug cu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20524: de la 'gro ba ris drug gi skad cig re re la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20525: drug cu drug cur phyes pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20526: sum brgya drug cu de ltar go zhing dngos su
NK077(tsu)001:20527: brda mjal ba'i gsung dang lnga pa nyid kyi tshul
NK077(tsu)001:20528: gyi don go ba de yang sku lnga po so
NK077(tsu)001:20529: so rang rang gi 'khor lnga po /
NK077(tsu)001:20531: spyi'i 'khor sdud pa po gsang bdag phyag na rdo
NK077(tsu)001:20532: rje dag gi skye med don gyi snyan dang dgongs
NK077(tsu)001:20534: rig pa byin rlabs kyi snyan dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20536: dbyer med rdo rje'i snyan te /
NK077(tsu)001:20538: ldan pa'i phyir sku lnga ka'i gsung thos pas na /
NK077(tsu)001:20539: sdud pa pos yi ger bkod pa'i tsheg gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud sde kun /
NK077(tsu)001:20540: sku bzhi'i dgongs pa la bshad ces pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20541: sprul sku'i gsung la thos zhes gsungs so //
NK077(tsu)001:20542: yang lugs gcig la gsung dbyangs kyi yan lag gi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20543: lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba drug po la rim par tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20546: ka la ping ka lta bu dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20550: dbyangs ring po bring nge ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20552: thung ba sha ta pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20554: 'bring po'am de gnyis 'dus pa las byung ba /
NK077(tsu)001:20557: de dag re re la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20558: dbyangs kyi yan lag bcu bcu dang ldan te /
NK077(tsu)001:20562: mi mthun pa med pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20565: gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20569: de ltar sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20570: gsung rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK077(tsu)001:20572: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20575: skye med don gnyis rang bzhin gyi bdag gcig pa 'brel ba yod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20576: 'khor gyi sgrib pa dag cing shes rab kyi dbang po dwangs pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20577: dper na rgya mtsho snyogs ma dwangs pa'i chu la
NK077(tsu)001:20578: nyi zla gza' skar gyi gzugs brnyan gsal bar 'char
NK077(tsu)001:20579: ba bzhin du / chos thams cad skyes shing skye ba med par brda' phrod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20580: chos sku skye med don gyi gsung mchog gis /
NK077(tsu)001:20581: sprul sku gsung ltar tshig tu smra brjod med par go bar byed pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20582: de yang chos sku'i dgongs pa skye med de /
NK077(tsu)001:20583: 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho'i blo la snang bar mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20584: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'i gsung rig pa byin gyis rlabs kyi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20586: rang rig pa'i ye shes de stong pa nyid kyi
NK077(tsu)001:20587: ye shes la sogs pa ming lnga dang ldan pas
NK077(tsu)001:20588: / gong gi gsung snga ma de bzhin du rang
NK077(tsu)001:20589: bzhin gyi 'brel ba'i rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung
NK077(tsu)001:20591: brjod bya'i don rang bzhin gsang ba snying po'i rgyud kyi don rnams kun /
NK077(tsu)001:20592: dper na nyi ma'i dal gyi 'od kyi thams cad gsal bar byed pa lta bur /
NK077(tsu)001:20595: longs sku'i gsung dgongs pa brda'i don dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20597: dper na me long lta bur /
NK077(tsu)001:20598: skyon sel bar byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20601: gzugs brnyan snang bar byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20604: ldan pa ma yin pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20605: mi ldan pa ma yin min pa dang chos brgyad
NK077(tsu)001:20606: kyis mtshon pa'i don dbang phyug chen po longs spyod
NK077(tsu)001:20608: 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyis mthong ba tsam
NK077(tsu)001:20609: gyis 'khor rgyu ba'i sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK077(tsu)001:20610: rnams dang / 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi byang chub
NK077(tsu)001:20611: sems dpa' chen po rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyis
NK077(tsu)001:20613: brda'i sgo nas gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i don snang bar byed do //
NK077(tsu)001:20614: sprul sku'i tshig tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20616: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las rnam par grol ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20617: thar pa'i gnas su bgrod pa lam gyi chos dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20618: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa 'khor ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:20619: chos su snang ba'i sgra skad thams cad sprul sku'i
NK077(tsu)001:20620: gsung gis rtsa ba tshangs dbyangs lta bu la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:20621: pa drug la ring thung gi yan lag 'du shes
NK077(tsu)001:20622: bskyed pa la sogs bcu bcu ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20623: sum brgya drug cu'i tshul gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20624: 'jig rten gyi myes po tshangs pa'i ngag ltar snyan
NK077(tsu)001:20625: cing yid du 'ong bas gsung gi gdul bya mos
NK077(tsu)001:20626: pa spyod pa'i sa las 'phro dang skal pa can
NK077(tsu)001:20627: rnams la / tshigs dang sgrar snang ba rang rang gi sha yi rna bas dngos su thos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20628: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung grags stong dbyer med du'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20630: gdul bya rnams rang rang so so'i ci ltar don go ba dang 'dul bar snang ba'i /
NK077(tsu)001:20631: gsung rnams dper na brag gi ngos la snod bcud
NK077(tsu)001:20632: so so'i sgras bskyed pa'i brag cha'i sgra grags kyang
NK077(tsu)001:20633: brag gi smras pa med pa ltar don grags stong
NK077(tsu)001:20634: dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung ston pas gsung pa med
NK077(tsu)001:20636: dbyer med kyi gsung de mthong zhing thos par byed pa'ang dbyer med de nyid kyi mathu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20638: rdo rje'i gsung dang rdo rje'i 'khor gnyis rang bzhin gyi 'brel pa de nyid kyi mthu yin pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20640: gsung lngas brda sprad lugs ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20641: gong gi dngos lnga tshul tshig gis skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:20644: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20646: 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK077(tsu)001:20647: phyi nang snod bcud sogs bye brag dbye ba yan
NK077(tsu)001:20648: lag dang bcas pa'i chos thams cad /
NK077(tsu)001:20649: rang rig pa byang chub sems kyi bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:20650: snang ba ma spangs pa rnam pa kun ldan gyi
NK077(tsu)001:20651: stong pa chen po'i don mngon du byas pa'i ye
NK077(tsu)001:20652: shes de nyid snang ba la dngos por lta ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:20653: zug rngu ma spangs pas ldan bzhin du mi dmigs
NK077(tsu)001:20654: pas bral ba yi don de ka la bde ba
NK077(tsu)001:20655: chen po mchog gi thugs zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20656: de yang dper na nam mkha' ni go skabs 'byed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20657: med la mi zad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20658: stong la thams cad 'byung bas na /
NK077(tsu)001:20659: 'byung chen gtos kyi nam mkha' lta bur thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:20660: ye nas sgrib g.yog med par gsal ba la ngo
NK077(tsu)001:20661: bos stong pa'o // me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20663: chos rnams spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid dbyer med
NK077(tsu)001:20664: pa'i chos kun yul dang yul can du rtog pa
NK077(tsu)001:20665: med par dper me long dwangs pa bzhin du dal
NK077(tsu)001:20666: gsal ba ltar / rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20667: mngon sum bzhi po kun gyi mchog rang rig mngon sum du rtogs pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:20668: de ka la rnam par mi rtog pa mchog gi thugs zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20669: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20671: dper na 'byung ba chen po lnga gang la yang
NK077(tsu)001:20672: bzang ngan dang skyon yon thams cad mnyam pa lta
NK077(tsu)001:20673: bur / 'khor 'das kyis chos thams cad la /
NK077(tsu)001:20674: bzang ngan dang skyon yon gang yang mi byed cing
NK077(tsu)001:20675: blang dor med par mnyam pa nyid du mkhyen zhing
NK077(tsu)001:20676: / dus thams cad du chos thams cad chos nyid
NK077(tsu)001:20677: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las dgongs pa mi g.yo
NK077(tsu)001:20678: / ba'i thugs kyis / mnyam pa chen po mchog gi thugs //
NK077(tsu)001:20680: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20682: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis su mi 'byed pa'i thugs rje chen pos /
NK077(tsu)001:20684: gdul bya ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel ba yod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20685: sangs rgyas de nyid kyi thugs ni chos nyid mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:20686: pa nyid kyi dbyings las gdul bya rnams mi gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:20688: lam pa ltar gdul bya'i don bya ba dang byed
NK077(tsu)001:20689: pa'i rtsol rtog med par phrin las zhi rgyas dbang
NK077(tsu)001:20691: 'gro ba sems can rnams 'khor ba las grol bar
NK077(tsu)001:20692: byed pa'i thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa yin
NK077(tsu)001:20693: pas na / 'gro ba sgrol ba'i thugs zhes bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20694: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK077(tsu)001:20696: yul chos nyid spros bral dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20697: chos can sems kyi 'dzin pa 'khor 'das ci snyed
NK077(tsu)001:20698: pa kun tha dad kyi 'dzin pa dang bral bas
NK077(tsu)001:20699: / chos can rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20700: chos thams cad spyi'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20701: dbyer med gsum dus gcig tu rig pa la gsal ba'i dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20702: nam mkha' la 'ja' tshon snang ba ltar rang spyi'am
NK077(tsu)001:20703: gsal stong dbyer med ma 'dres par gsal ba ni
NK077(tsu)001:20704: / so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes sam /
NK077(tsu)001:20705: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20706: rang spyi'am gsal stong dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje'i thugs mchog go //
NK077(tsu)001:20708: de ltar bstan pa'i thugs ye shes lnga po mdor bstan tsam ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20709: gzhung 'di nyid du bshad pa de dag go zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:20711: spyi'i mdo'i le'u sum cu so gnyis par lta bar bya'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20712: 'o na chos sku'i sku gsung thugs gsum ka skye med yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20714: ngo bo la khyad med kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:20715: mtshon tshul la skye med kyi rten byed pas sku dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20717: ngang du gsal bas thugs su phyes pa yin ni //
NK077(tsu)001:20720: zhing khams yon tan can dang /
