NK077(tsu)001:20722: sku gsung thugs phrin las dang bzhi'i yon tan kyang bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' la gzhan yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20723: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi chos sngar 'das pa ma lus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20724: da ltar ba mi lus kyis ma 'ongs pa lus
NK077(tsu)001:20725: pa med pa thams cad rang rgyud du grub pa
NK077(tsu)001:20726: med par rig pa rang snang ba nyid kyi phyir
NK077(tsu)001:20727: / sems nyid kyi ngo bo yid bzhin gyi nor
NK077(tsu)001:20728: bu rin po che lta bu ci ltar bsam pa
NK077(tsu)001:20729: / ltar snang ba'am / yon tan mang ba ni sprin phung tsam gyi tshogs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20730: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams ma lus pa thams
NK077(tsu)001:20731: cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa
NK077(tsu)001:20732: snang ba'o // gzhal yas khang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20733: drang 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa
NK077(tsu)001:20734: 'bad pa med par lhun gyis grub cing rdzogs pas
NK077(tsu)001:20735: rang snang ba rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20737: nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa gnyis dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20738: bral ba'i rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems nyid rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20739: rten can gyi lhar gnyis su med pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:20740: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun gyi bzhugs pa'i gnas so //
NK077(tsu)001:20741: de yang rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK077(tsu)001:20742: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK077(tsu)001:20747: 'dod yon la sogs gang yang ma spangs par lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:20748: sna tshogs kyi snang ba ma 'gags pa de ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20749: rang bzhin gyi dal chen po'i rgyan yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:20753: lta bas la sogs pa'i sna tshogs pas dal mdzes pa'i rgyan du byas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20756: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes lnga po nyid rang bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:20757: gyi mtha' gsum gyis ma bsgrib par 'od gsal ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:20764: dngul gyi kha dog lta bu dang drug po de
NK077(tsu)001:20765: re re la yang bye ba drug cu drug cu
NK077(tsu)001:20766: ste / sna tshogs pa'i 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro bas khyab cing rang bzhin gsal bar byed pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20771: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dbang bcu /
NK077(tsu)001:20772: phrin las bzhi la sogs pa 'bras bu'i chos kun lhun gyis grub cing rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:20773: gdan lnga'i bye brag tu rang snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20775: yang na seng ge la sogs pa lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20779: zla ba'i gdan lnga'i bye brag tu rang snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20781: zhing khams yon tan can ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20782: blo'i yul du gyur tshad chos sku'i ngo bor gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20784: gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral ba'i chos dbyings /
NK077(tsu)001:20785: chos thams cad 'byung gzhi lam pa'i gzhan yas khang du gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20787: 'dod yon lnga ma spangs lam du khyer bas /
NK077(tsu)001:20790: lha'i dbu rgyan snyan cha la sogs pa rnams su snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20792: gdul bya'i snying rje rgyun mi chad pa de /
NK077(tsu)001:20793: sangs rgyas pa'i dus su 'od zer gyi rnam par shar ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20795: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa nyid gdan khri la snang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20798: phrin las bzhi'i 'gro don mdzad tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20800: gdul bya ma lus pa 'dul ba'i phrin las kyi
NK077(tsu)001:20801: bye brag tha dad pa mang por snang ba yang
NK077(tsu)001:20803: zhi ba'i phrin las kyis gdul bya gdug pa'i sems can zhi bar bya ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20804: khro bo drag po phrin las kyis gdul bya dgra bgegs ma rung pa dgrol ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20805: dbang gi phrin las kyis gdul bya mi mos shing
NK077(tsu)001:20806: mi 'dud pa gang dag dbang du bya ba dang
NK077(tsu)001:20807: / rgyas pa'i phrin las kyis gdul bya tshe dang
NK077(tsu)001:20808: bsod nams longs spyod nyams pa gso ste rgyas par
NK077(tsu)001:20810: de ltar phrin las bzhi yis gdul bya gdul ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:20811: dgos ched kyis phyir zhi rgyas dbang drag rnam pa
NK077(tsu)001:20812: bzhi ye shes rol pa ste spyod pa rnams kyis
NK077(tsu)001:20813: / gdul bya zhi bas 'dul ba la zhi ba
NK077(tsu)001:20814: la sogs pas gang la gang 'tshams pa ltar snang
NK077(tsu)001:20815: nas gdul bya rnams 'dul bar mdzad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20816: rang bzhin gyi lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las so //
NK077(tsu)001:20818: de ltar phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i theg pa tha dad pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20819: bzhi po re re la'ang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lnga'i tshul gyis snang /
NK077(tsu)001:20821: phrin las bzhi po re re la yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20822: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20823: phrin las lnga'i tshul gyis nyer lnga gdul bya'i ngo la snang ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:20825: nyer lnga po der ci ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:20831: zhi ba'i lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20832: de bzhin du rgyas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20835: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las la /
NK077(tsu)001:20837: de'i rigs dang sbyar ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20838: phrin las bzhi po de zhi ba'i phrin las de de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20841: drag po rdo rje'i rigs te /
NK077(tsu)001:20842: rigs bzhi'i cha 'dzin par byed pa yang gtso che
NK077(tsu)001:20843: bar lnga pa las kyi rigs la spyir dril ba
NK077(tsu)001:20844: yin pas phrin las lnga kar lhun gyis grub pa
NK077(tsu)001:20845: yin no // las phyogs gcig gi mi 'dul ba'i 'thad pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20847: rnam pa bzhi'i gdul bya rnams 'dul bar mdzad pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20848: las bzhi phyogs re ba rnams kyi gdul bya 'dul ba'i rigs ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:20849: sangs rgyas kyi phrin las thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:20850: spyi don gnyis pa dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20854: gong gi de ltar sangs rgyas pa de'ang lam sbyangs pa'i mtha' ma rgyal tshab skyes bu pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20856: sangs rgyas nas ma 'dres par rigs lnga'i cha re lhun gyis grub pa des 'dzin par byed kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:20857: gcig shos te rgyal ba drug pa ni sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo bo nyid du bzhugs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20858: des na mtshan nyid sngags phyi pa'i sangs rgyas phyir drang ba'i don tsam yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:20860: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pas dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20863: tshig tu brjod pa'i mtha' las 'das pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20864: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20865: bden pa gsum gyis sgo nas bzhugs tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20866: drang don nges don gyi sgo nas bzhugs tshul lo /
NK077(tsu)001:20868: drang don bden pa gnyis ltar mi 'thad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20869: ngo bo bden pa dbyer med phyogs ris las grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20874: sangs rgyas de'i don phyogs re tsam du brjod par bya ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20875: drang ba'i don du snga ma byang sems dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20876: phyi ma sngags phyi pa'i sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20877: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20879: don dam ltar gcig pa mi 'thad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20881: don dam du rgyud gcig pur bzhugs pa ma yin pa'i phyir ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20882: dbu ma pa bzhin chu la chu thim pa ltar
NK077(tsu)001:20883: sangs rgyas rnams rgyud gcig tu bden pa med de
NK077(tsu)001:20884: / kun rdzob ltar tha dad du mi 'thad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20886: gcig shos kun rdzob tu tha dad rang rgyud par bden pa ma yin pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20887: sems tsam kri yog la so so tha dad du rigs su chad pa med do //
NK077(tsu)001:20888: ngo bo bden pa dbyer med phyogs ris las grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20890: 'o na ci ltar yin na bden pa gnyis dbyer med rtogs pa'i dbang du bsgyur ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20891: bdag gi dang gzhan gyi bya ba gnyis med de /
NK077(tsu)001:20892: so sor dbyer med pa'i phyir dang nar son pa ste mthar phyin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20893: yod med la sogs pa'i mtha' rnams kyi phyogs su ma song bas mtha' kun dang bral /
NK077(tsu)001:20894: gang du yang ma 'gag pas kun ldan par ye
NK077(tsu)001:20895: shes rang snang nyid zhen mtha' kun bral ba rang
NK077(tsu)001:20896: rig pa'i mngon sum byas pa sangs rgyas zhes ming
NK077(tsu)001:20897: brjod pa'i ngo bo 'di 'drar zhes phyogs gcig par
NK077(tsu)001:20898: ni gnas pa 'di yin zhes tshig tu smrar dka'
NK077(tsu)001:20899: zhing / brtag dpyad dang bral lo //
NK077(tsu)001:20900: drang don nges don gyi sgo nas bzhugs tshul gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20902: dgongs rgyud gcig tha dad du 'dod pa drang don du bzhugs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20904: sems tsam pa dang sngags phyi pa'i lugs kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:20905: dus gsum gyis sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:20906: mkhyen pa'i ye shes su ngo bo gcig pa la
NK077(tsu)001:20907: / 'on kyang sbyangs pa'i rtsal tha dad pas rgyud gcig tu 'dres pa'ang min te /
NK077(tsu)001:20908: dpe na shing gi me dpung gcig yin yang shing
NK077(tsu)001:20909: so so'i me tha dad pa ltar brjod pa ni
NK077(tsu)001:20910: / tha dad la mos pa'i gdul bya kun drang
NK077(tsu)001:20911: ba'i don tsam ste ngo bo rang de nyid du'ang
NK077(tsu)001:20913: de kho na nyid nges pa'i mthar thug ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:20914: dbu ma pa chu la chu thim pa ltar dgongs
NK077(tsu)001:20915: pa rgyud gcig par 'dod pa'ang gong gi de dang
NK077(tsu)001:20916: 'dra'o // 'dir gcig dang tha dad las grol te /
NK077(tsu)001:20917: dgongs pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par bzhugs tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:20919: de ltar gcig tha dad du 'dod pa ni drang ba'i don yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:20920: 'o na nges pa'i don ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:20921: 'dir bden pa gnyis su med par gnas pa'i tshul
NK077(tsu)001:20922: gyis gong gis rgyud 'dres ma 'dres phyogs rer 'dod
NK077(tsu)001:20923: pa rnams la skyon brjod pas 'dir drang ba'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:20924: yin la / skyon de dag gam /
NK077(tsu)001:20925: gzung 'dzin gnyis su 'dzin pa ngang gi dag pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:20926: gnyis med kyi rang byung ye shes de nyid de
NK077(tsu)001:20927: bzhin gshegs pa sangs rgyas kun gyi gnas yin par
NK077(tsu)001:20928: gsang ba'i tan tra ste rgyas pa'i rgyud nyid las
NK077(tsu)001:20929: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20930: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyis gnas /
NK077(tsu)001:20933: bder gshegs mi gnas mnyam pa'i ngang du byon /
NK077(tsu)001:20935: gnyis 'dzin gyi rtogs pa'i zug rngu med pas bde /
NK077(tsu)001:20936: de'i don mngon du byas pas gshegs /
NK077(tsu)001:20937: de yang mtha' gnyis gang la mi gnas pas mnyam
NK077(tsu)001:20938: pa chen po'i ngang nyid spyod yul dang bral bas
NK077(tsu)001:20939: byon / zhes rgyud las gsung shing tshig tu brjod pa yang /
NK077(tsu)001:20940: don dam skye med du mnyam pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20941: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:20942: mnyam pa gsum pa bden pa gnyis su med par
NK077(tsu)001:20943: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du byon nas yin pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:20944: phyir na / gsum pa des grub pa'i don bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20946: rgyal ba rnams kyis dgongs rgyud mnyam nyid de //
NK077(tsu)001:20948: ma 'dres te tha dad pa'i tha snyad tsam dang yang bral ba'i tshul du gnas so //
NK077(tsu)001:20951: dang po gzhung gi don la /
NK077(tsu)001:20952: snga ma rgyud gcig par 'dod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20953: gshis don dam gcig po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20954: kun rdzob gcig po ma yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20955: dbu ma pas chu la chu blug pa ltar /
NK077(tsu)001:20956: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas thams cad spros bral gyi ngang du gcig par 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20957: sems tsam dang sngags phyi pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20959: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas mtshan nyid mtshungs kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:20960: dgongs pa'i rgyud ma 'dres par 'dod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:20962: 'dir gshis bden pa gnyis su med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20963: gong gis tha snyad las grol lo //
NK077(tsu)001:20964: gnyis pa 'phros pa'i ngang don la /
NK077(tsu)001:20966: nye bar len pa'i rgyu tshogs gnyis la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:20967: 'bras bu de bas rab gcig log nas thob par mi 'dod te /
NK077(tsu)001:20968: 'dor sems nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor ye nas gnas pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:20969: rkyen tshogs gnyis kyis sgrib byed dag par byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20970: sems nyid rang 'bras bur snang ba la thob ces bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20971: dper na dmus long mig phye ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20972: rang gi mtshan dpe mthong ba lta bu'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20973: yang na dgongs rgyud bzhugs rgyud bzhugs tshul la /
NK077(tsu)001:20977: dbu mas 'dres te gcig par 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20978: sems tsam pas ma 'dres te tha dad par 'dod pa dgag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20979: dang po la dgod dgag bzhag gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:20981: kha cig spyir dus gsum gyi rgyu 'bras kyi sangs
NK077(tsu)001:20982: rgyas sku gsum mam lnga yis bsdus pa thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:20983: dgongs rgyud gcig par 'dod pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:20984: dper na chu la chu thim pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:20985: mar la mar thim pa bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:20987: bdag cag ci ltar sangs rgyas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20988: de ltar kho nar sangs rgyas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:20989: dper na mar dang mar nyid kyis nying khu mtshungs par gyur pa bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:20992: rgyu rkyen tha dad pas bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20993: dgongs pa rtag gi mthar 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20994: theg pa che chung 'bras bu khyad med du 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:20995: rgyu 'bras mtshungs par 'gyur ba'i brtsad pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:20997: rgyu rtog tshogs tha dad pa gnas 'gyur pas /
NK077(tsu)001:20998: sangs rgyas zhe gnyis la sogs pa mi thob par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:20999: dgongs pa gcig las med pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21002: de thob rgyud rnams ci lta ba //
NK077(tsu)001:21003: so so rnal 'byor tha dad pas //
NK077(tsu)001:21004: bsgrub pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK077(tsu)001:21005: rgyud dag lhun grub rgyal ba rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:21008: yang de phyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK077(tsu)001:21009: ye shes rgyud ni ma 'dres te //
NK077(tsu)001:21011: gcig la mthun snang sgrar mi 'jug /gal te snga phyi gcig 'gro na //
NK077(tsu)001:21012: stong pa'i myur thim rigs pas 'gags //
NK077(tsu)001:21013: snang ba spang pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21014: mtha' la reg par the tshom med //
NK077(tsu)001:21017: 'on te thams cad gcig zhe na //
NK077(tsu)001:21020: 'di nyid las don dam gcig pur ma yin phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:21021: chu la chu ltar gcig pa'ang med //
NK077(tsu)001:21023: rkyen tha dad kyi lam zhi khro la sogs pa bsgrub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21024: 'bras bu tha dad mi 'gyur bar 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:21026: 'dod na zhi khro la sogs byung bas gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:21029: dngos por gcig pa 'gal bas stong par gcig dgos la /
NK077(tsu)001:21030: de ltar na rgyal ba'i dgongs pa don dam rkyang par 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21032: bden pa gnyis ka dgongs pas gsal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21034: lhag med dang mur thug dang khyad med du 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21035: snang ba spangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21036: yang dgongs pa gcig po de dus thams cad du gnas na /
NK077(tsu)001:21037: rtag par 'gyur la mi gnas na skye 'gag can du 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21039: nyan rang dang dbu sems dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21040: sngags phyi nang gi sangs rgyas la dgongs pa khyad med du 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:21041: dgongs rgyud gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21043: khyad par yod pas gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:21046: so so'i grub mtha' bzhi char yang //
NK077(tsu)001:21048: so sor bsgrub phyir gcig pa 'gal //
NK077(tsu)001:21049: gal te rgyal ba'ang rang rgyud 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21052: de tshul sa bzhi'i rgyal ba dag /ces sogs bzhi bshad pas gsal lo //
NK077(tsu)001:21053: khyab pa dngos po la gnas so //
NK077(tsu)001:21054: bzhi pa rgyu 'bras mtshungs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21055: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa'ang khyad med du 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:21057: rgyu sems can thams cad kyang gcig par 'gyur te /
NK077(tsu)001:21058: rang bzhin gyi ni gcig go zhes /
NK077(tsu)001:21059: sems can rgyud kyang de ltar 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21062: dgongs rgyud tha dad par 'dod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:21063: 'dod pa dgod pa dang dgag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21065: dus gsum gyi rgyu 'bras sangs rgyas rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:21066: sangs rgyas tsam du mtshungs kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:21067: sbyangs pa'i rtsal tha dad pas dgongs rgyud rang mtshan ma 'dres te /
NK077(tsu)001:21068: dper na shing du ma'i me bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21074: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa ni rtogs dpyod dang bral ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21076: nam mkha' kun khyab rgyal ba dang //
NK077(tsu)001:21077: nyag gcig snang ba'i rgyal ba gnyis //
NK077(tsu)001:21078: gdul bya'i dbang gis khyad par las //
NK077(tsu)001:21079: sku dang gsung thugs gcig las med //
NK077(tsu)001:21083: 'on te de ltar mi gcig na'ang //
NK077(tsu)001:21084: rang rig rang byung mngon byas la //
NK077(tsu)001:21085: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas bla dwags brtags //
NK077(tsu)001:21086: rang byung rang la shar bar zad //
NK077(tsu)001:21087: rang byung rig dang rgyud med par //
NK077(tsu)001:21088: so sor tha dad gang gis rgyu //
NK077(tsu)001:21091: spyan drang byon dang ma byon 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21092: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa //
NK077(tsu)001:21093: dngos po rnams kyis de nyid na //
NK077(tsu)001:21094: de la gnyis pa yod par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21095: de phyir gzhi yi don dang 'gal //
NK077(tsu)001:21096: mi gcig gtan tshigs rgyas pa med //
NK077(tsu)001:21099: rgyal ba kun dang dus gsum chos //
NK077(tsu)001:21100: bdag phyir kun gyi spyi gzugs can //
NK077(tsu)001:21101: cha gnyis yod par gang gis rung //
NK077(tsu)001:21102: yod na bdag nyid chen po rdzun //
NK077(tsu)001:21105: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs rgyud ci lta bu //
NK077(tsu)001:21106: rang gi mtshan nyid ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NK077(tsu)001:21108: rigs pa dang 'gal ba la lnga ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21109: gzhi la bzang ngan yod par thal ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21110: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su mi gcig par 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21111: gdul bya thams cad la mthun par snang bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21112: don res mos byed par 'gyur ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21113: spyan drangs pa la byon mi byon yod par 'gyur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21116: gzhi gnas lugs kyi don la /
NK077(tsu)001:21117: dgongs pa bzhag pa yin nam min /
NK077(tsu)001:21118: yin na dgongs rgyud tha dad du 'gal /
NK077(tsu)001:21119: min na dgongs pa gang yin yin kyang dgongs rgyud tha dad na /
NK077(tsu)001:21121: gzhi mngon du byas pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dgong brgyud tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21124: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes brjod pa //
NK077(tsu)001:21125: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na //
NK077(tsu)001:21126: de la gnyis pa yod par 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21130: 'bras bu ye shes kyi dus su rang byung ci lta bar mkhyen pa mi gcig par thal /
NK077(tsu)001:21133: rang byung ye shes nyag gcig la //
NK077(tsu)001:21134: gdul bya'i mos dang bsam dbang gis //
NK077(tsu)001:21135: khyad par bye brag lnga sogs snang //
NK077(tsu)001:21136: rigs rgyud don la gcig tu gnas //
NK077(tsu)001:21139: 'on te de ltar mi gcig na //
NK077(tsu)001:21140: rang rig rang byung mngon byas la //
NK077(tsu)001:21141: snga phyi'i sangs rgyas bla dag tsam //
NK077(tsu)001:21142: rang byung rang la shar bar zad //
NK077(tsu)001:21143: rang byung rig dang rgyud med par //
NK077(tsu)001:21144: so sor ma 'dres gang gis rung //
NK077(tsu)001:21147: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK077(tsu)001:21148: drang ba tsam ste 'dod pa min //
NK077(tsu)001:21152: sprul pa yang tha dad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21153: sprul sku byang chub sems pa rnams la snang ba de /
NK077(tsu)001:21154: gdul bya thams cad la mthun par snang bar thal te /
NK077(tsu)001:21155: sprul pa gcig la du mar snang ba de tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21157: nyi zer nyi ma shing me bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:21158: ngo bo gcig la ye shes rgyu //
NK077(tsu)001:21159: so so yin na sprul pa yang //
NK077(tsu)001:21160: sems dpa' de tshe khyad med 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21163: rgyal bas sems can gyi don byed pa'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:21164: bgo basha'i tshul gyis res mos su byed par thal te /
NK077(tsu)001:21165: don byed mkhan tha dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21167: mnyam pa nyid du byed par bshad pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21168: skad cig gcig la lhun gyis grub //
NK077(tsu)001:21170: don mdzad res mos su dbyer med 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21174: skal ldan rnams kyi spyan drang ba'i tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:21175: zhi ba'i sangs rgyas lta bu 'ong la /
NK077(tsu)001:21176: khro bo lta bu mi 'ong bar thal te /
NK077(tsu)001:21177: mgron la bos ma bos bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21179: spyan drangs byon dang ma byon 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21182: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa gcig dang tha dad las grol ba /
NK077(tsu)001:21183: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba smra bsam las 'das pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21185: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21189: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK077(tsu)001:21192: so sor med cing der son pa //
NK077(tsu)001:21202: mtsho nyid brlab ltar thams cad kun //
NK077(tsu)001:21203: gdod nas rang byung ye shes gcig /ye shes de
NK077(tsu)001:21204: nyid 'di 'drar dka' //mtha' brjod ma lus der snang
NK077(tsu)001:21205: phyir // du ma nyid du gcig pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21206: du mar rgya chad yod gyur na //
NK077(tsu)001:21207: rang byung kun snang bden mi 'gyur //
NK077(tsu)001:21209: rnam pa gcig tu dgongs rgyud dbyer med 'dod pa rnams //
NK077(tsu)001:21210: rang don chos sku'i dgongs pa'i dbang yin gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21211: gzhan don gdul bya'i do la rgyud ma 'dres pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21212: de ltar ma 'dres par 'dod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21213: rten can gyi don byed par 'dod pa gcig par
NK077(tsu)001:21214: 'dod pa rten med kyi don byed par 'dod pa
NK077(tsu)001:21216: ngo bo nyid kyi don byed par 'dod pa'i lugs su blta'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21217: gsum pa 'bras bu'i khyad par la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:21221: gsang ba'i theg pa thun mong mi gcig pa'i sku lnga lhun grub gyi rgyal ba drug pa de'i /
NK077(tsu)001:21223: gong ltar bde bar gshegs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21226: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21227: dgyes pa chen po zhes bya ba la sogs pa ming gi rnam grangs mtha' yas pa brjod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:21228: 'dir lus mdor bstan na ngo bo tshul dang khyad par gsum yod pa'i grangs kyi snga ma /
NK077(tsu)001:21229: ngo bo dang tshul gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21230: ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par tsam gcig /
NK077(tsu)001:21231: 'dir mdo ru bsdus te brjod pa'i theg pa so
NK077(tsu)001:21232: so'i 'bras bu'i khyad par gyi don khung du chud
NK077(tsu)001:21233: par gyis shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21234: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:21238: ngo bo sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21239: de re re la'ang lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa
NK077(tsu)001:21240: lngar lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa kun
NK077(tsu)001:21241: tu bzang po de ni chos sku /
NK077(tsu)001:21243: sprul sku ste sku gsum mam /
NK077(tsu)001:21246: ye shes bla ma'i sa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21247: sa gsum rdzogs pa'i phyir lhun grub ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21250: yo ga man chad theg pa thun mong pa so
NK077(tsu)001:21251: so'i gzhung lugs kyi mthar thug /grub mtha' 'bras bu'i
NK077(tsu)001:21252: sangs rgyas du ma yod pa de dag las /
NK077(tsu)001:21257: 'dir ma h+aa yo ga'i 'bras bu sku gsung thugs
NK077(tsu)001:21258: yon tan phrin las nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs
NK077(tsu)001:21260: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi lha'i dal du ma'i grangs rdzogs khyad par dpags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21265: 'dir sku lnga dbyer med lhun gyis grub pas dpags so //
NK077(tsu)001:21267: gsum pas rang sa las mi 'gro la //
NK077(tsu)001:21268: 'di'i byin rlabs las yi ge 'khor lo 'gro bar snang bas spag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21269: don byed rgya che chung ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21274: man chad la don byed la /
NK077(tsu)001:21275: 'dis yo ga man chad la don byed pas rgya
NK077(tsu)001:21276: che chung gis dpag pa na 'bras bu rang gi
NK077(tsu)001:21277: ngo bo nyid kyi khyad par yod par gsal lo
NK077(tsu)001:21280: grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par ni yo ga man chad kyi 'bras bu ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21282: mthar thug sku lnga'i 'bras bu ma yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:21284: lta ba'i sgrib pas phye ba yin /
NK077(tsu)001:21286: lta ba bden pa dbyer med ma rtogs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:21287: chos sku gzugs sku dbyer med rdo rje'i sku ma thob /
NK077(tsu)001:21289: lta ba dbyer med ma rtogs pa de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:21290: shes bya'i sgrib pa yin pas spang bya lhag ma dang bcas la rdo rje'i sku ma thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21291: thob bya lha ma dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21292: sku lngas bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK077(tsu)001:21293: rigs pa la blang dor med par lhun gyis grub
NK077(tsu)001:21295: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ma thob /
NK077(tsu)001:21297: lta ba gong ltar ma rtogs pa de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:21298: shes bya'i sgrib pa yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21299: spang bya lhag ma dang bcas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:21300: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ma thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21301: thob bya lhag ma dang bcas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21302: spangs thob lhag ma can du gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21303: de'i phyir sku gsum tsam gcig thob kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:21304: 'bras bu mthar thug pa ma yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21305: shes bya'i gnas lugs 'khor 'das dbyer med mi 'dod de /
NK077(tsu)001:21306: 'bras bu thob pa sku nyid kyang 'khor ba la longs mi spyod do //
NK077(tsu)001:21308: 'og ma'i longs sku de nyid kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21309: 'khor ba'i chos la longs spyod mi mkhyen te /
NK077(tsu)001:21311: 'khor ba bcos bslad med par 'bras bu'i ngo bo
NK077(tsu)001:21312: yin par ston pa'i thabs zab mo'i man ngag la
NK077(tsu)001:21313: ma brten par / dag pa phyogs gcig pa'i lam
NK077(tsu)001:21314: kho na la brten pa'i 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:21315: ma brten par / / de mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu longs sku nyid la'ang /
NK077(tsu)001:21316: 'khor ba'i chos la bcos bslad med par longs spyod pa'i thabs mi 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:21317: de'i phyir spyod byed thabs la yang blang dor yod med kyi khyad par shin tu che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21319: 'og ma'i longs sku nyid kyis dgongs pa /
NK077(tsu)001:21320: spyod bya spyod byed kyi blang dor dang bcas te /
NK077(tsu)001:21321: dgongs pa chos nyid blang dor med cing /
NK077(tsu)001:21322: rang gis ngo bo las ma g.yos pa'i don /
NK077(tsu)001:21323: ci lta ba bzhin mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21324: 'dir ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku de nyid kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21325: 'khor ba'i chos mtha' dag la blang dor med par longs spyod de /
NK077(tsu)001:21327: gzhi 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi don ci lta ba bzhin mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu yin phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:21328: spyod bya'i yul phyogs su lhung ma lhung gi khyad yod de /
NK077(tsu)001:21330: nang pa'i longs spyod rdzogs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21331: 'khor ba'i chos la blang dor dang bcos bslad bde bar spyod do mkhyen te /
NK077(tsu)001:21332: gnas lugs 'khor 'das dbyer med yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:21333: de nyid ci ltar ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa'i thabs kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:21334: man ngag zab mo la brten pa'i 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:21335: nang pa'i longs sku nyid kyi 'khor ba'i chos mtha' dag la /
NK077(tsu)001:21336: bcos bslad blang dor med par longs spyod mkhyen pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21338: spyod byed kyi thabs la blang dor yod med kyi khyad par shin tu che'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21339: longs spyod pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21340: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dgongs par rang gi ngo bo /
NK077(tsu)001:21341: chos nyid la ma g.yos par bde ba chen por longs spyod pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:21342: ngo bo spyod bya spyod byed dang blang dor las grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21343: de'i phyir spyod pa'i ngo bo la spyod bya spyod byed /
NK077(tsu)001:21344: blang dor yod med kyi khyad par shin tu che'o /
NK077(tsu)001:21345: lnga pa ni sprul pa'i sku la /
NK077(tsu)001:21346: gdul bya zhing gi khyad par dang //
NK077(tsu)001:21347: gdul byed thabs kyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21348: gdul bya'i ngo bo khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21349: don byas pa 'bras bu'i khyad par dang don bzhi'o /
NK077(tsu)001:21351: yo ga man chad kyi 'bras bu sprul sku des /
NK077(tsu)001:21352: nyon mongs pa sbyongs ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21353: bsgyur te dag par 'dod pa'i gdul bya rnams 'dul gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:21354: nyon mongs pa rang ka ma la gnas pa'i gdul bya mi 'dul te /
NK077(tsu)001:21356: nyon mongs pa ci bzhin pa nyid lam du ma byas shing /
NK077(tsu)001:21357: nyon mongs pa dag par byed pa'i thabs kyis lam la brten pa'i 'bras bu yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21358: 'og ma'i sprul skus nyon mongs pa la gnas pa'i gdul bya mi 'dul ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21359: de'i phyir gdul bya'i zhing phyogs lhung can yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21362: nyon mongs pa dag par byed pa'i gdul bya rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:21364: nyon mongs pa rang kha mar gnas pa'i gdul bya
NK077(tsu)001:21365: 'dul mi mkhyen te nyon mongs pa ci lta ba
NK077(tsu)001:21366: bcos bslad med par nyams su len pa thabs kyis
NK077(tsu)001:21367: lam zab mo la brten par /
NK077(tsu)001:21368: nyon mongs pa dag par byed pa'i thabs kyi lam la brten pa'i 'bras bu yin pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21369: 'og ma'i sprul sku la nyon mongs pa rang ka
NK077(tsu)001:21370: ma la spyod pa'i gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs mi
NK077(tsu)001:21371: mnga' ba'o // de'i phyir gdul byed kyi khyad par blang dor dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21374: gdul yul du dmigs nas de la de ston mdzad pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21375: gdul bya gdul byed kyi gzung 'dzin blang dor dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21377: 'og mas gdul bya rnams kyis don byas pa'i tshe de'i yon tan gdul bya las dag pa nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:21378: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu sku gsum tsam la sbyor gyi /
NK077(tsu)001:21379: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga la sbyor mi nus so //
NK077(tsu)001:21381: sprul skus don byed tshul bzhi yod pa'i dang po /
NK077(tsu)001:21382: gdul bya zhing gi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21383: nang pa'i sprul skus nyon mongs pa dag par 'dod pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21384: nyon mongs la rang ka ma la zhen pa'i gdul bya mtha' dag 'dul bar mdzad de /
NK077(tsu)001:21385: nyon mongs pa nyid lam du byas pa'i 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21386: de'i phyir gdul bya'i zhing phyogs med yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21389: nyon mongs pa dag par 'dod pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21390: nyon mongs rang ka ma la zhen pa'i gdul bya gnyis ka /
NK077(tsu)001:21391: 'dul ba'i thabs khyad par can mkhyen te /
NK077(tsu)001:21392: dngos po'i gnas lugs nyon mongs pa dang byang chub
NK077(tsu)001:21393: sems dpa' gnyis su med pa'i don mthar thug ci
NK077(tsu)001:21394: bzhin pa nyid / phyin ci ma log par ston
NK077(tsu)001:21395: pa'i man ngag zab mo'i lam la brten pa'i 'bras
NK077(tsu)001:21396: bu mthar thug yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21397: de'i phyir 'dul ba'i thabs khyad par can mnga' bas blang dor can gyi phyogs las grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21400: gdul bya'i don mdzad pa'i tshe gdul bya tha dag
NK077(tsu)001:21401: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor nyid la ma g.yos pa'i ngang
NK077(tsu)001:21403: gdul bya gdul byed kyi gzung 'dzin dang blang dor gyi phyogs las grol ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21406: gdul bya mtha' dag la don mdzad pa'i yon tan
NK077(tsu)001:21407: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga la sbyor bas
NK077(tsu)001:21408: don mdzad pa'i yon tan mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21409: dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul gyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21411: sangs rgyas de dag gi dgongs rgyud bzhugs tshul kun tu 'od /
NK077(tsu)001:21415: sa bzhi'i rgyal ba dag /dbu ma pa rgyud gcig tu 'dres par 'dod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21416: sems tsam pas de las grol te tha dad par smra ba /
NK077(tsu)001:21417: ma h+aa yo ga'i sa 'di drang ba'i thabs kyis don tsam du bstan pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:21418: ngo bo ni gong du bshad pa bzhin gcig tha dad la grol bar gnas pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:21419: dgongs pa'i rgyud kyi bzhugs tshul gyi khyad par ni blos bsam pa'i tshad las 'das pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21420: ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par la bzhi /
NK077(tsu)001:21422: bder gshegs sam de bzhin gshegs pa'i khyad par la
NK077(tsu)001:21423: gnyis thun mong gi theg par bde bar de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:21425: de la ma h+aa'i bde ba de bzhin du gshegs pas dpag pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21427: grol lam gyi de bzhin dpag tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21428: thabs lam gyi gshegs tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21429: shag thub gshegs pa ltar gshegs tshul lo //
NK077(tsu)001:21432: mtshan nyid lugs kyi gshegs tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21434: 'bras bu'i ming gi rnam grangs kyi khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21435: rgyu'i theg pa chen po yin kyang 'bras bu sngags
NK077(tsu)001:21436: kyi theg pa la ltos na lta spyod dman pa
NK077(tsu)001:21437: / byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dbu ma sems tsam pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21438: rgyu thun mong gi tshogs bsod nams ye shes gnyis bsags pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:21439: grol lam gyi stobs kyis 'bras bu kun tu 'od kyi sa la bde bar gshegs shing /
NK077(tsu)001:21440: don dam skye ba med pa'i chos nyid stong pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:21441: de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gshegs pa de yang
NK077(tsu)001:21442: / dus kyi dbang du bskal pa grangs med gsum
NK077(tsu)001:21443: du tshogs gnyis bsags pa la sbyang dgos pa'i phyir
NK077(tsu)001:21444: / ro // snga ma bzhin du thun mong gi tshogs gnyis la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21445: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21446: sngags phyi pa'i lugs kyis gshegs lugs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21448: gsang ba sngags phyi pa'ang kri ya bya ba'i lugs
NK077(tsu)001:21449: kyis dbyings gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:21450: dang / cho ga'i yan lag kun rdzob tu rnal 'byor gyi lha drug gis bskyed pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21452: 'bras bu lam du byas pas dgongs pa bde bar
NK077(tsu)001:21453: gshegs pa'am 'bras bu kri ya rdo rje 'dzin gyi
NK077(tsu)001:21454: sar gnas lugs de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21455: thabs lam gyi gshegs lugs la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21456: mtshan nyid lugs kyi gshegs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21458: grol lam du gshegs pa las yang na thab lam dbang gi gshegs pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21459: dbang gnas gong du bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21460: spyi'i gnas rgya gar gyi bya rgod phung po'i ri'i 'dab logs kyi sa /
NK077(tsu)001:21461: bye brag tu bsod nams dang skal ba med pa
NK077(tsu)001:21462: phal gyi yul min cing yid tshod du ma gyur
NK077(tsu)001:21463: pa'i gnas dgon phug bye ma 'dab sna zhes bya
NK077(tsu)001:21464: ba ru bskur / gang gis bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21465: dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus nas bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21468: bcom ldan 'das kyis zhal mthong ba'i 'khor te zhes bden pa'i tshig gis bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21470: bram ze la za rgan mo'i bu dge slong sa
NK077(tsu)001:21471: ri zhes bya ba la bskur dgos ched ci'i bskur
NK077(tsu)001:21472: na / rgyal tshab tu byung ba'i phyir bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21473: rdzas gang la brten nas dbang bskur brtsi bzhin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21475: rna rgyud rdo rje zam pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:21476: bya rgod phung po'i 'dabs logs su //
NK077(tsu)001:21477: dgon phug bye ma 'dabs sna ru //
NK077(tsu)001:21478: dngos por lta ba'i rig can de /
NK077(tsu)001:21479: bram ze la za rgan mo'i bu //
NK077(tsu)001:21480: dge slong sa ri zhes bya ba //
NK077(tsu)001:21481: rang gis sdug bsngal zag pa zad //
NK077(tsu)001:21482: rgyal tshab skyes bu'i sa 'dzin zer //
NK077(tsu)001:21483: dge slong lta brgya stong gcig 'dus //
NK077(tsu)001:21484: skyes bu chen por dbang bskur ro //
NK077(tsu)001:21488: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang du yin pa 'dra ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21490: byang chub sems dpa' blo ldan gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:21491: 'dul ba'i sdom pa dam mnos te //
NK077(tsu)001:21492: bden gnyis rtogs pa'i lam bstan te //
NK077(tsu)001:21493: sems can rgyud kyi mtshan rtogs nas //
NK077(tsu)001:21494: zhi gnas 'brel pa'i gnas drug sbyar //
NK077(tsu)001:21495: lhag mthong gsal ba'i skabs gsum bkod //
NK077(tsu)001:21496: zhi gnas brtan pa'i gnas gnyer bas //
NK077(tsu)001:21498: stong pa nam mkha'i de nyid bya //
NK077(tsu)001:21499: zla ba gcig gi brtan gyur nas //
NK077(tsu)001:21500: de nyid stong par brtan par bya //
NK077(tsu)001:21501: de nyid stong pa'i klong chen las //
NK077(tsu)001:21502: char chen dbugs chen 'byin pa yin //
NK077(tsu)001:21503: skal pa du ma gnas pa'ang srid //
NK077(tsu)001:21504: smon lam stobs drag myur du'ang 'grub //
NK077(tsu)001:21505: sku byin ldan pas phyag brkyang nas //
NK077(tsu)001:21506: phyag gi gdugs kyis bkab nas ni //
NK077(tsu)001:21507: zhi gnas brtan pa'i dbyings nas bslang //
NK077(tsu)001:21508: mtshan ma'i thabs kyi brten byas te //
NK077(tsu)001:21509: mtshon pa'i sku yi rgya ldan byas //
NK077(tsu)001:21510: bde gshegs zhing khams kun tu bsgrags //
NK077(tsu)001:21511: rdo rje bum pa na bza' dang //
NK077(tsu)001:21512: rang rtags phyag rgyas dbang skur te //
NK077(tsu)001:21513: rig pa mchog gi dbang rnams bkur //
NK077(tsu)001:21514: 'dod la mos pa'i tshig yin pas //
NK077(tsu)001:21515: nga rgyal mtshan ma'i bde ba thob //
NK077(tsu)001:21516: de yang bcos ma'i dbang gis bde gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21518: kri ya'i lugs kyis gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21522: spyi'i gnas ba ra na se'i bye brag tu /
NK077(tsu)001:21523: rme khrod dang brtseg pa ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21524: mi gtsang ba'i dri ma med pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21525: bsil khang gi nang du bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21527: dam pa ni kri ya yi bstan pa yin la /
NK077(tsu)001:21528: de'i rigs su byung bas rigs can te /
NK077(tsu)001:21530: bram ze khyim bdag ku ku ra dza gsum la bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21532: gtsang ma lag na rdo rjes bskur //
NK077(tsu)001:21533: rjas gang la brten nas bskur na //
NK077(tsu)001:21534: rdo rje rgya gram la sogs pa lha'i mngon rtags brgyad dam dgus bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21535: dgos ched ci'i phyir bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21536: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la dgod pa'i ched du dbang bskur nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21537: 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob pa'i tshul ci bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:21538: rjes su 'jug pa rnams kyang de bzhin du mthun no //
NK077(tsu)001:21539: de yang rna rgyud rdo rje zam pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:21540: ba ra na se'i bsil khang du //
NK077(tsu)001:21541: gtsang ma lag na rdo rje yis //
NK077(tsu)001:21542: lag mthil gtsang ma'i dris byug ste //
NK077(tsu)001:21543: rigs gsum stobs kyi dal gyi //
NK077(tsu)001:21544: dam pa gsum la nges par bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:21545: brten pa'i tshig gis dbang 'di ni //
NK077(tsu)001:21546: 'dod la mos pa'i skam chags can //
NK077(tsu)001:21547: nga rgyal mtshan ma'i dbang thob bo //
NK077(tsu)001:21549: sh+aaka thub ltar gshegs pa la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21551: theg pa gsum pa thob pa rang gi gshegs lugs dang //
NK077(tsu)001:21553: sngon byung du sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang po yang /
NK077(tsu)001:21554: gong gi thun mong lam gyis tshul de dag ci lta ba bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:21557: rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs pa'ang rgyu yi theg pa'i bka' dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21558: bya ba kri ya yis rgyud dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21559: gnyis ka spyod pa u pa ya yis rgyud la
NK077(tsu)001:21560: sogs rang rang so so'i gzhung las ci ltar grags
NK077(tsu)001:21561: pa bzhin du gshegs pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21562: yo ga'i gzhung ltar gshegs lugs so //
NK077(tsu)001:21566: rgyal bu don thams cad grub par grags pa de nyid la bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21568: chu bo nee ra dz+nya na'i 'gram logs su bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21569: dus nam gyi tshe bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21570: lo drug tu chu thig pa re 'bras nyag ma
NK077(tsu)001:21571: re gsol ba dka' thub kyi dka' ba spyod pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:21572: tshe bskur / gang gis bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21573: phyogs bcu'i sprul pa gsang ba'i sku rnams dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21574: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rigs lngas bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21575: dgos ched ci'i bskur na 'og min du longs sku
NK077(tsu)001:21576: rnam snang du sangs rgya bar bya ba'i phyir bskur
NK077(tsu)001:21577: / rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21578: rin chen sna bdun la brten nas bskur tshul ci ltar du bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21583: sku yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21584: mngon par byang chub pa'i yan lag rnam pa lnga mngon du bstan te dbang bskur bas /
NK077(tsu)001:21585: de'i 'bras bu 'og min sdug po bkod pa'i gnas nyid du /
NK077(tsu)001:21586: rgyal bu don grub de nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:21587: sprul pa'ang lus kyi dka' thub mdzad pa'i khog pa nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21588: longs sku ye shes sgyu ma'i sku bcom ldan 'das
NK077(tsu)001:21589: dpal rnam snang gi lus su bde bar gshegs te
NK077(tsu)001:21590: sangs rgyas nas / ri rab kyi rtse mor rin po che'i khang bu brtsegs par /
NK077(tsu)001:21591: yo ga gzhung dum bu bzhi pa'i chos kyi 'khor
NK077(tsu)001:21592: lo sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la
NK077(tsu)001:21595: 'khor gyi rtog pa la snang ba'i gzugs sku yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21597: dbang rdo rje zam pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:21598: rin chen sdug po brtseg pa'i khang //
NK077(tsu)001:21599: ri bo 'bar ba'i rtse mo la //
NK077(tsu)001:21600: dbang phyug lag na rdo rje yis //
NK077(tsu)001:21601: rdo rje dbyings kyi da la du //
NK077(tsu)001:21602: rang bzhin da la mngon du byung //
NK077(tsu)001:21603: dam pa lnga la mngon du bstan //
NK077(tsu)001:21604: lha brag rdo rje'i rdzogs phug tu //
NK077(tsu)001:21605: gtsang ma'i rin chen gral du 'khod //
NK077(tsu)001:21607: ma h+aa'i de bzhin nyid kyi gshegs lugs la gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:21609: thab lam grol lam gnyis med kyi sgo nas gshegs lugs dpag pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21611: ma h+aa rang gi bde bar gshegs pa gang zhe na /
NK077(tsu)001:21612: nang thabs kyi lam dang phyi rab grol ba'i lam gnyis sam /
NK077(tsu)001:21613: yang na snang ba thabs dang shes rab stong pa gnyis med kyi lam gyi sgo nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21614: ngo bo nyid snying po byang chub kyi sar 'gro
NK077(tsu)001:21615: 'ong gi rtogs pa med par snying po byang chub
NK077(tsu)001:21617: gzhi gnas lugs chos nyid ci bzhin pa thun mong
NK077(tsu)001:21618: ma yin pa'i yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang
NK077(tsu)001:21619: du nar son cing mngon du byas pa'i bde bar
NK077(tsu)001:21620: gshegs pa de / 'og ma'i bde bar gshegs pa las /
NK077(tsu)001:21621: dgongs pa rgyud kyi gnas tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21622: 'bras bu rang gi dngos po shin tu khyad par dpag pas na che ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21623: sh+aaka thub gshegs lug ltar gshegs pa'i dpags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21625: de yang dbang gang du bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21626: chu bo nee ra dz+nya na'i 'gram logs su bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21628: rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa dka' thub lus can de nyid la bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21630: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad dbyar gyi nam mkha'i sprin dpung bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:21632: rdzas gang la brten nas bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21633: phal gyi spyod yul ma yin pa gsang ba'i longs spyod /
NK077(tsu)001:21634: kha sbyor gyi bde ba'i rdzas thig le la brten nas bskur ba'am /
NK077(tsu)001:21636: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sprin bzhin 'dus pa gsang ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:21637: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rnams kyis bskur
NK077(tsu)001:21638: / dus rnams kyi tshe bskur na /
NK077(tsu)001:21639: srod la rnam par rtogs pa nus pa dang //
NK077(tsu)001:21640: tho rangs ye shes 'char ba'i dus nyid du //
NK077(tsu)001:21641: longs sku yab yum gnyis su med par rol pa'i
NK077(tsu)001:21642: thig le nyi zla byang sems lce thog tu bzhag
NK077(tsu)001:21643: ste / khar za ba'i dbang rdzas byin te gsang dbang bskur cing /
NK077(tsu)001:21644: yab yum gnyis su med par rol pa'i ka ra
NK077(tsu)001:21645: sbyor thabs kyi bstan te sbyor du bcug pa yis
NK077(tsu)001:21646: / thig le lugs su 'ong ba yas 'bab kyi dga' ba bzhi la shes rab ye shes te /
NK077(tsu)001:21648: thig le lugs su bzlog pa mas brten gyi dga'
NK077(tsu)001:21649: ba bzhi la shin tu bstan pa ste bde ba
NK077(tsu)001:21650: chen po'i dbang rdzogs par thob pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21651: skye ba med pa rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi don mngon byas te /
NK077(tsu)001:21652: rgyal bu don grub nyid theg pa gzhan yo ga'i
NK077(tsu)001:21653: gzhung gi rnam snang du gshegs pa'i tshul de bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:21654: du / 'dir ma h+aa yo ga'i gnas lugs bde
NK077(tsu)001:21655: ba chen po'i de bzhin nyid dbyer med kyi ngang
NK077(tsu)001:21656: du sku lnga lhun grub kun tu bzang por gshegs
NK077(tsu)001:21658: gzhi chos nyid ci lta ba'i de bzhin nyid /
NK077(tsu)001:21659: 'bras bu'i sar de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21660: yang na lugs gcig pa la gang la bskur na //
NK077(tsu)001:21661: rgyal bu don 'grub nyid dka' thub lus can du bzhugs pa la bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21663: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sprin bzhin 'dus pas bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21664: gang bskur na gsang ba'i longs spyod kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21666: 'og nas nyi zla za ba'i dbang sbyin cing /
NK077(tsu)001:21668: ye shes brten rdzogs dbang zhes pas bskur /
NK077(tsu)001:21669: de yang gsang ba byang chub sems kyis longs spyod kyi tshe /
NK077(tsu)001:21671: srod la rtogs pa skye ba'i dus su thob pa /
NK077(tsu)001:21673: 'og na rol pa'i ka ra nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21674: phrin las kyi sbyor thabs drug cu yis /
NK077(tsu)001:21675: nyi ma yum gyi byang sems /
NK077(tsu)001:21676: zla ba yab kyi byang sems gsang ba'i dbang byin cing zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21678: zab mo'i dbang phyi ma gnyis bskur ba ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21683: tho rang ye shes 'char ba'i dus nyid du /
NK077(tsu)001:21685: ye shes brten rdzogs dbang thob nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21687: ye shes rang gnas shin tu brten pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21688: dbang rdzogs par bskur ba thob pas dbang thob pa'i yon tan /
NK077(tsu)001:21690: sh+aaka thub gshegs pa de bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:21691: rjes 'jug rnams kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21692: des na theg pa 'og ma las dpag tshul gtan tshigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21694: ma h+aa yo ga'i gshegs lugs de yis phyir thun mong gi theg pa rgyu mtshan nyid dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21696: yo ga rnam pa gsum las /
NK077(tsu)001:21697: ma h+aa yo ga'i gshegs lugs kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:21701: yo ga sdug po bkod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:21702: ma h+aa yo ga pad+ma spyan mngon du byas tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:21703: rnam par mi rtog pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21704: rigs gsum stobs su byas pa'i sa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21707: bden pa gnyis su med pa rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21711: sdug po bkod pa man chad kyi lta sgrib byang ba'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21712: dang ni sdud pa'i tshigs yin chub pa bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21713: 'bras bu kun tu 'od sku gsum dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21716: pad+ma spyan gyi sku lnga ye shes lngar chub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21717: bde bar gshegs pa bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21718: kun tu 'od sogs bzhi mngon du byas tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:21719: rgyun mtha' dang kun tu 'od dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21721: stug po bkod pa man chad kyi lta sgrib kyi zug rngu med pas bde bar /
NK077(tsu)001:21722: bdag gzhan gyi phyir gshegs pa bzhi'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21723: de bzhin gshegs pa bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21724: dbu ma'i don dam spros bral dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21725: kri ya'i dag pa mtha' bzhi'i dri ma dang bral ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21726: rnal 'byor yo ga'i mtshan med dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21727: ma h+aa yo ga'i snang stong gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin /
NK077(tsu)001:21728: de rnams kyi don nar son pas na gshegs pa bzhi ste brgyad do //
NK077(tsu)001:21730: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sku gsung thugs
NK077(tsu)001:21731: yon tan phrin las nyer lnga'i grangs ma rdzogs la
NK077(tsu)001:21733: grangs kyi khyad par du 'phags pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21734: theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo snang stong
NK077(tsu)001:21735: dbyer med yin pas ngo bos khyad par du 'phags
NK077(tsu)001:21736: so // 'dis yo ga man chad don byed nus pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21737: don byed pa'i nus pa'i rtsal che chung yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21738: rtsal gyis khyad par du 'phags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21739: de rnams kyi don rgyas par bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:21740: byang chub bzhi'i khyad par ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21741: de la byang chub sems dpa' ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21742: nyon mongs shes sgrib sbyangs te /
NK077(tsu)001:21743: grol bas byang la bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa thob pas chub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21745: nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu bsgyur te bral bas byas la /
NK077(tsu)001:21746: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin gyi sa thob pas chub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21748: nyon mongs pa la sogs sbyangs bsgyur dag pas byang la /
NK077(tsu)001:21749: rigs lnga stug po bkod pa'i sangs rgyas thob pas chub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21750: ma h+aa ni nyon mongs pa dang shes sgrib la sogs pa dbang du bsdus te /
NK077(tsu)001:21751: rang byung ye shes su grol bas byang la /
NK077(tsu)001:21752: sku lnga lhun gyi grub pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21753: ma chags pad+ma spyan sangs rgyas thob pas chub pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21754: bde bar gshegs pa'i khyad par ni bzhi ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21755: byang chub sems dpa' nyon mongs sbyangs te bral nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21757: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sar gshegs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21758: kri ya pas nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu bsgral te bral nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21759: dgongs pa bde bar rdo rje 'dzin gyi dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21760: yo ga bas nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu bsgyur zhing bral nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21761: byin rlabs dgongs pa bde bar gshegs stug po bkod pa'i sar gshegs dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21762: ma h+aas spros pa'i zug rngu thams cad dbang du bsdus te rang grol bas /
NK077(tsu)001:21763: dgongs pa bde chen gsal 'grib med par pad+ma spyan gyi sa la gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21764: de bzhin gshegs pa bzhi ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21765: byang chub sems dpas spros bral stong pa nyid rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21766: de bzhin du gshegs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21767: kri yas dbyings ye shes gnyis med dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21768: kun rdzob lha'i dal du rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21769: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21770: yo gas rang sems mtha' bral rnam snang chen po dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21771: kun rdzob snod bcud lha'i dal du rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21772: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21773: ma h+aa 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar rtogs nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21774: de bzhin nyid du 'gro 'ong med par gshegs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21775: rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das kyi khyad par gtan tshigs dang bcas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21777: des na theg pa so so'i rgyal ba dang bcom
NK077(tsu)001:21778: ldan 'das la yang theg pa thun mong gi dang
NK077(tsu)001:21779: mchog ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs gnyis snga ma bzhin
NK077(tsu)001:21780: du / thun mong gshegs tshul ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21781: theg pa bzhi po so so'i lam thabs lam dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21782: shes rab grol lam gnyis kyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21783: theg pa so so'i rang rang gi rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin bzhi rgyud la bskyed pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21784: rang rang gi bdud bzhi nges par bcom zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:21785: rang rang gi sdug bsngal gyi mya ngan las 'das shing /
NK077(tsu)001:21786: theg pa bzhi'i yod med rtag chad kyi mtha' bzhi las 'das pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21788: de ltar theg pa gang 'og mi mthun pa tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:21789: rang rang gi gzhung gi rang rang gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa de yang /
NK077(tsu)001:21790: theg pa de dag la rtogs pa'i lta ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21791: rjes mthun gyi spyod pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21792: nyams len ting nge 'dzin gyi lam rnams la gong 'og gi rim pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:21793: khyad par yod pa bzhin du /
NK077(tsu)001:21794: mthar thug grub pa'i mtha' 'bras bu sangs rgyas rnams
NK077(tsu)001:21795: la yang rim pa bzhin du khyad par yod pa
NK077(tsu)001:21797: lta ba'i sgrib pa yod med kyis sam /
NK077(tsu)001:21798: mngon zhen che chung gi rim pa khyad par phye ba yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21800: ro mnye gser gyi rgyu 'bras sku //
NK077(tsu)001:21801: sku rung mnyam ste rgyu 'bras che //
NK077(tsu)001:21804: de bzhin theg pa che chung gi //
NK077(tsu)001:21805: rgyu 'bras lta bas phye ba yin //
NK077(tsu)001:21806: de ltar 'og ma kun brtag pas //
NK077(tsu)001:21807: 'bras bu'ang kun brtag mthar phyin zad //
NK077(tsu)001:21808: gong ma gong ma de grol bas //
NK077(tsu)001:21811: 'bras bu khyad par med par 'dod pa ni //
NK077(tsu)001:21812: sngags la shin tu rmongs pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21813: dgyes pa longs spyod kyi khyad par dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21815: de ltar theg pa so so'i bcom ldan 'das la khyad par yod pa de na /
NK077(tsu)001:21816: dgyes pa chen po la'ang khyad par yod par ston pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:21817: dgyes pa chen po'i longs spyod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:21818: mang ste rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21819: bya ba kri ya'i rgyud kyi theg pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21820: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi theg pa la rnal 'byor yo ga phyi nang gnyis so //
NK077(tsu)001:21821: rang rang gi rgyud gzhung so so las ci ltar grags pa bzhin du longs spyod pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21823: don gong gi theg pa'i dgyes pa chen po de dag /
NK077(tsu)001:21824: 'og ma 'og ma'i yid tshod min zhes pa'am /
NK077(tsu)001:21825: don gong gi ma h+aa yo ga'i dgyes pa chen po /
NK077(tsu)001:21826: 'og ma ba'i yid tshod du gyur pa min zhes smos pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21827: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu'i khyad par la gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21829: sa'i khyad par dpag tshul dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21831: snga ma'i gtan tshigs de'i phyir theg pa gong 'og
NK077(tsu)001:21832: gi dgyes pa chen po la'ang rim pa yod pas
NK077(tsu)001:21833: / theg pa so so'i 'bras bu'i sa'i sangs rgyas rnams la'ang yon tan gyi khyad par ram /
NK077(tsu)001:21834: gong 'og gi rim pa yod pa'i phyir na /
NK077(tsu)001:21835: ming gi rnam grangs sam yon tan gyi cha shas re tsam gyi khyad min te /
NK077(tsu)001:21836: rim pa bzhin du ngo bo nyid kyis 'og ma 'og ma las /
NK077(tsu)001:21838: khyad par ma h+aa yo ga 'di kun las 'phags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21839: 'og ma'i 'bras bu drang don yin cing ma h+aa'i sa gsum yon tan gyi cha la btags pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21842: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu bshad pa la dgos pa ci yod ce na /
NK077(tsu)001:21843: theg pa 'og ma so so'i lam gyi rtsol bas shes rgyud ngal ba rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:21844: 'bras bu la blo brod pa bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK077(tsu)001:21845: rgyu'i theg pa la 'bras bu kun du 'od sangs
NK077(tsu)001:21846: rgyas kyi sar bstan kri ya pa la rigs gsum
NK077(tsu)001:21848: yo ga pa la stug po bkod pa'i sa zhes bya bar bstan pa yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21849: ma h+aa yo ga 'di nyid kyis mthar thug 'bras bu'i sa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21852: ye shes bla ma zhes gsum ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21853: bzang ngan dang mtho dman min te yon tan gyi cha las brjod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21854: tshig thog ma gsum ni gnas skabs kyi sa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21857: yi ge 'khor lo'i tshogs chen gyi sa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21860: sa'i khyad par bcu dang gsum //
NK077(tsu)001:21861: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:21865: pad+ma'i spyan du gyur pa na //
NK077(tsu)001:21866: rig pa'i byin rlabs chen por ston //
NK077(tsu)001:21869: a nu'i yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen /
NK077(tsu)001:21870: a ti'i ye shes bla ma'i sa zhes 'chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:21872: ma h+aa rdo rje sems dpa' mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21874: sangs rgyas gsang ba ltar na /
NK077(tsu)001:21875: sa de gsum ka ma h+aa'i sa'i yon tan gyi rnam grangs su 'chad do //
NK077(tsu)001:21877: spyod yul bral bas ma chags phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:21878: chu skyes spyan gyi sa yang thob //
NK077(tsu)001:21879: phung sogs rang bzhin lhar snang bas //
NK077(tsu)001:21880: mngon byang tshogs chen sa yang thob //
NK077(tsu)001:21881: de nyid rang bzhin 'od gsal bas //
NK077(tsu)001:21882: mngon gyur ye shes bla ma'i sa'o /
NK077(tsu)001:21884: mjug bsdus te khyad par gtan tshigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21886: khyad par yod pa de'i phyir theg pa gong 'og
NK077(tsu)001:21887: so so'i 'bras bu'i khyad par skan tsha skas kyi
NK077(tsu)001:21888: gdangs bu lta bur rim pa mtho dman yod pa
NK077(tsu)001:21889: ste / de yang gdul bya 'dren pa'i thabs mkhas pa /
NK077(tsu)001:21890: nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa 'di yis
NK077(tsu)001:21891: mthar thug gi 'bras bu dngos su thob par byed
NK077(tsu)001:21892: la / 'di la dngos su 'jug ma nus pa
NK077(tsu)001:21893: rnams thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa las gzhan
NK077(tsu)001:21894: la / pa yis / thun mong lam stegs kyi theg pa'i thabs la brten nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21895: gang la mos pa'i theg pa de la 'jug bcug cing theg pa 'og ma nas /
NK077(tsu)001:21896: gong ma nyid du 'du shes bsgyur bas mthar thug ma h+aa'i yo ga /
NK077(tsu)001:21898: thun mong gi theg pa rang re'i lam gyi thabs sna tshogs kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:21899: theg pa rang sa'i 'bras bu'i sangs rgyas kyi sa thob pa yin pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:21900: thun mong gi theg pa'i 'bras bu dang mchog gi theg pa'i 'bras bu gong 'og gnyis /
NK077(tsu)001:21901: ngo bo nyid gcig cing khyad par med par smra ba'i gang zag rnams ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21902: gsang sngags kyi gzhung don ma mthong bar rang blo'i mun sprul du smras pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21903: theg pa gong 'og gi 'bras bu la khyad yod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21904: gsang sngags bla med kyi rgyud gzhung thams cad nas ston la /
NK077(tsu)001:21905: khyad par du sgyu 'phrul la mnga' brnyes pa'i slob
NK077(tsu)001:21906: dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba nyid kyi gzhung 'di nyid
NK077(tsu)001:21907: du khyad par gsung pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21909: theg spyi'i 'bras bu'i skabs su khyad par med par
NK077(tsu)001:21910: bshad pa dang glan rang rig mgon po'i gsang sngags
NK077(tsu)001:21911: gzhi lam gyi 'bras bu'i skabs su khyad par yod
NK077(tsu)001:21914: gsang snying 'grel par khyad par ston to //
NK077(tsu)001:21915: theg pa che chung gi 'bras bu la khyad par med par 'dod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21916: theg dgu'i don ma rig cing /
NK077(tsu)001:21917: gsang don khung du ma chud pa'i rtags yin no //
NK077(tsu)001:21920: lam mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs
NK077(tsu)001:21921: pa bstan pa'i gzhung gi don gcod cing mtshams 'dzin
NK077(tsu)001:21922: pas na le'u zhes bya ste /
NK077(tsu)001:21923: yas bgrang dgu pa'i don du gada'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21926: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21928: gang gi phyir brtsam pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21929: 'gro ba lam log pa lnga ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21935: mu stegs chad pa ci yang med pa lta ba /
NK077(tsu)001:21936: rtag pa dngos por lta ba /
NK077(tsu)001:21937: byed pa po rtag par 'dod pa /
NK077(tsu)001:21940: lam stor 'gro ba ris drug gi sems can rnams la rgyud lnga dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21941: de ltar lnga tshan gnyis po de rnams drang don la bkri ba'i phyir gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:21942: gang brtsam pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21946: gnyis su med par ston pa'i nye ba bde ba
NK077(tsu)001:21947: rdzogs pa'i lam mchog rnam par bkod pa 'di sangs
NK077(tsu)001:21948: rgyas gsang ba bdag gis bgyis pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21949: de ltar brtsam pas sgo gsum ngal ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba gang yin pa des /
NK077(tsu)001:21950: 'gro ba sems can kun gyi rgyud yang dag par
NK077(tsu)001:21951: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po rdo rje
NK077(tsu)001:21952: 'chang nyid du grol bar shog cig /ces bsngo ba
NK077(tsu)001:21953: yin no // snod ngan dang ma 'phrad cig par gdams pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:21955: 'di las nang tshigs su bcad na gsum /
NK077(tsu)001:21956: snod ngan gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21957: byang chub gtan gyi chus sangs rgyas bsgrub thabs ni zhor la byed /
NK077(tsu)001:21958: tshe 'di nyid kyi bya bzhag khe dang grags pa don du gnyer ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21959: gsang sngags kyi bcud chen po man ngag dang lta sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:21960: gsang mi thub par snod med rnams la 'dzag cing /
NK077(tsu)001:21961: man ngag zab mo gzhan la gzhog ngam can gyi gang zag /gnyis pa snod ngan gyi dpe ni /
NK077(tsu)001:21962: dper na ra tsa stobs bzang gi btsun mo gtsug rgyal sgeg mo dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21963: bram ze me len sbur skyel lam /
NK077(tsu)001:21966: ne tsho kha na gshog tshags dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21968: ku ma ra'i a ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:21970: dka' thub ral gri greng sgom /
NK077(tsu)001:21971: la sogs pa dam pa chos kyi snod du mi rung ba'i g.yo sgyu can rnams so //
NK077(tsu)001:21972: 'di rnams kyis gtam rgyud rgyas par bshad na /
NK077(tsu)001:21973: rgyal po stobs bzang gi btsun mo gtsug rgyal sgeg mo zhes bya ba la /
NK077(tsu)001:21974: rgyal po stobs bzang gi rin po che'i sor gdub chung ngu gcig brgyab pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21976: mos a na zer zhing ngus so //
NK077(tsu)001:21977: gzhan me tog gtor nas kyang a na zer zhing ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:21978: phyis g.yog po gcig dang phag tu 'dod pa spyod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:21979: theb gcig mo phyis pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:21980: g.yog po'i tshig pa log te /
NK077(tsu)001:21981: dbyug pas brgyab pa la mo mi ngu bar he
NK077(tsu)001:21982: zer zhing 'dug pas khrel zhing ya mtshan skyes so
NK077(tsu)001:21984: bram ze sbur skyel yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:21985: bram ze'i drang srong gcig yod pas /
NK077(tsu)001:21986: ma byin par len pa spang ba yin zer zhing /
NK077(tsu)001:21987: gzhan la me slong tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:21988: chos gos la rdul 'byar ba skyel du 'ong /
NK077(tsu)001:21989: phag tu thob tshad rku ba gcig yod pas 'gar
NK077(tsu)001:21990: ba'i khyim na gser gyi sbrang bu yod pa mthong
NK077(tsu)001:21991: nas / mkhar sil gyi gsham la /
NK077(tsu)001:21992: gar spyin bskus nas 'gar ba'i khyim gyi gser gyi
NK077(tsu)001:21993: sbrang bu la mkhar sil mis mi tshor bar btsugs
NK077(tsu)001:21994: te / skar skur med par gser rkus so //
NK077(tsu)001:21996: ne tso kha na gshogs tshags yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:21997: ne tso gcig kha na gshog pa'i sgro bcug nas /
NK077(tsu)001:22000: chu la srog chags 'dug pa shi ba'i dog pa yin zer /
NK077(tsu)001:22001: mi mi 'dug pa dang chu nang gi srog chags btung zhing za ba mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:22002: ku ma ri'i a ma ni /
NK077(tsu)001:22003: mo khyo la ma dga' nas /
NK077(tsu)001:22004: bu gcig skyes nas yod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:22005: nga skyes pa pho dang reg pa spang ba yin zer te /
NK077(tsu)001:22006: bu la nu ma blud tsam na /
NK077(tsu)001:22007: gos la bug pa bug nas blud /
NK077(tsu)001:22008: phag tu skyes pa dang khrig pa spyod pa mthong /
NK077(tsu)001:22009: de yang rgyal bu mu tig 'beb zhes bya ba
NK077(tsu)001:22010: gad mo bgad pas mu tig skyug pa gcig yod
NK077(tsu)001:22011: pa la / rgyal bu stobs bzang gis mu tig 'dod nas /
NK077(tsu)001:22013: rgyal bu gzhan gyi mi mthong /
NK077(tsu)001:22014: rgyal po gzhan mthong ba'i sar bzhag nas /
NK077(tsu)001:22015: ngo mtshar can gyi mthong snang la /
NK077(tsu)001:22016: gad mo yod du re nas bzhag go //
NK077(tsu)001:22017: der rgyal bu gong gi de tsho mthong ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:22018: rgyal pos rgyal bu la rgod bro ba 'dra mthong ngam byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:22021: yi mug pa gcig byung byas pas /
NK077(tsu)001:22024: bus tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
NK077(tsu)001:22025: rgyal mo me tog 'thor bshum dang //
NK077(tsu)001:22026: ku ma ra'i a ma dang /
NK077(tsu)001:22027: ne tso kha na gshogs tshags dang //
NK077(tsu)001:22028: drang srong me len sbur skyel bzhi //
NK077(tsu)001:22029: mi dge bcu la 'jol nyog spyad //
NK077(tsu)001:22030: mu tig 'beb las ma gtogs pa //
NK077(tsu)001:22031: bden par smra ba ngas ma mthong //
NK077(tsu)001:22032: ha ha nga ni rgod re bro //
NK077(tsu)001:22033: zhes bgad pas mu tig lhug ste byung ngo //
NK077(tsu)001:22034: gsum pa snod ngan gyi dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:22035: de lta bu'i gang zag dam tshig dang sdom pa rnams tshul 'chos tsam du bslang bar byed cing /
NK077(tsu)001:22036: yang dag pa'i dam tshig ma mi gnas pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:22037: gsang ba'i theg pa'i lta spyod la sogs pa'i gzhung
NK077(tsu)001:22038: zab mo'i don nyams su len pa la shes rab
NK077(tsu)001:22039: gsum gyis sran mi tshugs shing brtson 'grus chung ba
NK077(tsu)001:22040: dang gzhung dang man ngag sna mang du bsgrub cing
NK077(tsu)001:22042: de dag gang la yang yid ches par dka' ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:22043: bla ma dam pa la dag snang mos gus mi byed zhabs rdul spyi bos mi len cing /
NK077(tsu)001:22046: mched grogs la sogs chos pa yongs la 'phrag dog dbang gis bskur pa btab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:22047: de lta bu'i snod pa mchan gyis ma 'khrol /
NK077(tsu)001:22048: 'ga' zhig bsdus 'grel tsam gcig snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:22049: don rgyas pa mi bdog go //
NK077(tsu)001:22050: 'grel pa gzhan rnams kyang 'ga' zhig 'bru 'grel snang yang /
NK077(tsu)001:22051: lam gyi chod tshul dag lugs /
NK077(tsu)001:22052: chos kyi rnam dbye'i stong thun rnam pa mi snang /
NK077(tsu)001:22056: gzhung don 'di nyid 'chad pa'i dus su /
NK077(tsu)001:22057: bshad pa sbyor ba'i 'grel par mi rung /
NK077(tsu)001:22060: rang gi rnam dpyod kyi shes rab kyis dpyad nas /
NK077(tsu)001:22061: don nye bar blangs pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:22062: rje btsun gong ma'i ngo sprod kyis gsang thig la brten nas yi ger bkod pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:22063: dmar mchan rang dang mi mthun pa'i bshad pa 'ga' zhig yod pa ni /
NK077(tsu)001:22064: mkhas pa gzhan gyi bshad srol la snang ba dang /
NK077(tsu)001:22066: mthun snying de che ba snang bas the tshom ma byed cig /e ma ho /
NK077(tsu)001:22067: rgya gar mkhas mchog sangs rgyas gsang ba yis //
NK077(tsu)001:22068: gsang sngags zab don rgya mtsho bcud bsdus la //
NK077(tsu)001:22069: man ngag rgyal po bstan pa'i yang snying 'di //
NK077(tsu)001:22070: sbyor dngos rjes gsum bstan nas rnam bzhag tshal //
NK077(tsu)001:22071: ya rab mkhas pa'i rnam thar ldan pas mdzes //
NK077(tsu)001:22072: gzhi lam 'bras gsum chos kyi rnam bzhag sogs //
NK077(tsu)001:22073: gzhi la gnas lugs 'khrul lugs snang tshul phyed //
NK077(tsu)001:22074: rnam gsum gnas tshul gsang sngags che yon rdzogs //
NK077(tsu)001:22075: lam lnga mtshan gsum lam gyi khog cing legs //
NK077(tsu)001:22076: gzhal bya gtan tshigs grub pa'i mtha' gsum mo //
NK077(tsu)001:22077: gtan la dbab bya 'beb thabs pheb tshul 'dzoms //
NK077(tsu)001:22078: rim dang cig char thar chag thod rgal sogs //
NK077(tsu)001:22079: dbang po'i rigs dang shes med rnams dang man ngag
NK077(tsu)001:22080: zab mo'i chos 'di ma 'phrad cig /snod ldan dang
NK077(tsu)001:22081: 'phrad par shog cig /ces smon lam btab pa'o //
NK077(tsu)001:22082: spyi don gsum pa 'chad nyan mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan la /
NK077(tsu)001:22084: spyir stod mnga' ris skor gyi mang yul /
NK077(tsu)001:22085: bye brag tu khri bab ces bya ba'i gnas su /
NK077(tsu)001:22086: pan chen sangs rgyas gsang ba tshes bar la byon nas /
NK077(tsu)001:22087: chos lugs dri ma med pa'i gsung /
NK077(tsu)001:22088: lo ts+aa ba dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras bsgyur ba yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:22089: lo ts+aa la bzhi yod pa la /
NK077(tsu)001:22091: u rgyan pad mas bsgrub chen gsang ba yongs rdzogs kyi /
NK077(tsu)001:22094: rje 'bang gi me tog dor ba'i dus na /
NK077(tsu)001:22095: rgyal po dang lo ts+aa 'di nyid che mchog gi bka' bab /
NK077(tsu)001:22096: de nyid kyi sgo nas gzhan snang zil gyis gnon /
NK077(tsu)001:22097: brag la bdud rtsi 'byin nus pa /
NK077(tsu)001:22098: gnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK077(tsu)001:22099: ye shes gzhon nu zhes bya bas bsgyur ba /
NK077(tsu)001:22100: yod pa gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum ka yod kyang /
NK077(tsu)001:22101: tshig don brjod bya'i gtso bo lam rgyas pas lam
NK077(tsu)001:22102: rnal 'byor bkod pa tshogs chung la don che ba'i
NK077(tsu)001:22104: zhes pa tshig don ma lus pa'i tha tshig yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:22105: sems can sangs rgyas kyi sa la bgrod pa'i lam rim chen mo /
NK077(tsu)001:22106: mtshan ma lha lam du khyer ba'i pra khrid /
NK077(tsu)001:22107: gsang sngags thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po'i
NK077(tsu)001:22108: mchog lam phyin ci ma log pa'i gdam ngag rdzogs
NK077(tsu)001:22112: rtogs ldan pa'i bsdus don dang /
NK077(tsu)001:22113: dmar mchan la gzhi blang nas byas pa yin te /
NK077(tsu)001:22114: mchan rang yang bris pa'i dbang gis mchan bu'i 'dogs dgongs par bcug /
NK077(tsu)001:22116: gzhung don gsal ma nus pa dang /
NK077(tsu)001:22117: 'ga' zhig gzhung rang yang bshad bya'i gcod tshul 'tshams //
NK077(tsu)001:22118: thabs lam grol lam mtshan bcas mtshan med sogs //
NK077(tsu)001:22119: gdul bya'i blo rim lam khyer chos lugs legs //
NK077(tsu)001:22120: gnas skabs rig 'dzin mthar thug sangs rgyas rnams /
NK077(tsu)001:22121: gsang sngags 'bras bu che yon lhun gyis grub //
NK077(tsu)001:22122: de lta'i gzhung lugs dri med lam 'di la //
NK077(tsu)001:22123: bdag 'dra ban sdom dz+ny+aa na'i ming can gyis //
NK077(tsu)001:22124: 'grel tig brtsom pa'i tshad dang mi ldan yang //
NK077(tsu)001:22125: bdag rjes 'brang ba rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK077(tsu)001:22126: legs bshad gsang don rtogs sla 'di byas so //
NK077(tsu)001:22127: ngag la nges 'dzin rnams la phan thog shog /
NK077(tsu)001:22128: 'on kyang gzhung 'di smra ba mang ste mkhas pa dkon //
NK077(tsu)001:22129: rnam dbye du ma'i bshad lugs byed na yang //
NK077(tsu)001:22130: da rung gzhung don rang yang the tshom gzhir //
NK077(tsu)001:22131: sgo them ma bardzisa phug gis rgyus bshad bzhin //
NK077(tsu)001:22132: de 'dra'i bshad srol 'di yang rab spang nas //
NK077(tsu)001:22133: dri med rnam dag gzhung lugs rtogs par shog /yang smras pa /
NK077(tsu)001:22134: sangs rgyas bstan pa rab dkar phu lung nas //
NK077(tsu)001:22135: gsang sngags rmad byung theg chen chu rlung las //
NK077(tsu)001:22136: thos bsam sgom gsum rba rlabs chil chil langs //
NK077(tsu)001:22137: nyams myong rtogs pa'i gsung snyan lhung lhung sgrogs //
NK077(tsu)001:22138: de lta'i don la mi sems su zhig yod //
NK077(tsu)001:22140: kha che'i yul na gur gum rtsa //
NK077(tsu)001:22141: ma la yang na tsan+da nags //
NK077(tsu)001:22142: rgya mtsho'i 'gram na rin chen rdo //
NK077(tsu)001:22143: nye skyo rgyang na rin thang che //
NK077(tsu)001:22144: de phyir chos dang chos min gyi //
NK077(tsu)001:22145: de don go ba shin tu gces //
NK077(tsu)001:22147: sgyu 'phrul lam rim gyi 'grel pa dri med mu tig phreng ba zhes bya ba 'di /
NK077(tsu)001:22148: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyi yang yang bskul nas
NK077(tsu)001:22149: rje btsun gong ma'i gdan sa dpal ldan kah thog
NK077(tsu)001:22150: ri khrod nor gling zhes bya bar ku su lu
NK077(tsu)001:22151: pa ye shes rgyal mtshan gyis yi ger bkod pa
NK077(tsu)001:22152: 'di / rjes 'jug rnams kyis gsang ba sgyu 'phrul
NK077(tsu)001:22153: lam gyi rim pa'i don khong na chud cing gdul
NK077(tsu)001:22154: bya la phan thogs nas dar zhing rgyas pa'i rgyur
